quran[6235]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,Yettoore nden ko Allah jooma tageefu On woodani
  1,2,Jooma yurmeende huЙ“tidinnde e heeriinde
  1,3,Jooma Гұalngu njoЙ“diiji
  1,4,Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo
  1,5,Feewnu min e laawol pooccingol
  1,6,Laawol ngol Й“een Й“e neemin-Й—aa Й“e ngonaa tikkanaaЙ“e te Й“e majjaani
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hulЙ“e Й“e"
  2,3,ЖҒeen goonЙ—inooЙ“e mbirniindi eЙ“e ГұiiЙ“na juulde eЙ“e nafga e ko Min njeЙ—i Й“e
  2,4,"E Й“een goonЙ—inooЙ“e ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, eЙ“e njananaa Гұalaande wattan"
  2,5,"ЖҒeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni daЙ—ooЙ“e"
  2,6,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e ngoonЙ—intaa foti a jeertinii Й“e wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, wirngallo woni noppi e gite maЙ“Й“e lette mawЙ—e na woodani Й“e"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yimЙ“e wi'ooЙ“e min ngoonЙ—inii Alla e Гұalaande wattan, tawa Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani"
  2,9,"EЙ“e koda Alla e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, alaa mbo Й“e kodata sonaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e tawa Й“e nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko Гұawo woni e Й“erЙ—e Alla Й“eydani Й“e Гұawu maa lette muusЙ—e njan e mum en sabu ko Й“e pennannoo
  2,11,So Й“e mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi Й“e mbi'a minen ko min moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e
  2,12,Ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni bonnooЙ“e kono Й“e tinataa Й—um
  2,13,"So Й“e mbi'aama ngoonЙ—inee wano yimЙ“e Й“ee ngoonЙ—iri, Й“e mbi'a mbela minen ngoonЙ—ina wano Й—aayЙ“e Й“ee ngoonЙ—iniri, kono ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni Й—aayЙ“e kono Й“e nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii Й“e kawrii e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e mbi'a: min ngoonЙ—inii, so Й“e njeewdii e seyЙ—anooji maЙ“Й“e Й—i Й“e mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita Й“e O Й“eydana Й“e bewre Й“e ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko Й“een ngoni soodirЙ“e peewal majjere njeeygu maЙ“Й“e alaa tono, te Й“e peewaano"
  2,17,ЖҒe nanndi ko e kuЙ“Й“uЙ—o jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre maЙ“Й“e O acci Й“e e niЙ“e Й“e nji'ataa hay huunde
  2,18,Ko fahЙ—uЙ“e muumЙ—uЙ“e wumЙ“e Й“e nduttotaako
  2,19,Wolla wano toЙ“o iwde asamaan na woodi niЙ“e e digaali e maje Й“e cukka noppi maЙ“Й“e sabu kartaali (parГұite) ngam reentaade maayde Alla noon Ombo hiЙ“indii geЙ—e heeferЙ“e
  2,20,"Majal ngal na Й—eЙ“a yulde gite maЙ“Й“e kala nde ngal yaynii Й“e njaha heen so niЙ“Й“iЙ—ii Й“e ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nanЙ—e e gite maЙ“Й“e sabu Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,21,Onon yimЙ“e ndewee Jooma mon tagЙ—o on tagi adiiЙ“e on mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,22,"Oon mbaЙ—anЙ—o on lesdi ndi mbertu O waЙ—i Asamaan o mahoodi tiiЙ—ndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e woni njeЙ—u mon, taa mbaЙ—anee Alla nanndidiiЙ“e te oЙ—on nganndi goonga o"
  2,23,"So tawii oЙ—on cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaaЙ—o Amen o, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, nodde wallidiiЙ“e mon gaa Alla so tawii oЙ—on ngoonЙ—i e nodditaandu mon ndu"
  2,24,"So tawii on mbaЙ—aani Й—um -te on mbaawataa Й—um- kulee jayngol kuЙ“Й“irtengol yimЙ“e e kaaЖҙe, ngol heblanaa ko heeferЙ“e Й“e"
  2,25,"Weltin Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi wonde Й“eЙ“ keЙ“a aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde Й“e njeЙ—aa toon Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e Й“e mbi'a ko Й—ee min njeЙ—anoo ko adii, kono si Й“e meeЙ—ii Й—e Й“e tawa eЙ—e ceerti, eЙ“e keЙ“a toon rewЙ“e laaЙ“Й“e Й“e ГұiiЙ“ida toon. @Corrected"
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano Й“owngu e ko Й“uri Й—um, so tawii ko goonЙ—inЙ“e eЙ“e nganndi ko goonga iwЙ—o e Jooma maЙ“Й“e, so tawii ko yedduЙ“e Й“e mbi'a holko Alla yiЙ—i e oo yeru Ombo majjina heewЙ“e O feewna heen heewЙ“e, alaa majjinteeЙ—o heen sonaa yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare. @Corrected"
  2,27,ЖҒeen firtooЙ“e aadi Alla Й“aawo tiiЙ—neede mbo eЙ“e taЖҙa ko Alla yamiri yo jokke eЙ“e mbonna ka lesdi ko kamЙ“e ngoni rusЙ“iiЙ“e (pertuЙ“e)
  2,28,Holno njeddirton Alla tawa ngoodaano O wuurni on rewa heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on Й“aawo Й—uum ko e Makko nduttoto-Й—on
  2,29,Kanko tagani on kala ko woni e lesdi ndi Й“aawo Й—uum O faandii asamaan O fotndi mbo asamaanji jeeЙ—iЙ—i Kanko gannduЙ—o kala huunde. @Corrected
  2,30,"Nde Joom maa wi'i malayka en maa Mi waЙ— lomto Am e lesdi ndi, Й“e mbi'i mbela waЙ—at heen bonnoowo dufoowo ЖҙiiЖҙe tawa minen ko Aan tan min njettata miЙ—en Ma teddina, O wi'i Miin MiЙ—o anndi ko on nganndaa"
  2,31,"O anndini Aadama inЙ—e Й—e fofo, rewi heen O holli Й—e malaykaaЙ“e Й“e O wi'i kaalanee Kam inЙ—e Й“ee Й—oo so tawii oЙ—on ngoonЙ—i"
  2,32,ЖҒe mbi'i senaande woodanii Ma alaa ko min nganndi sonaa ko nganndin-ЖҠaa min ko Aan tan woni ganndidЙ—o kala huunde ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o
  2,33,O wi'i aan Aadama anndin Й“e inЙ—e majji nde o anndini Й“e inЙ—e Й—ee O wi'i mbela Mi wi'aano on Miin MiЙ—o anndi mbirniindi asamanji e lesdi MiЙ—o anndi ko peГұГұinton e ko cuuЙ—oton fof
  2,34,Nde Min mbii malaykaaЙ“e Й“e cujjanee Aadama Й“e cujji sonaa Ibliisa o salii o mawnikinii ndeen o jeyaa e yedduЙ“e
  2,35,Min mbii aan Aadama yah hoЙ—oy aljanna aan e debbo maa Гұaamee toon ko welata on kala Й—o mbela-Й—on taa Й“ado-Й—ee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e tooГұЙ“e
  2,36,SeyЙ—aane hoomti Й“e haa yaltini Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere nde Й“e ngonndoo Min mbii Й“e njippo-Й—ee ngonon aГұondirЙ“e keЙ“on ГұiiЙ“al dow lesdi ndi e dakmitaare haa happu yonta
  2,37,Aadama heЙ“i konngi iwde e Joom mum O accani mo ko Kanko woni jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o
  2,38,Min mbi'i njippo-Й—ee toon onon fof so tawii Mi addii e mon peewal kala dewЙ—o peewam Am Й“een dey kulol alanaa Й“e kadi Й“e cunotaako
  2,39,ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e penni maandeeji Amen ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e jayngol ko toon Й“e ГұiiЙ“ata
  2,40,Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree moЖҙЖҙere Am nde Mi waЙ—ani on njottinee aadi Am Mi yottina aadi mon te kulon Kam Miin tan
  2,41,"NgoonЙ—inee ko njippin-Mi na goonЙ—ini ko njogi-Й—on ko taa ngonee adiiЙ“e yeddude Й—um wota on eto soodirde aayeeje am Й—e coggu hoyngu, kulee kam Miin tan"
  2,42,Taa jiiЙ“indiree goonga e fenaande oЙ—on cuuЙ—a goonga o tawa oЙ—on nganndi mbo
  2,43,Г‘iiЙ“nee juulde tottiron asakal Й—igganon njankinano-Й—on Alla
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yimЙ“e Й—iggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa oЙ—on njanga deftere nde, mbela on kakkilantaa Й—um"
  2,45,"Mballitoree muГұal e juulde, pellet honde saЙ—tani dow mbo yankiniiЙ“e Й“e"
  2,46,ЖҒeen yananaaЙ“e maa kawru e joom maЙ“Й“e ko he Makko Й“e nduttotoo
  2,47,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji Am Й—i neemin MI mon, ko Miin tigi Й“urni e dow winndre he"
  2,48,Kulee Гұande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu ndu jaЙ“antaake tefangol goЙ—Й—o coodtiigu kadi jaЙ“etaake Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndanndii on yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“e mbaЙ—ii on lette bonЙ—e Й“e kirsa Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“e ngoppa rewЙ“e mon nguura, ina e Й—uum lette mawЙ—e iwde ga Jooma mon"
  2,50,Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo Min ndanndi on Min njooli yimЙ“e Fir'awna oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon ЕӢaas
  2,51,Nde Min podani Muusaa jammaaji capanЙ—e nayi fawii heen ndew-Й—on ngaari ndi caggal Am onon ko on tooГұooЙ“e
  2,52,Fawii heen Min ngaccani on Й“aawo Й—uum mbela joo njetton
  2,53,Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere nde e Furgaana mbela joo peewon
  2,54,Nde Muusaa wi'i yimЙ“e makko onon yimЙ“e am on tooГұii ko'e mon nde ndew-Й—on ngaari ndi nduttoЙ—ee e tagЙ—o on o mbarto-Й—on Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙande on to Jooma mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo njurmotooЙ—o
  2,55,Nde mbii-Й—on Muusaa min ngoonЙ—itaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laaЙ“i ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) Й“ami on oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon
  2,56,Fawii heen Min nguurtini on Й“aawo nde maay-Й—on mbela joo njetton
  2,57,"Min Й—uwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri dakmundi e colli juЙ—aaЙ—i Гұaamee e belЙ—i ko Min njeЙ—i on, wonaa Minen Й“e tooГұi ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұatnoo"
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare Гұaamon heen ko mbela-Й—on mbeltoron naatee damal ngal oЙ—on njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“ee moЖҙЖҙereeji
  2,59,TooГұЙ“e Й“ee mbayliti konngol ngol Й“e mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee lette sabu ko Й“e ngonno ko faasqeebe
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yimЙ“e mum ndiyam Min mbi'i fiyu haayre nde sawru maa ndu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e Й—iЙ—i puccitii heen yimЙ“e Й“ee fof keЙ“i yarde, Гұaamee njaree e njeЙ—u Alla taa mbaЙ—ee bonannde dow lesdi ndi"
  2,61,"Nde mbii-Й—on aan Muusaa min min njondintaako e Гұaamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min puЙ—i lesdi gila e kappe e haakooji e buudi e Гұebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on njiЙ— lomtinde ko ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko, keЙ“on ko Й“uri jaasde Й—uum njippo-Й—ee Misara maa on keЙ“ ko tori-Й—on ko Й“e pawaa koyeera e woroЙ—de Й“e nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu Й“e njedduno aayeeje eЙ“e mbara AnnabaaЙ“e ko aldaa e goonga Й—uum noon ko goopi e tooГұe maЙ“Й“e"
  2,62,"ЖҒeen goonЙ—inЙ“e eЙ“Й“en feewЙ“e e nasaara en e Й“e ngalaa diine,kala goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalaande wattan o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“een keЙ“ata njoЙ“di to Jooma maЙ“Й“e kulol alanaa Й“e te kamЙ“e Й“e cunotaako"
  2,63,Nde Min Й“ami aadi mon Min ummini fello Tuur dow mon Жҙettee ko Min ngddani on e semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,64,Fawii heen caggal Й—uum nduЕӢti-Й—on taw naano Й“ural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraaЙ“e
  2,65,On nganndii Й“een tooГұЙ“e e mon Гұande hoore-biir (samdi) Min mbii Й“e ngontee baaЙ—i booraaЙ—i
  2,66,Min mbaЙ—i Й—um woni maande teskuye wonande Й“e e aroyooЙ“e e tinndinoore wonande hulЙ“e Alla Й“e
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yimЙ“e makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge Й“e mbii mbela nanngir-Й—aa min ko Й—aayЙ“e? o wi'i: miЙ—o moolii Alla jeyeede e majjuЙ“e"
  2,68,"ЖҒe mbii du'ano min Jooma maa O laЙ“Й“inana min no nge wa'i. O wii: ko nge wonaa nayeye wonaa Гұalel ko hakindiinge mbaЙ—ee ko njamira-Й—on ko"
  2,69,"ЖҒe mbii torano min Jooma maa O laЙ“Й“inana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wii ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde"
  2,70,ЖҒe mbii du'ano min Joom maa O laЙ“Й“inana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i Й—i nanndiri min maa min njiitu nge
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dee O wii ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, Й“e mbii jooni dey a addii goonga Й“e kirsi nge kono Й“e Й—eЙ“aani waЙ—de yamiroore nde"
  2,72,Nde mbar-Й—on fettaandu ngon-Й—on e tuumondirde ko Alla yaltini ko cuuЙ—no-Й—on
  2,73,Min mbii tappindiree Й—i ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maayЙ“e O holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon
  2,74,"Fawii heen Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e njoori Й“aawo Й—uum Й—e mba'i no kaaЖҙe maa Й“ura noon, sabu kaaЖҙe na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli goЙ—Й—e na peecoo njaltina ndiyam goЙ—Й—e kadi njowtoo janansabu hulde Alla, Alla noo yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,75,Mbela oЙ—on Й—aminii maa Й“e ngoonЙ—inan on tawa na woodi e maЙ“Й“e sete nanoowo haala Alla Й“e mbaylita ka caggal nde Й“e paami Й“e nganndi ka
  2,76,"So Й“e kawri e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“ee Й“e mbii min ngoonЙ—inii so Й“e njeewdii Й“e mbi'a mbela on kaalanat Й“e ko Alla udditani on, ndeen Й“e kaЙ“ora on Й—um to Jooma mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"
  2,77,Mbela Й“e nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko Й“e cuuЙ—ta e ko Й“e Й“aЕӢnginta
  2,78,"Na woodi e mum en humambinneeЙ“e Й“e nganndaa e deftere nde sonaa janngugol penaale Й—e Й“e nganndinaa, Й“e ngoni e sikkude tan"
  2,79,"Bone woodanii Й“een winndirooЙ“e deftere nde juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e eЙ“e mbi'a Й—um ko to Alla iwri haa Й“e coodira nde coggu hoyngu, bone wonan Й“e e ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e mbinndi e kala ko Й“e paggitii heen"
  2,80,ЖҒe mbii jayngol memataa min sinaa balЙ—e seeЙ—a wii Й“e mbela on keЙ“ii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-Й—on ko haalde e Alla ko on nganndanaa
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bonЙ—i makko piilii mo, ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e jayngol luttooЙ“e toon"
  2,82,ЖҒeen goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙereeji ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e aljanna luttooЙ“e toon
  2,83,Min Й“amii fodoore e Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla moЖҙЖҙon e jibnaaЙ“e e jiidaaЙ“e e waayЙ—uЙ“e e waasЙ“e oЙ—on kaalana yimЙ“e Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi darnon juulde tottiron asakal Й“aawo Й—uum cali-Й—on Й—uurni-Й—on sonaa seeЙ—a e mooЙ—on
  2,84,Nde Min Жҙetti fodoore mon wota on nduf ЖҙiiЖҙe mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon Й—i ndeen njaЙ“-Й—on ceediЙ—on Й—um
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon Й“ee oЙ—on mbara ko'e mon oЙ—on njaltina yimЙ“e e mon galleeji maЙ“Й“e, oЙ—on peГұГұina tooГұe mon e maЙ“Й“e, si Й“e arii e mon dahaaЙ“e coodtidonЙ“e yaltingol Й“e na harmi e mon, mbela on goonЙ—inat yoga e deftere nde njeddon yoga heen kala e mon waЙ—ooЙ“e Й—um njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ko koyeera weejo aduna Гұande darnga Й“e nduttee e lette Й“urЙ—e bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,86,ЖҒeen soodirЙ“e laakara nguurndam aduna Й“e koynantaake lette Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo
  2,87,Min ngaddanii Muusaa deftere nde Й“aawo makko Min ndewni heen nulaaЙ“e Min ngaddani Iisaa Й“ii Maryam laЙ“Й“inale Min cemmbirini mo wonki tedduki mbela kala nde nulaaЙ—o addi he mon ko welaani pittaali mon mawnikino-Й—on yoga heen njeddon Й“e yoga heen mbaron Й“e
  2,88,"ЖҒe mbii Й“erЙ—e amen Й—e ko uddiiЙ—e, accu tan ko Alla huЙ—i Й“e sabu keefeeru maЙ“Й“e, na famЙ—i ko Й“e ngoonЙ—inta"
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e maЙ“Й“e iwde e Alla, ende nuunЙ—ina ko Й“e njogii ado Й—uum Й“e ngonndoo ko wallitoraade Й—um dow Й“een yedduЙ“e nde ko Й“e nganndi ko ari he maЙ“Й“e Й“e njiddi Й—um, yo kuЙ—di Alla won e heeferЙ“e"
  2,90,Bone woni e koЙ“e coodiri ko'e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e njeddi -e tooГұe- ko Alla jippini Alla jippinta Й“ural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaaЙ“e Mako Й“e kaandii e tikkere mawnde heeferЙ“e Й“ee na keЙ“a lette bonЙ—e
  2,91,"Si Й“e mbi'aama ngoonЙ—inee ko Alla jippini ko Й“e mbi'a min ngoonЙ—ina ko jippinaa e amen Й“e njedda ko wonaa Й—uum te ko Й—uum woni goonga nuunЙ—inЙ—o ko Й“e njogii, wii Й“e ko waЙ—i oЙ—on mbarannoo annabaaЙ“e Alla Й“e so tawno oЙ—on ngoonЙ—ini"
  2,92,Nde Muusaa addani on laЙ“Й“inale njogiti-Й—on ngaari ndi Й“aawo makko onon ko on tooГұooЙ“e
  2,93,"Min Й“ami e mon fodoore Min Й“amti dow mon haayre Tuur Жҙettiree ko Min ngaddani on ko e semmbe nanee, Й“e mbii min nanii min ngoopi Й“erЙ—e mum en Й—e keewi dak rewde ngaari ndi e keefeeru maЙ“Й“e, wii bone wonii e ko goonЙ—ingol mon yamiri on so tawno oЙ—on ngoonЙ—ini"
  2,94,Wii so tawii ko onon tan keЙ“ata aljanna to laakara njeloЙ—ee maayde so tawii ko on goonЙ—uЙ“e
  2,95,ЖҒe njelotaako Й—um pooma e ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ngardini Alla Ombo anndi tooГұooЙ“e Й“e
  2,96,Maa a taw ko kamЙ“e Й“uri reerЙ—ude e nguurndam e Й“een renndinЙ“e e Alla mbela gooto e maЙ“Й“e na yiЙ—i wuurde duuЙ“e ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti woЙ—Й—intaa mo lette Alla Mo yi'a golle maЙ“Й“e
  2,97,Wii kala gonЙ—o gaГұo Jibriil yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder Й“ernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuunЙ—ini defte Й—e Й“e njogii ko nde peewal e malu goonЙ—inЙ“e
  2,98,Kala gonЙ—o gaГұo Alla e malaykaaЙ“e Makko e nulaaЙ“e Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko gaГұo heeferЙ“e Й“e
  2,99,Min njippinii e maa maandeeji laЙ“Й“inooji alaa jeddoowo Й—i sonaa faasigeeЙ“e Й“e
  2,100,Wolla kala nde Й“e piЙ“i aadi wooda e maЙ“Й“e firtuЙ“e mbo accu tan Й“urЙ“e heewde e maЙ“Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani
  2,101,"Nde NulaaЙ—o Alla ari e maЙ“Й“e ombo goonЙ—ina ko Й“e njogii ko, woodi heen sete salii rontii deftere Alla nde wa'i no Й“e nganndaa nii"
  2,102,"ЖҒe ndewi ko seyЙ—aneeji njannganta laamu Suleymaan Suleymaan yeddaani kono ko seyЙ—aneeji Й—i njeddi eЙ—i nganndina yimЙ“e mbilewu e ko jippina dow malaykaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o to Baabil e Haaruut e Maaruu kala nde Й“e nganndini goЙ—Й—o Й“e mbi'a minen dey ko min fitina taa yeddu, Й“e jnnga e maЙ“Й“e no Й“e ceerndirta neddo e debbo mum, Й“e lorataa hay gooto sinaa e yamiroore Alla Й“e njannga ko bonnanta Й“e, Й“e nganndii kala battindirЙ—o Й—um alaa geЙ—al to laakara ko bone Й“e mbattiti ko'e maЙ“Й“e tawiino Й“e nganndi"
  2,103,Tawno Й“e ngoonЙ—inii Й“e kuli Alla ko mbarjaari immorde e Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude
  2,104,"Onon goonЙ—inЙ“e taa mbi'ee aynu min mbi'ee ndaar (fadir) min nanee, heeferЙ“e Й“ee na keЙ“a lette. muusЙ—e"
  2,105,"ЖҒeen yimЙ“e deftere yedduЙ“e e renndinЙ“e e Alla njiЙ—ataa jooma mon jippina e mon moЖҙЖҙ ere,Alla noon ko MboO welaa o waЙ—anta yurmeend e Mum ko O jooma Й“ural mawngal"
  2,106,Kala nde Min itti aaye maa momti mbo deen Min ngadda Й“urЙ—o mbo maa wano mbo mbela a anndaa Alla Mo waawi kala huunde
  2,107,Mbela a anndaa wonde ko Alla jeyi laamu asamaanji e lesdi on ngalaa keedanoowo mon wolla ballo sonaa Alla
  2,108,"Wolla njiЙ—-Й—on ko naamnaade nulaaЙ—o mon o wano Muusaa naamnoranoo ko adi,i kala mbo wattiti goonЙ—ingol keefeeru tawa o majjii laawol peewngol"
  2,109,HeewЙ“e e yimЙ“e deftere njiЙ—i ruttude on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo goonЙ—ingol mon ko ngaГұgu pittaali mum en caggal nde Й“e laaЙ“aa goonga o njaafee ngaccanon haa yamiroore Alla ara Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde
  2,110,Г‘iiЙ“nee juulde tottiree asakal kala moЖҙЖҙere nde mbaЙ—an-Й—on ko'e mon maa on tawnde to Alla ko Kanko Alla woni ji'oowo ko ngolloton
  2,111,"ЖҒe mbii alaa naatoowo aljanna sonaa Yahuude maa nasaaraajo Й—uum woni muuyaande maЙ“Й“e, wii: Й“e ngaddee daliil mooЙ—on so tawii ko on goonЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,112,"Ko goonga kala mbo totti yeeso makko Alla o woni moЖҙЖҙini, ma o heЙ— mbarjaari makko to joomum kulol alanaa Й“e Й“e cunotaako"
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbii nasaara en ngonaani e hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani e hay huunde, tawa eЙ“e njannga deftere nde, ko noon Й“e nganndaa Й“e mbiinoo ko Alla Гұaawata luural hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұande darnga"
  2,114,"Hombo Й“uri tooГұe oon kaЙ—oowo yo innde Alla jante nder juulirЙ—e ombo daranii bonnude Й—e Й“een potaani naatde Й—e so wonaa e kulol, Й“e keЙ“a koyeera e aduna Й“e keЙ“a lette mawЙ—e to laakara"
  2,115,"FuЙ—naange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen Й—o kuccit, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaajЙ—o e ganngal Makko piiltingal"
  2,116,"ЖҒe mbii Alla Mo jogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o senaande woodanii Mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na Й—oftoo Mo"
  2,117,"PuЙ—Й—uЙ—o asamaanji Й—i e lesdi ndi, so O Гұaawii huunde O wi'ata Й—um tan ko: won Й—um wona"
  2,118,"ЖҒe nganndaa Й“e mbi'a mbela Alla haaldataa min wolla O addana min maande, ko noon adinooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e mbiinoo Й“erЙ—e mum en nanndi goonga tigi Min laЙ“Й“inii maandeeji Й—i wonande yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e Й“e"
  2,119,"Minen Min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, A naaЙ“ntaake ma yimЙ“e jayngol Jahannama"
  2,120,Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol maЙ“Й“e yo a wii Й“e nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й“aawo nde keЙ“Й—aa ganndal ndeen a daГұataa ballal Alla
  2,121,"ЖҒeen Й“e Min ngaddani deftere nde eЙ“e nde njannga no haaniri ko Й“een tigi ngoonЙ—ini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko Й“een tigi ngoni bonnoraaЙ“e"
  2,122,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree moЖҙЖҙereeji Am Й—i Mi waЙ—ani on, Miin tigi waЙ—i mon Й“urirЙ—on winndere"
  2,123,"Kulee Гұande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu te ndu jaЙ“antaake coodtiigu kadi tefaneede nafataa ndu, Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo"
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini Й—i, O Wi'i: Miin Mi waЙ—at ma gardotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“e Ibarahiima wi'i waЙ— Й—um kadi e Й“esngu am O wi'i tooГұooЙ“e Й“e keЙ“ataa fodoore Am"
  2,125,Nde Min mbaЙ—i suudu ndu ruttorde yimЙ“e e hoolaare njokito-Й—ee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde Min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo Й“e laЙ“Й“in suudu Amngam wanngotooЙ“e e ufnotooЙ“e e juulooЙ“e
  2,126,Nde Ibrahiima wi'i jooma am waЙ—an min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi njeЙ—aa yimЙ“e mum Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e wonande goonЙ—inЙ“e Alla e Гұande wattan O wi'i kala jedduЙ—o Mi weltina mo seeЙ—a fawoo heen Mi faana mon lette jayngol e battane bonЙ—e
  2,127,Nde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila Й“amtatnoo dosЙ—e suudu ndu eЙ“e mbi'a Jooma amen jaЙ“an min ko Aan woni nanoowo ngannduЙ—o fof
  2,128,Jooma amen waЙ— min jaЙ“anЙ“e Ma mbaЙ—aa e Й“esngu amen leГұol juulЙ“e yo A hollu min tinndinorЙ—e dewe amen njaafo-ЖҠaa min ko Aan tigi woni jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o
  2,129,"Jooma amen waЙ— e maЙ“Й“e nulaaЙ—o ombo janngana Й“e aayeeje Maa o anndina Й“e Kur'aana Maa o e sunna o, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e ko Aaan tigi woni jaaliiЙ—o ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  2,130,Alaa Й—uurnotooЙ—o (calotooЙ—o) laawol Ibrahiima sonaa mbo fittaandu mum Й—aayi nganndee Min cuЙ“iima mo e aduna kanko o jeyaa ko e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e to laakara
  2,131,Nde Jooma mum wii Mo jaЙ“anAm ngonaa juulЙ—o o wi'i mi jaЙ“anii Jooma binnde Й—e
  2,132,"Ibrahiima tinndini Й“iЙ“Й“e mum, Yaakuub kadi waЙ—i noon, onon Й“iЙ“Й“e am Alla suЙ“aniima on diine Й—e taa maayee sonaa ko on juulЙ“e"
  2,133,Mbela on ceediima nde maayde arani Yaakuuba nde o wii Й“iЙ“Й“e mum Й“ee holko ndewoton caggal amЙ“e mbii min ndewan deweteeЙ—o maa e deweteeЙ—o baabiraaЙ“e maa Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak deweteeЙ—o gooto minen ko oon min njebbilanii
  2,134,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol fagginoo, onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo"
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbii ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wii: -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko e diine Ibrahiima peewЙ— Й—e o jeyanooka e sirkuЙ“e Й“e"
  2,136,Mbi'ee min ngoonЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaaЙ“e Й“ee okka iwde e joomiraawo maЙ“Й“e min ceerndataa hay gooto e maЙ“Й“e ko kamЙ“e min njebbilanii
  2,137,So tawii Й“e ngoonЙ—inii wano ko ngoonЙ—in-Й—on ko ndeen tawa Й“e peewii so Й“e Й—uurniima ndeen Й“e ngoni ko e luutndaade maa Alla suran ma Й“e ko Kanko woni nanoowo ngannduЙ—o fof
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaЕӢkooje alaa diine baaЙ—e no diine Alla Й—e, minen ko Kanko min ndewata"
  2,139,"Wii mbela on njeddondirat e amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joomiroowo men, min keЙ“at golle amen keЙ“on golle mon minen ko Kanko min laaЙ“anta"
  2,140,"Mbela on njiЙ— wiide wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat Й“e ngonndoo ko yahudeeЙ“e maa nasaaraЙ“e, wii mbela ko onon Й“uri anndude Alla hol mbo Й“uri tooГұe oon cuuЙ—oowo seedanfaagu iwde e Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko Й“e ngollata ko"
  2,141,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo"
  2,142,"Arma ka Й“e fuyunngaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e mbi'a: \"E ko hucciЕӢtini Й“e ga'e Qibla maЙ“Й“e mo Й“e laatinoo e mu'un?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla Woodani fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange, Himo Fewnira on Mo O Muuyi faade laawol focciingol"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii Men waЙ—iri on mofte hakindiiЙ—e fii yo on laato seedoytooЙ“e e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, NulaaЙ—o on seeditoyoo e dow mo'on. Men waЙ—iraa oo Qibla mo fewtataa e mu'un si wanaa no Men anndira on jokkoowo NulaaЙ—o on e on ruttotooЙ—o batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii Й—um laatike ko sattu-Й—um, si wanaa e dow Й“en Й“e Allah fewni. Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on: Pellet, Allah ko HilnotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en Yurmee Й“e"
  2,144,"GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en Reeni waylitorgol yeeso maa ngon ka kammu. Ma Men Fewtinire Qibla waalaЕӢtooЙ—o ma:Fewtinir yeeso maaЙ—a ngon baЕӢЕӢe Juulirde HoormaЕӢteere nden.Nokku kala ko ngoЙ—on,fewtiniree geece mon Й—en baЕӢЕӢe mayru:Pellet,Й“en RokkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en no anndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e,Allah non siforaali WelsinsiiЙ—o e ko Й“e gollata"
  2,145,"Mi Woondii si a addanii Й“en rokkaaЙ“e deftere nden kala maande,Й“e jokkataa Qibla maa on,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla maЙ“Й“e on,yoga e maЙ“Й“e wonaali jokkooЙ“e Qibla yoga.Mi Woondii si a jokkii mЙ“eleeЙ—e maaЙ“e Й“aawo kon ko ari e maa e anndal,pellet,an ontuma a jeyaama e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  2,146,"ЖҒen Й“e Men Rokki Deftere nden hiЙ“e nganndiri Й—um wano Й“e nganndiri Й“iЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e; pellete, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino suuЙ—ude goonga kan hara hiЙ“e nganndi"
  2,147,"Goonga kan ko ko ummori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e"
  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala baЕӢЕӢe Й—e o fewtata e mun.Adondiree e moЖҙЖҙereeji,nokku kala ka laati-Й—on,Allah artiray on,on denndaangal. Pellete,Allah ko hattanЙ—o e dow kala huunde"
  2,149,"Nokku kala ka yaltirЙ—aa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, pellet, Й—um ko goonga ummoraade Joomi maa, Allah Wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e kon ko gollo-ton"
  2,150,"Nokku kala ka yaltirЙ—aa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngonЙ—on, fewtiniree geece mon Й—en baЕӢЕӢe mayru fii wata wonan yimЙ“e Й“en hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa Й“en tooГұuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Wata non on huluЙ“e, Hulee Lam, fii no Mi Timminira neema Am On e mo'on, belajo'o on feeway"
  2,151,"Wano no Men Nuliri non e mo'on NulaaЙ—o ummoraade e mo'on,Himo janngana on Aayeeje Amen,himo laЙ“Й“ina on,himo anndina on Deftere nden,o anndina on ko on anndaana"
  2,152,"JaЕӢtee Lam, Mi Anndita on; jaarnee Lam wata on yeddam"
  2,153,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, wallitoree muГұГұaare e juulde. Pellet, Allah Hino Wonndi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an Й“en wariraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en: \"ko Й“e maayЙ“e\". Ko woni, Й“en ko wuurЙ“e, kono on so'aa anndude"
  2,155,"Ma Men jaribo on huunde, immorde e kulol, e heege, e Й—uytagol jawle, e woЕӢkiiji, e dimЙ—e; Wewlin muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,156,"ЖҒen tawЙ“e si masiibo heЙ“iiЙ“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to Makko menruttortoo"
  2,157,"ЖҒen Й—on, hino e dow maЙ“Й“e toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaaЙ—e e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajjuЙ—o ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o waЙ—i Umra,ella woo fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii moЖҙЖҙere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,159,"Pellet, Й“en suudooЙ“e kon ko Men Jippini immorde e Й“anngannduyeeji e peewal, Й“aawo nde Men ЖҒannginani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en ka Deftere, Й“en Й—on, Allah ena HuЙ—ude Й“e, huЙ—ooЙ“e Й“en na huЙ—ude Й“e"
  2,160,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“e moЖҙЖҙini Й“e Й“aЕӢngini: Mi JaЙ“anay Й“en Й—on tuubuubuyee, ko Min Woni JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,161,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heereraaЙ“e, Й“en Й—on ena fawiiЙ“e kuddi Allah ndin e Malaa'ika en e yimЙ“e Й“en denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake leЙ“te Й—en, Й“e wonaali nennanaЕӢteeЙ“e"
  2,163,"ReweteeЙ—e mon On ko ReweteeЙ—e Gooto. ReweteeЙ—o Alaa tanaa Makko, JurmotooЙ—o Yurmeende heeriinde e nde heeraaki Yurmeende"
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e Гұalorma on, e leЙ—Й—e dogirooje Й—en ka bahru nafugol yimЙ“e Й“en, e kon ko Allah Jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O Wurniri Й—um leydi ndin Й“aawo maayugol mayri O Saakti e mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli Й—in e duule eltaaЙ—e Й—en hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  2,165,"Hino e yimЙ“e njogitiiЙ“e ko woori Allah yerondirЙ—i, hiЙ“e njiЙ—iraЙ—i wano Allah yiЙ—irtee, [ko] Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“uri saЙ—tude giggol wonande Allah. Hara Й“en tooГұuЙ“e annduno tuma Й“e nji'oyta lepte Й—en, wonde doole Й—en fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanooЙ“e Й“en pottitoyii jokkunooЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nji'a lepte Й—en, sabuuji Й—in taЖҙira Й“e"
  2,167,"JokkunooЙ“e Й“en mbi'a: \"Hara nun fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora Й“e wano Й“e pottitori men nii\". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta Й“e golleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in; hayrere e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ngonaali njaltooЙ“e e yiite ngen"
  2,168,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Г‘aamee yoga e ko woni ka leydi ko dagii ko laaЙ“i, wata on jokku juri=taabe seytaane Й—in : Pellet, ko o gaГұo mo'on feeГұuЙ—o"
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paЕӢkare, e nde wowloton e hoore Allah ko on anndaa"
  2,170,"Si Й“e wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", Й“e mbi'a:\"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen\";e hay si baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haqqilataa hay e huunde Й“e haanditaaki"
  2,171,"Misal Й“en yedduЙ“e hino wa'i wa on ewnotooЙ—o kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko faaЙ—uЙ—i, mumiЙ—uЙ—i, wumuЙ—i; kaЕӢji Й—i haqqiltaa"
  2,172,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Г‘amee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko KaЕӢko rewoton"
  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jiiЙ“e, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duГұaaЙ—o [e Гұaamugol Й—um] hara wanaa Й“ewЙ—o wanaa jaggituЙ—o, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotooЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  2,174,"Pellet Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hiЙ“e soodira Й—um cogguwel famЙ—ungel. ЖҒen Й—on alaa waЙ—ude ka deedi maЙ“Й“e si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa Й“e Гұalnde darngal, O LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  2,175,"Ko Й“en ngoni soodirЙ“e majjere nden peewal, e lepte Й—en ya'fuyee. kaawse ko muГұГұoriЙ“e ka yiite"
  2,176,"ЖҠuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii Deftere nden goonga. pellet Й“en luutondirЙ“e e Deftere nden Й“e ngonii e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiЕӢgol geece mon Й—en Й“aЕӢnge fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, e Malaa'ika en, e Deftere nden, e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en; o okki jawdi -e hoore yiЙ—ugol ndi- joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“ii hoore-laawol, e Й“en torotooЙ“e, e fii rinЙ—inngol daaЙ—e; o niiЙ“ni juulde, o totti asakal, e Й“en hunnooЙ“e aadondiral maЙ“Й“e si Й“e haldidaama, e Й“en muГұГұitooЙ“e ka baasi e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko Й“en ngoni goonguЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en kadi ngoni gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e,njottiigu farlaama e mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaaЙ—o sabu jeyaaЙ—o,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaaЙ—o goЙ—Й—um e musiЙ—Й—o makko,ko jokkitirogol no moЖҙЖҙiri tottira e makko no moЖҙЖҙiri.ЖҠum Й—oo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala on jaggituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—u'um,no woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  2,179,"No woodani on ka njottiigu nguurdam, yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqilaaji. Belajo'o on wonay gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibinЙ“e mo Й“en,e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri.Ko hannduyee e dow gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,181,"Kala on waylituЙ—o Й—um Й“aawo o nannde, pellet bakkaatu mun on ko Й“en waylituЙ“e fawii. Allah ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,182,"On mo huli ooГұaare immorde e wasiyiiЙ—o maa bakkaatu o moЖҙЖҙini hakkunde maЙ“Й“e,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo YurmotooЙ—o"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e Й“en adinooЙ“e on, Й“elajo'o laatoЙ—on gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,184,"Г‘alЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. Kala e mo'on laatiiЙ—o nawnuЙ—o maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol ГұalЙ—i goo. No fawii Й“en haЙ—tanЙ“e ka, Гұammingol Й“iliiЙ—o. Kala on gattuЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere Й—um no moЖҙЖҙani mo. Ko nde hooroton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si wonii hiЙ—on nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en e Й“angannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seediiЙ—o lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On tawЙ—o no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e ГұalЙ—i goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on saЙ—teende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ЖҒaЙ—iiЙ—o. MiЙ—o Jaabina toraare torotooЙ—o si o torike Lam. Yo Й“e nooto Lam, e yo Й“e gomЙ—inam, belajo'o Й“e feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rewЙ“e mon Й“en. Ko Й“e koltu mo'on ko on koltu maЙ“Й“e. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke jaЕӢfotooЙ“e ko*e-mon,O JaЙ“ani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e maЙ“Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“on ko Alla Winndani on.Г‘aamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol Й“aЕӢngirana on Й“alewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e maЙ“Й“e hara ko on ufniiЙ“e ka juulirЙ—e.ЖҠum ko keeri Allah, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й—i.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta yimЙ“e Й“en aayeeje Makko Й—en,belajo'o Й“e wona gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,188,"Wata on Гұaamir jawle mon Й—en hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron Й—e e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en fii yo fedde goo Гұaamira e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en bakkaatu, hara hiЙ—on nganndi"
  2,189,"HiЙ“e naamno-maa fii darorЙ—e lebbi, wi'u: \"ЖҠin ko waqaЕӢtinanayЙ—i yimЙ“e e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngardaЕӢton cuuЙ—i Й—in immorde ka Й“abbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—uЙ—o.Ngardanee cuuЙ—i Й—in ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol Й“en haЙ“ooЙ“e on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,191,"wareeЙ“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e, yaltineeЙ“e nokku ka Й“e yaltiniri on: ko geddi Й—in Й“uri mawnude e dii haЙ“ugol ngol. Wata on haЙ“uЙ“e ka Misiide HormaЕӢteere haa Й“e haЙ“a on e mayre. Si Й“e haЙ“ii on haЙ“ee Й“e. Ko wano nii woni njoЙ“di heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  2,192,"Si Й“e haЙ—itike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yumeende"
  2,193,"HaЙ“ee Й“e haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa Й“en tooГұooЙ“e"
  2,194,"Si Й“e haЙ“ii on e lewru hormaЕӢteeru, haЙ“ee Й“e e lewru hormaЕӢteeru, horminaaЙ—i Й—in ko yottondirtee Й—um. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow mooЙ—on. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,195,"WiЕӢtee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juuЙ—e mon Й—en faade e halakuyee. MoЖҙЖҙinee, pellet Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinayЙ“e Й“en"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon Й—en haa kirse Й—en yottoo nokku majje. On tawЙ—o e mo'on ko ГұawЙ—o maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo heЙ“aali, ko hoorugol balЙ—e tati ka hajju e jeeЙ—iЙ—i si on ruttike; Й—en ko sappo timmuЙ—e. Ko jaЕӢtaa koo, ko fii on tawЙ—o Й“eynguure mun nden laataaki hoЙ—uЙ“e ka Misiide hormaЕӢte. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaaЙ—i. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollugЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, Allah no Anndi Й—um.YooЙ“ee,ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e njooЙ“a,ko gomЙ—al. Hulee Lam yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde Й—aЙ“Й“oton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaЕӢtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. JaЕӢtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muuЙ—um ko on jeyaaЙ“e e majjuЙ“e"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimЙ“e Й“en yahri Й—on, InsinanoЙ—on Alla. Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaЕӢtoree innde Alla wano jaЕӢtorton baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, maa ko Й“uri Й—um tiiЙ—ude. No e yimЙ“e Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara geЙ“al-moЖҙЖҙal"
  2,201,"No e maЙ“Й“e wi'ooЙ“e: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e geЙ“al-moЖҙЖҙal e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Alla ko YaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  2,203,"JaЕӢtee Innde Alla e ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. On yaccinЙ—o e nder balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on neЙ“tinЙ—o kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonannde on gomЙ—uЙ—o. Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet ko ka Makko mooЙ“indiroyte-Й—on"
  2,204,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo konngol mun no haawne ka nguurdam aduna, himo seediЕӢtina Alla kon ko woni e ndeer Й“ernde makko, hara non ko kaЕӢko Й“uri saЙ—tude wennje"
  2,205,"Si o huccitii, o yaha ka leydi fii o bonnu e mayri, o halka gese e geГұГұi. Alla YiЙ—aa bononda"
  2,206,"Si o wi'anaama: \"Hulu Alla\", mawniЕӢtinaare heЙ“a mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi"
  2,207,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en: on mo no sooЙ—tira woЕӢkii mun kin Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluyee Alla. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, naatiree e lislaamu ka denndanngal, wata on jokku juri seytaane Й—in. On ko gaГұo mooЙ—on Й“aЕӢnguЙ—o"
  2,209,"Si on ooГұike Й“aawo koo ko ari on e Й“aЕӢngannduyeeji, nganndee pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,210,"Taw si Й“ee no sabbii: si wanaa nde Allaahu On ArdaЕӢta Й“e e ndeer niЙ“e duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku gasinee. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  2,211,"Naamno geЙ—alЙ“e Israa'iila en:ko jelu woni ko Men Rokki Й“e e maandeeji Й“aЕӢnguЙ—i! Kala waЙ—tituЙ—o neema Alla on Й“aawo on arude mo, pellet, Alla ko TiiЙ—uЙ—o lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna Й—am cuЙ—inanaama Й“eya heeferЙ“e, hiЙ“e jalkita Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—uЙ“e wonoyay dow maЙ“Й“e Гұalnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on Mo O Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore"
  2,213,"YimЙ“e Й“en laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en, wewlinooЙ“e e jeertinooЙ“e, O Jippindini e maЙ“Й“e Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko Й“e luuondiri e muuЙ—um. Luutondiraali e muuЙ—um, si wanaa Й“en rokkaaЙ“e nde, Й“aawo kon ko ari Й“e e Й“aЕӢngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Allah Fewniri duЕӢyee Makko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e kon ko Й“e luutondiri e muuЙ—um, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol"
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo Й“en wuliiЙ“e on? HeЙ“iino Й“en saЙ—tteende e lorra, Й“e dillinaa haa NulaaЙ—o wi'i, e Й“en gomЙ—indimЙ“e e makko: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?\", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal Й“aЙ—tiingal"
  2,215,"ЖҒe ngaray naamnaade ma ko honЙ—um Й“e sakkotoo, wi'u: \"Si won ko sakkiЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, ko fii jibinЙ“e on, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“iliiЙ“e Й“en, e seteeЙ“e Й“en. kalako golluЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Й—um"
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko aГұaande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka aГұoton huunde hara ko nde moЖҙЖҙere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yiЙ—oton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Ko Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,217,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii lewru hormaЕӢte ndun, haЙ“ugol e mayru, maaku: \"HaЙ“ugol e mayru ko mawnu-Й—um. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yimЙ“e mayre Й“en e mayre, Й“uri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi Й“uri mawnude dii wargol ngol; Й“e seerataa hiЙ“e haЙ“a on haa Й“e rutta on e diina mon, si Й“e haaЙ—tanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondirЙ—o e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: Й“en Й—on, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii aduna e laakara; ko Й“en ngoni yimЙ“e yiite, Й“en ko luttooЙ“e ton"
  2,218,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e Й“en feruЙ“e haЙ“iri fii laawol Alla, Й“en Й—on no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,219,"HiЙ“e naamno-maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: \"No e Й—in Й—iЙ—i bakkaatu mawЙ—o e nafawoy wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, ko bakkaatu majji on non Й“uri mawnude e dii nafawoy majji on\". HiЙ“e naamno-maa kadi hol ko Й“e sakkotoo? Maaku: \"yaafuya=Ko fawi e haaju\". Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o on miijitoto"
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hiЙ“e naamno-maa fii wonduЙ“e Й“en, maaku: \"Ko moЖҙЖҙagol e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude\". Si on jillondirii e maЙ“Й“e, ko musiЙ—Й“e mo'on. Alla no Anndi on moЖҙЖҙinoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ЖҒiЙ—tinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,221,"Wata on resu Й“en rewЙ“e shirkayЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina: Mi Woondii ko korЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin Й“en worЙ“e shirkooЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina: Mi Woondii ko maccuЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.ЖҒen Й—on hiЙ“e nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duЕӢyee Makko. Himo ЖҒaЕӢngina Aayeeje Makko Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e wa'ajitoto"
  2,222,"HiЙ“e naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ЖҠum ko nefinii Й—um; luncitee rewЙ“e Й“en fewndo fiilordu, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й“e haa Й“e laaЙ“a. Si Й“e laaЙ“ii, ngaree e maЙ“Й“e nokku ka Alla Yamiri on Й—on. Pellet Alla No YiЙ—i tuubayaЙ“e Й“en Himo YiЙ—i kadi Й“en laЙ“Й“inotooЙ“e"
  2,223,"RewЙ“e mon Й“en ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faaliraЙ—on, ngardinanee woЕӢkiiji mon Й—in. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawrooЙ“e e Makko. Weltin gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  2,224,"Wata on waЙ—u Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon Й—en; nde Й—iggoton, gomЙ—on hulon moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  2,226,"No woodani Й“en woondirooЙ“e suddiiЙ“e mun Й“en: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si Й“e ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si Й“e fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,228,"SeeraaЙ“e Й“en yo habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en laaЙ“e tati; dagaЕӢtaako Й“e suuЙ—ugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji maЙ“Й“e, si wonii hiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Гұalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e jojjidi ruttugol Й“e e Й—um, si hawrii hiЙ“e faalaa weldital. No woodani Й“en [rewЙ“e] yeru kon ko fawiiЙ“e, no moЖҙЖҙiri. No woodani worЙ“e Й“en: Й“ural e dow maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—: ko jogitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitira no moЖҙЖҙiri. DagaЕӢtaako on Жҙettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-Й—on Й“e, si wanaa hara Й“e hulii [kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o] nde Й“e niiЙ“nataa keeri Alla Й—in. Si on hulii roЕӢkude ГұiiЙ“nude keeri Alla Й—in, goopi alanaa Й“e e kon ko debbo on soktori. ЖҠin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-Й—i. kala jaggituЙ—o keeri Alla Й—in, ko Й“en ngoni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, on [debbo] dagitaЕӢtaako mo Й“aawo Й—u'um, haa o resindira e gorko goo. Si on [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e ruttondira, si Й“e fellitii ГұiiЙ“nugol keeri Alla Й—in.ЖҠin ko keeri Allah, Himo ЖҒaЕӢnginana Й—i Й“en yimЙ“e ngannduЙ“e"
  2,231,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike: jogitoree-Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitoron Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Wata on jogitor Й“e lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala waЙ—uЙ—o Й—um, gomЙ—ii o tooГұii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor Aayeeje Alla Й—en jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla Й—i O Neemini e mo'on, e ko O Jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e Г‘eeГұal; Himo Wa'ajora Й—um. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,232,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike, wata on laagu Й“e nde moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en resata Й“e; si Й“e welondirii hakkunde maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. ЖҠum no waajoree on tawЙ—o e mo'on no gomЙ—ini Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde. Ko jaЕӢtanaЙ—on koo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, Й“uri laaЙ“aande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,233,"JibimЙ“e Й“en yo muynin Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i timmuЙ—i; wonannde on faandiiЙ—o timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaaЙ—o on, Гұammingol holitinira [rewЙ“e] Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri. WoЕӢkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibinЙ—o on lorrire sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, wanaa jibinanaaЙ—o on kadi lorrirtee sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru Й—um. Si Й“e faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e. Si on faandike Й—aЙ“Й“ude muyninanoowo on Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko Й“en [muyninooЙ“e] hanndi e moЖҙЖҙere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O ReenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,234,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: yo Й“en habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e lebbi nayi e balЙ—e sappo. Si Й“e yottike laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Alla Ko HumpitiiЙ—o kon ko golloton"
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko weeЙ“itoton, e sabboyde suddiiЙ“e Й“en, maa suuЙ—uЙ—on Й—um ka woЕӢkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e maЙ“Й“e [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton koЕӢngol moЖҙЖҙol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No Anndi ko woni e woЕӢkiiji mo'on, ReЕӢtee e Makko, nganndon pellet Alla Ko Haforoowo MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on renndude e maЙ“Й“e maa jaЕӢtanagol Й“e teЕӢe, dakmitee Й“e:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri.Hannduyee fawiiЙ—o moЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on meemude Й“e, tawa on jaЕӢtanike Й“e teЕӢe: ko feccere kon ko jaЕӢti-Й—on, si wanaa hara Й“e ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juuЙ—e mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afotoЙ—on Й“urata Й“aЙ—tinnde gomЙ—al. Wata on yejjitu Й“ural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko ReenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e julЙ—e Й—en, e julde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖҙЖҙiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕӢgol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri. ko goongofawiiЙ—o gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali Й“en njaltunooЙ“e e galleeji mu'un, kamЙ“e ko Й“e guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani Й“e: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti Й“e? Pellet Alla ko Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on Гұawloowo Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e? Alla No ЖҒiЙ—ttina Himo YaГұГұa, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-Й—on"
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila, Й“aawo Muusaa, tuma nde Й“e wi'annoo Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on: \"Imminan men lamЙ—o, men haЙ“a fii laawol Alla Ngol?\" O maaki: \"Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde roЕӢkoton haЙ“ude?\" Й“e mbi'i: \"Ko haЙ—ata men haЙ“ugol e fii laawol Alla Ngol, gomЙ—ii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e amen?\" Nde hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hucciti, si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Alla Ko AnnduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,247,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e:\"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laamЙ—o\". ЖҒe mbi'i:\"Hol no laamu laatoraЕӢta mo e hoore amen,ko menen Й“uri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?\" O maaki:\"Alla SuЙ“ike mo e dow mo'on,O ЖҒeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka Й“anndu\". Alla No Rokka Laamu Makko Ngun on Mo O Muuyi,Alla ko YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural] AnnduЙ—o"
  2,248,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e: \"Nganndee Maande Alla nden, ko nde Arkawal ngal arata on; deeЖҙere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo, Maande wonannde on; si o laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: \"Alla No Jarribora on caangol: kala yarЙ—o e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo meЙ—aali ngol ko on Й—on jeyaa e am, si wanaa on ГұeЙ—irЙ—o junngo mun ГұeЙ—annde\". ЖҒe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, kaЕӢko e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonduЙ“e e makko, Й“en mbi'i: \"Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun\". ЖҒen fellituЙ“e hawray e Alla Й“en mbi'i: \"Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde Й—uuЙ—unde, duЕӢayee Alla\". Pellet Alla No Wondi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,250,"Nde Й“e feeГұannoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, Й“e mbi'i: \"Joomi amen, Rufu muГұal e dow amen, TabiЕӢtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-Й—aa men e Й“ee heeferЙ“e"
  2,251,"ЖҒe fooliriЙ“e DuЕӢayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla Rokki mo Laamu e Annabaaku, O Anndini mo kon ko O Muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla DuГұirnoo yimЙ“e Й“en yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom ЖҒural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Alla, MeЙ—en JaЕӢnga Й—e e dow maaЙ—a wondude e Goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  2,253,"ЖҒen NulaaЙ“e, Men ЖҒurnii yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga : No e maЙ“Й“e yeewtiduЙ“e e Alla, O ЖҒaЕӢti darjaaji yoga e maЙ“Й“e; Men Rokki Iisaa, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, Й“anngannduyeeji Men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laaЙ“undu ndun. Si Alla Muuyuno, womЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“en wartindirtaano Й“aawo nde Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in ari maabЙ“e. Kono Й“e luutondiri: no e maЙ“Й“e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, no e maЙ“Й“e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Si Alla Muuyuno, Й“e wartindirtaano, kono Alla no waЙ—a kon ko O YiЙ—i"
  2,254,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, sakkee e kon ko Men Arsiki on adii Гұalaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heeferЙ“e Й“en woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteezo si wanaa kanko, WuurЙ—o Г‘iiЙ“uЙ—o. ЕҠoЕӢre nanngataa Mo, wanaa kadi Й—oyngol. ko Kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka Makko si wanaa e duЕӢayee Makko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso maЙ“Й“e, e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe huЙ“indotaako huunde e Anndal Makko ngal si wanaa ko O Muuyi. Jullere Makko nden no yaaji Й“uri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Reenugol Й—i aaninaa Mo. Ko Kano woni ToowuЙ—o MawЙ—o On. @Corrected"
  2,256,"Doolugol alaa ka diina. GomЙ—ii peewal ngal Й“anngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yedduЙ—o Й—uuЙ—a bewreeru ndun o gomЙ—ini Alla, haray o jogitike Й“oggi finnde hoolaare Й—in, firtagol alanaa Й—i. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,257,"Alla Ko GiЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: Himo yaltina Й“e e niЙ“e, O naЙ“a Й“e e ndaygu. ЖҒeya yedduЙ“e, yiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e ko Й—uuЙ—a bewreeji Й—in: HiЙ—i yaltina Й“e e ndaygu naЙ“a Й“e e niЙ“e. ЖҒen ko yimЙ“e yiite, luttooЙ“e e magge"
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennjuЙ—o Ibraahiima e fii JeyЙ—o mo On, fii Alla no YeЙ—i mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"JeyЙ—o lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [WennjuЙ—o on] wi'i: \"Min kadi miЙ—o wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fuЙ—naange, addir nge hiirnaange\".YedduЙ—o on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtiiЙ—o wuro yeewngo ngo maadi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi*i hono Alla wuurtaninta Й—um caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duuЙ“i teemedere O ummini mbo O daali hono foti ГұiiЙ“Й—a o wi*i Гұalawma maa feccere Гұalawma, O daali alah a duumiima Й—o duuЙ“i teemedere Жҙeew Гұaamdu ma e njaram ma waylaaki ndaaru mbabba ma ba, ngam min mbaЙ— ma maande wonande yimЙ“e, Жҙeew Жҙi*e nomin cardataЙ—e refti Min muurdaЙ—e teew, nde Й—uum feeГұi mbo o wi*i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huundeЙ“Й—ЖҙЖҙГұj"
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollam na nguurtanirta maayЙ“e, O daali mate a goonЙ—inaani? o maaki ohonkay kono ko haa Й“ernde am deeЖҙa , O daali nanngu colli nay tappuЙ—i faade e ma refti mbaЙ—a e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti nodduЙ—i Й—i ngara e ma hoЙ—i njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko O ГұeeГұo"
  2,261,Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e e laawol Alla ko honbbere fuЙ—nunde butaali njeeЙ—iЙ—i in wutaandu fof teemedere abbere Alla na sowana Mo O welaa Alla ko jaacЙ—o Ganndo
  2,262,NafkooЙ“e jawdi mum en e laawol Alla refti Й“e ndewnatah e koЙ“e ko wacde wolla lor woodaniiЙ“e njobdi mum en ka joomi mum en kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonah sunotooЙ“e
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e sadaka dewnateeЙ—o lorla, Alla ko Gala yondaniiЙ—o munyoowo"
  2,264,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wacde e lorlude hono oon tottirЙ—o jawdi mum yeenga yimЙ“e o goonЙ—inaani Alla e Гұalngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haaЖҙre Й—aatnde toЙ“o yani e mayre acci nde honde wa*i e teeleende Й“een kattantah hay huunde e ko Й“e paggatii ko,Alla feewnatah yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“e"
  2,265,"Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e jawdi mum en ngam Й—aЙ“Й“ude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mum en ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde toЙ“o heewngo heewngo yani e heba ba, ba addi cowe Й—iЙ“Й—e ko ba addatno si ba toЙ“aam Гұuur Гұuur koba hecca mbelba balangol A na yi*a ko mbaЙ—aton ko"
  2,266,"Mbela gooto e mon na yiЙ—i nde o daГұata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala Й“eynaaЙ—e, o naywi hombo jogii Й“eyngu loongu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa he ba suma, ko hona nih Min Й“annganirta kaawisaaji Й—i mbela miictaЙ—on"
  2,267,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e tottiree ko laaЙ“i ummaade ko paggiti Й—on e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko soЙ“i ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngooЙ“e Й—um si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondaniiЙ—o MantaaЙ—o"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e Й“ural Alla ko jaacЙ—o ko O Ganndo"
  2,269,"Hombo totta ГұeeГұal mbo O wela kala tottaaЙ—o ГұeeГұal o tottaa ma moЖҙЖҙere mawnde, siftortah Й—um si wonah joman hakkiillaaji"
  2,270,"Kala ko tottirЙ—on e nafake wolla takkuЙ—on e takkere pellet Alla na anndi Й—uum, woodanaani tooГұooЙ“e wallooЙ“e"
  2,271,Si on Й“annginii sadakeeji na ЖҙЖҙi si on cuuЙ—i Й—i tottuЙ—on Й—i waasЙ“e ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande O hafrana on bonЙ—i mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton ko
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere tottite Й—um e mbaadi timmundi onon de on tooГұetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waasЙ“e suraaЙ“e gaa e laawol Alla Й“e mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majjuЙ“e na cikka koЙ“e alЙ—uЙ“e sabu Й—uurnaade aduna ana anndiraЙ“e maandeeji mum en Й“e Гұaagataaka yimЙ“e e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottirЙ—on Alla na anndi Й—um"
  2,274,"TootirooЙ“e jawdi mum en jemma e Гұalawma e mbaadi mbirniindi e mbaadi Й“anngundi, Й“een de woodaniiЙ“e njbdi mum en ummaade ka joomi mum en kulol woodanaani Й“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e"
  2,275,"Й“een ГұaamooЙ“e riba Й“e ummataako si wonah no mbo seytaani memi Й—uum noon ko sabu wiide Й“e pellet njeegu wa*i kono riba, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini riba, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o Й“enni ko fiyaaku makko e Alla fawii, kala duttiiЙ—o noon ko Й“een ngoni joman en yiite saasooЙ“e e henge haa pooma"
  2,276,Alla na momto riba na Й“amta sadakuuji Alla yiЙ—ah kala keeЙ—o keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne
  2,277,Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodaniiЙ“e jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e
  2,278,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goonЙ—uЙ“e
  2,279,Si on mbaЙ—aani Й—uum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaaЙ—o MakkoJJJЙ“J
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o muГұane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mon si on ngonii annduЙ“e"
  2,281,Kulee Гұalngu ngu ndutteteЙ—on ka Alla refti yoЙ“ee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si on Гұamlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaaЙ—o mbinndee nde, yo nuunЙ—uЙ—o winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko Й—aayЙ—o wolla lohЙ—o wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuunЙ—al, ceednee seede en Й—iЙ—o e worЙ“e mon, si worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ngalah ko gorko e rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Й“e mbelete Й—on e seedeeli ngam si gooto e maЙ“Й“e yrdditi goЙ—Й—o o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala siЙ“e noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko famЙ—i maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko Й—uum Й“uri nuunЙ—ude ka Alla Й“uri fooccaade wonande seede Й“uri kadi Й“adaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton Й—um winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on waЙ—ii Й—uum pellet Й—uum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e Й—atngal on keЙ“aani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaaЙ—o hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuuЙ—e seedanfaagu kala cuuЙ—o ngu pellet oon Й“ernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on Й“annginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuuЙ—i ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,285,"NulaaЙ—o goonЙ—anii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e gooninЙ“e Й“e fof Й“e goonЙ—anii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e NulaaЙ“e makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e NulaaЙ“e makko, Й“e wii min nanii min Й—oftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirnaЙ—a Й“een adiiЙ“e amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurmaЙ—a min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“e"
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  3,2,"Alla: reweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko O WuurЙ—o, Г‘iiЙ“uЙ—o"
  3,3,"O Jippinirii Deftere nden dow maaЙ—a e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde, O Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila"
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yimЙ“e Й“en, O Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. Alla Ko FooluЙ—o, Jom-yottagol"
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suuЙ—otaako Mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  3,6,"Ko KaЕӢko Woni Mbaadiniroowo on ka renngaaji noone woo no O Muuyiri. ReweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,7,"Ko KaЕӢko Woni JippinЙ—o Deftere nden e maaЙ—a, no e mayre aayeeje Й“aЕӢnguЙ—e; ko kaЕӢje woni neene Deftere nden, e goЙ—Й—e goo nannduЙ—e. Ammaa Й“en Й“e ooГұaare woni e nder Й“erЙ—e mun, hiЙ“e jokka ko nanndi kon e majje Й—aЙ“Й“ugol fitina e Й—aЙ“ugol firtugol Й—e. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. TutiiЙ“e Й“en e ganndal no wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen\". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en"
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata ooГұu Й“erЙ—e amen Й—en Й“aawo nde fewnu-Й—aa men, yeЙ—u men yurmeende immorde ka MaaЙ—a.Pellet An, ko An Woni YeЙ—oowo=dokko"
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet An ko A MooЙ“oyoowo yimЙ“e Й“en Гұalnde nde sikke alah e mun Pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden"
  3,10,"Pellet Й“en yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e duncaЕӢtaaЙ“e e lepte Alla Й—en hay e huunde. Ko Й“en woni carmale yiite ngen"
  3,11,"Wano mbowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe fennii aayeeje Amen Й—en, Alla Nanngitiri Й“e junubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  3,12,"Maakan Й“en yedduЙ“e: \"On fooloyte mooЙ“oye-Й—on ka jahannama\". Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi"
  3,13,"GomЙ—ii laatanike on aaya e Й—in feddeejji Й—iЙ—i fottuЙ—i fiihaЙ“ugol: fedde goo no haЙ“a e laawol Alla, wonnde goo ko yeddunde, hiЙ“e yi'iraЙ“e yeru maЙ“Й“e laawЙ“i Й—iЙ—i giiЙ—e gite. Alla no Semmbinira balla Makko ngal o Mo O Muuyi. Pellet, no e Й—um waaju wonannde joomiraaЙ“e-haqqillaaji"
  3,14,"YimЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—inanaama yiЙ—ugol tuuyooji: immorde e rewЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e, e jawle tuginidiraaЙ—e, immorde e kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise, e pucci ЕӢarЙ—iЙ—aaЙ—i, e neemoraaЙ—i, e remuru. ЖҠum Й—on, ko dakamme nguurdam aduna. Alla, no ka Makko moЖҙЖҙuЙ—um ruttorde"
  3,15,"Maaku: \"E yo mi humpitu on ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e Й—um mon?\". No woodani Й“en huluЙ“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, aljannaaji, no ila senngo ley majji, canЙ—i: ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton, wondude e sonnaaЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e, e yerluyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko ReЕӢtuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  3,16,"ЖҒen wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen, menen men gomЙ—inii, yawtan men junubaaji amen, daЙ—ndaa men lepte yiite"
  3,17,MuГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e goonguЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en e wiЕӢtooЙ“e=nafkoobe Й“en e insinotooЙ“e Й“en ka hoore-subaka
  3,18,"Alla Seedike wonde ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kaЕӢko, Malaa'ika en kadi, e joomiraaЙ“e ganndal Й“en, ko O DaraniiЙ—o nunЙ—al. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, On FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,19,"Pellet diina kan ka Alla, ko lislaamu. OkkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en lurraali si wanaa Й“aawo nde ganndal ngal arde Й“e; ka bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Kala yedduЙ—o aayeeje Alla Й—en, pellet Alla ko yaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  3,20,"Si Й“e wennjii ma, maaku: \"Mi jebbilanii yeeso an ngon e on jokkuЙ—o lam\". Maakanaa Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte e humambinne en: \" E on jebbilike?\" Si Й“e jebbilike, gomЙ—ii Й“e feewii, si Й“e huccitii, enee, ko fawi maa ko yottingol. Alla ko ReЕӢtuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,21,"Pellet, Й“en yeddooЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e wara AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga, Й“e wara Й“en yamirooЙ“e nunЙ—al, wewlinir Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,22,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e golleeji mun boni Й“en ka aduna e ka laakara, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e"
  3,23,"E a yi'aali okkaaЙ“e geЙ“al e Deftere nden, hiЙ“e noddee e Deftere Alla nden fii no nde Гұaawira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e huccita ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e"
  3,24,"ЖҠum non, ko tawde Й“e wi'ii: \"Yiite ngen meemataa men si wanaa ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i\". hodiiЙ“e e diina maЙ“Й“e kan, huunde nde Й“e fefindotonoo"
  3,25,"E ko hol no si Men MooЙ“oyiiЙ“e e Г‘alaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un, woЕӢkii kala hunnanee ko ki faggitii kon? KamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  3,26,"Maaku: \"Yaa An LaamЙ—o JeyЙ—o laamu, HiЙ—a Okka laamu on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a ЖҒoora laamu on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a Teddina on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a Hoyna on mo MuuyuЙ—aa. MoЖҙЖҙere nden ko e Junngo MaaЙ—a woni, pellet, An e huunde kala, ko A HaaЙ—tanЙ—o"
  3,27,"HiЙ—a Naadira jemma on nder Гұalorma on, HiЙ—a Naadira Гұalorma on nder jemma on. HiЙ—a Yaltina ko wuuri immorde e ko maayi, yaltinaa ko maayi immorde e ko wuur. HiЙ—a Arsika on mo MuuyuЙ—aa ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,28,"Wata muumini en jogitor heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—Й“e Й“e acca gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Kala huuwuЙ—o Й—um, o laataaki jeyraaЙ—o e diina Alla Kan hay e huunde, si wanaa nde huloton e maЙ“Й“e bone. Alla No ReЕӢtina on Hoore-Mun. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  3,29,"Maaku:Si on suuЙ—ii ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon maa si on feГұГұin Й—um,Alla no Anndi Й—um,Himo Anndi ko woni ka kammuuli e ko woni e leydi Alla ko kattan-Й—o kala huunde"
  3,30,"Г‘alnde kala woЕӢkii tawata ko ki golli kon e moЖҙЖҙere hino Й“annaa, e huunde ko ki golle e bone, ki yeloo sinno wonayno hakkunde makki e majje dumunne woЙ—Й—uЙ—o. Alla no ReЕӢtina on Hoore Mun. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,31,"wi*u si wonii hidon yidi Alla, cukke e am, mi yidno mon Alla, O yaafo mon bakkatuuji mon, Alla ko kafroowo jumotoodo"
  3,32,"Maaku: \"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on\", si Й“e huccitii, pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  3,33,"Pellet, Alla SuЙ“ike Aadama e Nuuhu e yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en e yimЙ“e Imraana Й“en e hoore tagoore nden"
  3,34,Jurriiya=genyol yoga e maЙ“Й“e iwde e yoga. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o
  3,35,"Nde debbo Imraana on wi'unoo: \"Joomi an, min mi takkanii Ma kon woni ka nder reedu am, ko rinЙ—inaa Й—um, jaЙ“anam, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  3,36,"Nde o jibinnoo mo o wi'i: \"Min mi jibinii mo ko o deyel\", ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ko O jibini, gorko laataaki wano debbo. \"Min mi innii mo Maryama, min mi moolnii mo e MaaЙ—a e jurriiya makko on immorde seytaane raЙ—aaЙ—o on"
  3,37,"Joomi makko JaЙ“irani mo jaЙ“annde moЖҙЖҙere,O Neiri mo needi moЖҙЖҙundi,O Halfini mo Jakariya.Tuma kala Jakariya naati e hoore makko ka Mihraab,o tawda mo e arsike,o wi'a:Hey, Mariyam hol no heЙ“irЙ—aa Й—um?O jaaboo:ЖҠum ko ka Alla iwri.Pellet,no Arsika on O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,38,"Ko ton Jakariraa'u noddi Jooma mun o maaki: \"Joomi am, YeЙ—am immorde ka MaaЙ—a, jurriiya laaЙ“uЙ—o, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo noddaandu"
  3,39,"Malaa'ika en noddi mo hawri himo darii juuugol ka ganngunal, wonde: \"Alla No Wewlinire Yahyaa, goonginЙ—o Konngol iwrungol ka Alla: koohoojo, e reenaaЙ—o [e tuuyo], e Annabaajo jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e\" @Corrected"
  3,40,"O maaki: \"Joomi an, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatorЕӢta lam, gomЙ—ii mi nawyii, debbo am on ko damaro?\" O Daali: \"Ko wano non Alla WaЙ—irta ko O Muuyi [waЙ—de]"
  3,41,"O maaki: \"Joomi, WaЙ—anam maande\". O Daali: \"Maande maa nden, ko nde a yeewtidataa e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“alЙ—e tati si wanaa e joopagol. JaЕӢtoЙ—aa Joomi maaЙ—a ko heewi: subbunhino-Й—aa kiiki e bimmbi"
  3,42,"Tuma nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, pellet Alla SuЙ“ike ma, O LaЙ“Й“inii ma [O SuЙ“ii] e rewЙ“e winndere nden"
  3,43,"Hey Maryam, toЖҙЖҙinano Joomi maa, sujjaa ruЖҙЖҙidaa e ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,44,"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite wirniiЙ—e, MeЙ—en Wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e weddotonoo kuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e ne'ata Maryama; a tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e kadi nde Й“e wennjaynoo"
  3,45,"Nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, Alla no Wewlinire Konngol immorde e Maako: Innde makko, ko meema-sella, Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, koohoojo aduna e laakara, jeyaaЙ—a e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e [ka Alla]"
  3,46,"Himo yeewtida e yimЙ“e Й“en ka woofordu=tiggu e ka sagatalaaku, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,47,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatoraЕӢta lam, Й“anndiЕӢke meemaali lam?\". O Daali: \"Ko wano non. Alla no Taga ko O Muuyi. Si O Г‘aawii fiyaake, O Daalanay mo [tun]: \"Laato! o laatoo"
  3,48,Himo Anndina mo Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal e Tawreeta e Linnjiila
  3,49,"E NulaaЙ—o faade e Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila en, wonnde: \"GomЙ—ii mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Wonnde miЙ—o tagana on immorde e loopal ko wa'i wa sonndu, mi wutta e muuЙ—um woЕӢtira sonndu e DuЕӢayee Alla. Mi wumtina bunЙ—o, mi sellina baadaaЙ—o, mi wuurnitira maayЙ“e e duЕӢayee Alla. Mi humpita on ko Гұaamoton e ko maroton ka cuuЙ—i mon. Pellet, hino e Й—um, maande wonanannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  3,50,"e goonginЙ—o ko woni yeeso am immorde e Tawreeta, e no mi dagininirana on yoga e ko harmannoo on, mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on lam"
  3,51,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol"
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngun e maЙ“Й“e, o maaki: \"Ko hommbo wallata lam e [diina] Alla [kan]?\". HawaaruyaЕӢko en wi'i: \"Menen ko men wallooЙ“e [e diina] Alla [kan], men gomЙ—inii Alla, seedo wonnde ko men jebbiiliiЙ“e"
  3,53,"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii ko JipinЙ—aa Kon, men jokkii NulaaЙ—o on, Winndu men e seediiЙ“e Й“en"
  3,54,ЖҒe fewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude e fewjooЙ“e Й“en
  3,55,"Nde Alla Daalunoo: \"Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ЖҒamtoowo ma faade ka Am, e LaЙ“Й“inoowo ma immorde e Й“en yedduЙ“e, e WaЙ—a Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma e hoore Й“en yedduЙ“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi Г‘aawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-Й—on e muuЙ—um"
  3,56,"Ammaa Й“en yedduЙ“e, Mi Lepta Й“en Й—on lepte muusuЙ—e ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaaЙ“e faabotooЙ“e"
  3,57,"Ammaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe, O Hunnanay Й“e mbarjaari maЙ“Й“e ndin. Alla YiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,58,"ЖҠum Й—oo, MeЙ—en Janngana maa Й—um, immorde e Aayeeje e JaЕӢtoore Г‘eГұГұaannde"
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e mbummbuldi, refti O Daalani mo: \"Laato!\" o laatii"
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e"
  3,61,"Kala wennjuЙ—o ma fii makko Й“aawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: \"Aree nodden Й“iЙ—Й“e amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e mo'on, e rewЙ“e amen e rewЙ“e mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti ГұaagoЙ—en waЙ—en kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,62,"Pellet Й—um Й—oo, ko Й—um woni fillayee goonga. Alaa reweteeЙ—o si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko Woni FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,63,"Si Й“e huccitii, pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,64,"Maaku: \"Hey yimЙ“e Defte, aree faade e konngol fotayngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : wonnde en rewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraaЙ“e ko woori Alla\". Si Й“e huccitii, wi'ee: \"Seeditee wonnde menen ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"
  3,65,"Hey yimЙ“e Defte, ko wennjaЕӢton fii Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila Jippinaaka si wanaa Й“aawo makko : e on haqqiltaa"
  3,66,"Hey ko onon Й“ee, on wennjii kon ko anndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaЕӢton ko anndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on anndaa"
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuudiЕӢke wanaa Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke ooГұiiЙ—o [e kala diina] jebbilaniiЙ—o [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e shirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,68,"Pellet, ko Й“uri hanndude e Ibraahiima e yimЙ“e Й“en : ko Й“en jokkuЙ“e mo, e oo Annabiijo, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e. Alla ko GiЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en yelike nde Й“e majjina on, Й“e majjiЕӢtaa si wanaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e so'aa anndude"
  3,70,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko yeddaЕӢton Aayeeje Alla ЖҠen hara onon ko on seediiЙ“e"
  3,71,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko jillaЕӢton goonga kan e meh-re nden hiЙ—on suuЙ—a goonga kan hara onon hiЙ—on anndi"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en wi'i: \"GomЙ—inee ko jippinaa kon e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ka arannde Гұallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, Й“e ruttoo"
  3,73,"Wata on gomЙ—in si wanaa on jokkuЙ—o diina mon kan\". Maaku: \"Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal\". [Ko kulil fii ] wata goЙ—Й—o goo okke sugu ko okkaЙ—on kon maa Й“e wennjiroya on Й—um ko Joomi mon. Maaku: \"Pellet Й“ural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Himo YeЙ—a ngal on Mo O Muuyi\". Alla ko yaajuЙ—o [Й“ural] AnnduЙ—o"
  3,74,Himo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nden on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko Jom ЖҒural Mawngal
  3,75,"No e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on mo halfiЕӢtaa jawdi wonayndi KINTAAR, on jonnite ndi; hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi, on mo halfiЕӢtaa \"diinaaru\", on jonnitataa ma ndu si wanaa a darani mo daЕӢkaranni-Й—aa. ЖҠum non, ko tawde kamЙ“e Й“e wi'i: \"Laatanaaki men e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“en laawol\"; hiЙ“e taЖҙa penaale huma e Alla hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e anndi"
  3,76,"Aa'a, kala hunnuЙ—o ahadi mu'un o huli, pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i hulooЙ“e Mo Й“en"
  3,77,"ЖҒen soktitorayЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin e goondooje maЙ“Й“e coggeloy famЙ—ukoy, Й“en Й—on, geЙ“al alaa Й“e ka laakara, Alla yeewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e, O Ndaaroytaa Й“e Г‘lande Darngal, O LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,78,"No e maЙ“Й“e fedde : hiЙ“e ooГұira Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e Deftere nden no sikkiron Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e Deftere nden, Й—um le jeyaaka e Deftere nden; hiЙ“e wi'a : \"ЖҠum ko ko iwri ka Alla\", Й—um le wanaa ka Alla iwri; hiЙ“e takka penaale hoore Alla hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e anndi"
  3,79,"Laatanaaki Й“anndiЕӢke nde Alla Okkata mo Deftere e fahmu e Annabaaku, refti o wi'ana yimЙ“e Й“en: \"Laatee jeyaaЙ“e am ko woori Alla\", si ko woni: \"Laatoree tutiiЙ“e-e-gannde-diina, ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on janngina Deftere nden e ko laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jannga\" @Corrected"
  3,80,Wanaa nde o yamirta on jogitorgol Malaa'ika en e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en reweteeЙ“e. E o yamiray on keeferaaku Й“aawo nde wonЙ—on julЙ“e
  3,81,"Tuma nde Alla Жҙettunoo ahadi e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en : \"Si Mi Addanii on Deftere e fahmu, refti NulaaЙ—o ari e mo'on goonginЙ—o kon ko jogiЙ—on, ma on gomЙ—in mo wallitoЙ—on mo\". O Daali: \"E on qirritike Й—um, on Жҙettii e hoore mun ahadi?\". ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men qirritike\". O Daali: \"Seeditee, MiЙ—o wondi e mo'on ka seeditiiЙ“e"
  3,82,"On huccituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en woni faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  3,83,"E ko woori Diina Alla kan Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata? Hino woodani Mo jebbilaare Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi, Й—oftaare maa waawneede, ko faade ka Makko Й“e ruttotoo"
  3,84,"Maaku: \"Men gomЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e TaaniraaЙ“e Й“en e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e, Menen wonannde Mo ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"
  3,85,"Kala Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o jaЙ“aЕӢtaake Й—um, on Й—on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e Й“e seedii wonnde NulaaЙ—o on ko goonga, Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in arii Й“e? Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,87,"ЖҒen Й—on, joЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko no fawii Й“e kuddi Alla ndin e Malaa'ika en e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e denndaangal"
  3,88,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake lepte Й—en, Й“e wonaali nennanaЕӢteeЙ“e"
  3,89,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“aawo Й—um Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Pellet, Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  3,90,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e Й“eydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“etaake; ko Й“en Й—on woni majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,91,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heererЙ“e, gooto e maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“aЕӢtaake, leydi ndin tew kaЕӢЕӢe; hay si o soktorii Й—um. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e"
  3,92,"On heЙ“ataa moЖҙЖҙere nden haa wiЕӢtoЙ—on e ko Й“uruЙ—on yiЙ—ude kon. Kala woo ko wiЕӢtiЙ—on, pellet Alla no Anndi Й—um"
  3,93,"Kala Гұaametee laatino daganii-Й—um Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila en, si wanaa ko Israa'iila harminanno hoore-mun ado Tawreeta Jippaade. Maaku: \"Addee Tawreetaare nden janngon nde, si on laatiima goonguЙ“e"
  3,94,"Kala fefindiiЙ—o fenaande [dammbi] e Alla Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,95,"Maaku: \"Alla goongii. Jokke diina Ibraahiima kan; ooГұiika [gaa diinaaji mehre], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en sirkooЙ“e"
  3,96,"Pellet, aranndu e Suudu waЙ—anaandu yimЙ“e Й“en, ko ndun wondu Bakkata; barkinaandu e peewal wonannde Winndere nden"
  3,97,"Ino e mayru Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e : darorde Ibraahiima nden. Kala naatuЙ—o e mayru, o laatoo hooliiЙ—o. No woodani Alla e dow yimЙ“e Й“en hajjugol ka Suudu [hormaandu], wonannde on hattanЙ—o e mayru laawol. Kala on yedduЙ—o, pellet, Alla ko YonndiniiЙ—o e winndere nden"
  3,98,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko yeddanton Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Alla ko SeediiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  3,99,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, ko falotoЙ—on e laawol Alla ngol, on gomЙ—inЙ—o HiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұanЙ—e hara ko on seediiЙ“e! Alla wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e ko golloton kon"
  3,100,"Hey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on Й—oftike fedde e Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte, Й“e ruttay on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal mon"
  3,101,"E ko honno yeddirton nde tawnoo Aayeeje Alla Й—en no janngeede e dow mooЙ—on, NulaaЙ—o Makko on kadi no hakkunde mo'on? Kala on mooliiЙ—o e Alla, gomЙ—ii o fewnaama e laawol foccii ngol"
  3,102,"Hey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, huliree Alla no O Haaniri hulireede, wata on maayu dey, si wanaa hara ko on jebbiliiЙ“e"
  3,103,"Jogitee Й“oggol Alla ngol on denndaangal, wata on sertu. JaЕӢtoЙ—on Neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on nde laatinoЙ—on ayruЙ“e, O Woowindiri hakkunde Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en woЕӢtirЙ—on Neema Makko on siЙ—Й—uЙ“e; on laatioke e tonndu ngayka yiite, O DaЙ—ndi on e magge. ko wano nii Alla ЖҒannginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, bela jo'o, on feeway"
  3,104,"Yo laato e mooЙ—on mofte : noddooje e moЖҙЖҙere, yamirooЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi haЙ—ooЙ“e ko aГұinii. Ko Й“en Й—on woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,105,"Wata on laato wa Й“en sertuЙ“e lurri Й“aawo nde Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in ari e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,106,"Г‘alnde geece rawnata geece goo Й“awla. Si ko Й“en Й“e geece mu'un Й“awli : \"e on yeddu Й“aawo gomЙ—inal mon? MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on yedda"
  3,107,"Si ko Й“en Й“e geece mun rawni, Й“e wonii e nder Yurmeende Alla, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton"
  3,108,"ЖҠee Й—oo, ko Aayeeje Alla, MeЙ—en Janngira Й—e e dow maaЙ—a e goonga. Alla wonaali muuyoowo tooГұe e e winndere he"
  3,109,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  3,110,"On laatike mofte Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude yaltinanaaЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en:hiЙ—on yamiraa ko moЖҙЖҙi haЙ—on ko aГұinii,hiЙ—on gomЙ—ini Alla.Si yimЙ“e Defte Й“en gomЙ—inno,Й—um laatotono moЖҙЖҙere wonannde Й“e.No e maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—imЙ“e, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude ko e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqeebe"
  3,111,"ЖҒe lorrirtaa on si wanaa lorra [Й—emЙ—e]. Si Й“e haЙ“ii on, Й“e hucciЕӢtinany on Й“abbe, hooti Й“e walletaake"
  3,112,"Koyeera faЕӢtike Й“e nokku kala ka Й“e tawaa, si wanaa Й“e Жҙettu ahadi ka Alla e ka yimЙ“e Й“en. ЖҒe hootidi e tikkere immorde ka Alla Й“e huuЙ“iЕӢtiniraa baasal : Й—um non, ko tawde Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yedda Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e wara AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga. ЖҠum non, ko sabu ko Й“e yeddi kon, Й“e laatii jaggitooЙ“e"
  3,113,"ЖҒe wonaali fotayЙ“e. No e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en fedde feewunde : hiЙ“e jannga Aayeeje Alla Й—en saangaaji jemma, hiЙ“e sujja"
  3,114,"HiЙ“e gomЙ—ina Alla e Г‘alannde Sakkitiinde nden, hiЙ“e yamira ko moЖҙЖҙi haЙ—a ko aГұinii, hiЙ“e yaccoo e moЖҙЖҙereeje. ЖҒen ko jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,115,"Huunde woo ko Й“e huuwi e moЖҙЖҙere, Й“e yeddantaake Й—um. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o hulooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,116,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en dunncantaa- Й“e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e lepte Alla Й—en hay huunde. Ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e yiite Й“en : kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton"
  3,117,"Sifa ko Й“e nafqata kon e Й—am nguurndam aduna; no wa'i wa henndu, no e mayru Й“uuЙ“ol, ndu hawri e coГұal yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e, ndu halka mba[ngesa]. Alla TooГұaali Й“e, si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұi"
  3,118,"Hey mon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on jogito weldiiЙ“e ko woori on : Й“e raЙ“Й“indinaЕӢtaako on e fii bonnugol on. ЖҒe yelike nde tampoton. GomЙ—ii ngayngu ngun feeГұirii ka kunndule maЙ“Й“e, ko ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en suuЙ—i kon Й“uri mawnude.GomЙ—ii Men ЖҒannginanii on Aayeeje Й—en, si on laatike haqqilooЙ“e"
  3,119,"Onon Й“ee, hiЙ—on yiЙ—i Й“e kamЙ“e Й“e yiЙ—aa on. HiЙ—on gomЙ—ini Deftere nden fow, si Й“e hawrii e mo'on, Й“e wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii\", si Й“e weddike, Й“e ЕӢatana on kolli immorde e tikkere. Maaku: \"Maayee e tikkere mon\", pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e"
  3,120,"Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii on, metta Й“e, si bone kadi heЙ“ii on, Й“e weltora Й—um. Si on muГұГұike on gomЙ—ii, pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en lorrataa on hay huunde. Pellet, Alla ko HuuЙ“itiiЙ—o golle maЙ“Й“e"
  3,121,"Tuma nde dawnoЙ—aa ka Й“eynguure maaЙ—a, hiЙ—a werna muumini en tommborЙ—e hare. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  3,122,"Tuma nde feddeeji Й—iЙ—i e mo'on himmu no, nde cooyoton, ko Alla non woni GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e. Ko Alla woni ko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haani hoolorde"
  3,123,"GomЙ—ii Alla Wallii on Гұalnde Badri, tawi ko on hoyЙ“e. Hulee Alla, belajo'o on yettay [Mo]"
  3,124,"Nde maakanaynoЙ—aa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Enee, yonaЕӢtaa on nde Joomi mo'on Й“eydanta on Malaa'ikaaЙ“e guluuje tato jippinaaЙ“e"
  3,125,"Pellet, si on muГұГұike on gomЙ—ii, e arday on hawjere maЙ“Й“e, Й—um Й—oo, Joomi mo'on no ЖҒeydira on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandinaaЙ“e"
  3,126,"Alla WaЙ—iraali Й—um si wanaa wewlere wonannde on, e no Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en Й—eeЖҙira Й—um. Ballal iwrataa si wanaa ka Alla, On FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,127,"Ko fii yo O TaЖҙu fedde e Й“en yedduЙ“e maa O Wirta Й“e, Й“e ruttoo ko Й“e sooyuЙ“e"
  3,128,"Laatanaaki ma e fiyaake on hay e huunde : maa O JaЙ“an Й“e tuubuubuyee, maa O Leptu Й“e, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГұooЙ“e"
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana on mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko Haforoowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  3,130,"Hey mon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Гұaamu ribaa, cowalle sowaaЙ—e. Hulee Alla, belajo'o, on malete"
  3,131,Hulee ngen yiite maranaange Й“en heeferЙ“e
  3,132,"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, belajo'o, on yurmete"
  3,133,"Yaccee faade e haforanal immorde ka Joomi mo'on e Aljanna, yannji Makko ndin no fota [e yaajeendi] kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, o maranaama Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  3,134,"ЖҒen nafqooЙ“e ka neweende e ka saЙ—teende neweende, e Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e tikkere, e Й“en yaafotooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en. Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,135,"e Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e huuwii panЕӢkare maa Й“e tooГұii ko'e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndita Alla Й“e insinanoo junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in. E ko hommbo haforata si wanaa Alla? Hara Й“e deppitaaki e ko Й“e huuwi kon, tawa hiЙ“e anndi"
  3,136,"ЖҒen Й—on, njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ko yaafuyee immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e Aljannaaji : no ila e ley majji, canЙ—i, duumotooЙ“e ton. MoЖҙЖҙii mbarjaari gollooЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  3,137,GomЙ—ii yawtii ado mon Й—ate. Yahee ka leydi ndaaron hol no battane fennunooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo
  3,138,"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko ЖҒanngannduyee wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, e peewal e waaju wonannde gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  3,139,"Wata on lo'ino, wata on suno, ko onon woni toowuЙ“e Й“en, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  3,140,"Si barme heЙ“ii on, gomЙ—ii barme sugu mun heЙ“ii yimЙ“e Й“en. ЖҠii ГұalЙ—i, MeЙ—en Yiltindira Й—i hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, e fii no Alla Anndira gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, O Jogitoo e mooЙ—on seedatooЙ“e. Alla YiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,141,e fii yo Alla LaЙ“Й“in Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e O Halka heeferЙ“e Й“en
  3,142,Kaa on sikku on naatay Aljanna hara Alla Anndaali Й“en tiЙ—niiЙ“e e mooЙ—on O Annda muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en
  3,143,"GomЙ—ii on laatike hiЙ—on yeloo maayde nden ado on hawrude e mayre, gomЙ—ii on yi'ii nde hiЙ—on ndaara"
  3,144,"Muhammadu wonaali si wanaa NulaaЙ—o : gomЙ—ii feЖҙЖҙii ko adii mo NulaaЙ“e. E si o faatike maa o waraama, on waylitoto e baЙ—te [keeferaaku] mo'on ? Kala waylitiiЙ—o e baЙ—te mu'un, o lorrirtaa Alla hay e huunde, arma Alla YoЙ“ita Й“en jaarnooЙ“e [Mo]"
  3,145,"Laatanaaki wonki nde ki maayata si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Ko winndaaЙ—um [waЙ—anaa] lajal. Mo faandike njoЙ“di aduna, Men Okkay mo e mayri, mo faandike kadi njoЙ“di laakara, Men Okkay mo e mayri, arma Men YoЙ“a jaarnooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,146,"Heewii e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e haЙ“i wondude e maЙ“Й“e jamaaji Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й“e lo'inanooki sabu ko heЙ“i Й“e kon e laawol Alla, Й“e lo'aano Й“e jaasiЕӢkinaaki. Alla no YiЙ—i muГұГұotooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,147,"Konngol maЙ“Й“e laataaki si wanaa wi'ugol: \"Joomi amen, haforan men junuubi amen e fantingol amen nder fiyaake amen, tabiЕӢtinaa teppe amen, wallaa men e dow yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  3,148,Alla Okki Й“e mbarjaari aduna ndin e moЖҙЖҙere mbarjaari laakara. Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en
  3,149,"Hey mon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on Й—oftike Й“en heeferЙ“e, Й“e ruttay on e batte [kaaferaaku] mon, waylitoЙ—on ko on hayruЙ“e(pertube)"
  3,150,"Si ko woni, ko Alla woni GiЙ—o mon, ko KaЕӢko woni moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o e wallooЙ“e Й“e"
  3,151,"Arma Men Welloo kulol e nder Й“erЙ—e Й“en heeferЙ“e, sabu ko Й“e kafidi Alla e kon ko O Jippinanaali hujja. Werde maЙ“Й“e ko ka yiite, bonii werde Й“en tooГұooЙ“e"
  3,152,"GomЙ—ii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde waraynoЙ—on Й“e e DuЕӢayee Makko, haa nde cooyЙ—on lurruЙ—on e fiyaake Й—en, yedduЙ—on Й“aawo o hollii on ko yiЙ—uЙ—on. No e mon Й“en faalaaЙ“e aduna, no e mon kadi Й“en faalaaЙ“e laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e maЙ“Й“e fii yo O Ndaarndo on. GomЙ—ii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ЖҒural e dow gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  3,153,"Tuma nde dogaynoЙ—on on yeЖҙЖҙitoaako hay e gooto, NulaaЙ—o on no noddira on Й“aawo mon. Suno e hoore suno heЙ“i on fii wata on sunito e kon ko laawii on wanaa e kon ko heЙ“i on. Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o e golloton"
  3,154,"Refti O Jippini e mo'on Й“aawo annde nden, hoolaare : ЕӢoЕӢre, hinde sudda fedde e mo'on ; fedde goo, pittaali maЙ“Й“e no aanini Й“e, hiЙ“e sikka Alla ko wanaa goonga ; sikke yimЙ“e majjere, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Hara no woodani men e fiyaake Й—en goЙ—Й—um ?\" Maaku: \"Pellet, fiyaake Й—en fow ko Alla woodani\". HiЙ“e suuЙ—a e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko Й“e feГұГұinantaa ma, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Si tawno no woodannoo men e fiyaake Й—en goЙ—Й—um, men waretanooke Й—oo\". Maaku: \"Hay si tawno on wonno ka cuuЙ—i mon, feeГұayno Й“en Й“e Alla Winndi e dow mun maayde ka lelorЙ—e maЙ“Й“e\", e fii yo O LaЙ“Й“in ko woni Й“erЙ—e mon. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e"
  3,155,"Pellet, Й“en dogunooЙ“e e mo'on Гұalnde koneeli Й—in Й—iЙ—i fottunoo, anndu pellet, ko seytaane fergitiЙ“e sabu yoga e ko Й“e faggitii. GomЙ—ii Alla Yaafike Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o MuГұoowo"
  3,156,"Hey mon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on wa'u wa Й“en heeferЙ“e Й“e wi'ani siЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en : \"Si Й“e yehii ka leydi, maa Й“e laatike haЙ“ooЙ“e, si Й“e laatino ka amen goo, Й“e waretanooke\", ko fii yo Alla WaЙ—ir Й—um Й—on nimse ka Й“erЙ—e mo'on, Alla ko RentuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  3,157,"Hay si on wara e fii laawol Alla maa on maayii, ko yaafuyee immorde ka Alla e yurmeende Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e mooЙ“ata"
  3,158,"Si on maayii maa on waraama, pellet, ko ka Alla mooЙ“eteЙ—on"
  3,159,"Ko sabu yurmeende imoorde ka Alla newaniЙ—aa Й“e. Si laatino saЙ—tuЙ—o tikka Й“erndeejo, Й“e lancotono Й“e iwa takko maa. Yaafo Й“e insinanoЙ—aa Й“e, diisinoЙ—aa Й“e e fiyaake Й—en. Si a fellitii, fawo e Alla. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i fawotooЙ“e Й“en [e Makko]"
  3,160,"Si Alla Wallii on fooloowo on alaa., si O Hoynii on ko hommbo wallata on Й“aawo Makko? Ko e Alla woni ko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haani fawaade"
  3,161,"Laatanaaki Annabaajo woo nde o janfotoo. Kala janfiiЙ—o o addoyay ko o janfii kon Г‘alnde Darngal.Hooti woЕӢkii kala yoЙ“ee njoЙ“di ko ki faggitii, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  3,162,E ko on jokkuЙ—o welayee Alla on wa'ata wa on hootiduЙ—o e tikkere immornde ka Alla kadi werde makko nden ko jahannama? nge bonii ruttorde
  3,163,"KamЙ“e ko Й“e darjaaji ka Alla, Alla ko ji*oowo ko Й“e gollata kon"
  3,164,"GomЙ—ii Alla MoЖҙЖҙike e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, tuma nde O Imminnoo e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, himo janngana Й“e Aayeeje Makko, himo laЙ“Й“ina Й“e, himo anndina Й“e Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal, hay si Й“e woniino adii nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  3,165,"E nde musiiba heЙ“unoo on, gomЙ—ii on heЙ“iino yeru mun Й—iЙ—i, wi'uЙ—on: \"No Й—um woniri?!\" Maaku: \"ЖҠum ko immorde e pittaali mo'on\". Pellet, Alla ko HaЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  3,166,"Ko heЙ“i on kon Гұalnde dente Й—en Й—iЙ—e fottunoo, ko e DuЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Alla, e fii no Alla Anndira gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  3,167,"e no O Anndira Й“en naafiqiiЙ“e, Й“e wi'anaa: \"Aree haЙ“on fii laawol Alla ngol maa duГұon\". ЖҒe wi'i: \"Si meЙ—en anndunoo hare men jokkay on\". KamЙ“e nden Гұalnde, ko keeferaaku ngun Й“urnoo Й“aЙ—taade e dii gomЙ—iЙ—al ngal : hiЙ“e wowlira kunndule maЙ“Й“e ko alaa e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude ko Й“e soomi"
  3,168,"ЖҒen wi'anЙ“e siЙ—Й“e mun, Й“e jooЙ—ii: \"Si tawno Й“e Й—oftino men, Й“e waretanooke\". Makku: \"Pottinee maayde nden e pittaali mo'on si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  3,169,"Wata a sikku Й“en waraaЙ“e fii laawol Alla ngol ko maayuЙ“e, ko woni: ko wuuruЙ“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e arsikee"
  3,170,"hiЙ“e weltori ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko, hiЙ“e wewlira Й“en [siЙ—Й“e] maЙ“Й“e Й“e Й“e hawraali e mu'un Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, wonnde kulol alanaa Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni ko sunoytoo"
  3,171,"HiЙ“e wewlira( weltoro) neema immorde ka Alla e Й“ural. E wonnde pellet, Alla yeebataako njoЙ“di gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  3,172,"ЖҒen nootiiЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde barmeere nden heЙ“i Й“e. Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e Й“e gomЙ—i, njoЙ“di mawndi"
  3,173,"ЖҒen Й“e yimЙ“e Й“en wi'annoo: \"Pellet yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“anike on, huleeЙ“e\". ЖҠum Й“eydi Й“e gomЙ—inal, Й“e wi': \"Alla yonii men, O moЖҙЖҙii yonndinoraaЙ—o"
  3,174,"ЖҒe ruttodi e neema immorde ka Alla e Й“ural, bone hewtaali Й“e, Й“e jokki yarluyee Alla on. Alla ko Jom-Й“ural mawngal"
  3,175,"Anndee pellet, Й—um mo'on ko seytaane : himo hulЙ“inira Й—um weldiiЙ“e makko Й“en. Wata on hulu Й“e, hulee Lam, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  3,176,"Wata sunine Й“en yaccotooЙ“e e keeferaaku, pellet, Й“en lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Alla YiЙ—i ko nde o waa-sata WaЙ—annde geЙ“al ka laakara. No woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e"
  3,177,"Pellet, Й“en soktitoriiЙ“e keeferaaku ngun gomЙ—inal, Й“e lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,178,"Wata Й“en yedduЙ“e sikku wonnde ko Men Nennirani Й“e kon ko moЖҙЖҙere pittaali Й—in. Anndu pellet, ko Men Nennirani Й“e ko no Й“e Й“eydora bakkaatu. Hino woodani Й“e lepte hoynayЙ—e"
  3,179,"Laatanaaki Alla nde O Accata gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e hoore ko wonЙ—on e mun kon haa O Senndindira soЙ“uЙ—o e laaЙ“uЙ—o. Laatanaaki Alla kadi nde O ЖіelliЕӢta on e ko wirnii kon, si ko woni, Alla no SuЙ“ora e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en on mo O Muuyi. GomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, si on gomЙ—inii on gomЙ—ii, hino woodani on njoЙ“di mawndi"
  3,180,"Wata Й“en wuddirooЙ“e ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko sikku Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere wonannde Й“e. Si ko woni, Й—um ko bone wonannde Й“e. Arma Й“e ЕӢannanoye ko Й“e wuddiri kon Г‘alnde Darngal. Ko Alla woodani ndonndi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  3,181,"GomЙ—ii Allaahu on Nanii konngol Й“en wi'uЙ“e: \"Alla ko baaso menen ko men alЙ—uЙ“e!\". Arma Men winnda ko Й“e wowli kon e wargol Й“e ngol AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga, Men Daala: \"MeeЙ—ee lepte sunna-royta"
  3,182,"ЖҠum waЙ—irii sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla Wonaali TooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,183,"ЖҒen wi'uЙ“e: \"Alla Ahodii e amen wota men gomЙ—in NulaaЙ—o woo haa on addana men Й“aЙ—torЙ—um, yiite no Гұaama Й—um\". Maaku: \"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo ado am addaniino on Й“anngannduyeeji e kon ko wi'uЙ—on, e ko waranЙ—on Й“en si on laatike goognuЙ“e"
  3,184,"Si Й“e fennii ma, gomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo ado maa fennanooma, Й“en adduno e ЖҒanngannduyeeji e ЖҠeri e Deftere jalbuunde"
  3,185,"Kala woЕӢkii meeЙ—ay maayde. Pellet, ko on hunnaЕӢteeЙ“e njoЙ“diiji mon Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal. Kala on pottinaaЙ—o e yiite ngen o naadaa Aljanna, gomЙ—ii o malaama. Nguurda aduna Й—am wonaali si wanaa dakammehun hodaykun"
  3,186,"Ma on jarribore jawle mon Й—en e pittaali mon Й—in, ma on nanir Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en ado mooЙ—o e Й“en sirkuЙ“e lorra Й—uЙ—uka. Si on muГұГұike on gomЙ—ii, pellet, anndee Й—um, ko jeyaaЙ—um e pellite fiyakuuji"
  3,187,"JaЕӢtii tuma nde Alla Жіettunoo Ahadi e okkaaЙ“e Deftere Й“en : \"Ma on Й“annginannde yimЙ“e hara on suuЙ—aali nde\". ЖҒe werlii ndi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“e sodtitori ndi coggel pamarel! Bonii ko Й“e soЙ—titori"
  3,188,"Wata sikke Й“en weltorayЙ“e huunde nde Й“e okkaa, hiЙ“e yiЙ—i nde Й“e yettirtee ko Й“e waЙ—aali, wata sikku Й“en ko daЙ—ayЙ“e lepte Й—en. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,189,Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Alla ko HattanЙ—o kala huunde
  3,190,"Pellet, no e tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e luutondirgol jemma e Гұalorma ngol, ko Aayeeje wonannde Й“en haqqilooЙ“e"
  3,191,"ЖҒen annditooЙ“e Alla ka Й“e darii e ka Й“e jooЙ—ii e ka Й“e lelori becce maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e miijitoo fii tagu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin : \"Joomi amen, A Tagiraali Й—um meere, senayee woodanii Ma, ЖҠaЙ—ndu men lepte yiite"
  3,192,"Joomo amen, pellet, An, Mo NaaduЙ—aa yiite, gomЙ—ii A Hoynii mo. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wallooЙ“e"
  3,193,"Joomi amen, menen men nanii noddoowo no nodda e gomЙ—inal wonnde : \"GomЙ—inee Joomi mon\", men gomЙ—ini. Joomi amen, Haforan men junuubi amen, Motanaa men boneeji amen, mbarda men e gguЙ“e Й“en"
  3,194,"Joomi amen, Okku men ko FoduЙ—aa men kon e dow NulaaЙ“e Maa Й“en, wata A Hoynu men Г‘alnde Darngal. Pellet, An A Lunndotaako fodoore"
  3,195,"Joomi maЙ“Й“e Jaabinani Й“e : Min Mi Yeebataa golle golloowo e mooЙ—on, woni gorko maa debbo, yoga e mooЙ—on iwde e yoga. ЖҒen ferЙ“e yaltinaa ka galleeji mun,Й“e lorraa e Laawol Am ngol, Й“e haЙ“idaa Й“e waraa, ko pellet Min hafratЙ“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e ko pellet Mi Naaday Й“e Aljanna Й—i canЙ—i no ila e mun, Й—um ko njoЙ“di immorde ka Alla, No ka Alla njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙundi. @Corrected"
  3,196,Wata hode yiltondirgol Й“en heeferЙ“e ka leydi
  3,197,"dakammeyon pamaroy, hooti werde maЙ“Й“e nden ko jahannama, nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—o"
  3,198,"Kono Й“en huluЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji, hino ila ley majji canЙ—i ; ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder majji, Й—um ko jipporde immorde ka Alla. Ko woni ka Alla kon moЖҙЖҙani Й—igguЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  3,199,"Pellet, no e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e ko Jippinaa e mon kon, e ko Jippinaa e maЙ“Й“e kon ; yaЕӢkinanii Й“e Alla, Й“e waЙ—titirtaa Aayeeje Alla Й—en coggeloy pamaroy. ЖҒen, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko YaawuЙ—o Гұaawoore"
  3,200,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, muГұГұee, fooliron muГұal, tabiton, hulon Alla, belajo'o on maloyete"
  4,1,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Hulee Joomi mon On Tagu on immorde e woЕӢkii wooti, O Tagi immorde e makki sonna makki, O Saaki immorde e Й“en Й—iЙ—o worЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e rewЙ“e. Hulee Alla On Mo naamnanirton sabu mun, [rentoЙ—on kadi] e enЙ—ammaaje Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow mon Deenoowo"
  4,2,"Jonne wonduЙ“e Й“en jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Wata on waЙ—titir soЙ“e Й—en ko laaЙ“i. Wata on Гұaamu jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en [waЙ—ton Й—um] e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Pellet, Й—um laatike bakkaatu mawЙ—o"
  4,3,"Si on hulee roЕӢkugol nunЙ—ude e wonduЙ“e Й“en, resee ko laaЙ“ani on e rewЙ“e, Й—iЙ—o e tato e nayo. Si on hulii roЕӢkugol nunЙ—ude, waЙ—ee gooto maa Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon ; ko Й—um Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade nde on tooГұu"
  4,4,"Jonniree rewЙ“e Й“en teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en dokkal. Si Й“e anniyanike on goЙ—Й—um e Й—en [teЕӢe] e hoore laaЙ“al woЕӢkii, Гұaamee Й—um, no newanii on Й“uuЙ“ani on"
  4,5,"Wata on jonnitu Й—aye Й“en jawle mon Й—en Й—e Alla WaЙ—irani on dartorЙ“e. Г‘amminee Й“e e majje, holtinon Й“e, wowlanon Й“e konngol moЖҙЖҙol"
  4,6,"Ndaarndee wonduЙ“e Й“en si Й“e yottike desal, si on so'ii e maЙ“Й“e peewal, jonniteeЙ“e jawle maЙ“e Й—en, wata on Гұaamir Й—e faЕӢtinngol e hawjugol Й—oo yo Й“e mawnude. On tawЙ—o ko o galo, yo o naЕӢto, on tawЙ—o ko o baaso, yo o Гұaamir no moЖҙЖҙiri. Si on jonnitiiЙ“e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, seedinee e dow maЙ“Й“e. Alla Yonii Hasboowo"
  4,7,"Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en : geЙ“al immorde e kon ko neene e baaba acci e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en, hino woodani kadi rewЙ“e Й“en : geЙ“al e kon ko neene e baaba acci e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en ; Й—uuЙ—i famЙ—i e mun, ko geЙ“al farlaangal"
  4,8,"Si joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral en e wonduЙ“e Й“en e waasuЙ“e tawaama senndoore nden, okkoreeЙ“e e mun, wowlanon Й“e konngol moЖҙЖҙol"
  4,9,"Yo hulu Й“en, si tawno ko kamЙ“e accunoo Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e geЙ—alЙ“e lo'uЙ“e, Й“e hulana Й“en, yo Й“e hulu Alla Й“e wowla konngol sawaaba=peewngol"
  4,10,"Pellet, Й“en ГұaamirooЙ“e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore tooГұee, pellet ko Й“e woni Гұaamude kon Й“e waЙ—a e deedi maЙ“Й“e, ko yiite, arma Й“e naata huЙ“Й“unge"
  4,11,"Alla no Yamira on e fii Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en : hino woodani gorko yeru ngeЙ—u rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Si Й“e laatike rewЙ“e Й“urЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e ko o acci. Si o laatike gooto, hino woodani mo feccere. Hino woodani neene e baaba makko gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e jeegobal, immorde e ko o acci, si tawii himo mari Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si o maraa Й“iЙ—Й—o, mawЙ“e makko Й“en roni mo, hino woodani yumma makko tataЙ“al. Si tawii himo mari neene-gootooЙ“e, hino woodani yumma makko jeegaЙ“al. ЖҒaawo siinugol wasiyee mo o wasiyii maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande nde o Гұawlinoo. BaabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, on anndaa ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri Й“adoraade on nafa. ЖҠum ko farilla immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,12,"Hino woodani on feccere e ko rewЙ“e mon acci, si tawii Й“e maraa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si tawii hiЙ“e mari Й“iЙ—Й—o, hino woodani on nayaЙ“al e kon ko Й“e aaci, Й“aawo siinugol wasiyee mo Й“e wasiyii maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande [maЙ“Й“e]. Hino woodani rewЙ“e mon Й“en nayaЙ“al e kon ko accuЙ—on, si tawii Й“iЙ—Й—o alanaa on. Si tawii hiЙ—on mari Й“iЙ—Й—o, hino woodani Й“e jeetataЙ“al e kon ko accuЙ—on, Й“aawo siinugol wasiyee mo wasiyiЙ—on maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande [mon]. Si wonii gorko no ronee rona-jala maaЙ—um debbo, hara himo mari neene-gooto gorko maa debbo, hino woodani kala maЙ“Й“e jeegaЙ“al. Si Й“e laatike Й“urЙ“e Й—um e Й—uuЙ—ude, kamЙ“e ko hawtuЙ“e ka tataЙ“al, Й“aawo wasiyee wasiyaaЙ—o maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande nde wonaa lorraynde. ЖҠum ko Wasiyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  4,13,"ЖҠin ko Keeri Alla. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o naaday mo Aljannaaji, canЙ—i no ila e ley majji : ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal. @Corrected"
  4,14,"Kala on yedduЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o jaggiti Keeri Makko Й—in, O Naaday mo yiite nge o luttata e muuЙ—um ; hino woodani mo lepte hoynooje"
  4,15,"ЖҒen huuwooЙ“e paЕӢkare immorde e rewЙ“e mon Й“en, seedinee e maЙ“Й“e nayo jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on. Si Й“e seedike, jogiteeЙ“e ka cuuЙ—i haa maayde nden hunna Й“e, maa Alla WaЙ—ane Й“e laawol [yaltirngol]"
  4,16,"ЖҒen Й—iЙ—o huuwuЙ“e fijuЙ“e [paЕӢkare Й—en] e mo'on, lorree Й“en. Si Й“e tuubii Й“e moЖҙЖҙinii, Й—uurnoЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatike JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,17,"Anndee tuubuubuyee on ka Alla, ko wonannde Й“en gollirooЙ“e bone sabu majjere, refti Й“e tuuba ka Й“adii. ЖҒen Й—on, Alla JaЙ“anay Й“e tuubuubuyee. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,18,"Tuubuubuyee alanaa Й“en gollirooЙ“e bone haa tuma maayde nden arani gooto e maЙ“Й“e o wi'a : \"Min mi tuubii jooni\", wanaa kadi Й“en maayooЙ“e hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e heeferaaЙ“e. ЖҒen Й—on, Men Hebilanii Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  4,19,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, dakantaako on nde ronirton rewЙ“e Й“en doolugol, wata on laagu Й“e fii yo on heЙ“tu yoga e ko okkunoЙ—on Й“e, si wanaa hara Й“e waЙ—u paЕӢkare Й“annguЙ—o. Wonndiree e maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Si on aГұii Й“e, hino jortaa nde aГұoton huunde, Alla WaЙ—a e mayre moЖҙЖҙere Й—uuЙ—unde"
  4,20,"Si on yiЙ—ii waЙ—titude debbo nokku debbo goo, hara hiЙ—on jonni goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e jawdi [heewundi], wata on jaЙ“itu e mayri hay e huunde. E on jaЙ“irayndi hoore bagamma e bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,21,"Ko honno Жҙettirton ndi, gomЙ—ii yoga e mon yottike e yoga, Й“e jogitike e mon ahadi tekkundi"
  4,22,"Wata on resu Й“en Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mon resi e suddiiЙ“e si wanaa Й—um ko feЖҙЖҙunoo. Pellet, Й—um laatinoke paЕӢkare e hutaare e bonnde laawol"
  4,23,"Harminanaama on : neeniraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e jiwЙ“e mon Й“en, e banndiraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e yaayiraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e neeniraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka dewol, e jiwЙ“e yumma gooto mon [gorko], e jiwЙ“e banndiraawo mon, e neeniraaЙ“e mon muynimЙ“e on, e banndiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka muynan, e neeniraaЙ“e Й“eynguuli mon, e njutteeЙ“e mon wonЙ“e ka cuuЙ—i mon iwЙ“e e Й“eynguuli mon Й“e naatiduЙ—on e suudu ; si tawii non on naatidaali e maЙ“Й“e suudu, bakkaatu fawaaki on [e resugol Й“en], e [rewЙ“e] daganiiЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en iwЙ“e ka keeci, e nde mooЙ“indirton hakkunde neene-gootooЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, si wanaa Й—um ko yawtunoo. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,24,"E saЕӢiiЙ“e Й“en ka rewЙ“e, si wanaa Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on ka Гұaame mon. ЖҠum ko Farilla Alla e dow mooЙ—on. Daginanaama on ko woni Й“aawo Й“en Й—on, nde Й—aЙ“Й“itorЙ“e jawle mon hara ko on saЕӢiiЙ“e wanaa on jinndooЙ“e. Kala mo dakmitorЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e desal : jonniteeЙ“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Ko farilla. Bakkaatu fawaaki e fii ko yarlondirЙ—on e mun Й“aawo farilla on. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,25,"Kala e mooЙ—on mo hattaaaki feere resugol seЕӢiiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e, ko [resugol] Й“en Й“e jeytirЙ—on Гұaame mon, immorde e curbaaЙ“e mon gomЙ—imЙ“e. Alla no Anndai gomЙ—inal mon ngal. Yoga e mon ko e yoga ResireeЙ“e duЕӢayee yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, jonniron Й“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en no moЖҙЖҙiri. SaЕӢiiЙ“e hara wanaa jinndooЙ“e njaatoo. Si Й“e seaЕӢike Й“e addii paЕӢkare, no fawii Й“e feccere ko fawii saЕӢiiЙ“e rimЙ“e Й“en e lepte. ЖҠum, ko fii on huluЙ—o e mo'on yanugol e jeeno. Ko nde muГұГұotoЙ—on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Alla Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,26,"Allaahu On no Faandii ЖҒannginanngol on O Fewna on e laawi Й“eya adinooЙ“e on, O JaЙ“ana on tuubuubuyee. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,27,"Alla no Faala nde O JaЙ“aЕӢta on tuubuubuyee, Й“en jokkuЙ“e mbeleeЙ—e faalaa nde ooГұorton ooГұannde mawnde"
  4,28,"Alla no YiЙ—i Hayfinanta on, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke tagaama ko o lo'uЙ—o"
  4,29,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Гұaamir jawle mon Й—en hakkunde mooЙ—on e mehre, si wanaa hara ko e njulaaku ngu welaЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Wata on waru pittaali mon Й—in. Pellet, Alla Laatike HinnotooЙ—o on"
  4,30,"kala huuwuЙ—o Й—um e hoore ngaynu e tooГұe, aray Men Naada mo yiite : Й—um laatike newaniiЙ—um Alla"
  4,31,"Si on woЙ—Й—itike [bakkaatu] mawЙ—i Й—i haЙ—aЙ—on Й—in e mun, Men Heefanay on boneeji mon Й—in, Men Naadira e naatirgal teddungal"
  4,32,"Wata on yelo ko Alla ЖҒurniri yoga e mon dow yoga. Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en geЙ“al immorde e ko Й“e faggitii kon, hino woodani kadi rewbe begeЙ“al immorde e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Tororee Alla immorde e ЖҒural Makko. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  4,33,"Wonannde kala Men WaЙ—anii Й—um ronooЙ“e [heftuЙ“e] e Й—um ko jibimЙ“e Й“en acci, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e ; e Й“en Й“e ahodunoЙ—on e mun : jonneeЙ“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal. Pellet, Alla Laatike ko O SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde"
  4,34,"WorЙ“e Й“en ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e [e daЕӢkiitagol] rewЙ“e Й“en, sabu ko Alla ЖҒurniri kon yoga maЙ“Й“e e hoore yoga, e sabu kon ko wintii e jawle maЙ“Й“e. [rewЙ“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, ko yaЕӢkiniiЙ“e reenotooЙ“e ka wirnii, sabu kon ko Alla Reenini Й“e.ЖҒen [rewЙ“e] Й“e huloton dartagol(cuwtagol) mun : waajeeЙ“e, feronЙ“e ka ndaЙ—Й—udiiji, piyonЙ“e. Si Й“e Й—oftike on, wata on aЙ“Й“ir e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol ! Pellet, Alla Laatike ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o"
  4,35,"Si on hulii lurral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, imminee Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e gorko on e Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e debbo on. Si Й“e faandike moЖҙЖҙinngol, Alla Hawrindinay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  4,36,"Rewee Alla wata on kafidu e Makko hay huunde. JibimЙ“e on Й“en moЖҙЖҙoЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e, e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral'en, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e waasuЙ“e Й“en, e kawtaljo jom-Й“adondiral, e kawtal baЕӢЕӢe, e wonndiЙ—Й—o baЕӢЕӢe, e Й“ii laawol, e Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa kala on laatiiЙ—o ГұaaЖҙoowo mantotooЙ—o"
  4,37,"ЖҒen Й“e no wudda, Й“e yamira yimЙ“e Й“en nguddam, Й“e suuЙ—a kon ko Alla okki Й“e e ЖҒural Makko. Men Maranii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje"
  4,38,"E Й“en Й“e no nafqira jawle mun Й—en ka yiinorgol yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa Alla wanaa Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Kala on mo seytaane wonani Й—um ciЕӢkotaaЙ—o : haray o bonii ciЕӢkodaaЙ—o"
  4,39,E ko honЙ—um fawinoo Й“e si Й“e gomЙ—inno Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden Й“e nafqi e kon ko Alla Arsike Й“e ? Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Й“e
  4,40,"Pellet, Alla TooГұirtaa yeru jarra-hun, si wonii ko moЖҙЖҙere, O Soway nde, O Okka immorde ka Mokko njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,41,"Ko honno si tawii Men Addoyii immorde e kala mofte seeditotooЙ—o, Men Adde e dow Й“ee Й—oo ko a seeditotooЙ—o"
  4,42,"Nden Г‘alnde, heeferЙ“e Й“n e yedduЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o on yeloto hara nun Й“e fonndeteno e leydi ndin, Й“e suuЙ—ataa Alla yeewtere"
  4,43,"Ko onon yo gimЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Й“aЙ—to julde den hara ko on siwruЙ“e haa anndon ko wowloton ; wanaa ka modduЙ—on e lonngal, si wanaa hara ko on taЖҙitooЙ“e laawol haa laЙ“Й“inoЙ—on. Si on laatike nawnuЙ“e, maa hiЙ—on e hoore jahal, maa Й“aawo hoggo arii goЙ—Й—o e mon(yaadon dow wuro), maa on soccondirii e rewЙ“e Й“en on heЙ“aali ndiyam, taamoree mbullaari(leydi) laaЙ“undi : mowlon geece mon Й—en e juuЙ—e mon Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Yawtanoowo"
  4,44,"E a yi'aali faade e Й“en okkaaЙ“e geЙ“al e Й—efte Й—en, hiЙ“e sooda majjere nden, hiЙ“e faalaa nde majjoton laawol [foccondirngol] ngol"
  4,45,"Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude ayЙ“e mon Й“en. Alla yonii GiЙ—o, Alla yonii Ballo"
  4,46,"Hino e Й“eya alyahuudaaЙ“e waylooЙ“e konngol ngol e nokku maggol Й“e wi'a: \"Men nanii men yeddii ; heЙ—o ko wanaa nannateeЙ—o, aynu men\", ka hallugol Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun Й“e wi'ayno : \"Men nanii men Й—oftike nanu ndaaraa\", ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e, Й“ura foccaade. Ko woni tun, Alla HuЙ—irii Й“e geddi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa si wanaa seeЙ—aa"
  4,47,"Ko onon yo Й“eya okkanooЙ“e Defte, gomЙ—inee nden nde Men Jippini googinnde Й—en wonЙ—e ka mon, ado Men Mehude geece [mon Й—en] Men RuttiraЙ—e Й“abbe majje, maa Men HuЙ—ira Й“e wano Men HuЙ—irnoo non yimЙ“e asewe Й“en. Fiyaake Alla on Laatke LaatiЕӢteeЙ—um"
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidoowo Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii o fepandiima bakkaatu mawЙ—o"
  4,49,"E a yi'aali Й“en Й“e no laЙ“Й“ina pittaali maЙ“Й“e ? Ko woni, Ko Alla LaЙ“Й“iЕӢta on Mo O Muuyi, Й“e tooГұoytaake yeru gurun tamaro"
  4,50,Ndaarii ko hol no Й“e woni fefindoraade e Alla fenaade ! ЖҠum Й—on yonii bakkaatu feeГұuЙ—o
  4,51,"E a yi'aali faade e Й“en okkanooЙ“e geЙ“al ka Deftere, hiЙ“e gomЙ—ina ndaaro e bewinayЙ—i Й—in, hiЙ“e wi'ana Й“en heeferЙ“e : \"Ko Й“ee Й—oo Й“uri feewude laawol e dii Й“eya gomЙ—ime"
  4,52,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla HuЙ—i Й“en, kala mo Alla HuЙ—i, a heЙ“aЕӢtaa mo ballo"
  4,53,"Kaa woodamЙ“e geЙ“al immorde e laamu ? Ountuma, Й“e okkataano yimЙ“e Й“en yeru hufol tamaro"
  4,54,"Kaa Й“e aГұay yimЙ“e Й“en e ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko ? GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Й“eynguure Ibraahiima nden Deftere e Faltaare, Men Okki Й“e Laamu Mawngu"
  4,55,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e on gomЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi on faddiiЙ—o nde. Jahannama yonii huЙ“Й“aynge"
  4,56,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, aray Men Naada Й“e yiite : tuma kala guri maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“enndi, Men WaЙ—titana Й“e guri goo fii no Й“e meeЙ—ira lepte Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,57,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, aray Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji canЙ—i, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ndeer ton poomaa hino woodani Й“e ton rewЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Men Naada Й“e Й—owdi duumiindi. @Corrected"
  4,58,"Pellet, Alla no Yamira on tottoton koolaaje Й—en faade e yimЙ“e majje Й“en, e si on Гұaaway hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en nde Гұaawirton nunЙ—al. Pellet, ko Alla Waajorta on kon labaama. Pellet, Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  4,59,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й—oftee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on e joomiraaЙ“e yamiroore Й“en e mooЙ—on. Si on pooЙ—ondirii e huunde, ruttee nde ka Alla e ka NulaaЙ—o on, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude Й“uri labeede battane"
  4,60,"E a yi'aali Й“en Й“e no aaЖҙoo wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—inii kon ko Jippinaa e maaЙ—a e kon ko Jippinaa ado maaЙ—a? HiЙ“e faalaa nde Й“e Гұaawinoytoo ka bewinayЙ—i Й—in, gomЙ—ii le Й“e yamiraama nde Й“e yeddata Й—i. Seytaane non hino faalaa majjinnde Й“e majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  4,61,"Si Й“e wi'anaama : \"Aree faade e kon ko Alla Jippini e faade e NulaaЙ—o on\", a yi'ay naafiqi en no faddoo e maaЙ—a faddagol"
  4,62,"Ko honno [wonirta] si tawii musiiba heЙ“irii Й“e sabu ko Й“e ardiniri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e ara e maaЙ—a hiЙ“e woondira Alla : \"Men faandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙinngol e hawrinndinal"
  4,63,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla Anndi ko woni ndeer Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й—uurno gaay maЙ“Й“e, waajoЙ—aa Й“e, wowolanna Й“e konngol yottotongol ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e"
  4,64,"Men Nuliraali NulaaЙ—o [woo] si wanaa fii yo o Й—ofte e DuЕӢayee Alla. Hara nun tuma Й“e tooГұunoo pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e aruno ma Й“e insinii e Alla, NulaaЙ—o on insinanii Й“e, Й“e tawayno Alla ko JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, jumotoodo"
  4,65,"Hey, Mi Woondirii Joomi maaЙ—a, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa haa Й“e Гұaawinora maa huunde ko yani hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e heЙ“ataa Й“itteende ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e e kon ko ГұaawuЙ—aa, Й“e jebbiloo jebbilagol"
  4,66,"Hara nun Men Farluno e maЙ“Й“e wonnde : \"Waree pittaali mon Й—in\", maa \"yalton e galleeji mon\", Й“e waЙ—ataano Й—um si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e huuwuno kon ko Й“e waajoranoo, Й—um laatotono moЖҙЖҙere wonannde Й“e, Й“ura tiiЙ—ude kadi tabital"
  4,67,"nden tuma, Men Okkayno Й“e immorde ka Amen, njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,68,Men Fewnayno Й“e laawol focciingol
  4,69,"Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o on : Й“en Й—on wonndoyay e Й“en Й“e Alla Neemini immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e, e goonguЙ“e, e sahiddinnooЙ“e, e moЖҙЖҙube. ЖҒen Й—on moЖҙЖҙii wonndiiЙ“e"
  4,70,"Ngal Й—on ЖҒural ko immorde ka Alla, Alla Yonii AnnduЙ—o"
  4,71,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, jogitee reЕӢtorЙ—i mon Й—in, runnjon ko on sertuЙ“e maa runnjon on rentuЙ“e"
  4,72,"Hino e mo'on on nennotooЙ—o, si musiiba heЙ“ii on, o wi'a : \"GomЙ—ii Alla Neeminii e am, nde tawnoo mi laatodanooki e maЙ“Й“e ceediiЙ—o"
  4,73,"Si tawii heЙ“ii on ЖҒural immorde ka Alla, ma o wi'a wa si tawii meeЙ—aali laataade hakkunde mon giggol : \"Ee jalla am si mi tawdano e maЙ“Й“e ! Mi malee malal mawngal"
  4,74,"Yo haЙ“ide fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“en Й“e no sooditira guurdam aduna Й—am laakara on ! Kala on haЙ“idaaЙ—o fii laawol Alla ngol o waraa maa o fooli, arma Men Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,75,"E ko heЙ“i on, on haЙ“idetaake fii laawol Alla ngol ? e Lo'inaaЙ“e Й“en ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e, e ka fayЙ“e, Й“en Й“e no wi'a: \"Joomi amen, Yaltin men e ndee saare nde yimЙ“e mun tooГұi, WaЙ—anaa men immorde ka MaaЙ—a giЙ—o, WaЙ—anaa Men immorde ka MaaЙ—a ballo"
  4,76,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e hino haЙ“idee fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“eya heeferЙ“e hino haЙ“idee e laawol Й“ewnayЙ—i Й—in. HaЙ“ee weldiiЙ“e seytaane Й“en : pellet, pewje seytaane Й—en laatike lo'uЙ—e"
  4,77,"E a yi'aali Й“en wi'ananooЙ“e : \"Suree juuЙ—e mon Й—en, Гұimnon julde, jonnon asakal\". Tuma hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, e jaka fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino hulira yimЙ“e Й“en wano Alla hulirtee, maa ko Й“uri tiiЙ—ude e kulol, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko honЙ—um FarlaЙ—aa e dow amen hare ? Ko haЙ—noo Nennitanaa men Й—um haa e lajal Й“adiingal ?\" Maaku : \"Dakamme aduna on ko seeЙ—a, ko laakara on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on hulЙ—o [Alla], on tooГұetaake yeru hufol tamara"
  4,78,"Nokku woo ka laatiЙ—on maayde nden hewtitoto on, hay si on laatike e nder tataaji mahaaЙ—i. Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e wi'a: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko immorde ka Alla\" Si bone heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e wi'a :\"ЖҠum Й—oo ko immorde e maaЙ—a !\" Maaku: \"Kala majji ko immorde ka Alla\". E ko nanngi Й“ee yimЙ“e Й“e Й“attitaako faamude yeewtere"
  4,79,"Huunde woo ko heЙ“u maa e moЖҙЖҙere ko immorde ka Alla, huunde woo ko heЙ“u maa e bone ko immorde e woЕӢkii maa kin. Men Nulii ma wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o. Alla Yonii Seede"
  4,80,"Mo Й—oftike NulaaЙ—o on gomЙ—ii o Й—oftike Alla. Mo huccitii, Men Nulaali ma e dow maЙ“Й“e reenoowo"
  4,81,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"ЖҠoftaare!\", si Й“e yaltii ka maaЙ—a, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e waaliday [e miijo goo] ko woori kon ko maakuЙ—aa. Alla no Winnda kon ko waalidata e mun. ЖҠuurno Й“e fawoЙ—aa e Alla. Alla Yonii HoolorЙ—o"
  4,82,"E Й“ee taskitortaa Qur'aana on ? Sinno nde iwru-nde ko wanaa ka Alla, Й“e tawayno e mayre lurre Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e"
  4,83,"Si arii Й“e e fiyaake immorde e hoolaare, maa kulol, Й“e lollina Й—um. Sinno Й“e ruttuno Й—um e NulaaЙ—o on e Й“en fewjooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e, Й“en Й“ullitayЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e anndayno Й—um. Si wanaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden, on jokkayno seytaane si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e"
  4,84,"HaЙ“u fii laawol Alla ngol, a fawaaka si wanaa hoore-maa. RerЙ—in gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, arma Alla nde Surata doole heeferЙ“e Й“en. Ko Alla Й“uri SaЙ—tude doole, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri SaЙ—tude muusnugol"
  4,85,"Kala on tefuЙ—o tefoore labaande wonay mo geЙ“al e mayre, kala kadi on tefuЙ—o tefoore bonnde wonany mo e mayre geЙ“al. Alla Laatike HattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  4,86,"Si on hiwroraama hiwraango, hiwritoree ko Й“uri ngon Й—on maa rutton ngo. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow kala huunde ko O Hasboowo"
  4,87,"Alla, reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, ma O MooЙ“itoy on Г‘alnde Darngal, sikke alaa e Mayre. E ko hombo Й“uri goongude Alla yeewtere"
  4,88,"Ko waЙ—i on e fii Й“ee naafiqiiЙ“e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i ?! Ko Alla woni UgginЙ—o Й“e sabu ko Й“e faggitii. E on faala fewnude on mo Alla Majjini ? Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a heЙ“antaa mo laawol"
  4,89,"HiЙ“e yeloo sinno on yeddayno wano Й“e yeddiri non, laatoЙ—on fotooЙ“e. Wata on jogito e maЙ“Й“e weldiiЙ“e haa Й“e fera e laawol Alla ngol. Si Й“e huccitii, nanngee Й“e waron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e.Wata on jogito e maЙ“Й“e weldiЙ—Й—o wanaa ballo"
  4,90,"Si wanaa Й“en Й“e hino jokkoo faade e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—un Й“e arii on Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en no Й“iЙ—tanii haЙ“ugol on, maa haЙ“ugol yimЙ“e Й“en. Si Alla Haajuno, O Wurtayno Й“e e dow mooЙ—on, Й“e haЙ“a on. Si Й“e pottitike on, Й“e haЙ“aali on, Й“e werlike kisal e mon, haray Alla WaЙ—anaali on e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol"
  4,91,"Arma tawon woЙ—Й“e goo faandiiЙ“e nde Й“e holnora on Й“e holnora yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Tuma kala nde Й“e ruttitaa e geddi Й—in,Й“e suЖҙЖҙitee e nder majji. Si Й“e pottitaaki on, Й“e werloo kisal e mon, Й“e suri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, nanngee Й“e waron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e. Ko Й“en Й—on mooЙ—on, [woni ke Men] WaЙ—ani on e maЙ“Й“e hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,92,"Haananaa gomЙ—inЙ—o nde o warata gomЙ—inЙ—o si wanaa [hara ko] faljere. On warЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o, yo rinЙ—in daande gomЙ—innde e diya jonneteeЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“en : si wanaa hara Й“en sakkii. Si wonii ko jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e ayЙ“e mon, hara kaЕӢko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, ko rinЙ—ingol daande gomЙ—innde. Si wonii ko jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e, ko diya jonneteeЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e rinЙ—ingol daande gomЙ—innde. On mo hebaali ko : hoorugol lebbi Й—iЙ—i jokkondirЙ—i tuubuubuyee immorde ka Alla. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,93,"Kala warЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o e hoore tewagol, njoЙ“di makko ndin ko Jahannama, luttoowo e nder magge ; Alla Tikkanii mo, O HuЙ—ii mo, O Hebilanii mo lepte mawЙ—e"
  4,94,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on yahii e laawol Alla, Й“annginee [tefon] wata on wi'an on werliiЙ—o e mon kisal : \"Wanaa a gomЙ—inЙ—o\", hiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“a jawdi nguurdam aduna, ko ka Alla konhoyri Й—uuЙ—undi woni. Ko wano non laatornoЙ—on ko adii, Alla Neemini e mon. ЖҒannginee. Pellet, Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  4,95,"GomЙ—imЙ“e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en, hara wanaa joomiraaЙ“e lorra Й“en, fotataa e Й“en tiiЙ—nortooЙ“e e laawol Alla ngol jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“e Й—in. Alla ЖҒurnirii tiiЙ—norЙ“e jawle mun Й—en e woЕӢkiiji mun Й—in, e dow jooЙ“iiЙ“e Й“en, darja. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e Alla Fodii Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, Alla ЖҒurnirii tiiЙ—notooЙ“e Й“en e dow jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,96,"Darjaaji immorde ka Makko, e haforanal, e Hinnayee. Alla Laatike Hafroowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,97,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e Malaa'ika en no warata, hara ko Й“e tooГұuЙ“e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e wi'a : \"Ko e honЙ—um wonunoЙ—on ?!\". ЖҒe wi'a : \"Men laatinoke lo'inanooЙ“e ka leydi\". ЖҒe wi'a : \"Leydi Alla ndin laatanooki yaajundi hanno feron e mayri ?\". ЖҒen Й—on, werde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,98,"Si wanaa Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e immorde ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e, e ka sukaaЙ“e Й“e hattanaa yahdu, Й“e feewataa e laawol"
  4,99,"ЖҒen Й—on, arma Alla Yaafanoo Й“e. Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o, Haforoowo"
  4,100,"Kala feruЙ—o e laawol Alla ngol o taway ka leydi yolЙ—ere Й—uuЙ—unde e yaajeende. Kala yaltuЙ—o e suudu mu'un ko o feruЙ—o faade e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, hooti maayde nden hewtitii mo, gomЙ—ii njoЙ“di makko ndin tabitii ka Alla. Alla Laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,101,"Si on jinndii ka leydi, haray bakkaatu fawaaki on nde ustoton julde nden, si on hulii nde yedduЙ“e Й“en fitiЕӢta on. Pellet, heeferЙ“e Й“en laatanike on ayЙ“e feeГұuЙ“e"
  4,102,"Si a tawdaama e maЙ“Й“e a darnanii Й“e julde, yo fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e darodo e maaЙ—a yo Й“e jogito jogaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ; si Й“e sujjii, yo Й“e wonu Й“aawo mon, yo fedde ndeya nde juulaali aru, yo Й“e juulidu e maaЙ—a yo Й“e jogito reetorЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in e jogaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. YedduЙ“e Й“en yelinoke sinno on welsindotono gaay e jogaaji mon Й—in e doЕӢle mon Й—en, Й“e ooГұoo e mooЙ—on ooГұannde wootere. Bakkaatu fawaaki on si Й—on wonndi e lorra immorde e toЙ“o, maa on laatike nawnuЙ“e nde walliЕӢton jogaaji mon Й—in. Jogitee reЕӢtorЙ—i mon Й—in. Pellet, Alla Hebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje"
  4,103,"Si on gaynii julde nden, jaЕӢtoree Alla e darnnde, e jonnde e ka hoore becce mon. Si on deeЖҙii, ГұiЙ“nee julde nden. Pellet, julde nden laatike e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en farill heeЖҙaa [waqiЕӢtinaa]"
  4,104,"Wata on lo*u e nder Й—aЙ“Й“itugol yimЙ“e Й“en. Si on laatike hiЙ—on naawee, kamЙ“e kadi hiЙ“e naawiree wano naawirteЙ—on, hiЙ—on jortii immorde e Alla ko Й“e jortaaki. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,105,Menen Men Jippinirii Deftere nden e maaЙ—aa e hoore goonga fii yo a Гұaawir hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko Alla Hollu maa. Wata on wonan janfotooЙ“e Й“en wennjanoowo
  4,106,"Insino e Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,107,"Wata a wennjondire fii Й“en janfotooЙ“e pittaali mun. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa on janfotooЙ—o, bakkondinЙ—o"
  4,108,"HiЙ“e suuЙ—oo yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e suuЙ—otaako Alla, Himo Wonndi e maЙ“Й“e tuma Й“e waalaynoo fewjude kon ko O Welaaka e konngol. Alla Laatike HuЙ“indiiЙ—o kon ko Й“e gollata"
  4,109,"Hey mon yo Й“e'e on wennjii fii maЙ“Й“e e Й—am nguurdam aduna, e ko hommbo wennjoyta Alla fii maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, kaa ko hommbo laatanoytooЙ“e fawtiiЙ—o"
  4,110,"Kala on golluЙ—o bone maa o tooГұi hoore makko, hooti o insinii e Alla, o taway Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,111,"Kala kadi faggitiiЙ—o bakkaatu, pellet, ko e hoore makko o woni faggitaade Й—um. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,112,"Kala faggitiiЙ—o goopol maa bakkaatu hooti o bugii Й—um e hoore daЙ—ndiiЙ—o, gomЙ—ii o ronnditike fenaande e bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,113,"Si wanaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a e Yurmeende Makko nden, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e himmirayno majjinngol ma, Й“e alaa e majjinnde si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e lorrirtaama hay e huunde. Alla Jippinii e maaЙ—a Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal, O Anndinii ma huunde nden a anndaano. ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a laatike mawnungal"
  4,114,"MoЖҙЖҙere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere maЙ“Й“e nden, si wanaa on yamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖҙЖҙere maa moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala waЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men HucciЕӢtinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—iinde"
  4,117,"ЖҒe alaa e rewude ko woori Alla, si wanaa [sanamuuji] rewЙ—inaaЙ—i, Й“e alaa e rewude si wanaa seytaane sanndalЙ—iinЙ—o"
  4,118,"Alla HuЙ—ii ndu, ndu wi'i : \"Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaЙ“e maa Й“en geЙ“al farlaangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinoyЙ“e, ma mi yelinoyЙ“e, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e, ma Й“e taЖҙu noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e waylu tagu Alla ngun !\". Kala jogitiiЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o ko woori Alla, gomЙ—ii o hayrii hayrere Й“anngunde"
  4,120,"Himo foda Й“e himo yelina Й“e, seytaane fodaali Й“e si wanaa hodo"
  4,121,"ЖҒen Й—on wemoolorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, Й“e heЙ“irtaa nge daЙ—irde"
  4,122,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, aray Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji canЙ—i : ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton poomaa. Fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla goongude konngol ? @Corrected"
  4,123,"Wonaali ko yelaaji mon Й—in wanaa yelaaji jomЙ“e Defte Й“en. Kala golluЙ—o bone o yoЙ“ete Й—um, o heЙ“anoytaake ko woori Alla giЙ—o wanaa ballo"
  4,124,"Kala golluЙ—o immorde e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, fota ko gorko maa ko debbo, hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, Й“en Й—on naatay Aljanna Й“e tooГұetaake yeru gurun [tamaro]"
  4,125,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude diina haa hewti on jebbilЙ—o yeeso mun ngon Alla, hara ko o moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, o rewi laawol Ibraahiima ruuЙ—iiЙ—o. Alla Jogitike Ibraahiima giЙ—o"
  4,126,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike HuЙ“indiiЙ—o kala huunde
  4,127,"HiЙ“e lamdo maa fii rewЙ“e Й“en, maaku : \"Alla no saggitude on fii Й“en [rewЙ“e], e kon ko jaЕӢngetee e dow mooЙ—on ka Deftere fii Й“en rewЙ“e wonduЙ“e, Й“en Й“e on jonnataa kon ko Й“e farlanaaa, hiЙ—on rerЙ—a fii resugol Й“e, e Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e immorde ka fayЙ“e, e nde daraЕӢtoЙ—on wonduЙ“e Й“en nunЙ—al. Kala ko huuwoton e moЖҙЖҙere, pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Й—um"
  4,128,"Si wonii debbo hulirii moodi makko suwtaade suwtaade maa Й—uurnaare, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtinirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e sulhu.Ko sulhu on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, pittaali Й—in tawdaama ndeereraaku.Si on moЖҙЖҙinii on gomЙ—ii, pellet Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  4,129,"On waawataa nunЙ—ude hakkunde rewЙ“e Й“en hay si on rerЙ—ii. Wata tun on ooГұo kala ooГұannde, accon mo wa yowaaЙ—o. Si on moЖҙЖҙinii on gomЙ—ii, pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,130,"Si Й“e sertii, Alla AlЙ—iniroyay kala maЙ“Й“e immorde e Yaajeende Makko nden. Alla Laatike YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural], Г‘eeЙ—uЙ—o"
  4,131,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli kon e ka leydi. GomЙ—ii Men Ahodinoke e Й“eya okkaaЙ“e Defte ado mon, e onon : \"Hulee Alla !\". Si on yeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  4,132,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii FawtiiЙ—o
  4,133,"Si O Muuyii, O NaЙ“ay on, onon yo yimЙ“e, O Adda woЙ—Й“e goo. Alla Laatike HattanЙ—o e dow Й—um"
  4,134,"Kala tawЙ—o no faandii mbarjaari aduna, ko ka Alla mbarjaari aduna e laakara woni. Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  4,135,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e nunЙ—al seedan- Й“e Alla, hay si ko e dow pittaali mon, maa jinnaaЙ“e mon Й“en maa Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en. Si wonii ko o galo maaЙ—um baaso, ko Alla ЖҒuri Haanndude e maЙ“Й“e. Wata on jokku mbeleeЙ—e, nde nunЙ—oton. Si on waylii maa on Й—uurnike, pellet, Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  4,136,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, gomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e Deftere nde O Jippini e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e Й—en Defte Й—e O Jippini ko adii. Kala yedduЙ—o Alla, e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e Defte Makko Й—en, e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, gomЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  4,137,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, hooti Й“e yeddi, hooti Й“e gomЙ—ini, hooti Й“e yeddi, hooti Й“e Й“eydorii keeferaaku, Alla Laatoraali Yawtanoowo Й“e wanaa O Fewnoowo Й“e e laawol"
  4,138,"Wewlinir naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, wonnde no woodani lepte muusuЙ—e"
  4,139,"ЖҒen Й“e no jogitoo heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—Й“e ko wanaa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ay e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e teddungal ? Pellet, teddungal ngal fow ko Alla Heeranii"
  4,140,"GomЙ—ii O Jippinii e mon ka nder Deftere Si on nanii Aayeeje Alla Й—en no yeddee Й—e jalikitee, wata on jooЙ—odu e maЙ“Й“e haa Й“e jumpana yewtere goo ko woori nden Й—on, si on waЙ—ii Й—um on fotii e maЙ“Й“e\". Pellet, Alla ko MooЙ“oyoowo naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en e heeferЙ“e Й“en ka Jahannama Й“e denndaangal"
  4,141,"ЖҒen habbitantooЙ“e on, si uddital laatanike on immorde ka Alla, Й“e wi'a : \"E, men wonndaano e mo'on ?\", Si geЙ“al laatanike heeferaaЙ“e Й“en, Й“e wi'a : \"E men foolinaano e mooЙ—on men haЙ—i on immorde e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ?\" Alla ko Г‘aawoowo hakkunde mon Г‘alnde Darngal, Alla WaЙ—aЕӢtaa heeferЙ“e Й“en laawol e hoore gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  4,142,"Pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en hino janfaade Alla, Kanko kadi ko O YoЙ“oowo Й“e. Si Й“e immanike julde nden, Й“e immoto ko Й“e aamuЙ“e, hiЙ“e yiinoo e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e jantotaako Alla si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  4,143,"HiЙ“e naЙ“a artira hakkunde Й—um, Й“e alaa e Й“ee Й—oo Й“e alaa e Й“ee Й—aa. Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a heЙ“antaa mo laawol"
  4,144,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on jogitor heeferЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e ko wanaa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. E on faala nde waЙ—anton Alla e dow mooЙ—on hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,145,"Pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en no ka ndenka yiite, a heЙ“antaa Й“e ballo"
  4,146,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e, Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, Й“e jogitii [diina] Alla Й“e laЙ“Й“ini diina maЙ“Й“e kan : Й“en Й—on wonndii e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Arma Alla YeЙ—a gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,147,"Ko honЙ—um Alla WaЙ—ata e leptugol on, si on yettii [Mo] on gomЙ—inii [Mo] ? Alla Laatike Jaarnoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  4,148,"Alla YiЙ—aa ko feeГұi kon e bone immorde e kongol, si wanaa on tooГұaaЙ—o. Alla Laatike Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  4,149,"Si on feГұГұinii moЖҙЖҙere, maa on suuЙ—ii nde maa on yaafike gaay e bone, pellet, Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o HattanЙ—o"
  4,150,"Pellet, Й“en wonЙ“e yeddude Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hiЙ“e faandii nde Й“e senndindirta hakkunde Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hiЙ“e wi'a :\"MeЙ—en gomЙ—ina yoga men yedda yoga\", hiЙ“e faala jogitaade hakkunde Й—um Й—on laawol"
  4,151,ЖҒen Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni yedduЙ“e Й“en tigiri. Men Hebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje
  4,152,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Й“e sen- ndindiraali hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e, Й“en Й—on, arma O YeЙ—a Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin. Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,153,"YimЙ“e Defte Й“en no lamndo maa nde jippintaa e dow maЙ“Й“e Deftere immorde e ka kammu ! GomЙ—ii Й“e lamndinoke Muusaa ko Й“uri Й—um mawnude : Й“e wi'i : \"Hollu Men Alla kene pettan \". Haacaango ngon nanngiri Й“e sabu tooГұe maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Refti Й“e jogitii ngaari ndin Й“aawo nde ko ari Й“e e Й“anngan- nduyeeji. Men Yaafii gaay e Й—um Men Okki Muusaa hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,154,"Men ЖҒamtiri dow maЙ“Й“e Tuur fello ngon sabu ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, Men Wi'ani Й“e :\"Naatiree ka damal ko on naayiiЙ“e\", Men wi'ani Й“e : \"Wata on jaggitu e asewe on\", Men Nanngi e maЙ“Й“e ahadi tekkundi"
  4,155,"Ko sabu firtugol Й“e ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, e yeddugol Й“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, e warugol Й“e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga e wi'gol Й“e :\"ЖҒerЙ—e amen Й—en no sokii\". Si ko woni, Alla Notii e majje sabu keefe-raaku maЙ“Й“e ngun -Й“e gomЙ—intaa si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  4,156,"e sabu keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun, e konngol maЙ“Й“e ngol dow Maryama fenaande mawnde"
  4,157,"e wi'ugol Й“e : \"Menen men warii Iisaa Meme-sella, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, NulaaЙ—o Alla on\". ЖҒe waraali mo, Й“e fetaali mo, ko woni, o nanndinana Й“e. Pellet Й“en Й“en luutondirЙ“e fii makko :Й“e wonii e sikkitaare fii makko. Alanaa Й“e e fii Й—um anndal, si wanaa jokku- gol sikke, Й“e waraano mo e taЖҙoral(yananeede)"
  4,158,"Ko woni, Alla ЖҒamtu mo faade ka Makko. Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,159,"Alaa hay gooto e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, si wanaa o gomЙ—inay mo ado maayde makko nden. Г‘alnde Dargal o laatoto seeditotooЙ—o e hoore maЙ“Й“e"
  4,160,"Ko sabu tooГұe immorde e Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e, Men HarmiannooЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Й“e daginanoo e sabu sakkagol(faddagol) laawol Alla ngol ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  4,161,"e jaЙ“ugol Й“e ngol ribaa, gomЙ—ii Й“e haЙ—aama e Й—um, e Гұaamugol jawle yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore meere. Men Hebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  4,162,"Kono tutiiЙ“e Й“en e ganndal e maЙ“Й“e e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, hiЙ“e gomЙ—ini ko Jippinaa ko e maaЙ—a e kon ko Jippinaa ado maaЙ—a. E ГұiiЙ“nooЙ“e julde Й“en, e tottooЙ“e asakal Й“en, e gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, Й“en Й—on, arma Men Okka Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,163,"Menen Men Wahyinii e maaЙ—a wano Men Wahyiniri e Nuuhu e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo makko. Men Wahyini faade e Ibraahiima, e Ismaa'iila, e Ishaaqa, e Yaaquuba, TaaniraaЙ“e Й“en, e Iisaa, e Ayyuuba, e Yuunusa, e Haaruuna, e Sulaymaana. Men Okki Daawuuda Jabuura"
  4,164,E NulaaЙ“e Й“e Men Fillani maa fii mun ko adii e NulaaЙ“e Й“e Men fillanaaki ma fii mun. Alla Yewtidii e Muusaa Yewtude
  4,165,"NulaaЙ“e wewlinooЙ“e e jertinooЙ“e fii wata hujja wonan yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore Alla Й“aawo NulaaЙ“e Й“en. Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,166,"Kono Alla no Seedii kon ko O Jippini e maaЙ—a, O Jippinirii Й—um Anndal Makko, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en no seeditoo. Alla Yonii Seedee"
  4,167,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, Й“e faddii gaay e laawol Alla ngol, gomЙ—ii Й“e majjii majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  4,168,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e tooГұi, Alla Laatataaka yaafatooЙ—o Й“e, wanaa nde O Fewnata Й“e laawol"
  4,169,"Si wanaa laawol Jahannama ngol, ko luttooЙ“e nder magge poomaa. ЖҠum laatike newiiЙ—um e dow Alla"
  4,170,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o on ardirii e mon goonga immorde e Joomi mon, gomЙ—inee ko moЖҙЖҙere mon. Si on yeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,171,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, wata on Й“urtin ka diina mon, wata on wowlu e hoore Alla si wanaa goonga. Pellet, Mema-sella Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla e Daalol Makko ngol O Werlii e Maryama e ruuhu immorde ka Makko. GomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on wi'u [Alla ko] :\"Tato\". HaЙ—itee, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Anndee Alla ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto. Senayee woodanii Mo nde Й“iЙ—Й—o laatantoo Mo ! Ko Kanko Woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii HoolorteeЙ—o"
  4,172,"Mema-sella on mawnitaaki nde o laatotoo jeyaaЙ—a Alla, wanaa Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“en. Kala Й“urnitiiЙ—o gaay e rewugol Mo o mawnintinii, ma O MooЙ“itoyЙ“e faade ka Makko Й“e denndaangal"
  4,173,"Si tawii ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, O Timminanay Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, O ЖҒeydana e ЖҒural Makko ngol. ЖҒeya Й“urnitiiЙ“e mawnintinii, O LeptayЙ“e lepte muusuЙ—e, Й“e heЙ“anoytaaЙ“e gaanin Alla, giЙ—o wanaa ballo"
  4,174,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! GomЙ—ii hujja arii e mooЙ—on immorde ka Joomi mon, Men Jippinii faade e mooЙ—on annnora Й“annguЙ—o"
  4,175,"Si tawii ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e jogiitii nde, arma O Naada Й“e e Yurmeende immorde ka Makko e ЖҒural, O Fewna Й“e faade e Makko laawol focciingol"
  4,176,"HiЙ“e faltino maa. Maaku : \"Alla no Falta on fii rona-jala : si neЙ—Й—o maayii o alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o himo mari banndiraawo [debbo], no woodani on feccere e kon ko o acci. Kanko kadi o ronay mo si tawii o alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si Й“e laatike Й—iЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e kon ko o acci. Si Й“e laatike siЙ—Й—uЙ“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e, hino woodani gorko on geЙ“al rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Alla no ЖҒannginannde on fii wata on majju. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  5,1,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, hunnee piЙ“e ahadiiji Й—in. NeemoraaЙ—i mummunteeji Й—in hunnanaama on si wanaa kon ko no janngee e dow mooЙ—on, hara wanaa on dagintimЙ“e waaГұugol hara hiЙ—on horminii. Pellet, Alla no Г‘aawa kon ko O Faalaa"
  5,2,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on dagin Sari'aaji Alla Й—in, wanaa lebbi hormaЕӢte Й—in, wanaa haddiyaaji Й—in neldaaЙ—i, wanaa Й—in maandinaaЙ—i, wanaa Й“en hooliiЙ“e [faandii] Suudu HormaЕӢte ndun, hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Й“ural immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e e welayee. Si on dagintinnike [ka hajju maa ka 'umra], waaГұee. Wata ngayngu yimЙ“e duГұu on fii Й“e sakkike on gaay e Suudu HormaЕӢte ndun, nde jaggiton. Wallindiree e dow diggere e gomЙ—al. Wata on wallindiri e hoore bakkaatu e jaggitugol. Hulee Alla. Pellet, Alla ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  5,3,"Harminaama e dow mooЙ—on : jiibe, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, e teewu ngiroowu, e kala ko ewnoraa ko wanaa Innde Alla e kirsol, e Й—eЙ—Й—ii kol, e luubaa(lukkangol) kol, e unii kol, e hawaa kol, e ko Гұanfenji Й—in Гұaami -si wanaa ko hirsuЙ—on, e ko hirsanaa sanamuuji Й—in, e nde senndinorton payanЙ—e Й—en. ЖҠum mooЙ—on ka faasiqoyaagal. Hannde yedduЙ“e Й“en taЖҙike e diina mon kan, wata on hulu Й“e, hulee Lam. Hannde Mi Timminanii on diina mon kan, Mi Timminii e dow mooЙ—on Neemaaji Am Й—in, Mi Welanaama on Lislaamu on diina. Kala on Й“ittiiЙ—o e heege hara wanaa o yawtuЙ—o [ooГұii] e bakkaatu on, pellet, Alla ko Haforowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,4,"HiЙ“e lamndo maa ko honЙ—um Й“e daginanaa ? Maaku : \"Daginanaama on laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, e ko anndinЙ—on immorde e barminayЙ—i, hiЙ—on anndina Й—i ko Alla Anndini on ; Гұaamee e ko Й—i nanngani on, jantoЙ—on Innde Alla e dow muuЙ—um. Hulee Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike YaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  5,5,"Hannde on daginanaama laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in. Г‘aametee okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en no daganii on, Гұaametee mon on no daganii Й“e. E saЕӢiiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e saЕӢiiЙ“e okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en ado mon, si on jonnii Й“e teЕӢeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, [wonon] saЕӢiiЙ“e hara wanaa jeenooЙ“e, wanaa jogitotooЙ“e njaatigi. Kala yeddu- Й—o gomЙ—inal ngal, gomЙ—ii golle makko Й—en bonii, on Й—on ka laakara ko o jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e(pertube) Й“en"
  5,6,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on immanike julde, lootee geece mon Й—en e juuЙ—e mon Й—en haa ka coЙ“Й“uli, maswon ko'e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en haa ka kolЙ“ule. Si on laatike janabante, laЙ“Й“intinee. Si on laatike nawnuЙ“e, maa e hoore laawol, maa Й“aawo hoggo arii gooto e mooЙ—on, maa on memondirii e rewЙ“e Й“en on heЙ“aali ndiyam, taamee e mbullaari laaЙ“undi : mashiron ndi geece mon e juuЙ—e mon. Alla Faandaaki nde O WaЙ—ata e dow mooЙ—on Й“itteende, ko woni, Ko O Faandii, ko laЙ“Й“ingol on, e nde O Timminta Neema Makko on e dow mooЙ—on, belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  5,7,"Annditee Neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on e Ahadi Makko ndi O Ahodi e mooЙ—on tuma wi'unoЙ—on : \"Men nanii men Й—oftike\". Hulee Alla. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  5,8,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, laatee ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e wonannde Alla seeditorayЙ“e nunЙ—al. Wata tikkangol yimЙ“e duГұu on e dow nde on nunЙ—ataa. NunЙ—ee, ko Й—um Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade gomЙ—al ngal. Hulee Alla, pellet, Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o kon ko golloton"
  5,9,"Alla Fodii Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, no woodani haforal e njoЙ“di mawnundi"
  5,10,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e fenni Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, ko yimЙ“e Jahiimi"
  5,11,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, jantee Neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on tuma nde yimЙ“e himmirnoo nde Й“e fontata e dow mooЙ—on juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Alla Suri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en gaay e mooЙ—on. Hulee Alla. Ko e Alla gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en yowitotoo"
  5,12,"GomЙ—ii Alla Nanngi ahadi Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, Men Immini e maЙ“Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i. Allaahu On Daali : \"Min MiЙ—o Wonndi e mooЙ—on : si on ГұiiЙ“nii julde nden, on jonnii asakal ngal, on gomЙ—inii NulaaЙ“e Am Й“en, o teddinii Й“e, on Гұawlii Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙunde, Ma Mi heefan on bonЙ—i mon Й—in, Ma Mi Naadoy on Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji canЙ—i. Kala on yedduЙ—o e mooЙ—on Й“aawo Й—um, gomЙ—ii on majjii laawol fotondirngol ngol\". @Corrected"
  5,13,"Ko sabu firtugol maЙ“Й“e ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin Men HuЙ—irnoo Й“e, Men WaЙ—i Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yooruЙ—e : hiЙ“e waylita konngol ngol gaay e nokku maggol, Й“e yejjiti geЙ“al e kon ko Й“e anndintinanoo e mun. A seerataa hiЙ—a Жҙellitoo e dow janfa iwruka e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e.Yaafano Й“e laaЙ“anaa [Й“e]. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,14,"E Й“en wi'uЙ“e : \"Menen ko men Annasaara\", Men Nanngii ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, Й“e yejjiti kon ko Й“e anndintinanoo e mun. Men Wurti hakkunde maЙ“Й“e ngayngu e konnaagu haa Г‘alnde Darngal. Arma Alla Humpita Й“e kon ko gollaynoo"
  5,15,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, gomЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o Amen on arii on himo Й“annginana on ko Й—uuЙ—i e kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on suuЙ—a ka Deftere, Himo Yaafoo gaay e ko Й—uuЙ—i. GomЙ—ii arii e mooЙ—on Annoora, e Deftere Й“anngunde"
  5,16,"Alla no Fewnira nde on jokkuЙ—o welayee Makko on laawi hisuЙ—i, Himo Yaltina Й“e e niЙ“e faade e Annoora e DuЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Makko, O Fewnna Й“e faade e laawol focciingol"
  5,17,"GomЙ—ii yeddii Й“en wi'uЙ“e : \"Allaahu on ko Mema-sella Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on\". Maaku : \"Ko hommbo waawani Alla goЙ—Й—un si O Faandike nde O Halkata Mema-sella Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, e yumma makko, e ko woni ka leydi kon fow ?\" Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji. Himo Taga ko O Muuyi. Alla ko HattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  5,18,"Alyahuuda e Annasaara'en wi'i : \"Menen ko men Й“iЙ—Й“e Alla e yiЙ—Й“e Makko\"! Maaku: \"Awa ko fii honЙ—um O Leptirta on juniibi mon Й—in?\" Ko woni, onon ko on Й“anndinke jeyaaЙ—um e kon ko O Tagi\". Himo Hafoana on Mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on Mo O Muuyi. Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon. Ko Faade ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  5,19,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, gomЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o Amen on arii on himo feГұГұinana on e dow taЖҙontinnde(fatra) immorde e NulaaЙ“e, fii wata on wi'u : \"Araali men weltinoowo, wanaa jertinoowo\". GomЙ—ii arii on weltinoowo, e jertinoowo. Alla ko HattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  5,20,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, annditee Neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on, tuma nde O WaЙ—unoo e mooЙ—on AnnabaaЙ“e, O WaЙ—i on laamЙ“e, O Okki on kon ko O Okkaali hay gooto e tageefo ngon"
  5,21,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, naatee ka leydi laЙ“Й“inaandi ndi Alla Winndani on, wata on yiltor Й“aawo e dow gaЙ—a-teppe mo'on ruttitoЙ—on hayruЙ“e"
  5,22,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Pellet, hino e mayri yimЙ“e dunndaranke, menen men naatataa e mayri haa Й“e yalta ton, si Й“e yaltii e mayri, pellet ko men naatooЙ“e"
  5,23,"WorЙ“e Й—iЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e e huluЙ“e, Й“e Alla Neemini e mu'un wi'i : \"NaatiraneeЙ“e ka damal, si on naatirii e maggal, pellet, onon ko o foolooЙ“e. Ko e Alla fawotoЙ—on si on laatike gomЙ—mЙ“e"
  5,24,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko on yo Muusaa, menen men naatataa ton poomaa fodde hiЙ“e ton. Yahu an e Joomi maaЙ—a haЙ“on. Menen Й—oo ko men jooЙ—iiЙ“e"
  5,25,"O Maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi jeytanaa si wanaa hoore-am e neene-gooto am on Haaruuna. Senndindir hakkunde amen e Й“en yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  5,26,"O Daali : \"Pellet, ndii [leydi] harminaama e dow maЙ“Й“e duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nayi. HiЙ“e weema ka leydi. Wata a suno e Й“en faasiqiiЙ“e"
  5,27,"Janngu e dow maЙ“Й“e kumpital Й“iЙ—Й“e-Aadma Й—iЙ—o, e goonga, nde Й“e Й“aЙ—tornoo Й“aЙ—tordi, gooto e maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“anaa, oya on jaЙ“anaaka. On wi'i : \"Ma mi ware\". O wi'i : \"Anndu ka Alla JaЙ“anta, ko gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  5,28,"Si a fontii junngo maa ngon e am fii yo a waram, mi mi wonaali fontoowo juungu am e maa fii yo mi ware. Min miЙ—o hula Alla JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  5,29,"Min miЙ—o yiЙ—i nde hootidataa e bakkaatu am on e bakkaatu maa on, laatodaa e yimЙ“e yiite ngen. Ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,30,"Wonkii makko kin cuЙ—ani mo warugol neene-gooto makko on, o wari mo, o waЙ—tini jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  5,31,"Alla Nuli kaakaaru(Jeyyal) hino wiЙ—oo ka leydi fii yo ndu hollu mo honno o surrirta Й“anndu neene-gooto makko on. O wi'i : \"E bone am ! E mi ronkay wa'ude wa nduu kaakaaru mi surra Й“anndu neene-gooto am on ?\". O WaЙ—tini jeyaaЙ—o e ninsuЙ“e Й“en"
  5,32,"Ko sabu Й—um Men Farliri e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, wonnde : \"Kala warЙ—o wonkii hara wanaa yottana- gol wonkii maa bonni ka leydi, haray o wa'ii wa warЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en fow, mo wuurnii ki kadi, o wa'ii wa on wuurnuЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en fow\". GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, refti pellet, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“e fantimЙ“e ka leydi"
  5,33,"Anndee njoЙ“di Й“en haЙ“ooЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, hiЙ“e yaha bonna ka leydi, ko nde Й“e waretee, maa Й“e dummbee, maa juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en taЖҙee luutindiree, maa Й“e riiwee e leydi ndin. ЖҠum Й—on, no woodani Й“e koyeera ka aduna ; no woodani Й“e kadi ka laakara, lepte mawЙ—e"
  5,34,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e ko adii on heЙ“ude feere maЙ“Й“e. Anndee pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,35,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, hulee Alla, Й—aЙ“Й“iron e Makko jokkorgal, tiiЙ—noЙ—on e Laawol Makko, bea ajo'o, on maloyte"
  5,36,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, sinno no woodannoo Й“e denndaagal ko woni ka leydi e yeru mun wonndude e Й—um, fii yo Й“e soktor Й—um immorde e lepte Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“e jaЙ“antaake. No woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  5,37,"HiЙ“e faalaa nde Й“e yaltata ka yiite, Й“e wonaali yaltooЙ“e e magge. Hino woodani Й“e lepte ГұiiЙ“ude"
  5,38,"Ngujjo [gorko] e ngujjo [debbo] : taЖҙee juuЙ—e maЙ“- Й“e Й—en, njoЙ“di ko Й“e faggitii kon, Й—um ko lepte immorde ka Alla. Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  5,39,"Kala tuuЙ“uЙ—o Й“aawo tooГұe makko Й—en, o moЖҙЖҙini, pellte, Alla JaЙ“anay mo tuubuubuyee. Pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,40,"E a anndaa wonnde no woodani Alla Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, Himo Lepta on Mo O Muuyi, O Haforana on Mo O Muuyi. Alla ko HattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  5,41,"Ko an yo NulaaЙ—o, wata Й“en yaccotooЙ“e e keeferaaku sunine immorde e Й“en wi'uЙ“e: \"Men gomЙ—inirii\" kunndule maЙ“Й“e, tawi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en gomЙ—inaali. E Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e heЙ—itantooЙ“e fenannde, heЙ—itantooЙ“e yimЙ“e goo Й“e araali e maaЙ—a : hiЙ“e wayla Konngolngol Й“aawo mbaaloodi maggol, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Si on jonnaama Й—um Й—oo Жҙettee, si on jonnaaka Й—um rentee\". Kala mo Alla Faandanii fitingol mo, a jeytantaa mo immorde hay e huunde immorde ka Alla. Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla Faalaaka LaЙ“Й“innde Й“erЙ—e mun. Hino woodani Й“e koyeera ka aduna, hino woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e ka laakara"
  5,42,"HeЙ—itantooЙ“e fenaande, ГұaamooЙ“e ngeenaari. Si Й“e arii ma, Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e maa Й—uurno-Й—aa Й“e. Si a Й—uurnike Й“e, Й“e lorrataa ma hay e huunde. Si a Гұaaway, Гұaawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i nunЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  5,43,"E ko honno Й“e Гұaawinoray maa, Tawreeta on no ka maЙ“Й“e, no e mayre Г‘aawoore Alla nden, refti Й“e Й—uurnoo Й“aawo Й—um. ЖҒen wonaali gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  5,44,"Menen Men Jippinii Tawreeta, hino e mayre Peewal e Annoora. Hino Гұaawira nden AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en jebbiliiЙ“e, wonannde Й“en alyahuudaa Й“e, e Й“en rewooЙ“e e jannguЙ“e Й“en, sabu kon ko Й“e reeninaa ka Deftere Alla, Й“e laatii e dow Й—um ko Й“e seediiЙ“e. Wata on hulu yimЙ“e Й“en, hulee Lam Min. Wata on sooditiri Aayeeje Am Й—en cogguyel pamaroy. Kala mo Гұaawiraali ko Alla Jippini kon, ko Й“en Й—on woni heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  5,45,"Men Farlii e maЙ“Й“e ka taTawreeta : wonnde wonkii ko wonkii yoЙ“irtee, yiitere ko yiitere, hinere ko hinere, nowru ko nowru, Гұiire ko Гұiire, barme Й—en ko ko yottondirtee. Kala sakkiiЙ—o Й—um, ko kaffaara wonannde mo. Kala mo Гұaawiraali ko Alla Jippini kon, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  5,46,"Men Jokkintini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, goonginЙ—o kon ko woni yeeso makko immorde e Tawreeta. Men Okki Linjiila, hino e mayre Peewal, e Annoora, goonginnde kon ko woni yeeso mayre immorde e Tawreeta, ko nde Peewal, e Waaju wonannde gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  5,47,"Yo yimЙ“e Linjiila Й“en Гұaawir kon ko Alla Jippini e mayre. Kala mo Гұaawiraali kon ko Alla Jippini, ko Й“en Й—on woni faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  5,48,"Men Jippinii Deftere nden e maaЙ—a goonga, ko nde goonginnde ko woni yeeso mayre immorde e Deftere, ko nde Жҙellitiinde e dow majje. Г‘aawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kon ko Alla Jippini, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en gaay e kon ko aru maa e goonga. Men WaЙ—anii kala e mooЙ—on Sari'a e Laawol. Sinno Alla YiЙ—uno, O WaЙ—ayno on mofte goote, ko woni, ko fii yo O Ndaarndo on e kon ko O Okki on. Adondiree e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde mon, O Humpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on fii mun"
  5,49,"Г‘aawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kon ko Alla Jippini, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, rento Й“e nde Й“e fitinte gaay e yoga e kon ko Alla Jippini e maaЙ—a. Si Й“e huccitii, anndu si ko woni, Alla Faala nde O Meminta Й“e sabu yoga e junuubi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko heewi e yimЙ“e Й“en ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  5,50,E ko Гұaawoore majjuyanko'en Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata ? Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla Гұaawoore wonannde yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e
  5,51,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on jogito Alyahuuda e Annasaara weldiiЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko weldiiЙ“e yoga. kala e mo'on welduЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, on Й—on ko e maЙ“Й“e jeyaa. Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,52,"A yi'ay Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mu'un no yaaw-nora e maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e wi'a : \"Men huli nde yiiloode heЙ“ata men\". Ar ma Alla Adda Uddital, maa fiyaake immorde ka Makko, Й“e wattina e kon ko Й“e suuЙ—i ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e ninsuЙ“e"
  5,53,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en no wi'a : \"E ko Й“ee Й—oo woni Й“en woondirnooЙ“e Alla hattirde woondooje maЙ“Й“e, [wonnde] pellet, hiЙ“e wonnde e mooЙ—on?\" Golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii, Й“e wattini ko Й“e hayruЙ“e"
  5,54,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, kala murtuЙ—o e mooЙ—on e diina mun, arma Alla Adda yimЙ“e Й“e O YiЙ—i kamЙ“e kadi Й“e yiЙ—i Mo, hara ko newaniiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ГұaaЙ—uЙ“e e heeferaaЙ“e Й“en, hiЙ“e tiЙ—noo e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e hulataa feloore feloowo. ЖҠum ko ЖҒural Alla, himo YeЙ—a ngal on Mo O Muuyi. Alla ko YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural], AnnduЙ—o"
  5,55,"Anndee giЙ—o mon on ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e : tottirooЙ“e julde, Й“e totta asakal, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  5,56,"Kala welduЙ—o e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e : pellet, fedde Alla nden ko Й“en woni foolooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,57,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on jogito Й“en jogitoriiЙ“e diina mon kan jalnori e fijindaaru, immorde e Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte ado mon, e heeferaaЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e. Hulee Alla si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  5,58,"Si on noddii faade e julde, Й“e jogitora nde jalnori e fijindaaru : ko waЙ—i Й—um, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e haqqiltaa"
  5,59,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, e on yoftoto men fii men gomЙ—inii Alla e kon ko Jippinaa e amen, e kon ko Jippinanoo ko adii, e wonnde pellet, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e mon ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  5,60,"Maaku : \"E on accay mi mi humpita on ko Й“uri Й—um Й—on bonnde mbarjaari ka Alla ? Kala mo Alla HuЙ—i, O Tikkani on, O WaЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e baaЙ—i e girayЙ—i(girji), e rewooЙ“e bewinayЙ—i Й—in. Ko Й“en Й—on Й“uri bonnde nokku, Й“uri majjude kadi laawol fotondirgol ngol"
  5,61,"Si Й“e arii e mo'on, Й“e wi'a : \"Men gomЙ—inii\". GomЙ—ii non Й“e naatidii e keeferaaku ngun, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e yaltiino e maggu. Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude kon ko Й“e suuЙ—aynoo"
  5,62,"A yi'a ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e no adodnira e bakkaatu, e jaggitugol, Гұaamugol Й“e ngeenaari. Bonii kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e golla"
  5,63,"Ko hanno Й“ee rewooЙ“e [maЙ“Й“e], e annduЙ“e [maЙ“Й“e] Й“en haЙ—a Й“e gaay e konngol maЙ“Й“e bakkaatuyankewol e Гұaamugol Й“e ngeenaari ndin ? Bonii kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e huuwa"
  5,64,"Alyahhuda'en wi': \"Junngo Alla ngon ko Гұobbaango ko JuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Гұobbaama, Й“e huЙ—iraama kon ko Й“e wowli ! Si ko woni, JuuЙ—e Makko Й—en [Й—iЙ—i] ko fontaaЙ—e, Himo Nafqira no O Muuyiri. Pellet, ko Jippinaa kon e maa immorde ka Joomi, Й“eyday ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e bewre e keeferaaku. Men Werlii hakkunde maЙ“Й“e ngayngu e konnaagu haa Г‘alnde Darngal. Tuma kala Й“e huЙ“Й“i yiite fii hare, Alla ЖҠannina nge. HiЙ“e yaha ka leydi bonnugl. Alla non YiЙ—aa bonnooЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  5,65,"Sinno yimЙ“e Defte Й“en gomЙ—inno Й“e huli (Alla), Men Heefanayno Й“e boneeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men Naadayno Й“e kadi Aljannaaji Neema"
  5,66,"Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e ГұiiЙ“nuno Tawreeta e Linjiila, e kon ko Jippinaa faade e maЙ“Й“e immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Гұaamirayno senngo dow maЙ“Й“e e ley koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. No e maЙ“Й“e mofte raЙ“Й“indiniiЙ—e, ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e bonii ko Й“e gollata"
  5,67,"Ko an yo NulaaЙ—o, yottin kon ko Jippinaa e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa, si a waЙ—aali, haray a yottinaali Nulal Makko ngal. Alla ko DaЙ—ndoowo ma e yimЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e yeddooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,68,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, on wonaa e huunde haa ГұiiЙ“non Tawraata e Linjiila e kon ko Jippinaa e mooЙ—on immorde ka Joomi mon\". Ko maa tun ko Jippinaa kon e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“eyda ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e bewre e keeferaaku. Wata a suno fii yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  5,69,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, e Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e, e Й“en rewooЙ“e koode, e Annasaara'en, kala on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, o golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe : kulol alanaa Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e sunoytoo"
  5,70,"GomЙ—ii Men Жіetii ahadi Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, Men Nuli e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ“e. Tuma kala nde NulaaЙ—o addani Й“e kon ko pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in welaaka : fedde goo Й“e fenni, fedde goo no wara"
  5,71,"ЖҒe tamЖҙinii fitna laatotaako, Й“e wumi Й“e faaЙ—i. Refti Alla JaЙ“ani Й“e tuubuubuyee. Refti ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e wumi Й“e faaЙ—i. Alla ko reenuЙ—o kon ko Й“e gollata"
  5,72,"GomЙ—ii yeddii Й“en wi'uЙ“e : \"Alla ko Almasiihu Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on\". Almasiihu on maaki : \"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila, rewee Alla Joomi am e Joomi mon. Pellet, kala sirkanЙ—o Alla, gomЙ—ii Alla Harminanii mo Aljanna, werde makko nden ko ka yiite. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ballo"
  5,73,"GomЙ—ii yeddii Й“en wi'uЙ“e : \"Alla ko tato tammituЙ—o\". Alaa reweteeЙ—o si wanaa ReweteeЙ—o gooto. Si Й“e haЙ—itaaki gaay e ko Й“e wowlata, ko maa mema Й“en yedduЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  5,74,"E Й“e tuubantaa Alla Й“e insinoo Mo?! Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,75,"Almasiihi Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on wonaali si wanaa NulaaЙ—o, gomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e feЖҙЖҙiino ado makko. Neene makko ko goonguЙ—o, kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o hiЙ“e Гұaamaynoo Гұaametee. Ndaaru ko honno Men ЖҒannginiranta Й“e Aayeeje Й—en, refti ndaaraa ko honno Й“e wonaa fefindoreede"
  5,76,"Maaku : \"E on reway ko wonaa Alla, kon ko jeytantaa on lorra wanaa nafa?!\", Alla non ko Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  5,77,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Defte, wata on fantin e diina mon kan ko woori goonga, wata on jokku mbeleeЙ—e yimЙ“e [Й“e tawta] gomЙ—ii Й“e majjii ko adii, Й“e majjini ko Й—uuЙ—i, Й“e majji laawol fotondirngol ngol"
  5,78,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en huЙ—iraama e Й—emngal Daawuda, e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on. ЖҠum le, ko sabu ko yeddi kon, Й“e laatii jaggitooЙ“e"
  5,79,ЖҒe haЙ—indirtaano e bone mo Й“e waЙ—i. Bonii kon ko Й“e gollaynoo
  5,80,"HiЙ—a yi'a ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e no welda e Й“en yeddu- Й“e. Bonii kon ko pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in ardinani Й“e, nde Alla Tikkani Й“e, ko ka lepte woni kamЙ“e ko Й“e heddotoo"
  5,81,"Sinno Й“e gomЙ—inayno Alla, e Annabaajo on e kon ko Jippinaa e makko, Й“e jogittonooko Й“en [yedduЙ“e] weldiiЙ“e. Kono ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  5,82,"A taway ko Й“uri yimЙ“e Й“en tiiЙ—ude e ngayngu wonannde Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e,ko Alyahuuda'en e Й“en sirkooЙ“e.A taway kadi ko Й“uri Й“e Й“aЙ—taade gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en giggol, ko wi'uЙ“e Й“en :\"Menen ko Annasaara\".ЖҠum non,ko tawde hino e maЙ“Й“e annduЙ“e e rewooЙ“e,e wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e mawnintintaako"
  5,83,"Si Й“e nanii ko Jippinaa kon e NulaaЙ—o on, a yi'ay gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en no yuppoo gomЙ—i, sabu kon ko Й“e anndi e goonga kan. HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii, Winndidu men e seediiЙ“e Й“en"
  5,84,"E ko haЙ—ata men gomЙ—inde Alla e ko ari e amen kon immorde e goonga, men tamЖҙinoo nde Joomi amen WaЙ—tida men e yimЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  5,85,"Alla YoЙ“iri Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e wi'i : Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. ЖҠum Й—on ko njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  5,86,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e fenni Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, ko yimЙ“e Jahiimi"
  5,87,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on harmin laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Alla Daginani on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,88,Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on dagiiЙ—i laaЙ“uЙ—i. Hulon Alla On Mo gomЙ—inЙ—on
  5,89,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on ko faljuЙ—on ka woondooje mon, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko fiЙ“uЙ—on woondooje Й—en e muuЙ—um. Kaffaara mun on, ko Гұammingol miskimЙ“e sappo immorde ko hakindii e ko Гұamminton Й“eynguureeji mon, maa koltu maЙ“Й“e, maa rinЙ—inngol daande. On mo heЙ“aali [Й—um], ko hoorugol Й“alЙ—e tati. ЖҠum Й—on ko kaffaara goondooje mon si on woondii. Reenee goondooje mon Й—en. Ko nii Alla ЖҒannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  5,90,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, annde esiwram= sanngara Й—am, e karte Й—en, e sanamuuji Й—in e payaloy koy [fow] ko soЙ“e jeyaaЙ—um e golle seytaane,woЙ—Й—itee Й—um, belajo'o, on maloyte"
  5,91,"Anndee ko seytaane faalaa, ko nde o liЙ“ata ngayngu e konnaagu hakkunde mo'on ka siwram e ka karte, o sakkoo on gaay e jantagol Alla e julde nden. Hara onon ko on haЙ—itotooЙ“e"
  5,92,"ЖҠoftee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, rentoЙ—on ! Si on huccitii, anndee pellet, ko fawii NulaaЙ—o Amen on, ko yottingol Й“anngina"
  5,93,"Bakkaatu fawaaki Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe e kon ko Й“e nyaamuno si Й“e gomЙ—ii Й“e gomЙ—inii Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe, refti Й“e gomЙ—i Й“e gomЙ—ini, refti Й“e gomЙ—i Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Alla No YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,94,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, ma Alla Jarribor on huunde e mbaroodi=raddo, hiЙ—on nanngira Й—um juuЙ—e mon Й—en e gaawe mon Й—en ; fii no Alla Anndira on huloowo Mo e birnal. Kala jaggituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um, hino woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  5,95,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on waru mbaroodi=raddaande hara ko on horminii Й“e. Kala warЙ—o ndi e mooЙ—on ko o tewiiЙ—o, njoЙ“di mun, ko yeru kon ko o wari neemoraaЙ—i, Гұaawa Й—um joomiraaЙ“e nunЙ—al Й—iЙ—o e mooЙ—on, neldaari yottotoondi Kaaba on, maa kaffaara Гұammingol miskiimЙ“e, maa ko fotata Й—um Й—on koorka fii yo o meeЙ—u battane fiyaake makko on. Alla Yaafike kon ko feЖҙЖҙi ; kala ruttiiЙ—o, Alla Yottoto e Makko. Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Jom-yottagol"
  5,96,"Daginanaama on yunngugol ka maayo, Гұaametee mun on ko dakamme wonannde on e setotooЙ“e Й“en. Harminanaama on waaГұugol ka njorndi fodde hiЙ—on hormii. Hulee Alla On Mo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on ka Mun"
  5,97,"Alla WaЙ—ii Kaaba on : Suudu Hormanteendu, ГұiiЙ“irndu wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, e lewru hormante ndun, e neldaari ndin, e ЕӢannaaЙ—i Й—in. ЖҠum Й—on, ko fii yo on anndu wonnde Alla no Anndi kon ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi, e wonndi Alla no Anndi kala huunde"
  5,98,"Anndee wonnde pellet, Alla ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte, e wonnde pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,99,Fawaaki NulaaЙ—o on si wanaa yottingol. Alla no Anndi ko feГұГұinton e ko suuЙ—oton
  5,100,"Maaku : \"ko soЙ“i kon e ko laaЙ“i kon fotataa, hay si hawnii ma Й—uuЙ—ugol ko soЙ“i kon\". Hulee Alla yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji, belajo'o, on maloyte"
  5,101,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on lamndo fii piiji, tawi si Й—i feГұГұinanaama on, mettay on. Si on lamndino fii majji fewndo AlQur'aanaare nden Jippotoo, Й—i feГұГұinante on. Alla Yaafike fii majji. Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  5,102,"GomЙ—ii yimЙ“e adinooЙ“e on lamndinoke fii majji, refti Й“e wontiri Й—in yedduЙ“e"
  5,103,"Alla WaЙ—aali e jelaaЙ—i Й—in, wanaa accitaaЙ—i, wanaa jokkindirmba debbi, wanaa kalaldi-wa, kono heeferЙ“e Й“en no fefindoo e Alla fenaande, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e haqqiltaa"
  5,104,"Si Й“e wi'anaa: \"Aree e ko Alla Jippini kon e faade e NulaaЙ—o on\", Й“e wi'a:\"Yonii men ko men tawri baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en\", e hay si baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en anndaa hay e huunde Й“e feewataa"
  5,105,Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Hino fawii on pittaali mon Й—in! Lorratah on majjuЙ—o si on feewi. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal; O Humpita on kon ko gollaynoЙ—on
  5,106,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! waЙ—ee seedee hakkunde mon, si maayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e mon, tuma wasiyagol, [seedeeЙ“e] Й—iЙ—o nunЙ—uЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, si tawii on yehii ka leydi masiibo maayde yanii e mon. Darnon Й“e ka batte julde, Й“e woondira Alla, si on sikkitike Й“e yoЙ“etaake fii Й—um coggu, hay si laatike joomiraawo badindiral, \"Men SuuЙ—ataa seedee Alla on, menen ontuma [si men waЙ—ii Й—um], haray men jeyaama e bakkondimЙ“e Й“en"
  5,107,"Si tawaama wonnde Й“e hanndi e bakkaatu, ko woЙ—Й“e Й—iЙ—o darotoo darnde maЙ“Й“e nden, hara ko jeyaaЙ“e e hannduЙ“e e hettugol , Й“e woondira Alla : \"Pellet, ko seedee amen on Й“uri jojjude seedee maЙ“Й“e on ; men jaggitaali. Menen ontuma [si men waЙ—ii Й—um], haray men jeyaama e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  5,108,"Ko Й—um Й—oo Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade nde Й“e addata seedee e hoore nden Й—on, maa Й“e hula nde woondoore ruttetee Й“aawo woondoore maЙ“Й“e nden. Alla Fewnataa faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  5,109,"Г‘alnde Alla MooЙ“oyta NulaaЙ“e Й“en, O Daala: \"Ko honЙ—um jaabanoЙ—on?\" ЖҒe maaka: \"Anndal alanaa men, pellet, An, ko An woni AnnduЙ—o ko wirnii"
  5,110,"Tuma nde Alla Daalunoo : \"Ko an yo Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, annditii Neema An on e dow maaЙ—a e dow yumma maaЙ—a, tuma nde Mi Semmbinirno maa fittaandu laaЙ“unde ndun, hiЙ—a yeewta yimЙ“e Й“en ka penuyaagal e ka ЖҙaЖҙЖҙurmayaagal. E tuma nde Mi Anndinno maa winndugol ngol e ГұeГұЖҙangal ngal, e Tawreeta e Linjiila. E tuma tagaynoЙ—aa e loope wano mbaadi sonndu e DuЕӢayee An ; wuttaa e mayru ndu laatoo sonndu e DuЕӢayee An. Sellinaa bunЙ—o e Й—amaaЙ—o e DuЕӢayee An. E tuma nde yaltinanynoЙ—aa maayЙ“e e DuЕӢayee An. E tuma nde Mi Surunoo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en e maaЙ—a nde addannoЙ—aa Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in, yedduЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa mbilewu feeГұungu"
  5,111,"Tuma nde Mi Wahyinnoo e laaЙ“amЙ“e ma Й“en, si ko woni: \"GomЙ—inee Lam Min e NulaaЙ—o An on\", Й“e wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—inii, seedito wonnde pellet, ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"
  5,112,"Tuma nde laaЙ“amЙ“e [ma] Й“en wi'unoo: \"Ko an yo Iisaa, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, hara Joomi maa hino waawi nde O jippinanta men kooliwal immorde ka kammu?\" O maaki: \"Hulee Alla, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  5,113,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men faala Гұaamude e maggal, Й“erЙ—e amen Й—en deeЖҙa, men annda gomЙ—ii a goonganii men, men wona e maggal jeyaaЙ“e e seeditiiЙ“e"
  5,114,"Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on maaki: \"Yaa An Alla, Joomi amen, Jippinan men kooliwal immorde ka kammu, ngal wonana men iidi wonannde aramЙ“e amen e sakkitiiЙ“e amen, e maande immorde ka MaaЙ—a. Arsikaa men: ko An woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"
  5,115,"Allaahu On Daali : \"Min, ko Mi Jippinanoowo on ngal. Kono kala yedduЙ—o e mo'on Й“aawo Й—um, Min, Mi leptay mo lepte Й—e Mi leptataa hay gooto e tagoore nden"
  5,116,"E tuma nde Alla Daaloyte : \"Ko an yo Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, e ko an wi'i yimЙ“e Й“en : \"Jogitee lam min e yumma am reweteeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ko wanaa Alla?\" O maaka : \"Senayee woodanii Ma! Haananaa lam nde mi yeetotooЙ“e ko alanaa lam e mun geЙ“al ! Si wonii mi wowlanii Й—um, haray pellet, A Anndii Й—um. HiЙ—a Anndi ko woni e wonkii am, mi anndaa ko woni e Wonkii Maa. Pellet, An, ko An woni AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i Й—in"
  5,117,"Mi wowlanaali Й“e si wanaa kon ko YamirЙ—aa lam, wonnde : \"Rewee Alla Joomi am e Joomi mon\". Min laatino e dow maЙ“Й“e seeditiiЙ—o yeru ko mi wonnoo. ЖҒaawo nde hunnuЙ—aa mi, wonuЙ—aa An, TommbiiЙ—o e dow maЙ“Й“e. An ko A SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde"
  5,118,"Si a leptii Й“e, pelletn kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e MaaЙ—a. Si A Haforanii Й“e, pellet, An, ko An woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  5,119,"Alla Daali : \"Ndee ko Гұalaande nde goonga nafata googunЙ“e Й“en goonga maЙ“Й“e on : hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji canЙ—i, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e e majji poomaa\". Alla Welaama Й“e kamЙ“e kadi Й“e weltorii Mo. Ko Й—um woni polagal mawngal ngal"
  5,120,"Ko Alla woodani laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin e ko woni nder majji. Kanko ko O HattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  6,1,"Gettooje woodanii Alla On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin,O WaЙ—i niЙ“e Й—en e annoora on.Refti Й“en yedduЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e on hobe firlito gaa Mum"
  6,2,"Ko Kanko woni TaguЙ—o on immorde e loopal, refti O Г‘aawi [gooto kala] lajal, e lajal innaangal ka Makko, refti onon hiЙ—on sikkitoo"
  6,3,"Ko Kano kadi woni Alla ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Hino Anndi gunndoo mon e FeГұГұinannde mon, himo Anndi kadi ko faggitotoЙ—on"
  6,4,"Aaya arataa e maЙ“Й“e immorde e Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e Й—uurnoto gaay e majje"
  6,5,GomЙ—ii Й“e fennii goonga kan nde ka ari e maЙ“Й“e. Arma ara e maЙ“Й“e kumpite Й—e Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita
  6,6,"E Й“e yi'aali Й—uuЙ—ii ko Men Halkunoo ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e gire? Men Newinanno Й“e ka leydi ko Men Newinanaano on ; Men Nuliri kammu ngun e maЙ“Й“e yuppagol, Men WaЙ—i canЙ—i Й—in no ila senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Men Halkiri Й“e junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in ; Men sinci Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e gire goo"
  6,7,"Sinno Men Jippinno e dow maaЙ—a Deftere e nder Й—eri, Й“e meemiri nde juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ayno : \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa mbilehu Й“anngu ngu"
  6,8,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko hanno Malaa'ikaajo jippinee e makko?\" Sinno Men Jippinno Malaa'ikaajo, fiyaaku on gasayno ; hooti Й“e nennantaake"
  6,9,"Sinno Men WaЙ—uno mo Malaa'ikaajo, Men WaЙ—ayno mo gorko, Men Jillindirayno Й“e kadi kon ko Й“e jillindirta"
  6,10,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo jalkitanooma ado maaЙ—a, jippii e Й“en jalkituЙ“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita"
  6,11,"Maaku : \"Yehee ka leydi refti ndaaron ko honno battane fennooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  6,12,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbe woodani ko woni ko ka kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Maaku : \"Ko Alla!\" O WaЙ—Й—inii e Hoore-Makko yurmeende. Pellet, O MooЙ“indiroyay on Г‘alnde Darngal : nde sikke alaa e mu'un. ЖҒen hayruЙ“e=pertinbe pittaali mu'un, kamЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  6,13,"Ko Kanko woodani ko deeЖҙi nder jemma e Гұalorma. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,14,"Maaku : \"E ko ko woori Alla mi jogitotoo giЙ—o? TaguЙ—o Kammuulu Й—in e leydi ndin, Kanko himo Г‘ammina O Гұammintaake\". Maaku : \"Min, Mi yamiraama nde mi wonata arano jebbiliiЙ—o\". Wata a jeye dey e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,15,"Maaku : \"Min miЙ—o huli si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Г‘alaande Mawnde"
  6,16,"On mo lepte Й—en woЙ—Й—inaa e mun nden Г‘alnde, haray gomЙ—ii [Alla] Yurmaama mo, ko Й—um woni malal Й“anngu ngal"
  6,17,"Si Alla Meminii ma lorra, huncoowo ka alaa si wanaa Kanko. Si o Meminii ma kadi moЖҙЖҙere, Kanko e dow kala huunde ko O HattanЙ—o"
  6,18,"Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o e hoore jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ; ko Kanko woni Г‘eeГұo, HumpitiiЙ—o. @Corrected"
  6,19,"Maaku : \"Ko honЙ—um e huunde Й“uri mawnude seedee?\" Maaku : \"Ko Alla, Ko O SeediiЙ—o hakkunde am e mo'on ; ndee Qur'aanaare Wahayinaama e am, fii yo mi rentinir on nde, e kala mo nde hewti\". E onon on seedoto wonnde no wonndi e reweteeЙ—i goo? Maaku : \"Min mi seedotaako\". Maaku : \"Anndee pellet, Kanko ko O ReweteeЙ—o Bajjo\". Min ko mi danndiiЙ—o kon ko kafidoton e makko"
  6,20,"ЖҒen Й“en Men Okki Deftere nden, hiЙ“e anndiri (NulaaЙ—o) on no Й“e anndiri Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. ЖҒen hayruЙ“e pittaali mun Й—in, kamЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—inta"
  6,21,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko Й—en. Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en maletaake"
  6,22,"Г‘alnde Men MoЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti Men Wi'ana Й“en sirkuЙ“e : \"Honto kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e aaЖҙotonoЙ—on"
  6,23,"Refti jaabawol maЙ“Й“e ngol laataaki si wanaa nde Й“e wi'i : \"Men woondirii Alla Joomi amen! Men laatanooki sirkooЙ“e"
  6,24,Ndaarii no Й“e feniri e pittaali maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“e fefindotonoo kon majjirii Й“e
  6,25,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e on heЙ—itotooЙ—o ma, Men WaЙ—ii ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e kiЙ“Й“ale fii wata Й“e faamu [Qur'aanaare] nden, e ka noppi maЙ“Й“e teddeendi. Hay si Й“e yi'ii kala Aaya, Й“e gomЙ—inta Mo. Haa si Й“e arii e maa, hiЙ“e wennjida e maaЙ—a, yedduЙ“e Й“en wi'a : \"ЖҠum Й—oo wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  6,26,"KamЙ“e hiЙ“e haЙ—a [yimЙ“e Й“en] gaay e maako, hiЙ“e haЙ—itoo kadi e makko. ЖҒe alaa e halkude si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kono Й“e so'aa anndude"
  6,27,"Sinno a tinu tuma nde Й“e darnanoo ka hoore Yiite, Й“e wi'a : \"Ee haaniinande men ruttetee, hara men fennataa Aayeeje Joomi amen Й—en, Men jeyee e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  6,28,"Si ko woni, feeГұanii Й“e kon ko Й“e suuЙ—aynoo ko adii. Sinno Й“e ruttita [aduna], Й“e artay e kon ko Й“e haЙ—anoo e mun, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e fenooЙ“e"
  6,29,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa nguurdam amen aduna, men wonaali immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  6,30,"Sinno a tinu tuma nde Й“e darnaa yeeso Joomi amЙ“Й“e. O Daala : \"ЖҠum laataaki goonga?\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!\". O Daala : \"Awa meeЙ—ee non lepte Й—en sabu kon ko yeddiraynoЙ—on"
  6,31,"GomЙ—ii hayrii Й“en fennuЙ“e hawroygol e Alla. Haa si Darngal ngal arii Й“e e juhal, Й“e wi'a : \"Ee nimse amen e kon ko men welsindinoo e Й—am [nguurdam aduna]\", hara hiЙ“e ronndorii bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e. Faamee bonii ko Й“e ronndoytoo"
  6,32,Nguurdam aduna wonaali si wanaa fijindaaru e mbeleeЙ—e. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e. E on haqqiltaa
  6,33,"GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en Anndi wonnde ko Й“e wowlata kon no sunine. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e alaa ma e fennude, kono tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ko Aayeeje Alla Й—en woni yeddude"
  6,34,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e fennanooma ado maaЙ—a, Й“e muГұГұii e kon ko Й“e fannaa, Й“e lorraa, haa ballal Amen ngal ari e maЙ“Й“e. Alaa waЙ—titoowo KonnguЙ—i Alla Й—in. GomЙ—ii arii e maaЙ—a kumpite NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  6,35,"Si tawii Й—uurnagol maЙ“Й“e ngol saЙ—tii e maa, si a haЙ—tanii nde Й—aЙ“Й“ataa yolnde ka nder leydi, maa Й“aargal ka kammu addanaaЙ“e Aaya, [haray waЙ—u Й—um]. Si Alla Muuyuno, O MooЙ“ayno Й“e e hoore peewal. Wata a jeye [ko saЙ—ti woo] e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,36,"Anndu ko noototoo, ko Й“en nanooЙ“e. MaayЙ“e Й“en, Alla Immintinoyay Й“e ; refti ko ka Makko Й“e ruttetee"
  6,37,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko hanno Aaya Jippinee e makko?\" Maaku : \"Alla ko HaЙ—atanЙ—o nde O Jippinta Aaya. Kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  6,38,"Alaa e ruЙ“oowel ka leydi, wanaa wiirayndu wiirira gabiti=bibje mun Й—iЙ—i, si wanaa ko mofte yeruuje mo'on. Men Accaali huunde ka Deftere. Refti ko ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e mooЙ“oytee=rentite"
  6,39,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en ko faaЙ—uЙ“e mumЙ“e e nder majjere. On mo Alla Muuyi majjinnde O Majjinay mo, on Mo O Muuyi O WaЙ—ay mo e laawol focciingol"
  6,40,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam : si lepte Alla Й—en arii on maa Darngal ngal arii on, e ko ko woori Alla noddoton, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  6,41,"Si ko woni, ko Kanko noddoton, O Hunca kon ko noddirton Mo e mun, si O Muuyii, yejjiton ko sirkoton"
  6,42,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii e mofte ado maa, Men Nanngiri Й“e saЙ—teendde e lorra -belajo'o, Й“e yankinoto"
  6,43,"Ko hanno nde saЙ—teende Amen nden arnoo Й“e, Й“e yankinoo ? Kono Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yoorii, seytaane kadi cuЙ—inanii Й“e kon ko gollaynoo"
  6,44,"Nde Й“e yejjitunoo kon ko Й“e waajoraa, Men udditanno Й“e dame kala huunde ; haa nde Й“e weltori kon ko Й“e okkaa, Men Nanngiri Й“e juhal, e jaka ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e"
  6,45,"Asko yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en taЖҙaa. Yettoore nden woodanii Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  6,46,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam! Si Alla nanngi nanЙ—e mon Й—en e giiЙ—e mon Й—en, O notii e Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en, ko hommbo e reweteeЙ“e ko woori Alla artiranta on Й—um? Ndaarii ko honno Men firlisirta Aayeeje Й—en! Refti hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo"
  6,47,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam! Si lepte Alla Й—en ardirii on e juhal maa e kene, enee, hara halkete si wanaa Й“en tooГұooЙ“e"
  6,48,"Men Nuliraali NulaaЙ“e Й“en si wanaa wewlinooЙ“e e rentinooЙ“e : Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, kulol alanaa Й“en wanaa kamЙ“e sunoytoo"
  6,49,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, lepte Й—en memirayЙ“e kon ko Й“e faasoqintonoo"
  6,50,"Maaku : \"Mi wi'ataa on miЙ—o mari ngaluuji Alla Й—in, mi anndaa kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa on kadi ko mi malaa'ikaajo. Min mi jokkaa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am\". Maaku : \"Hara bumЙ—o e yi'oowo fotay? E on miijitotaako"
  6,51,"Rentinir ndee [Al Qur'aanaare], Й“en hulooЙ“e nde Й“e mooЙ“indiroytee ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hara alanaa Й“e ko woori Mo giЙ—o wanaa tefoowo, belajo'o, Й“e hulay"
  6,52,"Wata a raЙ—o Й“en noddayЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e, hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Yeeso Makko ngon. Huunde e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e fawaaki ma, wanaa kadi huunde e Гұaawoore maa woni ko fawii Й“e sakko raЙ—oЙ—aa Й“e, jeyeЙ—aa e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,53,"Ko wano non Men Jerribornoo yoga maЙ“Й“e yoga, fii yo Й“e wi'u : \"E ko Й“ee Й—oo Alla Neemini e dow mu'un hakkunde amen?\" E Alla wonaali Й“urЙ—o Anndude yettooЙ“e [Mo] Й“en"
  6,54,"Si arii e maa Й“en gomЙ—inayЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, maaku : \"Yo kisal wonu e mo'on! Joomi mon WaЙ—Й—inii e Makko yurmeende nden : wonnde kala golluЙ—o e mo'on bone hara ko e majjere, refti o tuubi Й“aawo Й—um o moЖҙЖҙini, haray ko O Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  6,55,"Ko wano non Men Fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, fii no laawol bomЙ“e Й“en feeГұira"
  6,56,"Maaku : \"Min mi haЙ—aama nde mi rewata Й“en Й“e noddoton gaanin Alla\". Maaku : \"Mi jokkataa beleeЙ—e mon Й—en : gomЙ—ii haray mi majjii, haray kadi mi wonaali e feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,57,"Maaku : \"Min miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, on fennii Й—um. Mi alaa ko hawjanton kon. Г‘aawoore nden ko Alla woodani : Himo Fillo goonga, ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fensitooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,58,"Maaku : \"Sinno miЙ—o joginoo kon ko hawjiraynoЙ—on, fiyaaku on gasayno hakkunde am e mo'on\". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,59,"Ko ka Makko woni cottirЙ—e ko wirnii, anndaa Й—um si wanaa Kanko. Himo Anndi ko woni ka njorndi e ka maayo. Kaakol yanataa si wanaa hara himo Anndi fii maggol, wanaa abbere ka niЙ“e leydi, wanaa keccol wanaa yoorungol, si wanaa no e deftere Й“anngunde"
  6,60,"Ko Kanko woni Жҙettitoowo on jemma, himo Anndi ko faggitiЙ—on Гұalorma. Refti O Immintina on ontuma fii timmine lajal innaangal. Refti ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon, refti O Yeetitoo on kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  6,61,"Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o e dow jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Himo Nula e mo'on reenooЙ“e, haa si maayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e mo'on, nulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en Жҙettita mo, kamЙ“e Й“e welsindotaako. @Corrected"
  6,62,"Refti Й“e rutte ka Alla, giЙ—o maЙ“Й“e goonga on. Faamee ko Kanko tun Гұaawoore nden woodani, ko Kanko Й“uri yaawude ГұaawooЙ“e"
  6,63,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo daЙ—ndata on niЙ“e njorndi e maayo?\" HiЙ—on noddira Mo yankinaare e gunndoo : \"Si o daЙ—ndii men e Й—um Й—oo, ma men jeye e yettooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,64,"Maaku : \"Ko Alla DaЙ—ndata on e Й—um, e kala ngoЖҙo. Refti onon hiЙ—on sirka"
  6,65,"Maaku : \"Ko O HattanЙ—o nulugol lepte e dow mo'on, maa Й—e iwra ley koyde mon, maa O Jillindira on dente-dente, O MeeЙ—ina yoga e mo'on lepte yoga\". Ndaaru no Men Firlisirta Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o, Й“e faamay"
  6,66,"YimЙ“e maa Й“en fennii ndee [Al Qur'aanaare], ko kayre le woni goonga kan. Maaku : \"Mi wonaali e dow mon fawtiiЙ—o"
  6,67,Kala kumpital no mari ГұiiЙ“irde. Arma anndon
  6,68,"Si a yi'ii Й“en jumpayЙ“e e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й—uurno Й“e haa Й“e jumpa e yeewtere goo. Si seytaane yejjintinii ma, wata a jooЙ—odu Й“aawo annditugol ngol, e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,69,"Fawaaki Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e, hay huunde e Гұaawoore Й“eya nden. Si ko woni, ko waaju, belajo'o, Й“e hulay [Alla]"
  6,70,"Terto Й“en jogitoriiЙ“e diina mun kan fijindaaru e mbeleeЙ—e, nguurndam aduna Й—am hodi Й“e. Waajor ndee (Qur'aanaare) nde wonkii tigintee ko ki faggitori. Alanaa ki gaanin Alla giЙ—o wanaa tefoowo ; hay si ko sottorii kala sottorgal, ki Жҙettantaake Й—um. Ko Й“en woni tigintiniraaЙ“e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Hino woodani Й“e njaram wulЙ—am e lepte muusuЙ—e sabu kon ko Й“e yeddaynoo"
  6,71,"Maaku : \"E men nodday gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa men kadi lorrataa men? Men ruttitee e gaЙ—a-teppe amen Й“aawo nde Alla fewni men, wano on mo seytaane fijiri ka leydi himo weemi, himo mari wonndiiЙ“e Й“e no nodda mo e peewal : \"Aru e amen\"? Maaku : \"Pellet, peewal Alla ngal, ko ngal woni peewal. Men yamiraama jebbilanagol Jom-Winndere nden"
  6,72,e wonnde ГұiiЙ“nee julde nden hulon Mo. Ko Kanko woni on Mo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on ka Mun
  6,73,"Ko Kanko woni On tagirЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin goonga. Г‘alnde O Daaloyta : \"laato!\", Й—um laatoo, Daalol Makko ngol ko goonga. Ko Kanko [tun] laamu woodani Г‘alnde wuttoytee ka alaadu. AnnduЙ—o ko wirnii e ko feeГұi. Ko Kanko woni Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  6,74,"[Janto] tuma nde Ibraa hiima maakannoo ben makko Aazara: \"Ea jogitoto sanamuuji reweteeЙ—i?\" Pellet, min miЙ—o yi'e an e yimЙ“e maa Й“en,e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  6,75,"Ko wano non Men holliri Ibraahiima laamuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e fii yo o jeye e yananaaЙ“e Й“en"
  6,76,"Nde jemma on niЙ“Й“itunoo e makko, o tini hoodere, o maaki : \"Ndee Й—oo ko joomi am!\" ЖҒaawo nde mutii, o maaki : \"Mi yiЙ—aa mutooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,77,"Nde o tini lewru ndun no jalbi, o maaki : \"Nduu Й—oo ko joomi am!\" ЖҒaawo ndu mutii, o maaki : \"Si Joomi am fewnaali lam, ma mi jeye e yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,78,"Nde o tinunoo naange ngen no jalbi, o maaki : \"Ngee Й—oo ko joomi am! Ko ngee Й—oo Й“uri mawnude\" ЖҒaawo nge mutii, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko sirkoton"
  6,79,"Min dey mi fewtinirii yeeso am ngon e On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ; ooГұiiЙ—o=haniifiyanke, min mi jeyaaka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,80,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wennji mo ; o maaki : \"E on wennjay lam fii Alla, gomЙ—ii le O fewnii lam? Mi hulataa kon ko kafidoton e Makko, si wanaa nde Joomi am Muuyi huunde. Joomi am yaajanii kala huunde anndal. E on waajitotaako"
  6,81,Ko honno mi hulirta kon ko kafiduЙ—on on hulaali onon le on kafidii Alla e huunde nde O Jippinanaali on hujja? Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i Й“uri hanndude e deeЖҙere? Si on laatike annduЙ“e
  6,82,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e jillaali gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal e tooГұe, Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e hoolaare, Й“en ko feewuЙ“e"
  6,83,"ЖҠun ko hujja Amen mo Men Okki Ibraahiima e dow yimЙ“e Makko Й“en. MeЙ—en ЖҒamtana darjaaji on mo Men Muuyi. Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,84,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Men fewni Й“e kala. E Nuuhu Men Fewni mo ko adii, hino jeyaa e jurriiyaaji makko, Daawuuda e Sulaymaana e Ayyuuba e Yuusufa e Muusaa e Haaruuna. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,85,"E Zakariyaa e Yahyaa e Iisaa e Ilyaasa, kala maЙ“Й“e ko jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  6,86,"E Ismaa'iila e Alyasa'a e Luutu, kala maЙ“Й“e Men ЖҒurnii e Winndere nden"
  6,87,"E baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e Jurriiyaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Men SuЙ“ii Й“e, Men Fewni Й“e e laawol focciingol"
  6,88,"ЖҠum ko peewal Alla, himo Fewnira ngal on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Sinno Й“e sirkuno, poЙ“ayno=yirbatna gaay e maЙ“Й“e kon ko Й“e gollaaynoo"
  6,89,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Men Okki Deftere nden e Г‘eГұЖҙal ngal e Annabaaku ngun. Si Й“ee yeddii Й—in, gomЙ—ii Men Fawii Й—i yimЙ“e, Й“e laataaki yeddooЙ“e Й—i"
  6,90,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla Fewni : ko peewal maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұemtintaa. Maaku : \"Mi lamndotaako e Й—um njoЙ“di\". Nde wonaali si wanaa waaju Winndere nden"
  6,91,"ЖҒe mawniniraali Alla no O haani mawninireede non tuma Й“e wi'unoo : \"Alla Jippinaali e neЙ—Й—anke hau e huunde\". Maaku : \"Ko hommno jippini Deftere nde Muusaa addi nden, ko nde annoora e peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en? HiЙ—on waЙ—a nde Й—eri, feГұГұinon goЙ—Й—um e majji, suuЙ—on ko heewi.AnndinaЙ—on ko onon anndaano onon, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e mo'on. Maaku : \"Ko Alla\". Refti accaaЙ“e e jumpougol maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e fija"
  6,92,"Ndee Й—oo ko Deftere nde Men Jippini : barkinaande, goonginnde ko woni yeesi mayre, e fii yo a waajor nde yimЙ“e Makko Й“en e Й“en wonЙ“e takko Й—on. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e laakara, hino gomЙ—ini nden, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e reenoo e julde maЙ“Й“e nden"
  6,93,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa foti wa on fefindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande maa o wi'i : \"Wahayinaama e am\", hara hay huunde wahayinaaka e makko. E on wi'uЙ—o : \"Mi jippinay sugu kon ko Alla Jippini\". Sinno a tinuno nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en woni e paЙ—Й—e maayde, hara Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hino fonti juuЙ—e maЙ“e Й—en (no wi'a): \"Yaltinee pittaali mon Й—in. Hannde on yoЙ“ete lepte hoynooje sabu kon ko haalaynoЙ—on e hoore Alla ko wanaa goonga, laatiЙ—on gaay e Aayeeje Makko Й—en hiЙ—on mawnintinoo"
  6,94,"GomЙ—ii on ardirii Men telЙ—ugol, wano Men Tagirnoo on arannde laawol, on accii kon ko Men Jeynunoo on Й“aawo mon. Men Yiidaali e mon tefooЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e aaЖҙinoЙ—on wonnde kamЙ“e e mooЙ—on ko Й“e kafiduЙ“e. GomЙ—ii taЖҙondiral waЙ—ii hakkunde mo'on : majjirii on kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on aaЖҙoo"
  6,95,"Pellet, ko Alla woni feccuЙ—o abbere e kundin : himo yaltina ko wuuri e immorde e ko maayi, ko O yaltinoowo ka maayi immorde e ko wuuri. O mo'on ko Alla. Ko honno wonaЙ—on fefindoreede"
  6,96,"FeccuЙ—o subakaaji Й—in, O waЙ—i jemma on deeЖҙirde, naange ngen e lewru ndun limirЙ—i. ЖҠum ko hoddiroore On FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,97,Ko Kanko woni waЙ—anЙ—o on koode Й—en fii yo on fewnitorЙ—e ka niЙ“e njorndi e ka maayo. GomЙ—ii Men fensitii Aayeeje Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e annduЙ“e
  6,98,"Ko Kanko woni fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o on immorde e wonkii wooti, ko ГұiiЙ“irde e marorde. GomЙ—ii Men fensitii Aayeeje Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e faamooЙ“e"
  6,99,"Ko Kanko woni On Jippin jippinЙ—o ndiyam immorde ka kammu, Men yaltini e majjam puЙ—i kala huunde, Men yaltini e majjam e Й—in (puЙ—i) keccum, MeЙ—en yaltina e mun gabbe fawondirЙ—e ; e ka tamrooje immorde e piindi majje on dukke baЙ—tiiЙ—e, e gese immorde e inabuuje e nebbanteeje e rummaanaaje, nannduЙ—e e Й—e nanndaa. Ndaaree dimЙ—e mun Й—en si Й—e rimii e Й“enndugol mun. Pellet, no e Й—um Й—on mooЙ—on, Aayeeje wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  6,100,"ЖҒe waЙ—anii Alla jinnaaji kafidiiЙ—i, tawi le O tagii Й“e. ЖҒe waЙ—ani Mo Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e ko aldaa e ganndal! Senayee woodanii Mo, O WoЙ—Й—ike gaay e ko Й“e sifotoo kon"
  6,101,"FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko honno woodiranta Mo Й“iЙ—Й—o O maraa Й“eyngu?! O tagii kala huunde, Kanko ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  6,102,"On mon ko Alla, Joomi mon! ReweteeЙ—o alaa (e goonga) si wanaa Kanko, TaguЙ—o kala huunde. Rewee Mo. Kanko e dow kala huunde ko O fawtiiЙ—o"
  6,103,"GiiЙ—e Й—en huЙ“indotaako Mo, Kanko himo HuЙ“indoo giiЙ—e Й—en. Ko Kanko woni NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  6,104,"GomЙ—ii hujjaaji arii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon : kala jaЙ“uЙ—o yi'ude ko hoore-makko [o yi'ani], kala kadi huminkiniiЙ—o ko hoore-makko [o huminanii]. Mi wonaali e dow mooЙ—on reenoowo"
  6,105,"Ko wano non Men Firlisirta Aayeeje Й—en, e fii no Й“e wi'ira : \"A janngu\", e fii yo Men FeГұГұinan Й—um yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e"
  6,106,Jokku ko Wahyinaa kon e maa immorde ka Joomi maa. Alaa reweteeЙ—o (e goonga) si wanaa Kanko. ЖҠuurno gaay e sirkooЙ“e Й“en
  6,107,"Sinno Alla Muuyuno, Й“e sirkataano! Men WaЙ—aali ma e dow maЙ“Й“e reewnoowo ; a wonaali kadi e dow maЙ“Й“e fawtiiЙ—o"
  6,108,"Wata on on yennu Й“en rewooЙ“e gaani Alla, sakko Й“e yennira Alla yottagol ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko wano nii Men CuЙ—irani kala mofte, golle maЙ“Й“e, refti ko ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e ; O Humpita Й“e kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e golla"
  6,109,"ЖҒe woodndirii Alla hattirde woondoore maЙ“Й“e : si Aaya arii e maЙ“Й“e, maa Й“e gomЙ—in mo. Maaku : \"Anndee Aayeeje Й—en ko ka Alla woni\". E ko so'ini on wonnde si Й—e arii, Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  6,110,"Men Waylitiray Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, wano Й“e gomЙ—iniraali Й—e ka arannde laawol ; Men Acca Й“e e bewre maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e weema"
  6,111,"Sinno Men Jippinno e maЙ“Й“e Malaa'ika, maayЙ“e Й“en yeewtidi e maЙ“Й“e, Men MooЙ“i e maЙ“Й“e kala huunde yeeso maЙ“Й“e ; Й“e laatotanooko gomЙ—imЙ“e si wanaa nde Alla Muuyi. Kono ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e hino majjaa"
  6,112,"Ko woni nii Men WaЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo : seytaaneeji yimЙ“e e jinna ; yoga maЙ“Й“e no wahyina e yoga, cuЙ—aari konngol hodo. Sinno Joomi maa Muuyuno, Й“e waЙ—ataani Й—um, tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,113,"E fii yo heЙ—ito Й—um, Й“erЙ—e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara, e fii yo Й“e wele Й—um, e fii yo Й“e fefindo huunde nde Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,114,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata Гұaawoowo, ko Kanko woni JippinЙ—o e mo'on ndee Deftere fensitaande? ЖҒen Й“e Men Okki Defte Й“en, hiЙ“e anndi wonnde ko nde Jippinaande immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a goonga. Wata a jeye e sikkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  6,115,"Konngol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol timmirii goonga e nunЙ—al. Alaa wattitoowo konnguЙ—i Makko Й—in. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,116,"Si a Й—oftike ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en, Й“e majjinte e laawol Alla ngol : Й“e wonaalli hiЙ“e jokka si wanaa sikke, Й“e wonaali si wanaa hottotooЙ“e"
  6,117,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa Й“uri Anndude on majjuЙ—o laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri Anndude feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  6,118,Г‘aamee kon ko Innde Alla jantaa e mun si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Makko Й—en
  6,119,"E ko haЙ—ata on nde on Гұaamataa kon ko Innde Alla jantaa e mun? GomЙ—ii O Fensitanii on kon ko O Harmini e mon, si wanaa kon ko Й“ittorЙ—on e mun. Pellet, ko Й—uuЙ—i [e sirkooЙ“e Й“en] hino majjira mbeleeЙ—e mu'un ko alaa e ganndal. Pellet, ko Joomi Й“uri Anndude jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,120,"Tertee ko feeГұi e bakkaatu e ko wirnii e mun. Pellet, Й“en faggitotooЙ“e bakkaatu, Й“e yoЙ“oyte kon ko laatinoo hiЙ“e fefindoo"
  6,121,"Wata on Гұaamu kon ko Innde Alla jantaaka e mun, pellet, (salagol) Й—um ko faasiqiyaagal. E pellet, seytaaneeji Й—in no sowonsina e weldiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en no Й“e wennjira on. Si on Й—oftike Й“e, haray pellet, ko on sirkuЙ“e"
  6,122,"E ko on laatinooЙ—o maayЙ—o, Wuurniti mo, Men wuurniti mbo WaЙ—ani mo annoora himo yaara on hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wa'ata wa on wonЙ—on e niЙ“e mo wanaa yaltoowo ton? Ko wano non heeferЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—iranaa kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  6,123,"Ko wano non Men WaЙ—iri e kala hoЙ—o, mawЙ“e bonЙ“e, fii no Й“e fewjira e mayre. ЖҒe alaa e fewjude si wanaa e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, kono Й“e so'aa anndude"
  6,124,"Si Aaya arii e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wi'a : \"Men gomЙ—intaa haa men okkee sugu ko NulaaЙ“e Alla Й“en okkaa kon\". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ka O WaЙ—ata Nulal Makko ngal. Aray ka koyeera e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e heЙ“a Й“en bonЙ“e, sabu kon ko Й“e fewjanynoo"
  6,125,"Kala mo Alla Faandii fewnude, O YaГұГұanay=yaajnat Й“ernde makko nden Lislaamu. Kala kadi mo O Faandii Majjinnde, O WaЙ—ay Й“ernde makko nden faaЙ—unde Й“ittunde ; hara himo wa'i wa ЕӢabboowo yaha ka kammu. Ko wano non Alla WaЙ—irta lepte Й—en e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  6,126,Ko Й—um Й—oo woni laawol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol feewungol. GomЙ—ii Men Fensitii Aayeeje Й—en woannde yimЙ“e waajitotooЙ“e
  6,127,Hino woodanibe galle kisal ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko Kanko woni GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e gollaynoo
  6,128,"Г‘alnde O MooЙ“itoyta Й“e denndaangal : \"Ko onon yo onon yo dental jinna, gomЙ—ii on Й—uЙ—Й—inorii (majjingol) yimЙ“e Й“en\". YiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ka yimЙ“e wi'a : \"Joomi amen, yoga amen dakmitorii yoga, men yottike ngal caatal=lajal amen ngal saatinanЙ—aa men\". O Daala : \"Ko Yiite ngen woni werde mon, ko on luttooЙ“e ton, si wanaa kon ko Alla Muuyi\". Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,129,Ko wano non Men Wurtirta yoga e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e hoore yoga ; sabu kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo
  6,130,"Ko onon yo dental jinna e yimЙ“e, e araali e mo'on NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am Й—en, Й“e rentina on hawrugol ndee Й—oo Г‘alaande mon? ЖҒe wi'a : \"Men seedike e hoore pittaali amen\". Nguurndam aduna Й—am hodi Й“e ; Й“e seeditii e hoore pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in wonnde Й“e laatino heeferЙ“e"
  6,131,"ЖҠum ko tawde Joomi maa wonaali halkoowo ca'e sabu tooГұe, hara yimЙ“e majje ko welsindiiЙ“e"
  6,132,Hino woodani kala en darjaaji kon ko Й“e golli. Joomi maa wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e kon ko Й“e gollata
  6,133,"Ko Joomi ma woni Galo Jom-Yurmeende. Si O Muuyii O NaЙ“ay on, O Lontina Й“aawo mo'on ko O Muuyi ; wano O FuЙ—Й—ornoo on immorde e Й“iЙ—Й“e yimЙ“e goo"
  6,134,"Pellet, ko fodaЙ—on kon ko aray Й—um. On wonaali ronkinooЙ“e [Men]"
  6,135,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, gollee e nokku mo'on, min ko mi golloowo. On anndoyay ko hommbo (e men) laatantoo Й—um battane galle Й—en\". pellet,O malnatah tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,136,"ЖҒe waЙ—anii Alla geЙ“al e ko O Tagi kon immorde e gese e neemoraaЙ—i, Й“e wi'i : \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko Alla -e aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- ЖҠum Й—oo ko kafidiiЙ—i amen Й—in\". Ko wanani kon kafidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in hewtataa Alla, kono ko wonani kon Alla hewtay kadidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko Й“e Гұaawata kon bonii"
  6,137,"Ko wano non kafidiiЙ—i ko heewi e sirkooЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—irani Й“e warugol Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, fii yo Й—i halkuЙ“e e fii yo Й“e jiiЙ“itu diina maЙ“Й“e kan. Sinno Alla Muuyuno, Й“e waЙ—ataano Й—um. Tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotoo"
  6,138,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"ЖҠii Й—oo ko neemoraaЙ—i e gese feraaЙ—i : Гұaamataa Й—i si wanaa on mo men yiЙ—i.\"-Ka aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- E neemoraaЙ—i harminaaЙ—i Й“abbe mun, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—i Й“e jantotaako Innde Alla e mun, fefindagol e Makko ; O YoЙ“oyay Й“e kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo. Ma Alla yobbe fefindagol mu*en ngol"
  6,139,"ЖҒe wi'i kadi: \"Ko woni kon e deedi Й—ii neemoraaЙ—i, ko heeranii Й—um worЙ“e amen, harmani rewЙ“e amen\". Si Й—um wonii ko jiibuЙ—um, kamЙ“e ko Й“e kafooЙ“e Й—um. O YoЙ“oyay Й“e ko Й“e hanndi kon. Kanko ko O Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  6,140,"GomЙ—ii sooyii Й“en warirЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mun njofoyaagal ko aldaa e ganndal, Й“e harminiri kon ko Alla Arsiki Й“e fefindagol e hoore Alla. GomЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e wonaano feewuЙ“e"
  6,141,"Ko Kanko woni On FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o gese waЙ—aaЙ—e bente e Й—e waЙ—aaka bente, e tamarooje, e remuruuji sertuЙ—i Гұaamndu mu'un, e nebbanteeje, e rummaana nannduЙ—e e Й—e nanndaa. Г‘aamee e dimЙ—e majje si Й—e rimii, jonnon asakal mun Гұalnde soГұaa. Wata on Й“urtin, pellet, Kanko O YiЙ—aa Й“urtinooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,142,"Hino e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ronndotooЙ—i e joltuЙ—i. Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on, wata on jokku taaЙ“aЕӢlle seytaane Й—en, pellet, kanko ko o gaГұo mon feeГұuЙ—o"
  6,143,"[O Taganii on] nooneeji jeetati : no e baali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, no e be'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : \"E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O Harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i? Humpitiree lam ganndal si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  6,144,"No e gelooЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i, no e na'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : \"E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O Harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa on seedino tuma Alla Wasiyinoo on Й—um?\" Kohommbo Й“uri tooГұude haa fota wa on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla fii no o majjiniri yimЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e ganndal? Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,145,"Maaku : \"Mi tawaali e kon ko wahyinaa e am, ko harminaa e Гұaamoowo mo no Гұaama Й—um, si wanaa nde laatotoo ko maayi (jiibi), maa ЖҙiiЖҙam sankotooЙ—am, maa teewu kose -sabu Й—um ko soЙ“e- maa (ko hirsiraa) faasiqiyaagal\". Kala on Й“ittiiЙ—o, hara wanaa bewЙ—o, wanaa jaggituЙ—o, haray pellet, Joomi maa ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  6,146,"Ko en Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e (tun) woni ko Men Harmini kala ko jogii peЙ—aali. Na'i Й—in e dammi Й—in kadi, Men Harminii e maЙ“Й“e Й“elle majji Й—en, si wanaa ko Й“abbe majji ronndii, maa tete on, maa ko jillondiri e Жҙi'e. Ko Й—um Men YoЙ“irnoo Й“e berwre maЙ“Й“e nden. Pellet, ko Men GoonguЙ“e"
  6,147,"Si Й“e fennii ma, maaku : \"Joomi mon ko Jom-Yurmeende yaajunde, lepte Makko Й—en ruttetaake e yimЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  6,148,"Arma sirkuЙ“e Й“en wi'a : \"Sinno Alla Muuyuno, men sirkataano, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, men harmintaano kadi hay e huunde\". Ko non Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e fennirnoo haa Й“e meeЙ—i lepte Amen Й—en. Maaku : \"Hara ganndal no woodani on yaltinanon men ngal? Pellet, on jokkaa si wanaa sikke, onon on wonaali si wanaa fenooЙ“e"
  6,149,"Maaku : \"Ko Alla woodani hujja yottiiЙ—o on.Sinno O Muuyuno, O Fewnayno on denndaangal"
  6,150,"Maaku : \"Addee seedeeЙ“e mon Й“en, Й“e seeditoo wonnde Alla Harminii Й—um Й—oo\". Si Й“e seedike, wata a seedodu e maЙ“Й“e. Wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sirkana Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  6,151,"Maaku : \"Aree mi janngana on ko Joomi mo Harmini e mon : ko nde kafidoton e Makko huunde, waЙ—anon jibimЙ“e mon Й“en moЖҙЖҙere. Wata on waru Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en kulol immorde e baasal. Ko Menen Arsikata on e kamЙ“e. Wata on Й“aЙ—to pankare Й—en ko feeГұi e majje e ko wirnii. Wata waru wonkii ki Alla Harmini si wanaa e goonga. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  6,152,"Wata on Й“aЙ—to jawdi wonduЙ—o si wanaa hara ko no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙirde, haa o yottoo kellefuyee makko. Timminiree etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikirЙ—e= peesirde Й—en no nunЙ—iri. Men fawaa wonkii si wanaa ko ki townata. Si on wowlay nunЙ—ee hay si ko e hoore jom-Й“aЙ—todal. Ahadi Alla ndin hunnon. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on; belajo'o, on annditay"
  6,153,"E wonnde pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko laawol am focciingol, jokkee ngol ; wata on jokku laawoy senndaykoy on e laawol Makko ngol\". Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on rentoto"
  6,154,"Refti Men Okki Muusaa Deftere nden timmirnde (neema) mo o moЖҙЖҙiniri, fensitunde kala huunde, ko nde peewal e yurmeende ; belajo'o, Й“e gomЙ—inay hawrygol e Jommi maЙ“Й“e"
  6,155,"Ndee Й—oo ko Deftere (Alqur'aana), Men Jippiinde ko nde barkinnde - jokkee nde, rentoЙ—on ; belajo'o, on yurmedon"
  6,156,"Fii wata on wi'oy : \"Defte Й—en ko e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i Jippinaa, ado amen, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e janngugol Й—e"
  6,157,"maa Й—um wi'on : \"Sinno menen, Deftere nden Jippinano e amen, men laatotono Й“urЙ“e Й“en Й—on feewude\". GomЙ—ii arii on immorde ka Joomi mon, Й“anngannduyee, e peewal, e yurmeende. Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on fennuЙ—o Aayeeje Alla Й—en o Й—uurnii Й—e. Arma Men YoЙ“iroya Й“en Й—uurnotooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en lepte bonЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo"
  6,158,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en ara e maЙ“Й“e? Maa Joomi maa Ara? Maa yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ara? Г‘alnde yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ari, nafataa wonkii gomЙ—inal makki, ki laatanooki gomЙ—inki ko adii, maa ki faggitii e gomЙ—inal makki moЖҙЖҙere. Maaku : \"Habbitee! Menen ko men habbitiiЙ“e"
  6,159,"Pellet, Й“en sennduЙ“e diina mun kan, Й“e laatii feddeeji, a jeyaaka e maЙ“Й“e e huunde : Anndee fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e ko faade ka Alla. Refti O Humpita Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e golla"
  6,160,Kala arduЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani mo sappo yeru mayre ; kala kadi arduЙ—o e bone o yoЙ“itetaake si wanaa yeru makko. KamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake
  6,161,"Maaku : \"Min, Joomi am Fewni lam faade e laawol focciingol, diina ГұiiЙ“uka, diina Ibraahiima, ooГұiiЙ—o [e diina meere] ; o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,162,"Maaku : \"Pellet, julde am nden, e kirse am Й—en, e nguurndam am Й—am, e maayde am nden, ko All woodani, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  6,163,"KafidiiЙ—o alanaa Mo! Ko Й—um mi yamiraa, ko mi woni arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  6,164,"Maaku : \"E ko tanaa Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata reweteeЙ—o, ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o kala huunde?! Kala wonkii faggitantaako si wanaa e hoore-makki : wonkii ronndotaako bone wonkii goo. Refti ko faade ka Joomi mon woni ruttorde mon, O Humpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun"
  6,165,"Ko Kanko woni WaЙ—uЙ—o on lontiiЙ“e ka keydi, O ЖҒamtiri yoga mon dow yoga, darjaaji ; fii yo O Jarribo on e ko O Okki on. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—o lepte, Kanko kadi, ko O Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad"
  7,2,"Ko Deftere Jippinaande e maaЙ—a, wata Й“itteende wonu ka Й“ernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  7,3,"Jokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wata on jokku gaanin Й—um, weldiiЙ“e, fanЙ—ii ko waajitotoЙ—on"
  7,4,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ca'e Й—e Men halki! Lepte Amen Й—en ari e majje jemma hiЙ“e waalii Й—aanii, maa hara ko Й“e fowtiiЙ“e Гұalorma"
  7,5,"Noddaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun Й“aawo lepte Amen Й—en arde Й“e, wonaano si naa wi'ugol : \"Menen men laatino tooГұooЙ“e"
  7,6,"Ma Men Lamnditoyo Й“en Й“e (Men) Nulunoo e mun, Ma Men Lamnditoyo kadi NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,7,Ma Men Fillanoroyo Й“e (golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en) e ganndal. Men wonaano wirniiЙ“e
  7,8,"Manndakke=peesgol Й—en nde Г‘alnde, ko Й—e goonga. Kala mo manndake (moЖҙЖҙi Й—en) teddi, ko Й“en Й—on woni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (moЖҙЖҙi) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko Й“en Й—on woni sooyinirЙ“e pittaali mu'un saЙ“u ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e yedda Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,10,"GomЙ—ii Men Newinanii on ke leydi, Men WaЙ—ani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) fanЙ—ii ko yettoton"
  7,11,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii on, refti Men Mbaadini on, refti Men Wi'ani Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en : \"Sujjanee Aadama\", Й“e sujji, si wanaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,12,"O Daali : \"Ko haЙ—u-maa nde sujjataa nde Mi Yamir-maa?\" O wi'i : \"MiЙ—o Й“uri mo moЖҙЖҙude : A Tagii lam immorde e Yiite, A Tagii mo immorde e loopal"
  7,13,"O Daali : \"Jippo ton, haananaama nde mawnintintoЙ—aa ton. Yaltu, an ko a jeyaaЙ—o e hoyЙ“e Й“en"
  7,14,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Nennitanam haa Гұalnde Й“e immintintee"
  7,15,"[Alla] Daali : \"An, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e nennitanteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,16,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : \"Sabu ko bewinirЙ—aa lam kon, ma mi jooЙ—ano Й“e ka laawol Maa focciingol"
  7,17,"Refti mi ardiranay Й“e yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, e ka e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e e ka nane maЙ“Й“e. A tawataa ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko yettooЙ“e [Ma]"
  7,18,"[Alla] Daali : \"Yaltu ton, ko a ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o raЙ—aaЙ—o. Kala jokkuЙ—o ma e maЙ“Й“e, ma Mi hebbiiroy Jahannama onon denndaangal"
  7,19,"Ko an yo Aadama, hoЙ—u an e Й“eyngu maa ka Aljanna, Гұaamee kala nokku ka yiЙ—u-Й—on ; wata tun on Й“aЙ—to ngal Й—oo leggal, sakko laatoЙ—on e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,20,"Seytaane sowinsini Й“e, fii yo o feГұГұinan Й“e ko suuЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e e awraaji maЙ“Й“e, o wi'i : \"Joomi mon haЙ—iraali on ngal leggal si wanaa fii wata on laato Malaa'ika maa laatoЙ—on duumotooЙ“e [ka Aljanna]"
  7,21,"O woondani Й“e o wi'i : \"Min ko mi laaЙ“anooЙ“e on"
  7,22,"O hodiri Й“e janfa. Nde Й“e meeЙ—unoo laggal ngal, awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in feeГұani Й“e, Й“e waЙ—ti hiЙ“e surritora kaaki Aljanna Й—in. Joomi maЙ“Й“e noddi Й“e : \"E Mi haЙ—aano on e ngal leggal, Mi wi'ani on : Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo mo'on Й“annguЙ—o"
  7,23,"ЖҒe wi'idi Й“e Й—iЙ—o : \"Joomi amen, men tooГұii ko'e amen. Si A haforanaali men yurmeЙ—aa men, ma men jeye e sooyuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,24,"[Alla] Daali : \"Jippee (ka leydi), yoga mon ko ayЙ“e yoga. Hino woodani on ka leydi ton ГұiiЙ“irde e dakamme haa saanga"
  7,25,"[Alla] Daali : \"Ko (ka leydi) ton wuuroton, ko ton kadi maayoton, ko e mayri kadi yaltinoyteЙ—on"
  7,26,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadam! GomЙ—ii Men Jippinii e mo'on conci surrayЙ—i awraaji mon Й—in e cuЙ—aari. -Ko cocni kulol Й—in non Й“uri muЖҙЖҙude.- Ko Й—um jeyaaЙ—um e Aayeeje Alla. Belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e waajitoto"
  7,27,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Wata seytaane fitinir on wano o yaltinirnoo baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka Aljanna, himo Й“oora e maЙ“Й“e conci maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii yo hollu Й“e awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Pellet, himo reeni on kanko e gorol makko ngol nokku ka on yi'ataa Й“e. Menen Men waЙ—ii seytaaneeji Й—in weldiiЙ—i Й“en Й“en gomЙ—intaa"
  7,28,"Si Й“e waЙ—ii pankare, Й“e wi'a : \"Men tawru Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, ko Alla yamiri men Й—um\". Maaku : \"Pellet, Alla yamirtaa pankare. E on wowlay e hoore Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,29,"Maaku : \"Joomi am yamirii nunЙ—al. Г‘iiЙ“non geece mon Й—en nokku kala e ka juuloton, tororon Mo laЙ“Й“inangol Mo diina kan. Ko wano O FuЙ—Й—ori on non ruttirton"
  7,30,"Fedde goo O fewnii, fedde goo majjere nden jojji e hoore maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e Й“e jogitike seytaaneeji Й—in weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sikka ko Й“e feewuЙ“e"
  7,31,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama, Жҙettee cuЙ—aari mon ndin nokku kala ka juuloton. Г‘aamee yaron wata on fantin. Pellet, Kanko O yiЙ—aa fantinooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,32,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo harmini cuЙ—aari Alla ndi O Yaltinani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in ka arsikeeji?\" Maaku : \"ЖҠin Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ka nguurndam aduna woodani, heeraniiЙ—i [Й“e] Г‘alnde Darngal\". Ko wano non Men Fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, woanannde yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e"
  7,33,"Maaku : \"Joomi am ko Harmini : ko pankare Й—en -ko feeГұi e majje ko suuЙ—ii-, e bakkaatu, e bewrugol ko aldaa e goonga, e nde sirkanton Mo kon ko O Jippinanaali Й—um hujja, e nde wowloton e Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,34,"Hino woodani kala mofte laja. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e nennitantaake saa'i gooto, Й“e ardinantaake kadi"
  7,35,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Si aroyii e mon NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am, kala hulЙ—o [Alla] o moЖҙЖҙini [golle], kulol alanaa Й“en Й—on, wanaa kamЙ“e kadi sunoytoo"
  7,36,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en Й“e townitanii e heЙ—e, ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton"
  7,37,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұuЙ—o haa hewta on fefindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko Й—en? ЖҒen heЙ“ay Й“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal e binndoodi ndin ; haa si NulaaЙ“e Amen [warooЙ“e] Й“en arii Й“e, Й“e wara Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Ko honto kon ko rewaynoЙ—on gaanin Alla [woni]?!\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"ЖҠi majjirii men\". ЖҒe seeditoo e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde Й“e laatino yedduЙ“e"
  7,38,"[Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en] wi'a : \"Naate e moftaaji, gomЙ—ii yawtii ado mon immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e ka nder Yiite\". Tuma kala nde mofte naati, Й—e huЙ—a banndam majje. Haa si Й“e tawtindirii ton Й“e denndaanal, sakkitiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'ana aramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en : \"Joomi amen! Ko Й“ee majjini men : Okku Й“e lepte cowanЙ—e e Yiite ngen\". O Daala : \"Hino woodani kala [mon] cowanЙ—e, kono on anndaa"
  7,39,"AramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'ana sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en : \"Alanaa on e dow amen Й“ural, meeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu kon ko faggitotonoЙ—on"
  7,40,"Pellet, Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e townitanii Й—e, Й“e udditantaake dame kammuuli Й—in, Й“e naatataa kadi Aljanna haa ngelooba naata e wuddere meselal. Ko wano non Men yoЙ“irte Й“omЙ“e Й“en"
  7,41,"Hino woodani Й“e ka Jahannama ndaЙ—Й—udi, no dow maЙ“Й“e kadi kippoodi. Ko wanon non Men yoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,42,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Men fawataa wonkii si wanaa ko ki waawi - Ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e Aljanna : kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  7,43,"Men Й“oori e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en konnaagu, canЙ—i Й—in no ila senngo ley maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Yettoore woodani Alla On fewuЙ—o men e Й—um Й—oo, men wonaano feewooЙ“e si Alla fewnaano men. GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“en addii goonga\". ЖҒe noddee si ko woni : \"On Й—on mooЙ—on Aljanna, on roninaama mo, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  7,44,"YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en noddi yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en, si ko woni : \"GomЙ—ii men tawii ko Joomi amen fodi men kon ko goonga. Onon kadi on tawii ko Joomi mon fodi on kon ko goonga?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Eyyo\". Noddoowo nodda hakkunde maЙ“Й“e wonnde : Kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,45,"ЖҒen sakkotooЙ“e=falatoobe gaay e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara"
  7,46,"Heedo no hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Hino e dow tulde La'raafi nden worЙ“e hiЙ“e anndira kala e maande mun. ЖҒe nodda yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, si ko woni : \"Kisiyee woni e mon!\". ЖҒe naataali mo kono hiЙ“e tamЖҙinii"
  7,47,"Si giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fewtiniraa Й“annge yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en, Й“e wi'a : \"Joomi amen! Wata A waЙ—tidu men e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,48,"YimЙ“e La'raafi Й“en noddi worЙ“e, hiЙ“e anndira Й“en maandeeji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"Nafaali on mooЙ“ugol mon [jawle], e kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on mawnintinoo"
  7,49,"E ko Й“ee Й—oo woondirnoЙ—on [wonnde] Alla memintaa Й“e yurmeende?! Naatee Aljanna! Kulol alanaa on, wanaa onon woni ko sunoytoo"
  7,50,"YimЙ“e Yiite Й“en noddi yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, si ko woni : \"Yuppee e amen ndiyam, maa kon ko Alla arsiki on\". ЖҒe wi'a: \"Pellet, Alla harmini Й—in Й—iЙ—i e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  7,51,"ЖҒen jogitoriiЙ“e diina mun kan mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru, nguurndam aduna hodi Й“e. Hannde Men yejjitiray Й“e no Й“e yejjitirnoo hawrugol Г‘alaande maЙ“Й“e ndee, e kon ko Й“e yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,52,"GomЙ—ii Men addanii Й“e Deftere, Men fensitiri nde e dow anndal, ko nde peewal e yurmeende Й“en yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,53,"Hara hiЙ“e habbii si wanaa battane mun Й—en? Г‘alnde battane (firo) mayre arata, yejjitunooЙ“e Й—um Й“en ko adii wi'ay : \"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“en addii goonga. Hara tefooЙ“e no woodani men Й“e tefana men? Maa men ruttee [aduna] men golla ko wanaa ko men gollaaynoo?\" GomЙ—ii Й“e hayrinii wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e ; kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo majjiriЙ“e"
  7,54,"Pellet, Joomi mon ko Alla, On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e nder balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka hoore Arsi. Himo suddira jemma on Гұalorma, hiЙ—i Й—aЙ“Й“indira no yaccorii. Naange ngen e lewru ndun e koode Й—en ko eltiraaЙ—i yamiroore Makko. Faamee ko Kanko heeranii tagu ngun e yamiroore nden. Mawnii mawngu Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden. @Corrected"
  7,55,"Noddiiree Joomi mon yankinaare e gunndoo. Pellet, Kanko O YiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,56,"Wata on bonnu ke leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Noddiree Mo kulol e tama'u. Pellet, yumeende Alla nden no Й“adii moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  7,57,"Ko Kanko woni Nuloowo keneeli Й—in welo-welo yeeso Yurmeende Makko nden. Haa si ndu ronndike duulere teddunde, Men Sogga nde e leydi maayndi [yoori], Men Jippina e mayri ndiyam, Men Yaltinira Й—am kala dimЙ—e. Ko non Men Yaltiniroyta maayЙ“e Й“en. Belajo'o, on waajitoto"
  7,58,"Leydi moЖҙЖҙiri ndin, puЙ—i mayri no yaltira duЕӢayee Joomi mayri ; ndin ndi (puЙ—i mun) boni, ndi yaltintaa si wanaa no saЙ—tiri. Ko non Men ЖҒannginirta Aayeeje Й—en woannde yimЙ“e yettooЙ“e [Joomi mun]"
  7,59,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Г‘alaande mawnde"
  7,60,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  7,61,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,62,"MiЙ—o yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, miЙ—o laaЙ“ana on (reedu), miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,63,"E on haawi fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on rento, belajo'o, on (heЙ“ay) yurmeende [Alla]"
  7,64,"ЖҒe fenni mo. Men daЙ—ndii mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko ka laana, Men yooli Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, Й“e laatino yimЙ“e wumiЙ—uЙ“e"
  7,65,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla, reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. E on hulataa [Mo]"
  7,66,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e Й—ayre, menen meЙ—en sikku maa jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,67,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й—ayre (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,68,"MiЙ—o yottina e mo'on Nule Joomi am, min (non) ko mi laaЙ“anoo on (reedu), hoolniiЙ—o"
  7,69,"E haawnu on fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on, fii yo o jertin on?! Janntee tuma nde O WaЙ—unoo on lontiiЙ“e Й“aawo yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, O Й“eydi on ka tagu cemmbe. Jantee neemaaji Alla Й—in belajo'o, on malete"
  7,70,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"E a aru e amen fii yo men rewu Alla tun, men acca kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en rewaynoo?! Awa addan men ko foduЙ—aa men kon (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goognuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,71,"O maaki : \"GomЙ—ii yanii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon soЙ“e (lepte) e tikkere. E on wenjay lam fii inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on onon e baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, Alla Jippinaali fii majje hujja?! Faditee! Min, wonndude e mo'on, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e faditiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,72,"Men daЙ—ndiri mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko yurmeende Amen, Men taЖҙi Й“abbe Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatanooki gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  7,73,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Samuuda'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. GomЙ—ii arii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon : mbaa ko ngelooba Alla maande wonannde on, tertee mba Гұaama ka leydi Alla, wata on memir mba bone sakko lepte muusuЙ—e nannga on"
  7,74,"Annditee tuma nde O waЙ—unoo on lontiiЙ“e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, O weerni on ka leydi hiЙ—on jogitoo e ndantaaji mayri kuЙ“eeje, hiЙ—on lesa pelle (waЙ—on) cuuЙ—i. Annditee neemaaji Alla Й—in, wata on Й“urtinir ka leydi ko on bonnooЙ“e"
  7,75,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e lo'inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e : \"E hiЙ—on anndi wonnde Saalihu ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka Joomi makko?\" ЖҒe wi'i : Menen ko men gomЙ—imЙ“e ko o Nulidaa e mun kon"
  7,76,"ЖҒen mawnintiniiЙ“e wi'i : \"Menen, kon ko gomЙ—inЙ—on, ko men yedduЙ“e Й—um"
  7,77,"ЖҒe borii ngelooba mban, Й“e mawnintinii gaay e yamiroore Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko an yo Saalihu, addan men kon ko foduЙ—aa men (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,78,"Dillaango ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii"
  7,79,"O hucci Й“e o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, gomЙ—ii mi yottinii e mon Nulal Joomi am ngal mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu), konnon, on yiЙ—aa laaЙ“ooЙ“e (reedu) Й“en"
  7,80,"E luuti, tuma nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \" E o aray pankare Й—e goЙ—Й—o goo adaaki on e mun e Winndere nden"
  7,81,"Onon hiЙ—on yottoo e worЙ“e Й“en tuuyo accon rewЙ“e Й“en! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fantimЙ“e"
  7,82,"Jaabawol makko Й“en wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e wi'i : \"Yaltinee Й“e ka hoЙ—o mon ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"
  7,83,"Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on ; onЙ—on heddoduno e (leptaaЙ“e) Й“en"
  7,84,Men saaЖҙini toЙ“o e maЙ“Й“e. Ndaarii ko honno battane bomЙ“e Й“en laatornoo
  7,85,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Su'aybu, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. GomЙ—ii Й“anngannduyee arii on immorde ka Joomi mon. Timminee etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikke Й—en, wata on Й—uytan yimЙ“e Й“en piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wata on bonnu ko leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙannde si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  7,86,"Wata on jooЙ—o e kala laawol, hiЙ—on kammba, hiЙ—on sakko=faloo e laawol Alla ngol Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Mo, hiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұaare. Annditee tuma nde wonnoЙ—on seeЙ—aaЙ“e O Й—uЙ—Й—ini on. Ndaaree honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  7,87,"Si wonii fedde e mooЙ—on gomЙ—inii kon ko Nuliraa e mun, fedde goo gomЙ—inaali, muГұГұee haa Alla Гұaawa hakkunde me'en. Ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,88,"Mbatu mawnintiniingu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Ko maa men yaltine an Su'aybu, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonndude e maaЙ—a ka saare amen, maa ruttoЙ—on e diina amen\". -O maaki : \"Hay si tawii ko men aГұuЙ“e [Й—um]"
  7,89,"GomЙ—ii (haray) men fefindike e hoore Alla fenaande si men ruttike e diina mon Й“aawo nde Alla daЙ—ndi men e makka. Alanaa men nde men ruttoo e makka si wanaa nde Alla Joomi amen muuyi. Joomi amen yaajanii kala huunde Anndal. Ko e Alla men fawii. Joomi amen, Гұaawir hakkunde amen e yimЙ“e amen Й“en goonga, ko An woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,90,"Mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Pellet, si on jokkii Su'aybu, onon ontuma ko on hayruЙ“e"
  7,91,"Dillaango ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii"
  7,92,"ЖҒen fennunooЙ“e Su'aybu, (Й“e halkorino) wa si Й“e meeЙ—aa wuurude e ngon [hoЙ—o]. ЖҒen fennunooЙ“e Su'aybu, Й“e laatino kamЙ“e woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,93,"O Й—uurni Й“e, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, gomЙ—ii mi yottinii e mo'on Nule Joomi am Й—en mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu). E ko honno mi surnortoo e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e"
  7,94,"Men nulaali e saare hay e Annbaajo, si wanaa Men nanngirii yimЙ“e mayre Й“en saЙ—teende e lorra belajo'o, Й“e yankinoto"
  7,95,"Refti Men waЙ—titiri nokku bone on moЖҙЖҙere, haa Й“e Й—uuЙ—i, Й“e wi'i : \"GomЙ—ii saЙ—tteende e newennde heЙ“iino baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en\". Men nanngiri Й“e juhal, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa anndude"
  7,96,"Sinno yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en gomЙ—inno Й“e huli (Joomi maЙ“Й“e), Men udditanayno Й“e moЖҙЖҙereeji immorde ka Kammu e ka leydi. Kono Й“e fenni, Men nanngitiri Й“e (lepte Й—en) kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo"
  7,97,"Hara yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en hooli nde lepte Amen Й—en arataa Й“e jemma, hara hiЙ“e Й—aanii"
  7,98,"Kaa hara yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en hooli nde lepte Amen Й—en arataa Й“e ka walluhaa, hara hiЙ“e fija"
  7,99,E Й“e hooli pewje Alla Й—en? Hoolotaako pewje Alla Й—en si wanaa yimЙ“e hayruЙ“e Й“en
  7,100,"E Й“annganaali Й“en ronooЙ“e leydi Й“en Й“aawo (halkagol) yimЙ“e mayri Й“en, wonnde si Men Muuyuno Men meminirayno Й“e [lepte Й—en] junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in? Men nota e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hara kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa"
  7,101,"ЖҠen ca'e, MeЙ—en fillano maa kumpite majje. GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e wonaano gomЙ—inooЙ“e ko Й“e fenni kon ko adii. Ko wano nii All notirta e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  7,102,"Men tawaano ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e hunnooЙ“e ahadi ; si ko men tawi, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  7,103,"Refti Men Nulidi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Muusaa e Maandeeji Amen Й—in haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'un, Й“e yeddi Й—i. Ndaaru ko honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  7,104,"Muusaa maaki : \"Ko an yo Fir'awna, min ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,105,No hanndi e am nde mi wowlataa e hoore Alla si wanaa goonga. GomЙ—ii mi addanii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon. neldam e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en
  7,106,"[Fir'awna] wi'i : \"Si tawii a ardii e Maande, addu nde si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  7,107,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande=ngoolwa Й“anngundi"
  7,108,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaarooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,109,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en wi'i : \"Pellet, oo, ko mbileejo annduЙ—o"
  7,110,"O faala yaltinnde on ka leydi mo'on\". -\"Ko honЙ—um yamirton"
  7,111,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musiЙ—Й—o makko on, nulaa e ca'e Й—en mooЙ“ooЙ“e (mbile)"
  7,112,ЖҒe addane kala mbileejo annduЙ—o
  7,113,"MbileeЙ“e Й“en ari Fir'awna Й“e wi'i : \"Hara njoЙ“di no woodani men, si men wonii fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  7,114,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray on jeyaama e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,115,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, si Й—a yiЙ—i ko nde bugotoЙ—aa, maa men wona (adotooЙ“e) bugagol"
  7,116,"O maaki : \"Bugee\". Nde Й“e bugii, Й“e mbilЙ—ii gite yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e hulЙ“ini Й“e, Й“e addi mbilewu mawnungu"
  7,117,"Men wahyini e Muusaa wonnde : \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\". Jaka yoo hindi moЙ—a ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  7,118,"Goonga on feeГұi, ko Й“e gollaynoo kon [fow] boni"
  7,119,ЖҒe foolaa Й—on Й“e hooti ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e
  7,120,MbileeЙ“e Й“en suuyi sujji
  7,121,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men gomЙ—inii JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,122,JeyЙ—o Muusaa e Haaruuna
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : \"On gomЙ—in mo ado mi duЕӢinannde=sakkitoore on? Pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko fewjoore nde fewjuЙ—on ka saare fii no yaltiniron ton yimЙ“e mayre. ma on anndonu"
  7,124,"Ma mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal"
  7,125,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Menen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen"
  7,126,"A aГұiraali men si wanaa fii men gomЙ—inii Maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde Й—i arunoo men. Joomi amen! Yuppu muГұal e amen, Жҙettitaa men ko men jebbilii Й“e"
  7,127,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna ngun wi'i : \"A accay Muusaa e yimЙ“e mun Й“en no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e reweteeЙ—i maa Й—in?!\" O wi'i : \"Ma men waru Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en men accita Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en (wuura). Pellet, menen, e dow maЙ“Й“e ko men foolooЙ“e"
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \"Wallinoree Alla muГұГұoЙ—on. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en ko gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en woodani"
  7,129,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men lorranooma ado a arde men e Й“aawo nde arЙ—aa men\". O maaki : \"Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata gaГұo mon O lontina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko honno gollirton"
  7,130,"GomЙ—ii Men nanngirii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en kokke e Й—uytagol dimЙ—e ; belajo'o, Й“e waajitoto"
  7,131,"Si moЖҙЖҙere nden arii Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"MeЙ—en hanndi e ndee Й—oo\" ; si bone on heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e kiitinora Muusaa e wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en. Anndee pellet, kiiti maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  7,132,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Kala ko addan Й—aa Й“en e Aayaa fii no mbilЙ—oraa men Й—um ; men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e ma"
  7,133,"Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, ko Aayeeje fensitaaЙ—e, Й“e mawnintinii, Й“e laatii yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte Й—en yanunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i : \"ko an Muusaa, torano men Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maaЙ—a. Si a huncanii men Й—ee lepte, ma men gomЙ—ine, ma men accide kadi e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  7,135,"Nde Men huncannoo Й“e lepte Й—en haa e lajal ngal Й“e yottotoo, jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e firtooЙ“e (ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin)"
  7,136,"Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e ; Men yooliri Й“e ka maayo sabu ko Й“e fenniri kon Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatii welsindiiЙ“e e majje"
  7,137,"Men ronini yimЙ“e wonanooЙ“e lo'ineede Й“en fuЙ—naange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi Men barkini e mu'un. Konngol Joomi maa moЖҙЖҙongol ngol timmii e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon. Men halki ko Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mun Й“en moЖҙЖҙinanynoo, e kon ko Й“e Й“amtaynoo (e kuЙ“eeje)"
  7,138,"Men lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon, Й“e rewi ka yimЙ“e ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e (e rewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, waЙ—an men reweteeЙ—o wano reweteeЙ—i woodirani Й“e non\". O maaki : \"Pellet, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjooЙ“e"
  7,139,"Pellet, Й“ee Й—oo, ko Й“e woni e mun kon ko halkaaЙ—um, kadi ko mere woni ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“anta on reweteeЙ—o, Kanko O Й“urnii on e Winndere nden"
  7,141,"(Annditee) tuma nde Men daЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, hiЙ“e meeЙ—ina on lepte bonЙ—e : Й“e wara Й“iЙ—Й“e mon worЙ“e Й“e heddina rewЙ“e mon Й“en. No e Й—um mooЙ—on jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon"
  7,142,"Men haldidi e Muusaa jemmaaji cappanЙ—i tati, Men timminiri Й—i sappo, happu Joomi makko on timmiri jemmaaji cappanЙ—e nayi. Muusaa maakani neene-gooto makko on Haaruuna : \"Lonto lam ka yimЙ“e am, moЖҙЖҙinaa (fiyaake maЙ“Й“e), wata a jokku laawol bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,143,"Nde Muusaa arunoo fii happu amen on Joomi makko yewti mo, o maaki : \"Joomi, hollam mi ndaare!\" O Daali : \"A yi'ataa lam ; kono ndaaru fello ngon : si ngo ГұiiЙ“ii e nokku maggo, aray ka yi'aa lam\". Nde Joomi makko feeГұannoo fello ngon, O waЙ—ti ngo Й—iggu ngo, Muusaa yani faЙ—Й—aa. Nde o Й—iwtunoo, o maaki : \"Senayee woodanu Ma! Mi tuubanii Ma, min ko mi arano e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  7,144,"O Daali : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, Min Mi suЙ“orii ma e yimЙ“e Й“en Nule Am Й—en e konngol am ngol. Jogito ko Mi jonnu maa kon jeyeeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,145,"Men winndani mo ka alluuje kala huunde, waaju e fensitannde kala huunde. Jogitor nde doole, yamiraa yimЙ“e maa Й“en jogitagol ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mayre. Arma Mi holla on galle faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,146,"Mi suray gaay e Aayeeje Am Й—en Й“en mawnintinorayЙ“e ka leydi ko aldaa e goonga. Hay si Й“e yi'i kala Aaya Й“e gomЙ—intaa mo, si Й“e yi'ii laawol peewal ngol Й“e jogitotaako ngol laawol, si Й“e yi'ii laawol bewre ngol Й“e jogitoo ngol laawol. ЖҠum non, ko tawde Й“e fennii Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e woni welsindiiЙ“e e majje"
  7,147,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hawrugol e laakara, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii. Hara Й“en yoЙ“oyte si wanaa kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,148,"YimЙ“e Muusa Й“en jogitii Й“aawo makko cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin ngaari Й“anndinnke, hindi mari nuunaango=kuunaali. E Й“e yi'aali wonnde nde yewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e ndi fewntanaa Й“e kadi e laawol? ЖҒe jogitike ndii [ngaari reweteendi], Й“e laatii tooГұooЙ“e"
  7,149,"Nde yantunoo e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e yi'i wonnde gomЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e wi'i : \"Si Joomi amen yurmaaka men, O haforani men, pellet, men laatoday e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,150,"Nde Muusaa ruttinoo e yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o, suniiЙ—o, o maaki : \"Bonii kon ko lontiЙ—on lam Й“aawo am. E on hawjan yamiroore Joomi mon nden?!\" O weddii alluuje Й—en o nanngi hoore neene-gooto makko on himo pooЙ—a mo e makko. [Haaruuna] Maaki : \"Ko an yo Й“iЙ—Й—o neene am, Й“ee yimЙ“e lo'inii lam, Й“e do'i warugol lam. Wata a weltin ayЙ“e am, wata a waЙ—tidam kadi e yimЙ“e toonoЙ“e Й“en"
  7,151,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, haforanam min e neene-gooto am on, naadaa men ka yurmeende Maa. Ko An woni Й“urЙ—o yurmeede e yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,152,"Pellet, Й“en jogitii Й“e ngaari ndin (reweteendi), arma tikkere heЙ“a Й“e immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e koyeera ka nguurndam aduna. Ko wano non Men yoЙ“irta fefindotooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,153,"ЖҒen golluЙ“e boneeji, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—um Й“e gomЙ—ini, pellet, Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, ko haforoowo, hinnotooЙ—o"
  7,154,"Nde tikkere nden deeЖҙunoo e Muusaa, o Жҙetti alluuje Й—en. Tawi no e binndoodi majje, peewal e yurmeende wonannde Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun"
  7,155,"Muusaa suЙ“ii e yimЙ“e makko Й“en worЙ“e cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—o fii happu Amen. Nde dillaango ngon nanngunoo Й“e, o maaki : \"Joomi, si a muuyuno, A halkayno Й“e ado hannde, e min kadi. E A halkiray men ko Й—ayЙ“e amen Й“en huuwi? ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa jarrabuyee MaaЙ—a, HiЙ—a majjinira Й—um on Mo muuyu-ЖҠaa, HiЙ—a fewna on Mo muuyu-ЖҠaa. Ko An woni giЙ—o Amen, haforan men yurme-ЖҠaa men. Ko An woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e haforooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,156,"Winndanaa men ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere, e ka laakara. Menen men tuubanii Ma. O Daali : \"Lepte Am Й—en, Mi meminay Й—e on mo Mi muuyi. Yurmeende Am nden yaajanii kala huunde. Arma Mi winndana nde Й“en hulooЙ“e (Alla), Й“e totta zakka, e Й“en gomЙ—inooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,157,"ЖҒen jokkayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o on, Annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo Й“e tawta fii mun no winndaa ka maЙ“Й“e ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Himo yamira Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, o haЙ—a Й“e ЕӢiГұere, himo daginana Й“e dagiiЙ—i Й—in, o harminana Й“e soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, o ittana Й“e teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunooЙ—e e hoore-maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e mo, Й“e teddini mo, Й“e walli mo, Й“e jokki annoora JippinaaЙ—o wonndude e makko ; Й“en, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,158,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Alla e mooЙ—on on denndaangal, On Mo woodani Й—um laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kanko. Himo wuurna wara. GomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko Annabaajo humammbinneejo on, on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e KonnguЙ—i Makko Й—in. Jokkee mo, belajo'o, on feeway"
  7,159,"Hino e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en, mofte fewnirayЙ—e (yimЙ“e Й“en) e goonga, ko Й—um woni ko Й“e nunЙ—irta"
  7,160,"Men senndi Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i mofte. Men wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo yarnineede wonnde : \"Piyir tuggordu maa ndun hayre nden\". ЖҒulli sappo e Й—iЙ—i yallti e mayre. GomЙ—ii gorol kala andii yariride mu'un. Men Й—owdinirani Й“e duule, Men Jippini e maЙ“Й“e demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. \"Г‘aamee e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men arsiki on\". ЖҒe tooГұaali Men, kono ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұaynoo"
  7,161,"Tuma nde Й“e wi'anaa : \"HoЙ—ee e ndee saare, Гұaamon e mayre nokku kala ka yiЙ—uЙ—on, wi'on : Й“oran men [goopi amen], naatiron ka damal ko on sujjuЙ“e, Men haforanay on goopi mon. Arma Men Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  7,162,"TooГұuЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e wayliri konngol ngol ko wanaa ngol ngol Й“e wi'ananoo. Min Jippini e maЙ“Й“e lepte immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e tooГұa"
  7,163,"Lanndo Й“e fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde Й“e jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde liЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e Й—in araynooЙ“e Гұalnde Aseweere maЙ“Й“e nden ko Й—i hummbuЙ—i, Гұalnde woni wanaa aseweere maЙ“Й“e Й—i arataa Й“e. Ko wano nii Men jarriborta Й“e kon ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,164,"Tuma nde jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'unoo : \"Ko honЙ—um waajoantoЙ—on yimЙ“e, Allaahu ko halkoowo Й“e maa O lepta Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko [ittugol] nganto faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e rentoto"
  7,165,"Nde Й“e yejjitunoo ko Й“e waajanoo fii mun kon, Men daЙ—ndi Й“en haЙ—aynooЙ“e e bone on, Men nanngiri Й“en tooГұuЙ“e lepte sattuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,166,"Nde Й“e townitaninoo e ko Й“e haЙ—aa e mun kon, Men wi'ani Й“e : \"Laatee baaЙ—i jaasuЙ—i"
  7,167,"Janto tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (wonnde) ma O Nulu e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal on meeЙ—inoowo Й“e lepte bonЙ—e. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—e lepte, pellet kadi, ko O haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  7,168,"Men senndiri Й“e ka leydi jamaaji : hino e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e, hino e maЙ“Й“e ko jaasi Й—um. Men jarribori Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i e bonЙ—i, belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto"
  7,169,"Lontii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lontii Й“e (bomЙ“e), Й“e roni Deftere nden, hiЙ“e Жҙetta weeЙ“itanЙ—e oo aduna Й“e wi'a : \"Aray men haforanee\". Si weeЙ“itannde sugu mun arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Жҙetta Й—um. Hara ahadi Deftere nden Жҙettidaaka e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde wata Й“e wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! ЖҒe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en rentiiЙ“e. E on haqqiltaa"
  7,170,"ЖҒen jogitotooЙ“e Deftere nden Й“e Гұinna julde, pellet, Menen Men yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,171,"Janto tuma nde Men Й“orunoo fello ngon senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, a sikkay ko ngo Й—owdi.ЖҒe felliti ngo yanat e maЙ“Й“e. \"Jogitoree ko Men okki on kon doole, jantee ko woni e mayre, belajo'o, on kulon Alla"
  7,172,"Janto kadi nde Joomi maa Жҙettunoo e Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama Й“en ka keeci maЙ“Й“e jurriiyaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O seendintini Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in : \"Wanaa kon Min woni Joomi mon?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko non woniri, men seedike\". Ko fii (wata) on wi'oy Г‘alnde Darngal : \"Menen men woniino welsindiiЙ“e e Й—um Й—oo"
  7,173,"Maa wi'oyon : \"Anndee ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en sirkunoo ko adii, men wonti (tun) jurriiya Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. E A halkiray men ko bonnooЙ“e Й“en waЙ—i"
  7,174,"Ko wano nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, e belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto"
  7,175,"Janngan Й“e kumpite on mo Men okki Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o Й“oorii Й—e, seytaane jokki mo, e laatodii e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,176,"Sinno Men muuyuno, Men Й“amtirayno mo Й—e, ko woni tun o heddike ka leydi o jokki mbeleeЙ—e makko. Sugu makko ko sifa rawaandu, si a ronndii ndu ndu lahay, maa si a terti ndu du lahay. Ko Й—um woni misal yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Fillo qissaaji Й—in ; belajo'o, Й“e miijitoto"
  7,177,"[Alaa ko Й“uri] bonnde misal Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e woni ko Й“e tooГұaynoo"
  7,178,"Kala mo Alla fewni, ko on feewata ; kala kadi mo O majjini, ko Й“en hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,179,"GomЙ—ii Men taganii Jahannama ko Й—uuЙ—i e jinna e yimЙ“e. HiЙ“e mari Й“erЙ—e, Й“e faamirtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari gite, Й“e yi'irtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari noppi, Й“e nanirtaa Й—i. ЖҒen no wa'i wa neemoraaЙ—i, toode ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude. Ko Й“en woni welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,180,"Ko Alla woodani inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude Й—en. Noddiree Mo Й—e, tertoЙ—on Й“en ooГұotooЙ“e ka inЙ—e Makko : arma Й“e yoЙ“oyee ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,181,"Hino e Й“en Й“e Men tagi, mofte feewirayЙ—e goonga, ko Й—um kadi Й“e nunЙ—irta"
  7,182,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Men suyniray Й“e e nokku ka Й“e anndaa"
  7,183,"MiЙ—o nennana Й“e, pellet, pewje Am Й—en ko tiiЙ—uЙ—e"
  7,184,"E Й“ee miijitaaki? wonndiiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on aldaa e jinna : on wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  7,185,"E Й“e ndaaraali laamuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ko Alla tagi e piiji, e haawnaaki hara lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal Й“adike? E ko yewtere honnde Й“aawo ndee Й—oo Й“e gomЙ—inta"
  7,186,"Kala mo Alla majjini, fewnoowo mo alaa. Himo acca Й“e e bewre maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e bumam-bumannoo"
  7,187,"HiЙ“e lanndo maa fii darngal : \"ko honnde woni daragol maggal?\" Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Joomi am woni. Alaa feГұГұioowo waqtu maggal on si wanaa Kanko. Ngal teddii ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngal arataa e mon si wanaa e juhal\". HiЙ“e lanndo maa a sikkay ko a huЙ“indiiЙ—o e Й—um. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Alla woni\". kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa [Й—um]"
  7,188,"Maaku : \"Mi waawanaa hoore-am nafa wanaa lorra, si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Sinno miЙ—o anndunoo ko wirnii, mi hebbinorayno moЖҙЖҙere, bone kadi memataano lam. Mi wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo e wewlinoowo, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,189,"Ko Kanko woni taguЙ—o on immorde e wonkii wooti, O waЙ—i e makki genndo makko, fii yo o deeЖҙu e makko. Tuma nde o renndunoo e makko, o sowii sowannde hoyfunde, o duumodi e mun. Nde o teddidunoo [e reedu ndun], Й“e torodi Alla Joomi maЙ“Й“e : \"Pellet, si a yeЙ—ii men (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, ma men jeye e yettooЙ“e Ma Й“en"
  7,190,"Nde O yeЙ—unoo Й“e (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, Й“e waЙ—idani Mo kafidiiЙ“e e kon ko O yeЙ—i Й“e. Alla toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  7,191,"E Й“e kafiday (Mo) e kon ko tagataa hay e huunde, kamЙ“e tigi ko Й“e tagaaЙ“e"
  7,192,"ЖҠi waawanaa Й“e ballal, wanaa (hay) ko'e majji Й—i wallata"
  7,193,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i jokkataa on. Hino fotanan on ter, si on noddii Й—i maa hara ko on deyЖҙuЙ“e"
  7,194,"Pellet, Й—in Й—i noddoton gaanin Alla, ko jeyaaЙ—i yeruuji mon. Noddee Й—i, yo Й—i jaabinanii on, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  7,195,"Hara hiЙ—i mari koyЙ—e ko Й—i yahra? kaa hiЙ—i mari juuЙ—e ko Й—i duГұira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari gite ko Й—i yi'ira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari noppi ko Й—i nanira? Maaku : \"Noddee kafidiiЙ—i mon Й—in, refti fewjanon lam, wata on nennitanam"
  7,196,"Pellet, ko Alla woni heftuЙ—o e am on, On JippinЙ—o Deftetere nden, ko Kanko woni heftoowo moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,197,"ЖҠin Й—i noddoton gaanin Mo, Й—i hattanaa e wallugol on, wanaa kadi ko'e majji Й—i wallata"
  7,198,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i nanataa. A yi'ay Й—i hiЙ—i ndaare, (kono) kannji Й—i yi'ataa"
  7,199,"Jogito yaafuyee, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere nden Й—uurno-Й—aa e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,200,"Si sowinsinoore arii heЙ“ude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Alla. Kanko ko O nanoowo, annduЙ—o"
  7,201,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e, si sowonsinoore heЙ“ii Й“e immorde e sytaane, Й“e annditay [Alla] : jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e yi'ooЙ“e"
  7,202,"SiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en [ka yimЙ“e] hino pooЙ—a Й“e e bewre, refti Й“e raЙ“Й“indintaako"
  7,203,"Si a addanaali Й“e Aaya, Й“e wi'ay : \"Ko haЙ—unoo sincaa Й—um?\" Maaku : \"Anndee ko jokku-mi, ko kon wahyina e am immorde ka Joomi am. Ndee Й—oo [Alqur'aanaare] ko hujjaaji (Й“annguЙ—i) immorde ka Joomi mon, e peewal e yurmeende wonnande yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,204,"Si Alqur'aana no janngeede, heЙ—tee nde deЖҙЖҙiton ; belajo'o, on yurminte"
  7,205,"Annditu Joomi maaЙ—a ka wonkii maa, ka yankinaare e ka kulol, ko aldaa e feГұГұingol konngol, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e, wata a laatodo e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,206,"Pellet, Й“en [Malaa'ikaaЙ“e] wonЙ“e ka Joomi maa, Й“e townitantaako rewugol Mo, hiЙ“e subbunhinanoo Mo, ko Kanko woni ko Й“e sujjanta"
  8,1,"HiЙ“e lanndo maa fii konhoyri. Maaku : \"Konhoyri ndin ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on jeyi\". Hulee Alla, moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde mon Й—oftoЙ—on kadi Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  8,2,"Pellet, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en Й“e (tawata) si Alla jantaama, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hulay. Si Aayeeje Makko Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e Й“eyda Й“e gomЙ—inal. Ko e Joomi maЙ“Й“e (tun) Й“e fawotoo"
  8,3,ЖҒen ГұinnooЙ“e julde nden e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e hiЙ“e wintoo=nafqa
  8,4,"ЖҒen Й—on, ko kamЙ“e woni gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ka goonga : hino woodani Й“e darjaaji ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e haforaneede e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  8,5,"Ko wano Joomi maa yaltinirno maa non ka suudu maa sabu goonga, (tawi non) pellet, fedde e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ko aГұuЙ“e (Й—um)"
  8,6,HiЙ“e wennja maa fii goonga kan Й“aawo nde ka feeГұi ; a sikkay ko Й“e wonaaЙ“e soggeede e maayde hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e ndaara (Й—um)
  8,7,"(Jantee) tuma nde Alla fodunoo on gootel e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i, wonnde \"gootel e majji ko onon woodani, hiЙ—on yeloo sinno ko fedde nde alaa doole nden laatantoo on, (tawi) Alla no yiЙ—i nde O goonginirta goonga kan Daaluyeeji Makko Й—in O taЖҙa Й“abbe heeferaaЙ“e Й“en"
  8,8,"Fii yo O goonginiri goonga kan O bonne fii meere nden, hay si bomЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—aa"
  8,9,"(Jantee) tuma nde faabinoranoЙ—on Joomi mon O jaabinani on : \"Min ko Mi Й“eydiroowo on ujunere e Malaa'ika jokkondirooЙ“e"
  8,10,"Alla waЙ—iraali Й—um si wanaa welo-welo e fii no Й“erЙ—e mon deeЖҙira Й—um. Balla wonaali si wanaa immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,11,"E Tuma nde ЕӢoЕӢre nden hippaynoo on hoolaare immorde ka Makko, Himo Jippinana on ndiyam immorde ka kammu fii yo O laЙ“Й“inir on Й—am, O ittana on soЙ“e seytaane, e fii yo O tiiЙ—inir (Й—um) e Й“erЙ—e mon O tabintinira Й—am teppe [mon] Й—en"
  8,12,"Tuma nde Joomi maa wahyinaynoo e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“e : \"Min MiЙ—o wonndi e mo'on : tabintinee gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Arma Mi bugoo Й—enЖҙere e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en. Tappee dow daaЙ—e Й—en tappon e maЙ“Й“e kala wunnjere"
  8,13,"ЖҠum, ko fii kamЙ“e Й“e lunndike Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. \"Kala non lunndiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, pellet, Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  8,14,"ЖҠum mooЙ—on ; meeЙ—ee Й—um ! E wonnde pellet, no waadani heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte Yiite"
  8,15,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on hawrii e Й“en heeferЙ“e ko Й“e mooЙ“iiЙ“e, wata on huccintinan Й“e Й“abbe Й—en"
  8,16,"Kala hunccintinЙ—o Й“e nden Гұalnde (Й“abbal mu'un), -si wanaa hara ko on heЙ“Й“itantooЙ—o hare nden, maa hara ko ukkitotooЙ—o e fedde, -gomЙ—ii haray o ruttodii e tikkere immorde ka Alla, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama nge bonii ruttorde"
  8,17,"On waraano Й“e : Ko Allaahu On wari Й“e. A feranooki tuma ferinoЙ—aa : Ko Allaahu On ferii, e fii yo O jarribor gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Makko jarrabuyee moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  8,18,"ЖҠum mooЙ—on, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko lo'inoowo pewje heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  8,19,"Si on Й—aЙ“Й“ii uddital, gomЙ—ii uddital arii on. Si on haЙ—itike, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Si on fillitike, Men fillitoo. Fedde mon nden duncanoytaa on hay e huunde, hay si nde Й—uuЙ—ii. Tawde pellet, Alla no wonndi e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  8,20,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й—oftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on wata on huccu mo hara hiЙ—on nannde (Aayeeje Й—en)"
  8,21,"Wata on wa'u wa Й“en wi'unooЙ“e : \"Men nanii\", tawi kamЙ“e Й“e alaa e nanude"
  8,22,"Pellet, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko faaЙ—uЙ“e mumЙ“e Й“e haqqiltaa"
  8,23,"Sinno Alla annduno e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, O naninayno Й“e. Hay si O naninno Й“e, Й“e huccitayno hara ko Й“e Й—uurnii Й“e"
  8,24,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, Nootee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on si Й“e noddii on fi ko wuurnata on (e goonga), anndee pellet, Alla no heeda hakkunde neЙ—Й—o e Й“ernde mun, e wonnde pellet, ko ka Makko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on"
  8,25,"Rentee e bone tawЙ—o o memataa tooГұuЙ“e Й“en e mooЙ—on tun. Anndee pellet, Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  8,26,"Annditee tuma wonunoЙ—on fanЙ—uЙ“e, lo'inaaЙ“e ka leydi, hiЙ—on hula nde yimЙ“e Й“en jilotoo on. O weerni on, O semmbiniri on ballal Makko ngal, O arsiki on immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i belajo'o, on yettay (neemaaji makko Й—in)"
  8,27,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on janfo Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, janfoЙ—on koolaaje mon Й—en hara hiЙ—on anndi"
  8,28,"Anndee pellet, jawle mon Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ko fitina e wonnde no ka Alla njoЙ“di mawndi"
  8,29,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on hulii Alla, O waЙ—anay on senndindirЙ—um (goonga e meere), O heefana on bakkatuuji mon O haforana on. Alla ko Jom-ЖҒural mawnungal"
  8,30,"(Jantii) tuma nde heeferЙ“e Й“en fewjanayno maa fii yoЙ“e aamin maa Й“e ware maa Й“e yaltine. HiЙ“e fewja, Alla no fewja. Ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude fewjooЙ“e Й“en"
  8,31,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"GomЙ—ii men nanii, sinno men yiЙ—uno men wowlayno yeru Й—um, ndee wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  8,32,"E tuma Й“e wi'unoo : \"Yaa Alla, si tawii ko Й—um woni goonga immorde ka MaaЙ—a, haray saaЖҙin kaaЖҙe e amen immorde ka kammu, maa addanaa men lepte muusuЙ—e"
  8,33,"Alla wonaani leptoowo Й“e, hara an hiЙ—a hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Alla siforaali leptoowo Й“e, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e insinaade"
  8,34,"Ko haЙ—ata Й“e nde Alla leptataa Й“e, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sakkaade Juulirde hormante nden? ЖҒe wonaali heftuЙ“e nde. HeftuЙ“e Mo wonaali si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—umЙ“e, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  8,35,"Julde maЙ“Й“e nden ka Suudu wonaali, si wanaa wuuЙ—ugol e kellugol : \"MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu ko yeddiraynoЙ—on kon"
  8,36,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, hiЙ“e nafqira jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no Й“e sakkora (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Alla ngol. Maa Й“e nafqu Й—e, refti wontana Й“e ninse, refti Й“e foolee. ЖҒen yedduЙ“e non, ko ka Jahannama Й“e mooЙ“oytee"
  8,37,"Fii yo Alla senndindir soЙ“e Й—en e ko laaЙ“i kon, O waЙ—a soЙ“e Й—en yoga mun e dow yoga, O fawindira Й—um fow O waЙ—ta Й—um ka nder Jahamma. ko Й“en Й—on woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  8,38,"Maakan Й“en yedduЙ“e: si Й“e haЙ—itike; Й“e haforante ko yawti. Si Й“e fillitike, haray gomЙ—ii laawol adinooЙ“e Й“en yawtii"
  8,39,"HaЙ“ee Й“e haa ka tawata fitina laatotaako, diina kan fow laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray pellet, Alla ko reenuЙ—o ko Й“e golla kon"
  8,40,"Si Й“e huccitii, anndee pellet, ko Alla woni GiЙ—o mon. O yooЙ—ii GiЙ—o O yooЙ—ii Ballo"
  8,41,"Anndee wonnde kala ko konЙ—on e huunde, pellet, hino woodani Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on jowaЙ“al mun, e jom-Й“adondiral, e wonЙ—uЙ“e (Alyatimeebe) Й“en, e waasuЙ“e Й“en, e Й“iЙ—Й“e laawol Й“en, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e kon ko Men Jippini e jeyaaЙ—o Amen on, Г‘alnde sertugol (goonga e fenaande): Гұalnde dente Й—en Й—iЙ—i fottunoo. Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  8,42,"Nde tawnoo onon hiЙ—on ka baЕӢЕӢe Й“aЙ—tiiЙ—e, kamЙ“e (ayЙ“e Й“en) hiЙ“e ka baЕӢЕӢe woЙ—Й—itiiЙ—e, tawi waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e Й“en no senngo ley mon. Sinno on saatondirno, on luutondirayno ka caate. Kono ko fii yo Alla Гұaawu fiyaaku laatinooЙ—o golleteeЙ—o, fii yo maayowo maayu e ko Й“anngi, wuuroowo wuura e Й“anngi. E pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  8,43,"Tuma nde Alla hollayno maa Й“e ka Й—oyngol maaЙ—a ko Й“e seeЙ—aaЙ“e. Sinno O holluno Й“e ko Й“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e, on lo'ayno, on pooЙ—indiryno kadi e fiyaaku on. Kono Alla hisini. Pellet, Kanko ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  8,44,"E tuma nde Alla hollaynoo on Й“e, nde fottunoЙ—on, ko Й“e seeЙ—aaЙ“e e gite mon, Himo fanЙ—ina on kadi e gite maЙ“Й“e fii yo Alla Гұaawo fiyaaku laatinooЙ—o golleteeЙ—o. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  8,45,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on fottii e fedde (ayЙ“e Й“e), tabitee, jantoЙ—on Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i=heewi; belajo'o, on malete"
  8,46,"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on pooЙ—ondir sakko lo'on doole mon yaha. MuГұГұee, pellet, Alla no wonndi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  8,47,"Wata on wa'u wa Й“en yaltirnooЙ“e ka galleeji maЙ“Й“e townitaare e yiinagol yimЙ“e, hiЙ“e faddo laawol Alla ngol. Alla non ko fiiltiiЙ—o ko Й“e gollata"
  8,48,"E tuma nde seytaane cuЙ—aynnoo Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en o wi'i: \"Fooloowo on alaa hannde e yimЙ“e Й“en, min non ko mi kawtal mo'on\". Nde feddeeji Й—iЙ—i yi'indirnoo, o yiltorii gaЙ—a teppe makko o wi'i: \"Min ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o(kisЙ—o) e mon. Min miЙ—o yi'a ko on yi'ataa, min mi hulii Alla. Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—e lepte"
  8,49,"Tuma nde naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en e Й“en Й“e Гұawu [lo'ere iimaanu] wonu e Й“erЙ—e mun wi'aynoo : \"Diina Й“ee Й—oo kan hodii Й“e\". Kala non fawiiЙ—o e Alla, pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,50,"Sinno a yi'ayno tuma Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en warata heeferЙ“e Й“en, Й“e piya geece maЙ“Й“e e Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e (Й“e wi'ora Й“e) : \"MeeЙ—ee lepte cumu"
  8,51,"ЖҠum (heЙ“irii on) sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en addi ko. wonnde pellet, Alla wonaali TooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  8,52,"Wano mboowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe yeddii Aayeeje Alla Й—en. Alla Nanngitiri Й“e junubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Pellet, Alla ko TiiЙ—uЙ—o SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  8,53,"(Ko waЙ—i) Й—um, ko tawde Alla wonaali waylowo neema mo O neemini e yimЙ“e haa Й“e wayla ko woni e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e. E wonnde pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  8,54,"Wano mboowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe fennii Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Men halkiri Й“e junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men yooli yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en. Kala (maЙ“Й“e) laatino tooГұooЙ“e"
  8,55,"Pellet, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko Й“en yedduЙ“e, kamЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  8,56,"ЖҒen Й“e ahodiЙ—aa e mu'un refti Й“e firta ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin e kala laawol, kamЙ“e Й“e hulataa [Alla]"
  8,57,"Si waawii Й“e ka hare, yagginir (sar) Й“e arooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. Belajo'o, Й“e waajitoto"
  8,58,"Ammaa si a hulii e yimЙ“e janfa, bugita(werla) e maЙ“Й“e (firtugol ahadi ndin) dow fotondiral, tawde pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa janfotooЙ“e Й“en"
  8,59,"Wata Й“en yedduЙ“e sikku Й“e laawki. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e ronknitaa (Lam)"
  8,60,"Resoranee(heblanee) Й“e kala ko hattanЙ—on e doole e pucci hebilaaЙ—i, hulЙ“iniron Й—um ayЙ“e Alla Й“en e ayЙ“e mon Й“en, e woЙ—Й“e goo gaanin maЙ“Й“e Й“e onon on anndaabe Alla kaГұun no anndi Й“e. Kala ko nafkudon e laawol Alla ngol hunnanoyte on, onon on tooГұoytaake"
  8,61,"Si Й“e naayanike kisal nagl, naayano ngal (an kadi) fawoЙ—aa e Alla, pellet, Kanko ko O nanoowo annduЙ—o"
  8,62,"Si Й“e faandike nde Й“e janfoto maa, pellet, ko Alla yonay maa. Ko Kanko woni semmbinirЙ—o ma e ballal Makko ngal, e (wallitagol) gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  8,63,"O woowindiri hakkunde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Sinno a wintinonafkuna ko woni kon ka leydi fow, a woowindirtaano hakkunde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en; ko woni tun ko Alla woowindiri hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Kanko ko O FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,64,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, Alla yonii ma [O yoniii] kadi jokkuЙ“e ma e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  8,65,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, rerЙ—in gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e hare. Si no e mooЙ—on noogayo muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e foolay teemeЙ—Й—e Й—iЙ—o; si no e mooЙ—on kadi teemedere, Й“e foolay ujunere e heeferЙ“e Й“en; tawde Й“en ko yimЙ“e Й“e faamataa"
  8,66,"Jooni Alla hoynanii on,O anndii no e mooЙ—on lo'ere. Si no e mooЙ—on teemedere muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e foolay teemeЙ—Й—e Й—iЙ—o; si no e mooЙ—on kadi ujunere, Й“e foolay ujune Й—iЙ—o duЕӢaye Alla. Alla no wonndi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  8,67,"Haananaa Annabiijo nde laatantoo mo dahaaЙ“e haa o Й—uЙ—Й—ina waraaЙ“e ka leydi. HiЙ—on faala jawkoy aduna, Alla kan no faalanaa (on) laakara. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,68,"Si wanaano binndoodi aditiindi immorde e Alla, lepte mawЙ—e memirayno on kon ko nannguЙ—on. [e konhoyri ndin]"
  8,69,"Г‘aamee e kon ko honuЙ—on, ko dagiiЙ—um laaЙ“uЙ—um. Hulon Alla, pellet, Alla ko haforoowo hinnotooЙ—o=jurmotoodo"
  8,70,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, maakan dahaaЙ“e wonuЙ“e e juuЙ—e mon Й“en : \"Si Alla no anndi moЖҙЖҙere ka Й“erЙ—e mon, O okkay on ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko jaЙ“anoЙ—on kon, O haforana on. Alla ko haforoowo hinnotooЙ—o"
  8,71,"Si Й“e faandike janfagol ma, gomЙ—ii Й“e janfinoke Alla ko adii; O newinan (maa) e mabЙ“e. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,72,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e feri Й“e tiiЙ—norii jawle maЙ“Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e fii laawol Alla, e Й“en weernu Й“e walli (Й“e); Й“en Й—on yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e kono Й“e feraali, alanaa on wallugol Й“e hay e huunde haa Й“e fera. Si Й“e wallinorii on ka diina, no fawii on wallitagol (Й“e), si wanaa hara ko e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko reenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  8,73,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. Si on wЙ—aali Й—um [ko Mi Й—aЙ“Й“iri on wallugol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ayra e heeferЙ“e Й“en], wonay fitina ka leydi e bone mawЙ—o"
  8,74,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e feri Й“e tiiЙ—nii e laawol Alla ngol, e Й“en weernu Й“e walli (Й“e); ko Й“en woni gomЙ—imЙ“e goonga Й“en: no woodani Й“e haforanal e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  8,75,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“aawo (Й—um), Й“e feri Й“e tiiЙ—nodii e mon, Й“en Й—on ko jeyaaЙ“e e mon. JoomiraaЙ“e enЙ—ammaaji Й“en (ko) yoga maЙ“Й“e Й“uri hanndude e yoga ka Deftere Alla. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  9,1,Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on kisii e Й“en sirkooЙ“e Й“e ahoduЙ—on
  9,2,"Yahee ka leydi lebbi nayi; anndon pellet, onon o wonalli ronkinooЙ“e Alla e wonnde pellet, Alla ko hoynoowo heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  9,3,"E ewnaango immorde ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haa e yimЙ“e Й“en, Гұalaande Hajju Mawnde nden, wonnde : Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on ko daЙ—ndiiЙ“e e sirkooЙ“e Й“en. Si on tuubii, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Si on huccitii non, anndee pellet, on wonaali ronkinooЙ“e Alla. Humpitir Й“en yedduЙ“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  9,4,"Si wanaa Й“en sirkooЙ“e Й“e ahoduЙ—on, refti Й“e Й—uytaali [e ahodal] mon ngal hay e huunde, Й“e wallindiraali kadi e gooto hoore-mon : timminanee Й“en Й—on ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin haa ka dumunna maЙ“Й“e. Anndon pellet, Alla no yiЙ—i gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  9,5,"Si lebbi hormante Й—in timmii, waree sirkooЙ“e Й“en kala ka tawuЙ—on Й“e : nanngee Й“e, huuЙ“iton Й“e jooЙ—anoЙ—on Й“e e kala tommborde. Si Й“e tuubii, Й“e ГұiiЙ“inii julde Й“e tottii zakka, (haray) accitee laawol maЙ“Й“e ngol. Pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,6,"Si goЙ—Й—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en fatike(hoddiniimo) ma, fattin(hottu) mbo haa o nana konngol Alla ngol, refti yottinoy mo nokku hisirde makko. Tawde kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e anndaa"
  9,7,"Ko honno ahadi woniranta sirkooЙ“e Й“en ka Alla e ka NulaaЙ—o Makko on? Si wanaa Й“en Й“e ahoduЙ—on ka Juulirde hormanteere. Fodde hiЙ“e Гұinnani on, Гұinnanee Й“e. Pellet, Alla no yiЙ—i gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  9,8,"Ko honno si Й“e foolii on, Й“e aynitataa e mooЙ—on enЙ—am wanaa ahadi?! HiЙ“e weltinira on kunndule maЙ“Й“e, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en saloo; ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e kadi ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  9,9,"ЖҒe waЙ—titirii Aayeeje Alla Й—en coggu fanЙ—ungu Й“e sakkii(faddii) e laawol Makko ngol. Pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon na bonii"
  9,10,ЖҒe aynitataa e gomЙ—inЙ—o enЙ—am wanaa ahadi. Ko Й“en woni jaggitooЙ“e Й“en
  9,11,"Si Й“e tuubii, Й“e Гұinnii julde Й“e tottii zakka, haray ko Й“e siЙ—Й“e mo'on ka diina. MeЙ—en fensitana Aayeeje Й—en yimЙ“e annduЙ“e"
  9,12,"Si Й“e firtii goondooje maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“aawo ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin Й“e yuwi e diina mon kan, haray haЙ“ee hooreeЙ“e keeferaaku Й“en -tawde kamЙ“e ahadi alanaa Й“e - belajo'o, Й“e haЙ—itoto"
  9,13,"E on haЙ“ataa yimЙ“e firtuЙ“e goondooje maЙ“Й“e, Й“e himmiri yaltinngol NulaaЙ—o on, ko kamЙ“e kadi adii on Й—aЙ“Й“itude? E on hulay Й“e?! Ko Alla Й“uri hanndude Mo huloton si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  9,14,"HaЙ“ee e mabЙ“e. Alla leptira Й“e juuЙ—e mon Й—en, O hoyna Й“e, O walla on e dow maЙ“Й“e, O sellina Й“erЙ—e yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  9,15,O itta tikkere Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Alla no jaЙ“ana tuubuubuyee on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o
  9,16,"Kaa on sikku on accete, hara Alla anndaali Й“en tiiЙ—niiЙ“e e mon, hara Й“e jogitaaki gaanin Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e? Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  9,17,"Haananaa sirkooЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e wuurnitata JuulirЙ—e Alla Й—en, hara ko Й“e seeditaniiЙ“e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in keeferaaku. ЖҒen Й—on golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en yirbii yani; ko ka Yiite woni ko Й“e luttoyta"
  9,18,"Anndee ko wuurnitata JuulirЙ—e Alla Й—en : ko on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, o ГұiiЙ“ni julde nde, o totti zakka on hara kadi o hulaali ko wanaa Alla. Hino tijjaa ka Й“en Й—on wondata e feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  9,19,E on waЙ—ay yarnooЙ“e hajjunkeeЙ“e Й“en e wuurnitooЙ“e Juulirde hormanteere nden wano on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde O tiiЙ—nii e laawol Alla?! ЖҒen Й“e fotataa ka Alla. Alla non fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en
  9,20,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e feridi fii laawol Alla ngol jawle maЙ“Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“uri mawnude darja ka Alla. Ko Й“en woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  9,21,"Joomi maЙ“Й“e no wewlinira Й“e yurmeende immorde ka Makko, e yarluyee, e Aljannaaji, no woodani Й“e nder majji neemaaji ГұiiЙ“uЙ—i"
  9,22,"Ko duuminteeЙ“e nder majji poomaa. Pellet, njoЙ“di mawndi no ka Alla"
  9,23,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wota on jogitor baabi- raaЙ“e mon Й“en e musiЙ—Й“e mon Й“en weldiiЙ“e; si Й“e suЙ“ike keeferaaku e dow liimanaaku. Kala e mo'on welduЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  9,24,"Maaku : \"Si tawii ko baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, e musiЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, e resondiraa- Й“e mon Й“en, e bolondaa mon on, e jawle (mon) Й—e faggitiЙ—on, e ngeygu ngu hulaЙ—on yeebagol, e koЙ—ooli Й—i welaЙ—on- Й“uraa yiЙ—eede e mon diini Alla, e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e tiiЙ—norgol fii Makko, haray heЙ—itee haa Alla adda yamiroore Makko nden. Alla non fewnataa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  9,25,"GomЙ—ii Alla wallii on e nokkeeli Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i. [Annditee] kadi Гұalnde Hunayni, tuma nde Й—uuЙ—al mon haawnunoo on, ngal duncanaali on hay e huunde, leydi ndin faaЙ—ani on e hoore ko ndi yaaji kon fow, refti huccituЙ—on ko on doguЙ“e"
  9,26,"Refti Alla Jippini deeЖҙere Makko nden e dow NulaaЙ—o Makko on e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. O Jippini kadi konu ngu on yi'aali, O lepti Й“en yedduЙ“e. Ko Й—um woni njoЙ“du yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  9,27,"Refti Й“aawo Й—um, Alla jaЙ“ana tuubuubuyee on Mo O muuyi, Alla ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,28,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, anndee sirkooЙ“e Й“en ko soЙ“uЙ“e : wata Й“e Й“aЙ—to Juulirde hormanteere nden Й“aawo hitaande maЙ“Й“e ndee Й—oo. Si on hulii baasal, arma Alla alЙ—inira on Й“ural Makko ngal, si on muuyii. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,29,"HaЙ“ee Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, Й“e harmintaa ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on harmini kon, Й“e diininortaako diina goonga, Й“een jeyaaЙ“e e okkaaЙ“e Defte, haa Й“e jonnira sagalle=lempo on juuЙ—e [maЙ“Й“e], ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e"
  9,30,"Alyahuuda'en wi'i : \"Uzayru ko Й“iЙ—Й—o Alla\", Annasara'en kadi wi'i : \"Almasiihu ko Й“iЙ—Й—o Alla\". ЖҠum ko konngol maЙ“Й“e iwrungol e kunndule maЙ“Й“e. HiЙ“e nanndinoo konngol Й“en yeddunooЙ“e ko adii. Alla huЙ—ii Й“e. Ko honno Й“e wonaa fefindoreede (e meere)"
  9,31,"ЖҒe jogitorii jannguЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ruuЙ—iiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e Almasiihu Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama rewetee gaanin Alla, Й“e yamiranooka si wanaa nde Й“e rewa reweteeЙ—o gooto, reweteeЙ—o alaa ko wanaa Kanko. Senayee woodanii Mo e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  9,32,"HiЙ“e faandorii Гұifinirgol Annoora Alla on kunndule maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Alla no saloo si wanaa nde O timmiЕӢta Annoora Makko on, hay si heeferЙ“e Й“en aГұii [Й—um]"
  9,33,"Ko Kanko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o Makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o Й“amtu ka e hoore kala diina, hay si sirkooЙ“e Й“en aГұii [Й—um]"
  9,34,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, tabitii ko Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e jannguЙ“e (Alyahuuda) Й“en, e ruuЙ—iiЙ“e (Annasaara) Й“en, hino Гұaamira jawle yimЙ“e Й“en meere, hiЙ“e sakkoo e laawol Alla ngol. ЖҒen Й“e no mooЙ“indira kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise hara Й“e wintortaako(nafqataaЙ—e) fii laawol Alla, weltinirЙ“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  9,35,"Г‘alnde Й—en (jawle) wulnoytee ka Yiite Jahannama, Й—e sunniree geece maЙ“Й“e, e becce maЙ“Й“e e Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e : ko Й—um Й—oo mooЙ“annoЙ—on wonkiiji mon, meeЙ—ee non kon ko mooЙ“anaynoЙ—on"
  9,36,"Tabitii limoore lebbi Й—in ka Alla, ko lebbi sappo e Й—iЙ—i, ka Alluwal Alla (reenaangal), Г‘alnde O tagunoo kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. No e majji nayi hormanteeji : Ko Й—um woni diina ГұiiЙ“uka. Wata on tooГұu e majji wonkiiji mon. HaЙ“ee sirkooЙ“e fow maЙ“Й“e wano Й“e haЙ“irta on Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e. Anndon pellet, Alla na wondi e gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  9,37,"Anndee neeЙ“nugol ngol ko Й“eydaari e keeferaaku. ЖҠum no majjiniree Й“en yedduЙ“e : hiЙ“e dagintinira Й—um hitaande, Й“e harmintina Й—um hitaande, fii yo Й“e hawritoy e limoore nden nde Alla harmini, Й“e dagintina ko Alla harmini. ЖҒe cuЙ—anaama golle maЙ“Й“e bonЙ—e Й—en. Alla non fewnataa yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  9,38,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, ko heЙ“i on, si on wi'anaama : \"yaltee fii laawol Alla\"; teddintinoЙ—o ka leydi? E on wela nguurndam aduna e diini laakara? Dakamme aduna Й—am wonaali ka laakara si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  9,39,"Si on yaltaali, O leptiray on lepte muusuЙ—e, O waЙ—titira on yimЙ“e goo, on lorrirtaa Mo huunde. Alla ko haЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  9,40,"Si on wallaali mo, gomЙ—ii Alla walliino mo; tuma nde Й“en yedduЙ“e yaltinnoo mo, Й—iЙ—aЙ“o e Й—iЙ—ooЙ“e, tuma nde Й“e wonunoo ka fammeere=wimmba, tuma nde o maakanaynoo wondiiЙ—o makko on : \"Wata a suno, pellet, Alla no wondi e meeЙ—en\". Alla Jippini deeЖҙere Makko nden e makko, O semmbini- niri mo konuuli ko on yi'aali, O waЙ—i konngol Й“en yedduЙ“e lesЙ—ungol, Konngol Alla ngol woni toowungol. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,41,"Yehee [ka jihaadi] ko on hoyfiraaЙ“e, maa teddiraaЙ“e, tiiЙ—noron jawle mon e wonkiiji mon fii laawol Alla. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si on laatike annduЙ“e"
  9,42,"Sinno Й—um laatino weeЙ“itannde (konhoyri) Й“adiindi e setewu raЙ“Й“indungu=datangal ngal juutaani, Й“e jokketeno; kono saЙ—teende (yahdu ndun) woЙ—Й—anii Й“e. Aray ka Й“e woondira Alla: \"Sinno men hattanno, men yaltidayno e mo'on\".HiЙ“e halka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e. Alla no anndi pellet, ko Й“e fenuЙ“e"
  9,43,"Alla yaafanike ma! ko hЙ—aЙ—no accaa duЕӢagol (cakkitgol) Й“e haa Й“anngane goongunЙ“e Й“en, anndaa fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  9,44,ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden duЕӢinortaako ma nde Й“e waЙ—ata jihaadi jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ko annduЙ—o gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en
  9,45,"Anndu ko duЕӢinoto maa, ko Й“en Й“e gomЙ—intaa Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en sikkitii. KamЙ“e e sikkitaare maЙ“Й“e nden hiЙ“e rutti-ruttinnoo"
  9,46,"Sinno Й“e faalano yaltugol, Й“e hebilanayno ngol hebilaare. Kono Alla aГұii yaltugol Й“e ngol; O aamini Й“e. ЖҒe wi'anaa : \"JooЙ—odee e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en"
  9,47,"Sinno Й“e yaltiduno e mooЙ—on, Й“e Й“eydataano on si wanaa bone, Й“e liЙ“ayno kadi konnaagu hakkunde mon; hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana on fitina. Hino e mo'on heЙ—itantooЙ—o Й“e. Alla non ko annduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  9,48,"GomЙ—ii Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iino fitina on ko adii, Й“e waylitan-maa fiyaaku on haa goonga kan ari, fiyaaku Alla on feeГұi tawi ko Й“e aГұuЙ“e (Й—um)"
  9,49,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e wi'oowo : \"DuЕӢano(sakkitan) lam (heddagol), wata a fitinam.\" Anndee ko e fitina on (tigiri) Й“e yani; pellet, Jahannama ko huuЙ“itaynge(fiiltii) heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  9,50,"Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii ma, metta Й“e. Si musiiba heЙ“ii ma, Й“e wi'a : \"Banni men nanngunoo fiyaaku amen ko adii.\" HiЙ“e huccita ko Й“e weltiiЙ“e"
  9,51,"Maaku : \"HeЙ“ataa men si wanaa kon ko Alla winndani men. Ko Kanko woni GiЙ—o amen. Ko e Alla woni ko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotoo"
  9,52,"Maaku : \"Hara hiЙ—on habbitori men si wanaa gootel e moЖҙЖҙereeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i? Menen kadi meЙ—en faditii e mon, nde Alla meminirta on lepte immorde ka Makko, maa e juuЙ—e amen. Habbitee! Menen meЙ—en habbodi e mooЙ—on"
  9,53,"Maaku : \"Wintee(nafqe) hiЙ—on yiЙ—i maa hiЙ—on aГұi : on jaЙ“antaake, onon on laatinoke yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  9,54,"HaЙ—aali Й“e jaЙ“eede wintaaje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, si wanaa ko Й“e yeddiri kon Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e arataa e julde si wanaa hara ko Й“e aamuЙ“e, Й“e wintotaako si wanaa hara ko Й“e aГұuЙ“e"
  9,55,"Wata jawle maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e haawne! Anndu ko Alla faandii ko nde O leptirta Й—e Й“e ka nguurndam aduna, wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—oofee hara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e"
  9,56,"HiЙ“e woondira Alla [kamЙ“e naafiqi'en] wonnde ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on; Й“e wonaali jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on. Ko woni kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e hulooЙ“e"
  9,57,"Sinno Й“e heЙ“ayno doГұorgal, maa pammeeje maa pulfa(naatirde), Й“e huccayno e Й—um hara hiЙ“e yaccoo"
  9,58,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en aybinooЙ“e ma ka senndugol sadakaaji : si Й“e jonnaama e majji, Й“e weltoo; si Й“e jonnaaka non e majji, jaka yoo kamЙ“e hiЙ“e tikka"
  9,59,"Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e weltorno kon ko Alla okki Й“e e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e wi'i : \"Alla yonii men. Arma Alla okkora men e Й“ural Makko ngal e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Menen ko men rerЙ—uЙ“e faade e Alla"
  9,60,"Anndee sadakaaji Й—in ko fii waasuЙ“e Й“en, e miskiinaaЙ“e Й“en, e gollooЙ“e e majji Й“en, e woowinirteeЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun (Lislaamu) Й“en, e daaЙ—e rinЙ—inteeЙ“e, e Й“en ГұawliiЙ“e, e fii laawol Alla e Й“ii-laawol. Ko farilla immorde ka Alla. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,61,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en lorrayЙ“e Annabiijo on hiЙ“e wi'a : \"Ko o nopel\".-Maaku : \"Ko noppel moЖҙЖҙere mon. Himo gomЙ—ini Alla o goongini gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e yurmeende Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e mooЙ—on. ЖҒen lorrayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o Alla on, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  9,62,"HiЙ“e woondirana on Alla fii yo Й“e weltin on. Ko Alla -e NulaaЙ—o makko on- Й“uri hanndude e weltineede, si Й“e laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  9,63,"E Й“e anndaa woonde mo lunnduki Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray no woodani mo Yiite Jahannama, ko o luttoowo e magge? Ko Й—um woni koyeera mawЙ—o"
  9,64,"NaafiqiiЙ“e Й“en no huli nde cortewol(simoore) Jippintee e maЙ“Й“e ngol no humpita Й“e ko woni e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku : \"Jalkitee, pellet, Alla ko yaltinoowo kon ko huluЙ—on (wata jippo)"
  9,65,"Si a lanndike Й“e, Й“e wi'ay: \"Anndee men laatinoke meЙ—en jumpa meЙ—en fija.\" Maaku : \"E ko Alla, e Aayeeje Makko Й—en e NulaaЙ—o Makko on laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on jalkita"
  9,66,"Wata on ngantino: gomЙ—ii on yeddii Й“aawo gomЙ—inal mon. Si Men yaafike fedde goo e mooЙ—on, Men leptay fedde goo tawde kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke bonnooЙ“e"
  9,67,"Naafiqi'en worЙ“e, e naafiqi'en rewЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e no jeyaa e yaoga. HiЙ“e yamira ЕӢiГұere, Й“e haЙ—a moЖҙЖҙere, hiЙ“e tama juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe yejjitii Alla, Kanko kadi O yejjiti Й“e. Pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en ko kamЙ“e woni faasiqi'en"
  9,68,"Alla fodii naafiqi'en worЙ“e, e naafiqi'en rewЙ“e, e heeferЙ“e Й“en, Yiite Jahannama, ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e ton.Nge yonii Й“e. Alla huЙ—ii Й“e, hino woodani Й“e lepte duumiiЙ—e"
  9,69,"[HiЙ“e wa'i] wano Й“en adinooЙ“e on : Й“e laatinoke Й“urЙ“e on saЙ—tude doole, Й“urЙ“e on Й—uuЙ—ude jawle e Й“iЙ—Й“e. ЖҒe dakmitori [ontuma] e tagu maЙ“Й“e ngu dakmitorЙ—on geЙ“al mon ngal wano adinooЙ“e on Й“en dakmitornoo geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal, jumpirЙ—on wano Й“e jumpirnoo. ЖҒen Й—on, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en poЙ“ii(yirbii) aduna e laakara. Ko Й“en Й—on woni hayruЙ“e(perdube) Й“en"
  9,70,"E kabaaru Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e araali Й“e : yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, e Aadi'en, e Thamuuda'en, e yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en, e wonndiЙ“e Madyana Й“en e waylitanooЙ“e Й“en? NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e hujjaaji Й“annguЙ—i. Alla wonaali tooГұoowo Й“e, ko woni tun ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e wonunoo tooГұude"
  9,71,"GomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. HiЙ“e yamira moЖҙЖҙere, Й“e haЙ—a ЕӢiГұere, Й“e ГұiiЙ“na julde, Й“e totta zakka, Й“e Й—oftoo Alla e NualaaЙ—o Makko on. ЖҒen Й—on, arma Alla yurmee Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,72,"Alla fodii gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en Aljannaaji, Й—i canЙ—i ilata e ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder majji, e koЙ—ooli laaЙ“uЙ—i e nder Aljanna duumal. E yarluyee Alla Й“urЙ—o mawnude. Ko Й—um woni malal mawnungal. @Corrected"
  9,73,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, haЙ“u heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, saЙ—tinanaa Й“e; weerde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde"
  9,74,"HiЙ“e woondira Alla Й“e wowlaali, gomЙ—ii le Й“e wowlii konngol keeferaaku ngol, Й“e yeddi Й“aawo silmugol maЙ“Й“e, Й“e himmiri ko Й“e heЙ“aali. ЖҒe mettiniraali (Й“e aybiniri) si wanaa fii Alla - e NulaaЙ—o Makko on - alЙ—inirii Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. Si Й“e tuubii, wonanay Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Si Й“e huccitii non, Alla leptiray Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e aduna e laakara; giЙ—o alanaa Й“e ka leydi wanaa ballo"
  9,75,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e ЖҙettanЙ“e Alla ahadi : \"Si O okkorii men e Й“ural Makko ngal, ko ma men sakko, men laatoo jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  9,76,"Nde O okkunoo Й“e e Й“ural Makko nagl, Й“e wuddiri Й—um Й“e hucciti ko Й“e Й—uurnii Й“e"
  9,77,"O waЙ—tintinirani Й“e naafiqaaku ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Й“e hawroyta e Makko, sabu ko Й“e lunndii Alla kon ko Й“e fodunoo Mo e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e fena"
  9,78,"E Й“ee anndaa wonnde Alla no anndi sirru maЙ“Й“e e cowndi(gunndo) maЙ“Й“e e wonnde pellet, Alla ko annduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i Й—in"
  9,79,"ЖҒen aybinooЙ“e gattooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ka sadakaaji e Й“en Й“e heЙ“ataa si wanaa tiiЙ—naare maЙ“Й“e nden, hiЙ“e jalkita Й“en. Alla jalkitii Й“e. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  9,80,"Insinano Й“e, maa hara a insinanaaki Й“e -hay si a insinanike Й“e laaЙ“i cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i - Alla yaafantaako Й“e. Ko waЙ—i Й—um, Й“en Й“e yeddii Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Alla feewnataa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  9,81,"TultunooЙ“e Й“en weltorii jooЙ—agol maЙ“Й“e ngol lunndoo NulaaЙ—o Alla on, Й“e aГұiniri haЙ“irgol jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“e wi'i : \"Wata on yaltu e nguleendi ndin\". Maaku : \"Ko Yiite Jahannama Й“uri tiiЙ—ude nguleendi.\" - Sinno Й“e faamaynoo"
  9,82,Yo Й“e jalu seeЙ—a Й“e wulla buy njoЙ“di ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e faggitoo
  9,83,"Si Alla ruttitii ma faade e fedde jeyaande e maЙ“Й“e Й“e duЕӢinani maa yaltugol, maaku : \"On yaltidataa e am poomaa, on haЙ“idataa e am gaГұo. Onon on welaama jooЙ—agol ka laawol aranol, jooЙ—odee e lunndii Й“e Й“en"
  9,84,"Wata a juulu e gooto maЙ“Й“e maayЙ—o poomaa, wata a daro e qabru makko. KamЙ“e Й“e yeddii Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Й“e maayi ko Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  9,85,"Wata jawle maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e haawne! Anndu ko Alla faandii ko nde O leptirta Й—e Й“e ka aduna, wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—oofee hara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e"
  9,86,"Si Cortewol jippinaama : \"Si ko woni, gomЙ—inee Alla tiiЙ—nodon jihaadi e NulaaЙ—o Makko on\", jom-yaajeende'en e maЙ“Й“e duЕӢinoto ma Й“e wi'a : \"Accu men wontida e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en"
  9,87,"ЖҒe welaama heddodugol e lunndiiЙ“e Й“en. Notaama e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kamЙ“e Й“e faamataa"
  9,88,"Kono NulaaЙ—o on kaГұum e gomЙ—imЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en Й“e tiiЙ—norii jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e moЖҙЖҙereeji, ko Й“en kadi woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  9,89,"Alla heblanii Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Ko Й—um woni maloore mawnde nden. @Corrected"
  9,90,NgantinotooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e buruure Й“en ari fii yo Й“e duЕӢinane. ЖҒen fenanЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on luttiti (jooЙ—ii). Arma lepte muusuЙ—e mema Й“en yedduЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e
  9,91,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e lo'uЙ“e Й“en, wanaa nawnuЙ“e Й“en, wanaa Й“en Й“e heЙ“aali ko wintoo( nafqa) si Й“e laaЙ“anii Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Laawol feloore alanaa moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en. Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,92,"Wanaa kadi e Й“en arooЙ“e ka maaЙ—a fii yo a waЙ—Й—imЙ“e, wi'aa : \"Mi heЙ“aali ko mi waЙ—Й—ina on.\" ЖҒe huccita hara gite maЙ“Й“e no yuppa gomЙ—i suno fii Й“e heЙ“aali ko Й“e wintoo nafqi"
  9,93,"Anndu ko laawol (bakkaatu) fawii, ko Й“en duЕӢinotooЙ“e(sakkinkinotoobe) ma hara ko Й“e alЙ—uЙ“e. ЖҒe welaama nde Й“e laatoda e tultuЙ“e Й“en. Alla noti ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tawi kamЙ“e Й“e anndaa"
  9,94,"HiЙ“e ngantinoo e mooЙ—on si on ruttitike e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku : \"Wata on ngantino : Men goongintaa on. GomЙ—ii Alla habriino men kabaruuji moooЙ—on. Arma Alla yi'a golle mon Й—en, e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Refti ruttiteЙ—on e on annduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, O humpita on kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on golla"
  9,95,"Aray ka Й“e woondirana on Alla, si on ruttitike e maЙ“Й“e, fii yo on Й—uurno Й“e (on felaali Й“e). ЖҠuurnee Й“e. Pellet, Й“e koЙ“e soЙ“e. JaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, njoЙ“di kon kobe laatinoo hiЙ“e faggitoo"
  9,96,"hiЙ“e woondirana on fii yo on wele Й“e. Si on welaama Й“e, pellet, Alla weletaake yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  9,97,"YimЙ“e ladde en hino Й“uri tiiЙ—ude keeferaaku e naafiqaaku, Й“e Й“uri hanndude kadi nde Й“e anndataa keeri Й—i Alla jippini e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,98,"Hino e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, on mo no jogitoo ko wintotoo kon sooyo, himo habbitanoo on yiilotooЙ—i bonЙ—i. Ko e dow maЙ“Й“e yiilotooЙ—i bonЙ—i (yanata). Alla ko Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  9,99,"Hino e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en (fahin), on gomЙ—inoowo Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, o jogitora kon ko o nafqata Й“aЙ—torЙ—um ka Alla e [heЙ“ugol] du'aaji NulaaЙ—o on. Anndee Й—um ko Й“adorЙ—um (Alla) wonannde Й“e. Aray Alla naada Й“e ka Yurmeende Makko. Pellet, Alla Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,100,"ЖҒen adinooЙ“e [gomЙ—inal] adiiЙ“e e feruЙ“e Й“en e weernuЙ“e wallitiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“en jokkitoriiЙ“e Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri, Alla welaama Й“e, kamЙ“e kadi Й“e welaama Mo. O maranii Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton poomaa. Ko Й—um woni malal mawnungal. @Corrected"
  9,101,"Hino e Й“en wonЙ“e banЕӢe mon jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en,naafiqiiЙ“e,e yimЙ“e Madiina Й“en kadi.ЖҒe sandolЙ—inii e naafiqaaku.A anndaa Й“e, Menen MeЙ—en anndi Й“e.Aray Men lepta Й“e laabi Й—iЙ—i,refti Й“e ruttitee e lepte mawnuЙ—e"
  9,102,"E woЙ—Й“e goo, qirritiiЙ“e junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e jilli gollal moЖҙЖҙal e goЙ—ngal bongal. Hino tijja nde Alla jaЙ“anta Й“e tuubuubuyee.Pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,103,"Жіettu e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en sadaka, laЙ“Й“iniraaЙ“e lootiraaЙ“e mo, du'anoЙ—aa Й“e. Pellet, du'aa maa ko deeЖҙere wonannde Й“e. Alla ko Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  9,104,"E Й“e andaali wonnde ko Alla no jaЙ“ana jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en tuubuubuyee, himo jaЙ“a sadakaaji Й—in, e wonnde ko Alla woni JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, ko jurmotooЙ—o"
  9,105,"Maaku : \"Gollee, arma Alla yi'a golle mon Й—en, e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Aray ruttita-Й—on ka AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i Й—in, O humpita on ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  9,106,"E woЙ—Й“e goo ko nennanaaЙ“e e yamiroore Alla : immaa O lepta Й“e, maa O jaЙ“ana Й“e tuubuubuyee. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,107,"ЖҒen jogitorЙ“e juulirde fii lorra, e keefereegu, e senndude hakkunde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e tommbaade on habuЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on ko adii. Pellet, hiЙ“e woondira : \"Men faandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙere\" Alla no seedii wonnde pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e"
  9,108,"Wata a daro (juulugol) e mayre poomaa. Ko juulirda didiraande kulol Alla gila ka arannde Гұalaande, Й“uri jojjude nde darotoЙ—aa e mun [juulaa]. Hino e mayre worЙ“e yiЙ—uЙ“e nde Й“e laЙ“Й“inotoo. Alla no yiЙ—i laЙ“Й“inotooЙ“e Й“en"
  9,109,"E ko on didirЙ—o maadi mu'un kulol Alla e welayee Makko, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko on didirЙ—o maadi mu'un e sera ngayka yirbuka, o yirbida e mayri ka Yiite Jahannama?! Alla fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  9,110,"Ndin maadi maЙ“Й“e ndi Й“e mahi seerataa ko ndi sikke ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en taЖҙay tun. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  9,111,"Pellet, Alla sooditirii e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en wonnde no woodani Й“e Aljanna. HiЙ“e haЙ“a fii laawol Alla ngol : hiЙ“e wara, hiЙ“e waree. Ko fodoore goonga nde O fodi ka tawreeta, e ka Linjiila e Alqur'aana. Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla hunnugol ahdi mun? Wewliree ngeyngu mon ngu yeeyondirЙ—on e mun : ko Й—um woni malala mawnungal ngal"
  9,112,"Ko tuubooЙ“e Й“en, rewooЙ“e (Alla) Й“en, yettooЙ“e (Mo) Й“en, hoorooЙ“e Й“en, ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e Й“en, sujjooЙ“e Й“en, yamirooЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“en haЙ—a ko boni, e reenotooЙ“e e keeri Alla Й—in.Wewlin gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  9,113,"Haananaa Annabiijo on e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e nde Й“e insinantoo sirkooЙ“e Й“en, hay si Й“en laatike joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, Й“aawo nde feeГұani Й“e wonnde koЙ“e yimЙ“e Jahiimi"
  9,114,"Insinanagol Ibraahiima ngol ben makko wonaano si wanaa fodoore nde o fodannnoo mo. Tuma nde Й“anngannoo mo wonnde on ko gaГұo Alla, o daЙ—ndino(hisnii) mo. Pellet, Ibraahiima ko heewuЙ—o yankinaare, muГұГұiiЙ—o"
  9,115,"Alla siforaali majjinoowo yimЙ“e Й“aawo nde O fewni Й“e, haa O Й“annginana Й“e ko Й“e haani rentaade e mu'un. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  9,116,"Pellet, Ko Alla woodani laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna, himo wara. Alanaa on gaa nii Alla giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  9,117,"GomЙ—ii Alla jaЙ“anii Annabiijo on tuubuubuyee, e feruЙ“e Й“en e walluЙ“e weerni Й“en jokkuЙ“e e saa'a saЙ—tuЙ—o, Й“aawo nde Й“erЙ—e woЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e eЙ“Й“unoo ooГұaade. Refti Alla jaЙ“ani Й“e tuubgol. Pellet, Kanko ko O YaafotoooЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e"
  9,118,"[O jaЙ“anii tuubuubuyee on] kadi Й“en tato tultunooЙ“e, haa leydi ndin faaЙ—ani Й“e e hoore ko ndi yaaji kon; wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“ittaniiЙ“e, Й“e fellitii wonnde moolorde e Alla aalaa si wanaa ka Makko. Refti O hawrindini Й“e e tuubuubuyee fii yo Й“e tuubu. Pellet, ko Alla woni jaЙ“oowotuubabuya, HinnotooЙ—o"
  9,119,"Ko on yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, hulee Alla laatodon e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  9,120,"Haananaa yimЙ“e Madiina Й“en, e Й“en wonЙ“e sera maЙ“Й“e immorde e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, nde Й“e luttitata Й“aawo NulaaЙ—o Alla on, wanaa nde Й“e yiЙ—atanta ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“ura mo.Ko waЙ—i, noon ko heЙ“ataa Й“e, wanaa tampere, wanaa heege fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“e tippataa(yabbatah) e nokkuure tikkinaynde heeferЙ“e Й“en, Й“e hawrataa e gaГұo hawrannde, si wanaa Й“e winndante e Й—um gollal moЖҙЖҙal. Pellet, Alla yeebataako njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  9,121,"ЖҒe wintotaako(nafqatah) wintaari, fanЙ—undi maa mawnundi, Й“e taЖҙataa aynde(joolol), si wanaa Й“e winndante Й—um, fii yo Alla warjo Й“e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  9,122,"Haananaa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e yahata (jihaadi) Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e. Ko haЙ—no fedde kala e maЙ“Й“e yalta fii yo Й“e faamino ka diina, e fii yo Й“e jertin yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“e si Й“e ruttitike e maЙ“Й“e, belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e rentoto"
  9,123,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, haЙ“ee Й“en Й“aЙ—iiЙ“e on immorde e heeferЙ“e Й“en; yo Й“e taw e mooЙ—on Гұaande. Anndon pellet Alla no wonndi e gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  9,124,"Si cortewol(simoore) jippinaama, hino e maЙ“Й“e on wi'oowo : \"ko hommbo e mo'on woni ko ngol Й“eydi gomЙ—iЙ“al?\" Ammaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, ngol Й“eydu Й“e gomЙ—inal, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e weltoo"
  9,125,"Ammma Й“en Й“en Гұawu woni ka Й“erЙ—e mun, ngol Й“eydu Й“e soЙ“e e hoore soЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e maayi ko Й“e heeferЙ“e"
  9,126,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde kamЙ“e hiЙ“e fitninee hitaande kala laawol maa laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i? Refti Й“e tuubataa, Й“e wonnah waajitotooЙ“e"
  9,127,"Si tawii cortewol jippinaama, yoga maЙ“Й“e ndaara yoga [Й“e wi'a] : \"Hara goЙ—Й—o no yi*a on?\" Refti Й“e haЙ“ana. Alla surii Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tawde ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e faamataa"
  9,128,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o arii immorde e mooЙ—on, hino saЙ—ta e makko ko tampoton, rerЙ—uЙ—o e mooЙ—on, newaniiЙ—o hinnotooЙ—o(yurmotoodo) gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  9,129,"Si Й“e huccitii(runtiima), maaku : \"Alla yonii lam. Alaa reweteeЙ—o si wanaa Kanko. Ko e Makko mi fawii; ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o Arsi mawnuЙ—o on\". @Corrected"
  10,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Deftere ГұeГұaande nden"
  10,2,"Kere wonan yimЙ“e Й“en kaawasee, fii Men wahyii- ma e gorko jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde : \"Jertin yimЙ“e Й“en? Wewliniraa(weltina) gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en wonnde no woodani Й“e nokku goongaajo ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e? HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'i : \"Oo ko mbileejo feeГұuЙ—o"
  10,3,"Pellet Joomi mon ko Alla on taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow Arsi, himo toppitoo fiyakkuuji Й—in. Alaa woo e tefoowo si wanaa Й“aawo duЕӢayee Makko. Ko on mo'on woni Joomi mooЙ—on, rewee Mo. E on ciftortaho? @Corrected"
  10,4,"Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal, ko fodoore Alla goongunde! Ko kanko woni fuЙ—Й—ude tagu ngun, refti O ruttita ngu fii yo O yoЙ“a Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe e nunЙ—al. ЖҒen heeferЙ“e kan, hino woodani Й“e njaram immorde e fatayЙ—am, e lepte muusuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e yedda"
  10,5,"Ko kanko woni waЙ—uЙ—o naange ngen jalbunge e lewru ndun nurЙ—undu, O eЙ“Й“ani ndu jipporЙ—e fii yo on anndu emmbere duuЙ“i Й—in e limoore nden. Alla tagiraali Й—in si wanaa e goonga. Himo fensitana Aayeeje Й—en yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e"
  10,6,"Hino e luutindirgol jemma e Гұalorma ngol, e kon ko Alla tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, Maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  10,7,"ЖҒen Й“e jortaaki hawrugol e Amen, Й“e weltori nguurndam aduna Й—am, Й“e deeЖҙiri Й—am, e Й“en tawЙ“e no welsindii e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  10,8,"ЖҒen, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Yiite ngen, sabu kon ko faggittonoo"
  10,9,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Joomi maЙ“Й“e feewnayЙ“e e gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal. CanЙ—i no ila ley maЙ“Й“e ka Aljannaaji neema"
  10,10,"Noddaandu maЙ“Й“e nder ton, ko \"Ya Alla senaade woodaniima\", hiwrondiral maЙ“Й“e ngal ton, ko : \"Salaam\", [kisal]. Ko woni wattannde noddaandu maЙ“Й“e, ko : \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  10,11,"Sinno Alla yaccinanayno yimЙ“e Й“en bone wano O yacciniranta Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal timminanteno Й“e. Men acca Й“en Й“e tamЖҙinaaki hawrugol e Amen e bewre maЙ“Й“e nden hiЙ“e bumam-bumannoo"
  10,12,"Si lorra memii neЙ—Й—anke on, o nodda men Й“aЕӢЕӢe makko, maa ko jooЙ—iiЙ—o, maa ko o dariiЙ—o. Tuma nde Men huncini mo lorra makko kan, o feЖҙЖҙira wa si o noddaano Men e lorra memuka mo. Ko wano non fantinooЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—iranaa kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  10,13,"GomЙ—ii Men halkiino gire adinooЙ“e on nde Й“e tooГұunoo, NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. ЖҒe wonaano gomЙ—inooЙ“e. Ko wana nii Men yoЙ“irta yimЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  10,14,"Refti Men Men waЙ—i on lontotooЙ“e ka leydi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, ha min ndaara no gollirton"
  10,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“en Й“e tamЖҙinaaki hawrugol e Amen wi'a: \"Addu Alqur'aanaare goo hara wanaa ndee Й—oo\" maa \"wostonde\". Maaku : \"Haananaa lam nde mi waЙ—titira nde immorde e Й“aЕӢЕӢe wonkii am. Mi jokkataa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am. Min miЙ—o huli si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  10,16,"Maaku : \"Sinno Alla muuyuno, mi janngataano nde e dow mooЙ—on, mi aanndintaande mon kadi. GomЙ—ii mi ГұiiЙ“iino e mooЙ—on nguurndamado may- re. E on haqqiltaa"
  10,17,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko Й—en. Si ko woni, o malnatah bomЙ“e Й“en"
  10,18,"HiЙ“e rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa Й“e nafataa Й“e, hiЙ“e wi'a : \"Ko Й—ii Й—oo woni tefanooji men Й—in ka Alla\". Maaku : \"E on yeetoto Alla ko O anndaa ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi?\" Senayee woodanii Mo, O toowii gaay e ko Й“e sirkata"
  10,19,"YimЙ“e Й“en laatanooki si wanaa mofte goote. ЖҒe lurri. Sinno wanaa konngol adinoo ngol immorde ka Joomi maa, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e kon ko Й“e lurraynoo"
  10,20,"HiЙ“e wi'a : \"Ko haЙ—noo Aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku : \"Annde ko wirnii kon ko Alla woodanii.Habbitee; min komi habbitiiЙ—o wonndude e mo'on"
  10,21,"Si Men meeЙ—inirii yimЙ“e Й“en yurmeende Й“aawo lorra memnooka Й“e, jaka yoo hiЙ“e mari pewje e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Maaku : \"Ko Alla Й“uri yaawude fewjoore\". Pellet, NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hino winnda kon ko fewjoton"
  10,22,"Ko kanko woni doginoowo on ka njorndi e ka maayo, haa si on wonii ka laaЙ—e, Й—e doginira Й“e henndu laaЙ“ndu, Й“e weltora ndu. Ara e majje henndu bippooru, mollooЙ—e (bempejje) Й—en ara e maЙ“Й“e immorde e kala baЕӢЕӢe, Й“e fellita wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e huЙ“indaama, Й“e toroo Alla ko Й“e laЙ“Й“inana Mo diina kan, [Й“e wi'a]: \"Si A daЙ—ndii men e Й—um Й—oo, pellet, men laatoday e yettooЙ“e [Ma] Й“en"
  10,23,"ЖҒaawo nde O daЙ—ndi Й“e, e jaka yoo kamЙ“e hiЙ“e bewira ko leydi ko adaa e goonga. Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, anndee bewre mon nden yantay e wonkiiji mon. Ko dakamme nguurndam aduna. Refti ko ka Amen woni rutorde mon, Men yeetitoo on ko laatinoЙ—on gollaynoЙ—on"
  10,24,"Anndee misal nguurndam aduna Й—am, ko wano ndiyam Й—am Men jippini immorde ka kammu, puЙ—i leydi ndin jillondira e majjam Й—um ko yimЙ“e e neemoraaЙ—i Гұaamata. Haa si ndi leydi ndi Жҙettii cuЙ—aari mayri ndi cuЙ—ike, yimЙ“e mayri Й“en jikka wonnde ko Й“e hattamЙ“e (soГұugol) e mayri, yami- roore Amen ardira e mayri jemma maa Гұalorma, Men waЙ—a (puЙ—i) Й—in soГұaaЙ—i wa si tawii Й—i moЖҙ- Жҙaano hanki mun. Ko wano nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,25,"Alla no nodda on faade e galle kisal, Himo fewna on Mo o muyyi faade e laawol focciingol ngol"
  10,26,"Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) moЖҙЖҙere e Й“eydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  10,27,"ЖҒen faggitiiЙ“e boneeji Й—in, njoЙ“di bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay Й“e, Alanaa Й“e immorde ka Alla hay daЙ—ndoowo, A sikkay geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko hippiraa ko taЖҙontinnde jemma niЙ“Й“utuЙ—o. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko luttooЙ“e ton"
  10,28,"Г‘alnde Men mooЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti Men wi'ana Й“en sirkunooЙ“e : \"Wonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidiiЙ“e mon.\" Men senndindira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'a : \"Wonaa menen wonunoЙ—on e rewude"
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e gaay e dewe mon Й—en"
  10,30,Ko Й—on wonkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. ЖҒe ruttitee ka Alla GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on ka goonga; ko Й“e wonunoo fefindaande kon majjira Й“e
  10,31,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Kaa ko hommbo jeyti nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en, ko hommbo kadi yaltinta ko wuuri e nder ko maayi, o yaltina ka maayi e nder ko wuuri, ko hommbo kadi yiilata fiyaaku on?\" ЖҒe wi'ay : \"Ko Alla\". Maaku : \"E on hulatah"
  10,32,"Ko on Й—on mo'on Alla, woni jeyЙ—o on e goonga. Ko honЙ—um woni Й“aawo goonga si wanaa majjere? Ko honno firlitirte Й—on"
  10,33,"Ko wano nii konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjiri e hoore faasiqinЙ“e Й“en :wonnde pellet, Й“e gomЙ—intah"
  10,34,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en on mo no fuЙ—Й—a tagu refi o ruttita ngu [Й“aawo maayde]?\" Maaku :\"Ko Alla fuЙ—Й—ata tagu ngun refti O ruttita ngu. Ko honno fefindara Й—on [faade e meere]"
  10,35,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en on fewnoowo e goonga?\" Maaku: \"Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on fewnoowo e goonga Й“uri handude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewantaa (hoore mon) si wanaa on fewna? Ko heЙ“i on sifa no Гұaawirton"
  10,36,Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke Й—en duncataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e gollata
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaare fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde goonginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  10,38,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay : \"O fefindi nde?\" Maaku : \"Addee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo haЙ—tanЙ—on gaanin Alla, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  10,39,"Ko woni, Й“e fennii ko Й“e huЙ“indaaki ganndal mun, [ko Й“e fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araali Й“e taho. Ko wano non adinooЙ“e Й“en fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo"
  10,40,"No e maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi mo gomЙ—inaa nde. Ko Joomi maa Й“uri anndude bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,41,"Si Й“e fennii ma, maaku : \"No woodani lam (njoЙ“di) golle am, no woodani on (njoЙ“di) kuuЙ—e mon. Onon ko on daЙ—ndiiЙ“e ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o(kisdo) ko golloton"
  10,42,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en heЙ—otooЙ“e ma. E ko annannta faaЙ—u Й“e Й“en, hay tawii Й“e haqqiltah"
  10,43,"No e maЙ“Й“e on ndaaroowo ma. E ko an fewnata bunЙ—o on, hay si wonii Й“e yi'atah"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla tooГұirtah yimЙ“e Й“en huunde, ko woni, ko yimЙ“e Й“en tooГұata ko ko'e mun"
  10,45,"Г‘alnde O mooЙ“oyta Й“e, wa'ata kona si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano si wanaa sa'a gooto e Гұalorma, hiЙ“e anndandira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. GomЙ—ii Й“en fennuЙ“e kawral Alla ngal sooyii, Й“e wonaano feewuЙ“e"
  10,46,"Si Men hollii ma yoga e kon ko Men fodi Й“e, maa Й—um Men Жҙettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka Amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e. Refti Alla ko seediiЙ—o e kon ko Й“e gollata"
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala NulaaЙ—o. Si NulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on arii, Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  10,48,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  10,49,"Maaku : \"Mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e nennirantaake saa'a Й“e ardinantaake kadi"
  10,50,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si lepte Makko Й—en ardii on jemma maa Гұalorma, ko honЙ—um bomЙ“e Й“en hawjiranta Й—e"
  10,51,"E ko tuma Й—e yani gomЙ—in ton Й—e? E ko jooni non, gomЙ—ii on laatinoke hawjirЙ“e Й—um"
  10,52,"Refti tooГұuЙ“e Й“en wi'anee : \"MeeЙ—ee lepte luttugol. Hara on yoЙ“ete si wanaa kon wonunoЙ—on e faggitaade"
  10,53,"HiЙ“e habrino maa : \"ЖҠum ko goonga?\" Maaku : \"Ko non, mi woondirii Joomi am, pellet ko Й—e goonga. On wonaali ronkinooЙ“e"
  10,54,"Sinno tabitanno kala wonkii tooГұuki jeyno ko woni leydi, ki sottorayno Й—um. ЖҒe suuЙ—i ninse Й—en Й“aawo nde Й“e yi'i lepte Й—en. Г‘aawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  10,55,"Anndee ko Alla woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee pellet, fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  10,56,Kanko Himo wuurna Himo wara; ko faade ka Makko ruttoteЙ—on
  10,57,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, gomЙ—ii waaju arii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon, e lekki fii (Гұabbuuli) ko woni e Й“erЙ—e, e peewal, e yurmeende woannande gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  10,58,"Maaku : \"[Ko addan-mi on kon] ko Й“ural Alla e yurmeende Makko; yo Й“e weltor Й—um Й—on. Ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e mooЙ“ata"
  10,59,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, kon ko Alla jippinani on e arsike, waЙ—uЙ—on e mun ko harmi e ko dagii? -Maaku : \"Ko Alla duЕӢanii on? kaa ko e Alla fefindotoЙ—on (penaale)"
  10,60,"Ko honЙ—um woni sikke Й“en fefindotooЙ“e fenaande e hoore Alla, Г‘alnde Darngal? Pellet, Alla ko Jom Й“ural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e yettatah (neemaaji Й—in)"
  10,61,"A wonatah e fiyaaku, a janngataa e mayre e janngannde (Qur'aana), on gollataa e gollal si wanaa Men wonay seediiЙ“e e mooЙ—on tuma nde wonoton e mun. Wirnotaako gaay e Joomi maa yeru abbere jarra, wanaa ka leydi wanaa ka kam- mu; wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um fanЙ—ude, wanaa ko Й“uri mawnude si wanaa no e nder deftere Й“anngunde"
  10,62,"Anndee yimЙ“e Alla Й“en, kulol alanaa Й“e, Й“e wonah sunoytoo"
  10,63,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e woni hulooЙ“e [Alla]"
  10,64,Hino woodani Й“e welo-welo ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. - Alaa bayloowo konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in -. Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal
  10,65,"Wata konngol maЙ“Й“e sunine. Pellet, teddungal ngal denndaangal ko Alla woodani. Ko kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  10,66,"Anndee ko Alla Heeranii Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“en wonЙ“e ka leydi. E ko Й“en noddooЙ“e gaanin Alla jokkata e kafidiiЙ“e? ЖҒe jokkaali si wanaa sikke, Й“e wonaali si wanaa fenooЙ“e"
  10,67,"Ko Kanko woni waЙ—anЙ—o on jemma on fii yo on deeЖҙu e maako, e Гұalorma on yi'rЙ—o. Pellet, wonii e Й—um Maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e"
  10,68,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Alla jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Senayee woodanii Mo! Ko Kanko woni Galo yonndiЙ—iiЙ—o on. Hino woodani Mo kon ko woni ka kammuuli e kon ko woni ka leydi; alanah on cemmbe e Й—um. E on wowlay Alla ko on anndaa"
  10,69,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Й“en fefindotooЙ“e fenaande e hoore Alla Й“e maletaake"
  10,70,"Ko dakamme ka aduna, refti ko ka Amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e nden, refti Men meeЙ—ina Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e Й—en sabu ko Й“e yeddiraynoo kon"
  10,71,"Janngan Й“e kabaaru Nuuhu, tuma nde o maakan-no yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, si tawii ГұiiЙ“ugol am (hakkunde mon) mawnii e mon, e waa- jorgol lam Aayeeje Alla Й—en, ko e Alla woni ko mi fawii. Haray fellitee fiyaaku mon on, e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en. Refti wata fiyaaku mon on wonan on ko mugii. Refti fewjaon lam (ko faalaЙ—on), wata on nennitanam"
  10,72,"Si on runtiima, mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin wonaali si wanaa ka Alla. Mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  10,73,ЖҒe fenni mo. Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e wondiiЙ“e makko Й“en ka laana. Men waЙ—i Й“e lontotooЙ“e (ka leydi). Men yooli Й“en fennunooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Ndaaru ko honno battane jertinaaЙ“e (salii) Й“en waЙ—i
  10,74,Refti Men immini Й“aawo makko NulaaЙ“e haa e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. ЖҒe addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. ЖҒe wonaano gomЙ—inooЙ“e sabu ko fenniri Й—um kon ko adii. Ko wano nii Men notirta e Й“erЙ—e Й“en jaggituЙ“e
  10,75,"Refti Men immini Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Muusaa e Haaruuna haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun, wonndude e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. ЖҒe mawnikini, Й“e woni yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  10,76,"Nde goonga kan ari e maЙ“Й“e immorde e Amen, Й“e wi'i : \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko mbilewu feeГұungu"
  10,77,"Muusaa maaki: \"E on wi'anay goonga kan tuma ka ari e mon : E nee ko mbilewu nii? Hara le mbileeЙ“e Й“en maletaake"
  10,78,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"E a aru men fii yo a yiltu men e ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, mawngu ngun laatano on onon Й—iЙ—o ka leydi? Menen men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e on"
  10,79,"Fir'awna wi'i : \"Addanee lam kala mbileejo annduЙ—o"
  10,80,"Nde mbileeЙ“e Й“en arunoo, Muusaa maakani Й“e : \"Bugee(werle) ko bugotoЙ—on kon"
  10,81,"Tuma nde Й“e buginoo, Muusaa maaki : \"Kon ko adduЙ—on kon ko mbilewu, pellet, Alla bonnay Й—um. Pellet, Alla moЖҙЖҙintah golle bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,82,"Alla no tabintinira Goonga kan KonnguЙ—i Makko Й—in, hay si bomЙ“e Й“en aГұii"
  10,83,"GomЙ—inaano Muusaa si wanaa jurriiya e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, sabu kulol Fir'awna e mbatu maЙ“Й“e ngun, nde Й“e fitinta Й“e. Pellet, Fir'awna ko townintinooЙ—o ka leydi, pellet, ko e fantimЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa"
  10,84,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, haray ko e Makko fawotoЙ—on si on laatike jebbiliiЙ“e"
  10,85,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko e Alla men hoolori. Joomi amen, wata waЙ—u men fitina wonannde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,86,DaЙ—ndiraa men yurmeende Maa nden e yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en
  10,87,"Men wahayini faade e Muusaa e neene-gooto makko on, wonnde: \"Wernee yimЙ“e mon Й“en Misra e cuuЙ—i, waЙ—on cuuЙ—i mon Й—in fewtuЙ—i (qibla), ГұiiЙ“non julde nden. Wewlinaa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  10,88,"Muusaa maaki: \"Joomi amen, A okkii Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun cuЙ—aari e jawle ka nguurndam aduna, Joomi amen, fii yo Й“e majjin gaay e laawol Maa ngol. Joomi amen, mehu(momtu) jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, uddaa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara Й“e gomЙ—intaa haa Й“e yi'a lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  10,89,"O daali: \"GomЙ—ii toraare mon nden jaabinaama. Г‘iiЙ“ee (e diina), wata on jokku laawol Й“en Й“e anndaa"
  10,90,"Men lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon. Fir'awna konu mun ngun jokkitiri Й“e bewre e jaggitere. Haa nde yoolagol ngol hewtitii mo, o wi'i: \"Mi gomЙ—inii wonnde reweteeЙ—o Alla si wanaa on Mo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en gomЙ—ini. Min ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  10,91,"E ko jooni non? GomЙ—ii a yeddiino ko ado, jeyaya-Й—aa e bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,92,"Hannde Men daЙ—dnirte Й“anndu maa ndun, fii yo a wonan Й“en arooЙ“e Й“aawo maaЙ—a tasakuyee. Pellet, ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“en gaay e Aayeeje Amen Й—en ko welsindiiЙ“e"
  10,93,"GomЙ—ii Men weernii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en weerde teddunde, Men arsike Й“e immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i. ЖҒe lurraali haa nde ganndal ngal ari e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Joomi maa Гұaawoya hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e muuЙ—um"
  10,94,"Si a wonii e sikkitaare e kon ko Men jippinii e maaЙ—a, lanndii Й“en Й“e no jannga Deftere nden ado maaЙ—a. GomЙ—ii goonga kan arii maa immorde ka Joomi maa, wata a jeye e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e"
  10,95,"Wata a jeye e Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, laato-daa e sooyuЙ“e Й“en"
  10,96,"Pellet, Й“en Й“en konngol Joomi maa ngol jojji e mun Й“en Й“e gomЙ—intah"
  10,97,"hay si arii e maЙ“Й“e kala Aaya, haa Й“e yi'a lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  10,98,"MeeЙ—aali laataade e hoЙ—o gomЙ—ingo, gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e nafi Й“e si wanaa yimЙ“e yuunusa Й“en. Nde Й“e gomЙ—innoo, Men huncanno Й“e lepte koyeera Й—en ka nguurndam aduna, Men dakmiti Й“e haa e saanga"
  10,99,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyuno, wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en fow gomЙ—inayno. E an a doolay yimЙ“e haa Й“e wona gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  10,100,"Laatanaaki wonkii nde ki gomЙ—inta si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Himo waЙ—a soЙ“e [lepte] Й—en e hoore Й“en Й“e haqqiltaa"
  10,101,"Maaku: \"Ndaaree ko honЙ—um woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi\". Aayeeje Й—en e jertinooje Й—en nafatah yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa Й“en"
  10,102,"Hara hiЙ“e habbii si wanaa yeru ГұalЙ—e Й“en feЖҙЖҙunooЙ“e ado maЙ“Й“e? Maaku: \"Sabbitee, min miЙ—o wonndi e mo'on jeyaaЙ—o e sabbitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  10,103,Reft Men daЙ—nda NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en e Й“en gom- Й—imЙ“e. Ko woni non jojjiri e Amen daЙ—ndugol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en
  10,104,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, si on wonii e sikkitaare e diina am, (min) mi rewataa Й—in Й—i rewoton gaa nin Alla; ko mi rewata, ko Alla On waroowo on. Mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  10,105,"E wonnde : \"Г‘iiЙ“in yeeso maa ngon diina kan ko o ooГұiiЙ—o, wata a wonu jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,106,"Wata a noddu gaanin Alla, kon ko nafatah ma lorrataa ma. Si a waЙ—ii (Й—um), an dey haray a jeyaama ontuma e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,107,"Si Alla meminirii ma lorra, alaa huncoowo mo si wanaa Kanko. Si O faandike e maaЙ—a moЖҙЖҙere, alaa ruttoowo Й“ural Makko ngal. Himo memina nde on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ko Konko woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o on"
  10,108,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, gomЙ—ii goonga ka arii mon immorde ka Joomi mon. Kala feewuЙ—o, e haray ko hoore-makko o feewani; kala kaadi majju- Й—o, haray ko e makko defii. Min wonaali fawaaЙ—o e hoore-mon"
  10,109,"Jokku ko wona ko e wahayineede kon e maaЙ—a, muГұГұo-Й—aa haa Alla Гұaawa. Ko Kanko woni moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o Гұaawoore"
  11,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. ko Deftere nde Aayeeje mun ГұeГұaa refti Й—e fensitaa immorde ka on Г‘eeГұo HumpitiiЙ—o"
  11,2,wata on rewu si wanaa Alla.Min dee komi jeertinoo jeertinoowo ummaade e Makko
  11,3,"E nde insintoЙ—on Joomi mon; refti tuubanon mo. O dakmita on dakamme labaaЙ—o haa e lajal innangal O jonna kala jom Й“ural Й“ural makko ngal. Si on huccitii, haray min mi hulanii on lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  11,4,Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde mon. Kanko ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde
  11,5,"Anndee Й“en Й—on sowa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fii yo Й“e suuЙ—o e Makko. Anndee fewndo Й“e sudditoraynoo comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Himo anndi ko Й“e suuЙ—ata e ko Й“e feГұГұinta. Pellet ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  11,6,"Alaa e ruugayngel ka leydi si wanah ko Alla fawtii arsike maggel on, Himo anndi ГұiiЙ“irde maggel e daakorde maggel; fow no e Deftere Й“anngunde"
  11,7,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, hari arsi Makko kin no ka hoore ndiyam, fii yo O ndaarndo on ko hommbo e mo'on Й“urata moЖҙЖҙinnde gollal. Pellet si a wi'i: \"Onon ko on ummintinteeЙ“e Й“aawo maayde\", maa heeferЙ“e Й“en wi'u: \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa mbilewu feeГұungu\". @Corrected"
  11,8,"Pellet si Men nennaniiЙ“e lepte Й—en haa e dumunna limaaЙ—o, maa Й“e wi'u: \"Ko tonngi Й—e?\" Anndee Гұalnde nde arat e mabЙ“e, Й“e wonataa sureteeЙ“e e majje; jippoo e maЙ“Й“e kon ko laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita"
  11,9,"Si tawii Men meeЙ—inii neЙ—Й—anke on neema immornde ka Amen, refti Men Й“oori nde e makko, kanko ko otaЖҙaado, yeddoowo"
  11,10,"Si tawii kadi Men meeЙ—inirii mo neema Й“aawo lorra memuЙ—o mo, maa o wi'oy : \"Satteende nden iwii e am\", kanko (ontuma) ko o weltiiЙ—o, ГұaaГұoowo"
  11,11,"Si wanaa Й“en muГұГұii Й“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  11,12,"Belajo'o ko a accoowo yoga ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a, Й“ernde maa nden Й“iЙ—tora Й—um; fii hiЙ“e wi'i: \"Ko haЙ—no ngalu jippinee e makko? maa Malaa'ikaajo arda e makko?\" Anndu an ko a jertinoowo. Alla ko deenoowa kala huunde"
  11,13,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay : \"O fefindi nde?\" Maaku : \"Addee Corteeji( cimooje) sappo yeru mayre, pepindaaЙ—e, noddon kala mo haЙ—tanЙ—on gaanin Alla, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  11,14,"Si Й“e jaabitaaki on, anndee wonnde ko nde jippinira ko ganndal Alla, e wonnde reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko. Hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e"
  11,15,"Kala on tawЙ—o ko nguurndam aduna e cuЙ—aari majjam faandii, Men humnanay Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ton, hara kamЙ“e Й“e Й—uytantaake ton"
  11,16,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e alanah Й—um en ka laakara si wanaa Yiite. Ko Й“e golli ton kon firtii, ko meere woni koЙ“e gollaynoo"
  11,17,"E ko on laatiiЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, himo janngande mo seediiЙ—o immorde ka Makko, e nde aditiinde mo [kanko Muhammadu], Deftere Muusaa nden ardiinde e yurmeende [Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini ko alah hujja kon?]: ЖҒen Й—on hino gomЙ—ini nde; kala on yedduЙ—o nde e feddeeji Й—in, ko Yiite ngen woni fodoore makko. Wata a laato e sikke fii mayre. Pellet ko nde goonga immornde ka Joomi maa; ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en gomЙ—intaa"
  11,18,"Ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұude Й“uri on fefandiido fenaa- nde e hoore Alla? ЖҒen Й—on holliroyte ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, (malaa'ikaaЙ“e) seediiЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Ko Й“ee Й—oo feni bakki e Joomi maЙ“Й“e\". Hey, kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  11,19,"ЖҒen falotooЙ“e gaay e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, hara kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara"
  11,20,"ЖҒen Й“e wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, laatanaaki Й“e kadi weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, hiЙ“e sowoyanee lepte Й—en. ЖҒe laatanooki hattanЙ“e nanugol, Й“e wonaano kadi yi'ooЙ“e"
  11,21,Ko Й“e woni sooyinЙ“e wonkiiji mun Й—in. Kon ko Й“e fefintonoo majji gaay e maЙ“Й“e
  11,22,"Sikke alah, wonnde Й“en Й—on ka laakara, ko kamЙ“e Й“uroyta sooyude"
  11,23,"ЖҒen gonЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e yankinanii Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  11,24,"Misal feddeeji Й—in Й—in: ko wano bunЙ—o e faaЙ—uЙ—o, e yi'oowo e nanoowo. E Й“ee Й—oo Й—iЙ—i fotay e misal? E on waajitotaako"
  11,25,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulirii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Min wonannde on ko mi jertinoowo Й“annginЙ—o"
  11,26,wonnde wata on rewu si wanah Alla. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande musuunde
  11,27,"Mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i: Men yi'aali ma si wanah ko a Й“anndinke sifa amen, men yi'aali kadi Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma si wo- naa jaasuЙ“e amen faaЙ—uЙ“e feere, men yi'anaali on e amen Й“ural. Worin meЙ—en sikki ko on fenooЙ“e"
  11,28,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, yeetee lam si tawii miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O yeЙ—ii lam yurmeende (Annabaaku) immorde ka Makko, Й—um wumna e mooЙ—on, e menm baaw- nay on nde hara ko on aГұuЙ“e nde"
  11,29,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, mi lanndaaki on jawdi e Й—um. NjoЙ“di am wonaali si wanah ka Alla. Min mi wonaali raЙ—otooЙ—o Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e hawroyooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko woni tun, min mi yi'ii on yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e"
  11,30,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko hommbo walloytammi ka Alla si mi raЙ—ike Й“e? E on waajitotaako"
  11,31,"Mi wi'antah on miЙ—o mari ngaluujii Alla, mi annah kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa wonnde ko mi malayko, mi wi'antaa Й“en Й“e gite mon Й—en yawi, Alla okkoytaa-Й“e moЖҙЖҙere; ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e. Min ontuma [si mi waЙ—ii Й—um], haray ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  11,32,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Nuuhu, gomЙ—ii a wenjidii e amen, a Й—uЙ—Й—inii yeddondiral ngal e amen. Addan men kon ko fodu-Й—aa men, si a laatike jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  11,33,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko Alla addanta on Й—e -si O muuyii- on wonaali laawotooЙ“e"
  11,34,"LaaЙ“al-reedu am nafatah on, si mi faandike laaЙ“angol on, si tawii Alla no faandii bewnugol on (majjina). Ko Kanko woni Joomi mon, ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon"
  11,35,"Si ko woni, Й“e wi'ay : O fefidi-nde. Maaku: \"Si mi fefindi nde, haray bonnere am nden no fawii lam. Min no ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o ko bonnoton kon"
  11,36,"Wahayinaa e Nuuhu wonnde : \"GomЙ—intah e yimЙ“e maa Й“en si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—innooЙ“e. Wata a suno e ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  11,37,"MoЖҙЖҙin laana kan e ndeenka Amen e yamiroore Amen. Wata a yewtidoy e am fii Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yoolotooЙ“e. @Corrected"
  11,38,"Himo moЖҙЖҙina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moЖҙЖҙinta ton, Й“e jalkita mo. O maaki: \"Si on jalkitii men, menen kadi men jalkitoyay on wano jalkitirton [men non]"
  11,39,"Aray nde annduЙ—on ko hommbo lepte hoynayЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoo e makko"
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore Amen nden aroyii, huЙ“Й“inirЙ—e Й—en fati, Men daali: \"Ronndo e makka kala nooneeji Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i e Й“eynguure maa nden -si wanaa Й“en konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e\". GomЙ—inaano wonndude e makko si wonah seeЙ—aaЙ“e"
  11,41,"O maaki: \"WaЙ—Й—oree e makka Innde Alla ka dogugol makka e daragol makko. Pellet Joomi am ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  11,42,"Kan no dogida e maЙ“Й“e e mollooЙ—e waaЙ—e wa pelle. Nuuhu noddi Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, hari on no serindi: \"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, waЙ—Й—ida e amen, wata a wonndu e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  11,43,"O wi'i: \"Mi Жҙawoyay e fello daЙ—ndayngo lam ndiyam Й—am\". O maaki: \"DaЙ—oowo yamiroore Alla nden alaa hannde si wanah on Mo O yurmini\". Molloonde nden heedi hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, o laatodii e yoolaaЙ“e Й“en"
  11,44,"Wi'a: \"Ko an yo leydi, moЙ—u ndiyam maa Й—am! Ko an kadi yo kammu, jogito [sorombooji ndiyam Й—in]!\". Ndiyam Й—am Й“eeЙ“i, fiyaaku on Гұaawaa, [laana] kan daroyii ka dow fello juudiiy, wi'aa: \"Halkaare woodanii Й“en yimЙ“e tooГұuЙ“e"
  11,45,"Nuuhu noddi Joomi makko, o maaki: \"Joomi am, pellet Й“iЙ—Й—o am on ko jeyaaЙ—o e Й“eynguure am, pellet fodoore Maa nden ko goonga. Ko An Й“uri nunЙ—ude Гұaawoore ГұaawooЙ“e"
  11,46,"O daali: \"Ko an yo Nuuhu, pellet on jeyaaka e Й“eynguure maa, nden (toraare) ko gollal ngal moЖҙЖҙaa. Wata a toro Lam ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal. Min MiЙ—o waajo maa fii wata a jeye e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  11,47,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi moolorike Ma nde mi lanndoto Maa huunde nde mi alanah Й—um ganndal. Si wanaa A hafranam yurmin ЖҠaa mi, mi jeyete e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  11,48,"Wi'aa: \"Ko an yo Nuuhu, jippor kisiyee immorde ka Amen, e moЖҙЖҙi dow maaЙ—aa e mofte wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a. Mofte goo (no ton), aray Men dakmita Й“e, refti memoya Й“e immorde e Amen, lepte muusuЙ—e"
  11,49,"ЖҠii Й—oo ko jeyaaЙ—i e kabaruuji wiirniiЙ—i, MeЙ—en wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A anndaano Й—e an, wanaa yimЙ“e maa Й“en, ko adii Й—um. MuГұГұo, pellet battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en woanii gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  11,50,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla, reweteeЙ—o alanah on ko woori mo. On wonaali si wanaa fefindotooЙ“e"
  11,51,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, mi lanndaaki on e Й—um njoЙ“di. NjoЙ“di am wonaali si wanaa ka on taguЙ—o lam. En on haqqiltaa"
  11,52,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, insinee ka Joomi mon, refti tuubanon Mo O jippina e mooЙ—on toЙ“o jokkondirn-ngo, O Й“eyda on cemmbe e hoore cemmbe mon Й—en. Wata on huccitu ko on bomЙ“e"
  11,53,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Huudu, kala ko addan-Й—aa men e Й“anngannduyee, menen men wonaali accooЙ“e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in fii konngol maa ngol, menen men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e ma"
  11,54,"Men wi'atah si wanaa yoga e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in meminirii ma bone\". O maaki: \"Min miЙ—o seedina Alla -seeditee onon kadi- wonnde min, ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko sirkoton"
  11,55,"gaanin Makko. Fewjanee lam on denndaangal, refti wata on fadee kam"
  11,56,"Min mi fawike e Alla, Joomi am e Joomi mon. Alaa e ruugayngel si wanaa ko O nannguЙ—o jubuuru maggel. Pellet, Joomi am no e laawol focciingol"
  11,57,"Si on huccitii, gomЙ—ii mi yottinanii kon ko mi nulidaa e mooЙ—on. Joomi am lontinay yimЙ“e goo Й“e wonaa onon, on lorrirtaa Mo hay e huunde. Pellet, Joomi am ko deeno kala huunde"
  11,58,"Nde yamiroore Amen nden ari, Men daЙ—ndiri Huudi e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e makko yurmeende Amen. Men daЙ—ndi Й“e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e"
  11,59,"ЖҒen ko AadinkooЙ“e. ЖҒe yedduno Aayeeje Joomi amЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e yeddi NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e jokki yamiroore kala dunndaranke sanndolЙ—inЙ—o"
  11,60,"ЖҒe jokkindinaa ka aduna Й—oo, kuddi, e Г‘alnde Darngal. Anndee pellet, AadinkooЙ“e Й“en yeddi Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Anndee goЙ—Й—al woodanii Aadi'en, yimЙ“e Huudi"
  11,61,"[Men Nulii] kadi e Samuuda'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e Saalih, o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaano on ko woori Mo. Ko Kanko fuЙ—Й—i on ka leydi, O wuurni on e mayri. Insinanee Mo, refti tuubon ka Makko. Pellet Joomi am ko Й“aЙ—iiЙ—o, jaabotooЙ—o"
  11,62,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Saalihu, gomЙ—ii a woniino hakkunde amen yaakoraaЙ—o ado Й—um Й—oo. E a haЙ—ay men rewugol ko baabiraaЙ“e amen rewatno? Menen non, men wonii e sikke e huunde nde noddataa men e mun (sikke) jaaliiЙ—e"
  11,63,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Yeetee lam, si mi laatike e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O okkii lam immorde ka Makko yurmeende, ko hommbo faabotoo mi ka Alla si mi yeddii Mo? On Й“eydataa lam si wanaa hayrugol"
  11,64,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, mbaa Й—oo ko ngelooba wonannde on maande. Tertee mba, mba Гұaama ka leydi Alla. Wata on memir-mba bone, lepte Й“aЙ—tiiЙ—e heЙ“a on"
  11,65,"ЖҒe mborii-mba. o maaki: \"Dakmitee ka galleeji mon balЙ—e tati! ЖҠum ko fodoore nde fennetaake"
  11,66,"Nde yamiroore Alla nden arunoo, Men daЙ—ndiri Saalihu e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonduЙ“e e makko, yur-meende immorde ka Amen- e koyeera nden Гұalnde Pellet Joomi maa, ko Kanko woni DoolnuЙ—o, FooluЙ—o"
  11,67,Haacaango ngon nanngi tooГұuЙ“e Й“en.ЖҒe waЙ—tini ka galleeji maЙ“Й“e jicciiЙ“e
  11,68,"A sikkay Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano Й—on. Anndee pellet Samuudu en yedduno Joomi maЙ“Й“e, anndee goЙ—Й—al yurmee- nde (Alla) woodanii Samuuda'en"
  11,69,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en addanii Ibraahiima welo-welo, Й“e wi'i: \"Kisal (e mon)\". O maaki: \"Kisal (e mon). NeeЙ“aali o ardi e ngaari juЙ—aandi"
  11,70,"Nde o yi'unoo juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottaaki ndi, o faytiЙ“e (o sikkitii), o soomi kulol e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, ko men nulaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e Luuti Й“en"
  11,71,"Tawi suddiiЙ—o makko on no darii, o jali, Men weltiniri mo Ishaaqa, e Й“aawo Ishaaqa, Yaaquube"
  11,72,"[Debbo on] wi'i: \"Ee jalla am! E mi jibinay e hoore ko mi nayeejo, e hino oo Й—oo gorko am ko nayeejo? Pellet Й—um Й—oo ko huunde haawniinde"
  11,73,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"E a haawete fiyaaku Alla on? Yurmeende Alla e barkiiji Makko wonii e mon, yimЙ“e nduu suudu. Pellet ko O YettiniiЙ—o TedduЙ—o"
  11,74,"Nde kulol ngol iwunoo e Ibraahiima, welo-welo ngon ari e makko, himo yeddandira e Amen fii yimЙ“e Luuti Й“en"
  11,75,"Pellet, Ibraahiima ko muГұГұiiЙ—o, heewuЙ—o yankina-gol, tuuboowo"
  11,76,"Ko an yo Ibraahiima, Й—uurno gaayi e Й—um; gomЙ—ii yamiroore Joomi maa nden arii, e pellet, lepte aray e maЙ“Й“e lepte Й—e ruttetaake"
  11,77,"Nde NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en arunoo ka Luuti, o sunanii Й“e, o Й“iЙ—tori fonndo makko ngon fii maЙ“Й“e, o maaki: \"Ndee Й—oo ko Гұalaande saЙ—tunde"
  11,78,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en ari e makko e yaccoo. Ado Й—um hari hiЙ“e gollaynoo bonЙ—i. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й“ee Й—oo ko jwiЙ“e am: ko kamЙ“e Й“uri laaЙ“annde on. Hulee Alla, wata on hersinam e hoЙ“- Й“e am. E gorko feewuЙ—o alaa e mo'on"
  11,79,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet hiЙ—a anndi haaju alanah men e jiwЙ“e maa Й“en, pellet hiЙ—a anndi kadi ko men faalaa"
  11,80,"O maaki: \"Sinno miЙ—o marunoo doole e mon! Maa mi fattinoo(moolo) e soЙ“Й“undu sattundu(jookdu)"
  11,81,"[HoЙ“Й“e Й“en] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Luutu, pellet ko men NulaaЙ“e Joomi maa. ЖҒe hewtataa ma. Yaltinir Й“eynguure maa nden e taЖҙunnde jemma, wata gooto e mo'on yeЖҙЖҙito si wanaa suddiiЙ—o maa on, ko fii heЙ“ay mo ko heЙ“ata Й“eya kon. Anndon fodoore maЙ“Й“e nden ko ka subaka. E subaka on laataaki Й“aЙ—iido"
  11,82,"Nde yamiroore Amen nden arunoo, Men waЙ—tiri dow [saare] nden ley mayre, Men caaЖҙini e mayre kaaЖҙe iwruЙ—e loope juЙ—aaЙ—e rewondirЙ—e"
  11,83,MaandinaaЙ—e ka Joomi maa. ЖҠe wonaali woЙ—Й—uЙ—e e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en
  11,84,"[Men Nulii] kadi e Madyana'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Shu'aybu, o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla; reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Wata on Й—uytu Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en. Min on miЙ—o yi'i on e moЖҙЖҙere. Min non miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande fiiltiindede"
  11,85,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, hunniree Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en nunЙ—al. Wata on Й—uytan yimЙ“e Й“en coggu maЙ“Й“e ngun, wata on yahru ka leydi bonnugol"
  11,86,Ko keddiiЙ—e Alla Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e. Mi wonaali reenoowo on
  11,87,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Shu'aybu! E ko julde maa nden yamiru-maa nde men accata rewugol ko baabiraa- Й“e amen Й“en rewaynoo kon, maa nde men gollata huuwata e jawle amen Й—en ko men yiЙ—i? Pellet an ko a muГұГұiiЙ—o feewuЙ—o"
  11,88,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, yeetee lam: si miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O arsikii lam immorde ka Makko arsike moЖҙЖҙo?... Mi faandaaki lunndaade on e kon haЙ—ay-mi on e muuЙ—um. Mi faandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙingol fotde yeru am on. Kawral am wonaali si wanaa ka Alla. Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko mi ruttotoo"
  11,89,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, wata ngayngu am defu on haa heЙ“a on sugu ko heЙ“unoo yimЙ“e Nuuhu maa yimЙ“e Huudi maa yimЙ“e Saalih. YimЙ“e Luuti Й“en kan woЙ—Й—itaaki on"
  11,90,"Insinanee Joomi mon, refti tuubanon Mo. Pelet Joomi am ko HinnotooЙ—o, GiЙ—o"
  11,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Shu'aybu, men alah faamude ko Й—uuЙ—i e kon ko wi'ataa; menen meЙ—en yi'e hakku-nde amen lo'uЙ—o. Si wanaano gorol maa ngol, men piyirteno keeЖҙe. An a wonaali tedduЙ—o e amen"
  11,92,"O maaki: \"E ko gorol am ngol Й“uri teddudo e mon diini Alla, on waЙ—tirii mo Й“aawo mon hawkaaЙ—o? Pellet Joomi am ko huЙ“indiiЙ—o(fiiltiido) ko huuwoton kon"
  11,93,"Ko onon yom yimЙ“e am, gollee e nokku mo'on. Min kadi ko mi golloowo. Aray nde anndoton ko hombo lepte hoynooje arat e mu'u, e ko hommbo woni fenoowo on. (Jooni non) habbitee! Min kadi miЙ—o wondi e mon habbitiiЙ—o"
  11,94,"Nde yamiroore Amen nden arunoo, Men daЙ—ndiri Shu'aybu e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e makko yurmeende Amen. Haacaango ngon nanngi Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e jicciiЙ“e"
  11,95,A wi'ay Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano Й—on. Anndee woЙ—Й—ineede yurmeende wonanii Madayana wano Samuuda'en woЙ—Й—iniranoo
  11,96,GomЙ—ii Men Nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hujja Й“annguЙ—o
  11,97,"Ha e Fir'awna e mbatu mun. ЖҒe jokkii yamiroore Fir'awna nden, yamiroore Fir'awna non wanaa feewunde"
  11,98,"O ardoyto yimЙ“e makko Й“en Г‘alnde Darngal, o jolna Й“e ka Yiite. (Nge)bonii jolirde jolaande"
  11,99,"ЖҒe jokkinaama kuddi e oo (aduna), e Г‘alnde Darngal. Bonii ballal ngal Й“e jokkindiranaa"
  11,100,"ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite ca'e, MeЙ—en fillano maa Й—um: no e majje ГұiiЙ“uЙ—e e conyaaЙ—e"
  11,101,"Men tooГұaali Й“e. Ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e. ReweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—iЙ“e rewaynoo gaanin Й—in duncanaali Й“e hay e huunde, tuma nde yamiroore Joomi maa nden arunoo; Й—i Й“eydaali Й“e si wanaa hayrude"
  11,102,"Ko wano nii nanngal Joomi maa ngal, si tawii O nanngii ca'e Й—en hara ko Й—e tooГұuЙ—e. Pellet nanngal Makko ngal ko muusungal saЙ—tungal"
  11,103,"Pellet tasakuyee wonii e Й—um Й—oo wonannde on hulЙ—o lepte laakara. Nden ko Гұalaande aade en mooЙ“oyte e mun, nde kadi ko Гұalaande seedoyteende"
  11,104,Men neЙ“nataa nde si wanah haa e lajal limangal
  11,105,"Г‘alnde ngal arata, wonkii (woo) wowlatah si wanaa e duЕӢayee Makko. Hino e maЙ“Й“e malkisaaЙ—o e malaaЙ—o"
  11,106,"Si ko malkisaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka Yiite; hino woodani Й“e nder ton ookaango e hiikaango"
  11,107,"Ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e nder magge fotde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanah si Joomii maa muuyii; pellet Joomi maa ko waЙ—oowo kala ko O faandii"
  11,108,"Si tawii non ko malaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka nder Aljanna woni ko duumintee e mun fotde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanaa si Joomi maa muuyii. (ЖҠum) ko dokkal ngal taЖҙondirtaa"
  11,109,"Wata a wonu e sikke e huunde ko Й“ee rewata. ЖҒe rewiraali si wanaa no baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e rewiray- noo ko adii. Menen non, Men hunniranay Й“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal ko aldah e Й—uytugol"
  11,110,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, luutondi- raa e mayre. Si wanaano konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e kan hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o e e mayre"
  11,111,Wonaali kala maЙ“Й“e si wanaa Joomi maa hunna- nay Й“e (njoЙ“di) kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet ko O humpitiiЙ—o ko Й“e gollata kon
  11,112,"Г‘iiЙ“ir [e focciingol ngol] wano yamiraЙ—aa non, e tuubuЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a. Wata on bewu. Pellet ko O reenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  11,113,Wata on ooГұor e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en sakko Yiite ngen mema on. Alanah on gaanin Alla yiЙ—Й“e. Refti on walloytaake
  11,114,Г‘innu julde nden ka seraaji Й—iЙ—i Гұalorma e saa'iiji jemma. Pellet moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hino monta bonЙ—i Й—in. ЖҠum ko waaju wonannde Й“en waajitotooЙ“e
  11,115,MuГұГұo. Pellet Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en
  11,116,"Ko haЙ—noo wona e gire adinooЙ“e on Й“en, joomiraa- Й“e kedde, Й“e no haЙ—a e bonnugol ka leydi! si seeЙ—aaЙ“e e Й“en Й“e Men daЙ—ndunoo e maЙ“Й“e. TooГұuЙ“e Й“en jokki e ko Й“e neeminaa e mun kon, Й“e laatii bomЙ“e"
  11,117,Joomi maa siforaali halkiroowo ca'e e hoore tooГұe tawa yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e
  11,118,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyiino, O waЙ—ayno yimЙ“e Й“en moftal gootal. ЖҒe seerataa ko Й“e luutondirooЙ“e"
  11,119,"si wanaa Й“en Й“e Joomi maa yurmaa. Ko sabu Й—um O tagiri Й“e. Konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjii wonnde: \"Pellet, Mi hebbiniray Jahannama jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"
  11,120,"Kala e mu'un, MeЙ—en fillano maa kabaruuji NulaaЙ“e, ko Men tabintinra Й—um Й“ernnde maa ngon. Aranii ma e ngol (cortewol) goonga e waaju e janntoore wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  11,121,"Maakan Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inah: \"Gollee e nokku mo'on. Menen kadi, ko men gollooЙ“e"
  11,122,Habbitee kadi. Menen ko men habbitiiЙ“e
  11,123,"Ko Alla heeranii wirniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko ka Makko fiyaaku no fow ruttetee. Awa rewu Mo, fawo-Й—aa e Makko. Joomi maa wonaali welsindiiЙ—o e kon ko golloton"
  12,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Deftere Й“anngunde nden"
  12,2,"Menen Men jippiniriinde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] Aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  12,3,"Menen MeЙ—en fillano maa ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fillayee, e kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a ndee Alqur'aanaare, hay si woniino ado mayre, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  12,4,"Tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo ben makko: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, mi yi'ii [e koyЙ—ol] koode sappo e go'o, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun; mi yi'ii Й—in no sujjana lam"
  12,5,"[Ben makko] maaki: \"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, wata a fillano musiЙ—Й“e maa Й“en koyЙ—ol maa ngol sakko Й“e fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko gaГұoAade Й“annguЙ—o"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa suЙ“oray maa, O anndine firo koyЙ—i, O timmina neema Makko on e maaЙ—a e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano O timminirnoo mo e baabiraaЙ“e maa Й“en Й—iЙ—o: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  12,7,"GomЙ—ii wonii e Yuusufa e musiЙ—Й“e makko Й“en, taskuyeeji wonannde lanndotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,8,"tuma nde Й“e wi'unoo: \"Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto mun on Й“uraa yiЙ—eede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e. Pellet ben-men wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa feroЙ—on mo e leydi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, wonton Й“aawo Й—um yimЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  12,10,"Gooto e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: \"Wata on waru Yuusufa, weddee mo ka niЙ“e woyndu yoga e seteeЙ“e hoccay mo, si on laatike gllooЙ“e"
  12,11,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko heЙ“u-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men laaЙ“amЙ“e mo reedu"
  12,12,"Accitidu-mo e amen o Гұaama, o fija. Menen ko men reenooЙ“e mo"
  12,13,"O maaki: \"Min no suninay lam nde yahdoton e makko; miЙ—o huli nde boyeeru ndu Гұaamata-mo ka welsindi-Й—on e makko"
  12,14,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet si saafaandu Гұaamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e, haray ko men hayruЙ“e"
  12,15,"Nde Й“e yahdunoo e makko, Й“e fottani ukkugol mo ka niЙ“e woyndu, Men wahayini e makko: \"Ma a yeetitoyo Й“e Й—ee kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e hara Й“e so'aa anndude"
  12,16,ЖҒe arti ka ben maЙ“Й“e kiikiiЙ—e hiЙ“e woya
  12,17,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo baaben amen, menen men yehii meЙ—en adondira, men acci Yuusufa ka kaake amen saafaandu ndun Гұaami mo. A hoolotaako men non, hay si men wonii goonguЙ“e"
  12,18,"ЖҒe ardi e dolokke makko on hino moddi ЖҙiiЖҙam fenaande. O maaki: \"Si ko woni, wonkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—inanii on fiyaaku. Ko muГұal moЖҙЖҙal [heddanii lam]! Ko Alla woni wallitorЙ—o e ko sifotoЙ—on kon"
  12,19,"SeteeЙ“e ari, Й“e nuli Жҙoogoowo maЙ“Й“e on, o jippini baagal makko ngal. O wi'i: \"Ee welВЁ-welo am! E hino paykum!\" ЖҒe suuЙ—iri mo keyee maЙ“Й“e. Alla non ko annduЙ—o ko Й“e gollata kon"
  12,20,"ЖҒe yeeyiri mo coggel famЙ—ungel: dirhamu-woy limotoo-koy. ЖҒe woni welsindiiЙ“e e fii makko"
  12,21,"SooduЙ—o mo on Misra wi'ani Й“eyngu makko: \"Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa jogitoЙ—e mo Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Ko nii Men hoЙ—niri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo Men anndin mo firo koyЙ—i. Alla ko fooluЙ—o e fiyaaku Makko on: kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,23,"On [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun Й—aЙ“Й“iri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe Й—en o wi'i: \"Mi heblanii-mo-ma!\" O maaki: \"Moolaare Alla! JeyЙ—o lam on moЖҙЖҙinii weerde am. Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en maletaake"
  12,24,"GomЙ—ii [debbo] on himmanii oon. Kanko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [Men gerdiri] fii yo Men yiltu mo e bone e pankare. Pellet ko o jeyaaЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e amen laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en"
  12,25,"ЖҒe Й—iЙ—o kala Й“e adondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya on Й“aawo. ЖҒe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: \"Ko honЙ—um woni njoЙ“di on faalanaaЙ—o Й“eynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muusuЙ—e"
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: \"Ko kanko Й—aЙ“Й“iri lam hoore-am\". TawanooЙ—o e yimЙ“e [debbo] on seeditii: \"Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] on goongi, kanko [gorko] on ko jeyaaЙ—o e fenuЙ“e Й“en"
  12,27,"Si tawii non dolokke makko on ka Й“aawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kanko [gorko] on ko o jeyaaЙ—o goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'unoo dolokke on ko Й“aawo seekori, o wi'i: \"ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon Й—en ko haawniiЙ—e"
  12,29,"Yuusufa, Й—uurno gaayi e Й—um. An [debbo on], insinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa Й—in; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woopuЙ“e Й“en"
  12,30,"RewЙ“e Й“en ka saare wi'i: \"Debbo laamЙ—o on Й—aЙ“Й“irii kurkaadu makko ndun hoore-makko! GomЙ—ii giggol Й“urtirii mo. Menen dey meЙ—en yi'a oo [debbo] e majjere Й“anngunde"
  12,31,"Nde o nanunoo pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o nulani Й“e, o hebilani Й“e ngawluuji, o jonni gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e laЙ“i, o wi'i: \"Yaltu e maЙ“Й“e!\". Nde Й“e yi'unoo mo, Й“e mawnini mo, Й“e hetti juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Kaawee Alla! Oo wanaa Й“anndinke, oo wonaali si wanaa malaa'ikaajo tedduЙ—o"
  12,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko oo mo'on felirЙ—on lam fii mun, gomЙ—ii mi Й—aЙ“Й“irii mo hoore-makko o haЙ—itii. Si wonii o waЙ—aali ko mi yamirta mo kon, ma o soke ma o laato jeyaaЙ—o e hoyЙ“e Й“en"
  12,33,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, Ko kaso ngon Й“urani lam e ko Й“e noddata lam e mun kon. Si a pottinaani lam pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, mi ooГұoto e maЙ“Й“e, mi jeyee e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  12,34,"Joomi makko jaabinani mo, O firliti e makko pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  12,35,"Refti feeГұani (rewЙ“e) Й“en Й“aawo nde Й“e yi'i maandeeji Й—in, ma o sok-mbo tigi haa e saa'i"
  12,36,"SukaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o naatidi e makko ka kaso. GoЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: \"Min mi hoyЙ—ii hoore-am miЙ—o siiwa sanngara\". Oya kadi wi': \"Min mi hoyЙ—ii hoore-am miЙ—o ronndii ka hoore-am cobbal, colli no Гұaama e maggal\". Humpitii men firo Й—in, menen men yi'ii ma jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,37,"O maaki: \"Г‘aametee mo wonaЙ—on okkoreede on aratah on si wanaa mi humpitay on firo mun ado o arde on. ЖҠum mo'on ko jeyeeЙ—um e ko Joomi am anndini lam. Min mi Й—alii diina yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—inaa Alla, hara kamЙ“e e fii laakara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e"
  12,38,"Jokku-mi diina baabiraaЙ“e am Й“en: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e Й“ural Alla e dow amen e hoore yimЙ“e Й“en; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e yettataa"
  12,39,"Ko onon yo wondiiЙ“e am Й—iЙ—o ka kaso! E ko reweteeЙ—i sertuЙ—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Alla Gooto FooluЙ—o on"
  12,40,"On alah e rewde gaanin Makko, si wanah inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on Й—um, onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon, Alla jippinanaali Й—en hujja. Г‘aawoore nden alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wata on rewu si wanaa Kanko. Ko Й—um Й—um woni diina ГұiiЙ“uka kan; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e anndaa"
  12,41,"Ko onon yo wondiiЙ“e am Й—iЙ—o ka kaso! GoЙ—Й—o e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli Й—in Гұaama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo lanndiЙ—on fii mun on Гұaawaama"
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke daЙ—ay e maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o: \"Janto lam ka koohoojo maa on\". Seytaane yejjintini mo jantanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] ГұiiЙ“iti ka kaso yoga e duuЙ“i"
  12,43,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: \"Min mi yi'ii (e koyЙ—ol) na'i jeeЙ—iЙ—i fayЙ—i, na nyaama fooЖҙuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i Й—in, e dukke jeeЙ—iЙ—i kecce, e goЙ—Й—i goo yooruЙ—i. Ko onon yo dental, firtanee lam ngol koyЙ—ol am, si on laatike firtooЙ“e koyЙ—i"
  12,44,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko jiiЙ“u-jaaЙ“u koyЙ—i ! Men wonaali annduЙ“e firo koyЙ—i"
  12,45,"DaЙ—uЙ—o on e Й“eya Й—iЙ—o miijitii Й“aawo dumunna o wi'i: \"Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee lam"
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo goonguЙ—o! Yeetii men fii na'i jeeЙ—iЙ—i fayЙ—i, na nyaama fooЖҙuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i Й—in, e dukke jeeЙ—iЙ—i kecce, e goЙ—Й—i goo yooruЙ—i, belajo'o mi ruttoo ka yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o, Й“e annday"
  12,47,"O maaki: \"On remay duuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i jokkondirЙ—i. Kala ko soГұuЙ—on, accon Й—um ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa seeЙ—a e kon ko Гұaamoton"
  12,48,"Refti aroyay Й“aawo Й—um, duuЙ“i jeeЙ—iЙ—i saЙ—tuЙ—i, Й—in (duuЙ“i) no Гұaama kon ko marnaЙ—on Й—i si wanaa seeЙ—a e ko maroton [fii awdi]"
  12,49,"Refti aroya Й“aawo Й—um, hitaande, ko e mayre yimЙ“e Й“en toЙ“etee, ko e mayre kadi Й“e hamata"
  12,50,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: \"Addanee lam on\". Nde imminaaЙ—o on arunoo mo, o maaki: \"Rutto ka koohoojo maa on lanndoЙ—aa mo: Ko woni fiyaaku Й“en rewЙ“e hettunooЙ“e juuЙ—e mun Й—en? Pellet Joomi am ko annduЙ—o pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  12,51,"[LaamЙ—o on] wi'i: \"Ko honЙ—um wonunoo fiyaaku mon tuma Й—aЙ“Й“irnoЙ—on Yuusufa hoore-makko?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Moolaare Alla! Men anndiraa mo ko boni\". ЖҒeyngu laamЙ—o on wi'i: \"Jooni goonga kan feeГұii. Ko min Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo hoore-makko, pellet ko o jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  12,52,"ЖҠum ko fii yo o anndu wonnde mi janfaaki mo ka wirnii, e wonnde Alla fewnatah pewje janfotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,53,"Mi laЙ“Й“inaa hoore-am, tawde wonkii ko heewuki yamirde bone, si wanah kin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  12,54,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: \"Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am\". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: \"An on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku hoolaaЙ—o"
  12,55,"O maaki: \"WaЙ—am e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi reenoowo annduЙ—o"
  12,56,"Ko wano nii Men Гұimnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, himo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yiЙ—i. MeЙ—en heЙ“nira yurmeende Amen nden on mo Men muuyi, men yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,57,Pellet ko njoЙ“di laakara ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e laatii gomЙ—uЙ“e
  12,58,"Baaba-gootooЙ“e Yuusufa Й“en ari Й“e naati ka makko. O annditi Й“e, kono kamЙ“e Й“e paayti mo"
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannooЙ“e doЕӢlle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o maaki: \"Addanee lam musiЙ—Й—o mon baaba-gooto. E on yi'aali miЙ—o timmina Й“etu ngun, e wonnde ko mi Й“urdo moЖҙЖҙude e weernooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray Й“etu alanaa on ka am Й—oo; wata on Й“ado lam kadi"
  12,61,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men Й—aЙ“Й“iray mo ben makko, menen ko men gollooЙ“e (Й—um)"
  12,62,"O maakani gollooЙ“e makko Й“en: \"WaЙ—ee coggeeli(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka doЕӢlle maЙ“Й“e: belajo'o Й“e annditay Й—i si Й“e ruttike ka yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e yiltoto"
  12,63,"Tuma nde Й“e ruttinoo ka ben maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben(baaba) amen, men salanaama Й“etu. neldu amen musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“etanee. Ko men reenooЙ“e mo"
  12,64,"O maaki: \"Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo on non e neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni moЖҙЖҙo reenoowo, ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  12,65,"Nde Й“e udditunoo doЕӢlle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e tawi coggeeli(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ruttaama e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko men Й—aЙ“Й“ata [kadi]? ЖҠii ko coggeeli amen, Й—i ruttaama e amen. MeЙ—en jiggana yimЙ“e amen, men reena musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“eydora Й“etu ngelooba; Й—um ko Й“etu newiingu"
  12,66,"O maaki: \"Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e mooЙ—on haa Жҙettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara on huЙ“inda\". ЖҒaawo Й“e Жҙettanii mo ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, o maaki: \"Alla e dow ko wowluЙ—en kon, ko O deeno"
  12,67,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e am, wata on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame seertuЙ—e. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muyЙ—e) Alla hay e huunde. Г‘aawoore alanaa si wanaa Alla: Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,68,"Nde Й“e naatirnoo nokku ka ben maЙ“Й“e yamirnoo Й“e Й—on, Й—um wonaano no duncana Й“e [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunooЙ—o e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. Kanko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal Men anndini mo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e anndaa"
  12,69,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o maЙ“Й“i neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: \"Ko mi neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko Й“e huuwaynoo"
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo Й“e doЕӢlle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o waЙ—i etirgal ngal ka doЕӢngal neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotooЙ—o eewnii: \"Ko onon yo seteeЙ“e, Ko on wuyЙ“e"
  12,71,"ЖҒe fewtiti e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wi'i: \"Ko honЙ—um hattiЙ—on"
  12,72,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men hattike etirde laamЙ—o on. Hino woodani kala adduЙ—o ngal, doЕӢngal ngelooba, ko min woni fawtiiЙ—o Й—um"
  12,73,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, gomЙ—ii hiЙ—on anndi men araali bonnugol ka leydi, men laataaki kadi wuyЙ“e"
  12,74,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko wonata njoЙ“di makko si tawii ko on fenooЙ“e"
  12,75,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"NjoЙ“di makko: ko kala mo: [Й—um] tawaa ka doЕӢngal mun, haray ko kanko [tigir] woni njoЙ“di mun. Ko wano non men yoЙ“itirta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fuЙ—Й—ori doЕӢle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ado doЕӢngal neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doЕӢngal neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laamЙ—o on, si wanaa hara ko Alla muuyi. MeЙ—en Й“antana darajaaji on mo Men muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]"
  12,77,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Si o wujjii, haray neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii\". Yuusufu mari Й—um ka wonkii makko, o feГұГұinanaali Й“e Й—um. O maaki: \"Ko onon Й“uri bonnde nokku! Ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko sifotoЙ—on"
  12,78,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo laamЙ—o on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyuЙ—o oggos; Жҙettu gooto e amen lonto makko. Menen men yi'ii ma jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,79,"O maaki: \"Moolaara Alla nde men nanngata si wanaa on mo men tawi doЕӢlle amen Й—en e juuЙ—e mun. Mene haray ontuma ko men tooГұuЙ“e"
  12,80,"Nde Й“e taЖҙinoo fii hettugol mo, Й“e martiti ko Й“e gunndondirЙ“e. MawЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'i: \"E on anndaa wonnde ben mon Жҙettodii e mo'on ahadi ka Alla, e aranun tuma welsindinoЙ—on e Yuusufa? Mi seerataa leydi ndin haa ben am duЕӢanoo lam maa O Гұaawana lam [hettugol mo], ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,81,"Ruttee ka ben mon wi'on: \"Ko an yo ben amen, Й“iЙ—Й—o maa on wujjii. Men seedaaki si wanaa ko men anndi, men wonaali reenuЙ“e ko wirnii"
  12,82,"Lanndo (yimЙ“e) saare nden nde men wonunoo e mun, e seteeЙ“e Й“en Й“e men hawrondirnoo e mun. Pellet ko men goonguЙ“e"
  12,83,"[Yaaquuba] maaki: \"Wonkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—anii on fiyaake! Ko muГұal labangal. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi Й“e, Й“e denndaangal. Ko Kanko woni AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  12,84,"O Й—uurnii Й“e o maaki: \"Ee suno am e fii Yuusufa!\" Gite makko Й—en rawniri suno. Ko o suuЙ—Й—o suno"
  12,85,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woodirii Alla! A seerataa hiЙ—a janntoo fii Yuusufa, haa wonaa horsuЙ—o maa wonaa jeyaaЙ—o e halkiiЙ“e Й“en"
  12,86,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko e Alla mi wullitotoo annde am e sunaare am. MiЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  12,87,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e am, yehee tefon fii Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on. Wata on taЖҙo e yurmeende Alla. Ko fii, taЖҙotaako e yurmeende Alla si wanaa yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  12,88,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka makko [kanko Yuusufa], Й“e wi'i: \"Ko an yo laamЙ—o, lorra heЙ“ii men memen e Й“eynguure amen; men ardii e sil'a jaasuЙ—o. Hunnan men Й“etu ngun, sakko-Й—aa e amen. Pellet, Alla yoЙ“ay sakkotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,89,"O maaki: \"Enee, on annditii ko waЙ—unoЙ—on Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on kon tuma nde wonunoЙ—on majjuЙ“e"
  12,90,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Kere ko an woni Yuusufa?\" O maaki: \"Ko min woni Yuusufa. Oo Й—oo ko miГұam. GomЙ—ii Alla moЖҙЖҙike e amen. Ko fii, mo gomЙ—ii o muГұГұike, pellet, Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondiri Alla, Alla Й“urnii ma e amen, men woniino woopuЙ“e"
  12,92,"O maaki: \"Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde! Yo Alla yawtan on. Ko Kano woni MoЖҙЖҙo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  12,93,"Yahdee e oo dolokke am Й—oo, werloЙ—on mo ka yeeso baaben am: o wattinay yi'oowo. Addanon lam Й“eynguure mon nden Й“e denndaangal"
  12,94,"Nde seteeЙ“e Й“en seerti [yalti Misra]ben maЙ“Й“e maaki: \"Min miЙ—o heЙ“a balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo on Й—aytinam"
  12,95,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, an hiЙ—a e majjere maaЙ—a Й“ooyunde nden"
  12,96,"Nde wewlinoowo on arunoo, o werlii [dolokke] on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maaki: \"E mi wi'anaano on miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  12,97,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, insinano men junuubi amen. Menen men woniino woopuЙ“e"
  12,98,"O maaki: \"Armami insinano on Joomi am. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  12,99,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o weerni ka makko [Й—on] mawЙ“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o, o maaki: \"Naatiree Misra, si Alla muuyii, ko on hooliiЙ“e"
  12,100,"O towniri mawЙ“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o ka belorki(danki), Й“e naayirani mo sujjugol. O maaki:\"Ko onon yo baaba'en, ko Й—um Й—oo woni firo koyЙ—ol am ngol oya tuma, gomЙ—ii Joomi am waЙ—ii ngol goonga. GomЙ—ii O moЖҙЖҙike e am tuma O yaltinnoo lam ka kaso, O itti on ka ladde, Й“aawo nde seytaane bonnii hakkunde am e ben-gootooЙ“e am Й“en. Pellet, Joomi am ko newaniiЙ—o ko O muuyi kon. Ko Kanko woni AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  12,101,"Joomi am, gomЙ—ii A yeЙ—ii lam laamu, A anndinii lam kadi firo koyЙ—i. [An] TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko An woni giЙ—o am aduna e laakara. Жіettitam ko mi juulЙ—o, waЙ—itdaa lam e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  12,102,"ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite wirniiЙ—e, MeЙ—en wahayini Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Й“e eЙ“Й“unoo fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on hiЙ“e fewja"
  12,103,"Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, hay si a rerЙ—i, (Й“e) wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  12,104,A Й—aЙ“Й“iraali Й“e e Й—um njoЙ“di. Nde wonaali si wanaa waaju wonannde winndere nden
  12,105,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e Aayeeje ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hiЙ“e rewa e majje hara ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e Й—e"
  12,106,"Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—intaa Alla, si wanaa hara ko Й“e sirkuЙ“e"
  12,107,"E Й“e hooli nde hippooje arata Й“e e lepte Alla Й—en maa darngal ngal ardira Й“e juhal, hara kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa"
  12,108,"Maaku: \"Ko ngo'ol woni laawol am, miЙ—o noddira e Alla dow hujja, min e Й“en jokkuЙ“e lam. Senayee woodanii Alla! Mi wonaali jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,109,"Men Nulaali ado maa si wanaa worЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ca'e Й—en, MeЙ—en wahayina e maЙ“Й“e. E Й“ee [fennooЙ“e ma] yiilotaako ka leydi, Й“e ndaara ko honno battane Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e wa'unoo? Pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en huluЙ“e [Alla]. E on haqqiltaa"
  12,110,"Haa si tawii NulaaЙ“e Й“en taЖҙike, (heeferЙ“e Й“en) fellita wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e fennaama, ballal Amen ngal ara e maЙ“Й“e; Men daЙ—nda on mo Men muuyi, lepte Amen Й—en ruttetaake gaayi e yimЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  12,111,"GomЙ—ii wonii e fillayeeje maЙ“Й“e Й—in tasakuyye wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en. Nde wonaali yewtere fefindaande. Ko woni, ko nde goonginnde Й—en adinooЙ—e nde, e fensitunde kala huunde, e peewal e yurmeende wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  13,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Raa. ЖҠee ko Aayeeje Deftere nden; jippinaande nden e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  13,2,"Ko Alla woni Й“amtuЙ—o kammuuli Й—in doose Й—e on yi'ataa. Refti O fotondiri ka dow 'Arshi, O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun: kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Hino toppitoo fiyaakuuji Й—in, Himo fensita Aayeeje Й—en belajo'o on yananay hawroygol e Joomi mon. @Corrected"
  13,3,"Ko Kanko woni fontuЙ—o leydi ndin, O waЙ—i e majji pelle e canЙ—i. E kala (noone) e dimЙ—e, O waЙ—i e majje noone Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i. Himo suddira jemma on Гұalorma on. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e"
  13,4,"Hino ka leydi tummbe Й“adondirЙ—e, e gese 'inabu, e remuruuji, e tamarooje dukkinЙ—e e Й—e wonaa Й—ukkinЙ—e, hiЙ—e yarniree ndiyam gootam, MeЙ—e Й“urna yoga majji dow yoga ka dakamme. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  13,5,"Si a ЕӢalЙ—ay, haray ko konngol maЙ“Й“e ngol jojji ЕӢalЙ—ude: \"Eyoo si men wontii mbulmbuldi, mene men wontay e tagu hesu?\" Ko Й“en woni yedduЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en, ko Й“en tonngoytee ka daaЙ—e mun, ko Й“en kadi woni yimЙ“e Yiite; kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge"
  13,6,"HiЙ“e hawjirane bone on ado moЖҙЖҙere nden. GomЙ—ii wulike ado maЙ“Й“e [lepte] yeruuje majje. Pellet, Joomi maa ko Jom-haforanal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, e tooГұe maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Pellet kadi Joomi maa, ko sattuЙ—o lepte"
  13,7,"ЖҒen heefereЙ“e no wi'a: \"Ko haЙ—no maande jippiniree e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Anndu ko an ko a jertinoowo, hino woodani yimЙ“e kala fewnoowo"
  13,8,"Alla no anndi ko ronndotoo kala deyel, e ko renngaaji Й—in ustata e ko Й—i Й“eydata. Kala huunde ka Makko, ko eЙ“Й“aa-Й—um"
  13,9,"AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, MawЙ—o, TownitiiЙ—o"
  13,10,"Hino fota [ka Makko anndugol] on suuЙ—uЙ—o konngol e mooЙ—on, e on feГұГұinЙ—o ngol, on suuЙ—irayЙ—o jemma, e on yaltiniroowo Гұalorma"
  13,11,"Hino woodani mo lontondirooЙ“e yeeso makko e Й“aawo makko, hiЙ“e reenira mo yamiroore Alla. Pellet Alla waylataa ko woni e yimЙ“e, haa Й“e wayla ko woni kon e maЙ“Й“e. Si Alla faandanike yimЙ“e bone, alaa yiltoowo mo. Alanaa Й“e gaanin Makko giЙ—o-heftoowo"
  13,12,"Ko Kanko woni hollirayЙ—o on maЖҙe Й—en hulugol [Й—e] e tamЖҙinagol [toЙ“o]; O fuЙ—Й—a Й—en duule tedduЙ—e"
  13,13,"Digge Й—en no senina Mo yettugol Mo, e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, immorde e kulol Makko. O wurta parГұite Й—en, O meminira Й—e on Mo O muuyi. KamЙ“e hiЙ“e wennja fii Alla, Kanko non ko O saЙ—tuЙ—o nanngal"
  13,14,"Hino woodani Mo noddaandu goonga! ЖҠin Й—i Й“e noddata ko woori Mo, Й—i jaabotaako Й“e e huunde; si wanaa wano fontuЙ—o newe mun e ndiyam fii yo Й—am yotto hunnduko makko, kono Й—am wonaali yottotoo-Й—am kon (hunnduko). Noddaandu heefereЙ“e Й“en wonaali si wanaa e majjere"
  13,15,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjannta, denndaangal ko woni ka kammuuli e la leydi, Й—oftaare e waawneede, e Й—owdiiji maЙ“Й“e, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  13,16,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo jeyi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla\". Maaku: \"E on jogiti gaanin Makko, heediiЙ—i Й—i waawanaa ko'e majji nafa wanaa lorra?\" Maaku: \"Hara bunЙ—o e yi'iiwo no fota? Kaa hara niЙ“e Й—en fotay e ndaygu ngu? Kaa Й“e waЙ—an Alla kafidiiЙ“e tagirЙ“e wano tagu Makko ngun, tagu ngun nanndani Й“e? Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o kala huunde, ko Kanko woni Bajjo, FooluЙ—o"
  13,17,"O jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, Й—am ili e jooli emmbere majjam. Ilol ngol ronndii ngufo hummbu-ngo. No e kon ko Й“e huЙ“Й“ata yiite e mun fii Й—aЙ“Й“u Й—aЙ“Й“ugol cuЙ—aari maa nafa-hoy, ngufo sugu mun. Ko wano nii Alla waЙ—irta misal goonga e fenannde. Si ko ngufo ngon, ngo yahray Й“eeЙ“ugol, ammaa ko nafata yimЙ“e Й“en kon, Й—um ГұiiЙ“a ka leydi. Ko wano nii Alla waЙ—irta mise Й—en"
  13,18,"Hino woodani Й“en nootiiЙ“e Joomi mun moЖҙЖҙere. ЖҒen Й“e nootaaki Mo, sinno woodaniino Й“e denndaangal ko woni kon ka leydi, e yeru mun wonndude e mu'un, Й“e soktorayno(soottorto) Й—um. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e bonЙ—um hasboore, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama. Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—undi"
  13,19,"E ko on annduЙ—o wonnde ko jippinaa kon e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga, wa'ata wa on Й“unЙ—o? Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e-haqqillaaji Й“en"
  13,20,"Й“en hunnooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin, Й“e firtataa ahodal(hoolaare)"
  13,21,"e Й“en jokkooЙ“e kon ko Alla yamiri yo jokke, hiЙ“e hula Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e hula bonnde hasboore"
  13,22,"Й“en muГұГұoriiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiiЙ“ni julde, Й“e nafqii e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e, gunndoo e kene, hiЙ“e duГұira moЖҙЖҙere nden bone on. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e battane galle"
  13,23,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, hiЙ“e naata Й—i, e Й“en moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e geyngolji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Hara Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hino naatirana Й“e kala damal"
  13,24,"Kisal wonii e mo'on, sabu muГұal mon ngal. Battane galle Й—en moЖҙЖҙii"
  13,25,"ЖҒen (non) firtooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin Й“aawo fiЙ“ugol ndi, hiЙ“e taЖҙoo e ko Alla yamiri kon yo jokke, hiЙ“e bonna ka leydi, Й“e Й—on, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ—di, hino woodani Й“e kadi bonЙ—um galle"
  13,26,"Alla no yaГұГұana arsike on Mo O muuyi, Himo Й“ittina. HiЙ“e weltora nguurndam aduna, nguurndam aduna non wonaali ka laakara, si wanaa dakamme-hoy"
  13,27,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e no wi'a: \"Ko haЙ—no Aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Alla majjinay tun mo O muuyi, O fewna e Makko on tuubuЙ—o-ruttii"
  13,28,"Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e Й“erЙ—e mun deeЖҙirta jantagol Alla. Anndee ko jantagol Alla ngol Й“erЙ—e Й—en deeЖҙirta"
  13,29,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, welo-welo woodaniiЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  13,30,"Ko wano nii Men nulir-maa e mofte - gomЙ—ii mofte goo yawtiino ado majje - fii yo a janngan Й“e nden nde Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, kono hiЙ“e yedda YurmeteeЙ—o On. Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni Joomi am. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko. Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde am"
  13,31,"Sinno janngeteende naЙ“irano pelle Й—en, maa leydi ndin seekiraa sabu mayre, maa nde wowliniraa maayЙ“e Й“en (harayno ko ndee Й—oo). Ko woni, ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow. E gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en anndaali wonnde, sinno Alla muuyuno, O fewnayna denndaangal yimЙ“e Й“en? Masiibo seeraali no heЙ“ira yedduЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e faggitii kon, maa [ngon masiibo] yana takko galle maЙ“Й“e nden haa fodoore Alla nden ara. Pellet Alla firtataa fodoore"
  13,32,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e jalkitanoo ma ado maaЙ—a. Mi muГұГұanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, refti Mi nanngi Й“e. Ko honno lepte Am Й—en wonirnoo"
  13,33,"E hara ko On dariiЙ—o e kala wonkii ko ki faggitii kon [Й“uri hanndude e dewal?...] ЖҒe waЙ—anii Alla kafidii- Й—i. Maaku: \"Innee-Й—i\" Kaa on humpitay Mo ko O anndaa ka leydi? Kaa ko ko [tun] e konngol? Ko woni, heeferЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—inanaa ma pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e sakkaa(pala) e laawol ngol. Kala mo Alla majjini, fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  13,34,"Hino woodani Й“e lepte ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet ko lepte laakara Й—en Й“uri sattude, alanaa Й“e daЙ—ndoowo (Й“e) e Alla"
  13,35,"Sugu Aljanna mo gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en fodaa on: CanЙ—i no ila ley makko; ГұaamЙ—i makko Й—in ko duumiiЙ—um, e Й—owdi makko ndin. ЖҠum ko battane Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e, battane heeferbe non ko Yiite"
  13,36,"ЖҒen Й“e Men okki Deftere nden, hiЙ“e weltora kon ko jippinaa e maaЙ—a. No e leЖҙЖҙi kon Й“en yeddooЙ“e yoga mayre. Maaku: \"Anndee ko yamiraa-mi, ko nde reway-mi Alla hara mi sirkanaali Mo. Ko e Makko nodday-mi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde am"
  13,37,"Ko wano nii Men jippiniri nde Гұaawoore (e haala) aarabu. Pellet si a jokkii mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“aawo nde ganndal ari e maa, alanaa ma gaanin Alla immorde e giЙ—o, wanaa daЙ—ndoowo"
  13,38,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii NulaaЙ“e ado maa, Men waЙ—ani Й“e genndiraaЙ“e e geyngol. Haananaa NulaaЙ—o nde o addata Aaya, si wanaa e sakkitoore Alla. Hino woodani kala lajal caati"
  13,39,"Alla no meha ko O Muuyi O tabatina (ko O wela), ko ka Makko yumma defte Й—en woni"
  13,40,"Si Men holliima yogo e ko Men fodi Й“e, maa Men hunnu maa (ado mun), anndu ko fawi maa ko yottingol, haasboore nde ko Menen fawtii"
  13,41,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde MeЙ—en ara e leydi ndin, Men Й—uytira ndi ka seraaji mayri? Alla no Гұaawa, alaa wurtinoowo Гұaawoore Makko nden, ko O yacciiЙ—o Гұaawoore"
  13,42,GomЙ—ii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e fewjaniino (AnnabaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e); ko Alla non pewje Й—en fow heeranii. Himo anndi kala wonkii faggitotoo. Arma heefereЙ“e Й“en annda ko hommbo battane galle (moЖҙЖҙe) woodani
  13,43,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en hino wi'a: \"Wanaa a NulaaЙ—o\". Maaku: \"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon, e Й“en jogitiiЙ“e ganndal Deftere nden"
  14,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. (Ndee ko) Deftere nde Men jippini e maaЙ—a, fii yo yaltinir yimЙ“e Й“en e niЙ“e faade e annoora, e duЕӢayee Joomi maЙ“Й“e, haa e laawol FooluЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o"
  14,2,"Alla, On Mo woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Bone woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en, immorde e lepte sattuЙ—e"
  14,3,"ЖҒen Й“urdinooЙ“e nguurndam aduna Й—am e dow laakara, Й“e faddoo e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorgal. ЖҒen Й—ow wonii e majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  14,4,"Men nuliraali NulaaЙ—o (woo), si wanaa e Й—emngal yimЙ“e makko Й“en, fii no o Й“annginirana Й“e. Alla no majjina on Mo muuyi, O fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  14,5,"GomЙ—ii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen Й—en [wi'ugol Mo]: \"Yaltin yimЙ“e maa Й“en e niЙ“e faade e annoora, anndintinaa Й“e ГұalЙ—i Alla Й—in\". Pellet hino e Й—um, tasakuyeeji kala munyoowo, yettoowo (neema)"
  14,6,"(Janto) tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"siftoree neema Alla on e mooЙ—on, tuma O daЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“e no defaynoo on lepte bonЙ—e. HiЙ“e hirsa Й“iЙ—Й“e mon (worЙ“e) Й“e acca (Й“iЙ—Й“e) mon rewЙ“e. Wonii e Й—um mo'on, jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon"
  14,7,"e tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo: \"Pellet si on yettii, ma Mi Й“eydan on. Si on yeddii non, pellet lepte am Й—en ko saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  14,8,"Muusaa maaki: \"Si on yeddii, onon e wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en fow, [anndon] pellet Alla ko Galo YettiniiЙ—o"
  14,9,"E kumpite Й“en adinooЙ“e on araali on, yimЙ“e Nuuhu e Aadi, e Samuuda e Й“en wonunooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“- Й“e, anndaa Й“e si wanaa Alla? NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e rutti juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka kunndule maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Menen men yed- dii ko nulidaЙ—on e mun kon, menen, meЙ—en e sikkitii e ko noddoton men e mun sikkitiiЙ“e"
  14,10,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maaki: \"E hara sikke no e fii Alla, fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, himo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e junuubi mon, himo nennana on haa e lajal innaangal?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"On wonaali si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru amen. HiЙ—on faandii nde sakkotoЙ—on(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen rewaynoo. Addanee men hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  14,11,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maakani Й“e: \"[Ko goonga], men wonaali si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru mon, kono Alla no moЖҙЖҙoo e Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Laatanaaki men nde men addana on hujja, si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Ko e Alla gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotoo"
  14,12,"Ko haЙ—ata men nde fawotoo e Alla, gomЙ—ii O fewnii men (e) laawi amen? Ma men muГұГұo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotoo"
  14,13,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e (kadi) wi'ani NulaaЙ“e mun Й“en: \"Ma men yaltin on ka leydi amen, maa ruttoЙ—on e diina amen\". Joomi maЙ“Й“e wahayini e maЙ“Й“e: \"Ma men halku tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  14,14,"Ma Men hoЙ—nu on e leydi ndin Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠum ko wonannde on huluЙ—o daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa Am on"
  14,15,ЖҒe Й—aЙ“Й“i uddital. Sooyi kala dunndaranke ЖҙagguЙ—o
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ЖҙiiЖҙiiri"
  14,17,"himo wooЙ“a Й—am, e Й—eЙ“ataa Й“ennugol Й—am. Maayde nden ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaali maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte sattuЙ—e"
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa Й“en yedduЙ“e Joomi mun, kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tiiЙ—i e mun, e Гұalaande wippoore. ЖҒe hettoytaa huunde e ko Й“e faggitinoo. Ko Й—um woni majjere wonЙ—Й—unde"
  14,19,"E a yi'aali Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin goonga? Si O muuyii, O ittay on O adda tagu hesu"
  14,20,Й—um wonaali sattuЙ—um ka Alla
  14,21,"ЖҒe feeГұana Alla Й“e denndaangal. Lo'uЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Menen men wonanno on jokkuЙ“e. Taw si on duncanay men e lepte Alla Й—en goЙ—Й—um?\" ЖҒen wi'a: \"Sinno Alla fewnuno men, men fewnayno on. Hino fota e amen, si en Й—enЖҙi maa si en muГұГұi; daЙ—irde alanaa en"
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on Гұaawaa: \"Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi fodi on mi lunndii on. Alanaa lam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on jaabike lam. Wata on felam; felee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotooЙ—o on; wanaa on faabotooЙ“e lam. Mi yeddii ko kafidunoЙ—on mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)\". Pellet, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  14,23,"GomЙ—imЙ“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en naatnaa e Aljannaaji, canЙ—i hino ila ley majji, ko Й“e duumorayЙ“e ton e duЕӢayee Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Hiwraandu maЙ“Й“e ndun ton ko: \"Salaam\" (Kisiyee). @Corrected"
  14,24,"E a yi'aali ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laaЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabituЙ—i, calЙ—i maggal no ka weeyo"
  14,25,"Hingal okkira dimЙ—e maggal on tuma kala, e duЕӢayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yimЙ“e Й“en mise, belajo'o Й“e waajitoto"
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol soЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal soЙ“ungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa Й—um ГұiiЙ“irde"
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina tooГұooЙ“e Й“en. Alla no waЙ—a ko O muuyi"
  14,28,"E a tinaali Й“en waЙ—titirЙ“e neemaaji Alla Й—in keeferaaku, Й“e weerni yimЙ“e Й“en galle halkaare"
  14,29,"Jahannama, hiЙ“e naata nge, nge bonii ГұiiЙ“irde"
  14,30,"ЖҒe waЙ—ani Alla yerondiraaЙ—i fii yo Й“e majjin (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Alla ngol. Maaku: \"Dakmitee, pellet ruttorde mon nden ko ka Yiite"
  14,31,"Maakan jeyaaЙ“e am gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, yo Й“e Гұinnu julde Й“e wintoo e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e gunndoo e kene, ado nde arata Й“e Гұalaande nde jgeeygu alaa e mun wanaa weldigal"
  14,32,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi, O jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam; O yaltiniri Й—am dimЙ—e arsike wonannde on. O eltirani on laaЙ—e Й—en, fii yo Й—e dogir ka maayo e duЕӢayee Makko. O eltani on kadi canЙ—i Й—in"
  14,33,O eltani on naange ngen e lewru ndun dogooji Й—iЙ—i. O eltani on jemma on e Гұalorma on
  14,34,"O okki on e kala ko toriЙ—on Mo. Si on lintii neemaaji Alla Й—in, on moftataaЙ—i. Pellet neЙ—Й—anke on ko hee- wuЙ—o tooГұe, heewuЙ—o yeddugol"
  14,35,"(Janto) kadi tuma nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Joomi am, waЙ—u ndee saare hooliinde, daЙ—ndaa lam e Й“iЙ—Й“e am Й“en nde men rewata sanamuuji"
  14,36,"Joomi am, kannji (sanamuuji Й—in), Й—i majjinii ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala jokkuЙ—o lam, on Й—on ko jeyidaaЙ—o e am. Kala non yedduЙ—o lam, haray An ko A Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  14,37,"Joomi amen, min mi hoЙ—inii yoga e Й“iЙ—Й“e am Й“en e aynde nde wonaa remotoonde, ka Suudu Maa Hormanteeru, - Joomi amen - fii yo Й“e Гұinnu julde. WaЙ—u Й“erЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en no yiiloo e maЙ“Й“e, arsikaaЙ“e dimЙ—e, belajo'o Й“e yetta"
  14,38,"Joomi amen, pellet, An hiЙ—a anndi ko men suuЙ—i e ko men feГұГұini: hay huunde suuЙ—otaako Alla ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  14,39,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On yeЙ—uЙ—o lam e hoore mawngu, Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa. Pellet, Joomi am ko nanoowo du'aa"
  14,40,"Joomi am, waЙ—an Гұinnoowo julde e Й“eynugol am ngol. Joomi amen, jaЙ“u toraare am nden"
  14,41,"Joomi amen, haforanam min e jibimЙ“e lam Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Гұalnde Гұaawoore nden dorotoo"
  14,42,"Wata sikku Alla ko welsindiiЙ—o e ko tooГұooЙ“e Й“en huuwata. Anndu ko O nenniranta Й“e, ko haa e Гұalaande nde gite saafotoo e mun"
  14,43,"Ko Й“e heГұiiЙ“e, ЕӢallimЙ“e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, ndaarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yiltotaako e maЙ“Й“e, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko yeewuЙ—e"
  14,44,"Jertniri yimЙ“e Й“en Гұalaande nde lepte Й—en arata Й“e, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Joomi amen, nennan men haa lajal Й“aЙ—iingal, men nootoo noddaanndu Maa, men jokka NulaaЙ“e Й“en\". E on laatanooki on woondiino ado (hannde) alanaa on iwugol (ton)"
  14,45,"HoЙ—uЙ—on e koЙ—ooli Й“en tooГұuЙ“e ko'e mun. ЖҒanngani on ko honno Men huuwunoo Й“e, Men piyani on mise"
  14,46,"GomЙ—ii Й“e fewjii feere maЙ“Й“e nden. Ko ka Alla feere maЙ“Й“e nden woni, hay si feere maЙ“Й“e nden ittayno pelle Й—en"
  14,47,"Wata a sikku Alla ko lunndotooЙ—o fodoore Makko (nde O fodi) NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Jom yottagol"
  14,48,"Гұalnde leydi ndin waЙ—titirtee leydi goo, e kammuuli Й—in, Й“e feeГұana Alla, Bajjo On, FooluЙ—o On"
  14,49,"A yi'ay bomЙ“e Й“en nden Гұalnde, ko jokkindiraaЙ“e e kolombooje"
  14,50,"Dolokkaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko mbullam feewnira, Yiite ngen no sudda geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  14,51,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“itu kala wonkii ko ko faggitii. Pellet, Alla ko yaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  14,52,"Ndee (Alqur'aanaare) ko yottinoore yimЙ“e Й“en fii yo Й“e waajitornde, e yoЙ“e anndu kadi, wonnde Kanko ko O reweteeЙ—o Gooto, e fii yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en waajitor"
  15,1,"Alif, laam, raa. ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Deftere e janngeteende Й“annginnde"
  15,2,Na waawi HeeferЙ“e Й“en yeloyto sinno Й“e laatino juulЙ“e
  15,3,"Accu Й“e, Й“e Гұaama Й“e dakmitoo, yela soklina Й“e; arma Й“e anndoya"
  15,4,"Men halkaali saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde happu anndaaЙ—o"
  15,5,"Mofte woo adotaako lajal mun, Й“e nennantaake kadi"
  15,6,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mo Deftere nden jippinaa e mun, an ko a feetuЙ—o"
  15,7,"Ko haЙ—no addanaa men Malaa'ikaaЙ“e, si a laatike goonguЙ—o"
  15,8,"Men jippinirtaa Malaa'ika si wanaa fii goonga; Й“e wonataa ontuma, nennanteeЙ“e"
  15,9,"Menen Men jippinii Deftere nden, Menen kadi ko Men reenooЙ“e nde"
  15,10,"GomЙ—ii Men nuliino ado maa, e leГұi adinooЙ“e"
  15,11,NulaaЙ—o (woo) araali e maЙ“Й“e si wanaa Й“e jalkitay mo
  15,12,Ko wano nii Men naadiri Й—um e Й“erЙ—e bonЙ“e Й“en
  15,13,"ЖҒe gomЙ—intaa nde, gomЙ—ii sunna aramЙ“e Й“en yawtiino"
  15,14,"Hay si Men udditanno Й“e damal ka kammu, Й“e waЙ—tini hiЙ“e Жҙawra heen"
  15,15,"Й“e wi'ayno: \"Anndee gite amen Й—en hippa. Wurin ko men yimЙ“e mbilЙ—aaЙ“e"
  15,16,"GomЙ—ii Men waЙ—ii ka kammu koode, Men cuЙ—irani Й—e ndaarooЙ“e"
  15,17,Men reeni mbo e kala seytaane riiwaaЙ—o
  15,18,"Si wanaa on wujjuЙ—o nanЙ—e, o jokkintina hoodere-fiЙ—aynnde jalЙ“unde"
  15,19,"Leydi ndin, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fuЙ—ini e mayri kala huunde eЙ“Й“aande"
  15,20,"Men waЙ—ani on e mayri wuurirЙ—e, e Й“en Й“e on laatanooki arsikooЙ“e Й—um"
  15,21,"Huunde alaa si wanaa marga mun ko ka Amen, Men jippintaa Й—um si wanaa e eЙ“Й“oore anndaande"
  15,22,"Men wurti keneeli Й—in hawrondirooji e duule; Men jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam Men yarniri on Й—am, wonaa onon mari Й—am"
  15,23,"Ko Menen kadi woni ko wuurnata Men wara, ko Menen woni ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  15,24,GomЙ—ii Men anndii adiiЙ“e e mon Й“en GomЙ—ii Men anndii sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en
  15,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko mooЙ“oyta Й“e. Kanko ko O Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o"
  15,26,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii neЙ—Й—anke on e senЖҙayngal, e (cenlatngal) loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal"
  15,27,"E jinnaaji Й—in, Men tagir ndu ko adii, e yiite ooyunge"
  15,28,"Janto tuma nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: \"Min ko Mi tagiroowo Й“anndinke immorde e senЖҙayngal, e loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal"
  15,29,"si Mi fotndiii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu Am on, haray suuyanee mo ko on sujjuЙ“e"
  15,30,Malaa'ika'en fow sujji Й“e denndaangal
  15,31,"si wanaa ibuliisa, o salii tawdeede e sujjooЙ“e Й“en"
  15,32,"O daali: \"Ko an yo Ibuliisa, e ko heЙ“u maa a laatodaaki e sujjuЙ“e Й“en"
  15,33,"O wi'i: \"Mi wonatah sujjanoowo Й“anndinke mo TaguЙ—aa immorde e senЖҙayngal, e loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal"
  15,34,"O daali: \"Yaltu ton, an on ko a riiwaaЙ—o"
  15,35,"pellet, kuddi fawike e ma haa Гұalnde njoЙ“di diina"
  15,36,"O wi'i : \"Joomi am, nennitanam haa Гұalnde ndeЙ“e immintintee"
  15,37,"O daali:\"An,ko a jeyaaЙ—o e nennitanteeЙ“e Й“en"
  15,38,haa e Гұalaande happu anndaaЙ—o
  15,39,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, sabu ko bewinЙ—aa mi kon, ma mi cuЙ—inan Й“e ka leydi, ma mi bewnu Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  15,40,"si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Maa, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e"
  15,41,"O daali: \"Ngol Й—oo ko laawol ka Am focciingol"
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, a alanaa Й“e cemmbe, si wanaa Й“en bewЙ“e jokkuЙ“e ma"
  15,43,Pellet Jahannama on wonii fodoore maЙ“Й“e Й“e fow
  15,44,Hinge mari dame jeeЙ—iЙ—i; damal kala e majje no mari geЙ“al senndaangal
  15,45,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e aljannaaji e Й“ulli"
  15,46,"Naatiree Й—i e kisial, ko on hooliiЙ“e"
  15,47,"Men Й—oofi kala ko woni e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e konnaagu(cokotaagal): Й“e wonti musiЙ—Й“e fewtondirЙ“e e danЙ—e"
  15,48,"Tampere heЙ“ataa Й“e ton, Й“e wonah kadi yaltintee Й“e ton"
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, ko Min woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte Am Й—en, ko Й—en woni lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  15,51,Yeetito Й“e kadi fii hoЙ“Й“e Ibraahiima Й“en
  15,52,"Tuma Й“e naatunoo ka makko Й“e wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men Й—enЖҙii Й“e on"
  15,53,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a faay, menen meЙ—en wewlinire [Й“iЙ—Й—o] gorko ganndo"
  15,54,"O maaki: \"E on wewliniray lam [Й—um] e hoore ko mi nawyi kon? E ko wewlinirton mi"
  15,55,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men wewlinirii ma goonga, wata a jeye e taЖҙiiЙ“e Й“en"
  15,56,"O maaki: \"Ko hommbo taЖҙotoo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wanaa majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  15,57,"O maaki: \"Ko woni fii mon, onon Й“ee imminaaЙ“e"
  15,58,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Menen men nulaa ko e yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  15,59,"si wanaa Й“eynguure Luuti nden, pellet ko men daЙ—ndooЙ“e Й“e denndaangal"
  15,60,"si wanaa debbo makko on\". Men hoddirii on Й—on ko jeyaaЙ—o e halketeeЙ“e Й“en"
  15,61,Nde imminaaЙ“e Й“en aruno ka Й“eynguure Luuti
  15,62,"O maaki: \"Onon ko on yimЙ“e faaytaa Й“e"
  15,63,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wurin men addanii ma ko Й“e wonunoo e sikkitaade kon"
  15,64,"Men addanii ma goonga kan, pellet ko men goonguЙ“e"
  15,65,"Yahdu e Й“eynguure maa nden ka taЖҙitannde jem- ma, jokkaa Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e; hara gooto e mo'on yeЖҙЖҙitaaki, rewon ka yamiraЙ—on"
  15,66,"Men anndini mo on fiyaaku: wonnde wattannde Й“ee Й—oo, ko taЖҙeteeЙ—um ka subaka"
  15,67,YimЙ“e saare nden ari hiЙ“e wewla
  15,68,"O maaki: \"ЖҒee Й—oo ko hoЙ“Й“e am, wata on wirtam"
  15,69,"Hulee Alla, wata on hoynam"
  15,70,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"E men haЙ—aali ma [weernugol] tagoore nden"
  15,71,"O maaki: \"ЖҒee Й—oo ko jiwЙ“e am, si wonii ko on waЙ—ooЙ“e [goЙ—Й—um]"
  15,72,Mi woondirii nguurndam maa! ЖҒe wonii e siwrugol maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e wemmbii
  15,73,Haacaango ngon nanngiri Й“e ka puЙ—al
  15,74,"Men waЙ—tiniri dow mayre on ley mayre, Men saaЖҙini(toЙ“ri) e maЙ“Й“e kaaЖҙe iwruЙ—e e loope juЙ—aaЙ—e"
  15,75,"Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde Й“en teskotooЙ“e"
  15,76,"Pellet, Й—en [ca'e] no e jurol(bolol) ГұiiЙ“ungol"
  15,77,"Wonii e Й—um, maande wonannde Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  15,78,"GomЙ—ii yimЙ“e fitaare(sutu) Й“en [kadi] ko tooГұuЙ“e"
  15,79,"Men yoЙ“tii e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet Й—en [ca'e] Й—iЙ—i wonii e laawol Й“anngungol"
  15,80,GomЙ—i yimЙ“e (aynde) Hijiri nden fennii NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  15,81,"Men addani Й“e aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatii Й—uurniiЙ“e Й—e"
  15,82,"Hari hiЙ“e lesoynoo e pelle Й—en cuuЙ—i, ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e"
  15,83,Haacaango ngon nanngiri Й“e ka subaka
  15,84,NafaaniЙ“e kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e faggitoo
  15,85,"Men tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, si wanaa e goonga. Pellet, darngal ngal ko arayngal! yaafora jaafaggol labaangol"
  15,86,"Tabitii ko Joomi maa woni TaguЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o"
  15,87,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii ma jeeЙ—iЙ—i ummorde Й—immitaa-ngol, e Alqur'aanaare mawnde nden"
  15,88,"Wata a Й“amtu gite maa Й—en e neemaaji Й—i Men dakmiti Й“e e mum en, wata a sunu e maЙ“Й“e, lesЙ—in becce maa Й—en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  15,89,"Maaku: \"Min ko mi jertinoowo Й“annginoowo"
  15,90,"Wano Men jippinirnoo e senndooЙ“e [defte Alla] Й“en [lepte]"
  15,91,ЖҒen waЙ—uЙ“e Alqur'aanaare nden geЙ“e-geЙ“e
  15,92,Mi woondirii Joomi maa! Ma Men lanndoyo Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e
  15,93,fii ko Й“e wonunoo e huuwude
  15,94,"FeГұГұin ko yamira-Й—aa kon, Й—uurno-Й—aa sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  15,95,Menen Men yonii ma e Й“en jalkitooЙ“e
  15,96,Й“en waЙ—dooЙ“e e Alla reweteeЙ—o goo. Aray ka Й“e annda
  15,97,GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en anndi wonnde bernde maa nde na Й“iЙ—tora ko Й“e wowlata kon
  15,98,"Subbhinor yettugol Joomi maa, laato-daa e sujjooЙ“e Й“en"
  15,99,rewaa Joomi haa yananeede (maayde) ara e maa
  16,1,"Yamiroore Alla nden Й“adike, wata on hawjan nde. Senayee woodanii Mo! O toowii e ko Й“e sirkata"
  16,2,"Himo jippinira Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en e wayhu on e yamiroore Makko, dow mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, wonnde : \"Jertinree wiide reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Min. Hulee Lam"
  16,3,O tagiri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin goonga. O toowii e ko Й“e sirkoobe sirkata ko
  16,4,O tagiri neЙ—Й—anke iwde e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu); jaka yoo kanko ko wennjoowo Й“annguЙ—o
  16,5,"NeemoraaЙ—i Й—in, O tagani on Й—i; no e majji nguli nugguki e nafaaji. Ko e majji kadi Гұaamoton"
  16,6,"Hino woodani on e majji cuЙ—aari, tuma njofnoton Й—i e tuma oornoton Й—i"
  16,7,"HiЙ—i ronndoo donle mon naЙ“a e leydi ndi on yotto- tanooko si wanaa e tampere pittaali. Pellet, Joomi mon ko O YurmeteeЙ—o HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,8,"E pucci, e mbam-pucci, e mbabbi, fii yo on waЙ—Й—o Й—i, e cuЙ—aari. Himo taga kadi ko on anndaa"
  16,9,"Ko Alla woodani Й“anngingol laawol focciingol ngol, no e majji ngol feewaani. Si O muuyuno, O fewnay on denndaangal"
  16,10,"Ko Kanko woni jippinirЙ—o ndiyam ka kammu, hino woodani on e majjam njaram, leЙ—Й—e no (yalta) e majjam, ko e majjam kadi oornoton"
  16,11,"Himo fuЙ—nirana on Й—am aawruuji, nebbanteeje, e tamarooje, e inabuuje, e kala dimЙ—e. Wonii e Й—um, tasakuyee wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e"
  16,12,"O eltani on jemma on e Гұaloma on; naange ngen e lewru ndun. Koode Й—en kadi ko eltiraaЙ—e yamiroore Makko. Wonii e Й—um, tasakuyeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  16,13,"E ko O tagani on kon ka leydi sertuЙ—um nooneeji. Wonii e Й—um, tasakuyee wonannde yimЙ“e waajitorayЙ“e"
  16,14,"Ko Kanko woni eltanЙ—o on maayo ngon fii yo on Гұaamu e maggo teewu keccu, yaltinon e maggo cuЙ—aari ndi Й“ornotoЙ—on. A yi'ay laaЙ—e no feЖҙЖҙa e maggo, e fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u e Й“ural Makko ngal, belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  16,15,"O tuti penle ka leydi fii wata Й—e dillidu e mo'on, e canЙ—i, e Й—ate, belajo'o on feeway"
  16,16,"e maandeeji [laawi]. Koode Й—en hiЙ“e Й—owora Й—e"
  16,17,E hara tagoowo on wa'ay wa on tagataa? E on waajitotaako
  16,18,"Si on lintii neemaaji Alla Й—in, on moftataa Й—i. Pellet, Alla ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,19,Alla no anndi ko suuЙ—oton e ko feГұГұinton
  16,20,"ЖҠin Й—i Й“e rewata gaanin Alla, Й—i tagataa hay huunde, kannji tigi ko Й—i tageteeЙ—i"
  16,21,"KoЙ—i maayuЙ—i Й—i wuuraa, Й“e so'aa-anndude nde Й“e immintintee"
  16,22,"ReweteeЙ—o mon on ko ReweteeЙ—o gooto. ЖҒen Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko yedduЙ—e, Й“en ko townitiiЙ“e"
  16,23,Sikke alaa wonnde Alla no anndi ko Й“e suuЙ—ata e ko Й“e feГұГұinta. Kanko O yiЙ—aa townitiiЙ“e Й“en
  16,24,"Si Й“e wi'anaama : \"Ko honЙ—um Joomi mon jippini?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  16,25,"Fii yo Й“e ronndo bakkaatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in fow Г‘alnde Darngal, e bakkaatuuji Й“en Й“e majjinirta ko aldaa e ganndal; anndee bonii ko Й“e ronndoytoo"
  16,26,"GomЙ—ii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e fewjiino, Alla yirbiniri mahdeele maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka doose. Kippoodi ndin yanti e maЙ“Й“e, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e nokku ka Й“e so'aa-aanndude"
  16,27,"Refti Г‘alnde Darngal, O hoynoyayЙ“e, O wi'anaЙ“e: Ko honto kafidaaЙ—i am Й—in Й—i haЙ“iraynoЙ—on fii mun?\" ЖҒen okkaaЙ“e ganndal wi'a: \"Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  16,28,"ЖҒen Й“en Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hunnata, tooГұuЙ“e ko'e-mun, Й“e werloo jebbilraare, (Й“e wi'a): \"Men wonaa- no gollatnooЙ“e ko boni!\" -\"Wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko annduЙ—o ko huuwaynoЙ—on"
  16,29,Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en luttugol ton. Nge bonii ГұaaЖҙorde wonande townitiiЙ“e Й“en
  16,30,"Wi'anee Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e: \"Ko honЙ—um Joomi mon jippini?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko moЖҙЖҙere\". Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere; pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude. Nde moЖҙЖҙii saare gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  16,31,"Aljannaaji duumal, hiЙ“e naati Й—i, canЙ—i no ila ley majji. Hino woodani Й“e ton kala ko Й“e faaletee; ko wano nii Alla yoЙ“irta gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  16,32,"ЖҒen Й“e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en warta hara ko Й“e laaЙ“uЙ“e- Й“e wi'an [Й“en]: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon! Naatiree Aljanna on, sabu ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  16,33,"Hara [Й“ee sirkooЙ“e fenna] hino habbitii si wanaa nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en arata e maЙ“Й“e, maa yami- roore Joomi maa nden ara? Ko wano non Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e waЙ—irnoo. Alla tooГұaali Й“e; si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonunoo e tooГұuЙ“e"
  16,34,"Boneeji Й—i Й“e huuwi Й—in memi Й“en, kon ko Й“e jalkitaynoo jippii e maЙ“Й“e"
  16,35,"ЖҒen sirkuЙ“e wi'i: \"Sinno Alla muuyuno, men rewataano gaanin Makko hay huunde, wanaa menen wanaa baabiraaЙ“e amen; men harmintaa- no gaanin Makko hay huunde\". Ko wano non adi- nooЙ“e Й“en gerdunoo. Taw si no fawiiii NulaaЙ“e Й“en si wanaa yottingol Й“anngina"
  16,36,"GomЙ—ii Men imminii e kala mofte NulaaЙ—o, wonnde rewee Alla, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on bewnayЙ—i Й—in. Hino e maЙ“Й“e on Mo Alla fewni, hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi on mo majjere nden jojji e mun. Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane fennooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo"
  16,37,"Si a rerЙ—ii e peewal maЙ“Й“e, [anndu] pellet, Alla fewnataa on Mo o majjini, alanaa Й“e kadi wallooЙ“e"
  16,38,"ЖҒe woondirii Alla haЙ—tirde goondooje maЙ“Й“e: \"Alla immintintaa on maayuЙ—o\". Wanaa non! ЖҠum ko fodoore goonga ka Makko, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“e anndaa"
  16,39,"(O immintiniroyay Й“e) fii yo O Й“annginan Й“e ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e mun, e fii yo Й“en yedduЙ“e anndu wonnde hari ko Й“e fenooЙ“e"
  16,40,"Anndee daalol Amen wonannde huunde, si Men faandike nde, Men wi'anay nde tun: \"Laato\", nde laatoo"
  16,41,"ЖҒen ferunooЙ“e fii Alla, Й“aawo Й“e tooГұaama, ma Men hoЙ—nu Й“e ka aduna (e weerde) moЖҙЖҙere. Pellet, ko njoЙ“di laakara ndin Й“uri mawnude, si tawno hiЙ“e anndi"
  16,42,"ЖҒen muГұГұiiЙ“e, e tuugii e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  16,43,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a si wanaa worЙ“e, Men wahayina e maЙ“Й“e. Lanndee yimЙ“e defte Й“en si wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  16,44,"(Men nulirii Й“e) Й“anngudi e defte. Men jippini e maaЙ—a janngeteende nden, fii yo a Й“annginan yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko jippinaa e maЙ“Й“e, belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e miijitoto"
  16,45,"E hara Й“en fewjuЙ“e boneeji Й—in hooli wonnde Alla munnirtaa Й“e leydi ndin, maa lepte Й—en ardirana Й“e nokku mo Й“e so'aa-anndude"
  16,46,"maa O nanngira Й“e yahdu maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wonaali laawotooЙ“e"
  16,47,"Maa O nanngira Й“e e hoore kulol. Anndu Joomi mon ko YurmeteeЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,48,"E Й“ee yi'aali ko Alla tagi kon e huunde nde Й—owЙ—e mun yiiltondirta Гұaamo e nano, sujjangol Alla, hara ko Й—i yannkiniiЙ—i"
  16,49,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjanta kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, immorde e ruugayngel, e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako. @Corrected"
  16,50,"HiЙ“e hulira Joomi maЙ“Й“e, senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e waЙ—a ko Й“e yamiraa. @Corrected"
  16,51,"Alla daali: \"Wata on jogito reweteeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Anndee Kanko ko O reweteeЙ—o gooto. Ko Min woni ko huloton"
  16,52,Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi; ko Kanko Й—oftagol duumiingol tabitani. E ko ko woori Alla huloton
  16,53,"Kala ko heЙ“uЙ—on e neema ko immorde ka Alla. Refti si lorra memii on, ko Ka Makko wullitotoЙ—on"
  16,54,"Refti si O huncanii on lorra kan, e jaka fedde goo e mo'on, ko sirkanooЙ“e Joomi mun"
  16,55,"Fii yo Й“e yeddu ko Men okki Й“e kon. Awa dakmitee, arma anndon"
  16,56,HiЙ“e waЙ—ana huunde nde Й“e anndaa geЙ“al e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e. Wallaahi! On lannditete e kon ko fefindotonoЙ—on
  16,57,HiЙ“e waЙ—ana Alla Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e. Senayee woodanii Mo HiЙ“e (waЙ—ana) ko'e maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e wooЙ—itii
  16,58,"Si gooto e maЙ“Й“e wewliniraama Й“iЙ—Й—o debbo, yeeso makko ngon waЙ—tina wayliingo Й“alewo e, hara ko o suuЙ—-suno"
  16,59,"Himo suuЙ—ora yimЙ“e Й“en, sabu bone mo o wewliniraa on. E o jogitoray mo e hoore koyeera kaa o uway mo ka leydi? Annde bonii ko Й“e Гұaawata"
  16,60,"Hino woodani Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara sifa bonЙ—o on. Ko Alla woodani sifa toowuЙ—o on. Ko Kanko kadi woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  16,61,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yimЙ“e Й“en sabu tooГұe maЙ“Й“e Й—en, O ccataano e dow mayri ruugayngel. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana Й“e haa e lajal annda- ngal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e nennantaake yonta Й“e adintinantaake"
  16,62,"HiЙ“e waЙ—ana Alla ko Й“e aГұanta [ko'e-maЙ“Й“e]. ЖҠemЙ—e maЙ“Й“e no sifoo fenaande, wonnde no woodani Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Sikke alaa wonnde no woodani Й“e Yiite, e wonnde ko Й“e Й—aliiЙ“e"
  16,63,"Wallaahi! GomЙ—ii Men nulii e mofte adinooЙ“e ma, seytaane cuЙ—ani Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Ko kanko woni giЙ—o maЙ“Й“e hannde, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  16,64,"Men jippiniraali Deftere nden e maaЙ—a si wanaa fii yo a Й“annginan Й“e kon ko Й“e luutondiri e mun, kadi ko nde peewal, e yurmeende wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  16,65,"Alla jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitiri Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Wonii e Й—um, maande wonannde yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e"
  16,66,"Hino woodani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in tasakuyee: MeЙ—en yarna on e ko woni e deedi majji, - hakkunde coowo e ЖҙiiЖҙam - Й“iraaЙ—am laaЙ“uЙ—am, welЙ—am fii yarooЙ“e"
  16,67,"E dimЙ—e tamarooji e inabuuje, hiЙ—on jogitora Й—am siwran e arsike moЖҙЖҙo. Wonii e Й—um, maande wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  16,68,"Joomi maa wahayini e Гұaakii ngii, wonnde : \"Jaggu ka pelle cuuЙ—i, e leЙ—Й—e Й—en, e kon ko Й“e saГұГұata"
  16,69,"Refti Гұaamaa e kala dimЙ—e Й—en, naaton e Й—ate Joomi mon newinaaЙ—e. Hino yalta e deedi majji [kannji Гұaaki Й—in], njaram seruЙ—am nooneeji mun, no e majjam cellal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en. Wonii e Й—um, maande wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e"
  16,70,"Alla tagii on, refti O hunnay on. Hino e mooЙ—on on rutteteeЙ—o e jaasuЙ—um nguurndam, fii wata o anndu huunde Й“aawo ganndal [makko aranal]. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, HattanЙ—o"
  16,71,Alla Й“urnii yoga mon e dow yoga ka arsike. ЖҒurnaaЙ“e Й“en wonaali ruttirooЙ“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on e Й“en Й“e jeytiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en haa Й“e fota e mayri. E ko neema Alla on Й“e yeddata
  16,72,"Alla waЙ—iranii on e wonkiiji mon Й—in resondirЙ“e, O waЙ—irani on e resondiraaЙ“e mon Й“en Й“iЙ—Й“e e taaniraaЙ“e, O arsiki on immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i. E ko meere nden Й“e gomЙ—inta? E ko neema Alla on kamЙ“e Й“e yeddata"
  16,73,"HiЙ“e rewa gaanin Makko, huunde nde waawanaa Й“e (addude) arsike ka kammuuli e ka leydi hay huunde, Й—i hattanaaka [Й—um]"
  16,74,"Wata on waЙ—an Alla yerodniraaЙ—i. Pellet, Alla ko annduЙ—o, onon on anndaa"
  16,75,"Alla piyii misal maccuЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o, mo waawaa hay huunde, e on mo Men arsiki immorde e Amen arsike moЖҙЖҙo, hara on wintoo e Й—um gunndoo e kene. Hara Й“en no fota? Yettooree woodanii Alla! Ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  16,76,"Alla piyi kadi misal worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o: goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e ko mbobo, o waawaa hay huunde, kanko ko o donngal e hoore jeyЙ—o mo on; nokku kala ka on fewtiniri mo, o addataa moЖҙЖҙere; hara on Й—on fotay e on yamiroowo nunЙ—al, hara himo e laawol focciingol"
  16,77,"Ko Alla woodani wirniiЙ—i kammmuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Fiyaaku Darngal ngal wonaali si wanaa yeru kinЖҙan yiitere maa hara ko kaГұun Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade. Pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  16,78,"Alla yaltinii on ka deedi neeniraaЙ“e mon, on anndaa huunde, O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e, belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  16,79,"E Й“e yi'aali colli Й—in ko Й—i eltaaЙ—i ka weeyo kammu (wonnde) jogitaaki Й—i si wanaa Alla? Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,80,"Alla waЙ—anii on e cuuЙ—i mon Й—in hoЙ—o, O waЙ—ani on e guri neemoraaЙ—i Й—in tillisaaji Й—i taggoton Гұalnde eggoton e Гұalnde hoЙ—toton. No e leeЙ“i (baali) Й—in, e leeЙ“i (gelooЙ—i) Й—in e leeЙ“i (dammi) Й—in ndaЙ—Й—udi [suudu] e dakmitorЙ—i haa e saanga"
  16,81,"Alla waЙ—anii on e ko O tagi kon Й—owЙ—e. O waЙ—ani on e pelle Й—en suuЙ—orЙ—e. O waЙ—ani on conci daЙ—ndayЙ—i on nguleendi, e conci daЙ—ndayЙ—i on e hare mon. Ko wano nii O timminirta neemaaji Makko Й—in e dow mon, belajo'o on jebbiloto"
  16,82,"Si Й“e huccitii, anndu ko fawi maa, ko yottingol Й“anngina"
  16,83,HiЙ“e anndi neemaaji Alla Й—in; refti Й“e yedda Й—i. Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko heeferЙ“e
  16,84,"(Janto) kadi Гұalnde Men immintinoyta e kala mofte seedeejo, refti Й“en yedduЙ“e sakkitoyantaake (ngantinagol), wanaa kamЙ“e woni ko Й—aЙ“Й“iroytee ruttitagol [e yarluyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e]"
  16,85,"Si tooГұuЙ“e Й“en yi'ii lepte Й—en, Й“e hoynantaake, lette wanaa Й“e nennitanteeЙ“e"
  16,86,"Si sirkooЙ“e Й“en yi*i kafidaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e wi'a: \"Joomi amen, ko Й—ii woni kafidaaЙ—i amen Й—i men rewaynoo gaanin Maa\". [KafidaaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e] Й—in yilta e maЙ“Й“e konngol ngol: \"Onon ko on fenooЙ“e"
  16,87,"ЖҒe werloo e Alla nden Гұalnde jebbilaare, kon ko fefindotonoo majjira Й“e"
  16,88,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e faddii e laawol Alla ngol, Men Й“eydiranii Й“e lepte e hoore lepte, sabu ko Й“e bonniraynoo kon"
  16,89,"(Janto kadi) Гұalnde Men immintinoyta e kala mofte ko seeditoo e maЙ“Й“e, jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, Men adda maa [an Muhammadu] ko seeditoo e Й“ee Й—oo. Men jippini e maaЙ—a Deftere nden, ko nde Й“annginoore kala huunde, e peewal, e yurmeende, e welo-welo wonannde juulЙ“e Й“en"
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii nunЙ—al, e moЖҙЖҙingol, e moЖҙЖҙagol e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral. Himo haЙ—a gaay e pan-kare, e ko aГұinii, e bewre. Himo waajoo on, belajo'o, on waajitoray"
  16,91,"Hunnee ahadi Alla ndin si on ahodaama, wata on firtu goondooje Й—en Й“aawo Й—e tenntineede, gomЙ—ii on waЙ—ii Alla seedaniiЙ—o [on e hunnugol ngol]. Pellet, ko annduЙ—o ko golloton"
  16,92,"Wata on wonu wa on (debbo) firtunooЙ—o mottawol mun Й“aawo doole firtude, hiЙ—on jogitora goondooje mon Й—en janfondiro hakkunde mon, nde mofte [mon Й—en] wonata Й“urde tonaade e dii mofte goo. Anndee Alla no jarribora on Й—um. Ma O Й“anngina- na on Г‘alnde Darngal, kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun"
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, O waЙ—ayno on mofte goote. Kono, Himo majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ma on lannditoye e kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  16,94,"Wata on jogitor goondooje mon janfondiro hakkunde mon, sakko koyngal [mon] mortotoo (fergito) Й“aawo ngal tabitude, meeЙ—iron bone sabu ko sakkiЙ—on kon e laawol Alla ngol. Hino woodani on lepte mawЙ—e"
  16,95,"Wata on waЙ—titir ahadi Alla ndin coggu fanЙ—ungu. Anndee ko ko woni ka Alla kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si tawno hiЙ—on anndi"
  16,96,"Ko marЙ—on kon re'ay (lanna), ko woni ka Alla kon ko heddotooЙ—um. Ma Men warjor Й“en muГұГұiiЙ“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  16,97,"Kala golluЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, Ma Men wuurnu mo nguur- ndam laaЙ“uЙ—am. Ma Men warjor Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  16,98,"Si a janngay Alqur'aana, moolor Alla seytaane raЙ—aaЙ—o on"
  16,99,"Kanko on, mbawdi(cemmbe) alanaa mo e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e fawii e hoore Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  16,100,"Anndee mbawdi makko ndin, ko hoore Й“en welduЙ“e e makko woni, e Й“en sirkirooЙ“e sabu makko"
  16,101,"Si Men lontinii Aaya lonto Aaya goo - Ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko O jippinta - ЖҒe wi'a: \"An on ko a fefindiiЙ—o\". Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  16,102,"Maaku: \"Ko jippini ndee, ko [Jibriilu] Fittaanndu LaaЙ“undu ndun, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo o tabintin Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, e [fii yo nde wonu] peewal, e welo-welo wonannde juulЙ“e Й“en"
  16,103,"GomЙ—ii Men MeЙ—en anndi wonnde hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko neЙ—Й—anke woni mo anndinnde (Alqur'aana)\". ЖҠemngal ngal Й“e ooГұotoo e mun ngal ko ajami, ndee Й—oo non ka Й—emngal Aarabu Й“anngungal"
  16,104,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaali Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Alla fewnataa Й“e. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  16,105,"Anndee ko fefindotoo fenaande, ko Й“en Й“e gomЙ—i- aa Aayee Alla Й—en; ko kamЙ“e woni fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,106,"Kala yedduЙ—o Alla Й“aawo gomЙ—inal makko ngal - si wanaa on waawnaaЙ—o hara Й“ernde makko nden ko deeЖҙirnde gomЙ—inal , kono, Й“en yaГұГұamЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun keeferaaku, hino fawii Й“e tikkere immorde Alla, hino woodani Й“e kadi lepte mawЙ—e"
  16,107,"Ngol [murtugol maЙ“Й“e], ko tawde Й“e suЙ“ike nguurndam aduna e dow laakara, e wonnde Alla kan, O fewnataa yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  16,108,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla noti e Й“erЙ—e mun, e nanЙ—e mun e gite mun. Ko Й“en woni welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  16,109,"Sikke alaaa wonnde Й“en Й—on ka laakara, ko kamЙ“e woni sooyuЙ“e Й“en"
  16,110,"Refti pellet Joomi maa, wonannde Й“en ferunooЙ“e Й“aawo nde Й“e tampinaama, hooti Й“e tiiЙ—nii Й“e muГұГұii, pellet Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, Ko O Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,111,"(Janto) tuma Гұalnde kala wonkii arata, hara hiki wennja fii hoore-makki, wonkii kala yoЙ“ee ko ki golli kon, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  16,112,"Alla piyii misal hoЙ—o: hoЙ—o hoolinoongo, deeЖҙungo; arsike maggo no ardirana ngo nokku kala e yaaj- jeende. ЖҒe yeddi neemaaji Alla Й—in, Alla meeЙ—iniri Й“e koltu heege e kulol, sabu ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon"
  16,113,"GomЙ—ii arii e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e fenni mo. Lepte Й—en nanngi Й“e, tawi ko Й“e tooГұuЙ“e"
  16,114,"Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla arsike on dagiiЙ—i laaЙ“uЙ—i, yetton neemaaji Alla Й—in, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton"
  16,115,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jiiba, e ЖҙiiЖҙam (rufaaЙ—am), e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duГұaaЙ—o [e Гұaamugol Й—um] hara wanaa Й“ewЙ—o wanaa jaggi- tuЙ—o,Anndee pellet, Allah ko Ya'fotooЙ—o HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,116,"Wata on wi'u ko Й—emЙ—e mon sifotoo e penaale: \"ЖҠum Й—oo no dagii, Й—um Й—oo no harmi\", fii no fefindoron e hoore Alla fenaande. Pellet, Й“en fefindotooЙ“e fenaande e hoore Alla, Й“e maletaake"
  16,117,"Ko dakamme fanЙ—uЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  16,118,"E hoore AlyahuudaaЙ“e Й“en (kan), Men harminno ko Men fillani maa kon ko adii. Men tooГұaano Й“e; ko woni, ko ko'e-maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonunoo e tooГұude"
  16,119,"Refti pellel, Joomi maa, wonannde Й“en huuwirЙ“e bone on majjere, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—um Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, pellet Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,120,"Pellet, Ibraahiima woniino Й—owro hoykinaniiЙ—o Alla, ooГұiiЙ—o [e Й—iya diinaaji], o wonaali jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,121,"YettaynooЙ—o nemaaji Makko Й—in. [Alla] suЙ“ike mo, O fewni mo e laawol focciingol"
  16,122,"Men okki mo ka aduna moЖҙЖҙere. Kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  16,123,"Refi Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, wonnde: \" Jokku diina Ibraahiima ka naayaaki e diinaaji mehre o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,124,"Anndee [mawningol fii] aseweere nden ko waЙ—anaa, ko Й“en luutondirЙ“e e mayre. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Гұaawoyoowo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo fii mun"
  16,125,"Noddir e diina Joomi maa kan ГұeeГұal e waaju moЖҙЖҙu. Wennjiraa Й“e e noone Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on majjuЙ—o e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri anndi feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  16,126,"Si on yagginay, haray yagginiree yeru no waЙ—iranoЙ—on non. Ko si on muГұГұike, pellet ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  16,127,MuГұГұo! MuГұal maa ngal ko sabu Alla tan. Wata a suno fii maЙ“Й“e. Wata wonu Й“ittorЙ—o e kon ko Й“e fewjata
  16,128,"Pellet, Alla no wonndi e Й“en huluЙ“e [Mo] e Й“en moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e"
  17,1,"Senayee wondanii On RoyruЙ—o JeyaaЙ—o Makko on jemma, iwde ka juulirde hormante haa ka juulirde woЙ—Й—itiinde, nden nde Men Barkini banЕӢe mun,fii yo Men Hollu mo immorde e Aayeeje Amen. Pellet, Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, YiвҖҷoowo. @Corrected"
  17,2,"Men Jonniino Muusaa Deftere nden, Men WaЙ—i nde peewal, wonannde Й“iЙ—Й“e IsraaвҖҷiila Й“en, wonnde : \"Wata on jogito gaanin Am hooloraaЙ—o"
  17,3,"[Ko onon yo] Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“en Й“e Men waЙ—Й—innoo wonndude e Nuuhu.Pellet, o laatino jeyaaЙ—o yettoowo"
  17,4,"Men wahyiniino e Й“iЙ—Й“e IsraaвҖҷiila Й“en ka Deftere [wonnde] : \"On bonnayay ka leydi laabi Й—iЙ—i, on townitoyto kadi townitaare mawnunde"
  17,5,"Si fodoore gootel e Й—in Й—iЙ—i arii, Men wurtay e mon jeyaaЙ“e Amen, marЙ“e doole tiiЙ—uЙ—e, Й“e yiiloo hakkunde galleeji Й—in. ЖҠum wonii fodoore huuwoyteende =golloteende"
  17,6,"Refti Men ruttitanani on doole Й—en e hoore maЙ“Й“e; Men ЖҒeydi on jawle e Й“iЙ—Й“e,Men WaЙ—a on gorol Й“urngol Й—uuЙ—ude"
  17,7,"Si on moЖҙЖҙinii, ko ko'e mon moЖҙЖҙinanЙ—on ; si on bonnii kadi, ko koвҖҷe mon [bonnannЙ—on]. Si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, ko fii yo Й“e hoynu geece mon Й—en, e fii yo no Й“e naatiraa ka juulirde wano Й“e naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol aranol, e fii yo Й“e muncu yeru woo ko Й“e townani muncudee"
  17,8,"Hino jortaa ka Joomi mon yurmee on.Si on fillitike (non),Men fillitoo. Men waЙ—anii yedduЙ“e Й“en Jahannama on tonngorde"
  17,9,"Pellet, ndee AlqurвҖҷaanaare no fewnay e ko Й“uri e nunЙ—ude,hinde wewlinira=weltanira gomЙ—imЙ“e,Й“en gollooЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in, wonnde, no woodani Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  17,10,"E wonnde pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara on, Men maranii Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  17,11,"NeЙ—Й—o no toroo bone, wano o tororta non moЖҙЖҙere,neЙ—Й—anke on wonii ko heГұiiЙ—o"
  17,12,"Men waЙ—ii jemma on e Гұalorma on Aayeeje Й—iЙ—i, Men monti Aaya jemma on, Men waЙ—i Aaya Гұalorma on hentiiЙ—o, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u Й“ural immorde ka Joomi mon, e fii yo on anndu limoore duuЙ“i, e hasboore. Kala huunde, Men fensitirii nde fensitudee"
  17,13,"Kala neЙ—Й—anke, Men waЙ—Й—inii mo talkuru makko ndun ka daande makko. Men yaltinanoyay mo Г‘alnde Darngal, deftere, o hawra e mayre ko nde fontaande"
  17,14,"Janngu deftere maa nden, hoore-maa yonante hannde hasboowo"
  17,15,"Mo feewii, haray pellet, ko hoore-makko o feewani ; mo majii kadi, haray pellet, ko o majji kon yantay e hoore-makko. Wonkii ronndotaako bone wokki goo. Men wonaali leptooЙ“e, haa Men immina NulaaЙ—o"
  17,16,"Si Men faandike halkude saare, Men yamiray neeminaaЙ“e mayre Й“en, Й“e faasinqinoo e mayre, konngol (lepte) ngol jojja e mayre, Men munca nde muncudee"
  17,17,"Heewii gire Й—e Men halki Й“aawo Nuuhu! Joomi maa Yonii HumpitiiЙ—o, YiвҖҷoowo junuubi=bakkatuuji jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  17,18,"On tawЙ—o no faandii yaccinaneede=yaawnaneede, Men yaccinanay mo ton huunde ko Men muuyi, wonannde on mo Men yiЙ—i, refti Men waЙ—ana mo Jahannama, o naatoya nge ko o ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o, pottinaaЙ—o [yurmeende]"
  17,19,"On faalaaЙ—o laakara, o gollani ngal golle maggal, hara kanko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o ;Й“en Й—on, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en wonii jaarnaaЙ—e"
  17,20,"Kala (maЙ“Й“e),MeЙ—en Й“eydana ; Й“ee Й—oo e Й“ee Й—oo, immorde e dokkal Joomi maa. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaali haЙ—aa ngal"
  17,21,"Ndaarii no Men Й“urniri yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga, ko laakara on Й“uri mawnude darjaaji,Й“uri mawnude kadi Й“ural"
  17,22,Wata a waЙ—idan Alla reweteeЙ—o goo ; jooЙ—oyoЙ—aa ko a ЕӢiГұaaЙ—o woppaaЙ—o
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :\"Wata on rewu ko wanaa Kanko, jibimЙ“e Й“en,moЖҙЖҙagol [e maЙ“Й“e]:si nayewu goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e yottike ma,maa Й—um Й“e Й—iЙ—o non;wata a wiвҖҷan Й“e \"bis=uf!\" wata a wikko Й“e =wota a furo,wowlan Й“e konngol teddungol"
  17,24,"YankinanoЙ—aa Й“e yurmeЙ—aa Й“e, wiвҖҷaa: В« Joomi an, yurme Й“eвҖҷe, wano Й“e neвҖҷirnoo lan non hari ko mi tosokun В»"
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no Anndi ko woni ka nder wonkiiji mon, si tawii on wonuno moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ; pellet Kanko O wonanii ruttotooЙ“e Й“en Surroowo"
  17,26,"Jonnu jom Й“adondiral haqqee makko on, e Й“illiiЙ—o, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wata a funsu funsudee"
  17,27,"Pellet funsooЙ“e Й“en, ko siЙ—Й“e seytanuuji Й—in ; seytaane non wonii yedduЙ—o Joomi mun"
  17,28,"Si a Й—urnike Й“e fii Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, nde jortiЙ—aa Й—um, wi'an Й“e konngol newiingol"
  17,29,"Wata a waЙ—u junngo maa ngon ko lmbaango, ka daande maa ; wata a fontu ngo kadi kala fontugol, haa jooЙ—oЙ—aa ko a felniiЙ—o, ninsuЙ—o"
  17,30,"Pellet Joomi maa, no yanГұana arsike, on Mo O muuyi. O Й“ittina. Pellet Kanko O wonii HumpitiiЙ—o, YiвҖҷoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko"
  17,31,"Wota on warir Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“en kulol Й“illa=baasal, ko Menen arsikata Й“e, wonndude e mon ; pellet warugol Й“e ngol, wonii goopol manngol"
  17,32,"Wota on Й“atto jeeno ngon=fijrde nde, pellet Й—un wonii pankare e laawol bonungol"
  17,33,"Wata on waru wonkii, ki Allah harmini kin [warugol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo tooГұaama waraama, Men waЙ—anii heftuЙ“e e makko Й“en doole wota non o fantin ka warugol. Pellet Kanko o wonii wallaaЙ—o"
  17,34,"Wata on Й“atto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa Й“attagol Й“urngol moЖҙЖҙude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; humnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii lannditoytee ndi"
  17,35,"Hunnee Й“etu ngun si on etay, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese feewuЙ—e, ko Й—un moЖҙЖҙi, ko kaГұun Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude battane"
  17,36,"Wata a naatu e ko a anndaa fii mun. Pellet nanЙ—e Й—en, e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“ernde nden, Й—iiЙ—oo fow wonii lannditoyteeЙ—i ka Makko"
  17,37,"Wata a yaaru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙa bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle Й—en junndi=njuuteendi"
  17,38,"Й—in fow, bone majji on wonii aГұaaЙ—un ka Joomi maa"
  17,39,"ЖҠun, ko goЙ—Й—un e ko Joomi maaЙ—a wahayini faade e maa, immorde e Г‘eeГұal wata a waЙ—u reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla, sakko werleЙ—aa ka nder jahannama ko a felaaЙ—o raЙ—aaЙ—o"
  17,40,"E hara Joomi mon suЙ“ani on Й“iЙ“Й“e worЙ“e, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ikaЙ“e Й“en rewЙ“e? Pellet, onon hiЙ—in wowlude konngol mawnungol"
  17,41,"GomЙ—ii Men fensitii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare fii yo Й“e waajitor, Й—um Й“eydaali Й“e si wonaa woЙ—Й—itagol"
  17,42,"Maaku : В« Si tawno no wonndi e makko, reweteeЙ—i wano Й“e wiвҖҷiri non awa Й—i Й—aЙ“Й“ayno laawol ummaade Jom Arsi o.\" @Corrected"
  17,43,"Senayee wonanii Mo, O Toowii gaayi e ko Й“e wi'ata Toowal Mawnungal"
  17,44,"No subunhinannde Mo kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e leydi ndin e Й“en wonuЙ“e e majji, alaa e hay e huunde si wanaa hinde Subunhinaade sabu Yettugol Mo, kono on faamataa subunhinaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, pellet, Kanko O wonii MunГұiiЙ—o Surroowo"
  17,45,Si a janngii Alqur'aanaare nden Men waЙ—ay hakkonde maa e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laahara on heedo suuЙ—iingo
  17,46,"Men waЙ—i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cokooЙ—e fii wata Й“e faamu nde [Alqur'aanaare nden] e ka noppi maЙ“Й“e kadi teddeele, si a jantike Joomi maaЙ—a ka nder Alqur'aanaare Kanko Tun Й“e huccinay Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko Й“e dogooЙ“e"
  17,47,"Ko Menen Anndi ko Й“e heЙ—otoo kon, tuma Й“e heЙ—otoo faade e maaЙ—a [yo NulaaЙ—o], e tuma Й“e sowndondirta=ndeeydata, tuma nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wi'ata: В«On jokkaali si wanaa gorko mbilЙ—aaЙ—o=bilaadoВ»"
  17,48,"Ndaarii [yo NulaaЙ—o] ko honno Й“e piyiranay maa mise=yeruuji, Й“e majjii Й“e hattantaake [heЙ“ude] laawol"
  17,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: В«E hara si men wonii Жҙi'e e mbuЙ—u, haray ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e tagu hesu?В»"
  17,50,"Maaku: [yo NulaaЙ—o] В«Wonee kaaЖҙe maa jamЙ—eВ»"
  17,51,"MaaЙ—un tagu tawayngu no mawni ka Й“erЙ—e mon, aray Й“e wi'a: 'Ko hommbo ruttata men?\" Maaku: \"Ko On TaguЙ—o on ka laawol aranol\". Aray Й“e dimmba ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en faande e maa, Й“e wi'a: \"ЖҠun ko honnde tuma\", Maaku: 'No tijjaa nde tawata Й“adike"
  17,52,"Г‘annde O noddata on nootoЙ—on yetton Mo sikkon on ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  17,53,"Maakan jeyaaЙ“e an Й“en: \"Yo Й“e wowlu nden huunde Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude, pellet, Seytaane o bonnay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, pellet, Seytaane wonanii neЙ—Й—anke gaГұo Й“annguЙ—o"
  17,54,"Joomi mon ko O AnnduЙ—o fii mon, si O yiЙ—ii O hinnoo on, maaЙ—un si O yiЙ—ii O lepta on. Men nulaali ma e dow maЙ“Й“e fawtiiЙ—o"
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa Annde fii Й“en womЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, Men Й“urnii woЙ“Й“e e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en e dow woЙ“Й“e, Men Jonni Daawuuda Jabuura"
  17,56,"Maaku: \"Noddee Й“en Й“e aaЖҙiЙ—on [ko reweteeЙ“e] gaanin Makko, Й“e maraa huncugol lorra kan gaayi mo'on wonaa waylugol kadi"
  17,57,"ЖҒen, Й“e Й“e woni noddude, hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ude Й—oworgal faade e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri Й“adaade, hiЙ“e jortii Hinnayee Makko on hiЙ“e huli lepte Makko Й—en, pellet, lepte Joomi maa Й—en Й—e laatike ko rentaaЙ—e"
  17,58,"Alaa e saare si wanaa Menen ko Men halkayЙ“e nde ko adii Гұalde darngal, maa ko Men leptayЙ“e nde lepte sattuЙ—e, Й—un Й—on wonii ko winndaa Й—un ka Deftere"
  17,59,"HaЙ—aali Men nde Men nula Aayeeje Й—en, si wanaa sabu fenniino Й—e adiiЙ“e Й“en, Men okki Samuuda Naaqaawa mban yi'teemba Й“e tooГұi mba, Men nuliraali Aayeeje Й—en si wonaa hulЙ“inirЙ—e"
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde Men wi'anno maa: \"Pellet, Joomi maa O huЙ“indike yimЙ“e Й“en, Men waЙ—iraali nden yi'annde nde Men hollumaa si wanaa fitina wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en e lekki huЙ—aaki ki ka Alqur'aana, MeЙ—en hulЙ“ina Й“e kono Й“eydataa Й“e si wanaa bewre mawnde"
  17,61,"Nde Men Daalannoo Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en sujjanee Aadama, Й“e sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o wi'i: \"Hara mi sujjanay on mo taguЖҠaa e loopal"
  17,62,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii oo mo teddinЖҠaa e dow an, pellet, si A nennanii lan haa Гұalde darngal mi bonnay Й“iЙ“Й“e makko Й“en si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e"
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: \"Yahu, kala jokkuЙ—o ma e maЙ“Й“e pellet, ko jahannama woni njoddi mon, njoddi yonoori"
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo hattanaЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e hito maa ngon, pooЙ—u e dow maЙ“Й“e pucci maa e seppooЙ“e maa, ka fidu e maЙ“Й“e ka jawle e ka Й“iЙ“Й“e foduЙ“e, [kono] Seytaane fodaali Й“e si wanaa hodo"
  17,65,"Pellet, JeyaaЙ“e An Й“en a maraa doole e hoore maЙ“Й“e, Joomi maa yonii HooloraaЙ—o"
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganayЙ—o on laaЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u immorde e Й“ural Makko ngal, pellet, Kanko ko O YurmeteeЙ—o on"
  17,67,"Si lorra kan heЙ“ii on ka maayo, majjay Й“en Й“e noddayno Й—on, si wonaa Kanko [Alla] nde O danndi on ka njorndi Й—urnoЙ—on, neЙ—Й—anke on wonii te o seeraani wonde heewuЙ—o yeddugol"
  17,68,"Enee, on hooli O mutintaa on ka banЕӢe njorndi maaЙ—un O nula e mon damagariire [toЙ“o koccu], refti hara heЙ“antaake on fawtiiЙ—o"
  17,69,"Kaa on hooli O ruttaraa on e maggo laawol goo O accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli O yoolira on sabu ko yeddunoЙ—on kon, refti on heЙ“antaake jokkitirayЙ—o e dow amen cukkoowo"
  17,70,"GomЙ—ii, Men teddinii Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama Й“en, Men ronndike Й“e ka njorndi e ka maayo Men arsiki Й“e immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i Men Й“urni Й“e e dow ko heewi e Й“en Й“e Men tagi Й“urnudee"
  17,71,"Г‘annde Men noddiroyta kala yimЙ“e yeesoojo maЙ“Й“e on,kala on jonnitiroyaaЙ—o deftere makko nden ka Гұaamo makko Й“en Й—on Й“e janngay deftere maЙ“Й“e nden Й“e tooГұirtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro"
  17,72,"Kala on wonuЙ—o e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bunЙ—o, haray kanko, ko ka laahara o Й“urata wumude e majjude laawol"
  17,73,"Fii kala Й“e eЙ“Й“ii nde Й“e fitinaymaa gaayi nden huunde nde Men wahayini e maaЙ—a fii yo a fefindo e Amen ko wonaa Й—un [ko Men tellini e maa] ontuma Й“e jogitoto ma sehlaajo"
  17,74,"Si tawiino Men tabintinaanoma, gomЙ—ii hari a do'ii ooГұaade e maЙ“Й“e huunde seeЙ—aare"
  17,75,"Ontuma Men meeЙ—inteno cowale [lepte] ka ngurndan e cowale [lepte] ka mayde refti heЙ“antaake ma ballo e hoore Amen"
  17,76,"Fii kala Й“e eЙ“Й“iino dillinngol ma ka leydi fii yo Й“e yaltine e mayri, ontuma Й“e ГұiiЙ“ataano Й“atte maa si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  17,77,"ЖҠun ko Sunna Й“en Й“e Men nuli ko adimaa immorde e NulaaЙ“e Amen, a heЙ“antaa Sunna Amen on mbattiigu"
  17,78,"Г‘innu julde nden ka mortagol naange ngen haa ka niwre jemma, Julde subaha nden, pellet, Julde subaha nden wonii seedeteende"
  17,79,"Ka jemma tinno e makko ko Й“eydaari maaЙ—a, no jortaa nde Joomi maaЙ—a immintinay maa e darorde yettiniinde"
  17,80,"Maaku: \"Jooma, naadiran naatirgal goonga yaltiniraa mi yaltirgal goonga, waЙ—anaa mi immorde ka MaaЙ—a doole ballal"
  17,81,"Maaku: \"goonga kan arii meere nden fuuyii, pellet, meere nden wonii fuuyoore"
  17,82,"MeЙ—en tellina ka Alqur'aana huunde nde konde cellal e yurmeende wonnande gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Й“eydataa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en si wanaa hayrere"
  17,83,"Si Men neeminii e neЙ—Й—anke on o Й—uurnoo o townaa balaaje makko, si bone heЙ“ii mo o wona hattuЙ—o e taЖҙiiЙ—o"
  17,84,"Maaku: \"Mo kala yo gollu e laawol mun, ko Joomi mon woni AnnduЙ—o on Й“urЙ—o feewude laawol"
  17,85,"HiЙ“e lanndo maa fii fittaandu, maaku: \"Fittaandu ndun ko e fiyaake Joomi an, on okkaaka e ganndal si wanaa seeЙ—aГ©"
  17,86,"Mi woondii, si MeЙ—en yiЙ—unoo Men naЙ“ayno nden huunde nde Men wahyini faade e MaaЙ—a, refti heЙ“antaake ma fawtiiЙ—o Й—un e hoore Amen"
  17,87,"Ko woni tun, ko Hinnayee immorde ka Joomi maa, pellet, Й“ural Makko ngal e dow maa wonii mawnungal"
  17,88,"Maaku: \"Mi woondii, si yimЙ“e Й“en e jinnaaji Й—in hawtitii fii yo Й“e addu yeru ndee Alqur'aanaare, Й“e addataa yeru mayre, hay si wonii woЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e ko wallindrayЙ“e e woЙ“Й“e"
  17,89,"GomЙ—ii Men Й“annginanii yimЙ“e Й“en e ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en salii, si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,90,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—intaa ma, haa Й“ullitanaa men ka leydi Й“unndu"
  17,91,MaaЙ—un laatano maa ngesa immorde e tamorooje e inabuuje Й“ullitaa canЙ—i Й—in hakkunde majje Й“ullitugol
  17,92,"MaaЙ—un liЙ“aa kammu ngun e hoore amen wano aaЖҙorЙ—aa non kunte, maaЙ—un addaa Alla e Maalaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en [men] tiindondira"
  17,93,"MaaЙ—un laatano maa suudu immorde e cuЙ—aaje [kanЕӢe], maaЙ—un Жҙawaa ka kammu, men gomЙ—intaa Жҙawugol maaЙ—a ngol haa jippinaa e amen deftere men jannga nde. Maaku: \"Senaade Jom an, hara mi wonu, ko wonaa Й“anndinke NulaaЙ—o"
  17,94,"HaЙ—aali yimЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e gomЙ—inta tuma nde peewalngal arunoo Й“e, si wanaa fii Й“e wi'ii: \"E hara Alla nulay Й“anndinke NulaaЙ—o"
  17,95,"Maaku: \"Si tawiino laatinoke ka leydi Malaa'ikaaЙ“e hiЙ“e yaha ko Й“e deewuЙ“e, Men jippinayno e maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu Malaa'ikaajo NulaaЙ—o"
  17,96,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii SeediiЙ—o hakkunde an e mon, pellet Kanko O wonii HumpitiiЙ—o ReenuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  17,97,"On mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewuЙ—o, Й“e O majjini Й“en a heЙ“antaaЙ“e wallooЙ“e ko woori Mo. Men mooЙ“ay Й“e Гұalde darngal e dow geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko Й“e wumuЙ“e e mbobiЙ—u= fahdube Й“e e faaЙ—uЙ“e, werde maЙ“Й“e nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci Men Й“eydana Й“e huЙ“Й“unge"
  17,98,"ЖҠun ko njoddi maЙ“Й“e, sabu kamЙ“e Й“e yeddii Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"E hay si men wonii Жҙi'e e mbuЙ—u e hara menen ko men immintinteeЙ“e tagu hesu"
  17,99,"Enee, Й“ee yi'aali, wonnde Alla On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ko O HattanЙ—o nde O tagata yeru maЙ“Й“e, O waЙ—ani Й“e lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en salii si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,100,"Maaku: \"Sinndo onon hiЙ—on marunoo ngaluuji Hinnayee Joomi an on, ontuma, on jogitotono kulol nafkugol, neЙ—Й—anke on wonii nguddo"
  17,101,"GomЙ—ii Men okkiino Muusaa Aayeeje jeenay Й“annguЙ—e, lanndii Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en tuma nde o arunoo Й“e Fir'awna wi'ani mo: \"Min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbilЙ—aaЙ—o"
  17,102,"Maaku: \"GoЙ—ii hiЙ—a anndi jippinaali Й—ee si wanaa JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin Aayeeje [yi'eteeЙ—i]. Min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a halkiiЙ—o"
  17,103,O faalaa nde o dillinta Й“e ka leydi Men yooli mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“e denndaangal
  17,104,"Men Daalani Й“aawo makko Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en: \"HoЙ—ee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, Men adday on ko on muuЙ“iiЙ“e=fiiliibe"
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga Men telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Men nuliraali ma si wanaa [ko a] wewlinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo"
  17,106,"E Qur'aanaare Men Й“anngini nde fii yo a janngannde yimЙ“e Й“en e dow deeЖҙere, Men jippini nde jipinnde"
  17,107,"Maaku: \"GomЙ—inee nde, maaЙ—un wata on gomЙ—in, pellet, Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal ko adii nde si [nde] janngaama e taweende maЙ“Й“e Й“e suuyiray wokkuЙ—e ko Й“e sujjooЙ“e"
  17,108,"ЖҒe wi'a:Senaade woodanii Joomi amen,nde wonnoo Fodoore Joomi amen nden ko waЙ—oore"
  17,109,"HiЙ“e suuyira wokkuЙ—e Й“e wulla [Alqur'aana on] Й“ayda Й“e yankinaare"
  17,110,"Maaku: \"Noddiree Mo Alla maa noddiro Mo Hinnorante, kala no noddirЙ—on Mo, ko Kanko InЙ—e MoЖҙЖҙe Й—en heeranii, wata a fenГұin julde maaЙ—a nden wata a suudu nde Й—aЙ“Й“u hakkunde Й—un laawol"
  17,111,"Maaku: Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Mo jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o laatanaaki Mo kafidaaЙ—o e Laamu laatanaaki Mo tedduЙ—o mo O huykinantoo, Mawnin Mo Mawninndee"
  18,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On TippinЙ—o e dow JeyaaЙ—o Makko on Deftere nden O waЙ—anaali nde ooГұaare"
  18,2,"Feewunde fii yo o [NulaaЙ—o on] hulЙ“inir lepte sattuЙ—e immorde ka Makko o weltinira gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Й“en Й“e no golla MoЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in wonnde no woodani Й“e Njoddi MoЖҙЖҙiri"
  18,3,"Ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e e nder makko [Neema on] poomaa"
  18,4,"O rentina Й“en wi\"uЙ“e: \"Alla jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaaЙ“e e mun, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e woodani, mawnii konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunnduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wowlaali si wanaa fenaande"
  18,6,"Bala jo'o an a tanpinay hoore-maa e dow batteeji maЙ“Й“e, si gomЙ—inaali ndee Yewtere ka suno"
  18,7,"Menen Men waЙ—ii ko woni kon ka hoore leydi cuЙ—aari mayri, fii yo Men jarribo Й“e ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urata moЖҙЖҙinnde golle"
  18,8,Menen ko Men waЙ—ooЙ“e ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yimЙ“e fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi Й—in, Й—un wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawniiЙ—e"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaaЙ“e Й“en sorunoo ka fammeere, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka MaaЙ—a Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka nder fammeere limoore duuЙ“i
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini Й“e fii yo Men fenГұinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle Й—en Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moftude [limoore] ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“i kon dummunne"
  18,13,"Menen MeЙ—en fillanaade ma kumpital fii maЙ“Й“e e Goonga, Й“en Й—on, ko sukaaЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e Men Й“eydani Й“e Peewal"
  18,14,"Men haЙ“Й“i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Й“e darinoo, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko JeyЙ—o On kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo reweteeЙ—o, gomЙ—ii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"ЖҒee yimЙ“e amen, Й“e jogitike ko woori Mo reweteeЙ—i, ko haaanunoo ko yo Й“e addu e dow maЙ“Й“e dalil Й“annguЙ—o. Ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұude ko foti e on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande o fawi e Alla"
  18,16,"Tuma nde woЙ—Й—itinoЙ—on Й“e e ko Й“e rewata kon ko woori Alla, Й“e soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"
  18,17,"HiЙ—a yi'a naangi ngen si nge Жҙellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere maЙ“Й“e senngo Гұaamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay Й“e ka senngo nano, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e yaajeende e Й—un, Й—un ko jeyaaЙ—un e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewuЙ—o, kala moO majjini a heЙ“antaa mo hettuЙ—o fewnoowo. @Corrected"
  18,18,"HiЙ—a sikka Й“e ko Й“e finuЙ“e, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—aaniiЙ“e, MeЙ—en waylitira Й“e senngo Гұaamo e senngo nano, rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun no fonti kayЙ—e mun Й—en ka dammbugal, si a Жҙellitike e maЙ“Й“e a huccitayno e maЙ“Й“e dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e maЙ“Й“e"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri Й“e fii yo Й“e lanndondir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e maЙ“Й“e: \"No foti hewde ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maa goЙ—Й—un e Гұallal.\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni AnnduЙ—o emmbere ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on, nulee goЙ—Й—o e mon wonndude e Й—ii kaaki=ceede mon Й—oo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri laaЙ“ude Гұaamitee, yo o addan on Гұaametee immorde e on Й—on, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kamЙ“e si Й“e Жҙellitike e mon Й“e rajmay on, maaЙ—un Й“e rutta on e laawol maЙ“Й“e ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii maЙ“Й“e, fii yo Й“e anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde Й“e pooЙ—ondiraynoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e fiyaake maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore maЙ“Й“e maadi, ko Joomi maЙ“Й“e woni AnnduЙ—o fii MaЙ“Й“e.\" ЖҒen fooluЙ“e e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow maЙ“Й“e Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray Й“e wi'a: \"Ko Й“e tato nayaЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun.\" ЖҒe wi'a kadi: \"Ko Й“e njowo njeegaЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun ko fampaangol ka niЙ“e.\" ЖҒe wi'a kadi: \"Ko Й“e njeeЙ—iЙ—o njeetataЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni AnnduЙ—o limoore maЙ“Й“e, anndaa Й“e si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e.\" Wata a wennju fii maЙ“Й“e si wanaa yewtere feeГұunde, wata a lanndo fii maЙ“Й“e hay e gooto e maЙ“Й“e"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi waЙ—ay Й—un janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maaЙ—a si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko Й“uri Й“adaade immorde e Й—un Peewal"
  18,25,"ЖҒe ГұiiЙ“i ka fammeere maЙ“Й“e duuЙ“i teemeЙ—Й—e tati, Й“e Й“eydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni AnnduЙ—o emmbere ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“i, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa Й“e gaanin Makko giЙ—o, O kafidaa ka Г‘aawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko Й—in, a heЙ“ataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maaЙ—a kin wonndude e Й“en noddooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e ka bimmbi e ka kiikiiЙ—e hiЙ“e faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa Й—e yawtu gaayi maЙ“Й“e hara hiЙ—a faandii cuЙ—aari ngurdan aduna, wota a Й—ofto on mo Men welsindini Й“ernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki beleeЙ—e makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gomЙ—in mono faalaa yo o yeddu, Menen Men heblanii tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Yiite no hunnditi Й“e Й—enЙ—e magge Й—en si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ii faabo, Й“e faaboree ndiyan wa'uЙ—an wa sila taynaaЙ—o Й—an juЙ—a geece Й—en, bonii njaram bonii werde"
  18,30,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o golle"
  18,31,"ЖҒen Й—on no woodani Й“e Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al canЙ—i no ila ley maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e cuЙ—iree ton immorde e jawe kanЕӢe Й“e Й“ornoo conci haakiЙ—uЙ—i Й—ewluЙ—i e jalbuЙ—i ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, moЖҙЖҙii mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙii kadi fowtorde"
  18,32,"fiyan Й“e misal,worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Men waЙ—ani goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e gese Й—iЙ—i inab Menhunndintini =hurliride Й—e tamarooje Men waЙ—i hakkunde majje remuru"
  18,33,"ЖҠen gese Й—iЙ—i kala addi Гұaametee majje, Й—e tooГұaali hay e huunde e Й—un, Men seeki hakkunde majje [gese Й—en Й—iЙ—i] caangol"
  18,34,"Wonani mo dimЙ—e, o wi'ani wonndiiЙ—o makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Min miЙ—o Й“urumaa jawdi e teddude gorol"
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o tooГұuЙ—o hoore-makko, o wi'i: \"Mi sikkaa mbaa re'ay poomaa\". @Corrected"
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa kdai Darngal ngal daroto, mi woondii si mi artira le ka Joomi an, maa mi tawu sanne, waylitorde Й“urnde mba moЖҙЖҙude"
  18,37,"WonndiiЙ—o makko on wi'ani mo, tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Enee, a yeddii On TaguЙ—o ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] refti O fonndumaa gorko"
  18,38,"Kono min ko Kanko Alla woni Joomi an, mi kafidataa e Joomi an hay gooto"
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatuЙ—aa ka ngesa maaЙ—a wi'aa: \"Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alaa si wanaa Alla\". Si a yi'ii lan, min miЙ—o Й“urumaa fanЙ—ude jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e"
  18,40,No jortaa nde Joomi an okkoyta lan moЖҙЖҙere Й“urnde ngesa maa mban O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu mba wonta boowal Й“owrungal
  18,41,"MaaЙ—un ndiyan mabba Й—an wonta Й“eeЙ“uЙ—an, hara a hattantaake Й—aЙ“Й“ugol Й—an"
  18,42,"DimЙ—e makko Й—en bonnaa o weeti himo waylita newe makko Й—en e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiimba e daЖҙЖҙe mabba, himo wi'a: \"Ee jalla min, hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo gaanin Alla, o wonaali fooluЙ—o"
  18,44,No ton Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko Kanngo moЖҙЖҙi mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙi battane
  18,45,"Fiyan Й“e misal ngurdan aduna Й—an no wa'i wa ndiyan Men jippiniЙ—an immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjan puЙ—i leydi ndin, Й—i wonti munciiЙ—i keneeli no jarooЙ—i, Alla wonii ko O HattanЙ—o e dow kala huunde"
  18,46,"Jawdi ndin e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“en ko cuЙ—aari ngurndan aduna, moЖҙЖҙi heddotooЙ—i Й—in ko Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a e moЖҙЖҙude yela"
  18,47,"Г‘annde Men naЙ“ata pelle Й—en a yi'ay leydi ndin ko feeГұundi, Men mooЙ“a Й“e Men accataa immorde e maЙ“Й“e hay e gooto"
  18,48,"ЖҒe holliree ka Joomi maa [ko Й“e] saffewol, [O Daalana Й“e] gomЙ—ii on arii e Amen wano Men tagirnoo on non, ka laawol aranol, ko woni on aaЖҙino wonnde Men waЙ—anaali on fodoore"
  18,49,"Deftere nden wallinee, a yi'ay bomЙ“e Й“en ko hulЙ“e ko woni kon e mayre, Й“e wi'a: \"Ee bone amen, ko heЙ“i ndee deftere nde Й—alataa tosokun wanaa njanun si wanaa nde moftii Й—un, Й“e tawa ko Й“e golli kon no weeЙ“itaa, Joomi maaЙ—a tooГұataa hay e gooto"
  18,50,"Tuma nde Men wi'annoo Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en: \"Sujjanee Aadama, Й“e sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaaЙ—o e jinnaaji Й—in o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“en yimЙ“e gaanin An, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e ayЙ“e mo'on, bonanii tooГұooЙ“e Й“en battudi"
  18,51,"Mi tawnaali Й“e tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin wanaa tagugol ko'e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Mi wonaali jogitotooЙ—o majjinooЙ“e Й“en sembinooЙ“e. @Corrected"
  18,52,"E Гұannde O Daalata: \"Noddee kafidaaЙ“e An Й“en, Й“en Й“e aaЖҙiЙ—on, Й“e nodda Й“e, Й“e jaabotaako Й“e Men waЙ—i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e halkorde"
  18,53,"BomЙ“e Й“en yi'a Yiite ngen Й“e fellita wonnde kamЙ“e ko Й“e ukketeeЙ“e e magge, Й“e heЙ“ataa gaayi magge yiltorde"
  18,54,"GomЙ—ii Men fensitanii yimЙ“e Й“en e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, neЙ—Й—anke on wonii himo Й“uri kala huunde wennjugol"
  18,55,"HaЙ—aali yimЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e gomЙ—inta Й“e insinanoo Joomi maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Peewal ngal arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa nde arata e maЙ“Й“e sunna aranЙ“e Й“en maaЙ—un nde arata e maЙ“Й“e lepte Й—en ko Й—e feeГұuЙ—e"
  18,56,"Men Nuliraali NulaaЙ“e Й“en si wanaa ko weltinooЙ“e e jertinooЙ“e, Й“en heeferЙ“e hiЙ“e wennjana meere nden fii yo Й“e fuynir nde Goonga kan, Й“e jogitii Aayeeje An Й—en e ko Й“e jertiniraa kon jalnori"
  18,57,"Alaa fotayЙ—o tooГұude on waajuraaЙ—o Aayeeje Joomi makko o Й—uurii=fali e gaayi majje o yejjiti ko juuЙ—e makko Й—en ardini kon. Menen Men waЙ—ii e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cokooЙ—e fii wota Й“e faamu nde, ka noppi maЙ“Й“e kadi pahu, hay si a noddii Й“e faade e Peewal Й“e feewataa ontuma haapoomaa"
  18,58,"Ko Joomi mon woni Surroowo ko O Jom Hinnayee on, sinndo O nangitirno Й“e ko Й“e faggitii kon O yaccinanayno Й“e lepte Й—en, ko woni, no woodani Й“e fodoore Й“e heЙ“ataa gaanin mayre fattorde"
  18,59,"ЖҠen ca'e, Men halkuno Й“e tuma nde Й“e tooГұunoo Men waЙ—ani halkeede maЙ“Й“e nden Fodoore"
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagataa makko on: \"Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i, maaЙ—un mi wuloo jamaanu"
  18,61,"Tuma nde Й“e yottoyinoo hakkonde majje Й“e yejjiti linngil maЙ“Й“e ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo wuddere"
  18,62,"Nde Й“e lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: \"Anndanii en sojjaari=bottaari men ndin, gomЙ—ii en hawrii e nduu yaadu men Й—oo tampere"
  18,63,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii, nde sorunoЙ—en ka fetere, min mi yejjuno linngil ngil, yejjintinaali lan fii maggil si wanaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo no hawnori"
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko Й—on ko wonЙ—en Й—aЙ“Й“ude kon [woni], Й“e ruttii e Й“atteeji maЙ“Й“e fillitagol"
  18,65,"ЖҒe tawoyi jeyaaЙ—o immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Men Okki mo Hinnayee immorde ka Amen, Men Anndini mo immorde e Amen Ganndal"
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: \"Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinan goЙ—Й—un e ko anndinaЙ—aa kon Peewal"
  18,67,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Pellet, an a hattantaake muГұal wonndugol e an"
  18,68,Ko honno munГұuretaa e dow kon ko a huЙ“indoraa Й—un ganndal
  18,69,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"A taway lan si Alla Muuyi ko mi munГұiiЙ—o, mi yeddataa yamiroore maa"
  18,70,"O maaki: \"Si a jokkay lam wata a lanndo lan gaayi huunde haa mi yeewte immorde e mayre janta"
  18,71,"ЖҒe yahi haa nde Й“e waЙ—Й—inoo ka laana o yulika, [Muusaa] maaki: \"A yulii ka fii yo ka yoolu yimЙ“e makka?! gomЙ—ii a addii huunde mawnde"
  18,72,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake muГұal wonndugol e am"
  18,73,"[Muusaa] maaki: wata a jogoran ko mi yijjiti kon, wata a hewtinan e fiyaake an on satteende"
  18,74,"ЖҒe yahi haa nde Й“e fottunoo e suka o wari mo! O maakani [mo]: \"E a waru wonkii laaЙ“uki tanaa [yoЙ“tanagol] wonkii, gomЙ—ii a addii huunde aГұiinde"
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake muГұal wonndugol e an"
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Si mi lanndike ma gaayi huunde Й“aawo Й—ii, haray wata a wonndino e an, gomЙ—ii a timminii nganto e an"
  18,77,"ЖҒe yahi haa Й“e yaltiti e yimЙ“e saare, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iri Й“e Гұaametee Й“e salii wernude Й“e, Й“e tawi e nder mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: \"Sinno a yiЙ—uno a Жҙettayno njoddi e Й—un"
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Ko Й—um woni seedigal hakku- nde an e ma'a, aray mi yiito maa firo kon ko a hattananooka munГұaade e dow mun"
  18,79,"Si ko laana kan, ka laatanike miskineeЙ“e gollo- Й“e ka maayo, mi faalaa aybinnde ka, hari laatike Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lamЙ—o himo nannga kala laana o jaЙ“ta"
  18,80,"Si ko suka on mawЙ“e makko Й“en wonii gomЙ—imЙ“e , men huli wata o fawu Й“e bewre e keeferaaku"
  18,81,Men faalaa nde Joomi maЙ“Й“e waЙ—titanta Й“e Й“urЙ—o mo moЖҙЖҙude laaЙ“uЙ—o e Й“urЙ—o Й“attaade yurmeende
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o wonЙ—uЙ“e ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, hari baaba maЙ“Й“e laatinoke moЖҙЖҙo, Joomi maaЙ—a Faalaa nde Й“e yottotoo sagatalaaku maЙ“Й“e, O yaltina ngalu maЙ“Й“e ngun [Й—um] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi waЙ—iraali Й—um e yamirooree an, Й—um ko firo kon ko a hattanaali munГұaade e dow mun"
  18,83,"HiЙ“e fa'umaa lanndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: \"Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e Й—un janta"
  18,84,"Menen, Men weeЙ“inanno mo ka leydi, Men Okki mo immorde e kala huunde sabu"
  18,85,O jokki sabu
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde naange ngen o tawi hinge muta e loope Й“aleeje, o tawi ton yimЙ“e : Men wi'i: \"Ko an yo jom galaaЙ—i Й—iЙ—i, ko si a leptay maaЙ—un si a jogitoto e maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi"
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on tooГұuЙ—o aray men lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko O lepta mo lepte aГұiiЙ—e"
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gomЙ—inЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi no woodani mo njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙiri ndin, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen on neweende"
  18,89,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,90,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka Жҙellitorde naange ngen, o tawi hinge Жҙellitoo e dow yimЙ“e, Men waЙ—anaali Й“e gaanin magge heedo"
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gomЙ—ii Men huЙ“indike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal. @Corrected"
  18,92,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,93,Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji Й—in Й—iЙ—io tawi gaanin majji yimЙ“e Й“e Й—eЙ“ataa faamude konngol
  18,94,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnooЙ“e ka leydi. Enee, men waЙ—ante ngeenaari fii yo a waЙ—u hakkunde amen e maЙ“Й“e heedo"
  18,95,"O wi'i: \"Ko Joomi am weeЙ“inani lan kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, walliree lan doole mi waЙ—a hakkunde mo'on e maЙ“Й“e heedo"
  18,96,"Addanee lam kunte njamЙ—e haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde naЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i, o wi'i: \"Wifee haa nde o waЙ—unoo Й—um yiite, o wi'i: addanee lam sila mi wancina e dow mun"
  18,97,"ЖҒe hattantaake Жҙellitagol ndi, Й“e hattantaake kadi yulugol ndi"
  18,98,"O wi'i: Й—um Й—oo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii O waЙ—ay [heedo] ngon Й—iggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nden laatike ko nde Goonga"
  18,99,"Men Й—ala yoga e maЙ“Й“e nden Гұalnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Men mooЙ“a Й“e mooЙ“udee"
  18,100,Men weeЙ“itanay(holliray) Jahannama nden Гұannde yedduЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itugol=holllirgol
  18,101,"ЖҒen Й“e gite mun laatii e wirngallo gaayi janta An, Й“e laatiЙ“e hattantaake nanugol"
  18,102,"Enee, Й“en yedduЙ“e sikku Й“e jogoto jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en gaanin Am, Menen Men heblanii Jahannama on fii yedduЙ“eЙ“en wona werde. @Corrected"
  18,103,"Maaku: \"Taw si men hupitay on fii Й“urЙ“e hayrude(pertude) golle"
  18,104,Ko Й“en Й“e golle mun yeebii ka ngurdan aduna hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sikka hiЙ“e moЖҙЖҙinnde golle
  18,105,"Ko Й“en woni yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en e hawroygol e Makko, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bone Men ГұiiЙ“inantaaЙ“e Г‘alnde Darngal ЖҒetu"
  18,106,"Jahannama ko Й—un woni njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e, sabu ko Й“e yeddi kon Й“e jogitii Aayeeje Am Й—en e NulaaЙ“e Am Й“en jalkitde"
  18,107,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in laatanto Й“e Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)"
  18,108,"Ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ataa gaayi makko waylitorde"
  18,109,"Maaku: \"Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndawa fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am Й—in, maayo ngon re'ayno ko adii nde re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am Й—in, sinno Men addii yeru maggo e Й“eydude"
  18,110,"Maaku: \"Pellet min, ko mi Й“anndinnke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto, kala jortiiЙ—o hawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle moЖҙЖҙe wata o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"
  19,1,Kaaf Haa Yaa ayiin saad
  19,2,JaЕӢta Yurmeende Joomi maaЙ—a jeyaaЙ—o Makko on Jakariyaa
  19,3,Tuma nde O noddunoo Joom makko noddaannu suuЙ—iindu
  19,4,"O maaki: \"Jooma, min dey Жҙi'e Й—en lo'ii e am hoore nden lewndii puri, mi laataaki non Й—awaaЙ—o ka toragol Ma Jooma"
  19,5,"Min dey mi hulii lontotooЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo am, suddiiЙ—o am on laatike dimaro okkam immorde ka MaaЙ—a Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  19,6,"O rona lam, o rona kadi e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nden waЙ—aa mo Joomi weltoraaЙ—o"
  19,7,Ko an yo Jakariyaa Menen Men weltinirii ma suka innde makko ko Yahyaa Men waЙ—anaali mo ko adii tokoraajo
  19,8,"O maaki: \"Jooma ko honno laatoranta lam suka sonnaajo am on laatike dimaro min kadi mi yottike e nayewu yooruЙ—o tere"
  19,9,"[Malaa'ikaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: ЖҠum no neewii e Am gomЙ—ii Mi Tagiino ma ko adii, hari a laataaki huunde"
  19,10,"O maaki: \"Jooma waЙ—anam Maande\". O Daali: \"Maande maaЙ—a nden ko wata a wowlidu e yimЙ“e Й“en jemmaaji tati fotondirЙ—i"
  19,11,"O yalti hakkunde yimЙ“e makko Й“en immorde ka ganngunal o joopii faande e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um woni subunhinee bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  19,12,"Ko an yo Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, Men Okki mo Г‘eeГұal ko o suka"
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka Amen ko o laaЙ“uЙ—o o laatike huloowo [Alla]"
  19,14,Ko o Й—igganЙ—o jibimЙ“e mo Й“en o wanaali ndunndarankeejo ngeddo
  19,15,Kisiyee e makko Гұalnde o jibinaa e Гұalnde o maayata e Г‘alnde o immintintee ko o wuuruЙ—o
  19,16,"JaЕӢto ka Deftere Mariyama tuma nde o woЙ—Й—itinoo immorde e yimЙ“e makko Й“en [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyankoore"
  19,17,"O jogitii gaanin maЙ“Й“e wirngallo, Men Nuli e makko Ruuhu Amen o nanndintinanii mo e Й“anndinke fotondirЙ—o"
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii YurmeteeЙ—o On immorde e maaЙ—a si tawii a laatike ko a kulo [Alla]"
  19,19,"O wi'i: \"Pellet, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Joomi maaЙ—a fii yo mi okke suka laaЙ“uЙ—o"
  19,20,"O wi'i: \"Ko honno laatoranta lam suka hara Й“anndinke meemaali lam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"
  19,21,"O wi'i: \"ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: \"ЖҠum no newii e Am e fii yo Men waЙ—u mo Maande fii yimЙ“e Й“en e Yurmeende immornde e Amen Й—um laatike fiyaake Г‘aawaaЙ—o"
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure woЙ—Й—itiinde"
  19,23,"ЕҠata(qatwere) on fiЙ—i mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: \"Ee hara nun mi maayuno ko adii Й—um mi laatoo huunde yejjitaande"
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wata a suno gomЙ—ii Joomi maaЙ—a waЙ—ii ley maaЙ—a caangol"
  19,25,YeЖҙu(dimmbu) faade e maaЙ—a jullere tamarohi kin nde liЙ“a e maaЙ—a Й“ennduЙ—e teЙ“eteeЙ—e
  19,26,"Г‘aamu yaraa Й“uЙ“Й“inaa gite, si a yi'ii goЙ—Й—o immorde e Й“anndinke wi'u: \"Min dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotooЙ—o korka mi wowlidata e neЙ—Й—anke hannde)"
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yimЙ“e makko, himo tammbii mo Й“e wi'i: \"Ko an yo Mariyama gomЙ—ii a addii huunde hawnii nde"
  19,28,Ko an yo banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki neЙ—Й—o bonЙ—o neene maaЙ—a kadi laataaki jeenoowo=jinoowo
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, Й“e wi'i:\"Ko honno men yewtirta e on sanfaajo wonЙ—o e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu"
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: \"Min dey ko mi jeyaaЙ—o Alla O Okkii lam Deftere nden O WaЙ—ii lam Annabaajo"
  19,31,"O WaЙ—i lam BarkinaaЙ—o nokku kala ka mi woni, O Wasiyii lam Julde nden e Jakka on fodde miЙ—o wuuri"
  19,32,"Ko mi Й—igganЙ—o yumma am, O waЙ—aali lam ndunndarankeejo malkisaaЙ—o"
  19,33,Kisiyee on wonii e am Гұalnde mi jibinaa e Гұal- nde mi maayata e Г‘alnde mi immintintee ko mi wuuruЙ—o
  19,34,On ko Iisaa geЙ—al Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol hiЙ“e sikkitoo fii mu'un
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde O jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o Senayee wonanii Mo, si O Г‘aawii fiyaake O Daalanay mo tun: \"Wonu\" o wona"
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, Rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni Laawol Focciingol"
  19,37,"Feddeeji Й—in luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii Й“en yedduЙ“e seedagol Г‘alaande Mawnde"
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Й“e aroyta e Amen, kono tooГұooЙ“e Й“en hannde hiЙ“e e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  19,39,"HulЙ“inir Й“e Г‘alnde Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on Гұaawaa hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder welsindaare hara Й“e gomЙ—inaa"
  19,40,"Menen Men ronay leydi ndin e Й“en wonuЙ“e e dow mayri, ko ka Amen Й“e ruttetee"
  19,41,"JaЕӢto ka Deftere Ibraahiima, pellet, kanko o laatino GoonguЙ—o Annabaajo"
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo bem makko: \"Ko an yo baaba ko honЙ—un rewantaa kon ko nanataa yi'ataa hara duncantaa ma hay e huunde"
  19,43,"Ko an yo baaba min dey gomЙ—ii arii lam immorde e Ganndal kon ko araali e maaЙ—a, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol Focciingol"
  19,44,"Ko an yo baaba, wata a rewu Seytaane, pellet, Seytaane laatike yedduЙ—o Hinnorante"
  19,45,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey miЙ—o huli wta meeme Lepte immorde ka Hinnorante laatanoЙ—aa Seytaane giЙ—o"
  19,46,"[Baaba makko] wi'i: \"Enee, an a aГұu reweteeЙ—i am Й—in nee Ibraahiima, pellet, si a accaali mi rajmete selam dummunne [juutuЙ—o]"
  19,47,"[Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Kisal e maaЙ—a aray mi insinanomaa ka Joomi am, pellet, Konko O Laatike NewaniiЙ—o lam"
  19,48,"Mi martoo(deestoo) on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla, mi toroo Joomi am no gasa mi wonataa tampirЙ—o toragol Joomi am"
  19,49,"Tuma nde o martinoo(deestinoo) Й“e e ko Й“e rewata kon gaanin Alla, Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba kala [gooto e maЙ“Й“e] Men waЙ—i [mo] Annabaajo"
  19,50,"Men Okki Й“e immorde e Yurmeende Amen, Men waЙ—ani Й“e Й—enngal goonga toowungal"
  19,51,"JaЕӢto ka Deftere Muusaa, pellet, kanko o laatinoke laЙ“Й“inЙ—o o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabaajo"
  19,52,"Men noddi mo ka senngo Гұaamo [fello] Tuuri Men Й“attini mo gunndeteeЙ—o"
  19,53,Men Okki mo immorde e Yurmeende Amen musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna Annabaajo
  19,54,"JaЕӢto ka Deftere Ismaa'iila, pellet, kanko o laatinoke GoonguЙ—o fodoore o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabaajo"
  19,55,"O laatino himo yamira yimЙ“e makko Й“en Julde e Jakka on, o laatino kadi WeltoraaЙ—o ka Joomi makko"
  19,56,"JaЕӢto ka Deftere Idriisa, pellet, kanko o laatino GoonguЙ—o Annabaajo"
  19,57,Men Й“anti mo e nokkuure Toowunde
  19,58,"Ko Й“en woni Й“en, Й“e Alla Neemini e dow mu'un immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e ka geЙ—al Й“ebibbe Aadama e Й“en Й“e Men waЙ—Й—innoo wonndude e Nuuhu e geЙ—alЙ“e Ibraahiima e Israa'iila e Й“en Й“e Men Fewni Men SuЙ“ii si janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Hinnorante Й“e fukko koЙ“e sujjooЙ“e e wullooЙ“e. @Corrected"
  19,59,"Lontii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lontotooЙ“e, Й“e yeebi Julde nden Й“e jokki welnuruuji Й—in aray Й“e hawroya e bone"
  19,60,"Si wanaa on tuubuЙ—o o gomЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Й“en Й—on Й“e naatay Aljanna on Й“e tooГұiroy- taake hay e huunde"
  19,61,"Aljannaaji Adan Й—in Й—i Hinnorante On Fodi jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en e birnagal, pellet Kanko, Fodoore Makko nden laatike ko aroore"
  19,62,"ЖҒe nanataa nder ton rayrayti si wonaa kisiyee, no woodani Й“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on nder ton bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  19,63,"On Aljanna mo Men Roninta immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, on laatiiЙ—o kulo [Alla]"
  19,64,"Men jippotaako si wanaa e Yamaruyee Joomi maaЙ—a, no woodani Mo ko woni kon hedde yeeso amen e ko woni kon Й“aawo amen e ko woni kon hakkunde Й—um, Joomi maaЙ—a laataaki yejjitoowo"
  19,65,"Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, Rewu mo monГұitor Dewal Makko. Taw si hiЙ—a anndani Mo tokoraajo"
  19,66,"NeЙ—Й—anke on no wi'a: \"Eyoo, e jaka si mi maai aroyay ka mi yaltinee tawa ko mi wuuruЙ—o"
  19,67,"Enee, neЙ—Й—anke on annditaali Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii, hari o wonaali hay e huunde"
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaЙ—a Men mooЙ“ay Й“e sanne e Seytanuuji Й—in, refti Men adda Й“e sara Jahannama ko Й“e jiccii Й“e"
  19,69,Refti Men Й—oofa immorde e kala fedde ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urnoo saЙ—tude dartagol e dow Hinnorante On
  19,70,Refti ko Menen Anndi Й“en Й“urЙ“e hanndude e sumugol e magge
  19,71,"Alaa hay e gooto e mo'on si wanaa o joloyay e magge, Й—um laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘aawaaЙ—um Tentinaa"
  19,72,"Refti Men ndannda Й“en hulunooЙ“e [Alla] Men Й—ala tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e nder ton"
  19,73,"Si janngaama e taweede maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Amen ЖҒannguЙ—e Й—en; yedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ana gom- Й—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude darnde Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi mbatu"
  19,74,Heewii ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire tawi ko kamЙ“e Й“uri fotude mirannji suudu e mbaadi
  19,75,"Maaku: \"On laatiiЙ—o e nder majjere nden yo Hinnorante fontan mo fontudee, haa si Й“e yi'ii ko Й“e fodaa kon, si tawii ko lepte Й—en maa si ko Darngal ngal, aray Й“e annda on m bonuЙ—o nukkuure e Й“urЙ—o lo'ude konu"
  19,76,"Alla no Й“eydana Й“en feewuЙ“e Peewal, MoЖҙЖҙi heddotooЙ—i Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi ruttorde"
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on yedduЙ—o Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o wi'i: \"Maatun mi okkee jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  19,78,"Enee o Жҙelliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka Hinnorante Aadi"
  19,79,"Wanaa non, aray Men winnda ko o wi'ata kon Men Й“eydana mo immorde e Lepte Й—en Й“eydude"
  19,80,"Men Rona mo e ko o wi'ata kon, o ara e Amen ko o weddiiЙ—o(gooto)"
  19,81,ЖҒe jogitii gaanin Alla reweteeЙ—i fii yo Й—i laatano Й“e teddungal. @Corrected
  19,82,"Wonaa non, maЙ“e yedda rewugolЙ“e ngol, Й“e laatanoo Й“e ayЙ“e"
  19,83,Enee a yi'aali Menen Men Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en hiЙ—i Жҙuuna Й“e Жҙuunudee
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan Й“e, pellat, limonayЙ“ebe limugol"
  19,85,"Г‘alnde Men mooЙ“oyta hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en ka Hinnorante TeddinaaЙ“e"
  19,86,Men sogga bomЙ“e Й“en haa ka Jahannama ko Й“e jolooЙ“e
  19,87,ЖҒe maraa tefoore nden si wanaa on jogitiiЙ—o ka Hinnorante Aadi
  19,88,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Hinnorante jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  19,89,GomЙ—ii on addii huunde pankarЙ—ii nde. @Corrected
  19,90,Kammuuli Й—in no do'a(Й—esa) seekaade immorde e Й—um leydi ndin feera pelle Й—en uuya fii unagol
  19,91,fii Й“e noddanii Hinnorante Й“iЙ—Й—o
  19,92,Haananaa Hinnorante nde O jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o. @Corrected
  19,93,Alaa wonЙ—o ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa o aray ka Hinnorante hombo woni jeyaaЙ—o
  19,94,GomЙ—ii O moftii Й“e O limii Й“e kadi e limugol. @Corrected
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e maЙ“Й“e aray Mo Г‘alnde Darngal ko o woddiiЙ—o(teeldЙ—o)"
  19,96,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e golli ko moЖҙЖҙi kon aray ka Hinnorante waЙ—anaЙ“e Giggol"
  19,97,"Anndu ko Men newiniri nde ka Й—enngal maaЙ—a; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en jertiniraa nde yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e wennje"
  19,98,"Heewii ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire taw si hiЙ—a so'a e maЙ“Й“e immorde e goЙ—Й—o, maa hiЙ—a nana Й“e hito"
  20,1,Taa Haa
  20,2,Men Telliniraali Alqur'aanaare nden e maaЙ—a fii yo a tampu
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonannde on huloowo [Alla]"
  20,4,Ko Jippinaande immorde e On TaguЙ—o leydi ndin e kammuuli toowuЙ—i Й—in
  20,5,Hinnorante On O fotii ka dow Arsi kin. @Corrected
  20,6,No woodani Mo ko woni kon e kammuuli Й—in e ko woni kon e leydi nden e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji Й—iЙ—i e ko woni kon ka ley leydi
  20,7,"Si a fenГұinii konngol ngol, pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi gunndoo on e ko o suuЙ—i"
  20,8,"Alla reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko, no woodani Mo InЙ—e MoЖҙЖҙe Й—en"
  20,9,taw si arii e maaЙ—a Yewtere fii Muusaa
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'unoo yiite, o wi'ani Й“eynguure makko nden: \"Г‘iiЙ“ee, min dey mi haynike jaynge bela-jo'o mi addanay on immorde e magge docotal maaЙ—um mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo"
  20,11,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge o noddaa; \"ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko Min Woni Joomi maaЙ—a solu paЙ—e maa Й—en; pellet an, hiЙ—a ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa LaЙ“Й“inaande(seninangol)"
  20,13,Min Mi SuЙ“ike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede kon
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min Woni Alla reweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa Min Rewam; ГұiiЙ“ir e Julde nden fii Annditugol lam"
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aroowal MiЙ—o Й—eЙ“a suuЙ—ude ngal fii yoЙ“e kala wonkii ko ki huuwi kon"
  20,16,Wata faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gom- Й—inaa ngal o jokki mbeleeЙ—e makko o halkii
  20,17,Ko honЙ—um woni ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a an Muusaa
  20,18,"O maaki: \"Ndun ko tuggordu am miЙ—o tuggoo ndu miЙ—o liwtirana ndu dammi am Й—in, miЙ—o mari kadi haajuuji goo e mayru"
  20,19,"O Daali: \"LiЙ“u ndu, an Muusaa"
  20,20,"O liЙ“i ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mboddi wonundi yahude"
  20,21,"O Daali: \"Nanngu ndu wata a hulu Men artiray ndu e mbaadi mayru araniri ndin"
  20,22,Ukku junngo maaЙ—a ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e bone Й—um ko Aaya goo
  20,23,Fii yo Men hollle immorde e Aayeeje Amen MawЙ—e Й—en
  20,24,"Yahu ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,25,"O maaki: \"Jooma YanГұanam Й“ernde am nden"
  20,26,Newinanaa lam fiyaake am on
  20,27,Firtaa finnde nden ka Й—enngal am
  20,28,Fii yo Й“e faamu konngol am ngol
  20,29,WaЙ—anaa lam ballo jeyaaЙ—o ka Й“eynguure am
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiЙ—Й—o am on"
  20,31,Semmbinir mo darnde am
  20,32,Tawnaa mo e nder fiyaake am on
  20,33,Fii yo men Senine ko Й—uuЙ—i
  20,34,Men jaЕӢtoMaa ko Й—uuЙ—i
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Wonii HumpitiiЙ—o Men"
  20,36,"O Daali: \"GomЙ—ii a okkaama toraare maaЙ—a nden an Muusaa"
  20,37,GomЙ—ii Men Neeminiino ma e laawol goo
  20,38,Tuma nde Men Wahayinnoo faade e yumma maa ko Wahayinaa kon
  20,39,"[Men Daali] Bugo mo ka nder hontoore bugoЙ—aa nden kadi ka nder diidere, yo diidere nden kadi bugoyo mo ka fonngo; Жҙetta mo gaГұo Am e gaГұo makko, Mi werlii e maaЙ—a Giggol immorde ka Am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndenka Am"
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maaЙ—a on yahaynoo; o wi'a: \"Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?\" Men artirmaa ka yumma maaЙ—a fii yo gite makko Й—en Й“uuЙ“u hara o sunaaki. WaruЙ—aa wonkii Men danndumaa immorde e saЙ—teende nden, Men jarribimaa jarrabuyeeje ГұiiЙ“uЙ—aa duuЙ“i ka yimЙ“e Madyana refti aruЙ—aa ka fodoore ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,41,Mi SuЙ“imaa fii hoore-Am
  20,42,Yahu an e musiЙ—Й—o maa on wonndude e Aayeeje Am Й—en wata on derfu e jaЕӢtagol Lam
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,44,Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol bela-jo'o kanko o waajitoto maaЙ—um o hula
  20,45,"ЖҒe maaki: \"Joomi amen, menen dey meЙ—en huli nde murtata e hoore amen maa nde o bewata"
  20,46,"O Daali: \"Wata on hulu, pellet, Min MiЙ—o wonndi e mooЙ—on MiЙ—o Nana MiЙ—o Yi'a"
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'on: \"Menen ko Men NulaaЙ“e Joomi maaЙ—a, accitu wonndude e amen Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en wata a leptu Й“e, gomЙ—ii men addanii ma Aaya immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a, kisiyee on wonii e on jokkuЙ—o Peewal ngal"
  20,48,"GomЙ—ii Wahayinaama e amen; wonndema, Lepte Й—en no fawii ka fennuЙ—o Й—uuri"
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi mooЙ—on"
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Joomi amen, ko On OkkuЙ—o kala huunde tagu mayre ngun refti O Fewni"
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko honno gire arane Й—en fewndori"
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ganndal Й—um no ka Joomi am e nder Deftere, Joomi am majjataa O yejjitataa"
  20,53,"On waЙ—anЙ—o on leydi ndin weЖҙЖҙitaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri Й—am nooneeji immorde e puЙ—i sertuЙ—i"
  20,54,"Г‘aamee aynon neemoraaЙ—i mo'on Й—im. Pellet, no e nder Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- Й“e hakkillaaji Й—in"
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Men Tagi on, ko e nder mayri Men Ruttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Men Yaltinoyta on laawol goo"
  20,56,"GomЙ—ii Men hollii mo Aayeeje Amen Й—en kala majje, o fenni o salii"
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, a aru ka amen fii yo a yaltinir men ka leydi amen mbilaaku maaЙ—a ngun an Muusaa"
  20,58,"Maa men addane mbilewu yeru maggu, waЙ—u fodoore hakkunde amen e maaЙ—a hara men lunndataako nde wanaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde"
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore mooЙ—on nden ko Гұalnde saЙ—Й—ugol ngol, yo yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“indire ka walluhaa(fenynyaange)"
  20,60,Fir'awna hucciti o mooЙ“i pewje makko Й—en refti o ari
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani Й“e: \"On boniraama, wata on fefendo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gomЙ—ii sooyii on fefindiiЙ—o"
  20,62,"ЖҒe pooЙ—ondiri fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e suuЙ—i cowndi Й—in"
  20,63,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet Й“ee Й—iЙ—o ko mbileeЙ“e hiЙ“e faalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun Й“e itta laawol mon yeruyankeewol ngol"
  20,64,"MooЙ“itee pewje mo'on Й—en refti aron ko on lappol, gomЙ—ii malaama hannde on fooluЙ—o"
  20,65,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko si tawii ko onon bugotoo maaЙ—un si ko menen wonata adotooЙ“e bugaade"
  20,66,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ko woni, bugee(mbedde), tawi Й“okkoy maЙ“Й“e koy e cawoy maЙ“Й“e koy no wa'itana mo sabu mbilewu maЙ“Й“e ngun woni ko e yahude"
  20,67,Muusaa so'i kulol ka wonkii makko
  20,68,"Men Daali: 'Wata a hulu, pellet ko an woni fooloowo on"
  20,69,"Bugo ko woni kon ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a Й—um moЙ—ay ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini kon, pellet, ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini kon ko pewje mbile bileejo on maletaake nukkuwoo ka o ardi"
  20,70,"MbileeЙ“e Й“en werlaa ko Й“e sujjuЙ“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—inii Joomi Haaruuna e Muusaa"
  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gomЙ—inii mo ko adii mi duЕӢanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kanko woni mawЙ—o mo'on on anndinЙ—o on mbilaaku ngun, mi woondii, maa mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en taЖҙa luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen Й“uri lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e e heddotooЙ—e"
  20,72,"[MbileeЙ“e Й“en] wi'i: \"Men Й“urnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e Й“annganguyeeji, e On TaguЙ—o men, [an Fir'awna] Гұaawu ko Гұaawataa kon, pellet, ko Гұaawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna Й—oo"
  20,73,"Menen dey, men gomЙ—inii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko dooluЙ—aa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu ngun, ko Alla woni MoЖҙЖҙo HeddotooЙ—o. @Corrected"
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bonЙ—o; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi"
  20,75,"mo ari ka Makko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o hara gomЙ—ii o golliino moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, haray Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e Darjaaji ToowuЙ—i Й—in"
  20,76,"Aljannaaji Г‘iiЙ“al no doga e ley majji canЙ—i Й—in, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton, ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o. @Corrected"
  20,77,"GomЙ—ii Men wahaynii faade e Muusaa roЖҙidu e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en waЙ—an Й“e laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wata a hulu hewtiteede wata a hulu [yoolagol]"
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri Й“e koneeli makko Й—in, suumi Й“e ka maayo ko suumi Й“e kon"
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o fewnaali [Й“e]"
  20,80,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila gomЙ—ii Men danndiino on e gaГұo mon on, Men fodi on kadi ka banЕӢe Гұaamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Men jippini e mooЙ—on Manna= Й—acce njumri e doobe"
  20,81,"Г‘aamee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i ko Men arsiki on kon, wota on bewu e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden jippo e mo'on, on mo Tikkere Am jippii e mu'un gomЙ—ii haray o halkike"
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi heewuЙ—o Yawtanngol wonannde on tuubuЙ—o o gomЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi refti o feewi"
  20,83,Ko honЙ—un heГұinmaa gaayi yimЙ“e maa Й“en an Muusaa
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ЖҒeeЙ—oo, hiЙ“e iwtiri Й“aawo am, mi heГұike ka MaaЙ—a Joomi fii yo A welto"
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: \"Pellet, Mennen gomЙ—ii Men jarribike=finninii yimЙ“e maaЙ—a Й“en Й“aawo maaЙ—a, Saamiriiyu majjinii Й“e"
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o suniiЙ—o; o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodaali on Fodoore MoЖҙЖҙere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi mooЙ—on si lunndi Й—on fodoore am nden"
  20,87,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men lunndaaki fodoore maaЙ—a nden e sago amen, kono menen men ronndinaama teddeendi e cuЙ—aaje yimЙ“e Й“en men werlii Й—e, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirii"
  20,88,"O yaltinani Й“e Й“anndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko ko'ol woni reweteeЙ—o mon e reweteeЙ—o Muusaa on, o yejjitu [mo Й—oo]"
  20,89,"Enee, Й“ee yi'aali wonndema ruttataako e maЙ“Й“e konngol, ndi maranaa Й“e kadi lorra wonaa fii non [pooЙ—ugol] nafa"
  20,90,"GomЙ—ii Haaruuna maakaniino Й“e ko adii: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, pellet, on jarribora kol, pellet, Joomi mooЙ—on ko Hinnorante On jokkee lam Й—oftoЙ—on yamiroore am nden"
  20,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men seerataa ko men ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko an yo Haaruuna, nde yi'unoЙ—aa Й“e majjii ko haЙ—umaa"
  20,93,nde jokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamaruyee am on
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: \"Ko an yo neene-gooto am, wata a nanngu waare am nden wanaa hoore am nden kadi, min dey, mi hulu wata a wi'u: Mi senndii hakkunde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, mi heЙ—aaki konngol maaЙ—a ngol"
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko honЙ—um woni fiyaake maaЙ—a on an Saamiriiyu"
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: \"Mi yi'ii ko Й“e yi'aali Й—um, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaaЙ—o on [Jibriila] mi werlii Й—um ko nii cuЙ—irani lam wonkii am"
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii faade e rewteeЙ—o maa, on mo ГұalluЙ—aa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sunnay mo refti mi jaroo mo ka maayo e jaragol"
  20,98,"Pellet, ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko Alla, On Mo ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko, Ganndal Makko Yaajanii kala huunde"
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men filloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko feЖҙЖҙunoo kon, gomЙ—ii Men addanii ma immorde ka Amen jaЕӢta"
  20,100,"Mo Й—uurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto Г‘alnde Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]"
  20,101,"Ko o luttinteeЙ—o e nder majje, bonanii Й“e donngal Г‘alnde Darngal"
  20,102,"Г‘alnde wuttoytee ka alaadu Men mooЙ“a bonЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘alnde ko mbuliiЙ“e [gite]"
  20,103,"HiЙ“e sowndondira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e [Й“e wi'a] on ГұiiЙ“aali si wanaa [balЙ—e] sappo"
  20,104,"Ko Menen woni AnnduЙ“e ko Й“e wowlata kon, tuma nde koohooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e e laawol wi'ata: \"On ГұiiЙ“aali si wanaa Гұallal"
  20,105,"HiЙ“e lanndaade ma fii pelle Й—en, maaku: \"Joomi am jaroto Й—e e jaragol"
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndin ko ndi boowal Й“owrungal"
  20,107,A yi'ataa e mayri ooГұannde wanaa tintiire
  20,108,"Ko nden Г‘alnde Й“e jokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e selugol mo,, hitooji Й—in yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wanaa nyuumbaango"
  20,109,"Nden Г‘alnde tefoore nden nafataa, si wanaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti Й—um O weltori konngol makko"
  20,110,Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maЙ“Й“e e hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“e huЙ“indortaa Й—um ganndal
  20,111,"Geece Й—en yankinanii WuuruЙ—o DartiiЙ—o On, gomЙ—ii sooyii on ronndiiЙ—o tooГұe"
  20,112,On mo golli immorde e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o haray o hulaa tooГұe wanaa uytaneede kadi
  20,113,Ko nii Men Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji Й—in bela-jo'o kamЙ“e Й“e hulay maa nde fuЙ—Й—anoo Й“e waaju
  20,114,"Alla LamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On Toowii, wata a heГұor Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maaЙ—a wahayu mayre, maaku: \"Joomi Й“eydanam Ganndal"
  20,115,GomЙ—ii Men ahodiino e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Men heЙ“anaali mo pellital
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en sujjanee Aadama, Й“e sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii"
  20,117,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo Aadama, pellet, ooЙ—oo ko o gaГұo maa an e sonnaajo maa on, wata o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa"
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a weeletaake nder ton a holataa kadi"
  20,119,"Pellet, an a Й—omЙ—etaake nde ton e nguletaake kadi"
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngun"
  20,121,"ЖҒe Гұaami e maggal, feeГұani Й“e mettefooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e naati e suddirgol e dow maЙ“Й“e immorde e kaaki Aljanna on, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji"
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko SuЙ“ii mo, O Tuubini mo O Fewni [mo]"
  20,123,"O Daali: \"Jippee ton, on fow mo'on, yoga e mo'on ko ayЙ“e yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e Am Fewnoowo kala jokkuЙ—o Peewal Am ngal haray o majjataa o malkisataake kadi"
  20,124,"Kala Й—urniiЙ—o gaayi jaЕӢtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam Й“illuЙ—am Men mooЙ“oya mo Г‘alnde Darngal ko o bunЙ—o"
  20,125,"O wi'a: \"Joomi, ko fii honЙ—um mooЙ“anЙ—aa lam ko mi bunЙ—o, gomЙ—ii mi laatinoke yi'oowo"
  20,126,"O Daala: \"Ko wano nii arunoo e maaЙ—a Aayeeje Amen Й—en yejjituЙ—aa Й—e, ko wano nii kadi hannde yejjitirteЙ—aa"
  20,127,"Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta on fantinЙ—o hara o gomЙ—inaa Aayeeje Joomi makko Й—en, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara Й—en Й“uri saЙ—tude ko Й—en kadi heddotoo"
  20,128,"Kaa hara Й“annganaali Й“e no foti hewde ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire? HiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, pellet, no e Й—um Aayeeje wonannde joomiraaЙ“e hakkillaaji Й“en"
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a [Lepte] Й—en laatotono duumiiЙ—e e lajal innaangal"
  20,130,"MunГұo e dow ko Й“e wowlata kon, subuhinor yettugol Joomi maaЙ—a ko adii Жҙellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji Гұallal belajo'o a weltoto"
  20,131,"Wata a yawtin dey gite maa Й—en faade kon ko Men dekmini Й—um nooneeji immorde e maЙ“Й“e, cuЙ—aari ngurndam aduna fii yo Men jarribor Й“e e Й—um, Arsike Joomi maaЙ—a on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko on kadi heddotoo"
  20,132,"Yamir Й“eynguure maaЙ—a nden Julde nden monГұitoraa e Й—um, Men lanndaaki ma arsike ko Menen arsikaymaa. Battane [moЖҙЖҙe] Й—en kadi wonanii hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en"
  20,133,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko hanno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Enee, hara araali e maЙ“Й“e Й“anngal ko woni kon e Й—eri arani Й—in"
  20,134,"Sinndo Menen Men halkirno Й“e Lepte ko adii Й—um, Й“e wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen NulaaЙ—o men jokka Aayeeje Maa Й—en, ko adii nde Men hoyata men hesra"
  20,135,"Maaku: \"Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Focciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi"
  21,1,"ЖҒadanike yimЙ“e Й“en hasboore maЙ“Й“e nden, te kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder welsindaare ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,2,Arataa e maЙ“Й“e waaju immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko fuЙ—Й—aa si wanaa Й“e jentike nde hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e fija
  21,3,"ЖҒerЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko welsandiiЙ—e Й“en tooГұuЙ“e suuЙ—a cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, hara oo wonu si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru mo'on, kaa on aray e mbilewu hara onon hiЙ—on sutii (ndaara)"
  21,4,"O maaki: \"Joomi am no Anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kanko ko O Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o On"
  21,5,"Ko woni, Й“e wi'u: \"Ko nde jiiЙ“u-jaaЙ“u koyЙ—i, toode, o fefindi nde, ko woni, kanko ko o yimoowo, awa yo o addan en Aayewal wano aranЙ“e Й“en Nuliranoo non"
  21,6,"GomЙ—inaali ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e saare Men halki nde. Enee, hara ko kamЙ“e goomЙ—ita"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a si wanaa worЙ“e Men Wahayina e maЙ“Й“e, lanndee yimЙ“e defte Й“en si tawii wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  21,8,"Men waЙ—aali Й“e Й“alli Й“e Гұaamataa Гұaametee, Й“e laataaki kadi luttinteeЙ“e"
  21,9,"Refti Men Goonginani Й“e Fodoore nden Men danndi Й“e wonndude e Й“en Й“e Men Muuyi, Men halki fantinЙ“e Й“en"
  21,10,GomЙ—ii Men jippinii faade e mooЙ—on Deftere no e nder mayre jaЕӢtawol mooЙ—on. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,11,Heewii ko Men halki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko tooГұunde Men fuЙ—Й—i Й“aawo mayre yimЙ“e goo
  21,12,"Tuma nde Й“e so'unoo Lepte Amen Й—en, tawi kamЙ“e hiЙ“e doga Й—e"
  21,13,"Wata on dogu, ruttee faade e ko neeminaЙ—on kon e mu'un e koЙ—anЙ—e mo'on, belajo'o on lannditoyte"
  21,14,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, menen men laatinoke tooГұuЙ“e\". @Corrected"
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu maЙ“Й“e, haa Men waЙ—a Й“e coГұateeri ko Й“e mayЙ“e"
  21,16,Men tagaali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Men fijooЙ“e
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faandino nde Men jogotoo fijindaaru, Men jogitotono Й—um immorde ka Amen si tawii Men laatike waЙ—ooЙ“e"
  21,18,"Ko woni, MeЙ—en werloo Goonga kan e dow meere nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko sifotoЙ—on"
  21,19,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi Й“en wonuЙ“e ka Makko kadi Й“e mawnittaako gaayi rewugol Mo, Й“e hasrintaaka kadi"
  21,20,HiЙ“e Subhinoo jemma e Гұalorma Й“e aamataa
  21,21,"Kaa Й“e jogiti reweteeЙ—i ka leydi hara kannji hiЙ—i immintina [mayЙ“e Й“en]"
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin] rewteeЙ—i ko wonaa Alla Й—i bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin gaayi koЙ“e sifotoo. @Corrected"
  21,23,"O lanndetaake ko O gollata kon, kamЙ“e ko Й“e lannditoyteeЙ“e"
  21,24,"Kaa Й“e jogiti gaanin Makko reweteeЙ—i? Maaki: \"Addee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaЕӢta Й“en wonnduЙ“e e am e jaЕӢta Й“en adiiЙ“e lam\". Ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e Й“e anndaa Goonga kan kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ—o si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko; pellet, reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Min Rewee Lam"
  21,26,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Hinnorante On jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Senayee woodanii Mo, ko woni, [Й“en ko Й“e] jeyaaЙ“e teddinaaЙ“e"
  21,27,"ЖҒe adortaa Mo konngol ngol, kamЙ“e ko Yamiroore Makko nden Й“e gollata"
  21,28,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maЙ“Й“e e ko woni kon hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, Й“e tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo O Weltanii, kamЙ“e immorde e kulol Makko ko Й“e jootuЙ“e"
  21,29,"Kala e maЙ“Й“e kadi wi'uЙ—o: \"Min ko mi reweteeЙ—o gaanin Makko\". On Й—on Men YoЙ“ay mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Men YoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,30,"Enee, hara Й“en yedduЙ“e yi'aali wonndema kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin Й—i laatinoke hippondirЙ—i, Men Udditi Й—i Men waЙ—i immorde e ndiyam Й—am kala huunde wuuru nde. Kaa Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  21,31,"Men waЙ—i ka leydi pelle fii wata nde ooГұodo e maЙ“Й“e, Men waЙ—i e mayri Й—ate yaajuЙ—e, belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e feeway"
  21,32,"Men waЙ—i kammu ngun kippudi reenaandi, kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e gaayi Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  21,33,Ko Kanko woni On TaguЙ—o jemma on e Гұalorma on e naange ngen e lewru ndun kala majji hiЙ—i fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku
  21,34,"Men waЙ—anaali Й“anndunke ado maaЙ—a luttineede, enee, hara si a maayii ko kamЙ“e woni luttinteeЙ“e Й“en"
  21,35,"Kala wonkii meedat mayЙ—e nden, Men jarribora on bone on e moЖҙЖҙere nden jarrabagol, ko ka Amen kadi ruttotoЙ—on"
  21,36,"Si Й“en yedduЙ“e yi'ii ma, Й“e jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde [Й“e wiвҖҷa:] \"Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaЕӢtotooЙ—o reweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in?\" hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yedduЙ“e jantagol Hinnorante On"
  21,37,"NeЙ—Й—ake on Tagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am Й—en wata on hawju"
  21,38,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  21,39,"Sinndo Й“en yedduЙ“e anndiino tuma tawi Й“e ittataa Yiite ngen ka geece maЙ“Й“e wanaa kadi ka Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e kadi, kamЙ“e Й“e wonaali walloyteeЙ“e"
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee nge muga Й“e, hara Й“e hattantaake ruttugol nge, Й“e wonaali kadi nennanoyteeЙ“e"
  21,41,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo jalkitanooma ado maaЙ—a, jippii e Й“en jalkituЙ“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita"
  21,42,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e Гұalorma immorde e Hinnorante On, ko woni, kamЙ“e gaayi jaЕӢta Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani Й“e reeweteeЙ“e Й“e no dannda Й“e gaanin Amen? ЖҒe hattantaake wallude hay wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni wondateeЙ“e immorde e Amen"
  21,44,"Ko woni, Men dakmitii Й“ee e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haa ngurndam Й—am juutani Й“e. Enee, hara Й“ee yi'aali wonnde Menen MeЙ—en ara e leydi ndin Men ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kamЙ“e woni foolooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si Й“e jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii Й“e seeЙ—a immorde e Lepte Joomi maa Й—en, maa Й“e wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke tooГұuЙ“e"
  21,47,"Men waЙ—a manndikirЙ—e(peesirЙ—e) NunЙ—al ngal fii Г‘alnde Darngal hara wonkii woo toГұiroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii HasbooЙ“e"
  21,48,GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaЕӢta wonannde hulooЙ“e Й“en
  21,49,ЖҒen hulayЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e ka wirnii hara kamЙ“e immorde e Darngal ngal ko Й“e huli
  21,50,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] ko nde JaЕӢta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddayЙ“e nde"
  21,51,"GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi AnnduЙ“e mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Ko honЙ—um woni Й—ii nanndonlaaji nate mahiiЙ—e, Й—in Й—i ufiniЙ—on e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en no rewde Й—i"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"GomЙ—ii on laatike onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en e nder majjere Й“anngunde wonЙ—on"
  21,55,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addanЙ—aa men, kaa an ko e fijooЙ“e Й“en jeyaЙ—aa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin On TaguЙ—oЙ—i, min komi jeyaaЙ—o e seediiЙ“e Й“en e dow Й—um"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii Й—ii sanamuuji mo'on Й“aawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ruЕӢii Й“e"
  21,58,"O waЙ—i Й—i kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto e mayru"
  21,59,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko hommbo waЙ—i Й—u'un e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in? Pellet, on ko o jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,60,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men naniino suka no jaЕӢtoo Й—i ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"
  21,61,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Addee mo yeeso gite yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e seedoto"
  21,62,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, Ibraahiima ko an waЙ—i Й—u'um Й—oo e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in"
  21,63,"O maaki: \"Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle Й—um, lanndeeЙ—i si tawii Й—i laatike hiЙ—i wowla"
  21,64,"ЖҒe ruttii faade e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Pellet, ko onon woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,65,"Refti Й“e uggini ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en [Й“e wi'i:] gomЙ—ii hiЙ—a anndi Й—i'i wonaa wowlayЙ—i"
  21,66,"O maaki: \"Enee, on reway gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e huunde hara lorrataa on kadi"
  21,67,Bis mo'on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,68,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Sunnee mo, wallee reweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in, si tawii ko on gollooЙ“e"
  21,69,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo yiite, laato Й“uuЙ“ol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima"
  21,70,ЖҒe faandanii mo pewje Men waЙ—i Й“e pertube Й“en
  21,71,"Men danndi mo [Men danndi kadi] Luutu faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barkini e mu'un wonannde tageefooji Й—in"
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka Й“eydugol, kala maЙ“Й“e Men waЙ—i [Й“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  21,73,"Men waЙ—i Й“e AlmaamiiЙ“e hiЙ“e fewna e Yamiroore Amen Men Wahayini faade e maЙ“Й“e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in e Гұinnugol Julde nden e Okkugol Jakka on, Й“e laatinoke ko Й“e Reway Й“e Men"
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo Г‘eeГұal e Ganndal, Men danndi mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yimЙ“e mu'un] laatinoo no golla soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bonЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Men jaabinani mo kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden immorde e saЙ—teende mawnde nden"
  21,77,"Men walli mo immorde e Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatino yimЙ“e bonЙ“e, Men yooli Й“e, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  21,78,E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde Й“e Гұaawaynoo fii ngesa mban tuma nde bonnunoo e nder mabba dammi yimЙ“e Й“en Men woni seediiЙ“e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden
  21,79,"Men Faamini nde Sulaymaana [Гұaawoore nden] gooto-kala e maЙ“Й“e Men Okki Г‘eeГұel e Ganndal Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle Й—en hiЙ—e subhinoo e colli Й—in kadi, Men laatike golluЙ“e"
  21,80,"Men Anndini [Daawuuda] moЖҙЖҙinngol mekeГұaaji fii mo'on, fii yo Й—i reenu on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnooЙ“e"
  21,81,"[Men eltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barki e mu'un. Men laatike AnnduЙ“e kala huunde"
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo, Й—i golla golle gaanin Й—um. Men laatanike Й—i ReenooЙ“e"
  21,83,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] \"Min dey memii lam lorra kan, ko An woni ЖҒuroowo Yurmeede yurmtooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,84,"Men jaabinani mo Men hunci ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Men Okkiti mo Й“eynguure makko nden e yeru maЙ“Й“e wonndude e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й—um ko Yurmeende immorde ka Amen e waaju wonannde rewooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,85,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, Й“en fow ko e munГұЙ“e Й“en Й“e jeyaa"
  21,86,"Men naadi Й“e e nder Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,87,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahunoo ko o tikkuЙ—o o sikki wonnde Men Hattanaake e hoore makko, o noddi ka niЙ“e; \"Wonnde reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa An Senayee wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndi mo immorde e suno ngon, ko wano nii kadi Men danndirta gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  21,89,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wata A Й—alam bajjo, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo, Men Okki mo Yahyaa, Men moЖҙЖҙinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yaccoo e [gollugol] moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hiЙ“e nodda Men ka rerЙ—ere e kulol Й“e laatinoke yannkinaniiЙ“e Men"
  21,91,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] oya [suddiiЙ—o] reenunooЙ—o farju makko on Men wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu Amen, Men waЙ—i mo kanko e geЙ—aljo makko on Maande wonannde winndere nden"
  21,92,"Pellet, Й—ee mofte mo'on ko mofte goote, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam"
  21,93,"ЖҒe taЖҙi fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e fow ko faade ka Am Й“e ruttoytoo"
  21,94,"Kala golluЙ—o immorde e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in hara kanko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, dullugol alaa fii golle makko Й—en, pellet, Menen Men winndanay mo"
  21,95,"No Harmani saare nde Men halki Й—um, wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e ruttataako [ton]"
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Yaajuuja e Maajuuja, hara kamЙ“e immorde e kala naЙ—el hiЙ“e sortoo"
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nden Й“adike, tawi kayre puttini giiЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e, [Й“e wi'a:] \"Eeyoo bone amen, gomЙ—ii men laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e Й—u'um, ko woni, men laatike tooГұuЙ“e"
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyayЙ“e e magge"
  21,99,Sinndo Й“ee laatinoke reweteeЙ“e Й“e jolataano e magge. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e e nder magge
  21,100,"No woodani Й“e e nder magge haraango, kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa nder ton"
  21,101,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in adanii Й—um immorde ka Amen Й“en Й—on ko Й“e woЙ—Й—intinteeЙ“e gaayi magge"
  21,102,"ЖҒe nanoytaa wuuЙ—aango magge kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in lokaa(wooЙ—a) kon, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e"
  21,103,"SuninoytaaЙ“e Й—enЖҙere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en no jaЙ“Й“ooЙ“e [Й“e wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande mo'on, nden nde laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on fodee"
  21,104,"Г‘alnde Men taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol Й—erol defte. Ko wano Men fuЙ—Й—ori non ka arannde tagu Men ruttirta ngu, [Й—um] ko Fodoore e dow Amen, pellet, Menen Men laatike gollooЙ“e"
  21,105,"GomЙ—ii Men winndiino ka Jabuura Й“aawo Alluwal Reenaangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaaЙ“e Am moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en ronoyta ndi"
  21,106,"Pellet,no e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] jottingol wonannde yimЙ“e rewooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,107,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa Yurmeende wonannde winndire nden
  21,108,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonndema ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko O ReweteeЙ—o Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e?\". @Corrected"
  21,109,"Si tawii Й“e Й—urnike, maaku: \"Mi anndinii on e dow fotondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no Й“adii maaЙ—um si no woЙ—Й—i kon ko fodaЙ—on"
  21,110,"Pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi ko feeГұi kon e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suuЙ—oton"
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, belejo'o Й—um ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne"
  21,112,"Maaku: \"Jooma, Г‘aawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On woni WallitorteeЙ—o On e dow kon ko sifotoЙ—on"
  22,1,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, hulee Joomi mo'on, pellet, dillannde Darngal ngal ko huunde mawnde"
  22,2,"Г‘alnde yi'oton ngal, yejjitoyay kala muyninoowo ko o muyninaynoo kon, fukka kala sowiiЙ—o ko o sowiinoo kon, a yi'ay yimЙ“e Й“en no siwri, hara kamЙ“e Й“e siwraa, kono Lepte Alla Й—en ko saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  22,3,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal, o jakka kala Seytaane canndallo"
  22,4,"Winndaama e hoore-makko wonnde pellet, kala welduЙ—o e makko pellet, o majjinay mo, o Й—owa mo haa ka Lepte Sa'iiri"
  22,5,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, si tawii on laatike e sikke immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Menen Men Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu, refti e heЙ—Й—ere refti e huyre timmunde tagu e nde wonaa timmunde tagu fii yo Men Й“annginan on, MeЙ—en Г‘iiЙ“ina ka renngaaji ko Men Muuyi kon haa e happu innaaЙ—o, refti Men yaltini on ko on boobooЙ“e, refti fii yo on yotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on Й“en Й“e no maaya no e mo'on kadi Й“en Й“e no ruttee faade ka Й“uri jaasude e ngurndan Й—am fii wata Й“e anndu Й“aawo ganndal hay e huunde. A yi'ay leydi ndin ko yoorunde si Men jippinii e dow mayri ndiyam Й—an ndi dilla ndi Жҙura ndi fuЙ—ina immorde e kala noone wooЙ—uЙ—o"
  22,6,"ЖҠum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurnitay mayЙ“e Й“en, tawde pellet, ko O HattanЙ—o e dow kala huunde. @Corrected"
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, wonnde pellet, Alla immintinay Й“en wonЙ“e ka genaale"
  22,8,No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wanaa peewal wanaa deftere nurЙ—unde(jalbunde)
  22,9,"HofuЙ—o balaaji mu'un [mawnintiniiЙ—o] fii yo o majjin gaayi Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna oyeere Men meeЙ—inoyay mo kadi Г‘alnde Darngal Lepte sumoowe ngen"
  22,10,"ЖҠum ko sabu ko juuЙ—e maaЙ—a Й—en ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla wonaali TooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  22,11,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii mo o tabitira sabu Й—um si jarrabuyee kadi heЙ“ii mo o waylitoo e yeeso makko, o hayrii aduna on e Laakara on ko Й—um tigi woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden"
  22,12,"Himo rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa mo e kon ko nafataa mo kadi. ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko Й—um woni majjere woЙ—Й—unde nden"
  22,13,"Himo rewa on mo lorra muuЙ—um no Й“uri Й“adaade diini nafa muuЙ—um kan, bonii welddiЙ—o bonii kadi wuuridaaЙ—o"
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla hiMo naada Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji canЙ—i Й—in, pellet, Alla hiMo waЙ—a ko O faandii kon. @Corrected"
  22,15,On wonЙ—o no sikka wonnde Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka Laakara; haray yo o fontu Й“oggol faade ka kammu refti o taЖҙa ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko Й—en ittay ko tikkini kon
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Men Jippiniri nde Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e. Pellet, Alla hiMo Fewna on Mo O faandii"
  22,17,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e e Й“en YahuudinkooЙ“e e Saabi'iyankooЙ“e e AnnasaarankooЙ“e e MajuusinkooЙ“e e Й“en sirkooЙ“e, pellet, Alla O seerndoowo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal. Pellet, Alla e dow kala huunde ko O SeediiЙ—o"
  22,18,"Enee a yi'aali, wonndema Alla no sujjannde Mo Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“en wonЙ“e ka leydi, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun e koode Й—en e pelle Й—en e leЙ—Й—e Й—en e daabeeji Й—in e ko Й—uuЙ—i immorde e yimЙ“e Й“en, ko Й—uuЙ—i kadi wajibike e mu'un Lepte Й—en. Kala mo Alla hoyni haray alanaa mo teddinoowo, pellet Alla hiMo golla ko O Muuyi kon"
  22,19,"ЖҒee Й—oo Й—iЙ—o ko wennjondirЙ“e, Й“e wennjondirii fii Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“en yedduЙ“e non, taЖҙanoyte Й“e conci immorde e Yiite fatuЙ—am yuppee ka dow ko'e maЙ“Й“e"
  22,20,HiЙ—am honciniree(hayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi maЙ“Й“e e guri Й—in kadi
  22,21,No woodani Й“oole immorde e njamndi
  22,22,"Tuma kala Й“e faandii yaltugol nder ton immorde e suno, Й“e ruttee e nder magge, [Й“e wiвҖҷanee:] meeЙ—ee Lette sumoowe ngen"
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naada Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golle moЖҙЖҙi Й—in Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji canЙ—i Й—in, Й“e cuЙ—iree nder ton immorde jawe kanЕӢe e lu'ulu'uuje koltu maЙ“Й“e on nder ton ko hariire. @Corrected"
  22,24,"ЖҒe fewnaama faade e ko laaЙ“i immorde e konngol ngol, Й“e fewnaa kadi faade e Laawol Yettiniingol ngol"
  22,25,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e hiЙ“e faddaade gaayi Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Men waЙ—ani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en, no fota ter ГұiiЙ“uЙ—o on e mayre e liigotooЙ—o on. Kala faalaaЙ—o ooГұorde e mayre tooГұe, Men meeЙ—inay mo immorde e Lepte muusuЙ—e"
  22,26,"E tuma nde Men Jippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Men Daali:] Wata a kafidu e Am hay e huunde, laЙ“Й“in Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotooЙ“e Й“en e darotooЙ“e Й“en [juula] e ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e sujja Й“en"
  22,27,"Noddin e yimЙ“e Й“en fii Hajju ngun, Й“e aray e maaЙ—a ko Й“e seppooЙ“e e dow kala Й—ehiimba reedu, Й“e aray immorde e kala laawol woЙ—Й—ungol"
  22,28,"Fii yo Й“e seedo nafoore maЙ“Й“e, Й“e jaЕӢtoo Innde Alla e nder ГұalЙ—i anndaaЙ—i e dow ko O arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i, Гұaamee e majji, Гұamminon kadi baaso Й“illiiЙ—o on"
  22,29,"Refti yo Й“e ittu tuundi maЙ“Й“e ndin, yo Й“e humnu takke maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yo Й“e wanngo Suudu rimdinaa- dun"
  22,30,"ЖҠum [ko yamiraЙ—on], kala mawninЙ—o Hurumji Alla Й—in haray Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere makko ka Joomi makko. Daginanaama on neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, si wonaa kon ko janngaa e taweede mo'on, woЙ—Й—itee soЙ“udi Й—in immorde e sanamuuji, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on kadi konngol fenaande ngol"
  22,31,"NewaniiЙ“e Alla Й“e wanaali sirkanooЙ“e Mo, kala sirkanЙ—o Alla no wa'ita wa si o uuyu immorde ka kammu sonndu biftoo mo maaЙ—um henndu ndun ruuyida e makko [naЙ“a] e nokkure woЙ—Й—unde"
  22,32,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo hollii] kala mawninЙ—o Maandeeji Alla Й—in, pellet Й—um, ko e kulol Й“erЙ—e Й—en jeyaa"
  22,33,"No woodani on e majji nafaaji haa e dummunne innaaЙ—o, refti nokku majji on ko ka Suudu Ndimuru"
  22,34,"Men waЙ—anii kala mofte laawol fii yo Й“e jaЕӢto Innde Alla e dow ko O arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i. ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto ko Kanko jebbilatoЙ—on, weltinir Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en"
  22,35,"ЖҒen [tawЙ“e] si Alla jaЕӢtaama Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hulay, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e dow kon ko heЙ“i Й“e e ГұinnooЙ“e Julde nden hiЙ“e nafka goЙ—Й—um e ko Men arsiki Й“e kon"
  22,36,"E gelooЙ—i [fayЙ—i] Й—in Men waЙ—anii on Й—i jeyaaЙ—um e Maandeeji Alla no woodani on e majji moЖҙЖҙere, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko Й—i saffiniiЙ—i si becce majji Й—en yanii haray Гұaamee immorde e majji Гұamminon kadi yonndiniiЙ—o e weeЙ“itotooЙ—o, ko wano nii, Men eltirani on Й—i belajo'o onon on jarnay"
  22,37,"Hewtoytaa Alla tebbuuli majji wanaa ЖҙiiЖҙe majji kadi, kono hewtoy Mo kulol ngol immorde e mo'on. Ko wano nii O eltani on Й—i fii yo on mawnin Alla e dow ko O fewni on kon, weltin moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“en"
  22,38,"Pellet, Alla O solnanay(dunyanay) Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e, pellet, Alla O yiЙ—aa kala hodoowo heewuЙ—o geddi"
  22,39,"DuЕӢanaama Й“en wonaaЙ“e haЙ“eede [yoЙ“tagol] sabu kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГұaaЙ“e, pellet, Alla ko O HattanЙ—o e dow wallugol Й“e"
  22,40,"ЖҒen yaltinaaЙ“e ka galleeji mu'un ko aldaa e goo- nga si wanaa fii tun Й“e wi'ii: \"Joomi amen ko Alla\". Sinndo wanaano Alla duГұirde yimЙ“e Й“en yoga e maЙ“Й“e yoga, yirbinteno rewirЙ—i ruhbaaniyankooЙ“e Й“en e rewirЙ—i Annasaara en e rewirЙ—i Alyahuuda en e JuulirЙ—e Й—e Innde Alla jaЕӢtetee e nder mu'un ko heewi. ma Alla wallu Й“en wallooЙ“e Mo, pellet, Alla ko O DolnuЙ—o TedduЙ—o"
  22,41,ЖҒen tawЙ“e si Men newinanii Й“e ka leydi Й“e Гұinnay Julde nden Й“e totta askaal on Й“e yamira ko moЖҙЖҙi kon Й“e haЙ—a ko boni kon. Ko Alla woodani Й“attane fiyakuuji Й—in
  22,42,"Si Й“e fennii ma, haray gomЙ—ii fenniino ado maЙ“Й“e yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en"
  22,43,E yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en e yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en
  22,44,"E yimЙ“e Madyana Й“en Muusaa kadi fennaama, Mi nennani yedduЙ“e Й“en refti Mi nanngi Й“e, ko honno yagginngol Am ngol wonirnoo"
  22,45,"No foti hewde e Saare nde Men halki Й—um tawi ko nde tooГұunde, hara hinde ajjii e hoore kippudiiji mayre, e woyndu yirbundu e huЙ“eere toowunde [eggaande]"
  22,46,"Enee, hara Й“ee yahaali ka leydi sakko laatanooЙ“e Й“erЙ—e Й“e haqqilira Й—e, maaЙ—um noppi Й“e nanira Й—i? Pellet, [ko woni kon] wanaa gite Й—en wumi, kono ko Й“erЙ—e wonuЙ—e Й—en e nder becce Й—en wumi"
  22,47,"HiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ire yaccinaneede Lepte Й—en, [e Й—um le] Alla lunndataako fodoore Makko nden. Pellet Гұallal ka Joomi maaЙ—a ko wano duuЙ“i wuluure no limorton non"
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde Mi nennani Й—um hara kayre ko nde tooГұunde, refti Mi nannginde ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde nden"
  22,49,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, anndee min ko mi jertinoowo on Й“annguЙ—o"
  22,50,ЖҒen gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in no woodani Й“e haforanal e arsike tedduЙ—o
  22,51,"ЖҒen yacciiЙ“e [fii bonnugol] e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e ronkinaa [Men] ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e Jahiimaawe ngen"
  22,52,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ—o wanaa kadi Annabaajo si wanaa si o janngii Seytaane werloto e nder janki makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane werlii kon, refti Alla tabintina Aayeeje Makko Й—en. Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  22,53,"Fii yo O waЙ—u ko Seytaane werlotoo ko njarraboye wonannde Й“en Й“e nawnaare woni ka Й“erЙ—e mu'un e Й“e Й“erЙ—e mu'un yoori Й“en. Pellet, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Й“e wonii e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  22,54,"Fii yo Й“en okkaaЙ“e Ganndal ngal anndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“e gomЙ—ina nde, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yankinanoo Й—um. Pellet Alla Fewnay Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  22,55,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e seerataa hiЙ“e e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee maaЙ—um ara e maЙ“Й“e Lepte Г‘alaande saЙ—tunde"
  22,56,"Laamu ngun nden Г‘alnde ko Alla heeranii O Г‘aawoyay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli ko moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hiЙ“e e nder Aljannaaji NeemiiЙ—i"
  22,57,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e, Й“e fenni kadi Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e lepte hoynooje"
  22,58,"ЖҒen feruЙ“e e Laawol Alla refti Й“e waraa maaЙ—um Й“e maayi Alla arsikoyay Й“e arsike moЖҙЖҙo. Pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude ArsikooЙ“e"
  22,59,"Ma O naadoyЙ“e naatirgal ngal Й“e welaa Й—um. Pellet, Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  22,60,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], kala leptuЙ—o yeru ko o leptaa kon, refti bewaa e hoore-makko ma Alla wallu mo. Pellet, Alla ko O YaafotooЙ—o Surroowo"
  22,61,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko fii pellet, Alla hiMo naada jemma on e nder Гұalorma on, hiMo naada kadi Гұalorma on e nder jemma on. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo Yi'oowo"
  22,62,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko fii pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan pellet, kon ko Й“e noddata gaanin Makko ko Й—um woni meere nden. Pellet, ko Kanko woni ToowuЙ—o MawnuЙ—o On"
  22,63,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema Alla O jippinii ndiyam immorde ka kammu, leydi ndin wonti hecciЙ—undi? Pellet, Alla ko O NewiiЙ—o HumpitiiЙ—o"
  22,64,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Galo YettiniiЙ—o On"
  22,65,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema Alla eltani on ko woni kon ka leydi, laaЙ—e Й—en no dogira ka maaje Yamaruyee Makko on, hiMo jogitii kammu ngun fii wata ngu yanu e hoore leydi ndin si wonaa e duЕӢayee Makko. Pellet, Alla ko O newaniiЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en YurmteeЙ—o [Й“e]"
  22,66,Ko Kanko woni On wurnuЙ—o on refiti O wara on refti O wurnitoya on. Pellet neЙ—Й—anke on ko o heewuЙ—o geddi
  22,67,"Men waЙ—anii kala mofte laawol ngol Й“e rewata e mu'un, wata Й“e pooЙ—ondir e maaЙ—a e fiyaake on, noddu faade ka Joomi maaЙ—a. Pellet, an hiЙ—a e hoore Laawol Focciingol"
  22,68,"Si Й“e wennjii ma, Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni AnnduЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  22,69,Alla Г‘aaway hakkunde mo'on Г‘alnde Darngal fii kon ko luutondirton fii mu'un
  22,70,"Enee, a anndaali wonndema Alla hiMo Anndi ko woni kon ka kammu e ka leydi, pellet, Й—um no e nder Deftere. Pellet, Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] no newanii Alla"
  22,71,"HiЙ“e rewa gaanin Alla kon ko Dalil jippinaaka e fii mu'un, e kon ko ganndal alanaa Й“e e mu'un. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en walloowo"
  22,72,"Si jannganaama Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en Й“annguЙ—e a annday e geece Й“en yedduЙ“e mettinaare hiЙ“e Й—eЙ“a yanude e Й“en jannganayЙ“e Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Maaku: \"Yo mi habru on ko Й“uri bonde e Й—um mooЙ—on [ko jaЕӢtanaЙ—on kon] ko Yiite ngen Alla fodii nge Й“en yedduЙ“e bonii ruttorde"
  22,73,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, misal piyaama jentee ngal, pellet Й“en Й“e noddoton gaanin Alla, Й“e tagaa hay coongil, hay sinndo Й“e mooЙ“ondiriino fii Й—um. Si coongil(mbuubu)ngil jattii Й“e goЙ—Й—um Й“e hattantaake jaЙ“tugol ngil Й—um. ЖҠaЙ“Й“uЙ—o on e Й—aЙ“Й“aaЙ—o on fow no lo'i"
  22,74,"ЖҒe mawniniraali Alla no O haani Mawninirde non. Pellet, Alla ko O DolnuЙ—o TedduЙ—o"
  22,75,"Alla no suЙ“oo immorde e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e Й“en kadi. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo Yi'oowo"
  22,76,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maЙ“Й“e e ko woni kon hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, ko faade ka Alla fiyakuuji Й—in ruttetee"
  22,77,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e, RuЖҙЖҙee Sujjon Rewon Joomi mo'on, gollon ko moЖҙЖҙi kon belajo'o onon on maloyte"
  22,78,"WaЙ—iree Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, Kanko O SuЙ“ike on O waЙ—anaali on Й“itteende ka nder Diina, Diina baaba mooЙ—on Ibraahiima ko Kanko inni on julЙ“e ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo NulaaЙ—o on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi wonon seeditoytooЙ“e e hoore yimЙ“e Й“en. Г‘iiЙ“nee e Julde nden totton Jakka on jogitee Alla, ko Kanko woni GiЙ—o mooЙ—on moЖҙЖҙii giЙ—o moЖҙЖҙii walloowo on"
  23,1,GomЙ—ii malaama gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en
  23,2,ЖҒen hulooЙ“e ka nder Julde maЙ“Й“e koЙ“e yankiniiЙ“e
  23,3,E Й“en Й—urniiЙ“e gaayi rayrayti( bolle meere)
  23,4,E Й“en ittooЙ“e jakka on
  23,5,E Й“en reenuЙ“e farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in
  23,6,"Si wanaa e dow sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um Й“e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en jeyi(horbe), haray kamЙ“e Й“e wonaa feleteeЙ“e"
  23,7,"On mo Й—aЙ“Й“i Й“aawo Й—um, haray ko Й“en woni jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,8,E Й“en aynuЙ“e koolaaje maЙ“Й“e e aadiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in
  23,9,E Й“en Й“e kaГұun koЙ“e reenuЙ“e e dow JulЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en
  23,10,"ЖҒee [siforЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji Й—oo] ko kamЙ“e woni ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,11,ЖҒen ronoyayЙ“e Firdawsi on kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e e nder makko
  23,12,GomЙ—ii Men tagii neЙ—Й—anke on immorde e lasili loopal
  23,13,"Refti Men waЙ—i mo toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] e nder ГұiiЙ“irde huЙ“indiinde"
  23,14,"Refti Men Tagi toЙ“Й“ere nden heЙ—Й—ere, Men Tagi heЙ—Й—ere nden huyre, Men Tagi huyre nden Жҙi'e, Men holtini Жҙi'e Й—en teewu. Refti Men fuЙ—Й—anii mo Tagu woo, barkanii Alla MoЖҙЖҙo TaguЙ—o"
  23,15,Refti onon Й“aawo Й—um ko on maayooЙ“e
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon Г‘alnde Darngal on imminoyte"
  23,17,"GomЙ—ii Men Tagii dow mooЙ—on Й—ati jeeЙ—iЙ—i, Men wonaali kadi welsindiiЙ“e gaayi tagu ngun"
  23,18,"Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagu ngun], Men ndewni Й—am ka leydi, pellet, Menen ko Men HattanЙ“e e dow naЙ“ugol Й—am"
  23,19,"Men fuЙ—Й—ani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on nder ton dimЙ—e Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e ko e majje Гұaamoton"
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hingal fuЙ—ina guЖҙam [nebban wujeteeЙ—am] e li'am [maafirЙ—am] wonannde ГұaamooЙ“e"
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in tasakuyee, MeЙ—en yarna on goЙ—Й—un e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafaaji Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, ko immorde e majji kadi Гұaamoton"
  23,22,Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laaЙ—e Й—en ronndeteЙ—on
  23,23,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Enee, on hulatah"
  23,24,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu ngun wi'ani Й“en yedduЙ“e immorde e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Oo wonaali si ko o Й“anndinke yeru mo'on himo faalaa nde o Й“urnotoo e dow mooЙ—on. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaaЙ“e, men naniraali Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen aranЙ“e Й“en"
  23,25,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'un, habbitee mo tun haa seeЙ—a"
  23,26,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko Й“e fennimi kon"
  23,27,"Men wahayini faade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka Amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore Amen nden arii huЙ“Й“inirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naadu e nder makka immorde e kala nooneeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i-Й—iЙ—i. E koreeji ma, si wanaa Й“en konngol ngol aditii e mu'un, wata a haaldu e am fii Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yooleteeЙ“e"
  23,28,"Si a fotondirii an e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a e dow laana kan, haray maaku: \"Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, On dannduЙ—o Men immorde e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,29,"Maaku: \"Joomam, jippinam e jipporde barkinaande ko An woni MoЖҙЖҙo Jippinoowo"
  23,30,"Pellet, no e nder Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aayeeje, haysi men laatike ko men jarribotooЙ“e"
  23,31,Refti Men fuЙ—Й—i Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e yiirde woЙ“Й“e goo
  23,32,"Men Nulii e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um woni Rewee Alla, reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. E on hulatah [Mo]"
  23,33,"Batu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e fenni hawroygol e Laakara on, Men neemini Й“e ka ngurdan aduna wi*i: \"Oo wonaali si wanaa Й“anndunke yeru mooЙ—on himo Гұaama ko Гұaamoton kon himo yara kadi ko yaroton kon"
  23,34,"Mi woondii si on Й—oftike Й“anndinke yeru mo'on, pellet, haray onon ontuma ko on hayruЙ“e(pertube)"
  23,35,"Enee, o fodu on wonndema onon si on maayii on laatike mbullaari e Жҙi'e, wonndema onon ko on yaltinoyteeЙ“e"
  23,36,WoЙ—Й—ii woori kon ko fodaЙ—on
  23,37,"[ЖҒe wi'i:] \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa nguurdam amen aduna, meЙ—en maaya men wuura kadi, menen men wonaali immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  23,38,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko fefindiiЙ—o fenaande fawi e Alla, menen non, men wonaali gomЙ—inayЙ“e mo"
  23,39,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko Й“e fenni lam kon"
  23,40,"O Daali: \"SeeЙ—anii tun, Mi woondii Й“e wontay nimsuЙ“e"
  23,41,"Haacaango ngon nanngi Й“e e Goonga, Men waЙ—i Й“e duuГұo, halkaare wonanii yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,42,Refti Men fuЙ—Й—i Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e gire woЙ“Й“e goo
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako Й—e, Й“e nennantaake kadi"
  23,44,"Refti Men Nuli NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en ko Й“e jokkondirЙ“e, tuma kala ari e mofte NulaaЙ—o majje on Й“e fenna mo Men jokkini yoga e maЙ“Й“e yoga, Men waЙ—i Й“e yewtereeji, woЙ—Й—ineede wonanii yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa Й“en"
  23,45,Refti Men Nuli Muusaa e musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hujja Й“annguЙ—o
  23,46,"Faade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'un ngun, Й“e mawnintinii Й“e laatii yimЙ“e townitiiЙ“e"
  23,47,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gomЙ—inayyimЙ“e Й—iЙ—o yeru amen, hara yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko maccuЙ“e amen"
  23,48,"ЖҒe fenni Й“en Й—iЙ—o, Й“e laatii jeyaaЙ“e e halkaaЙ“e Й“en"
  23,49,GomЙ—ii Men Okkiino Muusaa Deftere nden belejo'o kamЙ“e Й“e feewa
  23,50,"Men waЙ—i geЙ—al Mariyama on e neene makko Maande, Men werni Й“e faade e tulde joomiraare ГұiЙ“rude e callungol"
  23,51,"Ko onon yo NulaaЙ“e, Гұaamee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in gollon ko moЖҙЖҙi, pellet Min, MiЙ—o Anndi ko golloton kon"
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on hulee Lam"
  23,53,"ЖҒe taЖҙi fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre"
  23,54,ЖҠalu Й“e e siwrere nden haa e dummunne
  23,55,"Enee, hara Й“e sikku wonndema ko Men Й“eydiri Й“e kon immorde e jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e"
  23,56,"Men yaccinanay Й“e e moЖҙЖҙereeji, ko woni Й“e so'aa"
  23,57,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e kaГұum immorde e kulol Joomi maЙ“Й“e hara ko Й“e huluЙ“e"
  23,58,E Й“en Й“e kaГұum ko Й“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en
  23,59,E Й“en Й“e kaГұum Й“e wonah sirkanooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e
  23,60,"E Й“en okkayЙ“e ko Й“e okkaa kon, hara Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko huluЙ—e [Alla], wonndema kamЙ“e ko faade ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e ruttoytoo"
  23,61,"ЖҒen [sifaaЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji Й—oo] hiЙ“e yaccoo e moЖҙЖҙereeji Й—in, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e adotooЙ“e e majji"
  23,62,"Men fawaali wonkii si wanaa fodde bawЙ—e makki, no ka Amen Deftere wowlaynde Goonga kan, hara kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұoytaake"
  23,63,"Ko woni, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en no e welsungo immorde e Й—um, no woodani Й“e kadi golle gaanin Й—um ko kamЙ“e gollate Й—e"
  23,64,Haa si Men nanngirii neeminaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Lepte Й—en jaka yoo kamЙ“e hiЙ“e haaca
  23,65,"Wata on haacu hannde, pellet onon, on wallataake immorde e Amen"
  23,66,"GomЙ—ii laatinoke Aayeeje Amen Й—en no janngee e taweede mooЙ—on, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on ruttoo e dow codduli mooЙ—on"
  23,67,"Ko on mawnintiniiЙ“e sabu [jeyeede makka] hiЙ—on hiira wowla bonЙ—i"
  23,68,"Enee, hara Й“e teskaaki konngol ngol, kaa hara aru e maЙ“Й“e ko araali e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,69,"Kaa Й“e anndaali NulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e faytuЙ“e mo"
  23,70,"Kaa hara Й“e wi'ay feetere no e makko? Ko woni, o addanii Й“e Goonga kan Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e ko aГұuЙ“e Goonga kan"
  23,71,"Sinndo Alqur'aana jokkuno beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin bonayno e Й“en wonuЙ“e e majji, ko woni, Men addaniiЙ“e waaju maЙ“Й“e ngun, kamЙ“e koЙ“e Й—urniiЙ“e gaayi waaju maЙ“Й“e ngun"
  23,72,"Kaa a tori Й“e ngeenaari? [Awa] ko ngeenaari Joomi maaЙ—a ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, ko Kanko woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"
  23,73,"Pellet, an hiЙ—a noddude faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  23,74,"E pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaali Laakara on ko Й“e seluЙ“e e Laawol ngol"
  23,75,"Sinndo Men Yurmino Й“e, Men hunci ko heЙ“i Й“e kon immorde e lorra, Й“e duumotono e nder bewre maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e wemmboo"
  23,76,"GomЙ—ii Men nanngirii Й“e Lepte Й—en, Й“e hoykinanaaki Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e yankinaaki"
  23,77,"Haa si Men udditii e dow maЙ“Й“e dammbugal marungal Lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, e jaka, kamЙ“e e nder Й—um ko Й“e taЖҙii Й“e"
  23,78,"Ko Kanko woni On fuЙ—Й—anЖҠo on nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“erЙ—e Й—en, fanЙ—ii ko yettoton"
  23,79,Ko Kanko woni On TaguЖҠo on ka leydi ko faade ka Makko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on
  23,80,"Ko Kanko woni On Mo no wurna O wara no woodani Mo luutindirgol jemma on e Гұalorma on, enee, kaa on hakkiltah"
  23,81,"Ko woni, Й“e wi'u yeru ko aramЙ“e Й“en wi'unoo kon"
  23,82,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, si men maayii men wonii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, hara menen ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  23,83,"GomЙ—ii men fodanooma Й—um menen e baabiraaЙ“e amen ko adii, Й—um wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  23,84,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo leydi ndin woodani e Й“en wonuЙ“e e mayri, si tawii hiЙ—on anndi"
  23,85,"Aray Й“e wi'a: \"Ko Alla woodani\" maaku: \"Enee, on waajitotaako"
  23,86,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo woni Jom kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e Jom Arsi mawki kin?\" @Corrected"
  23,87,"Aray Й“e wi'a: \"Ko Alla\" maaku: \"Enee, on hulatah [Alla]"
  23,88,"Maaku hommbo woni e Junngo Mu'un Laamu kala huunde hara Kanko hiMo walla O walletaake, si tawii on laatike hiЙ—on anndi"
  23,89,"Aray Й“e wi'a: \"Ko Alla woodani\" maaku: \"Enee, ko honno mbilirteЙ—on"
  23,90,"Ko woni, Men addanii Й“e Goonga kan, pellet kamЙ“e ko Й“e fenuЙ“e"
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o, reweteeЙ—o laataaki wonndude e Makko, e jaka [si waЙ—um waЙ—uno] kala reweteeЙ—o yaadayno e ko o tagi kon, yoga e maЙ“Й“e townitotono e dow yoga. Senayee wonanii Alla e gaayi kon ko Й“e sifotoo"
  23,92,AnnduЙ—o ko wirnii kon e ko seedaa kon O Toowii e gaayi ko Й“e sirkata kon
  23,93,"Maaku: \"Jooma am si A hollii lam ko Й“e fodaa kon"
  23,94,"Jooma am, wata A waЙ—am e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,95,"Pellet, Menen fii yo Men holle ko Men fodi Й“e kon ko Men HattanЙ“e [Й—um]"
  23,96,"DuГұir nden huunde Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude [huunde] bonunde nden, ko Menen Anndi ko Й“e sifoto kon"
  23,97,"Maaku: \"Jooma, mi moolorii Ma immorde e kodooje Seytanuuji Й—in"
  23,98,Mi moolorii Ma Jooma am nde Й—i tawata lam
  23,99,"Haa si maayde arii e goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e nden, o wi'a: \"Jooma am ruttee lam"
  23,100,"Belajo'o men, mi gollay ko moЖҙЖҙi e nder kon ko mi accunoo, Й—um waЙ—ataa, ngol ko kanngol ko kanko wowli ngol, no hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e heedo haa Г‘alnde nde Й“e imminoytee"
  23,101,"Si wuttaama ka alaadu, haray askaaji alah hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nden Г‘alnde, Й“e lanndandirtah"
  23,102,"Kala on mo jisti(teddi) manndake (peesirgal)muuЙ—um, haray ko Й“en Й—on woni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en"
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake [moЖҙЖҙi] muuЙ—um foygitii, (hoyi)haray ko Й“en Й—on woni hayruЙ“e pittaali muuЙ—um, ko ka nder Jahannama woni ko Й“e luttintee"
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e e nder magge ko Й“e ГұirЙ“iniiЙ“e"
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am Й—en laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on fenna Й—e"
  23,106,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii men, men laatinoke yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e"
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin men e magge, si men ruttike hara pellet, menen ko men tooГұuЙ“e"
  23,108,"O Daala: \"Г‘iiЙ“ee e nder magge wata on haalanam"
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii haforan men YurmeЖҠaa men ko An Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  23,110,"JogitiЙ—on Й“e jalnori(jalkigol), haa Й“e yejjintini on jaЕӢta Am, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jala Й“e"
  23,111,"Min Mi yoЙ“ii Й“e hannde sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon, pellet, kamЙ“e ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  23,112,"O Daali: \"No foti heewde ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on ka leydi, limoore duuЙ“i"
  23,113,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maaЙ—um yoga e Гұallal, lanndo limooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,114,"O Daali: \"On ГұiiЙ“aali si wonaa seeЙ—a, sinndo onon on laatino hiЙ—on anndi"
  23,115,"Enee, on sikku wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on ruttetaake faade ka Amen"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii LaamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On, Rewetee- Й—o alah si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  23,117,"Kala nodduЙ—o wonndude e Alla reweteeЙ—o goo, daliil alanah mo e Й—um, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet Kanko, O malnatah heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  23,118,"Maaku: \"Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko An ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  24,1,"Simoore, Men jippinii nde Men farlii nde, Men jippini e nder mayre Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e belajo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jeenoowo on foccee gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e paatawol(looci) teemedere, wata yurmeende maЙ“Й“e nanngu on e fii Diina Alla kan, si tawii on laatike hiЙ—on gomЙ—ini Alla e Г‘alaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol Й“e ngol jamaa immorde e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jeenoowo maaЙ—um sirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resatah mo si wanaa gorko jinoowo maaЙ—um sirkoowo, Й—um harminaama e dow gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  24,4,"E Й“en Й“e no tukka rewЙ“e saЕӢiiЙ“e Й“en refti hara Й“e addaali seedeeЙ“e nayo, haray piyee Й“e paatawol(looci) cappanЙ—e jeetati. Wata on jaЙ“an Й“e seedagol poomaa. ЖҒen Й—on, ko kamЙ“e woni FaasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  24,5,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“aawo Й—um Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  24,6,"E Й“en Й“e no tukka sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en hara laatanaaki Й“e seedeeЙ“e si wanaa wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, ko yo goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kanko ko e goonguЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa"
  24,7,"JowaЙ“un Й—um, wonndema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  24,8,"ЖҒe dunyira e [sonnaajo on] lepte Й—en, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenooЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa"
  24,9,"JowaЙ“un Й—um, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e goonguЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa"
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonndema Alla ko O jaЙ“oowo tuubuubuye Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  24,11,"Pellet, Й“en adduЙ“e penaale Й—en ko Й“e jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on, wata on sikku Й—um ko bone mo'on; ko woni Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere mo'on. No woodani kala neЙ—Й—o immorde e maЙ“Й“e ko o faggitii kon e junuubu, on fawtiiЙ—o mawЙ—um [junuubu on] immorde e maЙ“Й“e, no woodani mo Lepte mawЙ—e"
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde nanuЙ—on Й—um, worЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en e rewЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en Й“e yananee ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi, Й“e wi'a: \"ЖҠum ko penaale Й“annguЙ—e nii"
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde Й“e addata e Й—um seedeeЙ“e nayo, si Й“e addaali seedeeЙ“e Й“en; haray Й“en Й—on, ka Alla ko kamЙ“e woni fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  24,14,Sinndo wonaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e Yurmeende Makko nden e dow mooЙ—on ka aduna e ka laakara Lepte mawЙ—e meemayno on fii kon ko ukkiЙ—on e muuЙ—um
  24,15,"Tuma nde werloraynoЙ—on Й—um Й—ennЙ—e mooЙ—on, wowliron kunnduЙ—e mooЙ—on kon ko ganndal alanah on e muuЙ—um sikkon Й—um kadi ko newiiЙ—um, hara non Й—um ko mawnuЙ—om ka Alla"
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanuЙ—on nde, wi'on: \"Haanaa men nde men wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii Ma, Й—um ko fenaande mawnde nii"
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wata on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  24,18,Alla no Й“annginannde on Aayeeje Й—en Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o
  24,19,"Pellet, Й“en yiЙ—uЙ“e yo bone Й—en saako e [hoore] Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e; no woodani Й“e Lepte muusuЙ—e ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on anndah"
  24,20,"Sinndo wanaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko O NewiiЙ—o Hinndotooao"
  24,21,"Ko onon Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e, wata on jokku Й—ate Seytaane Й—en, kala jokkuЙ—o Й—ate Seytaane Й—en, pellet, o yamiray [mo] ko boni kon e ko aГұaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e mooЙ—on laaЙ“ataano poomaa, kono Alla hiMo laЙ“Й“ina on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  24,22,"Wata joomiraaЙ“e Й“ural ngal e yaajeende nden e mooЙ—on woondu wonndema Й“e okkortaa Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en e feruЙ“e Й“en ka Laawol Alla, yo Й“e yaafo. Kaa on yiЙ—aa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko O Yawtoowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  24,23,"Pellet, Й“en wonuЙ“e tukkude [sonnaaЙ“e] saЕӢiiЙ“e welsindiiЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e huЙ—aama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani Й“e Lepte mawЙ—e"
  24,24,"Г‘alnde seedoytoo e dow maЙ“Й“e Й—enЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko Й“e laatinoo kon hiЙ“e golla"
  24,25,"Nden Г‘alnde Alla huuЙ“inanay Й“e [njoЙ“di] Diina maЙ“Й“e Goongaha kan, Й“e annda pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga ЖҒannguka kan"
  24,26,"RewЙ“e soЙ“uЙ“e Й“en ko fii worЙ“e soЙ“uЙ“e Й“en. WorЙ“e soЙ“uЙ“e Й“en ko fii rewЙ“e soЙ“uЙ“e Й“en. RewЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en ko fii worЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en, worЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en ko fii rewЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en. ЖҒee Й—oo ko hisnaaЙ“e e kon ko Й“e wowlata, no woodani Й“e haforaneede e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—inЙ“e, wata on naatu e cuuЙ—i tanaa cuuЙ—i mo'on Й—in haa duЕӢinoЙ—on salminon e dow yimЙ“e majji Й“en, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Bela jo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,28,"Si on tawaali nder ton goЙ—Й—o, wata on naatu ton haa duЕӢaneЙ—on, si on wi'aama: \"Yiltee\" haray yiltee, ko Й—um Й“uri laaЙ“annde on. Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuuЙ—i Й—i hoЙ—iraaka hara no e nder majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko wonЙ—on e feГұГұinde e ko wonЙ—on e suuЙ—ude"
  24,30,"Maakan worЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en yo Й“e heltu ndarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e reena farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, ko Й—um Й“urata laЙ“Й“innde Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko O HumpitiiЙ—o ko Й“e huuwata"
  24,31,"Maakan rewЙ“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en yo Й“e heltu ndarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e reena farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wata Й“e feГұГұin cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin si wanaa ko feeГұi kon e mayri. Yo Й“e fawu tiggaaje maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka becce maЙ“Й“e, wata Й“e feГұГұinan cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin si wanaa genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maaЙ—um baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um baabiraaЙ“e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um Й“iЙ—Й“e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um Й“iЙ—Й“e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um Й“iЙ—Й“e banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um Й“en Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um Й“en worЙ“e jokkooЙ“e Й“e haaju mun alaa e rewЙ“e, maaЙ—um boobo mo Жҙellitaaki e awraaji sonnaaЙ“e Й“en. Wata Й“e tappindir koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fii yo Annde ko Й“e suuЙ—i kon immorde e cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e. Tuubee ruttoЙ—on ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gomЙ—inЙ“e bela jo'o on malete"
  24,32,"Resinee Й“e resaali Й“en e mooЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en immorde e muccuЙ“e mooЙ—on e horЙ“e mooЙ—on, si Й“e laatike waasuЙ“e Alla alЙ—inay Й“e immorde e ЖҒural Makko ngal, Alla ko O YaajuЙ—o AnnduЙ—o"
  24,33,"ЖҒe heЙ“aali feere resugol Й“en yo Й“e habbo haa Alla alЙ—inira Й“e ЖҒural Makko ngal. ЖҒen wonuЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ude soottaade e Й“en Й“e Гұaame mooЙ—on jeyi, soottaadede Й“e si on anndii e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, jonnee Й“e immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu horЙ“e mooЙ—on Й“en e fii jeeno, si Й“e faandike saЕӢaade, wata on Й—aЙ“Й“u jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuuЙ—o Й“e pellet, Alla Й“aawo baawnugol Й“e ko O Surroowo YurmiteeЙ—o"
  24,34,"GomЙ—ii Men jippinii e mooЙ—on Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e e misal immorde e Й“eya wulinooЙ“e ko adii on e waaju wonannde hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en"
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni Ndaygu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, sifa Ndaygu Makko ngun ko wano tuЙ—Й—ere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e nder biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde huЙ“Й“a immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyankowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyankowal nebban maggal Й—an no Й“adoo jalbude, hay si yiite meemaali Й—an, ndaygu e hoore ndaygu, Alla no fewnira ndaygu Makko ngun on mo O Muuyi, Alla no piyana yimЙ“e Й“en mise, Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde. @Corrected"
  24,36,E nder cuuЙ—i Й—i Alla duЕӢii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde Makko jantee e nder majji Subunhinanee Mo nder majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikiiЙ—e
  24,37,"WorЙ“e Й“e njulaaku e ngeyngu maapintaa Й—um gaayi jaЕӢtagol Alla e Гұimnugol Julde nden e tottu- gol Jakka on, hiЙ“e huli Г‘alaande nde waylitoytoo e muuЙ—um Й“erЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en"
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“oyЙ“e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e gollunoo kon, O Й“eydana Й“e e ЖҒural Makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore"
  24,39,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no wa'i wa merere wonunde e boowal, Й—onЙ—aaЙ—o on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e huunde, o tawa Alla ka Makko O huuЙ“inana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O YaawuЙ—o Hasboore. @Corrected"
  24,40,"MaaЙ—um ko wano niЙ“e e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo benpeЖҙЖҙe no dow maggo benpeЖҙЖҙe no dow majje duule, niЙ“e yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o Й“adotaako yi'ugol ngo. On mo Alla waЙ—anaali ndaygu hara o alaa ndaygu"
  24,41,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli Й—in kadi ko saffiniiЙ—i? Gooto kala e Й—ii gomЙ—ii anndii julde mu'un nden e subuhinaali mu'un Й—in, Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e Huuwata"
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko faade ka Alla woni waЙ—tinirde nden"
  24,43,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira nde, refti O waЙ—a nde fawondirnde hiЙ—a yi'a toЙ“o ngon no yalta e nder mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e nder mayre marmalle hiMo hewtina Й—e on mo O Muuyi, hiMo pottina Й—e on mo O Muuyi? Ndaneeri maЖҙe mayre no do'a naЙ“ude giiЙ—e Й—en"
  24,44,"Alla hiMo waylita jemma on e Гұalorma on, pellet, na wonii e Й—um tasakuyee wonannde joomiraaЙ“e giiЙ—e Й“en"
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala daabe hun immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muuЙ—um, no e majji yaarooji koyЙ—e muuЙ—m no e majji kadi yaarooji [koyЙ—e] nayi. Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi, pellet, Alla ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  24,46,"GomЙ—ii Men jippinii Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, Alla no fewna on mo O muuyii faade e Laawol foccii ngol"
  24,47,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, men Й—oftike, refti huccita fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“aawo Й—um, Й“en wonaali gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  24,48,"Si Й“e noddaama faade ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, tawa fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e"
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kamЙ“e mari goonga kan, Й“e aray ka makko ko Й“e Й—oftiiЙ“e"
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, kaa Й“e sikkiti, kaa Й“e hulu wata Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on tooГұu Й“e? Ko woni, Й“ee ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en si Й“e noddaama faade ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ko nde Й“e wi'ata: \"Men nanii men Й—oftike.\" ЖҒen Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  24,52,"Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on o huli Alla o rentii [e Lepte Makko Й—en] haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  24,53,"ЖҒe woondiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje maЙ“Й“e, si a yamirii Й“e ma Й“e yaltu sanne. Maaku: \"wata on woondu, Й—oftaare no anndaa, pellet, Alla ko humpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  24,54,"Maaku: \"ЖҠoftee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on\". Si Й“e huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda Й—on kon, si on Й—oftike mo on feeway, fawaaki NulaaЙ—o on si wanaa yottinngol Й“anngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e e mooЙ—on Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in O lontinay Й“e ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non Й“en adiiЙ“e Й“e, ma O weeЙ“inan Й“e diina maЙ“Й“e ka O welanaa Й“e, ma O wattitan Й“e Й“aawo kulol maЙ“Й“e ngol hoolaare, Yo Й“e rewam wata Й“e sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yedduЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  24,56,"Г‘iiЙ“ee e Julde totton Jakka on Й—oftoЙ—on kadi NulaaЙ—o on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“e laawoto ka leydi, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—inЙ“e, yo sakkintino e mooЙ—on Й“en Й“e Гұaame mooЙ—on jeyi, e Й“en Й“e yottaaki koyЙ—ol immorde e mooЙ—on, laabi tati ko adii Julde Peeral nden, e tuma wallinton conci mooЙ—on ka njolloro e ka Й“aawo Julde geeЖҙe ko awraaji mooЙ—on tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki Й“e Й“aawo majji, jinndooЙ“e hakkunde mooЙ—on, yoga e mooЙ—on e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla Й“anngini- rani on Aayeeje Й—en Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  24,59,"Si sukaaЙ“e mooЙ—on yottike kellefuyee, yo Й“e sakkitinono wano duЕӢinornoo non Й“en adiiЙ“e Й“e, ko wano nii Alla Й“annginiranta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  24,60,"E sonnaaЙ“e jottiiЙ“e Й“en, Й“en Й“e jortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e wallinta conci maЙ“Й“e Й—in hara Й“e wonaa feГұГұinЙ“e cuЙ—aari, ko nde Й“e nantotoo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e, Alla ko O Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  24,61,"Bakkaatu fawaaki bunЙ—u on, bakkaatu fawaaki laЖҙuЙ—o on, bakkaatu fawaaki nawnuЙ—o on, fawaaki e wonkiiji mooЙ—on nde Гұaamoton ka cuuЙ—i mooЙ—on maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i baabiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i neeniraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i musiЙ—Й“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i banndiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i bappiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i yaayiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—om ka cuuЙ—i kaawiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i neeniraaЙ“e mooЙ—on ka dewol, maaЙ—um Й—in Й—i jogiЙ—on cottirЙ—e muuЙ—um, maaЙ—um giЙ—o mooЙ—on. Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde hawtoton Гұaamon maaЙ—um Гұaamon ko on sertuЙ“e. Si on naatay e cuuЙ—i salminee e dow wonkiiji mooЙ—on, hiwraango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laaЙ“ungo, ko wano nii Alla Й“annguniranta on Aayeeje Й—en belajo'o onon on haqqilay"
  24,62,"Anndu gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ko Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, si Й“e laatike hiЙ“e wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftuЙ—o, Й“e yahatah haa Й“e duЕӢinoo e makko, pellet, Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irayЙ“e ma duЕӢayee ko Й“en Й—on woni gomЙ—inЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“irii ma duЕӢayee fii yoga e fiyaake maЙ“Й“e, duЕӢano on mo yiЙ—uЙ—aa [duЕӢanaade] e maЙ“Й“e, insinanoЙ—aa Й“e ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  24,63,"Wata on waЙ—u noddugol NulaaЙ—o on hakkunde mooЙ—on wano noddugol yoga e mooЙ—on yoga. GomЙ—ii Alla no Anndi Й“en sortotooЙ“e e mooЙ—on e moltagol, Й“en wonuЙ“e lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo Й“e rento fii wata fitina hiЙ“u Й“e maaЙ—um Lempte muusuЙ—e heЙ“a Й“e"
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gomЙ—ii hiMo Anndi ko wonuЙ—on e hoore mu'un kon, Г‘alnde Й“e ruttetee faade ka Makko O yeetoo Й“e ko Й“e gollunoo kon. Alla ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  25,1,Mawnii On JippinЙ—o Serndoore nden e dow jeyaaЙ—o Makko on fii yo wonan winndire nden jertinoowo
  25,2,"On Mo woodanii Й—um Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, o jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o laatanaaki Mo kadi kafidaaЙ—o ka Laamu. O tagii kala huunde O eЙ“Й“indiinde e eЙ“Й“ugol"
  25,3,"ЖҒe jogitii gaanin Makko reweteeЙ—i Й—i tagaani huunde kannji ko Й—i tagaaЙ—i, Й—i maranah ko'e majji lorra wanaa nafa Й—i marah mayde wanaa ngurndan wanaa Immital"
  25,4,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e wi'i: \"Ndee [Alqur'aanaare] wonaali si wonah pene Й—i o fefindii Й—um, walli mo e hoore majje yimЙ“e goo\". GomЙ—ii Й“e addii tooГұe e bagamma"
  25,5,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko nde tinndi adinooЙ“e o winnditi Й—i hiЙ—i fidanee mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  25,6,"Maaku: \"Jippinii nde On AnnduЙ—o ngunndoo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, Kanko O Laatike Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  25,7,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko heЙ“i oo NulaaЙ—o, himo Гұaama Гұaametee himo yaha kadi ka lokooji(jeereeji)В°? Ko haanunoo ko nde jippintee e makko Maalaa'ikaajo o laatoo wonndude e makko jertinoowo"
  25,8,"MaaЙ—um werlee e makko ngalu, maaЙ—um laatanoo mo ngesa o Гұaama e mabba. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"On jokkaali si wonaa gorko mbilЙ—aaЙ—o"
  25,9,"Ndaarii [yo NulaaЙ—o] ko honno Й“e piyiranay maa mise, Й“e majjii Й“e hattantaake [heЙ“ude] laawol"
  25,10,"Mawnii On tawЙ—o si O Muuyii O waЙ—ane moЖҙЖҙere, no e Й—um gese no ila ley majje canЙ—e Й—en, O waЙ—ane kadi kuЙ“eeje"
  25,11,"Ko woni, Й“e fennu Darngo ngo, Men heblorani Й“en fennuЙ“e Darngal ngal Yiite ooyunge"
  25,12,Si nge yi'ii Й“e immorde e nokkuure woЙ—Й—unde nananee nge tikkere e faraango
  25,13,"Si Й“e werlaama e nder magge e nokkuure Й“ittunde ko Й“e sinndindiraaЙ“e, Й“e nodda ton halakuyee"
  25,14,"Wata on noddu hannde halakuyee gooto, noddee halakuyeeji buy"
  25,15,"Maaku: \"Enee, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Aljanna luttoowo on, on mo hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en fodaa? O laatanike Й“e njoЙ“di e wattinirde"
  25,16,"No woodani Й“e nder ton ko Й“e welaa, ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e, Й—um laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a Fodoore lannditeteende"
  25,17,"Г‘alnde O mooЙ“idoyta Й“e e ko Й“e rewaynoo kon gaanin Alla, O Daala: \"Enee, ko onon majjini Й“ee jeyaaЙ“e Am, kaa ko kamЙ“e majji Laawol ngol"
  25,18,"ЖҠi wi'a: \"Senayee wonanii Ma, haananah men nde men jogitotoo gaanin MaaЙ—a immorde e reweteeЙ“e, kono, A dakmintinii Й“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haa Й“e yejjiti waaju ngun Й“e laatii yimЙ“e halkiiЙ“e"
  25,19,"GomЙ—ii Й“e fennii on, sabu ko wi'oton kon, Й“e hattantah yiltugol [Lepte Й—en] wanaa wallude, kala tooГұuЙ—o e mooЙ—on Men meeЙ—inay mo Lepte mawЙ—e"
  25,20,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ“e si wanaa kamЙ“e hiЙ“e nafoo Гұaametee hiЙ“e seenoo kadi ka luumaaji, Men waЙ—i yoga e mooЙ—on fitina yoga, fii yo on muГұГұo. Joomi maaЙ—a laatike ko O Yi'oowo"
  25,21,"ЖҒen Й“e jortaaki hawroyde e Amen wi'i: \"Ko hannoo jippinee e makko Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, maaЙ—um men yi'a Joomi amen?\" GomЙ—ii Й“ee mawnintinike ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e townitii townitaare mawnunde"
  25,22,"Г‘alnde Й“e yi'oyta Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en weltaare alanaa bomЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘alnde, Й“e wi'a: \"Heedo heedaango"
  25,23,"Men ardini faade e ko Й“e gollunoo kon immorde e gollal, Men waЙ—i ngal punndi caraandi"
  25,24,YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en nden Г‘alnde Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ГұiiЙ“irde Й“uri labeede kadi Гұallirde
  25,25,E Г‘alnde nde kummu ngun seekorta duule Й—en Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en jippinee jippineede
  25,26,"Laamu GoongAawu ngun nden Г‘alnde ko Hinnorante On ngu woodani, laatoo Г‘alnde saЙ—tunde e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  25,27,"E Г‘alnde tooГұuЙ—o on ЕӢatoyta junngo makko ngon, o wi'a: \"Eeh jalla min, mi jogitino wonndude e NulaaЙ—o on Laawol"
  25,28,"Eeh bone am haaniino min, mi jogitanooki kaariijo sehilaajo"
  25,29,"GomЙ—ii o majjinii lam gaayi Deftere nden Й“aawo nde arii a am, Seytaane laatike ko o jaasinoowo neЙ—Й—anke on"
  25,30,"NulaaЙ—o on maaka: \"Ko ann yo Jooma pellet, yimЙ“e am Й“en Й“e jogitike ndee Alqur'aanaare wikkaande(accaande)"
  25,31,"Ko wano nii, Men waЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo immorde e bonЙ“e Й“en, Joomi maaЙ—a yonii Fewnoowo e Ballo"
  25,32,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e wi'i: \"Ko hanno Alqur'aanaare nden jippinee e makko e jumla gooto?\" ЖҠum ko wano nii, fii yo Men tabintinir nde Й“ernde maaЙ—a nden Men rewnindira nde rewnindirgol"
  25,33,"ЖҒe addantaa ma misal, si wanaa Men addanii ma Goonga kan e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude firo"
  25,34,"ЖҒen mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e e dow geece muuЙ—um faade ka Jahannama, ko Й“en Й—on woni Й“uruЙ“e bonde nokkuure e Й“uruЙ“e majjude kade laawol"
  25,35,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Men waЙ—i wonndude e makko MusiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna ballo"
  25,36,"Men Daali: \"Yahee ka Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Men yirbini Й“e yirbinndee"
  25,37,"E yimЙ“e Nuuhu tuma nde Й“e fennunoo NulaaЙ“e Й“en, Men yooli Й“e Men waЙ—i Й“e maande fii yimЙ“e Й“en, Men heblani tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Lepte muusuЙ—e"
  25,38,E AadinkooЙ“e Й“en e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e Й“unndu ndun e gire Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e hakkunde Й—um
  25,39,"Gooto kala e maЙ“e Men piyani Й—um mise, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e men halki Й—um halkugol"
  25,40,"GomЙ—ii Й“e arii e nden saare toЙ“aande toЙ“o bonngo. Kaa Й“e laataaki hiЙ“e yi'a Й—e? Ko woni, Й“e laatinoke Й“e jortaaki Immotal"
  25,41,"Si Й“e yi'ii ma, Й“e jogitotaako ma si wanaa jalnori. Enee, ko oo Alla Immini NulaaЙ—o"
  25,42,Fii kala hari o Й“adike(Й—esi) majjinnde en gaayi reweteeЙ—i me'en Й—in si tawiino wanaa ko muГұГұi Й—en kon e dow majji. Aray Й“e anndoyat tuma Й“e yi'ata Lepte Й—en ko hommbo Й“urЙ—o majjude laawol
  25,43,"Enee, a tinii on jogitiiЙ—o reweteeЙ—o makko on beleeЙ—e makko Й—en. E hara ko an laatotoo e dow makko fawtiiЙ—o"
  25,44,"Kaa a sikku wonnde ko Й“uri heewude e maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e nana maaЙ—um hiЙ“e hakkila? Anndu kamЙ“e Й“e wonaali si wanaa wano neemoraaЙ—i, toode, ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude laawol"
  25,45,"Kaa a tinaali faade e Joomi maaЙ—a honno O fontiri Й—owdi ndin? Sinndo O Muuyuno O waЙ—ayno ndi deeЖҙundi, refti Men waЙ—i naange ngen tinndinaynge e mayri"
  25,46,Refti Men tami ndi ka Amen tamannde newiinde
  25,47,"Ko Kanko woni On waЙ—anЙ—o on jemma on koltu e Й—oyngol ngol fowtere, O waЙ—i Гұalorma on ngal saakorЙ—o"
  25,48,"Ko Kanko woni On accituЙ—o keni Й—in ko Й—i weltinooji hakkunde Yurmeende Makko nden, Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam laaЙ“uЙ—am"
  25,49,"Fii yo Men wurnitir Й—am leydi maayundi, Men yarnaЙ—am kadi kon ko Men tagi neemoraaЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e"
  25,50,"GomЙ—ii Men fensitii nde hakkunde maЙ“Й“e fii yo Й“e waajito, salii Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en si wanaa yeddugol"
  25,51,Sinndo Men Muuyuno Men Nulayno e kala saare jertinoowo
  25,52,Wata a Й—ofto yedduЙ“e Й“en haЙ“ e maЙ“Й“e hare jihaadi mawnde
  25,53,"Ko Kanko woni On jillindirЙ—o maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i, ngooЙ—oo ko welungo Жҙem ngooЙ—oo kadi ko lamЙ—amwo haaЙ—ungo tak, O waЙ—i wirngallo hakkunde majje, e heedo heedaango"
  25,54,"Ko Kanko woni on TaguЙ—o Й“anndunke immorde e ndiyam Й—am, O waЙ—i mo dammbe e esiraawo, Joomi maaЙ—a laatike ko O HattanЙ—o"
  25,55,"HiЙ“e rewa gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa Й“e lorrataa Й“e, yedduЙ—o on laatike ko o teeЙ—iiЙ—o Joomi makko"
  25,56,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa ko a weltinoowo e jartinoowo
  25,57,"Maaku: \"Mi naamaaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di si wanaa on yiЙ—uЙ—o jogitaade faade ka Joomi makko Laawol"
  25,58,"Wakkilo e On WuuruЙ—o Mo maayataa subuhinoЙ—aa wonndunde e yettugol Mo, O yonii e Й—um HumpitiiЙ—o junubaaji jeyaaЙ“e Makko"
  25,59,"On TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, e nder balЙ—e jeego'o refti O fotondiri ka dow Arsi, Hinnorante On lanndo Mo ko O HumpitiiЙ—o. @Corrected"
  25,60,"Si wi'anaama Й“e: \"Sujjanee Hinnorante On\" ЖҒe wi\"a: \"Ko hommbo woni Hinnorante On? Enee, hara men sujjanay kon ko yamirЙ—aa men?\" ЖҠum Й“eydi Й“e foЙ—Й—itaare"
  25,61,Mawnii On waЙ—uЙ—o ka kammu burjuuji(buurti) o waЙ—i e nder majji pitilol e leelewal jalbungal
  25,62,Ko Kanko woni On waЙ—uЙ—o jemma on e Гұalorma on lontondirayЙ—i fii on faandiiЙ—o annditugol maaЙ—um o faandii jarnugol
  25,63,"E jeyaaЙ“e Hinnorante On, Й“en yahooЙ“e ka leydi ko no newiri, si majjuЙ“e Й“en ewnike Й“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Kisiyee\". @Corrected"
  25,64,"E Й“en waalooЙ“e sujjannde Joomi maЙ“Й“e e daragol [juula]"
  25,65,"E Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen woЙ—Й—intinan men Lepte Jahannama Й—en, pellet, Lepte magge Й—en ko duumiiЙ—e"
  25,66,"Pellet, Й—en bonii ГұiiЙ“irde e darorde"
  25,67,"E Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e nafkii Й“e fantintaa Й“e Й“ittintaa kadi, [Й“e] woni ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e hakkunde Й—um"
  25,68,"E Й“en Й“e rewaali wonndude e Alla reweteeЙ—o goo, Й“e waraali fittaandu ki Alla harmini kin si wanaa sabu goonga, hara Й“e jeenataa. Mo waЙ—ii Й—um o hawray e junuubu"
  25,69,"Sowanoyte mo Lepte Й—en Г‘alnde Darngal, o luttinoyee e nder majje ko o hoynaaЙ—o"
  25,70,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—ini Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, haray Й“en Й—on Allalomtinay bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in moЖҙЖҙi. Alla wonii ko O Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  25,71,"Kala tuubuЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi haray pellet, kanko o ruttoto ka Alla ko o jaЙ“anaaЙ—o tuubuubuyee"
  25,72,"E Й“en Й“e seeditotaako penaale Й—en si Й“e rewii ka rayrayti Й—in [wowletee] Й“e feЖҙЖҙay ko tedduЙ“e @Corrected"
  25,73,E Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e waajoraama Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e hippotaako e dow majje ko Й“e faaЙ—uЙ“e e wumuЙ“e
  25,74,"E Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen, okku men immorde e sonnaaЙ“e amen e geЙ—alЙ“e amen Й“uuЙ“endan gite, waЙ—aa men wonannde hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en ГұentinteeЙ“e"
  25,75,"ЖҒenЙ—on Й“e yoЙ“oyte huЙ“eere nden sabu ko Й“e muГұГұii kon, Й“e hawroya nder ton e hiwraango e salminaango"
  25,76,Ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e nder ton moЖҙЖҙii ГұiiЙ“irde e darorde
  25,77,"Maaku: \"JeyЙ—o lam On haajaaka e mooЙ—on sinndo wanaano du'aaji mo'on Й—in, gomЙ—ii on fenniino aray Й—e laatoo duumiiЙ—e [Lepte laakara]"
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  26,2,ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Deftere Й“anngunde nden
  26,3,Belajo'o an a tampiniray hoore maaЙ—a kin fii Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e
  26,4,Si Men Muuyii Men jippinay e maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu Aaya daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Гұalla ko Й—e yankinaniiЙ—e mo
  26,5,Arataa e maЙ“Й“e waaju immorde ka Hinnorante On fuЙ—Й—aangu si wanaa Й“e laatike Й—uuriiЙ“e ngu
  26,6,GomЙ—ii Й“e fennii aroyay e maЙ“Й“e kabaruuji ko Й“e laatinoo koЙ“e jalkitano
  26,7,"Enee, Й“e yi'aali faade e leydi ndin, no foti hewde ko Men fuЙ—ini e mayri immorde e kala noone tedduЙ—o"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o On"
  26,10,"JaЕӢto tuma nde Joomi maaЙ—a noddunoo Muusaa, Й—um woni aru e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,11,"YimЙ“e Fir'awna, kaa on hulataa"
  26,12,"O maaki: \"Joom am , min miЙ—o huli wata Й“e fennam"
  26,13,"ЖҒernde am nden Й“ittoo hara Й—emngal am ngal wellitaaki, awa Nulu Haaruuna"
  26,14,No woodani Й“e e dow am bakkaatu miЙ—o huli fii wata Й“e waram
  26,15,"O Daali: \"Wanaa non, yahee onon Й—iЙ—o, MenЙ—en wonndi e mooЙ—on ko Men heЙ—iiЙ“e"
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna wi'on: \"Menen dey ko men NulaaЙ“e Jooma winndere nden"
  26,17,ЖҠum woni accitu Й“iЙ—Й“e Isra'iila Й“en wonndude e amen
  26,18,"O wi'i: \"Enee, men ne'aano ma ka amen Й—oo hari ko a boobo, ГұiiЙ“uЙ—aa ka amen Й—oo duuЙ“i e ngurndam maaЙ—am"
  26,19,"GolluЙ—aa gollal maaЙ—a ngal gollunoЙ—aa ngal, an ko e yedduЙ“e Й“en jeyaЙ—aa"
  26,20,"O maaki: \"Mi waЙ—ii Й—um, ontuma hara min ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi hulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal O waЙ—in mi jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,22,"ЖҠum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi Й—um, fii a maccinЙ—inii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nden"
  26,24,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaaЙ“e"
  26,25,"O wi'ani Й“en wonuЙ“e banЕӢe makko: \"Enee; on heЙ—ataako"
  26,26,"O maaki: \"Joomi mooЙ—on e Jooma baabiraaЙ“e ardiiЙ“e Й“en"
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Pellet, NulaaЙ—o mooЙ—on on NulaaЙ—o faade e mooЙ—on ko o feetuЙ—o"
  26,28,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma funnaange e hirnaange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike hakkilooЙ“e"
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Mi woondii si jogitike reweteeЙ—o tanaa am, mi waЙ—ete jeyaaЙ—o dummbaaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,30,"O maaki: \"Enee, hay si mi addanii ma huunde Й“anngunde"
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Awa addu Й—um, si tawii ko e goongu Й“en jeyaaЙ—aa"
  26,32,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande(ngoolwa) Й“annguba"
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaarooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngun fee makko: \"Pellet, ooЙ—oo ko mbileejo heewuЙ—o ganndal"
  26,35,Himo faandii yaltinirgol on ka leydi mooЙ—on mbilewu makko ngun. Ko hunЙ—un yamirЙ—on
  26,36,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musiЙ—Й—o makko on, nulaa e ca'e Й—en mooЙ“ooЙ“e (mbile)"
  26,37,ЖҒe addane kala mbileejo annduЙ—o
  26,38,MbileeЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“aa fii fodoore Гұalaande anndaande
  26,39,"YimЙ“e Й“en wi'anaa: \"Taw si onon ko on mooЙ“ike(ndenndi)"
  26,40,"Belajo'o menen men jokkay mbileeЙ“e Й“en, si Й“e laatike ko kamЙ“e woni fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbileeЙ“e Й“en arunoo; Й“e wi'ani Fir'awna: \"Enee, hara no woodani men njoЙ“di si tawii ko men woni fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  26,42,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray ontuma on jeyaama e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani Й“e: \"mbeddee, ko werloton kon"
  26,44,"ЖҒe liЙ“i Й“okkoy maЙ“Й“e koy e cawoy maЙ“Й“e kon, Й“e wi'i: \"Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko menen woni foolooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,45,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun, tawi kayru hindu moЙ—a ko Й“e fefindii kon"
  26,46,MbileeЙ“e Й“en suuyi Й“e sujji
  26,47,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men gomЙ—inii JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  26,48,JeyЙ—o Muusaa e Haaruuna
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, on gomЙ—inay mo, ko adii mi duЕӢanaade on? Pellet, ko kanko woni mawЙ—o mooЙ—on anndinЙ—o on on mbilewu ngun, kono aray anndon, mami taЖҙu juuЙ—e mooЙ—on e koyЙ—e mooЙ—on [taЖҙa] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fow mooЙ—on"
  26,50,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Tanaa alaa, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo"
  26,51,"Menen meЙ—en tamЖҙinii nde Joomi amen yawtani men goopi amen Й—in,tawde men laatike adiiЙ“e gomЙ—innde Й“en"
  26,52,"Men Wahayini faade e Muusaa: \"ЖҠum woni roЖҙidu e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en. Pellet, onon ko on jokkiteteeЙ“e"
  26,53,Fir'awna nuli ka ca'e mooЙ“ooЙ“e
  26,54,"[O wi'i:] Pellet, Й“ee ko Й“e mojobun pamarun"
  26,55,"Pellet, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e tikkinnde men"
  26,56,Enen non en fow ko en rentiiЙ“e
  26,57,Men yaltini Й“e immorde e gese e canЙ—i
  26,58,E ngaluuji e ГұiiЙ“irde teddunde
  26,59,"Ko wano nii, Men ronini Й—um Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  26,60,ЖҒe jokkiЙ“e ka puЙ—al
  26,61,"Tuma nde jamaaji Й—in Й—in yi'ndirnoo, yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en wi'i: \"Enen en hewtoyte"
  26,62,"O maaki: \"ЖҠum waЙ—ataa, pellet, Joomi am no wonndi e am O fewnay lam"
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa, Й—um woni piyir tuggordu maaЙ—a ndun maayo ngon, ngo seekii seekol kala seekol na foti e tulde mawnde"
  26,64,Men Й“anni ton heddiiЙ“e Й“en
  26,65,Men danndi Muusaa e wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en fow maЙ“Й“e
  26,66,Refti Men yooli heddii Й“e Й“en
  26,67,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,68,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,69,Janngan Й“e kumpital fii Ibraahiima
  26,70,Tuma nde o wi'annoo ben makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en; ko honЙ—um rewoton
  26,71,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"MeЙ—en rewude sanamuuji, men Гұallay ufinanaade Й—i"
  26,72,"O maaki: \"Yalli hiЙ—i nanana on, nde noddoton"
  26,73,Kaa hiЙ—i nafa on maaЙ—um Й—i lorra on
  26,74,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko woni, men tawii baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en konii Й“e golliraynoo"
  26,75,"O maaki: \"Enee, on yi'ii kon ko wonuЙ—on e rewude"
  26,76,Onon e baabiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on adinooЙ“e Й“en
  26,77,"Pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e ayЙ“e am, si wanaa Jooma winndire nden"
  26,78,"On TaguЙ—o lam, ko Kanko fewnata lam"
  26,79,On ko Kanko Гұamminta lam O yarnan-mi
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii, ko Kanko sellinta lam"
  26,81,E On warayЙ—o lam refti O wurnitan mi
  26,82,"On Mo mi tamЖҙinii kadi nde O yaafatoomi goopi am Й—in Г‘alnde [njoЙ“di] Diina kan"
  26,83,"Joomam, okkam Ganndal wattidaa mi e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  26,84,WaЙ—anaa lam Й—emngal goongungal ka sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en
  26,85,WaЙ—aa mi jeyaaЙ—o e ronooЙ“e Aljanna Neemaaji Й—in
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaaЙ—o e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  26,87,Wata A hersinoyam Г‘alnde Й“e Immital
  26,88,Г‘alnde nde jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e nafataa
  26,89,Si wanaa on arduЙ—o ka Alla e Й“ernde hisunde
  26,90,Aljanna on Й“atinanee hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en
  26,91,Jahiim ngen feГұГұinanee bewЙ“e Й“en
  26,92,"ЖҒe wi'nee: \"Honto woni ko laatinoЙ—on kon hiЙ—on rewa"
  26,93,Gaanin Alla? Taw si Й—i wallay on maaЙ—um Й—i wallay hoore majji
  26,94,ЖҒe hippee e nder magge kanЙ“e e bewЙ“e Й“en
  26,95,E konnuuji ibliisa Й—in Й—i fow majji
  26,96,ЖҒe wi'i tawi kamЙ“e hiЙ“e wennjondira nder ton
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla, men woniino e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  26,98,Tuma nde men fonnunoo on e Jooma winndere nden
  26,99,Majjinaali men si wonaa bonЙ“e Й“en
  26,100,Alanaa men tefooЙ“e
  26,101,Wanaa kadi giЙ—o ГұallamЙ“ereejo(tigi tigi)
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men rutteede, men laatoo jeyaaЙ“e e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,105,YimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en fenni NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on hoolaaЙ—o"
  26,108,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,110,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,111,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gomЙ—inte, jaasuЙ“e Й“en no jokkumaa"
  26,112,"O maaki: \"Ko honЙ—um woni ganndal am e ko Й“e wonunoo e gollude"
  26,113,"Hasboore maЙ“Й“e nden fawaaki si wanaa e Joomi am, sinndo hiЙ—on so'aynoo"
  26,114,Min mi wonaali raЙ—otooЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en
  26,115,Min mi wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o
  26,116,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondii si a accaali an Nuuhu, ma a laato sanne jeyaaЙ—o e rajmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  26,117,"O maaki: \"Joom am, pellet, yimЙ“e am Й“en Й“e fenni lam"
  26,118,"Г‘aawu hakkunde am e maЙ“Й“e Гұaawoore, danndaa mi e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e am jeyaaЙ“e e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  26,119,Men danndi mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko ka nder laana Жҙoltiika(loowaaka)
  26,120,"Refti Men yooli Й“aawo [maЙ“Й“e] heddiiЙ“e Й“en"
  26,121,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,122,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,123,AadinkooЙ“e Й“en fenniino NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,124,"Tuma nde Huudu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,125,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on hoolaaЙ—o"
  26,126,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,127,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,128,"Enee, on mahay maande e kala tulde hiЙ—on fija"
  26,129,"JogitoЙ—on kuЙ“eeje a wi'ayma onon ko on luttinteeЙ“e [ka aduna]"
  26,130,"Si on jaggitii, janggiton ko ndunndarankooЙ“e"
  26,131,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,132,Hulee On Й“eydirЙ—o on ko annduЙ—on
  26,133,O Й“eydiri on neemoraaЙ—i e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e
  26,134,E gese e canЙ—i
  26,135,"[O maaki] min dey, miЙ—o hulani on Lepte Г‘alaande mawnde"
  26,136,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"No fotana men ter, si a waajike maaЙ—um si a laataaki jeyaaЙ—o e waajotooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,137,"Pellet, Й—um wonaali si wanaa jikku adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,138,Menen men wonaali leptoyteeЙ“e
  26,139,"ЖҒe fenni mo, Men halki Й“e. Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,141,SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en fenniino NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,143,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on hoolaaЙ—o"
  26,144,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,145,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,146,"Enee, hara on accete e koo ko woni Й—oo ko on hooliiЙ“e"
  26,147,E nder gese e canЙ—i
  26,148,E remuruuji e tamarooje hara dukke majje ko Й“ennduЙ—um
  26,149,"HiЙ—on lesa pelle Й—en [waЙ—on] cuuЙ—i ko on haawitiiЙ“e"
  26,150,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,151,Wata on Й—ofto yamaruyee fantinooЙ“e Й“en
  26,152,ЖҒen bonnooЙ“e ka leydi hara Й“e moЖҙЖҙintaa
  26,153,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaaЙ—o mbilaaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,154,"An a wonaali si wanaa Й“anndunke yeru amen, awa addu Aaya, si tawii a laatike jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  26,155,"O maaki: \"MbaaЙ—oo ko naaqawa, no woodani mba yaramnde, no woodani on onon kadi yaramnde Гұalaande anndaande"
  26,156,"Wata on memir mba ko boni, sakko nannga on Lepte Г‘alnde Mawnde"
  26,157,"ЖҒe mborii mba, Й“e wonti nimsuЙ“e"
  26,158,"Lepte Й—en nanngi Й“e. Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,159,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,160,YimЙ“e Luutu Й“en fenni NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,161,"Tuma nde Luutu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,162,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on hoolaaЙ—o"
  26,163,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,164,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,165,"Enee, on aray worЙ“e Й“en immorde e winndere nden"
  26,166,"ЖҠalon ko Joomi mooЙ—on tagani on kon immorde e sonnaaЙ“e mooЙ—on? Ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e jaggituЙ“e"
  26,167,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondii si a accaali an Luutu, ma a laato sanne jeyaaЙ—o e yaltiteeЙ“e Й“en"
  26,168,"O maaki: \"Min dey, miЙ—o jeyaa e aГұuЙ“e Й“en golle mooЙ—on Й—en"
  26,169,"Jooma, danndam min e Й“eynguure am nden kon ko Й“e gollata"
  26,170,"Men danndi mo e Й“eynguure makko nden, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  26,171,Si wonaa jiidiraare(nayeejo debbo) nden ka halkaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,172,Refti Men oЖҙЖҙi heddii Й“e Й“en
  26,173,"Men toЙ“ini e dow maЙ“Й“e toЙ“o, bonii toЙ“o jertinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,174,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,175,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,176,YimЙ“e fitaare(sutu) nden fenniino NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  26,177,"Tuma nde Su'aybu wi'annoo Й“e: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,178,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on hoolaaЙ—o"
  26,179,Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi
  26,180,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,181,"Humnee Й“etu ngun, wata on laato jeyaaЙ“e e uytooЙ“e Й“en"
  26,182,Manndikiree(peesre) manndikirЙ—e feewuЙ—e Й—en
  26,183,"Wata on ustan yimЙ“e Й“en piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wata on lancito ka leydi hara ko on bonnooЙ“e"
  26,184,"Hulee On TaguЙ—o on, o tagu adinoongu ngun"
  26,185,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaaЙ—o mbilЙ—aaЙ“e Й“en"
  26,186,"An a wonaali si wanaa Й“anndunke yeru amen, tawde meЙ—en jikkumaa ko a jeyaaЙ—o e fenuЙ“e Й“en"
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  26,188,"O maaki: \"Ko Joomi am woni AnnduЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  26,189,"ЖҒe fenni mo, nanngi Й“e Lepte Гұalaande Й—owdiinde nden. Pellet, Й—en laatino Lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gomЙ—inЙ“e"
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Jooma winndere nden"
  26,193,Jippinii nde Ruuhu hoolaaЙ—o on
  26,194,Ka Й“ernde maaЙ—a fii yo a laato jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e Й“en
  26,195,E Й—emngal Aarabu Й“anngungal
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hinde ka Й—eri aranЙ“e Й“en"
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki Й“e Maande, nde tawata anndiino nde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila annduЙ“e Й“en"
  26,198,Sinndo Men jippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyankooЙ“e Й“en
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e laatotaako gomЙ—inЙ“e nde"
  26,200,Ko wano nii Men naadiri Й—um e Й“erЙ—e bonЙ“e Й“en
  26,201,"ЖҒe gomЙ—intaa nde, haa Й“e yi'a Lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  26,202,"ЖҠe ara e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee, hara Й“e so'aa"
  26,203,"Sakko Й“e wi'a: \"Taw si ko men nennanteeЙ“e"
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte Amen Й—en Й“e heГұorta"
  26,205,A tinii si Men dakmitii Й“e duuЙ“i
  26,206,Refti ari e maЙ“Й“e kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e fodee
  26,207,Nafaali Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo kon hiЙ“e dakmitoo
  26,208,"Men halkaali saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde jertinooЙ“e"
  26,209,"[ЖҠum] ko waaju, Men laataaki tooГұooЙ“e"
  26,210,Wanaa seytanuuji Й—in jippini nde
  26,211,"[ЖҠum] haananaaЙ—i, Й—i hattantaake kadi"
  26,212,"Pellet, kannji ko Й—i follateeЙ—i gaayi heЙ—agol ngol"
  26,213,"Wata a noddu reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla, sakko laatoЙ—aa jeyaaЙ—o e LepteteeЙ“e Й“en"
  26,214,Jertin gorol maaЙ—a Й“urЙ“e Й“adaade Й“en
  26,215,"LesЙ—inan balbe maaЙ—en, wonannde Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma immorde e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  26,216,"Si Й“e yeddii ma, haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi danndiiЙ—o kon ko golloton"
  26,217,Hoolor On TedduЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o
  26,218,On SutiiЙ—o ma fewndo darotoЙ—aa
  26,219,E waylitogol maaЙ—a e hakkunde sujjooЙ“e Й“en
  26,220,"Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o On"
  26,221,Taw si mi humpitay on ko e hommbo Seytanuuji Й—in jippotoo
  26,222,HiЙ—i jippoo e dow kala fefindotooЙ—o bakkodinЙ—o
  26,223,"HiЙ—i werloo nanЙ—e Й—en, ko Й“urЙ“e heewude e majji ko fenooji"
  26,224,"YimooЙ“e Й“en ko jokkata Й“e, ko bewЙ“e Й“en"
  26,225,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yinoo e kala aynde"
  26,226,E tawde kamЙ“e hiЙ“e wowla ko Й“e huuwataa
  26,227,Si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe Й“e jaЕӢtii Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i Й“e yoЙ“tii Й“aawo Й“e tooГұaama. Aray ka Й“en tooГұuЙ“e annday ko honde e waylitorde Й“e waylitotoo
  27,1,"Taa Siin, Й—en ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e Deftere Й“anngunde"
  27,2,Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonannde gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en
  27,3,"ЖҒen Й“e no ГұiiЙ“a e Julde nden Й“e totta Jakka on, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yananaa fii Laakara on"
  27,4,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaali Laakara on, Men cuЙ—anii Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yinoo"
  27,5,"Ko Й“en woni Й“en, Й“e woodani Й—um Lepte bonЙ—e Й—en, kamЙ“e ka Laakara ko kamЙ“e woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  27,6,"E pellet, an hiЙ—a lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka Г‘eeГұo AnnduЙ—o"
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo Й“eynguure makko nden: \"Min dey, mi haynike yiite, aray mi addana on ka nge woni Й—on kumpital maaЙ—um mi addana on docotal huЙ“Й“ungal, bela jo'o onon on iwloto"
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge, o noddaa: ЖҠum woni barkinaama on wonЙ—o ka yiite e Й“en wonuЙ“e banЕӢe magge, e Senayee wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden"
  27,9,"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla TedduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o On"
  27,10,"LiЙ“u tuggordu maaЙ—a ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hindu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboddi, o hucciti ko o doguЙ—o o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: \"Wata a hulu, Min dey NulaaЙ“e Й“en hulataa ka Am"
  27,11,"Si wanaa on tooГұuЙ—o, refti o lontini ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“aawo bone Й—en. Pellet, Min ko Mi Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  27,12,"Naadu junngo maaЙ—a ngon ka jiiba maaЙ—a, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, [Й—um no jeyaa] e nder Aayeeje jeenay nulaaЙ—e e Fir'awna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatike yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  27,13,"Tuma nde arunoo e maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en ko yi'eteeЙ—e, Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠu'um, ko mbilewu Й“anngungu"
  27,14,"ЖҒe yeddi [Aayeeje Й—en], tawi wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in no yananaa fii majje, tooГұe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,15,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal Й“e maaki: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Й“urnuЙ—o men e dow Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, men anndinaama haala colli Й—in, men okkaama immorde e kala huunde, Pellet, Й—umЙ—oo ko Й—um woni Й“ural Й“anngungal"
  27,17,"Sulaymaana mooЙ“anaa koneeli makko Й—in immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yimЙ“e e ka colli, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yuЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e"
  27,18,"Haa nde Й“e arunoo e aynde korndolli Й—in, korndolil wi'i: \"Ko onon yo korndolli, naatee ka koЙ—anЙ—i mooЙ—on, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'un Й—in muncu on, hara kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa"
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jaluЙ—o immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: \"Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maaЙ—a mo neeminЙ—aa e dow am on, e jibibinЙ“e lam Й“en, e nde mi gollata ko moЖҙЖҙi weltoraa Й—um, naadaami ka Yurmeende MaaЙ—a wonndude e jeyaaЙ“e MaaЙ—a moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,20,"O Жҙewtii colli Й—in, o maaki: \"Ko heЙ“i lam, mi yi'aali Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jeyaandu e wirniiЙ—i Й—in"
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e maaЙ—um maa mi hirsandu sanne, maaЙ—um ndu addana lam hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  27,22,"Ndu ГұiiЙ“e ko woЙ—Й—aa, ndu wi'i: \"Mi huЙ“indike ko a huЙ“indaaki Й—um, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal"
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii Й“e himo okkaa immorde e kala huunde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde"
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en hiЙ“e sujjana naange ngen gaanin Alla; Seytaane no cuЙ—aniЙ“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en o faddii Й“e gaayi Laawol ngol, kamЙ“e Й“e feewataa"
  27,25,Ko haЙ—ata Й“e sujjana Alla On yaltinoowo ko suuЙ—ii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi hiMo Anndi ko suuЙ—oton e ko feГұinton
  27,26,"Alla, ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  27,27,"O maaki: \"Aray men ndaara si a goongu, maaЙ—um si laati jeyaaЙ—o e fenuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,28,"Yahidu e nduu talkuru am werloЙ—aa ndu ka maЙ“Й“e, refti huccaa Й“e ndaaraa ko honЙ—um Й“e ruttata"
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, min dey werlaama ka am talkuru teddundu"
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: \"Innde Alla HuuЙ“uЙ—o Yurmeende HeeriiЙ—o Yurmeende On"
  27,31,"Wata on townitano lam, aree e am ko jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, waЙ—tee lam e feere e Й—ee fiyaake am, mi laataaki taЖҙoowo fiyaake haa tawdeЙ—on e am"
  27,33,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare saЙ—tuЙ—e, fiyaake Й—en ko ka maaЙ—a woni, ndaaru ko honЙ—um yamirtaa"
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: \"Pellet, lamЙ“e Й“en si Й“e naatii e saare Й“e bonnay nde, Й“e waЙ—a tedduЙ“e mayre Й“en hoyЙ“e, ko wanonii Й“e gollirta"
  27,35,"Awa min, mi nulay e maЙ“Й“e neldaari, mi ndaara ko honЙ—um nulaaЙ“e Й“en ruttodata"
  27,36,"Tuma nde Й“e arunoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: \"Enee, on Й“eydiray lam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkin mi, no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hiЙ—on farnora neldaari mooЙ—on ndin"
  27,37,"Rutto ka maЙ“Й“e, mamen addana Й“e koneeli Й—i Й“e maraa feere muuЙ—um, mamen yaltin Й“e ton ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e hara kamЙ“e ko hoyЙ“e"
  27,38,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, ko hommbo e mooЙ—on addanta lam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii Й“e arude ka am ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: \"Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maaЙ—a nden, e pellet, min e dow Й—um ko mi dolnuЙ—o hoolaaЙ—o"
  27,40,"On mo woni ka muuЙ—um ganndal immorde ka Deftere wi'i: \"Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndarЙ—e maaЙ—a Й—en ruttotoo e maaЙ—a\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde ГұiiЙ“unde ka makko, o maaki: \"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko immorde e ЖҒural Joomi am, fii yo O ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [Mo] maaЙ—um si mi yedday [Mo], kala jarnuЙ—o anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yedduЙ—o kadi pellet, Joomi am ko O Galo TedduЙ—o"
  27,41,"O maaki: \"Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditay, kaa o laatoto jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en Й“e annditataa"
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arunoo, [o] wi'aa: \"Enee, ko nii jullere maaЙ—a nden wa'i?\" O wi'i: \"Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii\". Men okkaama ganndal ko adii mo, men laatii jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,43,"Faddii mo, Й—um ko o laatinoo himo rewa gaanin Alla, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e"
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: \"Naatu ka huЙ“eere\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o Гұori dense (korle)makko Й—en. [Sulaymaana] maaki: \"Pellet, ndee ko huЙ“eere newЙ—iniraande ndaarorЙ—e\". [Debbo on] wi'i: \"Jooma, min dey mi tooГұii wonkii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wonndude e Sulaymaana"
  27,45,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii faade e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, Й—um woni rewee Alla. Tawi kamЙ“e ko Й“e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i hiЙ“e wennjondira"
  27,46,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko fii honЙ—un heГұornton bone Й—en ko adii moЖҙЖҙere nden?\" \"Ko haЙ—i insinanino Alla bela jo'o onon on yurminoyte"
  27,47,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men kiitinorii ma e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a\". O maaki: \"kiite mooЙ—on on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fitneteeЙ“e\" @Corrected"
  27,48,Laatinoke ka saare ton worЙ“e njeenayo hiЙ“e bonna ka leydi Й“e moЖҙЖҙintaa
  27,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: ЖҒe woondirii Alla, ma men waalanan mo ka suudu kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden refti ma men wi'an jeyЙ“e mo Й“en; men tawaaka warugol yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e pellet, menen ko men goonguЙ“e\". @Corrected"
  27,50,"ЖҒe hodi hodoore Menen kadi Men fewji fewjoore, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'ataa"
  27,51,"Ndaaru, ko honno laatorno battane hodo maЙ“Й“e ngon, Menen Men yirbinno Й“e kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  27,52,"ЖҠin cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e ko yeewuЙ—i sabu ko Й“e tooГұunoo kon. Pellet, wonii e Й—um Maande wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,53,"Men danndi Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e woni hulooЙ“e [Alla]"
  27,54,"E Luutu, tuma nde o wi'anno yimЙ“e makko Й“en: 'Enee, on aray pankare Й—en hara hiЙ—on sutii"
  27,55,"Eyoo, onon on aray e worЙ“e Й“en ka tuuyo accon rewЙ“e Й“en?! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"
  27,56,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e wi'i : \"Yaltinee yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en ka hoЙ—o (wura) mooЙ—on ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"
  27,57,"Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on; [on Й—on] Men hoddiranii mo ko o jeyaaЙ—o e halketaaЙ“e Й“en"
  27,58,"Men toЙ“ini e dow maЙ“Й“e toЙ“o, bonii toЙ“o jertinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  27,59,"Maaku: Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, kisiyee wonii e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en Й“e O suЙ“ii. Enee, ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Й—in Й—iЙ“e sirkanta"
  27,60,"Kaa ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin O jippinani on immorde ka kammu ndiyam? Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am gese joomiraaje ЕӢari. Wonantaa on nde fuЙ—inon leЙ—Й—e majje. Enee, hara reweteeЙ—o no woodi wonndude e Alla? Ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e ooГұotooЙ“e"
  27,61,"Kaa ko hommbo waЙ—i leydi ndin ГұiiЙ“undi, O waЙ—i hakkunde mayri calluЙ—i O waЙ—ani ndi pelle O waЙ—i hakkunde maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i heedo? Enee, hara na woodi reweteeЙ—o [goo] wonndude e Alla? ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e anndaa"
  27,62,Kaa ko hommbo jaabato Й“ittiiЙ—o on si o noddi Mo o hunca bone Й—en O waЙ—a on lontiiЙ“e ka leydi? Na woodi KoreweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? FanЙ—ii ko waajitoЙ—on
  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo fewnata on ka niЙ“e njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni Й—in wewlinirayЙ—i fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? Alla Toowii gaayi ko Й“e sirkata kon. @Corrected"
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o tagu ngun refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? Maaku: \"Addee daliili mooЙ—on on si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  27,65,"Maaku: \"Anndaa ko wirnii kon Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa Alla. ЖҒe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma Й“e immintinoytee"
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal maЙ“Й“e ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e wumuЙ“e fii Й—um"
  27,67,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e wi'i: \" Enee, hay si men laatike mbullaari e baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kadi, e hara menen ko men yaltinoyteeЙ“e"
  27,68,"GomЙ—ii men fodanooma Й—um menen e baabiraaЙ“e amen ko adii, Й—um wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  27,69,"Maaku : \"Yehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bonЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  27,70,"Wata a suno fii maЙ“Й“e, wata a laato e Й“itteende immorde e ko Й“e fewjata kon"
  27,71,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  27,72,"Maaku: \"No tijjaa nde tawata Й“adanike on yoga e kon ko Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—on yaccinaneede"
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko O Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e jarnataa [Alla]"
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a hiMo Anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en soomi e ko Й—e feГұГұinta kon"
  27,75,"Alaa e wirniikun ka kammu e ka leydi si wanaa [fii makkun] no e nder Deftere Й“anngunde"
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hinde filloo e dow Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en fii huunde nde Й“e Й“uri luutondirde nden e fii muuЙ—um"
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonannde gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a O Гұaawiray hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘aawoore Makko ngal, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o AnnduЙ—o"
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an hiЙ—a e hoore Goonga Й“annguka kan"
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa mayЙ“e Й“en, a nanintaa faaЙ—uЙ“e Й“en noddaandu ndun si Й“e Й—uurnike Й“e huccitii"
  27,81,An a wonaali fewnoowo bumЙ“e Й“en e gaayi majjere maЙ“Й“e nden. A nanintaa si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow maЙ“Й“e, Men yaltinana Й“e daabewa immorde ka leydi himba haalana Й“e wonnde yimЙ“e Й“en laatike Й“e yananaaka Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  27,83,E Гұalnde Men mooЙ“oyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaaЙ“e e Й“en fennooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e soggee
  27,84,"Haa si Й“e arii, O Daala: \"Eyoo, on fenniino Aayeeje Am Й—en, hara on huЙ“indoraali Й—i ganndal. Kaa ko honЙ—um wonЙ—on e gollude"
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e tooГұi kon, kamЙ“e Й“e wowlataa"
  27,86,"Enee, hara Й“e yi'aali, Menen Men waЙ—ii jemma on fii yo Й“e deeЖҙu e maako, e Гұalorma on yi'irЙ—o? Pellet, wonii e Й—um Aayeeje wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,87,"E Г‘alnde wuttoytee ka alaadu, Й—enЖҙoo Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“en wonuЙ“e ka leydi, si wanaa Й“en Й“e Alla muuyi, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e aray e Makko hara ko Й“e hoykiniiЙ“e"
  27,88,"HiЙ—a tina pelle Й—en, sikka ko Й—e fenndiiЙ—e, hara le kannje hiЙ—e wuloo wulagol duule Й—en, Й—um ko kuugal Alla, On ЕӢarЙ—inЙ—o kala huunde, pellet, Kanko ko O HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  27,89,"Mo ardii e moЖҙЖҙere nden haray no woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖҙЖҙude, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e immorde e Й—enЖҙere nden Г‘alnde"
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone Й—en, geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en hippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yoЙ“ete si wanaa kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on golla"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi Rewu Jooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini Й—um, no woodani Mo kala huunde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare nden, mo feewii haray ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje Makko Й—en anndon Й—e\". Joomi maaЙ—a wonaali welsindiiЙ—o gaay e kon ko golloton"
  28,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  28,2,ЖҠee ko Aayeeje Deftere Й“anngunde nden
  28,3,"MeЙ—en janngira e maaЙ—a hoore goonga, kumpital Muusaa e Fir'awna, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna townitino ka leydi; o waЙ—i yimЙ“e mayri ndin pecce-pecce: himo lo'ina fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e, o hirsa Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en o acca rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Pellet, ko e bonnooЙ“e Й“en o jeyanoo"
  28,5,"MeЙ—en faandinoo moЖҙЖҙagol e lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en ka leydi; Men waЙ—a Й“e koohooЙ“e, Men waЙ—a Й“e kadi ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,6,"Men huЙ“indina Й“e e leydi ndin, Men holla Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kon ko Й“e hulaynoo"
  28,7,"Men wahayini e yumma Muusaa, wonnde: \"Muynin mo\". Si a hulanoyii mo, ko yo a bugoyo mo ka maayo. Wata a hulu, wata a suno; pellet, Men ruttay mo ka maaЙ—a, Men waЙ—oya mo gooto e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  28,8,"YimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en hocci mo, fii yo laatano Й“e gaГұo e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e laatino woopuЙ“e"
  28,9,"Debbo Fir'awna on wi'i: \"(Kun entum ko) Й“uuЙ“eendi gite am e an kadi! Wata on waru mo, hino gasa ka o nafata en, maa jogitoren mo Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Hari Й“e so'aani"
  28,10,"ЖҒernde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewunde. Haa o eЙ“Й“i feГұГұinde fii makko, si wanaano Men tabintinnde Й“ernde makko nden, fii yo o laato e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  28,11,"[Yumma Muusaa] wi'ani banndiraawo makko on: \"Jokkitu mo\"; o haynii mo ka deestii, hari Й“e so'aa-anndude"
  28,12,"Men harminani mo ko adii, (enЙ—i) muynirЙ—i Й—in, (banndiraawo makko on) wi'i: \"On accay mi tinndinay on fii yimЙ“e suudu, Й“e ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laaЙ“anay Й“e mo"
  28,13,"Men rutti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo Й“ernde makko Й“uuЙ“u, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Men okki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, fewndo welsindaare yimЙ“e mayre; o tawi worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o no haЙ“a ton: goЙ—Й—o on ko jeyaaЙ—o e leГұol makko, oya on ko jeyaaЙ—o e ayЙ“e makko Й“en. JeyaaЙ—o e leГұol makko ngol Й—aЙ“Й“iri faabo e hoore jeyaaЙ—o e gaГұo makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: \"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kuuЙ—e seytaane. Pellet, ko o gaГұo, majjinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  28,16,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi tooГұii hoore-am; haforanam.\" O haforani mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  28,17,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, sabu ko neeminЙ—aa kon e am, mi wontataa ballo bomЙ“e Й“en"
  28,18,"O wonti hulЙ—o ka saare, himo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornooЙ—o mo on hanki, hino faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: \"Pellet, ko a bewЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol tawЙ—o on ko gaГұo maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, a faala warugol lam, wano ittirnoЙ—aa wonkii non hanki? A faandaaki, si wanaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka Й“uri woЙ—Й—ude e saare nden, himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii warugol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e laaЙ“anooЙ“e ma"
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o huluЙ—o, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: \"Joomi am, danЙ—ndam e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,22,"Nde o fewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: \"Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka Й“unndu Madyana, o tawi Й—on dental yimЙ“e, hiЙ“e yarna [daabeeji maЙ“Й“e], o tawi gaanin maЙ“Й“e, rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, no sogga [dammi maЙ“Й“e], o maaki: \"Ko honЙ—um habbi-Й—on?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men yarnataa haa aynooЙ“e Й“en deestoo, baaba amen, ko mawЙ—o nayeejo"
  28,24,"O yarnani Й“e [dammi Й—in], refti o huccitiri ka Й—owdi, o maaki: \"Joomi am, min ko jippinЙ—aa e am woo e moЖҙЖҙere, ko mi hatonjiЙ—o"
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiwЙ“e] Й“en ari e makko, himo yahra hersa, o wi'i: \"Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yoЙ“e njoЙ“di kon ko yarnan-Й—aa men\". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [mawЙ—o] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: \"Wata a hulu, a daЙ—ii yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiwЙ“e] Й“en wi'i: \"Жіettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mo Жҙettataa golle, ko doolnuЙ—o hoolniiЙ—o"
  28,27,"[MawЙ—o] on maaki: \"MiЙ—o yiЙ—i resingol ma gooto e jiwЙ“e am Й“en Й—oo Й—iЙ—o, e hoore yo a golla-nam duuЙ“i jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka saЙ—tinannde ma. A taway lam, si Alla jaЙ“ii, ko e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en mi jeyaa"
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ЖҠum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji Й—iЙ—i, Й—i mi hunni, haray Й“iЙ—teede alanaa e lam. En waЙ—ii Alla fawtiiЙ—o e ko wowluЙ—en kon"
  28,29,"Nde Muusaa timminnoo happu ngun, o yahdi e Й“eydnuure makko, o haynii yiite ka senngo (fello) Tuuri, o maaki Й“eunguure makko nden: \"Wonee Й—oo, min mi haynike yiite. Belajo'o mi addana on e magge kumpital maa te'annde(docotal) yiite ngen, belajo'o iwloron"
  28,30,"Nde o hewtunoo nge, o noddiraa ka fonngo Гұaamo aynde, ka tummbere barkinaande, ka (takko) lekki, wonnde: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Ko Min woni Alla, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  28,31,"Kadi: \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\"; nde o tinunoo hindu dillira wa mboddi,o huccitiri dogudu, o yeЖҙЖҙitaaki. [O noddaa]: \"Ko an yo Muusaa! Artu, wata a hulu; ko a jeyaaЙ—o e hooliiЙ“e Й“en"
  28,32,"Naadu juungo maa ngon ka jayba maa, ngo yaltay ranewo, ko aldaa e Гұawu. Bakaa e maaЙ—a, juuЙ—e maa Й—en, fii kulol ngol. ЖҠin ko hujjaaji Й—iЙ—i, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e Fir'awna e dental mun, pellet, Й“en laatike yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  28,33,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, mi ittiino wonkii e maЙ“Й“e, miЙ—o huli nde Й“e warata lam"
  28,34,"Ko musiЙ—Й—o am on Haaruuna, Й“uri lam laaЙ“ude Й—emngal. Immindin-mo e am, ko wallitoo lam, goonginan-mi; miЙ—o huli nde Й“e fennata lam"
  28,35,"[Alla] daali: \"Men semmbiniray tere maa Й—en, musiЙ—Й—o maa on, Men waЙ—ana on hujja (e cemmbe); Й“e hewtirtaa on Й—iЙ—o, sabu Aayeeje Amen Й—e [Men nuli e] mo'on, e Й“en jokkuЙ“e on fooluЙ“e"
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa ardunoo e maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en Й“annguЙ—e, Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu fefindaangu. Men naniraali Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko Joomi am Й“uri anndude on arduЙ—o e peewal, immorde ka Makko, e on mo battane moЖҙЖҙe woodani ka laakara. Pellet, O malnataa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Ko onon dental, mi anndanaa on reweteeЙ—o, si wanaa min. Ko an yo Haamaana, huЙ“Й“inanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa lam huЙ“eere toowunde, no gasa ka mi Жҙellitoo e ReweteeЙ—o Muusaa On; tawde miЙ—o sikki mo e fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kanko e koneeli makko Й—in, ko aldaa e goonga. ЖҒe sikki wonde Й“e ruttitetaako ka Amen"
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kanko e koneeli makko Й—in, Men bugii Й“e ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane tooГұuЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo"
  28,41,"Men waЙ—i Й“e ardiiЙ“e, noddoo Й“e e Yiite. Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“e walletaake"
  28,42,"Men jokkintiniri Й“e ka aduna Й—oo, kuddi. Г‘alnde Darngal, ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e woЙ—Й—intinoyteeЙ“e [e yurmeende Alla]"
  28,43,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Й“aawo nde Men halkunoo gire arane Й—en, ko nde ndayginorde yimЙ“e Й“en, e peewal e yurmeende. Belajo'o, Й“e waajitoray"
  28,44,"A tawanooka ka senngo hiirnaange, fewndo Men wahyinnoo e Muusaa yamiroore nden, a jeyanooka kadi e seediiЙ“e Й“en"
  28,45,"Kono Menen woni taguЙ“e gire, duuЙ“i maЙ“Й“e juuti. A hoЙ—aano kadi e yimЙ“e Madyana Й“en, hiЙ—a janngana Й“e Aayeeje Amen; ko Menen woni nulЙ“e"
  28,46,"A tawanooka ka senngo Fello Tuuri, fewndo Men noddunoo; ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa [woni ko Men nulir-maa], fii no jertiniraa yimЙ“e, Й“e reentinoowo araali e maЙ“Й“e, ado maaЙ—a, belajo'o, Й“e waajitoto"
  28,47,"Si wanaano fii yo lepte yanir e maЙ“Й“e, sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ardini, Й“e wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko haЙ—no imminaa NulaaЙ—o e amen? Men jokka nun Aayeeje Maa Й—en, men jeyee e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  28,48,"Nde o addirannooЙ“e goonga kan, immorde ka Amen, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko haЙ—no o okkee yeru ko Muusaa okkanoo kon?\" Kere Й“e yeddaano ko Muusaa okkanoo kon ko adii? ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko mbileeji Й—iЙ—i, Й—i no wallindira!\" ЖҒe wi'i kadi: \"Ko men yedduЙ“e fow e mun"
  28,49,"Maaku: \"Addee Deftere immorde ka Alla, hara hinde Й“uri Й—ee Й—iЙ—i feewude, mi jokkaynde, si on laatike goongunЙ“e"
  28,50,"Si Й“e jaabaaki ma, anndu ko mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й“e jokkata. Ko hommbo Й“uri majjude Й“uri on jokkirЙ—o mbeleeЙ—e mun, ko aldaa e peewal immorde ka Alla? Pellet, Alla fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,51,"GomЙ—ii Men hewtinii Й“e Konngol ngol, belajo'o, Й“e waajitora"
  28,52,"ЖҒen Й“e Men rokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko Й“e gomЙ—imЙ“e nde"
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet men woniino jebbiliiЙ“e, ado mayre"
  28,54,"ЖҒen Й—on, Й“e jonniroyte njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, laabi Й—iЙ—i, sabu ko Й“e muГұinoo kon, hiЙ“e duГұiraynoo moЖҙЖҙere nden, bone on, e huunde nde Men arsiki Й“e nden, hiЙ“e nafqa"
  28,55,"Si Й“e nanii meerente, Й“e Й—uurnoo e Й—um, Й“e wi'a: \"Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Men Й—aЙ“Й“ataa wonndugol e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  28,56,"Pellet, an (NulaaЙ—o), a fewnataa mo yiЙ—uЙ—aa; kono Alla no fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko Й“uri anndude feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  28,57,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Si men jokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen\". E Men hoЙ—iniraali Й“e e nokku horminaaЙ—o, hoolniiЙ—o, mo dimЙ—e noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  28,58,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko Men hakli, e yimЙ“e ca'e, bewrunooЙ“e nguuree mun, e hino non galleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, hoЙ—iraaka Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa seeЙ—a. Men laatii wonnde ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali wonde halkoowo yimЙ“e ca'e, haa O immina e lenyol maЙ“Й“eЙ—en, NulaaЙ—o, ko janngana Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Men siforaali kadi halkugol yimЙ“e ca'e, si wanaa hara yimЙ“e majje ko tooГұuЙ“e"
  28,60,"Kala ko okkaЙ—on e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna e cuЙ—aari mun; ko ko woni ka Alla kon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, woni kadi ko luttata. E on haqqiltaa"
  28,61,"E ko on mo Men fodi fodaari moЖҙЖҙuri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Men dakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kanko on, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko e tawneteeЙ“e (ka Yiite) Й“en o jeyaa"
  28,62,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kafidaaЙ—i am, Й—in Й—i aaЖҙoraynoЙ—on woni"
  28,63,"ЖҒen Й“e Konngol jojji e mu'un wi'a: \"Joomi amen, ko Й“ee woni ko men bewinnoo. Men bewinirno Й“e, wano men bewirnoo. Men daЙ—ndinike e MaaЙ—a. Wanaa menen Й“e rewaynoo"
  28,64,"[ЖҒe] wi'anee: \"Noddee non kafidaaЙ—i mon Й—in\". ЖҒe nodda Й—i, kono Й—i jaabotaako Й“e. ЖҒe yi'a lepte Й—en, (Й“e yeloo) sinno hara Й“e feewuno"
  28,65,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, o wi'a: \"Ko honЙ—um jaabinoЙ—on NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  28,66,"LamitorЙ—i Й—in wumiЙ—ana Й“e nden Гұalnde, Й“e lamndondirtaa"
  28,67,"Si ko tuubuЙ—o, o gomЙ—ini, o golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko O muuyi, O suЙ“oo; suЙ“agol alanaa Й“e. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en suuЙ—ata, e kon ko Й“e feГұГұinta"
  28,70,"Ko Kanko Alla woni, Mo reweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko Kanko yettoore woodani aduna e laakara. Hino woodani Mo Гұaawoore nden. Ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on"
  28,71,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on jemma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘alnde Darngal, ko reweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa"
  28,72,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on Гұalorma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘alnde Darngal, ko reweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo deeЖҙoton e mun? E on yi'ataa"
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O waЙ—iranii on jemma e Гұalorma; fii no deeЖҙiron e (jemma) on, e no Й—aЙ“Й“iron ( e Гұalorma on), Й“ural Makko, e no belajo'o yettiron [Mo]"
  28,74,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kadidaaЙ—i(renndidiiЙ—i) am, Й—in Й—in aaЖҙoraynoЙ—on woni"
  28,75,"Men Й—oofi e kala mofte, seedotooЙ—o, Men wi'a: \"Addee hujjaajji mon Й—in\". ЖҒe anndi wonnde goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko Й“e fefindotonoo kon majjitora Й“e"
  28,76,"Pellet,Qaaruuna ko e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en jeyanoo,kono o bewi e maЙ“Й“e.Men okki mo ngaluuji taway-Й—i soktirЙ—e mun,no teddana jamaa doolnuЙ—o.Nde yimЙ“e makko Й“en,wi'anno mo:Wata a weltor townitaare.Pellet Alla yiЙ—aa weltortooЙ“e toownitaare"
  28,77,"ЖҠaЙ“Й“ir ko Alla okku-maa kon, galle laakare Й—en. Wata a yejjitu geЙ“al maa ngal aduna. MoЖҙЖҙir no Alla moЖҙЖҙorii non e maaЙ—a. Wata a Й—aЙ“Й“u bonnugol ka leydi. Anndu pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,78,"O wi'i: \"Ko mi okkiraa Й—um, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii\". E o anndaa wonnde gomЙ—ii Alla halkiino gire, adiiЙ“e mo, Й“urЙ“e doole, Й“uri mo Й—uuЙ—ude jawle? ЖҒe lamndoytaake fii junuubi maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, cuЙ—aari makko ndin. YiЙ—uЙ“e nguurndam aduna Й“en wi'i: \"Hara nun men heЙ“ayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. Kanko on, pellet, ko o jom-geЙ“al mawnungal"
  28,80,"OkkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“en kan wi'i: \"Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on gomЙ—inЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi\". Kono hawrataa e Й—um, si wanaa muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  28,81,"Men mutindini mo e galle makko Й—en, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko faaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano faabotooЙ—o hoore-mun"
  28,82,"ЖҒen yelinooЙ“e nokku makko on hanki mun, Й“e waЙ—ti wiide: \"Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“iЙ—tinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wanaa Alla moЖҙЖҙinoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  28,83,"ЖҠen galle laakara, Men waЙ—anii Й—e Й“en Й“e yiЙ—aa townitaare ka leydi, wanaa kadi bonnugol. Battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en, ko fii gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  28,84,"Kala arduЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙere, hino woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖҙЖҙude; kala kadi arduЙ—o e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwuЙ“e bonЙ—i Й—in yoЙ“etaake, si wanaa ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon"
  28,85,"Pellet, jippinЙ—o Alqur'aana on e maaЙ—a, ko ruttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: \"Ko Joomi am Й“uri anndude arduЙ—o e peewal, e wonЙ—o e majjere Й“anngunde"
  28,86,"A wonaano tamЖҙininooЙ—o jippineede Deftere nden e maaЙ—a. Si wanaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wata wonu muk, walloowo heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  28,87,"wata Й“e falo ma kadi e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“aawo Й—e jippineede e maaЙ—a. Noddu (yimЙ“e Й“en) faade e Joomi maa, wata a wonu muk, jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  28,88,"Wata a rewudu e Alla, reweteeЙ—o goo. ReweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Huunde fow re'ay, si wanaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko Kanko woodani Гұaawugol; ko ka Makko kadi rutteteЙ—on. @Corrected"
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  29,2,"E yimЙ“e Й“en sikku Й“e accirte nii, fii Й“e wi'ii: \"Men gomЙ—inii!\" Hara Й“e fitninaaka"
  29,3,"GomЙ—ii, Men fitninii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. Maa Alla feГұГұin, fii goonguЙ“e Й“en, maa O feГұГұin kadi, fii fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  29,4,"Kaa huuwuЙ“e bonЙ—i Й“en sikku, wonnde Й“e laawoto Men? ko Й“e Гұaawata kon bonii"
  29,5,"Kala tawЙ—o himo jortii hawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  29,6,"Kala kadi tiiЙ—niiЙ—o, ko hoore-makko o tiiЙ—nanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko yonndiniiЙ—o e tageefo ngon"
  29,7,"ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men momtan Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men yoЙ“itra Й“e, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  29,8,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on, moЖҙЖҙugol e mawЙ“e makko Й“en. Si Й“e doolii maa fii sirkangol Lam, ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wata a Й—ofto Й“e ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  29,9,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men waЙ—tiduЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  29,10,"Hino e jimЙ“e Й“en, wi'oowo: \"Men gomЙ—inii Alla\"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o waЙ—ay lorra yimЙ“e Й“en, wano lepte Alla Й—en. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, Й“e wi'ay: \"MeЙ—en wondunoo e mo'on!\" Kere wanaa Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e Й“erЙ—e tageefo ngon"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ma O feГұГұina kadi fii naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  29,12,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon Й—in\". Kono Й“e wonaali fawtotooЙ“e hay huunde e goopi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e"
  29,13,"Kono maa Й“e fawtoo fii teddeendi junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e teddeendi goo, wonndude e teddeendi maЙ“Й“e ndin. Ko maa Й“e lamndoyee, Г‘alnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  29,14,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o ГұiiЙ“i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, duuЙ“i ujunere, ЕӢakkuЙ—um duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e jowi. Waame on nanngi Й“e, hari ko Й“e tooГұuЙ“e"
  29,15,"Men daЙ—ndi mo, kanko e yimЙ“e laana kan; Men waЙ—i ka kaawisa tageefo ngon"
  29,16,"(Janto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Rewee Alla, hulon Mo; ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si woni hiЙ—on anndi"
  29,17,"Anndee ko reweton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, hiЙ—on taЖҙa fenaande. Pellet, Й—in Й—i rewoton gaanin Alla, Й—i waawaa on arsikude; Й—aЙ“Й“iree arsike on ka Alla, rewon Mo, yetton Mo. Ko ka Makko woni rutteteЙ—on"
  29,18,"Si on fennii, haray mofte adinooЙ“e kadi fenniino (NulaaЙ“e mun). Alaa ko fawii e NulaaЙ—o on, si wanaa yottingol Й“annginngol"
  29,19,"E Й“ee yi'aali no Alla fuЙ—Й—orta tagu ngun, refti O ruttay ngu? Pellet, Й—um wonii ko newanii Alla"
  29,20,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O fuЙ—Й—ori tagu ngun. Refti Alla taga tagu sakkitoru ngun. Pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  29,21,"Himo lepte mo O muuyani, O yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on"
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on gaanin Alla, woni giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  29,23,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, e hawroygol e Makko ngol, Й“en taЖҙike e yurmeende Am, Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  29,24,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano, si wanaa wiide Й“e: \"Waree mo, maa sunnon mo\". Kono Alla daЙ—ndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  29,25,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yiЙ—indiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, Г‘alnde Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi huЙ—o yoga, hara non, jaaЖҙorde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara wallooЙ“e alanaa on"
  29,26,"Luutu gomЙ—ini mo. O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  29,27,"Men yeЙ—i mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Men waЙ—i e geyngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Men okki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  29,28,"(Janto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \" E on aray e pankare, Й—e gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun"
  29,29,"E on aray yottagol e worЙ“e Й“en? paloЙ—on kadi e laawol? Huuwon ko mbatirdu mon ko aГұinii?\" Kono jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano, si wanaa wiide Й“e: \"Addan men lepte Alla Й—en, si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  29,30,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, wallam e hoore yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  29,31,"Tuma nde ImminaaЙ“e Amen Й“en addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, Й“e wi\"i: \"Menen, ko men halkooЙ“ee yimЙ“e ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yimЙ“e mayre laatike tooГұooЙ“e"
  29,32,"O maaki: \"Kono Luutu no ton!\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko menen Й“uri anndude fii wonЙ“e ton. Ko ma men daЙ—ndu mo, kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketeeЙ“e Й“en"
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hewtunoo ka Luutu, o saЙ—tiraa fii maЙ“Й“e, Й“ernde makko Й“iЙ—torii fii maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, wata a suno. Ko men daЙ—ndooЙ“e ma an e Й“eynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaaЙ“e Й“en"
  29,34,"Ko men jippinooЙ“e lepte e yimЙ“e ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e yaltunoo e Й—oftaare kon"
  29,35,"GomЙ—ii Men accii e nden (saare), maande Й“anngunde, wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en"
  29,36,"(Men nuli) kadi e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla, jortoron Г‘alannde sakkitiinde nden, wata woniri e leydi ndin, bonnooЙ“e"
  29,37,"Kono Й“e fenni mo. Dillannde nden nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-maayi"
  29,38,"(Men halki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. GomЙ—ii caambbeje maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“annganii on. Seytaane cuЙ—inani Й“e, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ndu sakkii Й“e e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko Й“e rentunooЙ“e"
  29,39,"(Men halki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. GomЙ—ii le, Muusaa addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, kono Й“e townitii ka leydi, Й“e wonaano laawotooЙ“e"
  29,40,"Kala maЙ“Й“e, Men leptirno junuubi mun Й—in: no e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Men wuurti henndu e mun; no e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e haacaango halki; no e maЙ“Й“e, mo Men mutini Й—um ka leydi, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й“e Men yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali tooГұoowo Й“e; si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұunoo ko'e maЙ“Й“e"
  29,41,"Misal Й“en jogitiiЙ“e gaanin Alla reweteeЙ—i, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko Й“uri lo'ude non e cuuЙ—i Й—in, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno Й“e annduno"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala huunde nde Й“e noddata gaanin Makko. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  29,43,"ЖҠee ko mise Й—e Men piyanta yimЙ“e Й“en; ko woni tun, faamataa Й—en, si wanaa annduЙ“e Й“en"
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii Й—um, maande, wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  29,45,"Janngu kon ko waayinaa e maaЙ—a ka Deftere, ГұiiЙ“aa e julde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no haЙ—a pankare e ko aГұinii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol Й“uri (huunde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko golloton kon"
  29,46,"Wata on wennjir yimЙ“e Defte Й“en si wanaa e no Й“uri e moЖҙЖҙirde, si wanaa hara ko Й“en tooГұuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Wi'on: \"Men gomЙ—inii nden jippinaande e amen e Й—en jippinaaЙ—e e mon. ReweteeЙ—o amen On e reweteeЙ—o mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Men jebbilanii Й“e Mo"
  29,47,"Ko wano non Men jippiniri e maaЙ—a Deftere nden. ЖҒen Й“e Men okki Deftere nden, hiЙ“e gomЙ—ini nde. Hino e maЙ“Й“e on gomЙ—inЙ—o nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wanaa heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  29,48,"A wonaano hiЙ—a janngaynoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano Гұaamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnooЙ“e Й“en sikkittono"
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wanaa tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  29,50,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Hanno jippinee e makko maandeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  29,51,"Kere yonaali Й“e wonnde Men jippinii e maaЙ—a Deftere nden hinde janngee e maЙ“Й“e? Wonii e Й—um, yurmeende e waaju wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  29,52,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii hakkunde am e mooЙ—on seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. ЖҒen non gomЙ—imЙ“e meere nden Й“e yeddi Alla, ko Й“en woni sooyuЙ“e Й“en"
  29,53,"HiЙ“e hawjirane lepte Й—en. Si wanaano fii lajal innaangal, lepte Й—en ardirayno e maЙ“Й“e juhal, hara kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa-anndude"
  29,54,"HiЙ“e hawjirane lepte Й—en, hara non pellet, Jahannama ko fiiltiinge heefereЙ“e Й“en"
  29,55,"Г‘alnde lepte Й—en suddiroyta Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e e ka ley koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, O daala[na Й“e]: \"MeeЙ—ee ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  29,56,Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am gomЙ—imЙ“e! Anndee leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Ko Min woni ko rewoton
  29,57,Kala wonkii meeЙ—ay maayde. Refti ko ka Amen rutteteЙ—on
  29,58,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Men hoЙ—nu Й“e ka Aljanna e cuuЙ—i Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley majji, koЙ“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Iskin(heskey)В° moЖҙЖҙere njoЙ“di gollunooЙ“e, @Corrected"
  29,59,"Й“en muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e tuugii e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  29,60,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ruugayЙ—i Й—i yooЙ“otaako arsike majji! Ko Alla arsikata Й—i wonndude e onon. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  29,61,"Pellet, si a lanndike Й“e: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuu- li Й—in e leydi ndin, O elti naange ngen e lewru ndu?\" Ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Ko honno Й“e ferlitoraa (e gomЙ—ingol ngol)"
  29,62,"Alla no yaajinana arsike on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Himo Й“ittana mo. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  29,63,"Pellet, si a lanndike Й“e: \"Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu Й—am O wuurnitiri leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude?\", ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Maaku: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla!\". Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e haqqiltaa"
  29,64,"ЖҠam nguurndam aduna wonaali, si wanaa mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko hoЙ—o laakara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno Й“e annduno"
  29,65,"Si Й“e waЙ—Й—ike ka laana, Й“e nodda Alla Й“e laЙ“Й“inano Mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde O daЙ—ndi Й“e ka njorndi, ontuma Й“e sirka"
  29,66,"No Й“e yeddira ko Men okki Й“e kon, awa yo Й“e dakmito! Aray kaЙ“e annda"
  29,67,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde Men waЙ—ii hormorde hoolniinde, yimЙ“e Й“en no cifee(bifte) bannge maЙ“Й“e? E ko meere nden Й“e gomЙ—inta Й“e yedda neemaaji Alla Й—in"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұirde wa on fefindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  29,69,"ЖҒen tiiЙ—norЙ“e e (weltingol) Men, ma Men fewnirЙ“e e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  30,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  30,2,RuumiyankooЙ“e Й“en foolaama
  30,3,"ka Й“uri Й“adaade e leydi ndin, kamЙ“e kadi Й“aawo Й“e fooleede, Й“e fooloya"
  30,4,"e nder duuЙ“i seeЙ—aaji. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku (poolal ngal) ado e Й“aawo (maggal). Nden Гұalnde, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en weltota"
  30,5,"ballal Alla ngal. Himo walla mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko woni Fooloowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  30,6,"[ЖҠum] ko fodoore Alla. Alla lunndotaako fodoore Makko nden. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e anndaa"
  30,7,"HiЙ“e anndi ko feeГұi e nguurndam aduna, kono kamЙ“e e fii laakara on, ko Й“e welsindiiЙ“e"
  30,8,"E Й“ee miijitaaki fii ko'e-maЙ“Й“e? Alla tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, si wanaa goonga e lajal innaangal. Anndee ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“en, ko yedduЙ“e hawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  30,9,"E Й“ee yillaaki ka leydi Й“e taskoo ko honno battane Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e wa'unoo? ЖҒen wonuno Й“urЙ“e Й“e doole Й“e remi e leydi ndin Й“e wuuri e mayri Й“uri ko Й“ee wuuri e mayri kon. NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. Alla wonaali tooГұoowo Й“e, kono non ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonno e tooГұude"
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane bonnuЙ“e Й“en, ko bonande fii Й“e fennii Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e laatii e jalkitugol Й—e"
  30,11,Ko Alla fuЙ—Й—i tagu ngun; refti O rutta ngu; refti ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on
  30,12,"Г‘alnde Darngal ngal darii, bomЙ“e Й“en taЖҙoto"
  30,13,"WoodanoytaaЙ“e e kafidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in tefooji, Й“e woniino yedduЙ“e kafiduЙ“e Й“en"
  30,14,"Г‘alnde Darngal ngal darii,nden Гұalnde Й“e seertoyay"
  30,15,"Si ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“en Й—on wonoyay e beeli (Aljanna) hiЙ“e saЙ—nee(weltine)"
  30,16,"Si tawii non ko Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e fenni Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hawrugol ngol e laakara, Й“en Й—on ko tawnoyteeЙ“e e lepte Й—en"
  30,17,"Subbunhinanee Alla, tuma hiiroton e tuma weetoton"
  30,18,"Ko Kanko yettoore woodani ka kammuuli e ka leydi, e kiikiiЙ—e e saaga Гұalloton"
  30,19,"Himo yaltina ko wuuri e ndr ko maayi, O yaltina kadi ko maayi e nder ko wuuri. Himo wuurnita leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non yatainirte- Й—on (e genaale mon)"
  30,20,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: wonnde O tagii on immorde e mbum-mbuldi, refti jaka ko on Й“anndike saakotooЙ“e [e leydi ndin]"
  30,21,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in : wonnde O tagiranii on e wonkiiji mon Й—in, resondirЙ“e, fii yo on deeЖҙu e maЙ“Й“e, O waЙ—i hakkunde mon giggol e yumeende. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e"
  30,22,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e luutondirgol Й—emЙ—e mon e mbaadiiji mon. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji anduЙ“e Й“en"
  30,23,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: Й—oyngol mon ngol jemma e Гұalorma, e Й—aЙ“Й“ugol mon Й“ural Makko. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e"
  30,24,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: Himo hollira on maЖҙe Й—en kulol e tama'u (toЙ“o), Himo jippinira ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitira Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: nde kammu ngun e leydi ndin daroto e yamiroore Makko. Refti si O noddii on noddaandu ka leydi, e jaka onon hiЙ—on yalta (e genaale mon)"
  30,26,"Hino woodani (laamagol, e tagugol e toppitagol) Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi: kala maЙ“Й“e ko Й—oftiiЙ“e Mo"
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o tagu ngun, refti O ruttita ngu; ko Й—um Й“uri newanaande Mo. Hino woodani sifa Й“urЙ—o toowude ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko woni on FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o on"
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal immorde e ko'e-mon: hara no woodani on e Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon, immorde e kafidal e kon ko Men arsiki on, hara hiЙ—on fota e Й—um, hiЙ—on hulira Й“e wano hulirton ko'e-mon? Ko woni nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  30,29,"Si ko woni, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en jokkirii beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko hommbo fewnata mo Alla majjini? Alanaa Й“e wallooЙ“e"
  30,30,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina kan ГұiiЙ“ugol [e mun]. [ЖҠum] ko tagu Alla ngu O tagiri yimЙ“e Й“en e mun - waЙ—titugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun -. Ko Й—um woni diina focciika kan; kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotooЙ“e e Makko; hulon Mo, Гұinnon julde nden, wata on jeye e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  30,32,"(wano) Й“eya senndunooЙ“e diina mun kan, Й“e woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mun kon"
  30,33,"Si saЙ—teende memii yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e ruttitiiЙ“e e Makko; refti si O meeЙ—inii Й“e yumeende immorde e Makko, e jaka fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e no kafida e Joomi mun"
  30,34,"YoЙ“e yeddu ko Men okki Й“e kon. \"Awa dakmitee, arma anndon"
  30,35,"Kaa Men jippin e maЙ“Й“e hujja (Deftere), hara honde yewta fii ko Й“e sirkaynoo kon"
  30,36,"Si Men meeЙ—inirii yimЙ“e Й“en neema, Й“e weltoroo mo. Si bone memirii Й“e sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardiniri kon, e jaka hiЙ“e taЖҙoo"
  30,37,"E Й“e yi'aali wonnde Alla no yaГұГұana arsike on mo O muuyani, O Й“illina? Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  30,38,"Jonnu jom-Й“adiido o hakke makko on, e Й“illiiЙ“e e Й“ii-laawol. ЖҠum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude wonande Й“een faalaaЙ“e yarluyee Alla on; ko Й“en woni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnuЙ—on e riba, fii on Й“eydor e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en, Й—um Й“eydotaako ka Alla, kala non ko okkuЙ—on e Jakka, mo faandoriЙ—on welayee Alla, Й“en Й—on, ko sowanoyteeЙ“e [njoЙ“di] Й“en. @Corrected"
  30,40,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o on, refti O arsiki on, refti O wara on, refti O wuurnita on. Hara no e kafidaaЙ—i mon Й—in waЙ—ayЙ—i goЙ—Й—um e Й—um? Senayeewoo-dani Mo! O toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  30,41,"Bone on feeГұiri ka njoorndi e ka maaje, sabu ko juuЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en faggitii kon; fii yo O meeЙ—in Й“e yoga e ko Й“e huuwi; belajo'o, Й“e ruttoto"
  30,42,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo. Tawno ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko sirkooЙ“e"
  30,43,"Fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina focciika kan, ado Гұalaande arde immorde ka Alla nde ruttetaake. Nde Гұalnde, Й“e seeday"
  30,44,"Kala yedduЙ—o, haray geddi makko Й—in no fawii mo. Kala non golluЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, haray ko ko'e-maЙ“Й“e Й“e hebilani (Aljanna)"
  30,45,"fii yo O yoЙ“u Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, e Й“ural Makko ngal. Kanko On, O yiЙ—aa heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: Wurtugol Mo keneeli Й—in wewlinooji, e fii yo O meeЙ—in on e yurmeende Makko nden, e no laaЙ—e Й—en dogira e yamiroore Makko, e fii yo o Й—aЙ“Й“u e Й“ural Makko. Belajo'o, on yettay [Mo]"
  30,47,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii ado maaЙ—a NulaaЙ“e haa e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. Men yottii e Й“en bonnuЙ“e; tawi no jojji e Amen faabagol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo keneeЙ—i Й—in, Й—i sogga duule Й—en; O saakitira Й—um ka weeyo no O yiЙ—iri; O waЙ—ta Й—um taЖҙe-taЖҙe. A yi'ay toЙ“o ngon no yalta hakkude mun. Si O hewtinii ngo e on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e jaka kamЙ“e hiЙ“e weltoo"
  30,49,"GomЙ—ii Й“e laatinoke ado (toЙ“o) ngon jippineede e maЙ“Й“e, ko taЖҙinooЙ“e"
  30,50,"Ndaarii e battane yurmeende Alla nden, no O wuurnitorta leydi Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Pellet, waЙ—oowo Й—um On, ko wuurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, Kanko Ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  30,51,"[Hay] si Men nulii henndu, Й“e yi'i [gese maЙ“Й“e] Й—en no soyЙ—i, Й“e jokkay Й“aawo Й—um, hiЙ“e yedda"
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maayЙ“e Й“en, a nanintaa faaЙ—uЙ“e Й“en kadi noddaandu ndun, si Й“e runtiima Й“e huccinii Й“abbe (maЙ“Й“e)"
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoowo wumЙ“e Й“en e majjere maЙ“Й“e. A nanintaa si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, hara ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e"
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o on e lo'ere, refti O waЙ—i Й“aawo lo'ere nden cemmbe, refti O waЙ—i Й“aawo cemmbe Й—en lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Himo taga ko O muuyi, Ko Kanko woni AnnduЙ—o, HattanЙ—o"
  30,55,"Г‘alnde Darngal nal darotoo, bomЙ“e Й“en woonday Й“e ГұiiЙ“aali si wanaa saanga. Ko wano nii Й“e wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)"
  30,56,"OkkaaЙ“e ganndal e gomЙ—inal Й“en wi'a: \"GomЙ—ii on ГұiiЙ“ii e ko Alla winndi kon, haa Гұalnde ummital. Ko ndee woni Гұalaande ummital, kono onon on anndaano"
  30,57,"Nden Гұalnde, ngantooji Й—in nafoytaa tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, wanaa kamЙ“e woni ko Й—aЙ“Й“iretee welayee [Alla]. @Corrected"
  30,58,"GomЙ—ii Men piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii Й“e Aaya, Й“en yedduЙ“e wi'ay: \"On wonaali, si wanaa meerenteeЙ“e"
  30,59,Ko wano nii Alla notira e Й“erЙ—e Й“en Й“e anndaa
  30,60,"MuГұГұo, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goona. Wata Й“e hoynuma Й“en hoyfine"
  31,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  31,2,"ЖҠee, ko Aayeeje Deftere ГұeГұaande nden"
  31,3,Ko nde peewal e yurmeende wonannde moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en
  31,4,"Й“en ГұinnooЙ“e julde nden, Й“e totta aakkal on, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yananaaЙ“e (fii laakara)"
  31,5,"Ko Й“en woni e peewal immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  31,6,"Hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, soodiroowo mbeleeЙ—e konnguЙ—i haa o majjira e laawol Alla ngol ko aldaa e ganndal, o jogitora (Aayeeje) Й—en jalnitgol. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte hoynooje"
  31,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й—en janngaama e makko, o huccitira(runtora) townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali Й—e, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. weltanir-mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  31,8,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji neema"
  31,9,"Ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton, Й—um ko fodoore Alla goongunde. Ko Kanko woni On FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  31,10,"O tagirii kammuuli Й—in ko aldaa e tugaale, Й—e yi'oton; O werlii ka leydi pelle fii wata ndi dillidu e mon; O saaki e mayri kala ruugayngel. Men jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, Men fuЙ—ini e mayri kala nooneeji tedduЙ—i"
  31,11,"ЖҠum Й—oo ko tagu Alla. Hollee Lam ko Й—i (rewoton Й—in) gaanin Makko tagi?\" Si ko woni, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en no e majjere Й“anngunde"
  31,12,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Luqmaan ГұenЖҙal: \"Wonnde yettu Alla. Kala yettuЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o yettani; kala non yedduЙ—o, anndu pellet, Alla ko Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  31,13,"Janto tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo geЙ—al makko on, hari himo waajoo mo: \"Ko an Й“inngel am, wata a sirkan Alla. Pellet, sirku on ko tooГұe mawЙ—e"
  31,14,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on [Й—oftagol] jibimЙ“e mo Й“en; yumma makko saawirii mo lo'ere e hoore lo'ere: entugol mo ngol, ko e nder duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i. \"Wonnde yettam e jinnaaЙ“e maa Й“en. Ko ka Am woni waЙ—tinirde nden"
  31,15,"Si Й“e tiiЙ—norii ma fii sirkangol Lam e ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wata a Й—ofto Й“e; wonndir e maЙ“Й“e ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere. Jokku laawol on ruttiiЙ—o e Am. Refti ko ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi yeetitoo on, ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  31,16,"Ko an Й“inngel am, anndu Й—en [golle bonЙ—e maa moЖҙЖҙe], si fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi foГұГұe, Й—um wona e fetere, maa ka kammuuli maa ka leydi, Alla artiray nde. Pellet, Alla ko NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  31,17,"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, ГұiiЙ“nu julde nden, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere, haЙ—aa ЕӢiГұere(pankare), muГұГұo-Й—aa e ko heЙ“u-maa. Pellet, Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e fiyakkuji mawЙ—i. @Corrected"
  31,18,"Wata fal yimЙ“e Й“en yeeso maa ngon, wata a yahru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙagol. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙotooЙ—o mantoo"
  31,19,"Hakindo e yahdu-maa ndun, joltinaa(ustu) hito maa ngon; ko Й“uri aГұeede e hitooji Й—in, pellet, ko luukaadu mbabba"
  31,20,"E on yi'aali wonnde Alla eltanii on ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi? O huuЙ“itiri on neemaaji Makko feeГұuЙ—i e suuЙ—iiЙ—i. Hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, on wennjiroowo e fii Alla, ko aldaa e gannndal, wanaa peewal, wanaa Deftere jabunde"
  31,21,"Si Й“e wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", Й“e wi'a: \"Si ko woni, men jokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en\"; e hay si tawii seytaane wonii hino nodda Й“e e lepte dulboowe ngen"
  31,22,"Kala jebbiluЙ—o yeeso mun ngon faade e Alla, hara ko o moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, gomЙ—ii o jaggiima e Й“oggol tiiЙ—ungol. Ko ka Alla woni battane fiyakuuji Й—in"
  31,23,"Kala yedduЙ—o, wata keeferaaku makko sunine. Ko ka Amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e, Men humpita Й“e ko Й“e huuwunoo. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o jaati Й“erЙ—e"
  31,24,"Men dakmitay Й“e seeЙ—a, refti Men forsaЙ“e e lepte tekkuЙ—e"
  31,25,"Pellet, si a lamndike Й“e : \"Ko hommbo tagi kammiili Й—in e leydi ndin?\" Ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ko Alla!\" Maaku: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla!\". Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  31,26,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla, ko Kanko woni Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  31,27,"Hay si tawii ko woni ka hoore leydi kon e leЙ—Й—e, [settiraama] karambi, maayo ngon Й“eydora (wontugol ndaha) Й“aawo Й—um, yeru maaje jeeЙ—iЙ—i, konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in lannataa. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  31,28,"Tagugol on e immintingol wonaali, si wanaa wa (tagugol) wonkii gooti. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  31,29,"E a yi'aali wonnde Alla no naada jemma on e nder Гұalora on, O naada Гұalorma kadi e nder jemma on, O eltii kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal? E wonnde Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  31,30,"ЖҠum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga, e wonnde kon ko Й“e noddata gaanin Makko, ko Й—um woni meere nden, e wonnde ko Alla woni ToowuЙ—o, MawnuЙ—o On"
  31,31,"E a yi'aali wonnde laaЙ—e Й—en hino dogira ka maayo e neema Alla, fii yo O hollu on maandeeji Makko Й—in? Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde kala heewuЙ—o-muГұal, yettoowo (neema)"
  31,32,"Si tawii morlooЙ—e(bempejje) hippiriiЙ“e wa duule [maa pelle], Й“e nodday Alla, hara hiЙ“e laЙ“Й“inani Mo dewal; tuma nde O daЙ—ndunooЙ“e ka njorndi, tawi no e maЙ“Й“e hakindiiЙ—o. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wanaa kala heewuЙ—o janfa, keefeero"
  31,33,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Hulee Joomi mon, hulon Гұalaande, nde baaba duncanoytaa Й“iЙ—Й—o mun, wanaa Й“iЙ—Й—o on kadi duncanoyta ben mun hay huunde. Pellet, fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata hodu on e Alla, (seytaane) hodoowo"
  31,34,"Pellet, ko ka Alla woni anndal Darngal, Himo jippina toЙ“o; Himo anndi ko woni ka nder renngaaji. Wonkii (woo) anndaa ko ki faggitoto janngo, wonkii (woo) kadi anndaa ko e leydi honndi maayata. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  32,2,"Jippineede Deftere nden, sikke woo alaa e mu'un, ko immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  32,3,"Walla Й“e wi'ay kanko (Muhammadu) o fefindi nde? Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo a jertin yimЙ“e, Й“e jertinoowo araano e mun ado maaЙ—a, belajo'o, Й“e feeway"
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, e nder balЙ—e jeegoo. Refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arski\". Alanaa on gaanin Makko, giЙ—o wanaa tefoowo. E on waajitotaako? @Corrected"
  32,5,"Himo fewja fiyaakuuji Й—in ka kammu haa ka leydi, refti Й—i Жҙeenga ka Makko, e Гұalaande nde emmbere mun woni, duuЙ“i ujunere e ko limoton"
  32,6,"On [fewjoowo fii Й—um on], ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, FooluЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o"
  32,7,On labinЙ—o kala huunde nde O tagi. O fuЙ—Й—i tagude neЙ—Й—anke ndin e loopal
  32,8,"refti O waЙ—i geyngol makko ngol, e sortondiral, immorde ndihal [maniiyu] lo'uЙ—am"
  32,9,"refi O fotndindiri mo, O wutti e makko Ruuhu Makko on. O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. [Kono] fanЙ—ii ko yettonton"
  32,10,"ЖҒe wi': \"E nee, si min majjii ka leydi, eyoo men wontay e tagu hesu?\" Ko woni kamЙ“e e hawrugol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e [Й—um]"
  32,11,"Maaku: \"Ko hunnata on, ko malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaaЙ—o on. Refti ko ka Joomi mon rutteteЙ—on"
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'ayno, tuma nde bomЙ“e Й“en ugginta ko'e-maЙ“Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e! [lЖҒe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, men yi'ii men nanii, rutton men, men golla ko moЖҙЖҙi; menen men yananaama"
  32,13,"Sinno Men muuyuno, Men okkayno kala wonkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : \"Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"
  32,14,"MeeЙ—iree (lepte Й—en) sabu welsindagol mon hawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon Й—oo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. MeeЙ—iree lepte luttal, sabu ko huuwaynoЙ—on kon"
  32,15,"Anndee ko gomЙ—inta Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e waajoraama Й—e, Й“e suuyiray sujjugol, Й“e subbuhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako"
  32,16,"Becce maЙ“Й“e Й—en hino woЙ—Й—itoo e lelorЙ—e Й—en, hiЙ“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e kulol e tama'u; e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e, hiЙ“e wintoo"
  32,17,"Wonkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa Й“e e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“ernde, Й—um ko njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  32,18,"E on laatiiЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), Й“e fotataa"
  32,19,"Si ko Й“en omЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu koЙ“e gollaynoo kon"
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e, haray femporde Й“en Й—on nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala Й“e faalaa yaltugol e magge, Й“e ruttitee e magge, Й“e wi'anee: \"MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge fennayoЙ—on ngen"
  32,21,"Ma Men meeЙ—inir Й“e lepte aduna, ado lepte mawЙ—e Й—en (laakara), belajo'o, Й“e ruttitoto"
  32,22,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude wano waajoraaЙ—o Aayeeje Joomi mun Й—en, refti o Й—uurnii Й—e ! Pellet, Menen, ko Men yoftotooЙ“e e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  32,23,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, - wata a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Men waЙ—i nde Й—oworde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  32,24,"Men waЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ardiiЙ“e, Й—owirooЙ“e (yimЙ“e Й“en) yamiroore Amen, nde Й“e muГұГұinoo, Й“e woni yananaaЙ“e e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko senndoyta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e lurraynoo e fii mun"
  32,26,"E feeГұanaali Й“e, no foti Й—uuЙ—ude e ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire, hiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e? Pellet, no e Й—um, tasakuyeeji ! E Й“ee haqqiltaa"
  32,27,"E Й“e yi'aali, wonnde MeЙ—en soggira ndiyam Й—am ka leydi hokkundi, Men yaltinira Й—am remuru, ndu neemoraaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e e kamЙ“e Гұaamata e mun? E Й“e yi'ataa"
  32,28,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  32,29,"Maaku: \"Г‘alnde uddial ngal, ko heeferЙ“e Й“en gomЙ—inoyta nafoytaaЙ“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni nennanteeЙ“e"
  32,30,"ЖҠuurno Й“e, haЙ“Й“ito-Й—aa. KamЙ“e kan, ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itiiЙ“e (lepte)"
  33,1,"Ko an yo Annabiijo! Hulu Alla, wata a Й—ofto heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla laatike AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  33,2,"Jokku ko wahayinaa kon e maaЙ—a, immorde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, Alla laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  33,3,Fawo e Alla. Alla yonii faweteeЙ—o e mun
  33,4,"Alla waЙ—anaali neЙ—Й—anke Й“erЙ—e Й—iЙ—i e nder fulkuru makko. O waЙ—aali kadi resondiraaЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e nanndinirton, neeniraaЙ“e mon. O waЙ—aali kadi nodditirayЙ“e on (baaba Й“en), Й“iЙ—Й“e mooЙ—on. ЖҠum mooЙ—on, ko kongol mon [yaltungol e] kunndule mon. Alla non, no daala goonga, ko Kanko woni fewnoowo e focciingol ngol"
  33,5,"Noddiree Й“e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en: ko Й—um Й“uri nunЙ—ude ka Alla. Si tawii non on anndaa baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, haray ko musiЙ—Й“e mon ka diina e heftodiiЙ“e mon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on e ko woopoton (faayon) e mun, kono (on bakkondinay e) ko faandoriЙ—on Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en. Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,6,"Ko Annabiijo on Й“uri hanndude e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en diini ko'e maЙ“Й“e; suddiiЙ“e makko Й“en, ko neeniraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e. JoomiraaЙ“e enЙ—amaaji Й“en, ko yoga maЙ“Й“e Й“uri hanndude yoga [e ndonndi ndin] ka Deftere Alla, diini gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e feruЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa hara on waЙ—an weldiiЙ“e mon [Й“e ronataa] Й“en moЖҙЖҙere. ЖҠum wonii ko winndaa ka deftere"
  33,7,"Janto tuma nde Men Жҙettidunoo e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ahadi maЙ“Й“e, e ma'a an kadi, e Nuuhu, e Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on: Men Жҙettidi e maЙ“Й“e ahadi tiiЙ—undi"
  33,8,"fii no [Alla] lamdora goonguЙ“e Й“en e goonga maЙ“Й“e kan. O hebilanii yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte muusuuЙ—e"
  33,9,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Annditee neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on, tuma nde koneeli arunoo on, Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e henndu e konuuli, ngu on yi'aali. Alla siforii RentuЙ—o ko golloton"
  33,10,"Tuma nde Й“e ardirannoo on, ka senngo dow mon e ka ley [saare] mon, e tuma nde gite ooГұinoo, Й“erЙ—e Й—en hewtiri ka lookoЖҙe, hiЙ—on jikka Alla (ontuma) jikke luutondirЙ—e"
  33,11,"Ko Й—on gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en njariba, Й“e dilliniraa dillere saЙ—tunde"
  33,12,"Janto kadi, tuma nde naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun wi'aynoo: \"Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on fodaali men, si wanaa hodo"
  33,13,"E tuma nde fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e wi'unoo: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e Yathrib ! Г‘iiЙ“irde alanaa on (Й—oo), yiltitee [ka mon]\". Fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e no waynitoo Annabiijo on, hiЙ“e wi'a : \"CuuЙ—i amen Й—in ko na huncii\", hara non wanaa Й—i hunciiЙ—i: Й“e faandaaki, si wanaa dogugol"
  33,14,"Hay si tawno (ayЙ“e) Й“en naatiranno Й“e Й“annge mayre, refti Й“e lanndaa fitina (yeddugol), pellet, Й“e wonayno e mun, Й“e leelnataano e Й—um, si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  33,15,"hara le gomЙ—ii Й“e ahodiino e Alla ko adii, wonnde Й“e runtotaako Й“abbe. Ahadi Alla ndin non, ndi laatike lannditorteendi"
  33,16,"Maaku: \"Dogugol nafataa on, si on dogu maayde maa hare; haray Й—um, on dakmitetaake, si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  33,17,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo woni daЙ—ndoowo on e Alla, si O faandanike on bone, maa si O faandanike on yurmeende?\" ЖҒe heЙ“antaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e gaanin Alla, giЙ—o wanaa ballo"
  33,18,"GomЙ—ii Alla no anndi falaotooЙ“e Й“en e mon, e Й“en wi'anooЙ“e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en :\"Aree e amen\", hara non Й“e arataa e hare nden, si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  33,19,"ko wuddan Й“e on. Si kulol ngol arii, a yi'ay hiЙ“e ndaare, hara gite maЙ“Й“e no yiilora wa mo maayde suddaa e mun. Si kulo ngol non yehii, Й“e laggora Й—emЙ—e muusuЙ—e, wuddangol moЖҙЖҙere nden. ЖҒen Й—on, Й“e gomЙ—inaali, Alla bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. ЖҠum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  33,20,"HiЙ“e sikka koneeli Й—in yahataa. Hay si koneeli Й—in artii, Й“ee [naafiqiiЙ“e] yelotono sinno hara nun hiЙ“e ka ladde hakkunde yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, hara hiЙ“e lanndo fii mon. Hay si Й“e tawtodano e mon, Й“e haЙ“ataano si wanaa seeЙ—a nii"
  33,21,"GomЙ—ii laatanike on e NulaaЙ—o Alla on, Гұemtinal moЖҙЖҙal, wonannde on jortiiЙ—o Alla, e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, o jantii Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  33,22,"Nde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en yi'unoo koneeli Й—in, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko Й—um woni ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on fodi men; haray Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on goongii\". ЖҠum Й“eydaali Й“e, si wanaa gomЙ—inal e jebbilaare"
  33,23,"Hino e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, worЙ“e hunnuЙ“e ko Й“e ahodi e Alla kon : hino e maЙ“Й“e timminЙ—o takke mun Й—en (haa o sahodinaa), hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi haЙ“Й“itiiЙ—o; Й“e waЙ—titaali (ahadi ndin) mbattiigu"
  33,24,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“ir hunnuЙ“e Й“en sabu goongude maЙ“Й“e, O lepta naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, si Mo yiЙ—i, maa O jaЙ“ana Й“e tuubuubuyee. Tawde pellet, Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,25,"Alla ruttidii yedduЙ“e Й“en e tikkere maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e heЙ“aali moЖҙЖҙere. Alla yonii gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e hare. Alla siforii Cemmbe e Poolal"
  33,26,"O jipiini Й“en wallindirnooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, ka tataaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O weddii Й—enЖҙere e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e; fedde goo (e maЙ“Й“e) hiЙ—on wara, hiЙ—on daha kadi fede goo"
  33,27,"O ronini on leydi maЙ“Й“e, e galleeji maЙ“Й“e, e jawle maЙ“Й“e, e leydi ndi on tippaano e mun. Alla siforii hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,28,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Maakan suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en: \"Si wonii ko nguurndam aduna faalaЙ—on e cuЙ—aari majjam, haray aree mi dakmita on, mi seera on [ontuma] cergal moЖҙЖҙal"
  33,29,"Si tawii non ko Alla faalaЙ—on, e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e galle laakara Й—en, haray pellet, Alla maranii moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en e mooЙ—on, njoЙ“di mawndi"
  33,30,"Ko onon yo suddiiЙ“e Annabiijo on ! Kala adduЙ—o e mooЙ—on bone Й“annguЙ—o, lepte Й—en sowirante mo cowalle Й—iЙ—i! ЖҠum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  33,31,"Kala e mooЙ—on Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Men yoЙ“iray mo njoЙ“di makko ndin laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i, MeЙ—en marani mo kadi, arsike tedduЙ—o"
  33,32,"Ko onon yo suddiiЙ“e Annabiijo! On wa'aa wano gooto e suddiiЙ“e Й“en. Si on gomЙ—ii, haray wata on yergin konngol, sakko on mo Гұawu [tuuyo] woni e Й“ernde mun tamЖҙinoo. Wowlon konngol moЖҙЖҙol"
  33,33,"Г‘iiЙ“ee ka cuuЙ—i mon; wata on feГұГұinir cuЙ—aari mon, wano wirtaare majjere adinooЙ“e. Г‘iiЙ“nee Julde nden, totton askal on, Й—oftoЙ—on Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Anndee ko Alla faandii, ko ittanta on e tuuЙ—e, onon yimЙ“e suudu [Annabiijo], O laЙ“Й“inira on laЙ“Й“ingol"
  33,34,"Jantee ko wonaa e janngeede ka cuuЙ—i mon, immorde e Aayeeje Alla, e Sunna. Pellet, Alla laatike NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  33,35,"Pellet, juulЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e juulЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e Й—oftiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e goonguЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e goonguЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e muГұГұiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e muГұГұiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e yankiniiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e yankiniiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sakkotooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sakkotooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoorooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e hoorooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e worЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mun e rewЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mun, e worЙ“e jantotooЙ“e Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i Й“en e rewЙ“e jantotooЙ“e Й“en: Alla maranii Й“en, haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  33,36,"Alanaa gomЙ—iЙ—o gorko, wanaa gomЙ—inЙ—o debbo, si Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Гұaawii fiyaaku, nde suЙ“agol e fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on. Kala non yedduЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray o majjii majjere Й“anngunde"
  33,37,"Janto tuma maakanayno-Й—aa on mo Alla neemini e mun, moЖҙЖҙu-Й—aa e makko: \"Jogitano suddiiЙ—o maa on, hoore-maa, hulaa Alla\", hiЙ—a suuЙ—a e fonndo maa, ko Alla feГұГұinta. HiЙ—a hula yimЙ“e Й“en, kono ko Alla fotu-Й—aa hulude. Tuma Zaydu huntunoo e (suddiiЙ—o) on haaju, Men resin-maa mo, fii wata Й“ittere wonu e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, e (resugol) suddiiЙ“e nodditiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, si Й“en huntii e maЙ“Й“e haaju. Yamiroore Alla nden laatike golleteende"
  33,38,"Feloore alanaa Annabiijo on, e kon ko Alla daginai mo, Й—um ko Гұaawoore Alla e Й“en feЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ado makko. Г‘aawoore Alla nde wonii eЙ“Й“aande hoddiraande"
  33,39,"ЖҒen yottiinooЙ“e nule Alla Й—en, Й“e no hula Mo, Й“e hula goЙ—Й—o goo si wanaa Alla. Alla yonii hasboowo"
  33,40,"Muhammadu wonaali baaba hay goot e worЙ“e mon, ko [o] woni, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla e timmoode AnnabaaЙ“e. Alla laatike AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,41,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, jantoree Alla jantoore Й—uuЙ—unde"
  33,42,Subhinee Mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e
  33,43,"Ko Kanko woni yurmeteeЙ—o on, -e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en (du'orana on), - fii no O yaltinira on e niЙ“e faade e annoora. O siforii hinnotooЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұalnde Й“e hawrata e Makko, ko \"Salaam\" [kisiyee], O maranii Й“e mbarjaari teddundi"
  33,45,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men nulirii ma [fii yo wonu] seediiЙ—o, e wewlinoowo e jertinoowo"
  33,46,"e noddoowo faade e Alla, duЕӢayee Makko; e pitilol jalЙ“ungol"
  33,47,"Wewlinir gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, wonnde no woodani Й“e ka Alla, Й“ural mawnungal"
  33,48,"Wata a Й—ofto heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, Й—uurno (e) lorra maЙ“Й“e kan, fawo-Й—aa e Alla. Sabu Alla yonii ka fawee"
  33,49,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si resii rewЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, refti on seerii Й“e ado on meemondirde e maЙ“Й“e, haray alanaa on e maЙ“Й“e, edda mo Й“e eddinotoo. Dakmitiree Й“e [njooЙ“a], seeriron Й“e cergal laЙ“aangal"
  33,50,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men daginanii ma suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en Й“e jonnu-Й—aa teЕӢe mun Й“en, e Й“en [horЙ“e] Й“e jeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa, e Й“en [dahaaЙ“e] Й“e Alla neldu-maa, e jiwЙ“e bappa maa, e jiwЙ“e yaayiraaЙ“e maa, e jiwЙ“e kaawu-maa, e jiwЙ“e neeniraaЙ“e maa, - Й“en feridunooЙ“e e maa, - e suddiiЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o, si o yeЙ—ii hoore-makko Annabiijo on, si Annabiijo on kadi faandike resugol mo : Й—um ko ko heerani maa, gaanin gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en anndi ko Men farli e maЙ“Й“e kon, e fii suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ko Й“e jeytiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en, fii wata Й“iЙ—teende wonu e maaЙ—a. Alla laatike haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,51,"HiЙ—a nennintina on mo yiЙ—u-Й—aa (nennintinnde) e maЙ“Й“e, Й“aЙ—tinaa e maaЙ—a on mo yiЙ—u-Й—aa. E on mo Й—aЙ“Й“u-Й—aa (belagol ka mun) e Й“en Й“e nennitu-Й—aa, bakkaaku woo fawaaki ma. Ko Й—um Й“uri Й“adaade e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, hara Й“e sunotaako, Й“e weltora kadi ko okku-Й—aa Й“e kon, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e. Alla no Anndi ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon. Alla laatike AnnduЙ—o, MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  33,52,"RewЙ“e Й“en dagitantaako ma Й“aawo [Й“ee Й—oo], wanaa nde waЙ—titirtaa Й“e genndiraaЙ“e goo, hay si ЕӢari Й“en Й—on haawnii ma; si wanaa Й“e jeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa Й“en. Alla laatike tommbiiЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,53,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Wata on naatu ka cuuЙ—i Annabiijo on, si wanaa hara on nodda e Гұaametee, hara wanaa yo on habbito ko Й“enndi ka makko. Kono si on noddaa ma, naatee. Si on Гұaamii, sentee, hara on Й—aЙ“Й“aali haala. Anndon Й—um mooЙ—on, hino lorraynoo Annabiijo on, kono o hersa (haalannde) on, Alla non Й—alataa [yamirde] goonga. Si on lanndoto (suddiiЙ“e makko) Й“en haaju, lanndoree Й“e Й“aawo wirngallo: ko Й—um mooЙ—on, Й“uri laaЙ“annde Й“erЙ—e mon e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Haananaa on nde lorroton NulaaЙ—o Alla on, wanaa nde resoton suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“aawo makko, poomaa; pellet, waЙ—ugol mon Й—um, wonii ko mawni ka Alla"
  33,54,"Si on feГұГұinii huunde, maa on suuЙ—ii nde, pellet, Alla laatike annduЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,55,"Bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa kadi Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e miГұГұiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en, wanaa e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wanaa e Й“en Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e. Hulee Alla (yo suddiiЙ“e). Pellet, Alla siforii seediiЙ—o kala huunde"
  33,56,"Pellet, Alla e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hiЙ“e du'anaade Annabiijo on; ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, juulee e makko, toranoЙ—on [Mo] kisiyee"
  33,57,"Pellet, Й“en lorrooЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Alla huЙ—ii Й“en aduna e laakara, O hebilanii Й“e kadi lepte hoynooje"
  33,58,"ЖҒen kadi lorrooЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoore ko Й“e faggitaaki, gomЙ—ii Й“e ronndike fenaande e bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o"
  33,59,"Ko an yo Annabiijo! Maakan suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en, e jiwЙ“e maa Й“en, e genndiraaЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, nde Й“e joltinta e maЙ“Й“e, wutteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko Й—um Й“urata Й“aЙ—taade, nde Й“e annditetee, hara Й“e torraaka. Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  33,60,"Pellet, si naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en haЙ—itaaki, e Й“en Й“e Гұawu (sikkitaare) woni e Й“erЙ—e mun, e fena-fenta'en ka saare Madiina, ma Men wurtite e maЙ“Й“e, refi Й“e kawtirtaa e maaЙ—a ton, si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  33,61,"Ko huЙ—aa Й“e. Kala ka Й“e tawaa, ko Й“e nanngetee Й“e, Й“e waree wargol"
  33,62,"ЖҠum ko sunna Alla e Й“en wulinooЙ“e ko adii. A heЙ“antaa laawol (sunna) Alla ngol, battiigu"
  33,63,"YimЙ“e Й“en o lanndo maa fii Darngal. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal daragol maggal, ko ka Alla woni\". E ko anndin maa, wonnde no hasii hara Darngal ngal Й“adike"
  33,64,"Pellet, Alla huЙ—ii heeferЙ“e Й“en, O kammbiranii Й“e kadi dulboowe"
  33,65,"ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton poomaa. ЖҒe heЙ“ataa giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  33,66,"Г‘alnde geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en waylitetee ka Yiite, Й“e wi'ay: \"Ee jalla amen! Hara men Й—oftino Alla, men Й—oftii NulaaЙ—o on"
  33,67,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, Menen men Й—ofti hooreeЙ“e amen e mawЙ“e amen, Й“e majjini men e laawol ngol"
  33,68,"Joomi amen, tottu Й“e cowanlle Й—iЙ—i e lepte Й—en, huЙ—aa Й“e kuddi mawndi"
  33,69,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Wata on wa'u wa Й“en lorrunooЙ“e Muusaa, Alla woЙ—Й—ini mo e ko Й“e wi'i kon, tawde o wonii tedduЙ—o ka Alla"
  33,70,"Ko on yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Hulee Alla, wowlon konngol feewungol"
  33,71,"[Si on waЙ—ii Й—um], O moЖҙЖҙinanay on golle mon, O haforana on junuubi mon. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray o maliraama maloore mawnde"
  33,72,"Men weeЙ“itii hoolaare nden e dow kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin e pelle Й—en, Й—i haЙ—itii ronndagol nde, Й—i huli (battane) majji, neЙ—Й—o on kan ronndii nde; tawde pellet, o wonii Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o-tooГұude [hoore-mun], majjaaЙ—o [battane Й—um]"
  33,73,"[NeЙ—Й—o on ronndiraama Й—um], no Alla leptira naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sirkooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e (no) Alla jaЙ“irana gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en tuububuyee. Alla laatike Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  34,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On jeyЙ—o kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Hino woodani Mo kadi yettoore ka laakara. Ko Kanko woni Г‘eeГұo, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  34,2,"Himo anndi ko naatata ka leydi, e ko yaltata e mayri, ko jippotoo iwra ka kammu e ko Жҙawata e maggu. Ko Kanko woni Hinnotoo, Haforoowo"
  34,3,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Darngal ngal arataa men\". Maaku: \"aa'a! Mi woondirii Joomi am! pellet, ko aray e mon. [Joomi ma] ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i. Huunde wirnanaaki Mo, ko fotata e abbere jarra, woni ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um fanЙ—ude, wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um mawnude, si wanaa no e deftere feГұГұinnde"
  34,4,"Fii yo O yoЙ“oy Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede, e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  34,5,"ЖҒen non yaccii Й“e e bonnitugol Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte, immorde e Й“urЙ—e muusude"
  34,6,"ЖҒen okkaaЙ“e ganndal hino yi'ira jippiniraande nden e maaЙ—a, immorde ka Joomi maa, ko kayre woni goonga, hinde fewnira e laawol FooluЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  34,7,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kadi wi'i: \"On accay men tinndina on fii gorko, mo no humpita on, wonnde si on muncitaama kala muncitannde, on wontoyay e tagu hesu"
  34,8,"O fefindi fenaande e hoore Alla? Kaa hara ko jinna nanngi mo? Si ko woni, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara on, Й“e wonii e lepte e majjere woЙ—Й—iinde (goonga)"
  34,9,"E Й“ee yi'aali ko woni yeeso maaЙ“e e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Si Men muuyiino, Men munnirayno Й“e leydi ndin, maa Men fukkina e maЙ“Й“e taЖҙontine (lepte), immorde ka kammu. Wonii e Й—um, maande, wonannde kala jeyaaЙ—o ruttotooЙ—o (e Joomi mun)"
  34,10,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Daawuuda Й“ural, immorde e Amen. [Men wi'i]: \"Ko onon pelle e colli, subbunhinodee e makko. Men newinani mo (tafugol) njamndi ndin"
  34,11,"(Men wi'ani mo wonnde): \"Gollu wutteeji njamndi, eЙ“Й“aa ka tafoodi. Gollon golle moЖҙЖҙe, pellet, ko Mi ReenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  34,12,"(Men eltani kadi) Sulaymaana henndu ndun: dawol mayru ko yeru (yaadu) lewru, kirndol mayru kadi ko yeru (yaadu) lewu. Men honcinani mo Й“unndu sila (kire). Hino jinnaaji Й—in, golliraynooЙ—i yeeso makko, e duЕӢayee Joomi Makko. Kala ooГұiingii e majji, gaay e yamiroore Amen nden, Men meeЙ—ina ngii lepte dulЙ“oowe ngen"
  34,13,"HiЙ—i gollana mo ko o faalaa: gila e tataaji, e nanndollaaji, e looЙ—e wa'uЙ—e wa beeli, e payanЙ—e feЕӢiiЙ—e. \"Gollee, onon Й“eynguure Daawuuda, yetton (Alla)\", fanЙ—ii e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, yettoowo (Lam)"
  34,14,"Nde Men Гұaawunoo e makko maayde nden, anndinaali Й—i fii maayde makko nden, si wanaa gannguuji leydi(mooЖҙu) Й—in, hino Гұaama tuggordu makko ndun. Nde o fukkinoo, feeГұani jinnaaji Й—in, wonnde si Й—i anndunoo ko wirnii, Й—i ГұiiЙ“ataano e lepte [jeyaagu] hoynooje"
  34,15,"GomЙ—ii wonaniino yimЙ“e Saba'i Й“en e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, maande; gese Й—iЙ—i ka bannge Гұaamo e ka nano. (Men wi'ani Й“e): \"Г‘aamee e arsike Joomi mon, yetton Mo. Leydi ndin ko laaЙ“undi, e Joomiraawo Haforoowo"
  34,16,"(Kono) Й“e Й—uunii. Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e ndiyam waame, Men waЙ—titani Й“e gese maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й—iЙ—i, gese (goo) Й—iЙ—i, marЙ—e Гұaametee haaЙ—uЙ—o, e (leЙ—Й—e) duЙ“Й“eeje, e huunde e jaaЙ“e seeЙ—aaje"
  34,17,"Ngool (yaggingol), Men yoЙ“irЙ“e ko Й“e yeddi kon. E hara Men yoЙ“ay si wanaa yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  34,18,"Men waЙ—i hakkune maЙ“Й“e e koЙ—ooli Й—i Men waЙ—i barki e mun Й—in, koЙ—ooli feeГұondirЙ—i, Men eЙ“Й“i e majji yaadu. (Men wi'ani Й“e): \"Yehee ton jemmaaji e Гұalormaaji, ko on hooliiЙ“e"
  34,19,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, woЙ—Й—indir hakkunde yaaduuji amen\", Й“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e, Men waЙ—ti fillitee Й“e fii mun, Men senndindiri Й“e hattirde e senndirgol. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, maandeeji wonannde kala heewuЙ—o muГұal, yettoowo (neema)"
  34,20,"GomЙ—ii Ibuliisa goonginii jikke mun Й—en e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe jokki mo, si wanaa fedde e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  34,21,"E doole alanaa mo e dow maЙ“Й“e, cemmbe (wurtugol), si wanaa tun, ko fii no Men anndira on gomЙ—inЙ—o laakara e on wonЙ—o e sikke fii mun. Joomi maa non, e dow kala huunde, ko O reenuЙ—o"
  34,22,"Maaku: \"Noddee Й—in Й—i Й—aynitorЙ—on [ reweteeЙ—i] gaanin Alla. ЖҠi jeyaa hay yeru abbere jarra, ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi. Alanaa Й—i e Й—in (kammuuli e leydi ndin) kafidaaЙ—o (geЙ“al), alanaa Mo e Й—in, hay wallondirteeЙ—o"
  34,23,"Tefoore woo nafataa ka Makko, si wanaa on Mo O duЕӢanii. Haa si Й—enЖҙere nden yaltinaama e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'a: \"Ko honЙ—um Joomi mon daali?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko goonga kan; ko Kanko woni ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"
  34,24,"Maaku: \"Kon hombo woni arsikiroowo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla. Ko si ko menen maa si ko onon, woni e peewal maa e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  34,25,"Maaku: \"On lamnditoytaake fii ko men bonni, menen kadi men lamnditoytaake fii ko huuwoton"
  34,26,"Maaku: \"Joomi men renndinoyay en, refti O Гұaawira hakkunde men goonga; Ko Kanko woni Г‘aawoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  34,27,"Maaku: \"Hollee lam Й—in Й—i waЙ—tidu-Й—on e Makko kafidiiЙ—i. Wanaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko Kanko woni Alla FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o On"
  34,28,"Men nuliraali ma, si wanaa e yimЙ“e Й“en fow: wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa"
  34,29,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  34,30,"Maaku: \"Hino woodani on fodoore, nde o nennitantaake e mayre fotde saa'i, on ardintinantaake nde kadi"
  34,31,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—intaa ndee Alqur'aanaare muk, wanaa nden adiinde nde\". Sinno a tinayno tuma nde tooГұuЙ“e Й“en darnetee ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hara yoga maЙ“Й“e no rutta yoga konngol, lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Si wanaano onon nun, men wonayno gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  34,32,"TownitinooЙ“e Й“en wi'ani lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en: \"E ko menen falinoo on e peewal Й“aawo ngal arde e mon? Si ko woni, on woniino bomЙ“e"
  34,33,"Lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en kadi wi'ani townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Si ko woni, ko pewje (mon) jemma e Гұalorma, tuma yamiraynoЙ—on men yo men yeddu Alla, men waЙ—ana Mo fotondirЙ—i\". ЖҒe suuЙ—i ninse Й—en, nde Й“e yi'unoo lepte Й—en. Men waЙ—i kolombooje e daaЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Hara Й“e yoЙ“itete si wanaa ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon"
  34,34,"Men nulaali jertinoowo e yimЙ“e saare, si wanaa neeminaaЙ“e mayre Й“en wi'ay: \"Menen ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on kon"
  34,35,"ЖҒe wi'i kadi: \"Ko menen Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude jawle e Й“iЙ“Й“e, men wonaali kadi lepteteeЙ“e"
  34,36,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyi, O Й“illini (mo O muuyi). Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa"
  34,37,"Wanaa jawle mon, wanaa jiidi mon woni ko Й“aЙ—tinirta on ka Amen Й“adal. Si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe; Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di sowaande, sabu ko Й“e golli kon, kamЙ“e ka soorooji, ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e"
  34,38,"ЖҒen yaccotooЙ“e e ronkingol (yimЙ“e Й“en) e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, ka ka nder lepte woni ko Й“e tawnoytee"
  34,39,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am hino weertana arsike on, mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“illini mo (O muuyi e maЙ“Й“e). Kala non ko wintiЙ—on e huunde, Kanko O lontinay nde. Ko Kanko woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"
  34,40,"Г‘alnde O mooЙ“tindiroyta Й“e dendaangal, refti O daalana Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en: \"E ko Й“ee Й—oo (yimЙ“e) rewaynoo on"
  34,41,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Senayee woodanii Ma! Ko An woni giЙ—o amen gaanin maЙ“Й“e. Toode ko jinnaaji Й—in Й“e rewaynoo, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—in (jinnaaji) gomЙ—ini"
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Men wi'anoya Й“en tooГұuЙ“e: \"MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge fennaynoЙ—on fii mun"
  34,43,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaamma e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Oo wonaali, si wanaa gorko faalaaЙ—o falagol on e ko baabiraaЙ“e mon rewayno rewaynoo\". ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ndee (AlqurвҖҷaanaare) wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande\". YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ani goonga kan nde ka arunoo e maЙ“Й“e: \"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"
  34,44,"Men addanaali Й“ee, defte Й—e Й“e janngata. Men meeЙ—aali nulude e maЙ“Й“e, jertinoowo ado maa"
  34,45,"AdinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en [kadi] fenniino (nulaaЙ“e mun). [YimЙ“e maa Й“en] yottaaki sappaЙ“al ko Men okkunoo Й“en kon. ЖҒen fenni NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, taskii no lepte Am Й—en wa'unoo"
  34,46,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (huunde) wootere: \"Ko nde daroranton Alla Й—iЙ—o Й—iЙ—o e gooto gooto, refti miijitoЙ—on. (Anndon) wondiiЙ—o mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  34,47,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di, Й—um ko fii mon. NjoЙ“di am ndin wonaali, si wanaa ka Alla. Kanko Ko O SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde"
  34,48,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am ko werlortooЙ—o [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga kan, timminЙ—o anndugol wirniiЙ—i"
  34,49,"Maaku: \"Goonga kan arii [Iislaamu on], meere [keeferaaku] ngun alaa ka feeГұa, kadi, nde ruttotaako"
  34,50,"Maaku: \"Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko O Nanoowo, ЖҒadiiЙ—o"
  34,51,"Sinno a tinayno, tuma nde Й“e Й—enyii, - laaworde alanaa (Й“e), - Й“e nanngiree e nokkuure Й“adiinde"
  34,52,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii [Darngal] ngal\", e ko honno gomЙ—inal woonirani Й“e e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o"
  34,53,"Hara non Й“e yeddiino nde ko adii, hiЙ“e werlora ko wirnii e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko Й“e tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo maЙ“Й“e ko adii, tawde Й“e woniino e sikke cikkiniiЙ—a"
  35,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, TaguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, WaЙ—uЙ—o Malaa'ika'en nulaaЙ“e, marЙ“e gabitanji(bibje) Й—i Й—iЙ—i, Й—i tati e nayi. Himo Й“eyda ko O muuyi e tagu Makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yimЙ“e Й“en, jogitotooЙ—o nde alaa; kala kadi ko O jogitii, accitoowo Й—um alaa Й“aawo (jogitagol) Makko. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  35,3,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! jantee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko! E ko honno yiilirteЙ—on [e kaa goonga]"
  35,4,"Si Й“e fennii ma, pellet NulaaЙ“e (goo) fennanooma ado maa. Ko faade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  35,5,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Anndee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata (seytaane) hodoowo on hodu on e fii Alla"
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo wonani on. Haray jogitoree mo gaГұo. Anndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no Й“e jeydiree e yimЙ“e dulЙ“oowe ngen"
  35,7,"Hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. ЖҒeya gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  35,8,"E ko on cuЙ—inanaaЙ—o golle mun bonЙ—e, hara himo yi'a Й—e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—e? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna Mo O muuyi. Wata a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e woni huuwude"
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni wurtuЙ—o keneeli Й—in, Й—i sogga duule, Men yarnira Й—um leydi yoorundi; Men wuurnitira Й—um leydi ndin, Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non ummital ngal"
  35,10,"Kala tawЙ—o ko teddungal faalaa (yo o Й—aЙ“Й“ir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fow: ko ka Makko woni ko konngol laaЙ“ungol Жҙawata, golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en Й“amta ngol. ЖҒen fewjooЙ“e boneeji, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. Pewje Й“en Й—en, ko bonay Й—e"
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu), refti O waЙ—i on nooneeji. Deyel saawataa, ngel lelnataa kadi, si wanaa e anndal Makko. WuurnaaЙ—o wuurnetaake, Й—uytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wanaa no e deftere. Pellet, Й—um ko newanii Й—um Alla"
  35,12,"Maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i fotataa: [Ndiyam] goo Й—oo Й—am, ko welЙ—am, laaЙ“ungo, newiingo njaram mun, ngoo Й—aa, ko lanЙ—am haaЙ—uЙ—am. HiЙ—on Гұaama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hiЙ—on yaltina kadi hen, cuЙ—aari ndi Й“oornotoЙ—on. HiЙ—a yi'a laaЙ—e Й—en no awja e maggo, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“iron e Й“ural Makko. Belajoo on yettay [Mo]"
  35,13,"Himo naada jemma on e der Гұalorma on, O naada Гұalorma on e nder jemma on. O elti kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On mooЙ—on woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko Kanko Laamu woodani. ЖҠiya Й—i noddoton gaanin Makko, Й—i jeytaa yeru gorol tamara"
  35,14,"Si on noddu Й—i, Й—i nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si Й—i nanoy, Й—i jaabitotaako on. Г‘alnde Darngal, Й—i yeddoyay sirku mon on. Alaa habroowo ma, wano HumpitiiЙ—o On"
  35,15,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, ko onon woni hatonjimЙ“e e Alla Й“en, Alla kan, ko Kanko woni Galo YettiniiЙ—o On"
  35,16,"Si O yiЙ—ii, O naЙ“a on, O adda tagu hesu"
  35,17,ЖҠum wonaali sattuЙ—um ka Alla
  35,18,"Wonki ronndotaako doЕӢgal wonkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay huunde, hay si ko Й“adondiraaЙ—o Anndu ko jertintaa [nana waaju], ko Й“en hulirooЙ“e Joomi mun ka wirnii, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e Julde. Kala on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o, haray ko hoore makko o woni laЙ“Й“inanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  35,19,BunЙ—o e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa niЙ“e Й—en e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa Й—owdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuurЙ“e Й“en fotata e maayЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [NulaaЙ—o], woni naninoowo, wonЙ“e ka genaale Й“en"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo feЖҙЖҙii e maЙ“Й“e"
  35,25,"Si Й“e fennii ma, hari adinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en fenniino (NulaaЙ“e mun), fewndo Й“en NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e addannoo Й“anngannduyeeji, e ЖҠeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yedduЙ“e Й“en (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An Й—en waЙ—tinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am dimЙ—e seertuЙ—e noone. Hino ka pelle, Й—ate daneeje e boЙ—eeje seertyuЙ—e noone, e pete Й“aleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yimЙ“e Й“en, e daabeeji Й—in, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, Й—i nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, ko annduЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"ЖҒen janngooЙ“e Deftere Alla nden, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e julde, Й“e nafqii ko Men arsiki Й“e kon gunndoo e kene, hiЙ“e jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“diiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O Й“eyda Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a e Deftere nden, ko Й—um woni goonga, gomЙ—inde e Й—en wonЙ—e yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o RentuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, Й“en Й“e Men suЙ“ii e jeyaaЙ“e Amen. Hino e maЙ“Й“e tooГұuЙ“e hoore-mun, hino e maЙ“Й“e hakindinЙ—o, hino e maЙ“Й“e foolondirooЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙereeji, duЕӢayee Alla; ko Й—um woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i naatata e mun, hara hiЙ“e cuЙ—iree ton, jawe kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise e luвҖҷu-luвҖҷu; comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittanЙ—o en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, WarjotooЙ—o"
  35,35,"On weernirЙ—o en Й“ural Makko ngal, e galle ГұiiЙ“al, tampere (woo) heЙ“ataa en ton, wanaa ronkere heЙ“ata en ton"
  35,36,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani Й“en; maayde Гұaawetaake e maЙ“Й“e, sakko Й“e maaya, Й“e hoynantaake kadi lepte magge Й—en. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta kala yedduЙ—o"
  35,37,"Hara hiЙ“e ooloo nder ton [Й“e wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla moЖҙЖҙere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo Й“e]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotooЙ—o waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa meeЙ—ee, sabu faabo alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko O AnnduЙ—o ko suuЙ—ii e Й“erЙ—e"
  35,39,"Ko Kanko woni waЙ—uЙ—o on lontiiЙ“e ka leydi. Kala yedduЙ—o, ko e makko lorra geddi makko yantata. Yeddugol heeferЙ“e Й“en, Й“eydataa Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa tikkere. Yeddugol Й“eydataa heeferЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa hayrere"
  35,40,"Maaku: \"E on yi'ii rendiiЙ—i mon rewoton gaanin Alla Й—in? Hollee lam ko Й—i tagi ka leydi. Kaa hiЙ—i mari geЙ“al e [tagugol] kammuuli Й—in? Kaa Men addan Й“e Deftere, nde Й“e woni e Й“anndannduyee mun? Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en alaa e fodude yoga maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa hodo"
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, fii wata Й—i dirtu. Hay si Й—i dirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako Й—i e Й“aawo Makko. O laatike MuГұГұiiЙ—o, Haforoowo"
  35,42,"ЖҒe woodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje maЙ“Й“e, wonnde si jertinoowo arii e maЙ“Й“e, pellet, Й“e wonay Й“urЙ“e feewude wootere e mofte Й—en. Nde jertinoowo non arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um Й“eydaali Й“e, si wanaa woЙ—Й—itagol"
  35,43,"[ЖҒe waЙ—iri Й—um] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje Й“enЙ—e. Pewje bonЙ—e Й—en non huuЙ“itataa, si wanaa jom-mun'en. Hara hiЙ“e sabbitii, si wanaa sunna (Alla) on e adinooЙ“e Й“en? A heЙ“antaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a heЙ“antaa sunna Alla waylirЙ—um"
  35,44,"E Й“ee yiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e taskoo ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wonirnoo? Hari no Й“uri Й“e tiiЙ—ude doole. Alla siforaali wonnde goЙ—Й—um no ronkina Mo ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o, HattanЙ—o"
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yimЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e faggitorii kon, O accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana Й“e haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal hewtii, [O nanngay Й“e], tawde pellet, Alla ko ReenuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  36,1,Yaa-Siin
  36,2,Mi woondirii Al*ur'aana ГұeГұaande nden
  36,3,"Pellet, an (NulaaЙ—o), ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  36,4,E dow laawol focciingol
  36,5,"Jippinannde On FooluЙ—o, Hinnotoo"
  36,6,"Fii yo a jertinir nde yimЙ“e, Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mun jertinanooka: Й“en ko welsindiiЙ“e"
  36,7,"GomЙ—ii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e; Й“en Й—on gomЙ—intaa"
  36,8,"Menen Men waЙ—ii ka daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e kolommbooje, Й—en ko yottiiЙ—e ka bokkuЙ—e; hara ko Й“e ЕӢalliniiЙ“e"
  36,9,"Men waЙ—i yeeso maЙ“Й“e heedo, Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e kadi heedo, Men hippi Й“e (gite Й—en); waЙ—ti Й“e yi'ataa [goonga]"
  36,10,"Hino fota e maЙ“Й“e, foti a jertini Й“e, maa a jertinaali Й“e; Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  36,11,"Anndu ko jertintaa (jaЙ“a), ko on jokkuЙ—o Jantoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o huli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo haforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi"
  36,12,"Ko Menen woni wuurnitooЙ“e maayЙ“e Й“en, Men winnda ko Й“e ardini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e. Kala huunde, MeЙ—en mofti nde e deftere Й“anngunde"
  36,13,"Piyan-Й“e misal, fii yimЙ“e saare, tuma nde NulaaЙ“e arunoo Й“e"
  36,14,"Nde Men nulunoo e maЙ“Й“e, [NulaaЙ“e] Й—iЙ—o, Й“e fenni Й“en, Men sammbiniri Й“en, tataЙ“o, Й“e wi'i: \"Menen, ko men NulaaЙ“e e mo'on"
  36,15,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] wi'i: \"On wonaali, si wanaa ko on Й“anndinke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaali hay huunde, on wonaali, si wanaa ko on fenooЙ“e"
  36,16,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en] wi'i: \"Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko men NulaaЙ“e e mo'on"
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wanaa yottingol Й“anngina"
  36,18,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] wi'iti: \"Men hiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on haЙ—itaaki, ma men fiЙ—u on, lepte muusuЙ—e kadi memira on immorde e amen"
  36,19,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en kadi] wi'iti: \"Kiite mon Й—in, hiЙ—on wonndi e mun. Ko si on waajaama (hiitinoЙ—on)? Tigi on, ko on yimЙ“e fantinooЙ“e"
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka Й“uri woЙ—Й—ude e saare nden, o ari himo yaccoo, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, kori jokkee NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  36,21,"jokkee Й“en Й“e lamndotaako on njoЙ“di, Й“en ko fewnaaЙ“e"
  36,22,E ko haЙ—ata lam rewugol On taguЙ—o Lam? Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde mon
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto reweteeЙ—i gaanin Makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii lam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali lam hay huunde, Й—i dЙ—andataa lam kadi"
  36,24,"Haray min ontuma, mi wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  36,25,"Min on, mi gomЙ—inii Joomi mon, nananee lam"
  36,26,"wi'anaa: \"Naatu Aljanna\". O wi'i: \"Haaniino yimЙ“e am Й“en annda"
  36,27,"ko Joomi am haforani lam, O waЙ—i lam e teddinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  36,28,"Men jippiniraano koneeli ka kammu, e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, Й“aawo maako. Men wonaanii jippinooЙ“e [Й—in koneeli]"
  36,29,"(Halkeede maЙ“Й“e) wonaali, si wanaa haacaango wooto, tawi Й“e laatii maayЙ“e-Й“utti"
  36,30,"Ee hayreede jeyaaЙ“e [fenunooЙ“e]! NulaaЙ—o araali e Й“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e waЙ—tayno mo jalnori"
  36,31,E Й“ee yi'aali Й—uuЙ—ii e gire Й—e Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e? Wonnde Й“en ruttitotaako e maЙ“Й“e
  36,32,"ЖҒe fow wonaali, si wanaa ko mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e ka Amen"
  36,33,"Hino wonani Й“e maande: leydi yoorundi ndin, Men wuurniti ndi, Men yaltini gabbe e mayri, tawi ko e Й—en Й“e Гұaamata"
  36,34,"Men waЙ—i e mayri gese tamarooje e inabuuje, Men Й“ulni e mayri Й“ulli(ceewle)"
  36,35,fii no Й“e Гұaamira dimЙ—e mun Й—en e kon ko Й“e golliri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. E Й“e yettataa (Alla)
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii taguЙ—o nooneeji Й—in On fow: gila e ko leydi ndin fuЙ—inta kon, haa e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e kon ko Й“e anndaa"
  36,37,"Maande goo kadi wonanii Й“e: e jemma on, MeЙ—en sorta e makko Гұalorma on, tawa Й“e wontii e niwre"
  36,38,"E naange ngen, hinge doga haa e ГұiiЙ“irde magge; Й—um ko eЙ“Й“oore FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o On"
  36,39,"E lewru ndun, Men eЙ“Й“ani ndu jipporde, haa ndu waЙ—tinira wa baaЕӢal tamaro kiiЙ—ngal"
  36,40,"Wanaa naange ngen woni ko haanini hewtitagol lewru ndun, wanaa jemma on woni ko aditotoo Гұalorma on; kala majji non, ko e laawol mun woni dogude"
  36,41,"Maande goo wonanii Й“e, wonnde Men roondike geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol, ka laana hebbinaaka"
  36,42,"Men tagani Й“e sugu makko, ko Й“e waЙ—Й—oo"
  36,43,"Si MeЙ—en yiЙ—uno, Men yoolayno Й“e; hara faabo alanaa Й“e, wanaa kadi Й“e daЙ—ndeteeЙ“e"
  36,44,"si wanaa yurmeende immornde e Amen, e dakmitagol haa e saanga"
  36,45,"Si Й“e wi'anaama: \"Rentee e kon ko woni yeeso mon e Й“aawo mon, belajo'o, on yurminte"
  36,46,"Aaya woo e Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en araali e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e Й—uurnooЙ—e"
  36,47,"Si Й“e wi'anaama kadi: \"Wintee(nafqe) e kon Alla arsiki on\", yedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ana gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"E men Гұamminay on tawЙ—o si Alla muuyuno, O Гұamminayno mo? On wonaali, si wanaa e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  36,48,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  36,49,"ЖҒe habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango wooto, nanngayngo Й“e, hara hiЙ“e yeddondira"
  36,50,"ЖҒe waawoytaa wasiyagol ontuma, wanaa Й“e ruttoytooЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en"
  36,51,"Wutte ka Alaandu, Й“e yaltira e genaale Й—en, Й“e heГұora ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  36,52,"hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ee bone amen! Ko hommbo immini men e genaale amen?\" Ko Й—um woni ko Hinaranke On fodunoo; NulaaЙ“e Й“en goonginii"
  36,53,"(Ummital) ngal wonaano, si wanaa haacaango gooto, tawi Й“e fow Й“e addaama ka Amen"
  36,54,"Hannde non, wonkii tooГұirtaake hay huunde. On yoЙ“itirtaake, si wanaa kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  36,55,"YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“e hannde, pellet, hiЙ“e e nder soklio, hiЙ“e neeminoo"
  36,56,"kamЙ“e e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en,e ley Й—owЙ—e, hiЙ“e soЙ“Й“indii e hoore danЙ—e"
  36,57,"Hino woodani Й“e ton, Й“iЙ—Й“e leЙ—Й—e, hino woodani kadi, kon ko Й“e noddata"
  36,58,"Salaamun\", konngol [kisiyee], immorde e JoomiraaЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o"
  36,59,"Sertee non hande, onon Й“ee bomЙ“e"
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mon, onon Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama, wonnde wata on rewu seytaane? Tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o"
  36,61,"[Mi yamiri on] kadi rewugol Lam. Ko ngol woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  36,62,GomЙ—ii o majjinii tagu Й—uuЙ—ungu e mon. E on wonaano haqqilooЙ“e
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge wonanoЙ—on fodaneede ngen"
  36,64,"Naatiree nge hannde, sabu kon ko yeddiraynoЙ—on"
  36,65,"Hannde, Men notay e kunndule maЙ“Й“e Й—en, juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yewta Men, koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en kadi seeditoo e kon ko Й“e wonunoo e faggitagol"
  36,66,"Si Men yiЙ—uno, Men mehayno gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e adondira e laawol ngol. Kono ko honno Й“e yiirata"
  36,67,"Si Men yiЙ—uno kadi, Men montayno Й“e e nokku maЙ“Й“e on; hara Й“e hattantaa feЖҙЖҙugol Й“e yiltotaako"
  36,68,"Kala mo Men juutni nguurndam mun, Men yiltitay mo e tagu ngun. E Й“ee haqqiltaa"
  36,69,"Men anndinaali mo (kanko Muhammadu) gimЙ—i; Й—um haananaa mo. [Deftere] nden wonaali, si wanaa jantoore e janngeteende Й“anngunde"
  36,70,"fii yo o jertin nde, on wonЙ—o wuurЙ—o (Й“ernde), Konngol lepte ngol jojja e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  36,71,"E Й“e yi'aali, wonnde Men tagiranii Й“e neemoraaЙ—i, e ko juuЙ—e Amen golli, hara hiЙ“e jeyinooЙ—i"
  36,72,"Men eltani Й“e Й—i: no e majji Й—i Й“e waЙ—Й—otoo, no e majji Й—i Й“e Гұaamata"
  36,73,"hino woodani Й“e ton, nafooje e njaram. E Й“ee kan yettataa (Mo)"
  36,74,"ЖҒe jogitorii gaanin Alla reweteeЙ—i, jortagol Й“e faabeedee"
  36,75,ЖҠi hattanaa faabagol Й“e; ko Й“e konu tawneteengu e majji
  36,76,"Wata konngol maЙ“Й“e sunine. Pellet, MeЙ—en anndi ko Й“e suuЙ—ata e ko Й“e feГұГұinta"
  36,77,"E neЙ—Й—anke on yi'aali, wonnde Men tagirii mo e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu? Kono tawaa mo ko o wennjoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  36,78,"O fiyani Men misal, kono o yejjiti tageede makko; o wi'i: \"Ko hommbo wuurnitata Жҙi'e Й—en, si Й—e rappii"
  36,79,"Maaku: \"Ko wuurnitoowo Й—e, ko taguЙ—o Й—e On ka laawol aranol. Ko Kanko woni annduЙ—o fii kala tagu"
  36,80,"On waЙ—anЙ—o on yiite, iwde e leЙ—Й—e kecce, tawa ko e majje huЙ“Й“irton nge"
  36,81,"Kere taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin wonaali haЙ—tanЙ—o tagugol yeru maЙ“Й“e? ЖҠum ko pellet! Ko Kanko woni ЖҠuuЙ—uЙ—o tageefo, AnnduЙ—o"
  36,82,"Anndon fiyaaku Makko On, si O faandanike huunde, ko O wi'anay nde tun: \"Laato\", nde laatoo"
  36,83,Senayee woodanii On Mo laamateeri kala huunde woni e juuЙ—e Mun! Ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on
  37,1,Mi woondirii saffiniraaЙ—i Й—in saffaaji
  37,2,Mi woondirii soggirayЙ—i (duule) Й—in soggugol
  37,3,"Mi woondirii janngirayЙ—i Й—in, anndintinorgol"
  37,4,"Pellet, reweteeЙ—o mon On, ko bajjo"
  37,5,"JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, JeyЙ—o kadi fuЙ—irЙ—e Й—en"
  37,6,"Men cuЙ—irii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cuЙ—aari koode Й—en"
  37,7,e reenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane raЙ—aandu
  37,8,"ЖҠi haЙ—tanaaka heЙ—itagol mbatu [Malaa'ika'en] toowu ngu ngun; tawde hiЙ—i feroree e kala baЕӢЕӢe"
  37,9,"ka raЙ—agol (Й—i). Hino woodani Й—i kadi, lepte duumiiЙ—e"
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewniree hoodere tufaynde"
  37,11,"Lamndo Й“e: si ko kamЙ“e Й“uri saЙ—tude tagude kaa ko Й“en Й“e Men tagi? Men tagirii Й“e kamЙ“e, loopal narnungal"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, hiЙ“e jalnora"
  37,13,"Si Й“e waajaama, Й“e waajitortaa"
  37,14,"si Й“e yi'ii maande, Й“e jalkita"
  37,15,"Й“e wi'a: \"ЖҠum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"
  37,16,"Eyoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, haray ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  37,17,BaabiraaЙ“e amen adinooЙ“e Й“en kadi e minen
  37,18,"Maaku: \"Pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaaЙ“e"
  37,19,"Anndon Й—um, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, hiЙ“e ndaara"
  37,20,"ЖҒe wi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande njoЙ“di kuuЙ—e"
  37,21,"Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande Гұaawoore, ko fennaynoЙ—on fii mun"
  37,22,"MooЙ“ee tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, e nandadiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e kon ko Й“e wonunoo e rewde"
  37,23,ko wonaa Alla. SoggireeЙ“e ka laawol Jahiimi
  37,24,"Darnon Й“e, tawde ko Й“e lamnditeteeЙ“e"
  37,25,"Ko heЙ“i on, on wallindirtaa"
  37,26,"Ko woni kamЙ“e on hannde, ko Й“e jebbilii Й“e"
  37,27,"woЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e fewtita Й“eya, Й“e lamndondira"
  37,28,"Й“e wi'a: \"Ko onon woni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka Й“aЕӢЕӢe Гұaamo"
  37,29,"(KoohooЙ“e) Й“en wi'a: \"Ko woni kon, on meeЙ—aano wonnde gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  37,30,"Doole woo men alanaano on. Si ko woni, on wonuno yimЙ“e bewЙ“e"
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e men; pellet, ko en meeЙ—ooЙ“e [lepte Й—en]"
  37,32,"Men bewinno on, tawde hay menen, ko men bewnooЙ“e"
  37,33,"KamЙ“e on nden Гұalnde, ko Й“e hawtoyteeЙ“e ka lepte"
  37,34,Ko nii Menen Men huuwirta bomЙ“e Й“en
  37,35,"KamЙ“e si Й“e wi'anooma: \"ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Alla\", Й“e mawnintinoo"
  37,36,"Й“e wi'a: \"Kere men accitiray reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in, fii yimoowo haangaaЙ—o"
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (NulaaЙ—o) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on meeЙ—ay Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  37,39,"On yoЙ“itetaake, si wanaa yeru kon ko huuwaynoЙ—on"
  37,40,si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Alla laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,41,"hino woodani Й“en Й—on, fanndaari anndaandi"
  37,42,"muuyanteeЙ—i, kadi ko Й“e teddinaaЙ“e"
  37,43,ka Aljannaaji neeminiiЙ—i
  37,44,"e hoore danЙ—e, ko Й“e fewtondirЙ“e"
  37,45,"Hara kore hino wannginii e maЙ“Й“e, immorde e Й“ulirde"
  37,46,"daneere, lewГұunde, fii yarooЙ“e"
  37,47,"muusu hoore alaa e majjam, wanaa Й—am siwrinirteeЙ“e Й—am"
  37,48,"Hino woodani Й“e (ton): raЙ“Й“iduЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, yaaja giteeЙ“e"
  37,49,wa'uЙ“e wa boofo maraaЙ—e
  37,50,"WoЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e fewtita Й“eya, Й“e lamndondira"
  37,51,"GoЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'a: \"Min miЙ—o marunoo wonndiiЙ—o"
  37,52,"wi'aynooЙ—o: \"Kere ko a jeyaaЙ—o e googimЙ“e Й“en"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, haray ko en yoЙ“itoyteeЙ“e"
  37,54,"O wi'a: \"Taw si Й—on yiЙ—i Жҙeewude"
  37,55,"O Жҙeewa, o haynoo oya ka tummbo Dulbunge"
  37,56,"o wi'a: \"Mi woondirii Alla ! A eЙ“Й“uno fii no mi halkorde"
  37,57,"Si wanaano moЖҙЖҙere Joomi am nden, mi tawdeteno e [lepteteeЙ“e Й“en]"
  37,58,Wonaa non enen maayataa
  37,59,"si wanaa maayde men aranere nden, en wonaali kadi lepteteeЙ“e"
  37,60,"Pellet, ko Й—um Й—oo woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu Й—um Й—oo, woni yo gollooЙ“e gollan"
  37,62,"Hara ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude jipporde, kaa ko leggal \"Zaqquumi\" [ngal haaЙ—ungal]"
  37,63,Men waЙ—ii ngal jarrabuyee tooГұuЙ“e Й“en
  37,64,"Ngal, ko leggal yaltayngal ka tummbere Dulbunge"
  37,65,"DimЙ—e maggal, hino wa'i wa ko'e seytanooji"
  37,66,"KamЙ“e on, pellet, ko e maggal Й“e nyaamirta, Й“e hebbinira ngal deedi maЙ“Й“e"
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani Й“e e dow maggal, njaram fatinaaЙ—am"
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde maЙ“Й“e nden, ko ka DulЙ“oowe"
  37,69,"ЖҒe tawu baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, ko majjunooЙ“e"
  37,70,Й“e woni e yaccagol jokka baЙ—teeji maЙ“Й“e
  37,71,"GomЙ—ii, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e aramЙ“e Й“en, majjiino, ado maЙ“Й“e"
  37,72,"GomЙ—ii le, Men nuluno e maЙ“Й“e, jertinooЙ“e"
  37,73,"Kono ndaaru baЙ—tane Й“en jertinanooЙ“e, no wa'unoo"
  37,74,"Si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Alla, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,75,"GomЙ—ii Nuuhu nodduno Men, Men moЖҙЖҙii jaabotooЙ“e"
  37,76,"Men daЙ—ni mo, kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e suno mawnungo ngon"
  37,77,"Men waЙ—i geyngol makko ngol, heddotooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,78,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,79,"Kisal wonii e Nuuhu, e nder winndere nden"
  37,80,Ko non woni ko Men warjorta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en
  37,81,"Kanko, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,82,Refti Men yooli heddii Й“e Й“en
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokkuЙ“e mo Й“en, Ibraahiima"
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo ka Joomi makko, e Й“ernde hisunde"
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yimЙ“e mun Й“en: \"Ko honЙ—um rewoton"
  37,86,"E ko reweteeЙ—i fefindaaЙ—i, ko wanaa Alla, faalaЙ—on"
  37,87,Ko sikkuЙ—on e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon
  37,88,O ndaariri ndaarande ka koode
  37,89,"o maaki: \"Ko mi nawnuЙ—o"
  37,90,"ЖҒe acci mo, Й“e hucciti"
  37,91,"O moltii e reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, o maaki: \"E on Гұaamataa"
  37,92,"Ko heЙ“i on, on wowlataa"
  37,93,"O moltorani Й—i, piyirgol Й—i Гұaamo ngon"
  37,94,"ЖҒe fewri ka makko, hiЙ“e yaawno"
  37,95,"O maaki: \"E on reway kon ko lesuЙ—on"
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e kon ko golloton"
  37,97,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Mahanee mo maadi, bugoЙ—on mo ka dulЙ“ayange"
  37,98,ЖҒe faandanii mo feere; kono Men waЙ—i Й“e sooyube Й“en
  37,99,"O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O fewnata lam"
  37,100,"Joomi am, yeЙ—am geЙ“al moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  37,101,"Men wewliniri mo, geЙ—al muГұГұiiЙ—o"
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko an Й“iЙ—Й—o am, min mi yi'ii e Й—oyngol, wonnde miЙ—o hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'uЙ—aa\". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, waЙ—ee ko yamiraЙ—on kon, on tawoyay lam, si Alla jaЙ“ii, jeyaaЙ—o e muГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,103,"Nde Й“e jebbilaninoo (ymiroore Alla nden), o hippiri mo tiinde nden"
  37,104,"Men noddiri mo wiide: \"ko yo Ibraahiima"
  37,105,"Pellet, a goonginii koyЙ—ol ngol. Ko Menen Men yoЙ“irte moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,106,"Pellet, ko Й—um Й—oo woni jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o on"
  37,107,Men soktiri mo kirse mawЙ—e
  37,108,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,109,Kisiyee wonii e Ibraahiima
  37,110,Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en
  37,111,"Kanko, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,112,"Men wewlintiniri Ishaaqa, Annabaajo jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  37,113,"Men hebbini barki e makko e Ishaaqa. Hino e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol: moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, e tooГұuЙ—o hoore-mun Й“anngini"
  37,114,GomЙ—ii Men moЖҙЖҙike e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,115,"Men daЙ—ni Й“e, kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ngoЖҙo mawnungo"
  37,116,"Men walli Й“e, Й“e woni fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  37,117,Men okki Й“e Deftere Й“annginnde nden
  37,118,"Men fewniri Й“e, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  37,119,"Men accani Й“e mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,120,Kisal wonii e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,121,Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en
  37,122,"KamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, ko Й“e jeyanooЙ“e e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,124,"Janto nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"E on hulataa [Alla]"
  37,125,"E ko \"Ba'ala\" rewoton, accon Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude tagu On"
  37,126,"Woni Alla, JeyЙ—o on, Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,127,"ЖҒe fenni mo, awa non, ko Й“e tawnoyteeЙ“e (ka lepte)"
  37,128,Si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Alla laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,129,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,130,Kisal wonii e dow Ilyaasiina'en
  37,131,Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en
  37,132,"Kanko, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,134,"Janto nde Men daЙ—ndunoo mo, kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden fow"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaaЙ—o e luttunooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,136,refti Men oЖҙЖҙi heddii Й“e Й“en
  37,137,"Onon non, hiЙ—on rewa e hoore-maЙ“Й“e, dawol mon"
  37,138,e ka jemma. E on haqqiltaa
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,140,Janto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jeyaa e foolaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,142,"Linngii ngii moЙ—i mo, ko o felniiЙ—o"
  37,143,Si wanaano tawde himo jeyanoo e subbunhinotooЙ“e Й“en
  37,144,"o ГұiiЙ“ayno e reedu maggii, haa Гұalnde Й“e immintinoytee"
  37,145,"Men werlii mo ka ladde, ko o nawnuЙ—o"
  37,146,"Men fuЙ—ini e mayre, leggal buudi"
  37,147,"Men nuli mo e ujune teemeder yimЙ“e, maa ko Й“uri"
  37,148,"ЖҒe gomЙ—ini, Men dakmiti Й“e haa e dumunna"
  37,149,"Lamndii Й“e:\" E ko Joomi maa woodanta Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e, kamЙ“e kan worЙ“e"
  37,150,"Kaa Men tagir Malaa'ika'en rewЙ—inaaЙ—i, hara ko Й“e seediiЙ“e"
  37,151,"Faamee, kamЙ“e e pepindaale maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hiЙ“e wi'a"
  37,152,"Allah jibinii\"; pellet, Й“e fanay"
  37,153,Hara O suЙ“ay Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en e dow worЙ“e Й“en
  37,154,"Ko heЙ“i on, si Й—on Гұaawira non"
  37,155,E on miijitottaako
  37,156,Kaa hiЙ—on jogii hujja Й“annguЙ—o
  37,157,"Haray addee deftere mon nden, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  37,158,"ЖҒe waЙ—i hakkunde Makko e Malaa'ika'en, asko; hara non, Malaa'ka'en no anndi, Й“en ko tawnoyteeЙ“e (ka lepte)"
  37,159,"Senayee woodani Allah, e kon ko Й“e sifotoo"
  37,160,Si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Allah laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,161,Anndon onon e ko rewoton kon
  37,162,"on wonaali majjinooЙ“e Й—um [goЙ—Й—o goo]"
  37,163,si wanaa tawЙ—o on ko naatoowo ka DulЙ“aynge
  37,164,"[Malaa'ika'en wi'i]: \"Alaa e amen, mo alanaa Й—um, darorde anndaande"
  37,165,Ko menen woni saffinaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,166,Ko menen kadi woni subbunhinotooЙ“e Й“en
  37,167,ЖҒe woniino e wi'ugol
  37,168,"Hara Deftere iwnde e adinooЙ“e Й“en, no woodannoo men"
  37,169,men wonayno jeyaaЙ“e Allah laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e
  37,170,"ЖҒe yeddi nde, kono aray Й“e anndoya"
  37,171,"GomЙ—ii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii jeyaaЙ“e Amen, NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,172,"wonnde pellet, ko kamЙ“e woni walleteeЙ“e Й“en"
  37,173,"e wonnde ko konu Amen ngun, woni foolooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,174,"ЖҠuurno Й“ee, haa e saanga"
  37,175,"ndaaraa Й“e, Й“e aray yi'ude"
  37,176,E hara ko lepte Amen Й—en Й“e heГұorta
  37,177,"Si Й—e jippike ka tannde (dingiral)maЙ“Й“e, haray bimmbi waajonooЙ“e Й“en bonii"
  37,178,"ЖҠuurno Й“ee, haa e saanga"
  37,179,"ndaaraa, Й“e aray yi'ude"
  37,180,"Senayee woodanii Joomi maa, JeyЙ—o teddungal, e kon ko Й“e sifotoo"
  37,181,Kisyee wonii e NulaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,182,"Yettoore woodani Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  38,1,"Saad. Mi woondirii Alqur'aana, jom waaju"
  38,2,"Si ko woni, yedduЙ“e Й“en wonii e townitaare e lurral"
  38,3,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e gire Й—en Men halki, ado maЙ“Й“e, Й“en noddi faabo, kono tawi ko bonatno bonii"
  38,4,"ЖҒe ЕӢalЙ—i, nde jertinoowo jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, arata Й“e. YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Oo, ko mbileejo heewuЙ—o fenaande"
  38,5,"Kere o waЙ—ay reweteeЙ—i Й—in, reweteeЙ—o gooto? Pellet, Й—um ko huunde haawniinde non"
  38,6,"Mbatu maЙ“Й“e ngun huccitiri wiide: \"Yehee, tabiton e reweteeЙ—i mon Й—in. ЖҠum Й—oo, ko huunde eЙ“Й“anaande"
  38,7,"Men nanaali fii Й—um, e diina sakkitiika kan. ЖҠum wonaali, si wanaa ko fefindaa"
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko Jantoore nden jippotoo hakkunde amen?\" Si ko woni, Й“e wonii e sikkitagol Jantoore Am nden. Wurin, ko fii Й“e meeЙ—aali taho, lepte Am Й—en"
  38,9,"Kaa Й“e jogiti ngaluuji yurmeende Joomi maa, FooluЙ—o, Dokko On"
  38,10,Kaa ko kamЙ“e woodani laamagol kammuli Й—in e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji? Haray yo Й“e ЖҙeenЕӢu Й“e Жҙawa
  38,11,"Ko Й“e konu hoyngu non, fooleteengu e feddeeji Й—in"
  38,12,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en fennuno, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna jom-peme"
  38,13,"e Samuuda'en, e yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en, e yimЙ“e pitaaji Й“en; ko Й“en woni feddeeji (fennuЙ“e) Й“en"
  38,14,"Kala Й“ee wonaali, si wanaa o fennii NulaaЙ“e Й“en. Lepte Am Й—en jojji e maЙ“Й“e"
  38,15,"ЖҒee habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde"
  38,16,"ЖҒe wi': \"Joomi amen, yaccinan men geЙ“al lepte amen, ado Г‘alaande hasboore nden"
  38,17,"MuГұГұo e kon ko Й“e wi'ata; annditaa jeyaaЙ—o Amen on, Daawuuda, jom doole. Ko o Й—uuЙ—unooЙ—o tuubugol"
  38,18,"Men eltii pelle Й—en, hiЙ—e subbunhinoda e makko, ka kiikiiЙ—e e ka weetugol"
  38,19,"e colli Й—in, hiЙ—i mooЙ“indiraa, kala e majji no tuubana Mo"
  38,20,"Men semmbini laamu makko ngun, Men yeЙ—i mo Annabaaku e fasinteegal"
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenjunooЙ“e Й“en arii maa, nde Й“e Жҙawunoo ka ganngunal"
  38,22,"Nde Й“e naatuoo ka Daawuuda, o Й—enЖҙii Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu ! Ko wennjuЙ“e Й—iЙ—o; goЙ—Й—o e amen tooГұii oya. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde amen, wata a tooГұu, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol"
  38,23,"Oo ko musiЙ—Й—o am: himo jogii baali cappanЙ—e jeenay e jeenay, min miЙ—o jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: \"Henndinam ngii\"; o foolimi e yewtere"
  38,24,"O maaki: \"Pellet, o tooГұirii ma lamndagol baalii maa ngii, waЙ—tugol e baali makko Й—in\". ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko hawtuЙ“e tooГұindirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Й“en non no fanЙ—i. - Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarribike mo. O insinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi"
  38,25,"Men yaafanii mo Й—um. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko Amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  38,26,"Ko an yo Daawuuda, Men waЙ—ii ma lomto ka leydi. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e, sakko Й—e majjine e laawol Allah ngol\". Pellet, Й“en majjooЙ“e e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani Й“e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e yejjitiri kon, Г‘alaande hasboore nden"
  38,27,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, meere. ЖҠum ko sikke yedduЙ“e Й“en. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, e Yiite ngen"
  38,28,"Ka Men waЙ—ay Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi, wano bonnooЙ“e Й“en ka hoore leydi? Kaa Men waЙ—ay gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, wano faajireeЙ“e Й“en"
  38,29,"Ko Deftere barkinaande, woni ko Men jippini e maaЙ—a, fii no Й“e taskora Aayeeje mayre, e ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en waajitora"
  38,30,"Men yeЙ—i Daawuuda Sulaymaana, - jeyaaЙ—o moЖҙЖҙo - Ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo"
  38,31,"Janto nde o hollanoo kiikiiЙ—e, pucci yooЙ—uЙ—i yaawuЙ—i"
  38,32,"o maaki: \"Min Й“urnorii yiЙ—ugol jawdi, dii ko mi jantotoo Joomi am kon, haa [naange] ngen mutoyii"
  38,33,"Ruttee lam Й—i\". O woni e sodugol Й—i ka taape e ka daaЙ—e"
  38,34,"GomЙ—ii Men jarribike Sulaymaana, Men werlii e jullere makko nden Й“anndu. Refti o tuubi"
  38,35,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, haforanam, yeЙ—aa lam laamu, ngu heertantaako goЙ—Й—o goo, Й“aawo am. Pellet, ko An woni yeЙ—oowo On"
  38,36,"Men eltani mo henndu ndun, tawi hindu wifira e sago makko, neweende, nokku kala ko o yiЙ—i"
  38,37,"E seytanuuji Й—in, mahaynooЙ—i e mutaynooЙ—i"
  38,38,"GoЙ—Й—i Й—in, ko dummbaaЙ—i e penЙ—e"
  38,39,"ЖҠum ko dokkal Amen. Okkitir, maa jogitoraa ko aldaa e lamnditoreede"
  38,40,"Ko pellet, hino woodani mo ka Amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  38,41,"Janto kadi jeyaaЙ—o Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Seytaane memirii lam tampere e muuseendi"
  38,42,"[Allah wi'ani mo]: \"Latir tunndawal maa ngal [ka leydi]: ЖҠam Й—oo, ko lootorЙ—am, Й“uuЙ“uЙ—al e njaram"
  38,43,"Men yeЙ—i mo Й“eynguure makko nden, e yeru maЙ“Й“e tawti Й“e, yurmeende immorde e Amen, e waaju wonannde marЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  38,44,"Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere huЙ—o, piyiraa Й—um [suddiiЙ—o maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)\". Men tawu mo, muГұГұiiЙ—o. O moЖҙЖҙii jeyaaЙ—o. Pellet, ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo"
  38,45,"Janto kadi, jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraaЙ“e cemmbe e yi'anЙ—e"
  38,46,"Men heertinanii Й“e heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) Й—en"
  38,47,"E kadi Й“ee ka Amen, ko jeyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e"
  38,48,"Janto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala maЙ“Й“e, ko jeyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e"
  38,49,"ЖҠum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, ruttorde moЖҙЖҙunde"
  38,50,"ЖҠum ko Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i Й“e udditanaa dame mun"
  38,51,"hara ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indii Й“e ton, hiЙ“e nodda ton muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i e njaram"
  38,52,"Hino woodani Й“e (ton): raЙ“Й“iduЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, goreeЙ“e"
  38,53,"Ko Й—um woni ko fodaЙ—on, fii Г‘alaande hasboore nden"
  38,54,"Pellet, Й—um ko arsike Amen, gasugol alanaa mo"
  38,55,"ЖҠum, [ko njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e]. Pellet, hino woodani kadi bewЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“uri bonnde e ruttorde"
  38,56,"woni Jahannama, nge Й“e naatoyta. Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi"
  38,57,"ЖҠum, ko yo Й“e meeЙ—u: ko fatata, e ЖҙeЖҙЖҙiri"
  38,58,"goЙ—Й—e Й—en, nannduЙ—e e majje, ko nooneeji"
  38,59,"E hino dental naatiroyay ngal doole e mon, toolii alanaa Й“e; tawde ko Й“e naatooЙ“e Yiite"
  38,60,"ЖҒen wi'a: bismilla alanaa mon, ko onon defi men Й—um\". Nge bonii ГұiiЙ“irde"
  38,61,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, defuЙ—o men Й—um on, Й“eydan mo leptte cowalle ka Yiite"
  38,62,"ЖҒeya wi'i: \"Ko haЙ—i men yi'ugol worЙ“e, Й“e men limtaynoo e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  38,63,"Hara men jogitorno Й“e ton jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti Й“e"
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko Й—um woni yeddondiral yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en"
  38,65,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi jertinoowo. ReweteeЙ—o woo alaa, si wanaa Allah Gooto, FooluЙ—o On"
  38,66,"JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, FooluЙ—o, Haforoowo On"
  38,67,"Maaku: \"(Ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru mawЙ—o"
  38,68,kono hiЙ—on Й—uurnii Й—um
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano lam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde Й“e wennjaynoo"
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa wonnde min on, ko mi jertinoowo Й“anngina"
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: \"Min ko Mi tagiroowo Й“anndinke, immorde loopal"
  38,72,"si Mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu Am on, haray suuyanee mo sujjon"
  38,73,Malaa'ika'en fow sujji Й“e denndaangal
  38,74,"si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jeyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: \"Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko haЙ—u maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juuЙ—e Am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitiiЙ“e Й“en?\" @Corrected"
  38,76,"O wi'i: \"Ko min Й“uri mo moЖҙЖҙude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal"
  38,77,"O daali: \"Yaltu ton, an on, ko a riiwaaЙ—o"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi Am ndin fawike ma haa Г‘alnde njoЙ“di diina"
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : \"Joomi am, nennitanam, haa Гұalnde nde Й“e immintintee"
  38,80,"O daali: \"A jeyaama e nennitanteeЙ“e Й“en"
  38,81,haa e Гұalaande happu anndaaЙ—o
  38,82,"O wi'i: \"Mi woondirii mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnuЙ“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  38,83,"si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Maa, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e"
  38,84,"(Allah) daali: \"Mi woondirii goonga, ko goonga mi wowlata"
  38,85,"ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama, e Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma fow e maЙ“Й“e"
  38,86,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e fii Й—um; mi wonaali jeyaaЙ—o e sincooЙ“e(deftatoobe)"
  38,87,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"
  38,88,"Ma on anndu (fii) kabaaru mayre, ko neeЙ“aa"
  39,1,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  39,2,"Men jippiniirii Deftere nden e maaЙ—a, e hoore goonga. rewu Allah, laЙ“Й“inanaa Mo diina kan"
  39,3,"Anndee, ko Allah woodani diina laaЙ“uka kan. ЖҒen non Й“e Й“eya jogitori yiЙ—Й“e gaanin Makko (hara hiЙ“e wi'a): \"Men alaa rewirde Й—i, si wanaa tun no Й—i Й“annira men ka Allah, Й“adal\". Pellet, Allah Гұaawoyay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, e kon ko Й“e woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah fewnataa on wonЙ—o fewnoowo, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o yeddugol"
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yiЙ—uno, nde O siforta Й“iЙ—Й—o, O suЙ“ayno ko O yiЙ—i woo, e ko O tagi kon. Senayee woodanii Mo ! Ko Kanko woni Allah, Bajjo, FooluЙ—o On"
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, goonga.Himo suddira jemma on Гұalorma on, O suddira Гұalorma on jemma on. O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. Anndee, ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Haforoowo On"
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi O waЙ—i e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, nooneeji jeetati. Himo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu Й“aawo tagu, e nder niЙ“e tati. Ko On mooЙ—on Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko Kanko laamu woodani. ReweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa Allah. Ko honno ferlitoraЙ—on [e rewugol Mo]"
  39,7,"Si on yeddii, anndon Allah, ko yondiniiЙ—o e mon. O jaЙ“antaa jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, keeferaaku. Si on yettii Mo non, O weltanoo on Й—um.Hay gooto roondantaako goЙ—Й—o woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollaynoЙ—on. Pellet, ko O annduЙ—o, ko woni e Й“erЙ—e"
  39,8,"Si loraa memii neЙ—Й—o on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e Makko. Refti si O okkii mo moЖҙЖҙere, immorde ka Makko, o yejjita ko o noddaynoo kon ado Й—um, o waЙ—ana Allah kafidiiЙ—i, fii no o majjinira (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Makko ngol. MaAku: \"Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, seeЙ—a. Pellet, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en"
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotooЙ—o tummbo jemma, ko o sujjoowo, darotooЙ—o (naafe), hara himo laakara, himo jortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: \"Hara annduЙ“e Й“en fotay e Й“e anndaa Й“en?\" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,10,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am gomЙ—imЙ“e, hulee Joomi mon\". Hino woodani moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) Й“en e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Anndee muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en timminirante njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko aldaa e limoore"
  39,11,"Maaku: \"Min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah, laЙ“Й“inana Mo diina kan"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, wonugol arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  39,13,"Maaku : \"Min miЙ—o huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Г‘alaande Mawnde"
  39,14,"Maaku: \"Ko Allah mi rewata, mi laЙ“Й“inan Mo diina am"
  39,15,"rewee ko yiЙ—uЙ—on onon, hara wanaa Kanko. Maaku: \"Ko woni hayruЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en Й“e tawata Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“e hayrinii ko'e maЙ“Й“e, e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e\". Anndee ko nden woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden"
  39,16,"Hino woodirani Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—um woni ko Allah hulЙ“inirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am, kori hulee Lam"
  39,17,"ЖҒen woЙ—Й—itorЙ“e rewugol bewnooji Й—i, Й“e ruttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani Й“e. Wewlinir jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en"
  39,18,"nanooЙ“e Konngol Й“en, Й“e jokka ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e maggol. Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah fewni Й“en, ko Й“en woni joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,19,E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mun... E ko an daЙ—ndata wonЙ—o ka Yiite
  39,20,"Si ko Й“en huluЙ“e Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ“eeje [ka Aljanna] e kuЙ“eeje mahaaЙ—e dow majje, hara canЙ—i no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore. @Corrected"
  39,21,"E a yi'aali, wonnde Allah saaЖҙinirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi Й—am e nder Й“ulli ka leydi; refti O yaltinira Й—am remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu Й—ayЙ—a, yi'aa hindu soyЙ—i; refti O waЙ—a Й—um ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, waaju, wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaГұГұani Й“endre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii Й“en yooruЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun, e jantagol Allah. ЖҒen wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [Гұaawooje], Й—immitunde. Nde guri Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun riЙ“irta (nanugol nde), refti guri e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e deeЖҙira jantoore Allah nden. Ko Й—um woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentariiЙ—o yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bonЙ—e Й—en Г‘alnde Darngal... TooГұuЙ“e Й“en wi'anee ontuma: \"MeeЙ—ee kon ko wonunoЙ—on faggitanaade"
  39,25,"AdinooЙ“e Й“en fenniino, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e, ka Й“e so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah meeЙ—iniri Й“e koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara Й—en non, Й“uri mawnude, si tawno hiЙ“e anndunoo"
  39,27,"GomЙ—ii Men piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, Й“e waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooГұaare, fii no Й“e gomЙ—ira"
  39,29,"Allah waЙ—ii misal, gorko mo lurruЙ“e hawti Й—um, hiЙ“e pooЙ—ondira mo, e gorko laaЙ“anЙ—o gorko [goo]: Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e maayooЙ“e"
  39,31,"refti onon, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"
  39,32,"E ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұde wa on fenuЙ—o e hoore Allah, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  39,33,"On non arduЙ—o e goonga, o goongini Й—um, ko Й“en woni gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko Й“e faaletee, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e; ko Й—um njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  39,35,"fii no Allah yawtirana Й“e, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko Й“e golli kon, O yoЙ“itira Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaaЙ—o Makko on? HiЙ“e hulЙ“inire Й—in Й—i wonaa Mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah fewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali wonnde FooluЙ—o, Jom lepte"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a lamndike Й“e: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?\", ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ko Allah\". Maaku: \"Yeetee lam fii Й—in Й—i rewoton gaanin Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara Й—i huncanay lam lorra Makko kan? Maa si O faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si Й—i haЙ—ay lam yurmeende Makko nden? Maaku: \"Allah yonii lam, ko e Makko hoolnotooЙ“e Й“en tuuginotoo"
  39,39,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, gollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi gollirta. Aray ka anndon"
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte hoynayЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoo e makko"
  39,41,"Men jippinirii Deftere nden e maaЙ—a, fii yimЙ“e Й“en, e hoore goonga. Kala feewuЙ—o, ko hoore makko [o feewani]; kala kadi majjuЙ—o, ko hoore makko o majjani. A wonaali wakiil e dow maЙ“Й“e"
  39,42,"Allah hino Жҙettita pittaali Й—in, saanga maayde majji, e Й—in Й—i maayaali, ka Й—oyngol majji. O jogitoo Й—in Й—i Гұaawani maayde, O accita Й—iya, haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. Pellet, maandeeji woni e Й—um, wonannde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e"
  39,43,"Kaa Й“e jogiti tefooji, gaanin Allah? Maaku: \"Hay si tawii Й—i jeyaa huunde, Й—i haqqiltaa kadi"
  39,44,"Maaku: \"Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Ko Kanko woodani laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Refti ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on"
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jantaama, Й“erЙ“e Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara Й“en, tamoo. Si fii Й—iya, Й—i wonaa Mo [Kanko Allah] jantaama, e jaka yoo, hiЙ“e wewla"
  39,46,"Maaku: \"Yaa Allah, FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, ko An Гұaawata hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en, kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e mun"
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodanno tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, ko woni kon ka leydi fow, e yeru mun, wonndude e mum, Й“e sottorayno Й—um, bone lepte Й—en, Г‘alnde Darngal; feeГұirana Й“e ka Allah, kon ko Й“e tijjanooki"
  39,48,"boneeji Й—i Й“e faggitinoo Й—in feГұana Й“e, ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon huuЙ“ita Й“e"
  39,49,"Si lorra heЙ“ii neЙ—Й—o on, o nodda Men. Refti si Men okkii mo neema, immorde ka Amen, o wi'a: \"Anndee ko e ganndal [am] mi okkiira Й—um\". ЖҠum ko jarrabuyee kan; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  39,50,"GomЙ—ii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e wi'iino Й—um. Kono kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo, nafaani Й“e"
  39,51,"boneeji Й—i Й“e faggitotonoo Й—in memi Й“e. TooГұuЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, kon ko Й“e wonunoo e faggitagol, memoyay Й“e, Й“e wonaali laawotooЙ“e"
  39,52,"E Й“e anndaa wonnde Allah no yaГұГұana arsike on mo O muuyani, O Й“illina [mo O muuyani]? Pellet, maandeeji wonii e Й—um, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  39,53,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am fantimЙ“e e hoore mun, wata on taЖҙo yurmeende Allah nden. Pellet, Allah ko haforoowo junubaajo Й—in fow. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  39,54,"Tuubee ruttoЙ—on ka Joomi mon, jebbilanoЙ—on Mo, ado lepte Й—en arde e mon, hara on faabetaake"
  39,55,"Jokkee ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko jippinaa e mon, immorde ka Joomi, ado lepte Й—en ardude on, juhal, hara on so'aa anndude"
  39,56,"fii wata wonkii wi'oy: \"Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e fii Allah. Pellet, mi jeyano e Й“en jalkitooЙ“e"
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: \"Si Alah fewnuno lam, mi wonanyno jeyaaЙ—o e gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte Й—en: \"Si feere ruttagol no woodannoo lam, mi jeyee e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  39,59,"Gasataa ! Tawde Aayeeje Am Й—en aruno e maaЙ—a, fennuЙ—aa Й—e, mawnintiniЙ—aa, laatiЙ—aa jeyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  39,60,"Г‘alnde Darngal, a yi'oya fennonooЙ“e e hoore Allah Й“en, hino Й“awli geece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“en"
  39,61,"Allah na daЙ—ndira gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, sabu maloore maЙ“Й“e nden. Bone memataa Й“en, wanaa kamЙ“e woni sunoytooЙ“e"
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni TaguЙ—o kala huunde, ko Kanko kadi woni FawtiiЙ—o kala huunde"
  39,63,"Ko Kanko sottirЙ—e kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin woodani. YedduЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й“en non, ko Й“en woni hayruЙ“e(pertuЙ“e) Й“en"
  39,64,"Maaku: \"E ko woori Allah, yamirton mi, yo mi rewu, onon Й“ee majjuЙ“e"
  39,65,"GomЙ—ii wahayinaama e maaЙ—a, e Й“en adinooЙ“e ma: \"Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa Й—en bonay jeyeЙ—aa e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, jeyeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e (Mo) Й“en"
  39,67,"ЖҒe mawniniraali Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fow, ko tamannde Makko, Г‘alnde Darngal, kammuuli Й—in kadi taggiree Гұaamo Makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkanta Mo"
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi kon faЙ—Й—ee, si wanaa Й“en Й“e Allah muuyani [daЙ—ugol]. Refti wuttee e mayru Й—iЙ—aЙ“ol, tawa ko Й“e dariiЙ“e habbitii"
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru ndun wallinee, AnnabaaЙ“e e seedeeЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addee; goonga Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wanaa Й“e tooГұeteeЙ“e"
  39,70,"wonki kala yoЙ“ee ko golli kon. Ko Kanko [Allah] Й“uri anndude ko Й“e gollata"
  39,71,"YedduЙ“e Й“en soggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si Й“e hewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenuЙ“e nge Й“en wi'ana Й“e: \"E NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on hewtaano on, janngaynooЙ“e Aayeeje Joomi mon, e mooЙ—on, Й“e rentina on hawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  39,72,"[ЖҒe] wi'anee: \"Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en lutton ton. Nge bonii jaaЖҙorde mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“en"
  39,73,"HulooЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en kadi Й—owitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si Й“e hewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenuЙ“e mo Й“en wi'ana Й“e: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon, on laaЙ“ii, naatiree mo, duumagol"
  39,74,"ЖҒe wi'a ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinanЙ—o men fodoore Mun, O ronini men leydi [Aljanna] ndin, meЙ—en weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka men yiЙ—i\". Mbarjaari gollunooЙ“e moЖҙЖҙere Й“en moЖҙЖҙii"
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, hiЙ“e taarii Arsi kin, hiЙ“e subbunhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Goonga Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Wi'ee ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o tegeefo ngon"
  40,1,"Haa, Miim"
  40,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o On"
  40,3,"Haforoowo junubaaji Й—in, JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte, Jom yaajeende. ReweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa kanko. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  40,4,"Alaa ko wennjata e Aayeeje Allah Й—en, si wanaa yedduЙ“e Й“en. Wata a hoditor ko Й“e dillirta kon ka leydi"
  40,5,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en e feddeeji Й—in Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, fennuno (NulaaЙ“e mun Й“en), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol NulaaЙ—o mun on. ЖҒe wennjiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Mi nanngi Й“e. Taskii no nanngal Am ngal waЙ—tinirnoo"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yedduЙ“e Й“en : \"Wonnde pellet, ko Й“e yimЙ“e Yiite"
  40,7,"ЖҒen (Malaa'ikaaЙ“e) roondiiЙ“e Arsiki kin, e wonЙ“e bannge makki Й“en, hiЙ“e subbunhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e gomЙ—ina Mo, Й“e insinorana gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en (wiide): \"Joomi amen, A yaГұГұirii kala huunde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan Й“en tuubuЙ“e, Й“e jokki laawol Maa ngol, daЙ—ndaa Й“e kadi lepte DulЙ“oowe ngen"
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naaduЙ“e ka Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—in Й—i foduЙ—aa Й“e, e kala moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, e geyngol maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko An woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o On"
  40,9,"DaЙ—ndaaЙ“e [kuuЙ—e] e bonЙ—e Й—en. Kala mo daЙ—nduЙ—aa [kuuЙ—e] mun bonЙ—e Й—en nden Г‘alnde, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo\". Ko Й—um woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  40,10,"YedduЙ“e Й“en noddiroyte: \"Ko tikkere Allah nden Й“uri mawnude, e dii ko tikkanЙ—on ko'e mon kon, tuma noddetenoЙ—on e gomЙ—inal, yeddon"
  40,11,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, A warii men laawi Й—iЙ—i, wuurnituЙ—aa men laawi Й—iЙ—i: men qirrike junuubi amen Й—in. Taw si laawol yaltirngol hino woodi"
  40,12,"ЖҠum mooЙ—on, ko tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, on yeddon; si O kafidaama, gomЙ—inon. Г‘aawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"
  40,13,"Ko Kanko woni holloowo on maandeeji Makko Й—in, O jippinirana on toЙ“o ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wanaa ruttotooЙ—o [e Allah]"
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, laЙ“Й“inirangol Mo diina kan, hay si heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—aa"
  40,15,"Ko o toowuЙ—o darjaaji, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin. Himo jippiniria wahayu on, yamiroore Makko, e on mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, no o jertinira Гұalnde Kawral ngal, @Corrected"
  40,16,"Гұalnde Й“e feeГұoyta. Huunde suuЙ—otaako Allah, e fee maЙ“Й“e. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, FooluЙ—o On"
  40,17,"Hannde, wonkii kala yoЙ“ete ko faggitii. TooГұe woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko yaawuЙ—o Гұaawoore"
  40,18,"JertnirtЙ“e, Гұalaande dillere nden, tuma Й“erЙ—e Й—en Жҙawtirta ka konondi, hara hiЙ“e (heewuЙ“e) ngoЖҙo. GiЙ—o woo alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en, wanaa tefoowo jaЙ“anteeЙ—o"
  40,19,"Himo anndi janfa gite, e ko Й“erЙ—e Й—en suuЙ—i"
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga Гұaawirta. ЖҠi Й“e rewata Й—in non, gaanin Makko, hay huunde Й—i Гұaawirtaa. Pellet, ko kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,21,"Hara Й“ee yiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e ndaara no battane ado mabbe Й“en wa'unoo? ЖҒen le no Й“urunoo tiiЙ—ude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri Й“e junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e heЙ“aano daЙ—ndoowo Й“e e (lepte) Allah Й—en"
  40,22,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addayno Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e yedda. Allah halki Й“e. Pellet, ko O DoolnuЙ—o, SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  40,23,"GomЙ—ii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, e hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono Й“e wi'i: \"Ko mbileejo, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o fenaande"
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo Й“e goonga kan, immorde e Amen, Й“e wi'iti: \"Waree Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e gomЙ—imdimЙ“e Й“en e makko, accon rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en\". Pewje heeferЙ“e Й“en wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,26,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Accee mi wara Muusaa. Yo o noddu Joomi makko ! MiЙ—o huli nde o waylata diina mon kan, maa o feГұГұina bonnere ka leydi"
  40,27,"Muusa maaki: \"Mi moolorii JeyЙ—o lam On, jeyi on, e bone kala mawnintiniiЙ—o, mo gomЙ—inaa Гұalaande hasboore"
  40,28,"Gorko gomЙ—inoЙ—o goo, jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en - suuЙ—unooЙ—o gomЙ—inal mun - :\"E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: \"Joomi am ko Allah?\" Hara le o addanii on Й“anngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kanko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, heЙ“ay on\". Pellet, Allah fewnataa on fantinoowo fennoowo"
  40,29,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, ko on fooluЙ“e ka leydi. Kono ko hommbo wallata en, e lepte Allah Й—en, si Й—e arii e men?\" Fir'awna wi'i: \"Mi hollataa on, si wanaa ko mi yi'i kon. Mi tindintaa on kadi, si wanaa e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,30,"GomЙ—inЙ—o on wi'iti: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min on miЙ—o hulani on, sugu Гұalaande heЙ“unoonde feddeeji Й—in"
  40,31,"Sugu mbowka yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arnooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“en\". Allah faandanaaki tooГұude jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  40,32,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min miЙ—o hulani on, Г‘alaande noddindirton"
  40,33,"Г‘alnde huccitiroyton, hoЙ—on ndoga, hara daЙ—ndoowo on alanaa on e Allah\". Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  40,34,"GomЙ—ii Yuusufu ardanii on e Й“annganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraali e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, wi'uЙ—on: \"Allah nultataa NulaaЙ—o goo, Й“aawo makko\". Ko non majjinirta kala wonoЙ—o fantinoowo sikkitiiЙ—o"
  40,35,"ЖҒen wenjirooЙ“e e Aayeeje Allah Й—en ko aldaa e hujja arЙ—o Й“e, [kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Ko wano non Allah notirta e Й“ernde kala mawnintiniiЙ—o dundarankeejo"
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko an yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo Й—ate Й—en"
  40,37,"Й—ate kammuuli Й—in, mi Жҙeewoya ReweteeЙ—o Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo fenoowo\". Ko wano non Fir'awna cuЙ—iranaa, golle makko bonЙ—e Й—en; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wanaa e hayrere"
  40,38,"[Gorko] gomЙ—inЙ—o on wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, jokkee lam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,39,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, anndee Й—am nguurndam aduna, ko dakamme-hun tun, ko laakara on woni, galle ГұiiЙ“al Й—en"
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yoЙ“itetaake, si wanaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi moЖҙЖҙere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, Й“en Й—on naatay Aljanna, Й“e arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore"
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko waЙ—i si miЙ—o nodda on e daЙ—al, hiЙ—on nodda lam e Yiite"
  40,42,"HiЙ—on nodda lam e yeddugol Allah, sirkana Mo e ko mi alanaa Й—um ganndal, hara non, min miЙ—o nodda on e FooluЙ—o, Suuroowo bakkaatu On"
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, wonnde ko noddoton lam e mun kon, dewal alanaa Й—um aduna, wanaa laakara. E wonnde ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e wonnde ko fantimЙ“e Й“en, woni Yiite ngen"
  40,44,"Aray nde anndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko ReenuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  40,45,"Allah daЙ—ndi mo, boneeji Й—i Й“e fewjunoo, O fiiltii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, ko Й“uri bonnde e lepte"
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, Й“e weeЙ“itoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e. Г‘alnde Darngal daroytoo (wi'oyte): \"Naatee yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, ka Й“uri saЙ—tude e lepte"
  40,47,"Janto tuma Й“e yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unooЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: \"Menen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on duГұanay men geЙ“al e Yiite ngen"
  40,48,"TownitinooЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"En fow, hiЙ—en e magge. GomЙ—ii Allah Гұaawii hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  40,49,"WonЙ“e ka Yiite Й“en kadi wi'ana ayninaaЙ“e Jahannama Й“en: \"Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men, Гұalaande (wootere) e lepte Й—en"
  40,50,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"NulaaЙ“e mon Й“en ardanaano on e Й“anngannduyeeji?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"Oo'owoye !\" [AyninaaЙ“e] Й“en wi'a: \"Awa toree, onon tigiri !\" Kono toraare heeferЙ“e Й“en wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,51,"Pellet, Men wallay NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ka nguurndam aduna, e Г‘alnde seedeeЙ“e Й“en daroytoo"
  40,52,"Гұalnde de ngantinagol nafoytaa tooГұunooЙ“e Й“en, hara kuddi hino woodani Й“e, e galle bonЙ—e"
  40,53,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa ganndal [Tawreeta] ngal, Men ronini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, Deftere nden"
  40,54,"ko nde peewal e waaju, wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  40,55,"MuГұГұo tun, pellet, fodoore Allah nden ko goonga, insinano junuubi maa Й—in, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Joomi maa, kiikiiЙ—e e bimmbi"
  40,56,"Pellet, wennjirooЙ“e e Aayeeje Allah Й—en, ko aldaa e dalil arЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, alaa e Й“erЙ—e Й—en, si wanaa mawnintinagol. ЖҒe yottotaako non, e Й—um. Moolor Allah, Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,57,"Pellet, ko tagde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, Й“uri mawnude e dii tageendi yimЙ“e Й“en. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa"
  40,58,"BunЙ—o e yi'oowo fotataa, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kadi golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, fotataa e bonnuЙ—o. FanЙ—ii ko waajitorton"
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'un. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e gomЙ—inaa"
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: \"Toree Lam, Mi jaabinana on. MawtinantooЙ“e rewugol Lam Й“en, ko pellet, Й“e naatoyay Jahannama, ko Й“e hoyЙ“e"
  40,61,"Ko Allah waЙ—irani on jemma on, ka fowtoЙ—on e mun, e Гұalorma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom Й“ural e yimЙ“e Й“en, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e yettataa (neema)"
  40,62,"Ko On mooЙ—on Allah Joomi mon, woni TaguЙ—o kala huunde. ReweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno firlitortaЙ—on (e Й—um)"
  40,63,"Ko non Й“eya yeddaynooЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й—en, ferlisortenoo"
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni waЙ—iranЙ—o on leydi ndin, ГұiiЙ“irde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O moЖҙЖҙini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laaЙ“uЙ—i. Ko On mooЙ—on woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuurЙ—o On. ReweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Rewee Mo kisan; laЙ“Й“inano Mo diina kan. Yettoore woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  40,66,"Maaku: \"Min mi haЙ—aama rewugol Й—in Й—i noddoton gaanin Allah, tuma nde Й“annganduyeeji Й—in ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  40,67,"Ko Kanko woni taguЙ—o on e mbumbuldi, refti e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu), refti e heЙ—Й—ere, refti O yaltiniri on penuuЙ“e fii no yottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayeeЙ“e, - no e mo'on, ЖҙettiteteeЙ“e ado Й—um, - haa no yottoron lajal happaangal, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  40,68,"Ko Kanko woni wuurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: \"Laato\", o laatoo"
  40,69,"E a tinaali, Й“en yeddondirteeЙ“e e Aayeeje Allah Й—en, ko honno Й“e firlitoraa"
  40,70,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Deftere nden, e kon ko Men nuliri NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en; Й“e aray anndude"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje Й—en waЙ—oyaa e daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e jolokooje(callalle) Й—en, hara hiЙ“e daasiree"
  40,72,ka nder wulЙ—am; refti Й“e huЙ“Й“oyee ka nder Yiite
  40,73,"Refti Й“e wi'anee: \"Ko honto woni Й—in Й—i kafidaynoЙ—on"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?\" ЖҒe wi'a: \"ЖҠi majjitike men. Wurin, men wonaano ko adii, e rewugol hay huunde\". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  40,75,"Ko waЙ—i on Й—um, ko ko weltoraynoЙ—on kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko wewliraynoЙ—on kon"
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en, luttugol ton. Nge bonii jaaЖҙorde wonande mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“en"
  40,77,"MuГұГұo. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Men hollete yoga e ko Men fodi Й“e kon, maa hara Men Жҙettite (ado mun) ko ka Amen Й“e ruttirtee"
  40,78,"GomЙ—ii Men imminii NulaaЙ“e ado maa. Hino e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Men sifani maa fii mun; hino maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Men sifanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa NulaaЙ—o, addugol Aaya, si wanaa e duЕӢayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga Гұaawirte meerente'en sooya nden Гұalnde"
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni waЙ—iranЙ—o On neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ko waЙ—Й—oron, Гұaamon kadi e majji"
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino woodani on e majji, e no yottoron e majji, haaju hittuЙ—o e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laaЙ—e Й—en, woni ko ronndeteЙ—on"
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji Makko Й—in. Ko honЙ—um e maandeeji Allah Й—in, woni ko yeddoton"
  40,82,"E Й“ee yiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e ndaara ko honno battane Й“eya ado maЙ“Й“e wattinirnoo? ЖҒen no Й“urunoo Й“e Й—uude e saЙ—tude doole e batteeji [waЙ—aaЙ—i] ka leydi. Kono kon ko Й“e faggotonoo, duncanaano Й“e"
  40,83,"Nde NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addannooЙ“e Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in, Й“e wewliri ganndal ko woni ka maЙ“Й“e kon. ЖҒe huuЙ“itiraa kon ko Й“e jalkitaynoo"
  40,84,"Nde Й“e yi'unoo lepte Amen Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—inii Allah tun, men yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e sirkannde"
  40,85,"Kono gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e wonaano ko nafata Й“e, fewndo Й“e yi'unoo lepte Amen Й—en; Й—um ko laawol Allah non, gomЙ—ii Й—un yawtiino e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. YedduЙ“e Й“en sooyi Й—on nden Гұalnde"
  41,1,"Haa, Miim"
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka YurmeteeЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande Aayeeje mun, janngeteende e Й—emngal aarabu, wonannde yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e"
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jertina. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, Й—uurnii, Й“en Й“e nanataa"
  41,5,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"ЖҒerЙ—e amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mun kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi meЙ—en e golle amen"
  41,6,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko neЙ—Й—anke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, wonnde ReweteeЙ—o mon on, ko ReweteeЙ—o gooto. Г‘iiЙ“ee e Й—um, insinanoЙ—on Mo\". Bone woodanii sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  41,7,"Й“e jonnataa Й“en zakka, hara kadi hiЙ“e yeddi fii laakara"
  41,8,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di ndi taЖҙondirtaa"
  41,9,"Maaku: \"E onon on yedday On taguЙ—o leydi ndin nder balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, waЙ—anon Mo goreeЙ“e? Awa ko On woni JeyЙ—o winndere nden. @Corrected"
  41,10,"O waЙ—i pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O eЙ“Й“i nguureeji mayri Й—in e nder balЙ—e nayi timmuЙ—e, wonannde lamndotooЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  41,11,"Refti O fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: \"Ardiree Й—oftaare, maa karheede\". ЖҠi wi'idi: \"Men arii ko men Й—oftii Й“e\". @Corrected"
  41,12,"O timminiri Й—i kammuuli jeeЙ—iЙ—i nder balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Men cuЙ—iniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenirЙ—um. ЖҠum ko eЙ“Й“oore FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o On. @Corrected"
  41,13,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike, haray wi'u Й“e: \"Men jertinirii on haacaangu, sugu haacaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en"
  41,14,"nde NulaaЙ“e Й“en ardirannooЙ“e, yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, wonnde: \"Wata on rewu dey, si wanaa Allah\", Й“e wi'i: \"Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa menen, ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulaЙ—on mun kon"
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, Й“e mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, Й“e wi'i: \"Hara ko hommbo Й“uri men doole?\" E Й“ee yi'aali, wonnde Allah taguЙ—o Й“e On no Й“uri Й“e tiiЙ—ude doole? ЖҒe woni e yeddugol Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  41,16,"Men wurti henndu Й“uuЙ“undu e maЙ“Й“e e ГұalaaЙ—e hiitaaЙ—e, fii no Men meeЙ—inira Й“e lepte koyeera Й—en ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara Й—en Й“uri wonnde koyeera, kadi Й“e faaboytaake"
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Men Й“annginanno Й“e; kono Й“e suЙ“ii bumЙ—am Й—am e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje Й—en nanngiri Й“e, sabu ko Й“e faggitotonoo kon"
  41,18,Men daЙ—ndi gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e woniina hulnooЙ“e Й“en
  41,19,Г‘alnde non ayЙ“e Allah Й“en mooЙ“iroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara hiЙ“e ГұoЖҙЖҙindiree
  41,20,"Haa si Й“e hewtii nge, nannЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, e guri Й“alli maЙ“Й“e Й—in seeditoo e dow maЙ“Й“e, kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  41,21,"ЖҒe wi'ana guri maЙ“Й“e Й—en: \"Ko fii honnЙ—um seeditaniЙ—on e amen?\" ЖҠe wi'a: \"Ko Allah wowlinЙ—o kala huunde On, wowlini men. Ko Kanko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka Makko kadi rutteteЙ—on"
  41,22,"On wonaali hiЙ—on suuЙ—ora, fii wata nanЙ—e mon, e giiЙ—e mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on sikkuno, wonnde Allah anndaa ko Й—uuЙ—i e ko huuwoton"
  41,23,"Ko Й—um mooЙ—on, wonunoo ko sikkunoЙ—on Joomi mon, Й—um halki on. WaЙ—tinЙ—on jeyaaЙ“e e pertuЙ“e Й“en"
  41,24,"Hay si Й“e muГұГұike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e; si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ii feleede accitee, Й“e wonaali feleteeЙ“e accitee"
  41,25,"Men wurtani Й“e wondiiЙ“e, Й“en cuЙ—inani Й“e ko woni yeeso maЙ“Й“e, e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e maЙ“Й“e, wondude e mofte yawtunooЙ—e ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e. Pellet, Й“e laatino hayruЙ“e"
  41,26,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"Wata on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) belajo'o, on foolay"
  41,27,"Ma Men meeЙ—iniroy yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, Men yoЙ“ira ko Й“uri bonde e ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon"
  41,28,"Ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di ayЙ“e Allah Й“en: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani Й“e ton, njoЙ“di kon ko Й“e yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  41,29,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Joomi amen, hollii men majjinnooЙ“e men Й“en ka jinna e ka yimЙ“e, men yaaЙ“a Й“e men fuga, haa Й“e wona e Й“urЙ“e joltude Й“en"
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“en : \"Joomi amen ko Allah\", refti Й“e tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e maЙ“Й“e (wiide): \"Wata on hulu, wata on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonanoЙ—on fodeede"
  41,31,"Ko menen woni wallooЙ“e on Й“en ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko wonkiiji mon wooЙ—etee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e Haforoore, HinnotooЙ—o"
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude konngol, wano on nodduЙ—o e fii Allah, o golli moЖҙЖҙere, o wi'i: \"Min, ko e juulЙ“e Й“en mi jeyaa"
  41,34,"MoЖҙЖҙere nden fotataa e bone on. DuГұir (golle bonЙ—e Й—en) kon ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mun, himo wa'ita wa giЙ—o saЙ—tuЙ—o giggol"
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e Й—um, si wanaa muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en; hawrataa e Й—um, si wanaa jom geЙ“al mawnungal"
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii heЙ“ude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. Kanko ko O Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o"
  41,37,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in, jemma on e Гұalorama on, e naange ngen e lewru ndun. Wata on sujjan naange ngen wanaa kadi lewru ndun. Sujjanee Allah, taguЙ—o Й—i On, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton"
  41,38,"Si Й“e townitike, Й“en wonЙ“e ka Joomi maa kan, hiЙ“e subbunhinorana Mo jemma e Гұalorma, hara Й“e haaЙ“ataa"
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in, tawde a yi'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Men jippinii ndiyam toЙ“o e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa wuurnituЙ—o ndi On, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, tawde pellet, ko O hattanЙ—o haka huunde"
  41,40,"Pellet, ooГұotooЙ“e Й“en e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e suuЙ—otaako Men. E ko feroyteeЙ—o on ka Yiite Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko aroyoowo on Г‘alnde Darngal hino hoolii? Gollee ko faalaЙ—on, ko pellet, Himo reeni ko golloton kon"
  41,41,"YedduЙ“e Й“en Alqur'aana tuma nde arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, pellet non, ko nde Deftere teddunde [foolunde]"
  41,42,"meere iwrantaa nde yeeso mayre, wanaa Й“aawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Г‘eenyo, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wanaa ko NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en wi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte muusuЙ—e"
  41,44,"Si Men waЙ—uno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, Й“e wi'ayno: \"Ko haЙ—no Aayeeje mayre Й—en fensitee? E nde wonay e haala ajami, [NulaaЙ—o] on wona aarabuujo?\" Maaku: \"Kayre wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ko nde peewal e cellal\". ЖҒe gomЙ—inaa Й“en kan, noto hino e noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kayre ko nde niЙ“e e dow maЙ“Й“e; Й“en hino noddiree e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o"
  41,45,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wanaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұaaweteno. KamЙ“e kan, pellet, hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o nde"
  41,46,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o, yantay e makko. Joomi maa siforaali wonnde, tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  41,47,"Ko ka Makko woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee. DimЙ—e yaltataa e coomЙ—i mun, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko.Г‘alnde O noddiroyta Й“e:\"Ko honto woni kafidaaЙ—i Am Й—in?\", Й“e wi'a:\"Men anndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotooЙ—o [Й—um]"
  41,48,ЖҒe majjira e kon ko Й“e rewaynoo ko adii; Й“e yananee wonnde daЙ—irgal alanaa Й“e
  41,49,"NeЙ—Й—anke on haaЙ“ataa toragol moЖҙЖҙere. Si bone memii mo, ko o taЖҙotooЙ—o, yonndiniiЙ—o"
  41,50,"Si Men meeЙ—inir mo moЖҙЖҙere immorde ka Amen, Й“aawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko min ! Mi fellitaani si Darngal daroto. Si mi ruttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani lam ka Makko\". Ma Men humpitu yedduЙ“e Й“en, fii ko Й“e huuwi kon, ko ma Men meeЙ—inoy Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  41,51,"Si Men neeminii e neЙ—Й—anke on, o Й—uurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non heЙ“ii mo, o wona jom toraare yaajunde"
  41,52,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti yedduЙ—on nde; haray ko hommbo Й“uri majjude on wonЙ—o e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  41,53,"Aray Men holla Й“e maandeeji Amen Й—in ka tatteeji e maЙ“Й“e tigi, haa Й“anngana Й“e wonnde ko nde goonga. E yonaali wonnde Joomi maa, ko O seediiЙ—o kala huunde"
  41,54,"Anndee hiЙ“e e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Anndee non, ko O huЙ“indiiЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,1,"Haa, Miim"
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf"
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah TeЙ—Й—uЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On wahayiniri e maa, e Й“en adinooЙ“e ma"
  42,4,"Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko kadi woni ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"
  42,5,"Kammuuli Й—in no eЙ“Й“a seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e insinanoo wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en. Anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  42,6,"ЖҒen non jogitiiЙ“e yiЙ—Й“e goo gaanin Makko, Allah ko reenuЙ—o Й“e. A wonaali reenoowo Й“e"
  42,7,"Ko wano non Men wahayniri e maaЙ—a, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jertin yimЙ“e neene ca'e Й—en e wonЙ“e takko mayre Й“en, jertinaa fii Гұalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'un - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite"
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O waЙ—ayno Й“e mofte goote. Kono himo On mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende Makko. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en non, giЙ—o alanaa Й“e, wanaa ballo"
  42,9,"Kaa Й“e jogiti yiЙ—Й“e goo gaanin Makko? Awa ko Allah woni GiЙ—o On, ko Kanko wuurnitata maayЙ“e Й“en; ko Kanko kadi woni kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondirЙ—on e fii mun, haray Гұaawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On mooЙ—on Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"
  42,11,"FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kamuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. O waЙ—iranii on e pittaali mon Й—in genndooЙ“e, ka neemoraaЙ—i kadi nooneeji; Himo Й—uЙ—Й—inira on Й—um. Hay huunde yerondiraa e Makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  42,12,"Ko Kanko heerori soktirЙ—e kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wertana arsike on mo O muuyani, O Й“iЙ—tinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, konko ko O yamirnoo Nuuhu, e kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, e kon ko Men yamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, wonnde: \"Г‘iЙ“nee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka\". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkooЙ“e Й“en e mun kon, mawnii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah non hino suЙ“anoo Й—um, mo O muuyani, O fewna e Makko, kala tuuboowo"
  42,14,"ЖҒe seertaano, si wanaa Й“aawo nde ganndal ngal arde e maЙ“Й“e, sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si wanaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal taЖҙaangal, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, roninaaaЙ“e Deftere nden Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitiiЙ“e"
  42,15,"Noddu (yimЙ“e Й“en) kisan; ГұiiЙ“iraa no yamiraЙ—aa non, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, maakaa: \"Mi gomЙ—inii ko Allah jippini kon (fow) e Defte, mi yamiraama kadi, nunЙ—ugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah mooЙ“oyay e denndaandal. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  42,16,"ЖҒen wennjirooЙ“e e diina Allah kan, Й“aawo ka jaЙ“aneede, hujja maЙ“Й“e on ko meere, tikkere no fawii e maЙ“Й“e, hino woodani Й“e kadi lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri Deftere nden goonga, e manndakke Й—en. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara Darngal ngal ko ko Й“adii"
  42,18,"ЖҒeya Й“e gomЙ—inaali ngal Й“en, hiЙ“e heГұoringal; gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Й“e hulu fii maggal, e hoore hiЙ“e felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee wonЙ“e yeddondireede Й“en fii Darngal, ko pellet, Й“e wonii e nder majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  42,19,"Allah ko newaniiЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Himo arsike on mo O muuyani. Ko Kanko woni DoolnuЙ—o, FooluЙ—o On"
  42,20,"Kala tawЙ—o ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men Й“eydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi tawЙ—o ko jayru ndun aduna o yiЙ—i, Men okkay mo Й—um, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) geЙ“al"
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaaЙ—i hino woodani Й“e, sar'inanЙ—i Й“e e diina kan, kon ko Allah duЕӢaaki fii mun? Si wanaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde maЙ“Й“e], Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, lepte muusuЙ—e"
  42,22,"A yi'ay tooГұuЙ“e Й“en hino huli e ko Й“e fggitii kon, Й—um le ko yantayЙ—um e maЙ“Й“e. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hiЙ“e e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kala ko Й“e faaletee. Ko Й—um tigiri, woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal"
  42,23,"Ko Й—um woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe. Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e Й—um, si wanaa tun giggol enЙ—am Й—am\". Kala faggitiiЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, Men Й“eydanay mo moЖҙЖҙere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, mantoowo"
  42,24,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notayno e Й“ernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol Makko ngol. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o gunndooji Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  42,25,"Ko Kanko woni jaЙ“anoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bonЙ—i Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi ko golloton kon"
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, O Й“eydana Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. HeeferЙ“e Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГұГұanno jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en [fow] arsike, pellet, Й“e bewayno ka leydi; kono Himo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O HummpitiiЙ—o, yi*oowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo toЙ“o ngon Й“aawo Й“e taЖҙaade, O saaka yurmeende Makko nden. Ko Kanko kadi woni GiЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ruugayЙ—i Й—i O saaki Й—in hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngol, si O haajii, ko O hattanЙ—o"
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: dogayЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, wa'uЙ—e wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O deeЖҙinay henndu ndun, ndu waЙ—tinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde kala muГұГұotooЙ—o, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yooliraЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko Й—uuЙ—i
  42,35,"WennjooЙ“e Й“en e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, hino anndi Й“e alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okkaЙ—on e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotooЙ“e e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  42,37,"woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkaatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare Й—en, si wonii Й“e tikkii, hara Й“e yaafoto"
  42,38,"Й“en nootiiЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiЙ“ni julde nden, Й“e tawata fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on ko diisondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, nafqooЙ“e e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e"
  42,39,"e Й“en tawЙ“e si bewre heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e yottoto"
  42,40,"NjoЙ“di bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafiiЙ—o o moЖҙЖҙintini, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й“e tooГұeede, ko Й“en woni Й“e laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko tooГұooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en, hara hiЙ“e bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: Й“e Й—on, hino woodani lepte muusuЙ—e"
  42,43,"MuГұГұiiЙ—o on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, Й—um no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray giЙ—o (goo) alanaa mo Й“aawo Й—um. A tinay tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, tuma Й“e yi'i lepte Й—en, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi"
  42,45,"A tinay Й“e kadi, hiЙ“e weeЙ“itee e magge, hara hiЙ“e yankinii koyeera on, hiЙ“e ndaarira ndaarЙ—e leppagol. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en wi'aya: \"Ko woni hayru Й“e Й“en, ko Й“en hayrimЙ“e ko'e mun e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal\". Anndee pellet, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en no e lepte duumiiЙ—e"
  42,46,"YiЙ—Й“e alanaa Й“e, ko wallitoo Й“e, hara wanaa Allah. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo"
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado Гұalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa Й—um ka Allah. Nden Гұalnde, faaborde alanaa on, yeddugol kadi alanaa on"
  42,48,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike non, haray Men nuliraali ma, aynoowo Й“e: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol. Si wonii Men meeЙ—iniri neЙ—Й—anke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non heЙ“i Й“e, sabu kon ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardiniri, a taway pellet, neЙ—Й—o on ko jedduЙ—o sanne"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko O muuyi. Himo yeЙ—a mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e, O yeЙ—a kadi mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e"
  42,50,"maa O jillira Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e; Himo waЙ—a dimaro, on mo O muuyani. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o, HaЙ—tanЙ—o"
  42,51,"Sellantaa neЙ—Й—anke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e Й“aawo heedo, maa O immina NulaaЙ—o (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O ToowuЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maaЙ—a, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gomЙ—inal; si ko woni, Men waЙ—unde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jeyЙ—o ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji Й—in ruttotoo"
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
  43,2,Mi woondirii Defere Й“anngunde nden
  43,3,"Men waЙ—ii nde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  43,4,"Pellet, hinde woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma Defte, toowunde, ГұeГұaande"
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinangol on jantoore nden, Й—uurngal on, fii on wonii yimЙ“e fantimЙ“e"
  43,6,ЖҠuuЙ—ii e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e Men nuli e adinooЙ“e Й“en
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e jalkitay mo"
  43,8,Men halki ko Й“uri Й“e saЙ—tude doole ! Toode mise adinooЙ“e Й“en yawtiino
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?\" ЖҒe wi'ay: \"Ko FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o On tagi Й—i"
  43,10,"On waЙ—iranЙ—o on leydi ndin weertaandi, O waЙ—ani on Й—ate e mayri, fii no Й—oworon"
  43,11,"On jippinrЙ—o toЙ“o ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Men wuurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko non yaltinirteЙ—on"
  43,12,"On taguЙ—o nooneeji Й—in fow, O waЙ—irani on e laaЙ—e Й—en e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ko waЙ—Й—oron"
  43,13,"fii yo on fotondir e hoore majji, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma fotondirЙ—on e majji, wi'on ontuma: \"Senayee woodanii eltanЙ—o men Й—um On, men wonaano taaqanaaЙ“e Й—um"
  43,14,"menen non, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko men ruttotoo"
  43,15,"ЖҒe waЙ—ani Mo geЙ“al e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ! Pellet, on neЙ—Й—anke ko yedduЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“en"
  43,17,"Si goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wewliniraama ko o waЙ—irani kon Hinaranke On misal, yeeso makko ngon niЙ“Й“ita metteendi hombo suuЙ—i"
  43,18,"E ko on ne'eteeЙ—o e cuЙ—aari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, wanaa o Й“annginoowo haala"
  43,19,"ЖҒe waЙ—i Malaa'ikaaЙ“e tawЙ“e Й“en ko jeyaaЙ“e Jom Hinaranke On, rewЙ“e ! Kere Й“e seedino tageede Й“en? Awa fii seedagol maЙ“Й“e ngol winndete, Й“e lamnditoyee"
  43,20,"ЖҒe wi'iti: \"Si Jom Hinaranke On haajuno, men rewataano Й“e\". ЖҒe alanaa Й—um hay e ganndal; Й“e wonaali, si wanaa hiЙ“e fena"
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani Й“e ado ndee Й—oo, hara ko nden woni ko Й“e jogitii"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, Й“e wi'iu: \"Menen men tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en e diina, haray ko e batteeji maЙ“Й“e men feewirta"
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Men nulaali jertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wanaa hooreeЙ“e maЙ“Й“e neemiiЙ“e wi'ay: \"Menen men tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en e diina, Й—um non ko batteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in men Гұentinta"
  43,24,"O maaki: \"Hay si mi addan on ko Й“uri feewude kon ko tawruЙ—on baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Menen dey, ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on e mun kon"
  43,25,Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e. ndaare no battande fennuЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo
  43,26,"Janto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Min on ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko rewoton"
  43,27,"si wanaa On taguЙ—o lam, Kanko On, O fewnay lam"
  43,28,"O waЙ—i ngol konngol heddotoongol Й“aawo makko, belajo'o, Й“e ruttoto"
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii Й“ee Й—oo e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, haa nde goonga kan arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, e NulaaЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠum ko mbilewu, menen ko men yedduЙ“e Й—um"
  43,31,"ЖҒe wi'iti: \"Ko hanno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko mawЙ—o ca'e Й—en Й—iЙ—i"
  43,32,"E ko kamЙ“e senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ka nguurndam aduna. Men Й“amti yoga maЙ“Й“e e hoore Й“eya, darjaaji, fii no yoga maЙ“Й“e jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e kon ko Й“e mooЙ“ata"
  43,33,"Si wanaano fii wata yimЙ“e Й“en wonu mofte goote, Men waЙ—ayno e cuuЙ—i kala yedduЙ—o Hinnaranke On: kiЙ“Й“e kaalisi e ЕӢabbirЙ—e ka Й“e Жҙawra"
  43,34,"(Men waЙ—ayno kadi) e cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, dame e ndaЙ—Й—ude ka Й“e soЙ“Й“indoo"
  43,35,"e cuЙ—aari. Kono Й—um fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  43,36,"Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e jantoore Hinaranko On, Men wuurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata"
  43,37,"ЖҠin (awaseeji) non, ko sakkorayЙ—i Й“e e peewal ngal, haa ka Й“e sikkata hiЙ“e feewi"
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amen, o wi'a: \"Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa woЙ—Й—irayno goЙ—Й—al fuЙ—Й—irЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i woЙ—Й—iri ! A bonii cinndadiiЙ—o"
  43,39,"[ЖҠum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on tooГұii - wonnde ko ka lepte hawtuЙ—on"
  43,40,E ko an naninta faaЙ—uЙ—o maa fewnaa bumЙ—o e on wonЙ—o e nder majjere Й“anngunde
  43,41,"Si Men aru Жҙettitude ma, haray ko Men yottotooЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e"
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Men kammbirani Й“en kon, haray noon ko Men gaynooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e"
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a. Pellet, hiЙ—a jokki laawol focciingol"
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yimЙ“e maa Й“en. Aray nde lamnditeЙ—on"
  43,45,"Lamndii e Й“en NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“e Men nulunoo ado maa, si Men waЙ—uno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, reweteeЙ—i goo"
  43,46,"GomЙ—ii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: \"Ko mi NulaaЙ—o JeyЙ—o tagu ngun"
  43,47,"Nde o addannooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, e jaka yoo hiЙ“e jalaЙ—i"
  43,48,"Men hollaali Й“e Aaya, si wanaa haray on Й“uri adiiЙ—o mo on mawnude. Men nanngiri Й“e lepte Й—en, belajo'o, Й“e ruttoto"
  43,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano men Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maaЙ—a. Pellet, ko men feewooЙ“e"
  43,50,"Nde Men huncannooЙ“e lepte Й—en, e jaka yoo, hiЙ“e firta [ahadi]"
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yimЙ“e Й“en, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, wanaa min jey laamu Misra? E hino Й—ii canЙ—i no ila e ley kuЙ“eeji am? E on yiyataa"
  43,52,Kaa mi Й“uraa teddude oo hoyЙ—o mo eЙ“Й“ataa laЙ“Й“innde haala
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawle kaЕӢЕӢe werlee e makko? MaaЙ—um Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri"
  43,54,"O Й—aytini yimЙ“e makko Й“en, Й“e Й—owtii mo. Pellet, Й“en Й—on laatino yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  43,55,"Nde Й“e tikkinnoo Men, Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e; Men yooli Й“e fow"
  43,56,"Men waЙ—i Й“e ardiiЙ“e e misal, wonannde sakkiitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  43,57,"Tuma nde geЙ—al neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yimЙ“e maa Й“en no sooЖҙira Й—um"
  43,58,"Й“e wi'i: \"Ko reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko kanko?\" ЖҒe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wanaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko Й“e yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e wennje"
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaali, si wanaa jeyaaЙ—o mo Men neemini e mun, Men waЙ—i mo misal woannde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno, Men waЙ—titirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi"
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wata on sikkito fii maggal. Jokkee lam, ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e Й“annguЙ—i Й—in, o maaki: \"GomЙ—ii mi ardanii on e ГұeeГұal, e no mi Й“annginirana on yoga e ko luutondirЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Haray hulee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on mi"
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,65,"Feddeeji Й—in luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, immorde e lepte Гұalaande muusuЙ—e"
  43,66,"Hara Й“e habbi si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata Й“e e juhal, hara Й“e so'aa anndude"
  43,67,"WelduЙ“e Й“en, nden Гұalnde, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko ayrooЙ“e yoga; si wanaa gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  43,68,Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotooЙ“e kadi
  43,69,"Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e woni jebbiliiЙ“e"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nannduЙ“e e mon, hiЙ—on saЙ—nee"
  43,71,"[GollooЙ“e] hino wanngindinee e maЙ“Й“e, mirannji kaЕӢЕӢe e ГұedduЙ—e; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotooЙ“e ton"
  43,72,"Ko on woni Aljanna mo roniniraЙ—on, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й—i Гұaamoton e mun"
  43,74,"Pellet, bomЙ“e Й“en, ko ka lepte Jahannama Й“e luttoyta"
  43,75,"Й“e hoynantaake, tee hara ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e ton"
  43,76,"Men tooГұaani Й“e few, si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  43,77,"ЖҒe nodda: \"Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !\" O wi'i: \"Pellet, ko on luttooЙ“e [ton]"
  43,78,"GomЙ—ii Men addanii on goonga kan ; kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e mon, ko aГұuЙ“e goonga"
  43,79,Kaa Й“e eЙ“Й“u feere ? Doo ko Men fewjooЙ“e
  43,80,Maa hara Й“e sikku Men nanataa gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e sirru maЙ“Й“e? OoвҖҷowoye! NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hino maandina takko maЙ“Й“e
  43,81,"Maaku: \"Si Hinaranko On no jogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko min adotonoo rewude on"
  43,82,"Senayee woodanii JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin; laaЙ“uЙ—o e kon ko Й“e sifrotta Mo. @Corrected"
  43,83,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e fija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e ndeЙ“e fodaa"
  43,84,"Ko Kanko woni On reweteeЙ—o ka kammu e reweteeЙ—o ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  43,85,"Barke heewanii On Mo woodani Й—um, laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka Makko kadi rutteteЙ—on"
  43,86,"ЖҠi Й“e rewata Й—in gaanin Makko jeyah tefoore, si wanaa seediiЙ“e goonga Й“en, hara hiЙ“e anndi"
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e, ko hommbo woni ko tagi Й“e? ЖҒe wi'ay: \"Ko Allah\". Ko honno non Й“e yiiliraa"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (NulaaЙ—o) on maakunoo kon: \"Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  43,89,"Awa yaafo Й“e, maakaa: \"Kisal !\" Aray ndebe annda"
  44,1,"Haa, Miim"
  44,2,Mi woondirii Defere Й“anngunde nden
  44,3,"Men jippinirii nde e jemma barkinaaЙ—o, Men siforii wonde jertinooЙ“e"
  44,4,Ko e on (jemma) woni ko senndetee kala fiyaaku ГұeГұaaЙ—o
  44,5,ЖҠum ko yamiroore immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde NulooЙ“e
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  44,7,"JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaaЙ“e"
  44,8,"ReweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara. JeyЙ—o on Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon aramЙ“e Й“en"
  44,9,"Ko woni tun, Й“e wonii e sikke, hiЙ“e fija"
  44,10,Habbito Гұalnde kammu ngun ardata e curki feeГұuuki
  44,11,"suddayki yimЙ“e Й“en. [ЖҒe wi'anee]: \"ЖҠum ko lepte muusuЙ—e"
  44,12,"Joomi amen, huncan men lepte Й—en. Menen ko men gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  44,13,"Ko honno Й“e waajitorta, ko goongo NulaaЙ—o Й“annginЙ—o ariino Й“e"
  44,14,"Refti Й“e hucciti, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko tinndinaaЙ—o, haangaaЙ—o"
  44,15,"Awa ko Men ittooЙ“e lepte Й—en seeЙ—a; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotooЙ“e"
  44,16,"Г‘alnde Men nanngiroyta wippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Men yottoytooЙ“e"
  44,17,"GomЙ—ii Men jarribinoke ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, NulaaЙ—o tedduЙ—o ari e maЙ“Й“e"
  44,18,"wonnde: \"WaЙ—ee e juuЙ—e am, jeyaaЙ“e Allah Й“en. Min ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mon, hoolniiЙ—o"
  44,19,"E wonde wata on townitano Allah, tawde mi addanay on hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  44,20,"Min kadi non, mi moolorii JeyЙ—o lam On Jeyi on, nde fiЙ—otonmi kaaЖҙe"
  44,21,"Si on gomЙ—inaa lam, haray selee lam"
  44,22,"O noddi Joomi makko, wonnde: \"ЖҒee Й—oo, ko yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  44,23,Yaadir e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en jemma; anndon ko on cukketeeЙ“e
  44,24,"Accaa maayo ngon deeЖҙa [si on lummbii] Й“eya kan, ko konu yooleteengu"
  44,25,ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko Й“e acci e gese e Й“ulli
  44,26,e remuruuji e koЙ—ande teddunde
  44,27,e neemaaji Й—i Й“e wonunoo e neeminireede
  44,28,Ko wano non. Hooti Men ronini Й—i yimЙ“e goo
  44,29,"Kammu ngun toЙ“aali Й“e, wanaa leydi ndin, Й“e wonaali kadi muГұanteeЙ“e"
  44,30,GomЙ—ii Men daЙ—ndii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en e lepte hoyneeje
  44,31,"immorde e Fir'awna, tawde o laatino townitiiЙ—o, jeyaaЙ—o e fantimЙ“e Й“en"
  44,32,GomЙ—ii Men suЙ“orike Й“e e dow ganndal e hoore winndere nden
  44,33,"Men okki Й“e maandeeji, Й—i jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o woni e mun"
  44,34,ЖҒee kan no wi'a
  44,35,"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa maayde amen aranere nden tun. Men wonatah immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  44,36,"Awa artiree baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  44,37,"Kere ko kamЙ“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko yimЙ“e \"Tubba'in\" Й“en e Й“eya adinooЙ“e Й“e? Men halkuno Й“en, tawde hari ko Й“e bomЙ“e"
  44,38,"Men tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijooЙ“e"
  44,39,"Men tagiraali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, si wanaa e goonga. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  44,40,"Pellet, ko Г‘alaande Senndindiro ngon, woni ko Й“e saatinanaa, kamЙ“e fof"
  44,41,"Г‘alnde nde giЙ—o duncanoytaa giЙ—o [mun] hay huunde; Й“e wonaali kadi walloyteeЙ“e"
  44,42,"si wanaa mo Allah yurmaa woo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal"
  44,44,ko Гұaametee bakkondimЙ“e Й“en
  44,45,A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka nder deedi
  44,46,Wano wulЙ—am fatirta
  44,47,Nanngee mo pooЙ—iron ka hakkunde dulЙ“aynge
  44,48,"refti yuppon ka hoore makko, lepte fatinaaЙ—e Й—en"
  44,49,"MeeЙ—u non ! An [sikkunooЙ—o] ko a fooluЙ—o, tedduЙ—o"
  44,50,Awa ko Й—um woni kon ko sikkitiЙ—on e mum
  44,51,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e weerde hoolniinde"
  44,52,e nder gese e Й“ulli
  44,53,"hiЙ“e Й“oornoo ko Й—aati e ko tekki, hara hiЙ“e fewtondiri"
  44,54,Ko wano non. Men resini Й“e kadi yaajuЙ“e gite
  44,55,"HiЙ“e nodda toon, kala muuyanteeЙ—i, hara ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e"
  44,56,"ЖҒe meeЙ—ataa ton maayde, si wanaa maayde aranere nden. O daЙ—nda Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—en"
  44,57,"ko dokkal non, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko Й—um woni maloore mawnde nden"
  44,58,"Ko Men newiniri nde e Й—amngal maaЙ—a, ko no Й“e waajitora"
  44,59,Habiito. KamЙ“e ko Й“e habbitiiЙ“e
  45,1,"Haa, Miim"
  45,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, maandeeji wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  45,4,"Hino e tagugol on ngol kadi, e kon ko O saaki e ruugayЙ—i, ko maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e Й“en"
  45,5,"E luutondirgol jemma e Гұalorma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e toЙ“o, O wuurnitiri ngo leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude, e firlitagol keneeli Й—in, ko maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en"
  45,6,"ЖҠin ko maandeeji Allah Й—i Men janngirante hoore goonga. E ko honЙ—um e yewtere Й“e gomЙ—inta, Й“aawo [yewtere] Allah nden e Aayeeje Makko Й—en"
  45,7,Bone woodanii kala fenoowo bakkondinЙ—o
  45,8,"Mo no nana Aayeeje Allah Й—en hino janngee e dow makko, refti o hedditora e townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali Й—e. Awa wewlinir mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  45,9,"Si o anndii goЙ—Й—um e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o jogitora Й—um jalnori. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani lepte hoynooje"
  45,10,"Jahannama hino caggal maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“e faggitinoo duncanoytaaЙ“e hay huunde, wanaa kon ko Й“e jogitinoo yiЙ—Й“e ko wonaa Allah. Hino woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e"
  45,11,"Ndee [Deftere]ko peewal. ЖҒen yedduЙ“e non Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hino woodani lepte soЙ“uЙ—e muusuЙ—e"
  45,12,"Ko Alla oon woni ko eeltanta mon maaya ngam laaЙ—e ndoga e hengo e dow yamiroore Makko, ngam Й—aЙ“Й“on e Й“ural Makko e yaama joo njetton"
  45,13,"O eeltani on ko woni e kammuuji e ka leydi fof, wonii e Й—uum kaawisaaji wonande yimЙ“e miijatooЙ“e"
  45,14,Maakan Й“een goonЙ—iЙ“e yoЙ“e njaafa Й“een Й“e tijjaaki nyalЙ—i Alla ngam O yoЙ“a Й“e yimЙ“e koЙ“e paggittono ko
  45,15,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi,ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o,yantay e makko refti ko ka Joomi maa woni ruttorde mon"
  45,16,Min tottii banii Israa*iil deftere e nyeenyal e annabaagal Min njeЙ—iЙ“e e dagiiЙ—i Min Й“urniЙ“e ko heewi e binnde hee
  45,17,Min totti dallillaaji Й“annginooji Й“e luuraani si wonah caggal nde ganndal ari e mum en sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e pellet Jooma na nyaawa hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nyande darnga koЙ“e njeddandiratnoo ko
  45,18,"Refti Min mbaЙ—ma e laawol e yamiroore Amen, woto rew belaaЙ—e Й“een Й“e nganndah"
  45,19,"Pellet Й“een Й“e nafataama gaa e Alla hay huunde pellet toonyooЙ“e yogo e mum en ko weldiiЙ“e, Alla woni keeda hulЙ“e Й“e"
  45,20,O quraana kombo gite e peewal e yurmeende wonande yananaaЙ“e
  45,21,Mbela Й“een waЙ—Й“e boneeji na nanndi e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli golle lobbe hoЙ“e fota e nguurndam mum en e maayde maЙ“Й“e bonii koЙ“e nyaawata
  45,22,Alla tagrii kammuuji e leydi goonga ngam kala fittaandu yoЙ“ee kondu fagginoo ko kamЙ“e Й“e toonyetaake
  45,23,"Mbela a yiyaani oon jaggirЙ—o belaaЙ—e makko deweteeЙ—o Alla majjini mbo e dow ganndal O uddi nanЙ—e makko e Й“ernde makko, O waЙ—i e gite makko hee cuddi ko hombo feewnata oon caggal Alla mate on miiccataaka"
  45,24,"HeeferЙ“e wii Й—um wonah si wonah nguurndam aduna min maaya min nguura, halkataa min si wonah jamaanu, Й“e ngalanah Й—uum ganndal Й“e cikkita tan"
  45,25,Si aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e njanngaama e mum en hujja maЙ“Й“e wonatah si wonah ngaddee baabiraaЙ“e amen si on ngonii goonguЙ“e
  45,26,"Maaku ko Alla wuurnata on refti O wara on refti renndina on faade Гұalawma darnga mbo sikke alah e mum, kono ko Й“uri heewde e yimЙ“e nganndah"
  45,27,"Woodanii Alla laamu kammuuji e leydi, Гұande darnga darii Гұande heen meerenteeЙ“e perta"
  45,28,"HaЙ—a yiya -aan nulaaЙ—a- kala lenyol na gurfanii e koppi mum,kala lenyol na noddiree deftere mum hannde woni ko njoЙ“eteЙ—on ko ngollatnaЙ—on e nder aduna"
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere amen honde wowla goonga, Min ngoniina Min ceeraani wonde emin njamira nde winndate ko ngollatna Й—on"
  45,30,"Tawi ko Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle lobbe O naatnatЙ“e e yurmeende makko, ko Й—uum woni mala Й“anngungal"
  45,31,Tawi ko Й“een heefareeЙ“e mbela aayeeje Am Й—e njanngetanooke e dow mon mawnikiniЙ—o laatiЙ—on yimЙ“e bonЙ“e
  45,32,"SibЙ“e wiyaama pellet fodoore Alla ko goonga sikke alah heen mbi*on min nganndah ko woni darnga, min cikkiti cikkitagol min ngonaani yananaaЙ“e"
  45,33,"boneeji Й—i Й“e faggitinoo Й—in feГұana Й“e, ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon fiiltoo Й“e"
  45,34,"Й“e wi*ana hannde Min njejjita mon hono no njejjitirЙ—on pottal Гұalngu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni hoЙ—orde mno on ndanyatah walladiiЙ“e"
  45,35,"Й—uum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla Й—e jalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde Й“e njaltatah e yiite Й“e nduttataaka aduna Й“e golla golle lobbe haa Alla weleeЙ“e"
  45,36,Woodanii Alla yettoore nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde
  45,37,Na woodani Mbo manngu nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni mbo gooto foolah ГұeeГұuЙ—o
  46,1,"Haa, Miim"
  46,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, si wanaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mun]. YedduЙ“e Й“en ko Й—uurniiЙ“e e ko Й“e rentiniraa kon"
  46,4,"Maaku: \"On yi'ii ko rewoton kon hara wanaa Allah, hollee lam ko Й—i tagi e leydi ndin? Kaa hara hiЙ—i mari geЙ“al e [tagugol] kammuuli Й—in? Awa addanee lam Deftere jippinaande ado ndee Й—oo maaЙ—um batte ganndal, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  46,5,"Ko hommbo Й“uri majjude, wa on rewoowo ko wanaa Allah, kon ko jaabotaako mo haa Г‘alnde Darngal? Hara Й—in [reweteeЙ—i] ko welsindiiЙ—i e dewal majji"
  46,6,"Si yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“oyaama [ka Darngal], Й—i wontanoyay Й“e ayЙ“e, Й“e wona e yeddugol ko Й“e rewaynooЙ—i kon"
  46,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, yedunooЙ“e goonga Й“en tuma nde arnoo e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'a: \"ЖҠum ko mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"
  46,8,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay woni :\"O fefindi nde?\" Awa maaku: \"Si taw mi fefindi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam huunde e [lepte] Allah Й—en. Ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko Kanko woni Haforowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  46,9,"Maaku: \"Mi wonaa arano e NulaaЙ“e Й“en; mi anndaa kadi ko waЙ—etee mi, maa ko waЙ—eteЙ—on. Mi jokkaa si wanaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wanaa jertinoowo Й“anngina"
  46,10,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, yedduЙ—on Й—um, seedotooЙ—o e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila Й“en seedii e [sellugol] Й—um, o gomЙ—ini, onon kan townitiЙ—on...Pellet, Allah fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,11,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Si tawno Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere, Й“en (waasuЙ“e) adototaako men e mun\". Nde wonunoo Й“e fewnoraali nde, ma Й“e wi'u: \"Ndee ko fenaande neeЙ“unde"
  46,12,"Hino aditiinde, Deftere Muusaa nden, Й—owornde e yurmeende. Ndee Й—oo kadi, ko Deftere goonginir- nde [Й—eya Defte] e Й—emngal aarabu, fii yo jertinir (nde) tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e wewlinirnde moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“en: \"Ko Allah woni Joomi amen\", refti Й“e tabiti (e gomЙ—inal), kulol alanaa Й“en, wanaa kamЙ“e sunoytoo"
  46,14,"Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en duumotooЙ“e ton, njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  46,15,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on moЖҙЖҙagol e jibimЙ“e mo Й“en: Jiido makko soworike mo saЙ—teende, o jibiniri mo kadi saЙ—teende; soweede mo e enteede mo ko lebbi cappanЙ—e tati, haa ka o si o yottike sagatalaaku makku ngun o timminii duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nayi, o wi'a: \"Joomi, longinam yettugol neema Ma mo neeminirЙ—aa mi min e jibimЙ“e lam, e nde mi gollata moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i weltinayЙ—e Ma, moЖҙЖҙinanaa lam geyngol am ngol. Mi tuubanii Ma, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  46,16,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Men jaЙ“anta ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e golli, Men yawtana Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e, (Й“e jeyaama) e yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en. ЖҠum ko fodoore goonga nde Й“e fodanoo"
  46,17,"Kala non wi'anЙ—o jibimЙ“e mo Й“en: \"Uf mo'on ! Kere on foday lam immintineede hara le gomЙ—ii mofte yawtiino ado lam?\" Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o no faabtinora Allah [wiide mo]: \"Ee bone maa, GomЙ—in ! Pellet, fodooree Allah nde ko goonga\". O wi'a: \"ЖҠum wonaali, si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,18,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Konngol ngol jojji e mun, (Й“e jeyaama) e mofte yawtunooЙ—e ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e. Pellet, Й“e laatino sooyuЙ“e"
  46,19,"Hino woodani kala [fedde e maЙ“Й“e]: darjaaji e ko Й“e golli kon, fii no O hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“di golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en; e hoore Й“e tooГұetaake"
  46,20,"Г‘alnde heeferЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen (Й“e wi'anee): \"On naЙ“ii moЖҙЖҙi mon Й—in ka nguurndam mon aduna, dakmitorЙ—on Й—i. Hannde non, on yoЙ“itirte lepte hoynooje, sabu ko townitoraynoЙ—on kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko huuwiraynoЙ—on kon faasiqaaku"
  46,21,"Janto fii musiЙ—Й“e Aadi (Huudi) Й“en, nde o jertinirnoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en aynde nden - gomЙ—ii hari jertinooji yawtiino yeeso makko e Й“aawo makko - wonnde: \"Wata on rewu si wanaa Allah. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  46,22,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"E a aru men fii yo a firliaa men e rewetee- Й—i amen Й—in? Awa addan men ko kammbiranЙ—aa men kon, si wonii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  46,23,"O maaki: \"Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Min mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"
  46,24,"Nde Й“e yi'unoo ruulde honde weeЙ“itii fewtiri ayЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Ndee ko duulere toЙ“aynde e men\". Ko nden kan woni ! ko hawjirnoЙ—on kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte muusuЙ—e woni e mun"
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala huunde, yamiroore Joomi mayru\". ЖҒe waЙ—tini, tawi yi'etaake si wanaa koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,26,"GomЙ—ii Men yeЙ—iino Й“e, e kon ko Men yeЙ—aali on e mun. Men waЙ—ani Й“e nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. Kono Й—en nanЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e (fow) duncanaali Й“e goЙ—Й—um, tawde Й“e laatino yeddooЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й—en. Ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon jippii e maЙ“Й“e"
  46,27,"GomЙ—ii Men halkiino ca'e wonunooЙ“e sera mon; Men firlitiri Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o Й“e ruttoto"
  46,28,"Ko haЙ—no Й—in Й—i Й“e jogitornoo reweteeЙ—i Й“aЙ—tinorЙ—i gaanin Allah, faaboo Й“e? Tigi on, Й—in majjirii Й“e; ko Й—um wonunoo fenaande maЙ“Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  46,29,"Janto tuma nde Men imminnoo fedde jinna e maaЙ—a, hiЙ—i heЙ—oo Alqur'aana. Nde Й—i tawanoo Й—um, Й—i wi'i: \"HeЙ—ee\"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, Й—i huccitiri ka yimЙ“e majji, jeertinooji"
  46,30,"ЖҠi wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu amen, men nanii Deftere jippinaande Й“aawo Muusaa, goonginnde Й—en adiiЙ—e nde. Hinde fewna e goonga e laawol focciingol"
  46,31,"Ko ono yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, gomЙ—inon mo. [Ontuma] O haforanay on junuubimon Й—in, O daЙ—nda on lepte muusuЙ—e"
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotooЙ—o ka leydi, o alaa kadi giЙ—o gaanin Makko. Ko Й“en woni e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  46,33,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde ko Allah tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, O ronkiraali tagugol Й—i, wonnde ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o wuurnitugol maayЙ“e Й“en? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  46,34,"Г‘alnde heeferЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen, [Й“e wi'anee]: \"Wanaa goonga nii?\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!\". O Daala : \"Awa meeЙ—iree non lepte Й—en, sabu kon ko yeddiraynoЙ—on"
  46,35,"MuГұГұor muГұal joomiraaЙ“e pellital Й“en ka NulaaЙ“e; wata a hawjan Й“e. Г‘alnde Й“e yi'oyta ko Й“e kammbiranaa kon, Й“e wa'oyay wa si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wanaa dumunna-hun Гұalorma. ЖҠun ko yottinal. Ko homЙ“e halketee si wanaa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  47,1,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,2,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e gomЙ—ini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immorЙ—o e Joomi maЙ“Й“e - O yawtanii Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O moЖҙЖҙinii fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on"
  47,3,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde yedduЙ“e Й“en jokkii meere nden, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e on. Ko wano nii Allah piyiranta yimЙ“e Й“en mise maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,4,"Si on arii hawrude e yedduЙ“e Й“en (ka hare), ko soppugol daaЙ—e Й—en. Haa si on Й—uЙ—Й—inii warugol Й“e, haЙ“Й“on koyЙ—e Й—en. Ko si on moЖҙЖҙoray e maЙ“Й“e accitugol Й“e Й“aawo Й—um, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare nden wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non Гұaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. WaraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en, pellet, O yeebataa golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,5,"Arma O fewna Й“e, O moЖҙЖҙina fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e"
  47,6,"O naadoya Й“e Aljanna, mo O anndini Й“e fii mun"
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on wonii wallooЙ“e fii Allah, O wallay on, O tabintina teppe mon Й—en"
  47,8,"YedduЙ“e Й“ee kan, halkaare woodanii Й“e, O majjinii kadi golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,9,"ЖҠum le ko tawde Й“e aГұii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,10,"E Й“ee yiilaaki e leydi ndin, Й“e teskoo ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii maЙ“Й“e. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  47,11,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde ko Allah woni giЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en; hara non yedduЙ“e Й“en, giЙ—o (woo) alanaa Й“e"
  47,12,"Pellet, Allah naadoyay gomЙ—imЙ“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en, Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley (kuЙ“eeje) majje. YedduЙ“e Й“en kan, hiЙ“e dakmitoo, Й“e Гұaamira wano neemoraaЙ—i Й—in Гұaamirta; hara non ko Yiite ngen woni jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e. @Corrected"
  47,13,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ca'e, Й“urnooЙ“e tiiЙ—ude cemmbe, e dii ndeen saare maa raЙ—iinde ma, Й“e Men halki, ballo alanaa Й“e"
  47,14,"Kere ko on wonЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mun, wa'i wa Й“en cuЙ—inanaaЙ“e kuuЙ—e mun bonЙ—e Й—en, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e"
  47,15,"Ko woni sifa Aljanna fodaaЙ—o on gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en: ina toon canЙ—i ndiyam Й—i dakamme mun waylaaki, e canЙ—i Й“ira Й—i waylataa dakamme mun, e canЙ—i konnjam welayЙ—am yarooЙ“e, e canЙ—i njuuri laЙ“Й“inaandi. Hino woodani Й“e kadi ton: kala dimЙ“e, e haforaneede immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. [ЖҒen wa'oyay] wa luttinoyteeeЙ“e Й“en ka Yiite, Й“e yarnee ndiyam fatayЙ—am, Й—am taЖҙa tetekki maЙ“Й“e Й—in"
  47,16,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e heЙ—itotooЙ“e ma. Kono ko haa si Й“e yaltii ka maaЙ—a, Й“e wi'ana okkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“en: \"Ko honЙ—um dee, o wi'unoo naanen?\" Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah noti e Й“erЙ—e mun Й—en, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,17,"FeewuЙ“e Й“en kan, O Й“eydu Й“e peewal O okkiЙ“e gomЙ—al maЙ“Й“e"
  47,18,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa Darngal ngal nde ardata Й“e e juhal? GomЙ—ii le maandeeji maggal arii. Ko honno Й“e waajitoroyta, si ngal ardanii Й“e (juhal)"
  47,19,"Awa anndu pellet, reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Allah, insinanoЙ—aa junuubi maa Й—in, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en. Allah no anndi Гұallirde mon e hiirirde mon"
  47,20,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en hino wi'a: \"Hara nun cortewol (hare) jippotono!\" Si tawii le cortewol ГұeГұaangol jippinaama, fii hare jantaama e maggol, a tinay Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun hino ndaare, ndaarЙ—e mo maayde faЙ—Й—ini. Ko haanannoo Й“e"
  47,21,"ko Й—oftagol e konngol moЖҙЖҙol. Si fiyaaku on fellitii, hara nun Й“e gomЙ—inno Allah, ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e"
  47,22,"E on tamЖҙinaaki, si wonii on Й—uurnike, nde bonnoton e leydi ndin, taЖҙon enЙ—amaaji mon"
  47,23,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah huЙ—i Й“en, O faaЙ—ini Й“e, O wumini giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,24,"E Й“ee tasktaako Alqur'aana, kaa ko sokirЙ—e woni woni e Й“erЙ—e mum en"
  47,25,"Pellet, Й“en ruttorЙ“e Й“abbe mun Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannoo Й“e, ko seytaane cuЙ—inani Й“e, o hodi Й“e"
  47,26,"Ko tawde Й“e wi'anii Й“en aГұuЙ“e ko Allah jippini kon: \"Men Й—oftoto on e yoga e piiji\". Allah non no anndi gunndooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in"
  47,27,"Ko honno (Й“ee wa'oyta) tuma nde Malaa'ika'en timmini fii maЙ“Й“e, hara hiЙ“e bantoo geece maЙ“Й“e e dote maЙ“Й“e"
  47,28,"Ko tawde ko Й“e jokkii ko tikkinta Allah, Й“e aГұii welayЙ—i Mo Й—in, O bonni fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,29,Kaa Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun sikuu wonnde Allah yaltintaa ngaynguuji maЙ“Й“e
  47,30,"Sinno Men haajuno, Men holleteno Й“e. Anndiraa Й“e maandeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in; ko pellet, a anndirayno Й“e ka konngol welngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon Й—en"
  47,31,"Ma Men jarribo on, haa Men annda tiiЙ—niiЙ“e Й“en e mon, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en. Men jarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon"
  47,32,"Pellet, yedduЙ“e Й“en Й“e faddi laawol Allah ngol, Й“e lunndii NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannde Й“e, Й“en lorrataa Allah hay huunde. Ma O bonnu fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,33,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e! ЖҠoftee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, wata on bonnu golle mon Й—en"
  47,34,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti Й“e maayi ko Й“e heeferЙ“e, Allah haforanoytaa Й“e"
  47,35,"Wata on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni fooluЙ“e Й“en, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njoЙ“di golle mon Й—en"
  47,36,"Anndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbeleeЙ—e tan; hara le si on gomЙ—iii, on hulii [Allah], O yeЙ—ay on njoЙ“di mon ndin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon Й—en"
  47,37,"Si O aru lamndaade on fii majje, haa O duГұii on (e mun), wuddon, O feГұГұina non konnaagu mon ngun"
  47,38,"Hey mon onon Й—oo, hiЙ—o noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wuddayЙ“e. Kala non wudduЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon wonЙ—on waasuЙ“e Й“en. Si on huccii, O waЙ—titira on woЙ—Й“e goo, hara non Й“en wa'ataa wano mon"
  48,1,Men udditanii ma uddital Й“anngungal
  48,2,"fii no Allah yawtirani kon ko ardinЙ—aa e junuubi, e ko sakkitii, e fii no O timminira neema Makko on e maaЙ—a, O fewne e laawol foocciingol"
  48,3,e no Allah wallire ballal tiiЙ—ungal
  48,4,"Ko Kanko woni jippinЙ—o deeЖҙere nden e Й“erЙ—e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, fii no Й“e Й“eydora gomЙ—inal e dow gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal. Ko Allah woodani koneeli kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin; Allah siforii wonnde AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  48,5,"e fii no O naadira gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley mun, ko Й“Й—e duumotooЙ“e e majji, e no O montira-naЙ“e banЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. ЖҠum wonii ka Allah, malal mawnungal. @Corrected"
  48,6,"E no O leptira naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sirkooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, sikkooЙ“e Allah sikke bonЙ—e. Yiiloonde bonЙ—i ngonii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah tikkaniiЙ“e kadi, O huЙ—ii Й“e, O hebilanii Й“e Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  48,7,"Ko Allah woodani konuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Allah siforii wonnde FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  48,8,"Men nulirii ma seedotooЙ—o, wewlinoowo, e jertinoowo"
  48,9,"fii no gomЙ—iniron Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, mawninon mo, teddinon mo, subbunhinanoЙ—on Mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  48,10,"Pellet, Й“en wonЙ“e ahodude e maaЙ—a, anndu ko Allah Й“e woni e ahodude. Junngo Allah ngon no senngo dow juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Kala non firtuЙ—o, haray ko hoore makko o firtani; kala kadi hunnuЙ—o ko o ahodi kon e Allah, aray nde O okkata mo njoЙ“di mawnundi"
  48,11,"Aray nde tultuЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en wi'ane: \"Jawle amen Й—en e Й“eynguureeji amen Й—in sokolinii men. Insinano men\". HiЙ“e wowlira Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, ko alaa e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku: \"Ko hommbo waawani on ka Allah, si O faandanike on lorra maa hara O faandani on nafa? Wurin Allah siforiino wonnde HumpitiiЙ—o ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  48,12,"Wurin on sukkuno NulaaЙ—o on e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en artataano fes ka Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠum cuЙ—inaa e Й“erЙ—e mon; sikkuЙ—on sikke bonЙ—e, laatiЙ—on yimЙ“e halkaaЙ“e"
  48,13,"Kala dee mo gomЙ—inaali Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray MeЙ—en heblani yedduЙ“e Й“en (Yiite) dulbaynge"
  48,14,"Ko Allah heeranii laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo haforana mo O muuyani, O lepta mo O muuyani. Allah siforii wonnde Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  48,15,"Aray nde luttuЙ“e Й“en wi'a, tuma fokkitanoyton henndagol konu-hoyri ndin: \"Accee men jokka on\". HiЙ“e faalaa waЙ—titugol daalol Allah ngol. Maaku: \"On jokkataa men fes. Ko wano mon nii Allah daalirnoo oya tuma\". Ma Й“e wi'u: \"On aГұanay men tun woni\". Tigi on, Й“e faamataano si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  48,16,"Maakan tultuЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en: \"Arma nde noddeteЙ—on e yimЙ“e joomiraaЙ“e doole tiiЙ—uЙ“e. HoЙ“on Й“e maaЙ—um Й“e silma. Si on Й—oftike, Allah okkay on mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙundi; si on huccitirii no huccitirnoЙ—on oya tuma, O leptira lepte muusuЙ—e"
  48,17,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e hoore Й“unЙ—o on, wanaa e laЖҙoowo on wanaa kadi e nawnuЙ—on bakkaatu fawii. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, O naadoyay mo Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley mun. Kala kadi Й—uurniiЙ—o, O leptiray mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  48,18,"GomЙ—ii Allah welano gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, tuma Й“e ahondiraynoo e maaЙ—a ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, O jippini deeЖҙere nden e maЙ“Й“e, O warjoriiЙ“e uddital Й“adiingal"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri Й—uuЙ—undi ndi Й“e henndotoo. Allah siforii wonnde FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri Й—uuЙ—undi ndi henndotoЙ—on, O yaccinani on ndii Й—oo, O suri juuЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en e mo'on, fii yo wonu maande wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, O fewnira on laawol focciingol"
  48,21,"E wonndi goo ndi on haЙ—tanaali taho, Allah kan no huЙ“indii ndi. Allah siforii wonnde haЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  48,22,"Hay si yedduЙ“e Й“en haЙ“iino on, Й“e huccintinayno Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en, refti Й“e heЙ“ataano giЙ—o wanaa ballao"
  48,23,"ЖҠum ko sunna Alla feЖҙЖҙunooЙ—o ko adii. A heЙ“antaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu"
  48,24,"Ko Kanko woni suranЙ—o on juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e mo'on, e suruЙ—o juuЙ—e mon Й—en e maЙ“Й“e, ka aynde Makka, Й“aawo O foolnude on e maЙ“Й“e. Allah siforii wonnde ReenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  48,25,"Ko Й“en woni ko yeddi, Й“e faddii on e Juurlirde Hormorde nden, [Й“e haЙ—i] neldaari ndin nde ndi yottotoo nokku mayri. Si wanaano sabu worЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e e rewЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e on anndataano haa haЙ“on Й“e, bakkaatu heЙ“a on e fee maЙ“Й“e, ko aldaa e anndugol... fii yo Allah naadu e yurmeende Makko nden, on mo O muuyani. Si Й“e senndondir-no [e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en], ko pellet, Men leptirayno yedduЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, lepte muusuЙ—e"
  48,26,"Tuma nde Й“eya yedduЙ“e waЙ—unoo ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e jinngo, jinngo majjiyanke...Allah jippini deeЖҙere Makko nden e dow NulaaЙ—o Makko on e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, O fawi Й“e konngol gomЙ—al, Й“e woni Й“urЙ“e jojjude e hanndude e maggol. Allah siforii Anndugol kala huunde"
  48,27,"GomЙ—ii Allah goonginiranii NulaaЙ—o Makko on, koyЙ—ol ngol e hoore goonga : Ko maa naaton e juulirde Hormorde nden si Allah muuyii, hara ko on hooliiЙ“e, femmbuЙ“e ko*e mon maa Й—uytuЙ“e (cukuli), on hulataa. Himo anndi ko on anndaa. O waЙ—i ko wanaa ngol (naatugol Makko) Й—on, uddital Й“adiingal"
  48,28,"Ko Kanko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o Makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o fawaka ka e hoore kala diina. Allah yonii seedee"
  48,29,"Muhammdu ko NulaaЙ—o Allah. WonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en ko ГұaaЙ—uЙ“e e yedduЙ“e Й“en, yurmondirЙ“e hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. A yi'ay Й“e hiЙ“e ruЖҙЖҙa, hiЙ“e sujja, hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ira Allah Й“ural e welayee. Maandeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in no ka geece maЙ“Й“e batte sujjugol ngol. Ko Й—um woni ko Й“e siforaa ka Tawreeta. No Й“e siforaa ka Linjiila kan, ko wano remuru yaltingu puЙ—i mayru, ngu Й“anngini Й—i, Й—i tekki, Й—i fotondiri e binndeeje majji, hara Й—um no haawna remooЙ“e, fii no [Allah] tikkinira Й“e yedduЙ“e Й“en. Allah fodii e maЙ“Й“e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in, haforanal e njoЙ“di mawnundi"
  49,1,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on adito yeeso Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  49,2,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on towu sowtooji mon e hoore sowto Annabaajo on, wata on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon Й—en bonata, hara on so'aa-anndude"
  49,3,"Pellet, Й“en joltinooЙ“e sowtooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka NulaaЙ—o Allah on, ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla jarabii Й“erЙ—e mun Й—en gomЙ—al. Hino woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  49,4,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e no noddire ka Й“aawo cuuЙ—i, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, wanaa haqqilooЙ“e"
  49,5,"Sinno Й“e muГұГұino haa yaltaa e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e. Allah ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  49,6,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si faasiqiijo ardanii on e kumpital, tefee fii wata on heЙ“or e yimЙ“e sabu majjeede, wonton ninsuЙ“e e kon ko waЙ—uЙ—on"
  49,7,"Anndee wonnde NulaaЙ—o Allah on hino hakkunde mon. Si o tewtino on e ko Й—uuЙ—i e fiyakuuji, on tampayno. Kono Allah yiЙ—ini on gomЙ—inal, O cuЙ—ini ngal e Й“erЙ—e mon; O aГұini on keeferaaku, e faasiqaaku e geddi. Ko Й“en woni feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  49,8,"Й—um ko Й“ural immorde ka Allah e neema. Allah ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  49,9,"Si feddeeji Й—iЙ—i e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haЙ“ii, moЖҙЖҙintinee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si fedde goo bewii e hoore ndeya, ko haЙ“ugol wonnde e bewude nden, haa nde ruttoo e yamiroore Allah nden. Si nde ruttike, moЖҙЖҙintiniree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al. NunЙ—ee, tawde pellet, Allah no yiЙ—i nunЙ—ooЙ“e Й“en"
  49,10,"Anndee gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ko jeyduЙ“e. Haray moЖҙЖҙinee hakkunde jeydal mon ngal, hulon Allah, belajo'o on yurminte"
  49,11,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Wata yimЙ“e jalnor yimЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en (jalaaЙ“e) hino Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wanaa rewЙ“e woni ko jalnorta rewЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en no Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wata on aybidnir ko'e-mon, wata on bugondir jammooje (bonЙ—e). Innde faasiqaaku nden bonii Й“aawo nde gomЙ—inal nden. Kala mo tuubaali, ko Й“en woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  49,12,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! WoЙ—Й—itee e ko Й—uuЙ—i e sikke. Pellet, yoga e sikke ko bakkaatu. Wata on wiЙ—ondir, wata yoga mon Гұo'u yoga. Hara gooto e mo'on yiЙ—ay Гұaamugol teewu musiЙ—Й—o mun maayЙ—o? HiЙ—on aГұi Й—um. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, HinnotooЙ—o"
  49,13,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! Men tagiriii on immorde e gorel e deyel, Men waЙ—iri on leЖҙЖҙi e gori, fii yo on anndindir. Pellet, Й“urЙ“e teddude e mon Й“en ka Allah, ko Й“urЙ“e gomЙ—ude Й“en e mon. Pellet, Allah ko AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"
  49,14,"YimЙ“e ladde Й“en wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—inii\". Maaku: \"On gomЙ—inaali taho. Wi'ee kan : Men silmii. GomЙ—inal ngal naataali taho ka Й“erЙ—e mon. Si on Й—oftike Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, O Й—uytantaa on huunde e golle mon Й—en\". Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  49,15,"GomЙ—imЙ“e (tigi) Й“en, ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, refti Й“e sikkitaaki, Й“e tiiЙ—nori kadi jawle e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii laawol Allah ngol. Ko Й“en woni goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  49,16,"Maaku: \"Kere on anndinay Allah diina mon kan, hara non Allah no anndi kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi?\" Allah ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  49,17,"HiЙ“e waj Ma fii Й“e silmii. Maaku: \"Wata on wajitam silmugol mon. Si ko woni, ko Allah wajitata on fii O fewnirii on e gomЙ—inal, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  49,18,"Pellet, Allah no anndi wirniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Allah ko ReenuЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  50,1,Qaaf. Mi woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden
  50,2,"Si ko woni, Й“e ЕӢalЙ—u ko tawi kon jertinoowo arii Й“e iwЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e ; heeferЙ“e Й“en wi'i: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko huunde haawniinde"
  50,3,"Kere si men maayii, men wontii mbulmbuldi...? ЖҠum Й—on ko ruttitagol woЙ—Й—ungol non"
  50,4,GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en anndi ko leydi ndin Гұaamata kon e maЙ“Й“e ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenunde
  50,5,"Si ko woni, Й“e fennu goonga kan tuma nde ka arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e e nder fiyaaku jilЙ“uЙ—o"
  50,6,"E Й“ee ndaaraali kammu ngun dow maЙ“Й“e, ko honno Men mahiri ngun Men cuЙ—ini ngu ; hara perЙ—i alanaa ngu"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fuЙ—ini e mayri kala nooneeji [puЙ—i] wooЙ—uЙ—i"
  50,8,fii tasakuyee e waaju wonannde kala jeyaaЙ—o ruttotooЙ—o
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam barkinaaЙ—am ummaade ka kammu, Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am gese e gabbe soГұeteeЙ—e"
  50,10,e leЙ—Й—e tamaro juutuЙ—e wonduЙ—e e piindi fawondirndi
  50,11,ko arsike jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. Men wuurnitiri Й—am kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko non woni fii ummital ngal
  50,12,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e nuuhu Й“en, e yimЙ“e ЖҒunndu Й“en e Samuuda'en [fow] fennuno"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musiЙ—Й“e Luutu Й“en"
  50,14,"e yimЙ“e fitaare nden, e yimЙ“e Tubba' Й“en. Kala maЙ“Й“e fennuno NulaaЙ“e Й“en, kammbaa Am on jojji"
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno fii tagu aranu ngun? Ko woni kamЙ“e, hiЙ“e e jiЙ“aare fii tagiteede laawol kesol"
  50,16,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii neЙ—Й—anke on, MeЙ—en anndi ko wonkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Menen Й“uri Й“adaade mo e dii Й—aЙ—ol (makko) daande ngol"
  50,17,"tuma nde jaЙ“Й“oytooЙ“e Й“en Й—iЙ—o jaЙ“Й“oroytoo [golle makko Й—en] Гұaamo e nano, hara hiЙ“e jooЙ—ii"
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wanaa hino takko makko winndoowo tawaaЙ—o"
  50,19,"ЖҠeЙ—Й—ere maayde nden ardi e goonga : \"Ko Й—um wonunoo ko dogaynoЙ—aa"
  50,20,Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni Г‘alaande kammbaa nden
  50,21,"Wonkii kala ara, hara hiki wonndi e soggoowo e seedotooЙ—o"
  50,22,GomЙ—ii a laatinoke welsindiiЙ—o e ndee. Men hunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa Й—en hannde ko seeЙ“uЙ—e
  50,23,"WonndiiЙ—o makko on wi'a: \"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ka am Й—oo, maandinaa-Й—um"
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon Й—iЙ—o, kala yedduЙ—o canndallo"
  50,25,"haЙ—oowo moЖҙЖҙere, jaggitoowo, sikkitiiЙ—o"
  50,26,on waЙ—iduЙ—o e Allah reweteeЙ—o goo. Bugee mo ka nder lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere woЙ—Й—unde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am Й—oo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol waЙ—titetaake ka Am Й—oo ; Mi siforaa kadi tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en
  50,30,"Г‘alnde Men wi'anoyta Jahannama on : \"E a heewii?\" Nge wi'a: \"Ko Й“eydee hino woodi"
  50,31,"Aljanna on Й“aЙ—tinanee gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, hara wanaa ka woЙ—Й—i"
  50,32,"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ko fodaЙ—on, wonannde kala ruttiiЙ—o [e Joomi mun] reeniiЙ—o"
  50,33,"on huluЙ—o Jom Hinaranke On ka wirnii, o ardi e Й“ernde laaЙ“unde"
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam\". Ko nden woni Гұalaande luttaynde nden"
  50,35,"Hino woodani Й“e ton kala ko Й“e faaletee, hara kadi Й“eydaari hino ka Amen"
  50,36,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e gire Й—en Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“en Й“urnooЙ“e doole, Й“en wanngorii e leydi ndin, ndaarugol taw si Й“e heЙ“ay laaworde"
  50,37,"Pellet, wonii e Й—um, waaju wonannde kala jom Й“ernde, maa tuЙ—uЙ—o noppi hara ko tawaaЙ—o"
  50,38,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, nder balЙ—e jeegoo, tampere woo heЙ“aali Men. @Corrected"
  50,39,"MuГұГұo e ko Й“e wowlata kon, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Joomi maa ado puЙ—al naange ngen e ado mutal ngal"
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Mo e ka battane [julЙ—e] farlaaЙ—e"
  50,41,"HeЙ—o, Гұalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e nokkuure Й“adiinde"
  50,42,"Гұalnde Й“e naniroyta haacaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko nden woni Г‘alnnde yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]"
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Menen wuurnata Men wara, ko ka Amen kadi woni ruttorde nden"
  50,44,"Г‘alnde leydi ndin seekotoo [Й“e yaltira] heГұagol; ko nde woni mooЙ“irde newaniinde Men"
  50,45,"Ko Menen Й“uri anndude ko Й“e wowlata kon. A wonaa dooloowoЙ“e. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala huloowo kammbaa An on"
  51,1,Mi woondirii keneeli jarorayЙ—i (leydi) jaragol
  51,2,Mi woondirii duule ronndotooЙ—e toЙ“o tiiЙ—ngo
  51,3,Mi woondirii laaЙ—e dogirayЙ—e newaare
  51,4,E peccooji yamiraande
  51,5,"ko podete Й—on ko, ko goongo"
  51,6,Haasbeede ko ko wonata
  51,7,Mi woondirii kammu jom Й—ate ngun
  51,8,"Pellet, hiЙ—on e konngol luurrangol"
  51,9,Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaaЙ—o e gomЙ—inal
  51,10,FenooЙ“e Й“en huЙ—aama
  51,11,Й“en yolliiЙ“e e majjere welsindiiЙ“e
  51,12,"HiЙ“e lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni Г‘alaande njoЙ“di kuuЙ—e"
  51,13,Г‘alaande nde Й“e leptoyteeЙ“e ka Yiite
  51,14,MeeЙ—ee lepte mon Й—en; ko Й—um woni ko keppatnoЙ—on kon
  51,15,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e aljannaaji e Й“ulli"
  51,16,JaggatnooЙ“e ko Joom maЙ“Й“e okkiЙ“e Й“e te ko adii Й—uum koЙ“e moЖҙЖҙinatnooЙ“e
  51,17,HoЙ“e pamЙ—uno koЙ“e Й—aanatoo jemma
  51,18,E saanga ndoogu hoЙ“e toro yaafeede
  51,19,Ina e jawЙ—e mumen hakke wonande ГұaagatooЙ“e e Й“e Гұaagataako
  51,20,Ina e nder leydi he maandeeji wonande yananaaЙ“e
  51,21,E nder pittaali mon mate on teskataaka
  51,22,Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante Й—on
  51,23,E Joom kammu e leydi koЙ—um goongo hono no kaalirton nih
  51,24,Mbela arii e maa yeewtere hoЙ—Й“e Ibraahiima teddinaaЙ“e
  51,25,"Tuma Й“e naatunoo ka makko Й“e wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men Й—enЖҙii Й“e on"
  51,26,O naayii faade e koreeji makko O addori ngaari payndi
  51,27,O Й“adaniЙ“e ndi o wii on Гұaamata
  51,28,"O so*i e mum en kulol, Й“e wii woto hul, Й“e weltiniriЙ“e cuklel"
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii yeesa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara"
  51,30,Malaykaaji Й—i mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko Kanko woni ГұeeГұo Ganndo
  51,31,"[Annabai Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko woni fii mon, onon Й“ee nelaaЙ“e"
  51,32,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Menen men nela e yimЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  51,33,"fii yo men accitu e maЙ“Й“e, kaaЖҙe iwЙ—e e loope (juЙ—aaЙ—e)"
  51,34,"maandiniraaЙ—e ka Joomi maa, fii fantinooЙ“e Й“en"
  51,35,Men yaltini toon kala gomЙ—imЙ“e wonunooЙ“e ton
  51,36,"Men tawaano ton, si wanaa suudu juulЙ“e wooturu"
  51,37,"Men acci ton maande, wonannde Й“en hulooЙ“e lepte muusuЙ—e Й—en"
  51,38,"[Men acci kadi maande] e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  51,39,"Kono o Й—uurnodii e cemmbe makko, o wi'i [Muusaa]: \"Ko mbileejo maa feetuЙ—o"
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko Й—in, Men bugodii Й“e ka maayo, tawde ko o felniiЙ—o"
  51,41,"E 'Adi'en, tuma Men wurtunoo henndu bonndu ndun e maЙ“Й“e"
  51,42,"ndu accataa hay huunde nde ndu arani, si wanaa ndu waЙ—tay nde wa ndoondi"
  51,43,"E Samuuda'en kadi, tuma nde Й“e wi'ananoo : \"Dakmitee haa seeЙ—a"
  51,44,"ЖҒe townitanii yamiroore Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, haacaango ngon nanngi Й“e, tawi hiЙ“e Жҙeewa"
  51,45,"ЖҒe waawaano daragol (laawoo), Й“e wonaano kadi faabaaЙ“e"
  51,46,"Ko non kadi yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en ko adii[Й“e]. ЖҒen ko yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e wonunoo"
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen. Pellet, ko Men yaГұГұuЙ“e"
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertundi. Men moЖҙЖҙii weertuЙ“e"
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone Й—iЙ—i; belajo'o on waajitoray"
  51,50,"Awa dogee kisan faade e Allah. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  51,51,"Wata on waЙ—idane Allah reweteeЙ—o goo. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  51,52,"Ko wano non. NulaaЙ—o araali e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e, si wanaa Й“e wi'ay : \"Ko mbileejo maa feetuЙ—o"
  51,53,"Hara Й“e wasondir e Й—um? Ko woni kon, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e bewuЙ“e"
  51,54,"Runto Й“e, a felnaaki [e fiiaЙ“Й“e]"
  51,55,"Waajo tun; sabu waajagol ngol, hino nafa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yimЙ“e, si wanaa fii yo Й“e rewan"
  51,57,Mi Й—aЙ“Й“iraa Й“e arsike; Mi Й—aЙ“Й“aa yo Й“e Гұammina
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo On, Jom cemmbe tiiЙ—uЙ—e"
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, bakkaat yeru bakkaat nanndo maЙ“Й“e'en, wata Й“e hawju"
  51,60,"Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, e nden Г‘alaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e kammbanaa"
  52,1,"Mi woondirii [Fello] Tuuri ngon"
  52,2,E Deftere winndaande nden
  52,3,e Й—eri fontaaЙ—i
  52,4,E Suudu wuurniraandu ndun
  52,5,E Kippoodi toowundi ndin
  52,6,E maayo heewuno ngon
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Joomi maa Й—en ko yanooje"
  52,8,Alaa duГұoowo Й—e
  52,9,Г‘alnde kammu ngun dillirta dillere
  52,10,pelle Й—en wona e yahugol
  52,11,"haray nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  52,12,"Й“en wonuЙ“e e jumpugol, hiЙ“e fija"
  52,13,Г‘alnde Й“e duГұiroytee doole ka Yiite Jahannama duГұannde
  52,14,"[ЖҒe wi'anee] : \"Ko ngee Yiite woni ko fennaynoЙ—on"
  52,15,E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on alaa yi'ude
  52,16,"Sumee e magge! MuГұГұiЙ—on maa on muГұГұaaki, fow no fota e mon. Anndee ko yoЙ“eteЙ—on, ko kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  52,17,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji"
  52,18,"ko Й“e dakimitotooЙ“e kon ko Joomi maЙ“Й“e okki Й“e, Joomi maЙ“Й“e daЙ—ndi Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—en"
  52,19,"[ЖҒe wi'anee] : \"Г‘aamee yaron, ko newi moЙ—deum, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  52,20,"hara ko on soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e e hoore danЙ—e weertindiraaЙ—e\", Men resina Й“e kadi yooЙ—a e yaaJa giteeЙ“e"
  52,21,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e, geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol kadi jokki Й“e e gomЙ—inal, Men tawtindinay Й“e e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol. Men Й—uytantaa Й“e huunde e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en; neЙ—Й—o kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa"
  52,22,Men Й“eydani Й“e muuyanteeЙ—i e tebbeeli kala ko tuuyetee
  52,23,"HiЙ“e jaaЙ“ondira ton, ГұedduЙ—e Й—e jillaa meere wanaa ko bakkondinta"
  52,24,"SukaaЙ“e no eltanaaЙ“e hino wanngoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wa'uЙ“e wa kaЕӢЕӢe maraaЙ—e"
  52,25,"Yoga maЙ“Й“e fewtita yoga, Й“e lamndondira"
  52,26,"Й“e wi'a: \"Pellet, men laatino ado [hannde], hulunooЙ“e [lepte Й—en] hakkunde yimЙ“e amen"
  52,27,"Allah moЖҙЖҙii e amen, O daЙ—ni men lepte Norngal"
  52,28,"Men laatino ado [hannde], torotonooЙ“e Mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni MoЖҙЖҙo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  52,29,"Anndintin tun, sabu neema Joomi maa on, a wonaa ndureejo wanaa a feetuЙ—o"
  52,30,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay wonnde : \"Ko yimoowo ! Men habbitani mo tun jikke maayde"
  52,31,"Maaku : \"Awa habbitee ! Min kadi miЙ—o habbitodi e mon"
  52,32,Kaa ko haqqille maЙ“Й“e Й—en yamirЙ“e Й—um? Kaa hara ko Й“e yimЙ“e bewuЙ“e tun
  52,33,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay wonnde : \"O sincu nde?\" Si ko woni, wanaa Й“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  52,34,"Awa yo Й“e addii yewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko Й“e goonguЙ“e"
  52,35,Kaa Й“e tagira Й“aawo taguЙ—o? Kaa ko kamЙ“e woni taguЙ“e Й“en
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kamЙ“e tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, Й“e yananaaka"
  52,37,Kaa Й“e jogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa Й—in? Kaa ko kamЙ“e woni huЙ“indiiЙ“e Й“en
  52,38,Kaa Й“e jogiti Й“argal ngal Й“e jentorta? Awa yo heЙ—itiiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on addu hujja Й“annguЙ—o
  52,39,"Kaa hara ko Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e woodanta Mo, onon kan worЙ“e Й“en"
  52,40,"Kaa a lamndi Й“e njoЙ“di, hara yoЙ“ugol ndi no teddani Й“e"
  52,41,"Kaa Й“e anndu fii wirniiЙ—i Й—in, hara hiЙ“e winnda"
  52,42,"Kaa Й“e faala fewjoore? Doo ko yedduЙ“e Й“en, woni fooleteeЙ“e pewje Й“en"
  52,43,"Kaa hiЙ“e mari reweteeЙ—o ko woori Allah? Senaade woodanii Allah, e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  52,44,"Si Й“e yi'ii taЖҙatine immornde ka kammu no yani, Й“e wi'a: \"Ko duule fawondirЙ—e"
  52,45,"Terto Й“e, haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e leptoytee e mun"
  52,46,"Г‘alnde nde pewje maЙ“Й“e duncanoytaa Й“e hay huunde, Й“e wonaa kadi walloyteeЙ“e"
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, lepte goo ko wanaa Й—en Й—on. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude kon e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  52,48,"MuГұГұo Гұaawoore Joomi maa nden. Tawde pellet, hiЙ—a e ndenka Amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma Й“aЕӢotoЙ—aa"
  52,49,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Mo e ka mutugol koode"
  53,1,E hoodere si konde fukkiima
  53,2,Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaaГұi
  53,3,O haalata belaaЙ—e
  53,4,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju bahyateeЙ—o"
  53,5,Ko jom semmbe janngini Й—um mbo
  53,6,Jom mbaadi njoondi o fotondiri
  53,7,Hombo e jookli toowЙ—i
  53,8,Refti o Й“adi o Й“attii
  53,9,O woni Й“adiiЙ—o fotde laanye Й—iЙ—e wolla ko Й“uri Й“adaade
  53,10,O wahyii e maccuЙ—o makko ko O wahyii ko
  53,11,Й“ernde mum fennaani ko o yi*i ko
  53,12,mbela haЙ—a yeddandira e Mum ko O yi*i
  53,13,Ko noon tigi o yi*ii Jibriir laawol goЙ—ngol
  53,14,ka lekki sidar njani sanne
  53,15,ka kiin lekki woni aljanna koЙ—irЙ—o
  53,16,Nde muurata e lekki sidra-he ko naatata
  53,17,Yitere oonГұaaki nde yawtaani keerol
  53,18,Ko goonga o yi*ii e kaawsaaji Alla Й“urЙ—i mawnude
  53,19,Onon heeferЙ“e mbela on nji*ii laata e ujjaa
  53,20,E manaata tataЙ“iija goЙ—Й—o o
  53,21,Mbela na woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo
  53,22,Й—uum de wadde ko feccoore nde nuunЙ—aani
  53,23,Й—i ngonah si wonah inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil Й“e ndewaani si wonah sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e maЙ“Й“e ummaade to Joom mum en
  53,24,wolla mbela na woodani neЙ—Й—o ko o wooЙ—a ko
  53,25,Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii
  53,26,Heewii e malaykaaji e nder kammuuji Й—i tefoore majji nafatah huunde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonande mbo O wela O
  53,27,Pellet Й“een Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani laakira hoЙ“e innira malaykaaji inЙ—e rewЙ“e
  53,28,"Woodanaani Й“e ganndal, alah kove ndewata si wonah sikke, pellet sikke nafatah e goonga hay huunde"
  53,29,Й—uurno oon nduntiiЙ—a jikru amen mbo yiЙ—ah si wonah nguurndam aduna
  53,30,"Ko Й—oon ganndal mum en haaЙ—i, pellet ko Alla Й“uri anndude oon majjuЙ—o laawol Makko, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri anndude oon peewЙ—o"
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yoЙ“a Й“een bonnuЙ“e koЙ“e mbonni ko, O yoЙ“a kadi moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi"
  53,32,"Й“en woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare [Й“e faggitotaako] si wanaa tokoosi Й—in. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaajuЙ—o yaafuyee. Ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on gila O fuЙ—Й—unoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde wonunoЙ—on fuЖҙЖҙannde ka deedi neeniraaЙ“e mon. Wata on mantu ko'e mon; ko Kanko Й“uri anndude gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  53,33,E a tinaali Й—uurniiЙ—o on
  53,34,"hino okka seeЙ—aa, hooti o Й—awa"
  53,35,Kere o jogi ganndal wirniiЙ—i ngal o yiirata
  53,36,Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e Й—eri Muusa Й—in
  53,37,"e [ka Й—eri] Ibraahiima hunnuЙ—o [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"wonnde wonkii [woo] ronndotaako doЕӢgal (bakkaatu) wokkii goo"
  53,39,"e wonnde alanaa neЙ—Й—anke, si wonaa ko o golli kon"
  53,40,"e wonnde golle makko Й—en, aray ka yi'ee"
  53,41,refti o yoЙ“iree Й—e njoЙ“di timmundi
  53,42,e wonnde ko ka Joomi maa woni haattirde nden
  53,43,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Weltinoowo Wullina
  53,44,ko Kanko kadi woni Warooro Wuurnita
  53,45,"e wonnde O tagii resindirayЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i : gorel e deyel"
  53,46,immorde e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu si rufaama
  53,47,e wonnde ko Kanko woodani tagitugol Й—immun
  53,48,e wonnde ko Kanko woni alЙ—inЙ—o e okkЙ—uЙ—o
  53,49,e wonnde ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o hoodere Si'ira nden
  53,50,e wonnde ko Kanko halki Aadi'en adinooЙ“e
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, O heddinaano hay e gooto"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en ko adii[Й“e], pellet, Й“en laatino Й“urЙ“e tooГұude e bewde"
  53,53,e yimЙ“e fitaare Й“en (Й“e) O waylitunoo
  53,54,O hippiri Й—e kon ko O hippiri
  53,55,Ko honЙ—um e neemaaji Joomi ma Й—in sikkitotoЙ—aa
  53,56,Awa oo ko jertinoowo jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e adinooЙ“e
  53,57,Darngal ngal non Й“adike
  53,58,"DuГұoowo ngal ko woori Allah, alaa"
  53,59,"E ko ndee yewtere [Alqur'aana] haawetoЙ—on"
  53,60,"HiЙ—on jala, on wullataa"
  53,61,Hara ko on welsindiiЙ“e
  53,62,"Koni sujjanee Allah, rewon [Mo]"
  54,1,"Darngal ngal Й“adike, lewru ndun kadi seekike"
  54,2,"Si Й“e yi'ii maande, Й“e Й—uurnoo Й“e wi'a: \"Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"
  54,3,"ЖҒe fenni, Й“e jokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Hara le huunde kala no mari ГұiiЙ“irde"
  54,4,"GomЙ—ii kumpite arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e haЙ—itorЙ—um woni e mun"
  54,5,"[ЖҠum] ko ГұeГұЖҙal yottiingal. Kono jertingol ngol nafaali"
  54,6,Selu Й“e. Г‘alnde noddoowo on noddoyta e huunde aГұiniinde
  54,7,"jaasuЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, hiЙ“e yaltira e genaale Й—en wano kanuuji caratooЙ—i"
  54,8,"heГұaniiЙ“e noddoowo on. HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Ndee ko Гұalaande sattunde"
  54,9,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e nuuhu Й“en yedduno. ЖҒe fenni jeyaaЙ—o Amen on, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko jinnaaЙ—o!\", o kammbanaa"
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Min on ko mi foolaaЙ—o, faabo [lam]"
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbuЙ—e kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam"
  54,12,Men fuccitiri leydi ndin Й“ulli. Ndiye Й—en fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde
  54,13,"Men roondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peЕӢe"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka Amen. ЖҠum ko njoЙ“di [Nuuhu] fennanooЙ—o on. @Corrected"
  54,15,"GomЙ—ii Men accirii [kon ko Men waЙ—i Й“e] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi waajitorayЙ—o"
  54,16,Taskii ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,17,GomЙ—ii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorЙ—o
  54,18,Aadi'en fennuno. Taskee ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,19,"Men wurtu e maЙ“Й“e henndu sattundu, e Гұalaande hiitaande, duumiinde"
  54,20,"hindu wippitira yimЙ“e Й“en, wa si tawii ko Й“e daЖҙЖҙe tamaro irtaaЙ—e"
  54,21,Taskee ko honno lepte Am Й—en e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,22,GomЙ—ii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorЙ—o
  54,23,Samuuda'en fennuno waaju ngun
  54,24,"Й“e wi'i: \"Kere ko neЙ—Й—o gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Haray men wonii ontuma e nder majjere e tamperere"
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jantoore nden werlaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitiiЙ—o"
  54,26,"Aray Й“e annda (Г‘alnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitiiЙ—o on"
  54,27,"Ko Men wurtirooЙ“e ngelooba ndewa mbam, jarribagol Й“e. Aynitu Й“e, muГұГұoЙ—aa"
  54,28,"Humpitu Й“e wonnde ndiyam Й—am ko sennndaaЙ—am hakkunde maЙ“Й“e [e ngelooba mbam]; kala yaray geЙ“al mun"
  54,29,"ЖҒe noddi wonndiiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [mba]"
  54,30,Teskii ko honno lepte Am Й—en e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wa'i wa ledde yooruЙ—e muncaaЙ—e"
  54,32,GomЙ—ii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorЙ—o
  54,33,YimЙ“e Luutu Й“en fennuno jertine Й—en
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaaЖҙe e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa e Й“eynguure Luutu nden, Men daЙ—ndirno Й“en ka wenndo"
  54,35,"moЖҙЖҙere immorde e Amen. Ko non Men yoЙ“itirta kala yettuЙ—o [neema Allah on]"
  54,36,GomЙ—ii le o jertinirno Й“e nanngal Amen cattungal ngal. Kono Й“e sikkitii jertinol ngol
  54,37,"GomЙ—ii Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“irno mo [bonidugol e hoЙ—Й“e makko Й“en]. Men mehi gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en. \"MeeЙ—ee lepte Й—en e jertinol Am ngol"
  54,38,"GomЙ—ii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumiiЙ—e dawirani Й“e"
  54,39,MeeЙ—ee lepte e jertinol Am
  54,40,GomЙ—ii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorЙ—o
  54,41,GomЙ—ii jertinaango ngon arii e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en
  54,42,"ЖҒe fenni Aayeeje Amen Й—en fow. Men nanngiri Й“e, nanngal FooluЙ—o HattanЙ—o"
  54,43,Kere ko heeferЙ“e mon Й“en Й“uri Й“eya moЖҙЖҙude? Kaa ko daЙ—ugol woodani on ka ЖҠeri
  54,44,"Kaa hara Й“e wi'ay : \"Menen ko men dental wallindirooЙ“e"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [maЙ“Й“e] ngal foolee, Й“e runntina Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e"
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal woni kammbaa maЙ“Й“e on, Ko Darngal non Й“uri mawnude e haaЙ—ude"
  54,47,"Pellet, bomЙ“e Й“en wonii e majjere e ooyunge"
  54,48,"Г‘alnde Й“e daasiroytee geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka nder Yiite, (Й“e wi'anee): \"MeeЙ—ee meemugol Saqara"
  54,49,Menen Men tagir huunde kala e eЙ“Й“oore
  54,50,"Yamiroore Amen wonaali, si wanaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hinЖҙaango yiitere"
  54,51,GomЙ—ii Men halkiino yeradiiЙ“e mon. Hara wooday waajitorayЙ—o
  54,52,Kala huunde nde Й“e golli no ka nder Й—eri
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko winndaaЙ—um"
  54,54,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e Aljannaaji e canЙ—i"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka LaamЙ—o HattanЙ—o"
  55,1,Jom HinaraЕӢke On
  55,2,O anndinii Alqur'aana
  55,3,O tagi neЙ—Й—aЕӢke
  55,4,O anndini mo Й“anngingol
  55,5,"Naange ngen e lewru ndun [hino dogira] limoore"
  55,6,"koode Й—en kadi e leЙ—Й—e Й—en, hino sujjude"
  55,7,"Kammu ngun, O toownu ngu. O waЙ—i nunЙ—al ngal"
  55,8,fii wata on bewu ka peesirЙ—e
  55,9,Г‘inniron etugol ngol no nunЙ—iri. Wata on Й—uytu peesirЙ—e Й—en
  55,10,"Leydi ndin, O waЙ—anndi tagoore nden"
  55,11,"muuyanteeЙ—i hino e mayri, e leЙ—Й—e tamaro marЙ—e poЖҙЖҙi"
  55,12,"e gabbe marЙ—e Гұaande, e uurngol"
  55,13,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in woni ko fennoton
  55,14,"O tagiri neЙ—Й—o on immorde e loopal, wa'ungal wa ko juЙ—aa"
