  55,17,JeyЙ—o fuЙ—irЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i Jeyi kadi mutirЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i
  55,18,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,19,"O Tuppindiri maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i, hiЙ—e fotta"
  55,20,"heedo hino hakkunde majje, Й—e jillondirtaa"
  55,21,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,22,"Hino yalta e Й—en [maaje] Й—iЙ—i: kaЕӢЕӢe \"Lu'lu'u\" e \"Marjaan"
  55,23,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,24,"Ko Kanko woodani dogooje lesaaЙ—e ka nder maayo, wa'uЙ—e wa pelle"
  55,25,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,26,Kala ko woni e hoore mayri ko ko re'ata
  55,27,"heddoo Jaati Joomi maa Kin, Jom mawngu e teddungal. @Corrected"
  55,28,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,29,"ЖҒen wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino naamnoo Mo. Г‘alnde woo, Himo e fiyaaku"
  55,30,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,31,"Aray nde Men faandii hasbude on, onon yo tedda ko'e en Й—iЙ—o"
  55,32,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,33,"Ko onon yo dental jinna e yimЙ“e ! Si on hattanii wuЙ—Й—irgol ka seraaji kammuuli e ka leydi, haray wuЙ—Й—ee. On wuЙ—Й—irtaa si wanaa e doole"
  55,34,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,35,"Hino wurtee e mon - [onon jinna e yimЙ“e] - Й—emngal yiite e curki [maa sila taayuЙ—o], on faabondirtaa"
  55,36,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,37,"Si wonii kammu ngun seekike, ngu wojjirii wa piindi hono pentiir boЙ—e"
  55,38,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,39,"Nden Гұalnde, wanaa neЙ—Й—o maa jinne woni ko lanmditetee fii junuubi mun"
  55,40,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,41,BomЙ“e Й“en hino annditiree maandeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. ЖҒe nanngiroyee ka njubuuji-tin tinЙ—i- e ka koyЙ—e
  55,42,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in woni ko fennoton
  55,43,Ko ngee woni Jahannama nge bomЙ“e Й“en fennaynoo fii mun
  55,44,HiЙ“e wanngoo hakkunde magge e fatayЙ—am hattuЙ—am wulde
  55,45,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,46,"Hino woodani kala hulЙ—o daragol yeeso Joomi mun, aljannaaji Й—iЙ—i"
  55,47,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,48,marЙ—e calЙ—i Й—iЙ—i dukke
  55,49,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,50,"ЖҒulli Й—iЙ—i hino e nder majji, ilayЙ—i. @Corrected"
  55,51,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,52,"Hino e nder majji kala muuyanteeЙ—i Й—in, noone Й—iЙ—i"
  55,53,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,54,"Hara ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e e ndaЙ—Й—ule tekkirЙ—e nder, dimЙ—e majje Й—en Й—iЙ—i ko Й“adiiЙ—e"
  55,55,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,56,"(RewЙ“e) raЙ“Й“iЙ—a ndaarЙ—eЙ“e hino toon, Й“e neЙ—Й—o memaali ado maЙ“Й“e wanaa kadi jinna"
  55,57,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,58,"[LabiraaЙ“e] wa kaЕӢЕӢe yaaquutu e marjaan"
  55,59,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,60,"Hara njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙere no woodi, si wanaa moЖҙЖҙere"
  55,61,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,62,"Hino gaanin Й—in Й—iЙ—i, aljannaaji Й—iЙ—i kadi"
  55,63,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,64,hecciЙ—uЙ—i Й—iЙ—i
  55,65,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,66,"ЖҒulli Й—iЙ—i hino e nder majji, Й“ulayЙ—i"
  55,67,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,68,"Hino e majji : muuyanteeЙ—i, e leЙ—Й—e tamaro e rummaana"
  55,69,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,70,"Hino e Й—in Й—iЙ—i : rewЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e labaaЙ“e"
