  55,75,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,76,"Ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indotooЙ“e e hoore ngawluuji haakooji, e ndaЙ—Й—ule abqari labaaЙ—e"
  55,77,E ko honЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in yeddoton
  55,78,"Barkinii Innde Joomi maa nden, Jom Mawngu e Teddungal"
  56,1,Si darotoongal ngal darike
