  56,24,njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo kon
  56,25,"ЖҒe nanataa nder ton haala meere, wanaa ko bakkondiЕӢta"
  56,26,"si wanaa wi'aneede : \"Salaaman! Salaaman!\" [SaЙ—i mon! saЙ—i mon]"
  56,27,"E wontirooЙ“e Гұaamo Й“en, ko woni Й“en yimЙ“e Гұaamo"
