  56,31,e ndiyam juurayЙ—am
  56,32,e Й“iЙ—Й“e leЙ—Й—e Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e
  56,33,Й—e taЖҙondirtaa Й—e haЙ—etaake
  56,34,e danЙ—e Й“amtaaЙ—e
  56,35,Ko Menen tagi fuЙ—Й—i Й“e
  56,36,Men waЙ—i Й“e curbaaЙ“e-boomi
  56,37,"yiЙ—uЙ“e worЙ“e mun, goreeЙ“e"
  56,38,"[Men marani Й“e] yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“en"
  56,39,"Dental jeyaaЙ“e e [mofte] adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  56,40,"e seeЙ—aaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e [mofte] sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  56,41,E wontirooЙ“e nano Й“en. Ko homЙ“e woni Й“en yimЙ“e nano
  56,42,"[ЖҒen] no e nguleendi e fatayЙ—am"
  56,43,e Й—owdi curki Й“awluki
  56,44,"wonaa Й“uuЙ“undi, wanaa teddundi"
