  56,46,Й“e laatino hiЙ“e deppitoo e bakkaat mawЙ—i Й—in
  56,47,"hiЙ“e wi'aynoo: \"Enee, si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, hara ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  56,48,hay baabiraaЙ“e amen adinooЙ“e Й“en
  56,49,"Maaku : \"Pellet, aramЙ“e e sakkitiiЙ“e"
