  56,64,Ko onon fuЙ—inta Й—um? Kaa ko Menen woni fuЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno, pellet, Men waЙ—ayno ndu foron. Wattinon hiЙ—on haawoo [wi'a]"
  56,66,Menen ko men lepteteeЙ“e perte ko min nafqi ko
  56,67,wurin ko men haЙ—aaЙ“e
  56,68,On yi'ii ndiyam Й—am yaroton Й—am
  56,69,"E ko onon jippiniri Й—am ka duule? Kaa ko Menen jippini [Й—am]"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno, Men waЙ—ayno Й—am kaaЙ—Й—am. Ko haЙ—i yetton [Allah]"
  56,71,On yi'ii yiite nge huЙ“Й“oton ngen
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini waЙ—i leЙ—Й—e mum? Kaa ko Menen woodini [Й—e]"
  56,73,"Men waЙ—ir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotooЙ“e"
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, MawЙ—o On"
  56,75,Mi woondirii mutirЙ—e koode Й—en
  56,76,"Pellet, Й—um ko woondoore mawnde, si hiЙ—on anndunoo"
  56,77,Pellet ndee ko Alqur'aanaare konde teddunde
  56,78,wonnde e deftere reenaande
  56,79,meemataa nden si wanaa laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en
  56,80,ko jippiniraande ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden
  56,81,E ko ndee yewtere wonki ko pennoton onon
  56,82,"HiЙ—on waЙ—a arsike mon (toЙ“o ngon) ko on fennooЙ“e [arsikuЙ—o On]"
  56,83,Ko haЙ—ata nde wonkii yottii ka lookoЖҙere
  56,84,hara onon hiЙ—on ndaara ontuma
  56,85,"hara non ko Menen Й“uri on Й“adaade mo, kono on yi'ataa"
  56,86,"Ko haЙ—ata on, si tawiino hara on warjetaake"
  56,87,"rutton kin [wonkii], si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  56,88,Si tawii on ko jeyaaЙ—o e Й“attinaaЙ“e Й“en
  56,89,"haray ko fowtere, e moЖҙЖҙere, e Aljannaaji neema (woodani mo)"
  56,90,Si tawii kadi ko jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“en
  56,91,"haray [o jaЙ“Й“oroyte] : \"Kisal maa\" e Й“aЕӢge yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“en"
  56,92,Si tawii non ko jeyanooЙ—o e fennuЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“en
  56,93,haray hoЙ—torde makko on ko fatayЙ—am
  56,94,e sumeede Jahiimi
  56,95,"Pellet, ko Й—um woni goonga yananaaЙ—o on"
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, MawЙ—o On"
  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  57,2,"Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, Kanko ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  57,3,"Ko Kanko woni Arano e SakkitiiЙ—o, FeeГұuЙ—o e WirniiЙ—o, Kanko ko O annduЙ—o kala huunde"
  57,4,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arsi\"; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko Жҙawata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko Жҙawata e maggu. Himo wonndi e mon kala ka wonЙ—on. Allah no reeni ko golloton kon. @Corrected"
  57,5,Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji Й—in ruttirtee
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e nder Гұalorma on, O naadira Гұalorma on kadi e nder jemma on. Kanko ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e nder Й“erЙ—e"
  57,7,"GomЙ—inee Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, nafqon kon ko O waЙ—iri on lomtinaaЙ“e e mun. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e mon, Й“e nafqi [jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en], hino woodani Й“en njoЙ“di mawnundi"
  57,8,"E ko heЙ“i on, on gomЙ—intaa Allah? E hino NulaaЙ—o on hino nodda on e gomЙ—ingol Joomi mon. GomЙ—ii [Allah] Жҙettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  57,9,"Ko Kanko jippinta e jeyaaЙ—o Makko on Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, fii no o yaltinira on e niЙ“e faade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko Yuminoowo on, HinnotooЙ—o"
  57,10,"E ko heЙ“i on, on sakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, Й“en sakkinooЙ“e ado uddital ngal Й“e haЙ“idaa; ko Й“en Й“uri mawnude darja e dii Й“en sakkiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й—um Й“e haЙ“idaa. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e non, Allah fodii Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Allah no humpitii ko golloton kon"
  57,11,"Ko hommbo Гұawlirta Allah Гұamaande labaande, O sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njoЙ“di teddundi"
  57,12,"Г‘alnde yi'oytaa gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, hara annoora maЙ“Й“e yaara yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Гұaamo maЙ“Й“e (Й“e wi'anee): \"Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley mun, ko on duumotooЙ“e nder ton\". Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal ngal"
  57,13,"Г‘alnde naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en wi'anoyta gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". ЖҒe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree Й“aawo mon, Й—aЙ“Й“oyon annoora\". Heedo waЙ—ee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, Й“aawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"
  57,14,"HiЙ“e nodda Й“e : \"E men wondaano e mon?\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitaniЙ—on [gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en bone], sikkitiЙ—on, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e moЖҙЖҙere Allah nden"
  57,15,"Hannde on, on jaЙ“antaake soktorЙ—um wanaa e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hannduЙ—on. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  57,16,"E yontaani gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en nde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en deeЖҙirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara Й“e wa'aali wa Й“en okkanooЙ“e Defte Й“en ko adii, dumunna on juutani Й“en, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yoori, ko Й—uuЙ—unoo e maЙ“Й“e kon ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorii. GomЙ—ii Men Й“annginiranii on Aayeeje Й—en, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotooЙ“e (jawle mun Й“en) ka worЙ“e e ka rewЙ“e Й“e Гұawli Allah Гұamaande labaande, Й“e sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  57,19,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, ko Й“en woni goongiyaЕӢke en. SahodinЙ“e Й“en ka Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“en njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e e annoora maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen non yedduЙ“e Й“e fenni Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Jahiimi ngen"
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna Й—am ko fijindaaru, e mbeleeЙ—e, e cuЙ—aari, e Й“urondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e Й“iЙ—Й“e. Wano toЙ“o haawnungo remooЙ“e Й“en puЙ—i mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soyЙ—i; refti ngo wonta munciiЙ—um. Hino ka laakara, lette saЙ—tuЙ—e, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna Й—am wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"
  57,21,"Adondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. ЖҠum ko Й“ural Allah ngal O okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawnungal"
  57,22,"Bone woo heЙ“ataa [on] e leydi ndin maa e pittaali mon Й—in, si wanaa Й—um woniino e deftere ado Men tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, Й—um ko ko newanii Allah"
  57,23,"Ko fii wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, wanaa kadi weltorgol ko O okki on kon. Allah yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙoowo, mantiiЙ—o"
  57,24,"ЖҒen wuddooЙ“e Й“e yamira yimЙ“e Й“en nguddam... kala Й—uurniiЙ—o, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  57,25,"GomЙ—ii Men nulirii NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en Й“anngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani Й“e Defte e sariyaare, fii no yimЙ“e Й“en ГұiiЙ“ira e nunЙ—al. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tiiЙ—uЙ—e woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, e no Allah feГұГұinira Й“en wallooЙ“e Mo e NulaaЙ—o Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, FooluЙ—o. @Corrected"
  57,26,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Men waЙ—i e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol Annabaaku e Defte. Hino e maЙ“Й“e feewuЙ“e, ko Й—uuЙ—i kon e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkindini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, NulaaЙ“e Amen [goo], Men jokkintiniri [Й“e] Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men waЙ—i e Й“erЙ—e jokkuЙ“e mo Й“en : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal Й“e sinci ngal, Menen Men waЙ—Й—inaa ngal e maЙ“Й“e. [Men lamndaaki] si wanaa Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Allah. Kono Й“e ayniraali Й—um no haani aynireede. Men okki njoЙ“di gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—uuЙ—unoo kon e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e! Hulee Allah, gomЙ—inon NulaaЙ—o Makko on; O yeЙ—ay on geЙ—e Й—iЙ—i e mbarjaari Makko ndin, O waЙ—ana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  57,29,"Fii no yimЙ“e Defte Й“en anndira wonnde Й“e hattanaa hay huunde e Й“ural Allah ngal, e wonnde Й“ural ngal ko e juuЙ—e Allah woni; Himo yeЙ—a ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawngal"
  58,1,Ko goonga Alla nani konngol oon duttondiroowo e ma haala ko faati e jom galle makko hombo wullito faade e Alla; Alla na nana yeewtere mon nde pellet Alla ko nanoowo ji*oowo
  58,2,"Й“een nanndinooЙ“e suddiiЙ“e mum en e yummiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, Й“een Й“e ngonah yummiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“Жҙe, woni yummiraaЙ“e mum en ko Й“een jibinЙ“e Й“e pellet hoЙ“e haala pankare e fenaande e pellet Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jarlotooЙ—o bakkatuuji"
  58,3,"Й“een nanndinooЙ“e rewЙ“e mum en refti Й“e ndutto ko Й“e mbiino ko yoЙ“e ndimЙ—in daande ko adi ndeЙ“e memandirta ko Й—um woni ko mbaajete Й—on ko, Alla na humpati ko ngollaton ko"
  58,4,"Kala mbo daГұaani yo o hoor lebbi Й—iЙ—i dewandirЙ—i ko adii ndeЙ“e mandirta kala mbo hattanaani yo o Гұammin miskineeЙ“e capanЙ—e njeegom, Й—uum ko ngam ngoonЙ—inon Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko ko Й—uum woni keerol Alla woodanii heeferЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e"
  58,5,"Pellet Й“een luundotooЙ“e Alla e NelaaЙ—o Makko Й“e hoynaama hono no adiiЙ“e Й“e koynirano, Min tellinii aayeeje peeГұЙ—e, woodani heeferЙ“e lepte koynooje"
  58,6,"Г‘ande O ummini Й“e kamЙ—e fof O holla Й“e koЙ“e golluno ko, O tonngii Й—uum Й“e njejji Й—um Alla na seedii kala huunde"
  58,7,"Mbela a anndah wonde Alla na anndi ko woni e nder kammuuli e ko woni e nder leydi, gunndo wonatah hakkunde tata si wonah O nayЙ“itaЙ“e ngo wonatah hakkunde noyo si wonah O wona jeegoЙ“o ngo wonatah ko jaasi Й—uum si wonah O wonda e mum en toЙ“e mbaawi wonde fof, refti O habraЙ“e ko Й“e golli Гұande darnga, pellet Alla na anndi kala huunde"
  58,8,"Mbela a yiyaani Й“een haЙ—aaЙ“e ndeeyu refti Й“e nduttoo koЙ“e kada ko Й“e ndeeyandira e bakkatuuji e aГұanaagal e woopde nelaaЙ—o, siЙ“i ngarii e ma Й“e calmanir ma na Alla salminiraani ma nih Й“e wiya e pittaali mum en ko haЙ—i Alla leptira min ko min kaalata ko, yoniiЙ“e jahannama hoЙ“e naatne heen bonii wattannde"
  58,9,"Eehey mon gooЙ—inЙ“e si on ndeeydii e nelaaЙ—o wotee ndeeyde e makko e bakkaat e aГұanaagal e woopde nelaaЙ—o, ndeeydee e Й—iggere e kulol Alla Mbo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on to Makko"
  58,10,"Pellet gunndo ko e seytaane ngam o sunina Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e o lorotaaЙ“e hay ndiga si wonah e sakkitoore Alla, e dow Alla woni ko goonЙ—iЙ“e wakkilto"
  58,11,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si on wiyaama yaacne e jolle yaacne Alla yaajnana mon, si on wiyaama umme, ummЙ—on Alla Й“amta Й“een goonЙ—in Й“e e mon e joman en ganndal darajaaji, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,12,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si on ndeeydii e nelaaЙ—o tottire e ndeeyu mon sadak, ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mon ko Й—uum Й“uri laaЙ“de, si on keЙ“aani Alla de ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  58,13,"Mbela on kul tottirde sadaka saanga ndeeydaton e nelaaЙ—o, si on tottiraani Alla jaЙ“ani on tuubuubuya, ndarnee juulde toottiron askal Й—oftoЙ—on Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,14,"Mbela a yi*aani Й“een heedninЙ“e aade en Й“e Alla tikkani Й“e njeyaaka e mon Й“e njeyaako e maЙ“Й“e, hoЙ“e ngoondira penaale te hoЙ“e nganndi"
  58,15,Alla heblaniiЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e pellet bonii koЙ“e golluno ko
  58,16,"Й“e nanngarii goondooje mum en Й—e heedo, Й“e palii laawol Alla ngol, woodaniiЙ“e lepte koynooje"
  58,17,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en duncantaaЙ“e e lepte Alla Й—en hay huunde. Ko Й“een Й—on woni yimЙ“e yiite Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton"
  58,18,"Г‘ande Alla umminiЙ“e kamЙ“e fof, Й“e ngoondana Mbo hono noЙ“e woondaranta mon nih, hoЙ“e sikka won koЙ“e ngoni e dow mum, Й“e tigi ngoni fenooЙ“e Й“e"
  58,19,"Seytaane tehriiЙ“e o yejjitini Й“e jantaade Alla ko Й“ee tigi ngoni fedde seytaane, pellet ko fedde seytaane woni pertuЙ“e"
  58,20,"Й“een haЙ“atooЙ“e Alla e nelaaЙ—o Makko,ko Й“een Й“uri hoyde"
  58,21,"Alla Гұaawi ma Mi fool Miin e nelaaЙ“e am, pellet Alla ko cemmbuЙ—o tedduЙ—o"
  58,22,"A heЙ“atah yimЙ“e goonЙ—inЙ“e e Гұalawma cakkatiiЙ—o na njiЙ—andira e luundiiЙ“e Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko haysi Й“e ngonii baabiraaЙ“e mum en wolla Й“iЙ“Й“e wolla musiЙ“Й“e, wolla gorol mum en, ko Й“e Й“erЙ—e mum en mbinnda iimaan O semmbiniЙ“e e ruuhu ummade e Makko, O naatnaЙ“e aljannaaji na dogo ley majji caatli Й“e duumo toon haa pooma, Alla weleeЙ“e Й“e mbele Alla, ko Й“een ngoni fedde Alla, ko fedde Alla tigi woni malaaЙ“e. @Corrected"
  59,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  59,2,"Ko kanko yaltini Й“een heefeeeЙ“e jom en defte en e galleeji mum en e mooЙ“du adanuru ndu, on cikkaana maЙ“e njaltu, Й“e cikki galli mum en Й—i ndeenatЙ“e e Alla, O ardiЙ“e Й—oЙ“e cikkaana, O werlii e Й“erЙ—e mum en kulol, hoЙ“e njirbinira galleeji maЙ“Й“e juuЙ—e mum en e juuЙ—e goonЙ—inЙ“e, teskee onon joman en hakkillaaji"
  59,3,Si Alla farlaana e mum en yaltineede ma O leptuЙ“e e aduna woodanaЙ“e lepte yiite
  59,4,"ЖҠum, ko fii kamЙ“e Й“e lunndike Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. \"Kala non lunndiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, pellet, Alla ko CaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  59,5,"Kala ko taЖҙЙ—on e tamaroowi wolla accuЙ—onki hoki dari e pooЙ“e makki, ko e yamiroore Alla ngam O hoyna faasiqeeЙ“e"
  59,6,"Ko Alla rutti faade e nelaaЙ—o Makko ummaade e mum en, on keГұaraaki e mum pucci wolla geloobi, kono Alla na wuurta nelaaЙ“e makko e dow mbo o wela, Alla na hattani kala huunde"
  59,7,"Ko Alla neemini e nelaaЙ—o Mum e yimЙ“e gure dow, na woodani Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko e Й“adiiЙ“e nelaado e alyatitm en e miskineeЙ“e e Й“iy laawol ngam Й—um waasa yiilaade hakkunde alЙ—uЙ“e mon, ko nelaaЙ—o totti on Й“ame ko o haЙ—i on ngacce, ndeene Alla, pellet Alla ko cattuЙ—o lepte"
  59,8,"Woodani waasЙ—e yaltinaaЙ“e galleeji mum en e jawЙ—eele mum en hoЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Й“ural ummaade e Alla e weluya hoЙ“e mballa Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko, ko Й“een de ngoni goonЙ—uЙ“e tigi"
  59,9,"E Й“een telliiЙ“e e madiina e iimaan ko adii Й“e, hoЙ“e njiЙ—i oon perЙ—o faade e maЙ“Й“e Й“e keЙ“atah e Й“erЙ—e mum en tikkere koЙ“e totta ko, hoЙ“e Й“urna e dow ko*e mum en haysi hoЙ“e wondi e baasal, kala mbo Alla reeni fittaandu mum e Й—awre, ko Й“een de ngoni malaaЙ“e"
  59,10,"E Й“een arЙ“e caggal mum en na mbi*a joomo amen yaafa amen minen e musiЙ“Й“e amen adiiЙ“e amen e iimaan wotah waЙ— e Й“erЙ—e amen cokotaagal wonande Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e,joomi amen ko Aan woni enЙ—iiЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  59,11,"Mbela a yi*aani Й“een naafaqinЙ“e wiiЙ“e musibbe mum en yedduЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e defte, si on yaltii pellet ma min yaltid e mon, min Й—ototaako e dow mon hay gooto, si on kaЙ“aama ma min mballu mon Alla na seedo koЙ“e fenooЙ“e"
  59,12,SiЙ“e yaltinaama Й“e yaltidtah e mum en si Й“e kaЙ“aama Й“e wallataa Й“e siЙ“e walliiЙ“e maЙ“e runta refti Й“e walletaake
  59,13,"Ko onon Й“uri sattu kulo e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e gaa nih e Alla, waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e paamatah"
  59,14,Й“e haЙ“atah e mon si wonah hoЙ“e e gure taartinaaЙ—e galli wolla caggal mahdeele bone maЙ“Й“e hakkunde mum en na satti haЙ—a sikka koЙ“e gootum kono Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e na ceerti waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e kakkiltah
  59,15,Hona yeru Й“een adiiЙ“e Й“e ko Й“adii Й“e meeЙ—i lepte fiyaaku mum en woodaniiЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e
  59,16,"Ko hono seytaane nde wi*i neЙ—Й—anke o yeddu, nde o yeddi o wi*i miin komi kisЙ—o e ma, miin mbeЙ—o huli Alla jom binnde O"
  59,17,"Laati batte mum en kanЙ“e Й—iЙ—a ko yiite saasooЙ“e toon, Й—uum ko njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e"
  59,18,"Eehey mon goonЙ—ibe ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule Alla pellet Alla ko kumpatiiЙ—o ko ngolloton ko"
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono Й“een yejjitЙ“e Alla, O yejjitini Й“e pittaali mum en ko Й“een ngoni faasiqeeЙ“e"
  59,20,"YimЙ“e yiite e yimЙ“e aljanna potatah, ko yimЙ“e aljanna ngoni foolЙ“e"
  59,21,Si min tellinna o quraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde huli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla Й—i tinndi emin piyaniЙ—i yimЙ“e ko ngam Й“e miijo
  59,22,"Ko kanko woni deweteeЙ—o deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah kanko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kank woni jom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde"
  59,23,Ko kanko Alla mbo deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah kanko laamЙ—o ceniiЙ—o kisЙ—o goonЙ—iЙ—o kiilndiiЙ—o tedduЙ—o cemmbinЙ—o mawЙ—o senaare woodanii Alla e koЙ“e ndenndinta mbo ko
  59,24,"Ko kanko woni Alla tagЙ—o gootnuЙ—o mbaadinЙ—o tagu woodanii mbo inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude, woodanii mbo ko woni e nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni pooloowo mbo hay gooto foolatah Г‘eeГұЖҙuЙ—o"
  60,1,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e wote njaggire aГұЙ“e Mi e aГұЙ“e mon heetЙ“e hoЙ—on mberlo e mum en gilli te koЙ“e yedduЙ“e goongo garЙ—o o e mon, hoЙ“e njaltina nelaaЙ—o e onon sabu tan on ngoonЙ—anii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e Й—aЙ“jude weluya am, hoЙ—on cuurtanaЙ“e kabaruuji juulЙ“e ngam Й“e mbele mon, MbeЙ—a anndi ko cuuЙ—oton e ko Й“anngiЙ—on, kala e mon baЙ—Й—o Й—uum o majji laawol peewngol"
  60,2,SiЙ“e peewnatiima e mon Й“e ngOnana mon aГұЙ“e Й“e mberta juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й—emЙ—e mum en e mbaadi mbonndi Й“e njiЙ—iina nde ngonaton heefereeЙ“e
  60,3,Nafatah on enЙ—ameeje mon wonah Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Гұande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  60,4,"Woodanii on Гұeemtinirde moЖҙЖҙere e Ibraahiima e Й“een wonduЙ“e e mum nde Й“e mbi*i pellet ko min hisЙ“e e mon e ko ndewaton ko wonah Alla ko, min njeddii on feeГұi hakkunde men ngaГұngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngoonЙ—inon Alla gooto O, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima wonande baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay huunde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e Ma ko e Ma min ndutti e ko e Ma woni wattande"
  60,5,"joomi amen wota waЙ— min fitina wonande Й“een yedduЙ“e, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni tedduЙ—o mbo fooletaake ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e maЙ“Й“e Гұeemtanirgal moЖҙЖҙal wonande oon joortiiЙ—o e Alla e Гұalngu laakara, oon Й—uurniiЙ—o noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaaЙ—o"
  60,7,"Yaama nde Alla waЙ—ata hakkunde mon e Й“een Й“e ngaГұandirЙ—on gilli, Alla ko kattanЙ—o Alla ko kafroowo bakkatuuji jurmotooЙ—o"
  60,8,Alla haЙ—ataa mon Й“een Й“e kaЙ“aani e mon e diine Й“e njaltinaani mon e galleeji mon nde Й—iggantonЙ“e nuunЙ—on faade e maЙ“Й“e pellet Alla ko jiЙ—Й—o nuunЙ—uЙ“e
  60,9,"Kono Alla haЙ—ata mon ko Й“een haЙ“atooЙ“e mon e diine yaltinooЙ“e mon galleeji mon Й“e mballandiri e yaltinde mon, nde keetnaton Й“e kala baЙ—Й—o Й“e keeda ko Й“een ngoni tooГұooЙ“e"
  60,10,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si goonЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e ngarii e mon njaribeeЙ“e Alla na anndi iimaan mum en, si on nganndii koЙ“e goonЙ—inЙ“e wotee ndutteeЙ“e e heeferЙ“e Й“e ndaganaaki heeferЙ“e Й“e heeferЙ“e Й“e kadi ndaganaaki Й“e, totteeЙ“e koЙ“e nafqi ko bakkaat alah e mon nde ndesaton Й“e si on tottii Й“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e wote nanngite piЙ“le rewЙ“e heeferЙ“e naamnee ko nafquЙ—on kamЙ“e ne yo Й“e naamna ko Й“e nafqi ko, ko Й—uum woni Гұaawoore Alla hakkunde mon Alla ko gannda ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  60,11,Si huunde faatiima mon e rewЙ“e mon faade e heefereeЙ“e leptuЙ—on Й“e tottee Й“een Й“e rewЙ“e mum en njahi fotde koЙ“e tottirno kulee Alla mbo goonЙ—in Й—on O
  60,12,"Eehey ma annabi si rewЙ“e juulЙ“e ngari e ma hoЙ“e coodandira e ma nde Й“e ndenndintah Alla e hay gooto,ngujjatah, njinatah, mbaratah sukaaЙ“e mum en,ngaddatah fenaande fepindaande hakkunde juuЙ—e mum en e koyЙ—e mum en,Й“e ngoopataa Ma e moЖҙЖҙere ndeen de soodandir e mum en, yaafnanoЙ“e Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  60,13,"Eehey mjon goonЙ—iЙ“e wote keetne yimЙ“e Й“e Alla tikkani e dow mum en, Й“e piЙ“tiima e laakara hono no heeferЙ“e piЙ“tari e yimЙ“e genaale"
  61,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  61,2,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e ko waЙ—i hoЙ—on kaala ko on mbaЙ—atah
  61,3,Mawni tikkere ka Alla nde kaalaton ko on gollatah
  61,4,Pellet Alla na yiЙ—i Й“een haЙ“ateeЙ“e e laawol Alla hoЙ“e ngoni saffeeji hono maadi potndaandi
  61,5,"Tumo nde o maakani yimЙ“e makko, yimЙ“e am holko taki hoЙ—on lora mi te hoЙ—on nganndi komi nelaaЙ—o Alla faade e mon, ndeЙ“e ooГұi Alla ooГұi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Alla feewnatah yimЙ“e faasiqeeЙ“e"
  61,6,"E nde Iisa Й“iy Maryama maaki eehey mon banii Israa*iil komi nelaaЙ—o Alla tigi faade e mon goonЙ—inЙ—o ko woni ko e hakkunde juuЙ—e am Tawreet e beltinoowo nelaaЙ—o garoowo caggal hombo wiyee Ahmadu, nde o anndani Й“e hujjaaji laaЙ“Й—i Й“e mbi*i Й—um ko mbilewu Й“anngungu"
  61,7,"Alah Й“urЙ—a tooГұde oon pepandiiЙ—o e dow Alla te hombo noddee e islaam, Alla feewnatah tooГұooЙ“e"
  61,8,"HoЙ“e faala Гұifrude annoore Alla nde kunduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Alla ko timminoowo annoore makko nde haysi heefereeЙ“e ngaГұii"
  61,9,"Ko Kanko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o Makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o Й“amtu ka e hoore kala diina, hay si sirkooЙ“e Й“en aГұii [Й—um]"
  61,10,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e mbele mi tinndintah on njulaagu ndaЙ—natngu on e lepte muusЙ—e
  61,11,NgoonЙ—inon Alla e nelaaЙ—o Makko mbaЙ—iron jihaadi e laawol makko jawdi mon e pittaali mon ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande si on ngonii annduЙ“e
  61,12,"Alla hafrana on bakkatuuji mon, O naatna on aljannaaji Й—i caatli ndogata ley mum e koЙ—orЙ—e belЙ—e ka aljanna Adan ko Й—uum woni malal manngal. @Corrected"
  61,13,E goЙ—Й—o mbo njiЙ—Й—on ballal ummaade e Alla e uddital Й“adingal weltin juulЙ“e Й“e
  61,14,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e ngonee wallooЙ“e Alla hono no Iisa Ibnu Mariya maaki suЙ“aaЙ“e mum hombo wallata mi faade e Alla suЙ“aaЙ“e mum mbii ko mjinen ngoni wallooЙ“e Alla, heen fedde e Banii Isra*eel goonЙ—ini wonnde nde yeddi Min cemmbini goonЙ—innde nde e dow aГұЙ“e mum en Й“e ngonti foolЙ“e"
  62,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino seninnde Allah, LaamЙ—o, SeniiЙ—o, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  62,2,"Ko kanko nuli e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, himo janngana Й“e Aayeeje Makko Й—en, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e, o anndina Й“e Deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii Й—um, Й“e laatino e majjere Й“anngude"
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e woЙ—Й“e goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hawrondiraali e Й“en taho. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  62,4,"ЖҠum ko Й“ural Allah, Himo okka ngal mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawnngal"
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaaЙ“e Tawreeta Й“en refti Й“e golliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Misal yimЙ“e fennooЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en bonii. Allah fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  62,6,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo HuudiЕӢkooЙ“e ! Si on aaЖҙike wonnde ko on yiЙ—aaЙ“e Allah ko wanaa yimЙ“e heddiiЙ“e Й“en, haray yelee maayde, si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  62,7,"ЖҒe yelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardini kon. Allah ko annduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  62,8,"Maaku: \"Ndee maayde nde dogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti rutteЙ—on ka On annduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, O humpita on ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama Гұalnde Juma, yaccee e jantagol Allah, acciton ngeyngu. Ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si tawno ko on annduЙ“e"
  62,10,"Si julde nden gasii, haray saakitee ka leydi, Й—aЙ“Й“on Й“ural Allah ngal [woni arsike], janntoron innde Allah ko Й—uuЙ—i, belajo'o on maloyte"
  62,11,"Si Й“e yi'ii ngeyngu maa fijindaaru, Й“e hammira ton, Й“e acce hiЙ—a darii. Maaku: \"Ko ko woni ka Allah kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude beleeЙ—e e njulaaku. Ko Allah Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude e arsikooЙ“e Й“en"
  63,1,"Si naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en arii e maa, Й“e wi'a: \"MeЙ—en seedii wonnde ko a NulaaЙ—o Allah\". Allah no anndi wonnde pellet, ko a NulaaЙ—o Makko; Allah no seedii wonnde pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en ko fenooЙ“e"
  63,2,"ЖҒe jogitorri goondooje maЙ“Й“e Й—en heedo, Й“e sakkii laawol Allah ngol. Pellet, fii ko Й“e gollaynoo kon bonii"
  63,3,"ЖҠum non ko tawde Й“e gomЙ—inii, refti Й“e yeddi, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en notaa e mun; kamЙ“e on Й“e faamataa"
  63,4,"Si a yi'ii Й“e, Й“alli maЙ“Й“e welete; si Й“e wowlii, a heЙ—oto konnguЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. HiЙ“e wa'i wa pecce Й“aaraaЙ—e, hiЙ“e sikka kala eewnaango ko e hoore maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“en tigi woni aГұЙ“e Й“en, reenoЙ“e. Allah huЙ—ii Й“e ! Ko honno Й“e yiiltiratool (e goonga)"
  63,5,"Si Й“e wi'anaama: \"Aree NulaaЙ—o Allah on insinanoo on\", Й“e hayla ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yi'aa hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo hara ko Й“e townitiiЙ“e"
  63,6,"Hino fota e maЙ“Й“e, foti a insinani Й“e maa hara a insinanaaki Й“e: Allah yaafotaako Й“e fes, pellet, Allah fewnataa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  63,7,Ko Й“een woni wi*ooЙ“e wote nafqee wonЙ“e e sera NelaaЙ—Г  haa Й“e ceerta na woodani Alla moftirЙ—i kammuuli e leydi kono tan naafiqeeЙ“e Й“e paamatah
  63,8,"HoЙ“e wi*a si en ruttiima Madiina ma Й“urЙ“e teddude yaltin Й“urЙ“e hoyde Й“e, woodanii Alla teddungal e nelaaЙ—o makko e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, kono tan naafige en nganndah"
  63,9,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e woto sokli mon jawle mon e Й“iЙ“Й“e mon gaa e innude Alla kala baЙ—Й—o Й—uum ko Й“een ngoni pertuЙ“e Й“e
  63,10,"Nafqe ko Alla arsakini on ko, ko adii nde maayde arata e gooto e mon o wiya joom am A leelnantaa kam haa e happu Й“adiiЙ—o mi sakkoro mi wona e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  63,11,Alla neemnantah hay fittaandu wooturu si happu manndu arii Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko
  64,1,"Ina subhinanoo Alla kala ko woni e kammuuli e ka leydi, na woodani Mbo laamu na woodani Mbo jettooje ko O kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  64,2,Ko kanko tagi on ina e mon keefeero ina e mon goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  64,3,O tagrii kammuuli e leydi goongo O mbaadini on O moЖҙЖҙini mbaadiili mon ko e Makko woni battane mon
  64,4,Hombo anndi ko woni e kammuuli e leydi hombo anndi ko wirnaton e ko Й“annginton Alla na anndi ko woni e Й“erЙ—e
  64,5,"Mbela araani e mon kabaruuji Й“een yedduЙ“e ko adi,Й“e meeЙ—i lepte fiyakuuji mum en woodaniiЙ“e lepte muusЙ—e"
  64,6,"Woni sabu Й—een lepte noon ko nelaaЙ“e mum en na ngaddanatnoo Й“e dallillaaji Й“annguЙ—i Й“e wi*a ee ko Й“anndiyankooЙ“e peewnata min,Й“e njeddi, Alla yondanii,Alla ko galo jettaaЙ—o"
  64,7,"HeefereЙ“e Й“e aaЖҙiima Й“e ummintaake,maaku oho kay ma on ummine mi woondarii joom am ma on ummine,refti ma on kumpite ko golluuЙ—on, Й—uum na newanii Alla"
  64,8,GoonЙ—inee Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko e annoore nde O tellini pellet Alla ko kumpatiiЙ—o ko golloton ko
  64,9,"Гұande O renndi mon Гұalngu denndingol oon woni Гұalngu basandiral, ka goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla o golli ko lobbi o momtone boneeji mum, O naatna mbo aljanaaji Й—i caatli ndogata les majji Й“e caasa toon haa pooma, ko Й—uum woni malal manngal. @Corrected"
  64,10,"Ko Й“een yedduЙ“e penni aayeeje amen ngoni yimЙ“e yiite saasooЙ“e e henge, nge bonii battane"
  64,11,"Musiiba heЙ“atah hay gooto si wonah e sakkitoore Alla, kala goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla O feewna Й“ernde makko, Alla na anndi kala huunde"
  64,12,"ЖҠoftee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, rentoЙ—on ! Si on huccitii, anndee pellet, ko fawii NulaaЙ—o Amen on tun, ko yottingol Й“anngina"
  64,13,"Allaahu alah deweteeЙ—o e goongo si wonah Kanko, ko e dow makko goonЙ—inЙ“e mbakkilato"
  64,14,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e pellet ina e yogo e suddiiЙ“e mon e Й“iЙ“Й“e mon ko aГұЙ“e mon ndeenteeЙ“e, si on njaafiima on njarliima pellet Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  64,15,"Anndee pellet, jawle mon Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ko fitina ina ka Alla njoЙ“di mawndi"
  64,16,"Kulee Alla ko kattanЙ—on nanee Й—oftaЙ—on nafqe ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙande pittaali mon, oon deenaaЙ—o fittaandu makko e Й—awre, ko Й“een ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“e"
  64,17,"Si on Гұamlii Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere O sowana Й—um en nde, O yaafoЙ“e Alla ko jettoowo ko muГұЙ—o"
  64,18,"AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, MawЙ—o, ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  65,1,"Eehey ma annabi si on ceerii suddiiЙ“e ceereeЙ“e e edda mum en tonnge edda o, kulee Alla joomi mon wotee njaltineeЙ“e e cuuЙ—i mum en wotoЙ“e njaltu si wonah Й“e mbaЙ— pankare peeГұЙ—e ko Й—iin ngoni keeri Alla kala jawtuЙ—o keerol Alla o tooГұi hoore makko, a anndah yaama de Alla waЙ—ata caggal Й—uum fiyaaku"
  65,2,"Si Й“e yottinii edda mum en nanngireeЙ“e no moЖҙЖҙi wollo ceerdonЙ“e no moЖҙЖҙi,ceednon seedeeji Й—iЙ—i ummaade e mon ndarnee seedanfaagal fii Alla ko Й—uum woni ko waajete wonande oon goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalnde sakkatiinde kala deentiiЙ—o Alla,Alla waЙ—ana mbo yaltirde"
  65,3,"O arsikina mbo to o sikkaana, kala bakkaliiЙ—o e Alla yonii mbo, pellet yamiroore Alla nde ko yottotoonde, Alla waЙ—anii kala huunde fotde mum"
  65,4,"Й“een suddiiЙ“e mon fiЙ“tiiЙ“e fiilayru si on cikkatiima edda mum en ko lebbi tati e Й“een Й“e piilataako edda mum en ko lebbi tati, debadeedi en noon edda maЙ“Й“e gasata ko nde Й“e njibini, kala kulЙ—o Alla O waЙ—ana mbo newaare e fiyaaku makko"
  65,5,"Й—uum ko Гұaawoore Alla O tellaniinde e mon, kala kulЙ—o Alla O hafrana mbo bakkatuuji makko, O mawninana mbo njoЙ“di"
  65,6,"KoЙ—neeЙ“e Й—o koЙ—Й—on fotde kattane mon wotee loreeЙ“e ngam Й“ittinandeЙ“e, nafqeeЙ“e haa Й“e keЙ“to tawde koЙ“e korinoo Й“e, si wonii Й“e muyninanii on njonnee Й“e njoЙ“di mum en njandire moЖҙЖҙere hakkunde mon, si on cattiraama yo goЙ—Й—o muynin mbo"
  65,7,"Yo nafqu gala e ngalu makko he, oon paaЙ—aaЙ—o noon yo nafqu e ko Alla totti mbo ko,Alla fawatah hay fittaandu si wonah ko tottindu ko, ma Alla waЙ— caggal satteende newuya"
  65,8,"Heewii saare saliinde yamiroore joom mum e nelaaЙ“o mum, min kaasbii nde haasbo sattungo Min leptinnde lepte bonЙ—e"
  65,9,Nde meeЙ—i lepte golle mayre laati batte fiyaaku mayre ko perte
  65,10,"Alla heblaniЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e kulee Alla onon joman en hakkillaaji Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e, Alla tellinii e mum en ko siftinta"
  65,11,"NelaaЙ—o taratooЙ—o e mon aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e ngam O yaltina Й“een goonЙ—in Й“e golluЙ“e golle lobbe ummaade e niwre faade e annoore, kala goonЙ—inЙ—o Alla golli ko moЖҙЖҙi O naatna mbo aljannaaji Й—i caatli ilata les majji Й“e nduumo toon, ko goongo Alla moЖҙЖҙinanii mbo arsuka. @Corrected"
  65,12,"Alla tagЙ—o kammuuli jeeЙ—iЙ—i e leydi yeru majji, yamiroore Alla na tello hakkunde majji ngam nganndon wonde Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde Alla fiiltariima kala huunde e ganndal"
  66,1,"Eehey ma annabi ko taki ana harmina ko Alla dagnan ma sabu Й—aЙ“Й“ude welnaade suddiiЙ“e ma, Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  66,2,Alla farlii e mon dagtinde goondooje mon Alla ko keedo mon ko kanko woni ganndo Г‘eeГұЖҙudo
  66,3,"Tuma nde annabi deeyi faade e yogo e suddiiЙ“e makko yeewtere, nde o habri yeewtere nde, Alla feГұГұinani mbo O anndini yogo e yeewtere he, O falii heen yogo, nde O habri mbo Й—um o wi*i hombo habru ma Й—um O maaki habrii kam Gannda KumpatiiЙ—o"
  66,4,"Si on tuubi faade e Alla sabu Й“erЙ—e mon Й—e ooГұinooma si on wallandirii e dow makko, ko Alla woni ballo makko e jIbriil e goonЙ—inЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e e Malayka en caggal Й—um koЙ—i ballooji"
  66,5,Yaama de joom makko si O ceeriiЙ“e nde O wostantoo mbo Й“urЙ“e mon moЖҙЖҙude juulЙ“e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й—oftiiЙ“e tuubooЙ“e rewooЙ“e Alla hoorooЙ“e SeemedЙ“e e boomi
  66,6,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e ndeene ko*e mon e koreeji mon e yiite docate mannge ko yimЙ“e e kaaЖҙe ina e dow henge malaykaaji tekkuЙ—i cattuЙ—i Й—i ngoopatah ko Alla yamariЙ—i te hoЙ—i ngolla ko Alla yamiriЙ—i
  66,7,Eehey mon heeferЙ“e wote ngantinee hannde njoЙ“eteЙ—on tan koko ngollatna Й—on
  66,8,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e tuubee faade e Alla tuubgol laaЙ“ngol yaama joomi mon hafrana on bonЙ—i mon O naatna mon aljannaaji na ila ley majji caatli, Гұande Alla hoynatah annabi e Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e wondude e mum, annoore mum en na yaha yeesa mum en e Гұaama mum en hoЙ“e mbiya joomi amen timminan amen annoore amen yaafa min pellet ko a kattanЙ—o kala huunde. @Corrected"
  66,9,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, haЙ“ e heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, saЙ—tinanaa Й“e; weerde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde"
  66,10,"Alla fiyani misal wonande Й“een yedduЙ“e soknaaja Nuuhu e luutu Й“e ngoniina e les jiyaaЙ“e amen Й—iЙ—o moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e njanfiiЙ“e Й—uum nafaaniЙ“e ka Alla hay huunde,Й“e wi*e naatee yiite wondude e naatЙ“e Й“e"
  66,11,"Alla fiyani misal goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e debbo fir*awna nde o wiino joom am mahanam ka Ma suudu ka aljanna ndaЙ—ndaa mi e fir*awna e golle mum, daЙ—ndam e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e"
  66,12,E Maryama Й“iy imraana oon reeni hoore makko e jina Min ngutti heen ruuhu amen o goonЙ—ini konngi joomiiko e defte Makko o tawa e Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“e
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juuЙ—e Mun On mawnii, ko Kanko woni hattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  67,2,"On tagirЙ—o maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude golle. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Haforoowo On"
  67,3,On taguЙ—o kammuuli jeeЙ—iЙ—i fawondirЙ—i. A yi'ataa Й“ura-Й“urda e tagu Jom hinaraЕӢke On. Yiltu ndaarЙ—e maa Й—en (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ceekol
  67,4,"Refti ruttaa ndaarЙ—e Й—en laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i, gite maa Й—en ruttoto e maaЙ—a hara ko Й—e hoyЙ—e, taЖҙiiЙ—e"
  67,5,"GomЙ—ii Men cuЙ—inirii kammu aduna ngun [koode] pitilli, Men waЙ—i Й—e fiЙ—irЙ—e seytanuuji, Men hebilani Й“e lette HuЙ“Й“unge negn"
  67,6,"Hino woodani Й“en yedduЙ“e Joomi mun, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  67,7,"Si Й“e weddaama e nder magge, Й“e naniray nge haacaango, hara hinge fata"
  67,8,"Hinge eЙ“Й“a fultagol, sabu tikkere nden. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaaЙ“e nge Й“en lamndoo Й“e : \"E hara jertinoowo araano e mo'on"
  67,9,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Pellet ! Jertinoowo aruno e amen tigi, kono men fenni men wi'i: Allah jippinaali hay e huunde, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde"
  67,10,"ЖҒe wi'ita : \"Si meЙ—en nanaynoo maa hara meЙ—en haqqilaynoo, men jeyetanooke e yimЙ“e HuЙ“Й“unge ngen"
  67,11,ЖҒe qirritii junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Halakuyee woodanii jom en HuЙ“Й“aynge ngen
  67,12,"Pellet, hulooЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en ka wirnii, hino woodani Й“en haforaneede e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  67,13,SuuЙ—ee konnguЙ—i mon maa Й“anninon Й—um. Kanko On ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e nder Й“erЙ—e
  67,14,"E hara taguЙ—o On anndaa? Ko Kanko le woni NewiiЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o On"
  67,15,"Ko Kanko waЙ—ani on leydi ndin eltaandi : haray yehee e seraaji mayri, Гұaamon e arsike Makko. Ko ka Makko woni ummital ngal"
  67,16,"E on hooli On wonЙ—o ka kammu nde O munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, Tawa yoo hindi dilla? @Corrected"
  67,17,Kaa on hooli On wonЙ—o ka kammu nde O wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon
  67,18,Sellii adinooЙ“e Й“en Й—on Й“en fenniino. Taskii ko honno lette Am Й—en wattinirnoo
  67,19,"E Й“ee yi'aali colli Й—in dow maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ—i fonta gabitannji Й—i Гұobba? [Wonnde] jogitaaki Й—in si wanaa Jom hinaraЕӢke On. Pellet, ko O reenuЙ—o kala huunde"
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wanaa Jom hinaraЕӢke On? Tigi on, heeferЙ“e Й“en wonaali si wanaa e nder hodo"
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si O jogitike arsike Makko on? Si ko woni, Й“e duumike e Жҙaggere e woЙ—Й—itagol"
  67,22,Kere ko on yahoowo no hippi yeeso mun Й“uri feewude? Kaa ko on yahoowo no fotondiri e laawol focciingol
  67,23,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni ko fuЙ—Й—i on, O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e\". Kono fanЙ—ii ko yettoton [neema]"
  67,24,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni saakituЙ—o on leydi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ko mooЙ“itoyteЙ—on"
  67,25,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  67,26,"Maaku : \"Anndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Min on ko Mi jertinoowo [tun] Й“anngina"
  67,27,"Nde Й“e yi'oyta (lette) Й—en ka Й“adii, geece yedduЙ“e Й“en suni geece heeferЙ“e, [Й“e] wi'anee : \"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ko Й—aЙ“Й“aynoЙ—on"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah Жҙettitii lam min e wonndiiЙ“e am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo daЙ—ndata heeferЙ“e Й“en lette muusuЙ—e"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraЕӢke On. Men gomЙ—inii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere Й“anngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon Й—am wattinii Й“eeЙ“uЙ—am, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilayЙ—am"
  68,1,Nuun. Mi woondirii karambol e ko Й“e winndirta kon
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joomi maa on, haangaaЙ—o"
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa njoЙ“di ndi taЖҙondirtaa"
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hiЙ—a e jikku mawngu"
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa, Й“e yi'a kamЙ“e kadi"
  68,6,ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaaЙ—o on
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa Й“uri anndude majjuЙ—o on laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri anndude feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  68,8,Wata a tewto fennooЙ“e Й“en
  68,9,"HiЙ“e yiЙ—i si a newantono (Й“e), Й“e newano-(maa)"
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o woondugol, hoyЙ—o"
  68,11,"Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o nyo*ugol, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o yaarugol baddi"
  68,12,"Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o haЙ—ugol moЖҙЖҙere, jaggitoowo, bakkondinЙ—o"
  68,13,"yoora-Й“erndeejo e hoore Й—um, heЙ“iraaЙ—o nii"
  68,14,fii o wonii jom jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й—en janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  68,16,Aray nde Men maandina mo e hoore kinal
  68,17,"Men jarribor Й“e wano Men jarribornoo jeyЙ“e ngesa mba : fewndo Й“en woondunoo pellet, Й“e soГұay mba subaka ko Й“e dawuЙ“e"
  68,18,"Й“e ittintinaali [wiide] :\"Si Allah jaЙ“ii"
  68,19,Yiite immori ka Joomi maa ari huuЙ“iti mba tawi hiЙ“e Й—aanii
  68,20,mba wa'iti wa jemma Й“aleejo
  68,21,ЖҒe noddindiri bimmbi on
  68,22,"Kori dawee ka ngesa mon, si tawii ko on soГұooЙ“e"
  68,23,ЖҒe hucciti hiЙ“e Й“Й—uumbo
  68,24,"Wonnde \"Miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"
  68,25,"ЖҒe ndawidi e Й—awugol [waasuЙ“e Й“en] ko Й“e eЙ“Й“uЙ“e"
  68,26,"Nde Й“e yi'unoo mba, Й“e wi'i: \"Pellet, men majjii [laawol ngol]"
  68,27,wurin ko men Й—awaaЙ“e
  68,28,"ЖҒurЙ—o Й“e moЖҙЖҙude on wi'i: \"Mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko subbunhinoЙ—on"
  68,29,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Senaade woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko men tooГұuЙ“e"
  68,30,"WoЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e fewtiti Й“eya, hiЙ“e felindira"
  68,31,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men bewuЙ“e"
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men Й“uri mban Й—on moЖҙЖҙude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reerЙ—ube e [yaafeede]"
  68,33,"Ko non tigi woni lette Й—en; ko lette laakara Й—en non Й“uri manude, sinno hiЙ“e anndunoo"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Aljannaaji neema"
  68,35,Kere Men waЙ—ay jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en wano bomЙ“e Й“en
  68,36,"Ko heЙ“i on, si Й—on Гұaawira non"
  68,37,"Kaa hiЙ—on mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko suЙ“otoЙ—on"
  68,39,"Kaa ko fodooje woodani on e Amen, hoolniiЙ—e haa Г‘alnde Darngal, wonnde pellet, hino woodani on ko Гұaawoton kon"
  68,40,Lamndii Й“e ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e fawtaniiЙ“e Й—um
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidiiЙ“e woodani Й“e? Awa yo Й“e addu kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, si tawii ko Й“e goonguЙ“e"
  68,42,"Г‘alnde belenru Гұoroytee, Й“e noddee e sujjugol kono hara Й“e waawataa. @Corrected"
  68,43,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en no heli, koyeera no suddi Й“e. Ko tawde Й“e noddeteno e sujjugol fewndo ka Й“e waawunoo"
  68,44,Accidam e kala fennuЙ—o ndee yewtere; aray nde Men suynira Й“e nokku ka Й“e anndaa
  68,45,"MiЙ—o nennan Й“e. Pellet non, pewje Am Й—en ko tiiЙ—uЙ—e"
  68,46,"Kaa a lamndi Й“e njoЙ“di, hara ko yoЙ“ugol ndi teddani Й“e"
  68,47,"Kaa Й“e anndu fii wirniiЙ—i Й—in, hara hiЙ“e winndira [Й—im hujjaaji maЙ“Й“e]"
  68,48,"MuГұГұor Гұaawoore Joomi maa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndiiЙ—o linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joomi makko] himo sunii"
  68,49,"Si tawno moЖҙЖҙere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o felniiЙ—o"
  68,50,"Joomi makko suЙ“ii mo, O waЙ—i mo e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  68,51,"Hay yedduЙ“e Й“en eЙ“Й“iinoo yuwirgol ma gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en, nde Й“e nanunoo Janntoore nden, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"On ko haangaaЙ—o"
  68,52,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"
  69,1,Darngal
  69,2,Ko honЙ—um woni Darngal
  69,3,Ko honЙ—um anndin maa ko woni Darngal
  69,4,Samuudu e Aadi en fennii duЙ—Й—ugol Darngal
  69,5,"Si ko Samuuda en, Й“e halkira haacaango"
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, Й“e halkira henndu bippooru hattinndu tiiЙ—ude"
  69,7,"O elti ndu e hoore maЙ“Й“e jemmaaji jeeЙ—iЙ—i e Гұalormaaje jeetati jokkondirЙ—e; yi'aa yimЙ“e Й“en no pukkii e Й—in [koЙ—ooli] wa si tawii ko Й“e daЖҙЖҙe tamaro irtiiЙ—e"
  69,8,Taw si a yi'anay Й“e ko heddii
  69,9,Fir'awna e adinooЙ“e mo e ca'e junnitanooЙ—e Й—en ardi e goopi
  69,10,"Й“e yeddi NulaaЙ—o Joomi maЙ“Й“e on, O nanngiri Й“e nanngal sattungal"
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam Й—am hummbunoo, Min roondi on ka dogayka"
  69,12,"fii no Men waЙ—irana Й—um waaju, nowru nanayndu nana Й—um"
  69,13,Si wuttaama ka allaandu wuttaande wootere
  69,14,leydi ndin e pelle Й—en Й“amtee moГұГұe mo Й“ГұГұannde wootere
  69,15,"Nden Гұalnde, Darngal ngal daroto"
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekoo, hara ko ngu lo'ungu nden Гұalnde"
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en wontira ka seraaji maggu, njeetato [e maЙ“Й“e] ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin e hoore maЙ“Й“e nden Гұalnde"
  69,18,Nden Гұalnde ko on weeЙ“itetee; hay huunde e fii mon suuЙ—otaako
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaaЙ—o talkuru mun ndun ka Гұaamo mun, o wi'oyay : \"JaЙ“ee ! Janngon talkuru am ndun"
  69,20,Min mi fellituno mi hawroygol e hasboore am moЖҙЖҙere nden
  69,21,Hara himo e nguurndam welЙ—am
  69,22,E nder Aljanna toowuЙ—o
  69,23,mo dimЙ—e mun Й“adii
  69,24,"Г‘aamee yariron no newori, sabu ko ardin-Й—on kon e ГұalaaЙ—e feЖҙЖҙuЙ—e"
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonntiiroyaaЙ—o talkuru mun ndun ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : \"Haaaniino lam hara mi jonnitaaka talkuru am ndun"
  69,26,Hara mi anndaali ko woni Гұaawoore am
  69,27,"Hara [maayde] nden wononu timmoode [am]"
  69,28,Jawdi am ndin duncanaali lam
  69,29,Mbaawko am kon halkirii lam
  69,30,Nanngee mo kolmbon bmo
  69,31,refti naadon mo ka Jahiimi
  69,32,refti naadon mo e jolokooje-callale- Й—e juuteendi mun woni cogone cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i
  69,33,Tawde o gomЙ—inaano Allah MawЙ—o On
  69,34,O reerЙ—intaa e Гұammiingol miskiino
  69,35,GiЙ—o Й“adondiraaЙ—o alanaamo Й—oo hannde
  69,36,"wanaa Гұaametee, si wanaa e ЖҙiЖҙЖҙiЖҙiri"
  69,37,"Г‘aamataa ndin, si wanaa bakkondimЙ“e Й“en"
  69,38,Mi woondirii ko yi'oton kon
  69,39,E ko on yi'ataa kon
  69,40,"wonnde pellet, [Alqur'aana] ko konngol NulaaЙ—o tedduЙ—o"
  69,41,wanaa nde konnguЙ—i yimoowo; kono fanЙ—ii ko gomЙ—inton
  69,42,"wanaa kadi nde konnguЙ—i mbileejo, kono famЙ—ii ko waajitotoЙ—on"
  69,43,ko jippiniraande ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden
  69,44,Si tawno o fefindino e Amen yoga e konnguЙ—i
  69,45,"ko pellet, Men nanngirayno mo doole"
  69,46,Hooti Men taЖҙayno e makko Й—aЙ—ol Й“ernde ngol
  69,47,Alaa e mo'on hay gooto haЙ—oowo Men e makko
  69,48,"Pellet, ndee [Alqur'aanaare] konde waajitorgol gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  69,49,"Haray kadi, MeЙ—en anndi ina e mon fennooЙ“e [nde]"
  69,50,"ko pellet non, Й—um ko nimse e hoore yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  69,51,"pellet kadi, ko nde goonga yananaaЙ—o"
  69,52,"Haray subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, MawЙ—o On"
  70,1,TorotooЙ—o torike lette yanayЙ—e
  70,2,"wonannde heeferЙ“e Й“en, alaa duГұanoowo Й“e Й—e"
  70,3,"ko immorde ka Allah, Jom ЖҙawruЙ—e"
  70,4,"Malaa'ka'en wonndude e Jibriilu hino Жҙawa faade e Makko, e nder Гұalaande nde eЙ“Й“oore mun woni duuЙ“i ujune cappanЙ—e jowi"
  70,5,"MuГұГұo tun, muГұal labaangal"
  70,6,KamЙ“e hiЙ“e yi*a (lette) Й—en ko woЙ—Й—uЙ—e
  70,7,MeЙ—en reeni Й—e Menen ko Й“adiiЙ—e
  70,8,Г‘alnde kammu ngun wa'oyta wa ko taayinaa
  70,9,pelle Й—en wa'oya wa hottolle kardaako
  70,10,ka Й“adondiraaЙ—o lamdotaako fii jeydaaЙ—o mun
  70,11,"HiЙ“e hollindiree. BonЙ—o on yeloto sottorgol lette Й—en nden Гұalnde, Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“en"
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e neene gooto makko on"
  70,13,e gorol makko ngol moolayngol mo
  70,14,"e kala wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en, fii no Й—um daЙ—ndira mo"
  70,15,"ЖҠum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge"
  70,16,Й“oltaynge guri hoore
  70,17,Hinge nodda on Й—uurniiЙ—o o hucciti
  70,18,o mooЙ“i (jawle) o mari e marirgel
  70,19,"Pellet, neЙ—Й—o tagaama ko o Й—enЖҙotooЙ—o"
  70,20,"si bone memii mo, o faaya"
  70,21,"si ko mo moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“i mo, o salora"
  70,22,Si wanaa juulooЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected
  70,23,Й“en tawЙ“e ko Й“e duumiiЙ“e e juulde maЙ“Й“e nden
  70,24,E Й“en tawЙ“e hino ka jawle maЙ“Й“e haqqee anndaaЙ—o
  70,25,wonannde torotooЙ—o e haЙ—itiiЙ—i
  70,26,e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Гұalaande njoЙ“di diina
  70,27,E Й“en tawЙ“e ko Й“e huluЙ“e lette Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en
  70,28,"tawde pellet, lette Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en wanaa hoolniiЙ—e"
  70,29,E Й“en tawЙ“e ko reenuЙ“e farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in
  70,30,"si wanaa e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maa Й“en horЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e, Й—on on Й“e feletaake"
  70,31,"Kala non Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o [ka dakmitora] caggal Й—um, haray ko Й“en woni jaggituЙ“e Й“en"
  70,32,E Й“en tawЙ“e ko aynituЙ“e koolaaje e aadiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in
  70,33,E Й“en tawЙ“e ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e seedeeji mun
  70,34,e Й“en tawЙ“e ko reenooЙ“e e juulde maЙ“Й“e nden
  70,35,ЖҒen Й—on ko teddinoyteeЙ“e e Aljannaaji
  70,36,"E ko heЙ“i yedduЙ“e Й“en takko maaЙ—a, hiЙ“e heГұora"
  70,37,"ka nano e ka Гұaamo, ko Й“e dentoy-dentoy"
  70,38,Hara gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e tamЖҙinoto naatoygol Aljanna neemaaji
  70,39,ЖҠun waЙ—ataa ! Men tagiriЙ“e ko Й“e anndi
  70,40,"Mi woondirii JeyЙ—o fuЙ—irЙ—e e mutirЙ—e On, pellet, ko Men hattanЙ“e"
  70,41,"wattitirgol Й“e ko Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude, Men siforaa ronkugol [Й—um]"
  70,42,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e fija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e kammbirananoo"
  70,43,"Гұalnde Й“e yaltiroyta e genaale Й—en heГұaare, wa si tawii ko kaaЖҙe (sanamu) Й“e woni wugganaade"
  70,44,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e no heli, koyeera no suddi Й“e. Ko nden Гұalaande woni ko Й“e kammbirananoo"
  71,1,"Men nulii Nuuhu haa e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, wonnde : \"Jertin yimЙ“e maa Й“en, ado lette muusuЙ—e arde e maЙ“Й“e"
  71,2,"O maakani [Й“e] : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi jertinoowo on Й“annguЙ—o"
  71,3,"wonnde yo on rewu Allah, hulon Mo, Й—oftoЙ—on lam"
  71,4,"O haforanay on junuubi mon Й—in, O nenna on haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. [Ko woni tun] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si tawii hiЙ—on anndunoo"
  71,5,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi noddirii yimЙ“e am Й“en jemma e Гұalorma"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am ndun Й“eydaali Й“e, si wanaa dogugol"
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi Й“e fii no Hafaranaa Й“e, Й“e waЙ—ay kolli maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka nder noppi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e buumora comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e deppitoo, Й“e townitora townitaadee"
  71,8,Refti mi noddirii Й“e e kene
  71,9,"Refti mi feГұГұinani Й“e, mi gunndii Й“e gunndaadee"
  71,10,"Mi wi'i [Й“e] : \"Insinanee Joomi mon, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoow"
  71,11,O wurtira toЙ“o ngon e mo'on rewnindiral
  71,12,"O Й“eydira on jawle e Й“iЙ—Й“e, O waЙ—ana on gese, O waЙ—ana on canЙ—i"
  71,13,"E ko heЙ“i on, on jortaaki manngural Allah ngal"
  71,14,Hara le O tagir on taaЙ“e-taaЙ“e
  71,15,E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuulli jeeЙ—iЙ—i tegondirЙ—i
  71,16,"O waЙ—i lewru ndun jalЙ“undu e majji, O waЙ—i naange ngen pitilol"
  71,17,Ko Allah fuЙ—niri on ka leydi fuЙ—nugol
  71,18,"refti O ruttiray on e mayri, O yaltina on yaltinndee"
  71,19,Allah waЙ—iranii on leydi ndin weertaandi
  71,20,fii yo on naatir e mayri laawi yaajuЙ—i
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : \"Joomi am, Й“ee yeddii lam, Й“e jokkii on mo jawle mun e Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“eydaali Й—um si wanaa hayrugol"
  71,22,ЖҒe fewji feere mawnde
  71,23,"Й“e wi'i: \"Wata on terto dey reweteeЙ—i mon Й—in: wata on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"
  71,24,"Ko pellet, Й“e majjinii ko Й—uuЙ—i. [Joomi] wata A Й“eydir tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa majjere"
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e yooliranoo, Й“e naadaa Yiite, Й“e heЙ“anaano ko'e maЙ“Й“e faabotooЙ—o gaanin Allah"
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : \"Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo"
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A accii Й“e, Й“e majjinay jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en, Й“e jiidoytaako si wanaa bonnooЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e geddi"
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam min e jibimЙ“e lam Й“en, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e naatuЙ“e ka suudu am, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en; wata A Й“eydir tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa halakuyee"
  72,1,"Maaku : \"Wahayinaama e am, wonnde dental jinna heЙ—ino [lam miЙ—o jannga Alqur'aana], Й—i wi'i: \"Menen men nani janngeteende haawniinde"
  72,2,"Hinde Й—owira e peewal. Men gomЙ—inii nde. Men kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto"
  72,3,"E wonnde manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, O siforaali jogitagol genndo, wanaa Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  72,4,"E wonnde [Ibuliisa] Й—ayЙ—o on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah"
  72,5,Menen men sikkuno wonnde yimЙ“e e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah
  72,6,"Hari le worЙ“e yimЙ“e hino mooloraynoo worЙ“e jinna, Й“e Й“eydi Й—i bewre"
  72,7,"KamЙ“e [yimЙ“e Й“en] Й“e sikkir no sikkirЙ—on non, wonnde Allah immintintah hay gooto"
  72,8,"E wonnde men meemii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynooЙ“e tiiЙ—uЙ“e e docote"
  72,9,"E wonnde meЙ—en jooЙ—otonoo ton fii heЙ—agol. Kala non heЙ—itiiЙ—o jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal"
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa si ko bone faandanaa wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en, kaa hara Joomi maЙ“Й“e faandani Й“e peewal"
  72,11,"E wonnde hino e amen moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi Й—um. Hari meЙ—en e laawi seertuЙ—i"
  72,12,"E wonnde men fellituno men laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e wonnde men laawortaa Mo dogugol"
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo peewal nagl, men gomЙ—ini ngal. Kala gomЙ—inЙ—o Joomi mun, on hulataa Й—uytaneede [moЖҙЖҙi] wanaa Й“eydaneede [bonЙ—i]"
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen jebbiliiЙ—i, hino e amen kadi ooГұiiЙ—i. Kala jebbilii ngii, Й—in Й—on faandike peewal"
  72,15,"OoГұiiЙ—i Й—in kan, Й—i laatanike Jahannama on carmalle"
  72,16,"E wonnde si Й“e ГұiiЙ“uno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Men yarnayno Й“e ndiyam Й—uuЙ—uЙ—am"
  72,17,"fii yo Men ndaarndoro Й“e heen. Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e jantoore Joomi mun nden, O naaday mo e lette sattuЙ—e"
  72,18,E wonnde juulirЙ—e Й—en ko Allah heeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma jeyaaЙ—o Allah on darinoo himo rewa Mo, Й—i Й—eЙ“uno waЙ—Й—ondirgol e hoore makko"
  72,20,"Maaku : \"Anndee ko Joomi am (tun) mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo kadi hay e gooto"
  72,21,"Maaku : \"Min on mi waawanaa on duГұude lorra, wanaa fii pooЙ—ugol nafa"
  72,22,"Maaku : \"Hay gooto waawaa daЙ—ndugol lam e Allah; mi heЙ“ataa ko woori Mo ЖҙooГұorde"
  72,23,"si wanaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule Makko Й—en. Kala yedduЙ—o Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, Й“e luttay e magge poomaa"
  72,24,"Haa si Й“e yi'ii ko Й“e kammbirananoo kon, Й“e aray anndude ko hombo Й“uri lo'ude ballo, Й“uri kadi fanЙ—ude limoore"
  72,25,"Maaku : \"Mi anndaa si ko kammbiranaЙ—on kon hino Й“adii, maa si Joomi am waЙ—anay Й—um dumunna"
  72,26,Ko O ganndo wirniiЙ—i. O Жҙellintinantaa wirniiЙ—i Makko Й—in hay e gooto
  72,27,"si wanaa mo O welanaa e NulaaЙ—o, O naadnay yeeso on e Й“aawo makko tommbotooЙ“e"
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu wonnde Й“en yottinii nule Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en. O huЙ“indorii (anndugol) ko woni ka maЙ“Й“e kon, O mofti limoore kala huunde"
  73,1,"Ko an yo buumorЙ—o [comci mun]"
  73,2,"ЖҒaЕӢo (wuurnitaa) jemma on, si wanaa seeЙ—a [e makko]"
  73,3,"feccere makko, maa Й—uytaa seeЙ—a e Й—um"
  73,4,maa Й“eydaa Й—on. Janngiraa Alqur'aanaare nden rewnindiral
  73,5,MeЙ—en saatii tellinnde e maaЙ—a konngol teddungol
  73,6,"Pellet, ko dewal tummbo jemma ngal, Й“uri tiiЙ—ude batte e fooccaade konngol"
  73,7,"Anndu hino woodan-maa e Гұalorma on, ferlitagol juutungol"
  73,8,"Janto innde Joomi maa nden, taЖҙo-Й—aa yahaa e Makko hattirde taЖҙagol"
  73,9,"JeyЙ—o On fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange.ReweteeЙ—o woo alaa e si nwona Kanko,Jogito Mo hoolorteeЙ—o"
  73,10,MuГұГұo e ko Й“e wowlata kon; woЙ—Й—ito-raa Й“e woЙ—Й—itannde labaande
  73,11,Accidam e fennooЙ“e joomiraaЙ“e neemaaji Й“en; habbito-Й—aa Й“e seeЙ—a
  73,12,"Ko pellet, hino ka Amen gaa : Tonngii e Jahiimi"
  73,13,"e Гұaametee Й—eЙ—Й—oowo, e lette muusuЙ—e"
  73,14,"Г‘alnde leydi ndin e pelle Й—en dillata, pelle Й—en wa'a wa njaare ilayndi"
  73,15,Min nelii e mon nelaaЙ—o haa o wona seede e dow mon hono no Min nelduno faade e Fir*awna NelaaЙ—o
  73,16,Fir*awna woopi nelaaЙ—o O Min nanngi mbo nanngugol cattungol
  73,17,Hono ndeenraton pittaali mon si on yeddi Гұalawmo baЙ—oowo sukaaЙ“e danndalinde
  73,18,Kammu o na fetti e kulhuli hembo laatiima fodoore Alla ko wonoore
  73,19,Ko oon woni waaju goongo kala faalaaЙ—o daЙ—de nanngira joomiiko ruttorde
  73,20,"Pellet joom Ma na anndi haЙ—a juula ko Й“uri famЙ—ude e tataЙ“al jemma wollo feccere mammbo wondude e fedde e Й“een wonduЙ“e e Ma Alla hoddira jemma e Гұalawma O anndi on tonngataa mbo O yaafii mon, njannge ko newanii on e Quraana hombo anndi ma won e mon ГұawЙ“e goo ngona e Й—atngal ka leydi hoЙ“e ndaarta Й“ural Alla woЙ“Й“e kadi na kaЙ“ano laawol Alla njannge ko newanii mon e hembo ndarnon juulde tottiron askal Гұamlon Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere kala ko mbaЙ—aЙ—on ko*e mon e jam tawon mbo ka Alla hombo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mawnude njobdi njaafnee Alla sabu Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o ko jurmotooЙ—o"
  74,1,Ko an yo mojiiЙ—o
