  74,28,Nge heddatah nge accatah
  74,29,Sumoowe geece
  74,30,Ina e dow mannge sappa e jeenay
  74,31,"Men waЙ—aali aynooЙ“e yimЙ“e Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ika. Men waЙ—iraali limoore maЙ“Й“e si wanaa jarraborgol yedduЙ“e Й“en, e fii yo henan okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en, e fii no gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Й“eydora gomЙ—inal, e fii wata okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en sikkito; e fii yo Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mun e heeferЙ“e Й“en wi'u: \"Hara ko honЙ—um Allah faandorii e ngal misal?\" Ko wano non Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani. Hay gooto anndaa yeru koneeli Joomi maa Й—in, si wanaa Kanko. Ngen [Yiite] wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde neЙ—Й—anke"
  74,32,Kono yo henane! Mi woondirii lewru ndun
  74,33,O woondiri jemma si mbo runtii ma
  74,34,E subaka si mbo fooyni
  74,35,Ko mbo gootel e mawЙ—i
  74,36,Ko nge jertinirde wonannde neЙ—Й—anke
  74,37,"Wonannde on yiЙ—uЙ—o e mo'on, nde o yaccotoo maa nennoo"
  74,38,Wonkii kala ko faggii kon nanngirte
  74,39,Si wanaa yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“en
  74,40,"hiЙ“e e nder gese, hiЙ“e lamndondira"
  74,41,fii bomЙ“e Й“en
  74,42,ko hoЙ—um naadi on Saqara
  74,43,"ЖҒen wi'a: \"Men jeyanooka e juulooЙ“e Й“en"
  74,44,men jeyanooka kadi e ГұamminooЙ“e miskimЙ“e Й“en
  74,45,Hari men jumpidayno kadi e jumpooЙ“e Й“en
  74,46,Hari kadi men fennayno fii Гұalaande njoЙ“di nden
  74,47,"Haa [maayde] yananaande nden arani men"
  74,48,NafataaЙ“e tefoore tefooЙ“e
  74,49,Hol ko waЙ—i Й“e sirkuЙ“e na Й—uurno Quraana
  74,50,HoЙ“e mba*i e bamЙ—i laawatooЙ—i na ndoga
  74,51,DokЙ—i mbaroodi
