  74,53,Alah woni koЙ“e kulaani laakara
  74,54,Alah Й—uum ko ciftanirgol
  74,55,Ko kala faalaaЙ—o waactaroo mbo o waaccaroo mbo
  74,56,"Й“e mbaactaaka si wonah Alla na haaja, ko Kanko woni kaanduЙ—o e huleede ko Kanko woni kaanduЙ—o e yaafaade"
  75,1,MbeЙ—a woondira Гұande ndarnga
  75,2,MbeЙ—a woondira fittaandu felooru
