  75,40,Mbela Oon hattanaani wuurtinde maayЙ“e
  76,1,Mbela arii e aade tumo e yonta nde o wonaana hay huunde jantateende
  76,2,Min tagii aade e toЙ“Й“ere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo Min kumpitoo mbo Min laatini mbo nanoowo ji*oowo
  76,3,Min peewnii mbo e laawol o yetta wollo o yedda
